section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/afflicted.lua"

t("Afflicted", "痛苦系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Some walk in shadow, alone, unloved, unwanted. What powers they wield may be mighty, but their names are forever cursed.", "他們是一羣漫步於陰影中、孤獨的、討人厭的、被遺棄的人。他們的力量或許很強大，但他們的名字永遠被詛咒着。", "_t")
t("Afflicted classes have been twisted by their association with evil forces.", "痛苦系因爲他們使用了邪惡的力量而變得扭曲。", "_t")
t("They can use these forces to their advantage, but at a cost...", "他們能將這股力量轉化爲優勢，但會爲此付出一定的代價……", "_t")
t("Cursed", "被詛咒者", "birth descriptor name")
t("Affliction can run to the soul, and hatred can fill one's entire being. Overcome someone else's hated curse to know its dreaded meaning.", "詛咒可以深入靈魂，使某人充滿憎恨。戰勝另外一個人的憎恨詛咒來領會這種可怕的力量。", "_t")
t("Through ignorance, greed or folly the Cursed served some dark design and are now doomed to pay for their sins.", "被詛咒者曾經因爲無知、貪婪或者愚昧，服從於黑暗的指示。現在，他們因罪惡而身受災難折磨。", "_t")
t("Their only master now is the hatred they carry for every living thing.", "他們現在唯一的主人，是對那些生者心中的憎恨。", "_t")
t("Drawing strength from the death of all they encounter, the Cursed become terrifying combatants.", "他們從他們遇到的死亡中吸取力量，成爲恐怖的戰士。", "_t")
t("Worse, any who approach the Cursed can be driven mad by their terrible aura.", "更可怕的是，任何接近被詛咒者的人，會受可怕光環的影響而發狂。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量和意志。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +4 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +4 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "_t")
t("Doomed", "末日使者", "birth descriptor name")
t("In shaded places in unknown lands thou must overcome thyself and see thy doom.", "在遙遠大陸的一個一男的地方，你必須戰勝你自己並看到你自己的末日。", "_t")
t("The Doomed are fallen mages who once wielded powerful magic wrought by ambition and dark bargains.", "末日使者是一些墮落的法師，他們曾經由於野心，通過黑暗的契約，獲得了強大的魔法。", "_t")
t("Stripped of their magic by the dark forces that once served them, they have learned to harness the hatred that burns in their minds.", "被黑暗剝奪了魔法力量的他們，開始學習如何驅使他們心頭燃燒的憎恨的力量。", "_t")
t("Only time will tell if they can choose a new path or are doomed forever.", "只有時間會證明他們是選擇了一條新的道路還是一條永遠的末日懲罰之路。", "_t")
t("The Doomed strike from behind a veil of darkness or a host of shadows.", "末日使者操縱陰影，從黑暗中發動攻擊。", "_t")
t("They feed upon their enemies as they unleash their minds on all who confront them.", "他們可以汲取敵人的靈魂，並對所有面對它的人的精神施加懲罰", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Willpower and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：意志和靈巧。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +4 Willpower, +5 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +4 意志 , +5 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")


