section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/celestial.lua"

t("Celestial", "天空系", "birth descriptor name")
t("The magic of the heavens is known to but a few, and that knowledge has long passed east, forgotten.", "天空魔法很少被人瞭解，這些知識在失落的遠東大陸。", "_t")
t("Celestial classes are arcane users focused on the heavenly bodies.", "天空系職業是使用天體能量的奧術使用者。", "_t")
t("Most draw their powers from the Sun and the Moons.", "大部分都是從太陽和月亮汲取能量。", "_t")
t("Sun Paladin", "太陽騎士", "birth descriptor name")
t("The sun rises in the east in full glory, but you must look for it first amidst the darkest places.", "東方升起的太陽充滿榮耀，但你首先得從黑暗之地尋找到它。", "_t")
t("Sun Paladins hail from the Gates of Morning, the last bastion of the free people in the Far East.", "太陽騎士出生於晨曦之門，那是遙遠東方自由生活的人們的最後堡壘。", "_t")
t("Their way of life is well represented by their motto 'The Sun is our giver, our purity, our essence. We carry the light into dark places, and against our strength none shall pass.'", "他們的事業受人尊敬，他們的座右銘是：太陽賜予我們力量、聖潔和精華。我們爲黑暗帶去光明，任何反抗我們的力量都休想通過。", "_t")
t("They can channel the power of the Sun to smite all who seek to destroy the Sunwall.", "他們能施展太陽之力將任何試圖破壞太陽堡壘的力量擊退。", "_t")
t("Competent in both weapon and shield combat and magic, they usually burn their foes from afar before bashing them in melee.", "他們同時精通武器和盾戰術並熟悉魔法，在近身猛擊對手之前他們通常在遠處就可以灼燒敵人。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Magic", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量和魔法。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Magic, +0 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 魔法 , +0 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "_t")
t("Anorithil", "星月術士", "birth descriptor name")
t("The balance of the heavens' powers is a daunting task. Mighty are those that stand in the twilight places, wielding both light and darkness in their mind.", "平衡天空的力量是一件令人望而生畏的任務。他們站在黎明深處同時掌控着黑暗與光明的力量。", "_t")
t("Anorithils hail from the Gates of Morning, the last bastion of the free people in the Far East.", "星月術士出生於晨曦之門，那是遙遠東方自由生活的人們的最後堡壘。", "_t")
t("Their way of life is well represented by their motto 'We stand betwixt the Sun and Moon, where light and darkness meet. In the grey twilight we seek our destiny.'", "他們的事業受人尊敬，他們的座右銘是：我們站在太陽與月亮之間，光暗交替之界。在灰色的黎明中尋找我們的使命。", "_t")
t("They can channel the power of the Sun and the Moons to burn and tear apart all who seek to destroy the Sunwall.", "他們可以施展太陽、月亮的法術將任何試圖破壞太陽堡壘的人消滅。", "_t")
t("Masters of Sun and Moon magic, they usually burn their foes with Sun rays before calling the fury of the stars.", "他們掌握日月魔法，可以使用灼熱的太陽射線和羣星的憤怒毀滅對手。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：魔法和靈巧。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +6 Magic, +0 Willpower, +3 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +6 魔法 , +0 意志 , +3 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")


