section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/chronomancer.lua"

t("Chronomancer", "時空系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Some do not walk upon the straight road others follow. Seek the hidden paths outside the normal course of life.", "他們是一些另闢蹊徑的人，在平凡的道路上尋找出一條隱藏的路。", "_t")
t("Exploiting a hole in the fabric of spacetime, Chronomancers learn to pull threads from other timelines into their own.", "通過在時空的連續性上打開孔洞，時空法師可以在時間線中來回穿梭。", "_t")
t("Pulling these threads creates tension and the harder they pull the more tension is produced.", "這些穿梭時空的行爲會在時空中留下張力，他們改變現實的程度越大，造成的張力就越大。", "_t")
t("Constantly they manage this tension, which they call Paradox, to avoid or control the anomalies they inevitably unleash on the world around them.", "他們需要小心控制這些被他們成爲紊亂值的時空張力。否則，這樣的張力會不可避免在他們周圍的世界產生各種異常現象。", "_t")
t("Paradox Mage", "時空法師", "birth descriptor name")
t("A hand may clap alone if it returns to clap itself. Search for the power in the paradox.", "如果一隻手能拍到過去的自己，那麼就可以單手鼓掌。在時空悖論中尋求力量吧。", "_t")
t("A Paradox Mage studies the very fabric of spacetime, learning not just to bend it but shape it and remake it.", "時光法師學習時空的構造，不僅僅是扭曲時空而且還能重塑時空。", "_t")
t("Most Paradox Mages lack basic skills that others take for granted (like general fighting sense), but they make up for it through control of cosmic forces.", "大多數時光法師沒有基本的格鬥技能，但他們可以利用宇宙的力量來進行戰鬥。", "_t")
t("Paradox Mages start off with knowledge of all but the most complex Chronomantic schools.", "時光法師不掌握普通法術知識，他們學習的是更加複雜的時空法術。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：魔法和意志。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +2 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +2 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Magic, +2 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 魔法 , +2 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")
t("Temporal Warden", "時空守衛", "birth descriptor name")
t("We preserve the past to protect the future. The hands of time are guarded by the arms of war.", "我們平衡過去，守護未來，我們用戰鬥來維持時間的秩序。", "_t")
t("Their lifelines braided, Temporal Wardens have learned to work with their other selves across multiple timelines.", "通過纏結不同的時間線，時空守衛可以召喚其他世界線的分身，和自己一同戰鬥。", "_t")
t("Through their study of chronomancy, they learn to blend archery and dual-weapon fighting, seamlessly switching from one to the other.", "時空守衛通過學習時空法術，可以將箭術和雙手武器格鬥聯合在一起，在兩者之間隨意切換。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic, Dexterity, and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：魔法、敏捷和意志。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
