section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/mage.lua"

t("Mage", "法師系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Mages are the wielders of arcane powers, able to cast powerful spells of destruction or to heal their wounds with nothing but a thought.", "法師們用奧術魔法來武裝自己，只要一閃念就能夠釋放破壞性的法術或者治療自己", "_t")
t("Alchemist", "鍊金術師", "birth descriptor name")
t("An Alchemist is a manipulator of materials using magic.", "煉金術士使用魔法來操縱物質。", "_t")
t("They do not use the forbidden arcane arts practised by the mages of old - such perverters of nature have been shunned or actively hunted down since the Spellblaze.", "他們不使用那些遠古的被禁止的法術，那些法術自從魔法大爆炸之後就被人們禁止和追捕。", "_t")
t("Alchemists can transmute gems to bring forth elemental effects, turning them into balls of fire, torrents of acid, and other effects.  They can also reinforce armour with magical effects using gems, and channel arcane staffs to produce bolts of energy.", "煉金術士可以將元素力量輸入各種寶石，使它們變成火球、酸液和其他效果。另外他們也可以利用寶石來強化裝甲並使用法杖發射能量球。", "_t")
t("Though normally physically weak, most alchemists are accompanied by magical golems which they construct and use as bodyguards.  These golems are enslaved to their master's will, and can grow in power as their master advances through the arts.", "煉金術士自身非常脆弱，但是他們可以建造鍊金傀儡來保護他們。傀儡服從主人的意志，並依靠主人來強化它們的力量。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic and Constitution", "他們最重要的屬性是：魔法和體質。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +3 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +3 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Magic, +1 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 魔法 , +1 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -1", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -1", "_t")
t("Golem", "傀儡", "birth facial category")
t("Golem becomes a Drolem", "傀儡成爲龍傀儡", "_t")
t("Archmage", "元素法師", "birth descriptor name")
t("Hated, harrowed, hunted, hidden... Our ways are forbidden, but our cause is just. In our veiled valley we find solace from the world's wrath, free to study our arts. Only through charity and friendship can you earn our trust.", "憎恨、折磨、追捕、隱藏……我們的道路被禁止，但是我們的事業是正義的。在我們隱藏的山谷裏我們自由學習我們自己的魔法藝術，從這個世界的憤怒中尋求安慰。只有友誼和寬容才能獲得我們的信任。", "_t")
t("An Archmage devotes his whole life to the study of magic above anything else.", "對一個元素法師來說魔法超越一切，他們傾盡一生學習魔法。", "_t")
t("Most Archmagi lack basic skills that others take for granted (like general fighting sense), but they make up for it by their raw magical power.", "元素法師缺乏最基本的物理格鬥技能，他們用魔法取而代之。", "_t")
t("Archmagi start with knowledge of many schools of magic. However, they usually refuse to have anything to do with Necromancy.", "元素法師學習各種學科的魔法知識。然而，他們通常拒絕任何死靈法術。", "_t")
t("Most Archmagi have been trained in the secret town of Angolwen and possess a unique spell to teleport to it directly.", "元素法師在一個名叫安格利文的祕密小鎮接受訓練，並擁有一個直接傳送到那裏的獨特技能。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -4", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -4", "_t")
t("Necromancer", "死靈法師", "birth descriptor name")
t("The road to necromancy is a macabre path indeed. Walk with the dead, and drink deeply of their black knowledge.", "通往死靈法師的道路是極其可怕的，與死亡相伴隨並沉溺在他們的黑暗知識之中。", "_t")
t("While most magic is viewed with suspicion since the Spellblaze, the stigma surrounding the black art of Necromancy has been around since time immemorial.", "儘管自從魔法大爆炸以來，大部分魔法受到質疑，但自遠古以來，死靈法師的黑暗魔法始終揹負着罵名。", "_t")
t("These dark spellcasters extinguish life, twist death, and raise armies of undead monsters to sate their lust for power and pursue their ultimate goal: Eternal life.", "這些黑暗的施法者泯滅生命、扭曲死亡、召喚不死亡靈作爲他們的軍隊來滿足他們對力量的渴求，達到他們的最終目標：永垂不朽。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：魔法和意志。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Magic, +3 Willpower, +1 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 魔法 , +3 意志 , +1 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -3", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -3", "_t")


