section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/psionic.lua"

t("Psionic", "靈能系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Weakness of flesh can be overcome by mental prowess. Find the way and fight for the way to open the key to your mind.", "肉體的軟弱可以被精神的強大所克服。尋找一條能夠進入你精神世界的路。", "_t")
t("Psionics find their power within themselves. Their highly trained minds can harness energy from many different sources and manipulate it to produce physical effects.", "靈能力者發掘自身的潛在力量。他們經過高度開發的精神力能夠利用許多不同的能量源吸收能量，並對現實世界產生影響。", "_t")
t("Mindslayer", "心靈殺手", "birth descriptor name")
t("A thought can inspire; a thought can kill. After centuries of oppression, years of imprisonment, a thought shall break us free and vengeance will strike from our darkest dreams.", "思想可以鼓舞人，思想也能殺人，在幾個世紀的壓抑、數年的監禁之後，我們心中的復仇思想會從我們最黑暗的夢境中爆發。", "_t")
t("Mindslayers specialize in direct and brutal application of mental forces to their immediate surroundings.", "心靈殺手專門使用直接而殘酷的精神力量來對付周圍的敵人。", "_t")
t("When Mindslayers do battle, they will most often be found in the thick of the fighting, vast energies churning around them and telekinetically-wielded weapons hewing nearby foes at the speed of thought.", "心靈殺手在戰鬥時，他們總是在戰場中心，大量的敵人包圍他們，他們以心靈感應控制武器極快地揮砍敵人。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +1 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +1 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +4 Willpower, +4 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +4 意志 , +4 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -2", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -2", "_t")
t("Solipsist", "織夢者", "birth descriptor name")
t("Some believe that the world is the collective dream of those that live in it.  Find and wake the sleeper and you'll unlock the potential of your dreams.", "有些人認爲世界由許多個夢境組成，而我們生活在這些夢境裏。尋找並喚醒沉睡者，你可以打開通往夢境之門。", "_t")
t("The Solipsist believes that reality is malleable and nothing more than the collective vision of those that experience it.", "織夢者們相信現實具有可塑性，而沒有任何方面能比的過幻想對這個世界的重塑能力。", "_t")
t("They wield this knowledge to both create and destroy, to invade the minds of others, and to manipulate the dreams of those around them.", "他們依靠此理論進行創造和毀滅，侵入他人的思維並操縱他人的夢境。", "_t")
t("This knowledge comes with a heavy price and the Solipsist must guard his thoughts, lest he come to believe that the world exists only within his own mind.", "使用此理論需要付出巨大的代價，織夢者必須對自己的思維有很強的控制力，否則他將會失去自我，世界於他而言將成爲虛幻。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Willpower and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：意志和靈巧。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +5 Willpower, +4 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +5 意志 , +4 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -4 (*special*)", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -4 (*特殊*)", "_t")


