section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/rogue.lua"

t("Rogues are masters of tricks; they can strike from the shadows, and lure monsters into deadly traps.", "盜賊是詭計大師，他們可以從陰影中發動攻擊，也可以引誘怪物到他們的死亡陷阱裏。", "_t")
t("Rogue", "盜賊系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Rogues are masters of tricks. A Rogue can get behind you unnoticed and stab you in the back for tremendous damage.", "盜賊是詭計專家。盜賊可以潛行到你背後而不被發現，然後通過背後刺殺中造成巨大傷害。", "_t")
t("Rogues usually prefer to dual-wield daggers. They can also become trapping experts, detecting and disarming traps as well as setting them.", "盜賊通常雙持匕首，他們同樣可以成爲陷阱專家，除了安裝陷阱以外他們可以偵測並拆除陷阱。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +1 Strength, +3 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +1 力量 , +3 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +0 Willpower, +5 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +5 靈巧", "_t")
t("Shadowblade", "影舞者", "birth descriptor name")
t("Shadowblades are Rogues that are touched by the gift of magic, able to kill with their daggers under a veil of stealth while casting spells to enhance their performance and survival.", "影舞者是擁有魔法天賦的特殊盜賊，他們可以在陰影之中發動偷襲同時可以施展魔法來強化他們的攻擊和生存能力。", "_t")
t("Their use of magic is innate and not really studied; as such they do not naturally regenerate mana and must use external means of recharging.", "他們的魔法並非習得而是與生俱來的，因此他們不能依靠自然的法力恢復而必須依靠額外的方法來恢復法力值。", "_t")
t("They use the schools of Phantasm, Temporal, Divination and Conveyance magic to enhance their arts.", "他們使用幻覺、時間、預知和傳送技能來增強他們的能力。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Dexterity, Cunning and Magic", "他們最重要的屬性是：敏捷、靈巧和魔法。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +3 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +3 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 Magic, +0 Willpower, +3 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 魔法 , +0 意志 , +3 靈巧", "_t")
t("Marauder", "掠奪者", "birth descriptor name")
t("I will not hide and I will not sneak - come dance with my blades and we'll see who's weak. Snapping bone and cracking skull, it's the sounds of battle that make life full!", "我不會隱藏也不潛行，與我的雙刀起舞看看誰纔是最終的強者，撕碎骨頭敲碎頭顱，戰鬥的聲響讓生活豐富多彩！", "_t")
t("The wilds of Maj'Eyal are not a safe place. Untamed beasts and wandering dragons may seem a great threat, but the true perils walk on two legs. Thieves and brigands, assassins and opportunistic adventurers, even mad wizards and magic-hating zealots all carry danger to those who venture beyond the safety of city walls.", "埃亞爾的野外不是個安全的地方。野獸和到處遊蕩的龍似乎是巨大的威脅，然而真正危險的是兩條腿的人。竊賊、強盜、刺客投機冒險家、瘋狂的巫師甚至狂熱的獵魔者都會讓那些走出安全的城牆之外的冒險者喪命。", "_t")
t("Amidst this chaos wanders one class of rogue that has learned to take by force rather than subterfuge. With refined techniques, agile feats and brawn-backed blades the Marauder seeks out his targets and removes them by the most direct methods. He uses dual weapons backed by advanced combat training to become highly effective in battle, and he is unafraid to use the dirtiest tactics when the odds are against him.", "在這混亂之中誕生了一種特殊的盜賊，他們擅於正面交鋒而不是使用詭計。擁有精準特技、靈巧步伐和鋒利刀刃的掠奪者搜尋他的目標並直接消滅他們。他們通過高等戰鬥訓練使雙持武器更加有效，情形不利時他們不會忌諱使用骯髒的手段取得勝利。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength, Dexterity and Cunning", "他們最重要的技能是：力量、敏捷和靈巧。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Strength, +4 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 力量 , +4 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +0 Willpower, +1 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +1 靈巧", "_t")
t("Skirmisher", "散兵", "birth descriptor name")
t("Fleet of foot and strong of throw, overwhelming every foe, from afar we counter, strike and thud, in the chaos'd skirmish spilling blood.", "腳底抹油，百發百中，從遠處發動格擋反擊，在混戰中給予敵人痛擊。", "_t")
t("While able to take maximum advantage of their sling by using deft movements to avoid and confuse enemies that try to get close, the Skirmisher truly excels when fighting other ranged users.", "靈活的移動讓散兵甩開試圖接近的對手，並得以最大程度地發揮投石索的威力，這讓他們在與其他遠程職業作戰時也佔據優勢。", "_t")
t("They have mastered the use of their shield as well as their sling and are nearly impossible to defeat in a standoff.", "他們也精通盾牌的使用，這讓他們在持久戰中也幾乎處於不敗之地。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Dexterity and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：敏捷和靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +4 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +4 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +1 Willpower, +4 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +1 意志 , +4 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")


