section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/tutorial.lua"

t("Tutorial Adventurer", "探索模式冒險家", "birth descriptor name")
t("Adventurers have a generic talent set to teach to young ones.", "冒險家們有一套通用的理論可以傳授給菜鳥們。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/warrior.lua"

t("Warrior", "戰士系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Warriors train in all aspects of physical combat. They can be juggernauts of destruction wielding two-handed greatswords, or massive iron-clad protectors with gleaming shields.", "戰士精通於各種物理系戰鬥技能，他們可以手持雙手大劍造成成噸的打擊，也可以身穿重甲手持盾牌成爲一個強大的護衛。", "_t")
t("Berserker", "狂戰士", "birth descriptor name")
t("A Berserker wields huge two-handed weapons of destruction, bringing pain and death to his foes as he cleaves them in two.", "狂戰士手持雙手武器，以毀滅性的傷害將他的敵人砍成兩半。", "_t")
t("A Berserker usually forfeits all ideas of self-defense to concentrate on what he does best: killing things.", "狂戰士通常專注於造成傷害而忽視自我防禦。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Constitution", "他們最重要的屬性是力量和體質。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +1 Dexterity, +3 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +3 體質", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +3", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +3", "_t")
t("Bulwark", "盾戰士", "birth descriptor name")
t("A Bulwark specializes in weapon and shield combat, rarely leaving the cover of her many protective techniques.", "盾戰士精通於武器和使用盾牌格鬥，並擁有極高的防禦技能。", "_t")
t("A good Bulwark is able to withstand terrible attacks from all sides, protected by her shield, and when the time comes lash out at her foes with incredible strength.", "一個好的盾戰士能夠使用盾牌承受來自各方的攻擊，當時機一到就立即將對手置於死地。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Dexterity", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量和敏捷。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +2 Dexterity, +2 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +2 敏捷 , +2 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +0 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +6", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +6", "_t")
t("Archer", "弓箭手", "birth descriptor name")
t("Archers are dexterous ranged fighters, able to pin their foes to the ground and rain down a carpet of arrows on them.", "弓箭手是身手矯健的遠程戰士，能將他的敵人釘在原地再射出如雨般的箭矢消滅對手。", "_t")
t("Skilled archers can fire special shots that pierce, cripple or pin their foes.", "高等級的弓箭手可以射出特殊的箭矢，可以是射穿目標，減速或者使目標釘在原地。", "_t")
t("Archers can become good with either longbows or slings.", "弓箭手可以使用長弓和投石索。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Dexterity and Strength (when using bows) or Cunning (when using slings)", "他們最重要的屬性是：敏捷和力量（裝備弓時）或靈巧 (裝備投石索)", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 Strength, +5 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 力量 , +5 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +0 Willpower, +2 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +2 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")
t("Arcane Blade", "奧術之刃", "birth descriptor name")
t("The Arcane Blade is a warrior who has been touched by the gift of magic.", "奧術之刃是一個擁有魔法的戰士。", "_t")
t("Their use of magic is innate and not really studied; as such they do not naturally regenerate mana and must use external means of recharging.", "他們的魔法並非習得而是與生俱來的，因此他們不能依靠自然的法力恢復而必須依靠額外的方法來恢復法力值。", "_t")
t("They can cast spells from a limited selection but have the unique capacity to 'channel' their attack spells through their melee attacks.", "他們能施展一些有限的法術，同時也能將法術融合在他們的近戰攻擊中。", "_t")
t("They are adept with two-handed weapons, for the sheer destruction they can bring.", "他們擅長使用雙手武器，造成最大的傷害", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength, Cunning and Magic", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量、靈巧和魔法。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 Magic, +0 Willpower, +3 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 魔法 , +0 意志 , +3 靈巧", "_t")
t("Brawler", "格鬥家", "birth descriptor name")
t("Though you may fight alone against many, destined to fight till you die, still you do not relent. In a ring of blood you learn that a pair of fists can face the world.", "雖然你擊敗了許多對手，你也知道你命中註定要戰鬥至死，但你毫不退縮，在鮮血之環你會知道只有依靠你的雙拳來面對這個世界。", "_t")
t("The ravages of the Spellblaze stretched armies thin and left many unprotected. Not everyone could afford the luxury of a weapon.", "魔法大爆炸造成的物資匱乏使得武器成爲一種奢侈品，並不是每個人都能擔負的起。", "_t")
t("Without steel or iron, poor communities of all races turned to the strength of their own bodies for defense against the darkness.", "沒有鋼鐵打造的裝備，窮人們開始依靠他們自身的力量開始與黑暗鬥爭。", "_t")
t("Whether a pit-fighter, a boxer, or just an amateur practitioner, the Brawler's skills are still handy today.", "無論是一個職業拳手還是個業餘的門外漢，格鬥技能直到現在仍然十分有用", "_t")
t("Many of the Brawler's abilities will earn combo points which they can use on finishing moves that will have added effect.", "格鬥家的許多技能可以累積連擊點數然後用一個終結技能造成額外的打擊效果。", "_t")
t("The unarmed fighting styles the Brawler uses rely on maneuverability and having both hands available. As such, they cannot make use of their training wearing massive armour or while a weapon or shield is equipped.", "格鬥家徒手戰鬥依靠雙手的靈活機動性，所以他們無法學習裝備重甲、盾牌或者武器。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength, Dexterity, and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量、敏捷和靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 Strength, +3 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 力量 , +3 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +0 Willpower, +3 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +0 意志 , +3 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/wilder.lua"

t("Wilder", "野性系", "birth descriptor name")
t("Natural abilities can go beyond mere skill. Experience the true powers of nature to learn of its amazing gifts.", "自然能力超越了純粹的技能。經歷自然的真正力量來領略它神奇的恩賜。", "_t")
t("Wilders are one with nature, in one manner or another. There are as many different Wilders as there are aspects of nature.", "無論從哪一方面來說，野性系都是大自然的守護者。就像自然的力量多種多樣一樣，也有着不同的野性系職業。", "_t")
t("They can take on the aspects of creatures, summon creatures to them, feel the druidic call, ...", "他們可以繼承某些生物的特性技能，也可以召喚生物，或感受德魯伊的召喚，……", "_t")
t("Summoner", "召喚師", "birth descriptor name")
t("Not all might comes from within. Hear the invocations of nature, hear its calling power. See that from without we can find our true strengths.", "不是所有的力量來自於你自己，傾聽自然的祈禱，感受自然的力量，從中發現我們真正的力量。", "_t")
t("Summoners never fight alone. They are always ready to summon one of their many minions to fight at their side.", "召喚師從不孤身戰鬥，他們時刻準備召喚出寵物爲他們而戰。", "_t")
t("Summons can range from a combat hound to a fire drake.", "召喚師可以召喚從戰爭獵犬到火龍的各種生物。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +1 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +5 Willpower, +3 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +5 意志 , +3 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "_t")
t("Wyrmic", "龍戰士", "birth descriptor name")
t("Sleek, majestic, powerful... In the path of dragons we walk, and their breath is our breath. See their beating hearts with your eyes and taste their majesty between your teeth.", "雄偉、莊嚴、強壯……在通往龍的道路上和他們一同呼吸，用你的眼睛凝視他們跳動的心臟，在你的脣間品味他們的威嚴。", "_t")
t("Wyrmics are fighters who have learnt how to mimic some of the aspects of the dragons.", "龍戰士是學習守護巨龍戰鬥方式的戰士。", "_t")
t("They have access to talents normally belonging to the various kind of drakes.", "他們從不同的龍中學習技能。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量和意志。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +1 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +1 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +3 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +3 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("Oozemancer", "軟泥使", "birth descriptor name")
t("Magic must fail, magic must lose, nothing arcane can face the ooze...", "魔法必定失敗，魔法終會消亡，任何奧術能量都不能對抗軟泥的力量…", "_t")
t("Oozemancers separate themselves from normal civilisation so that they be more in harmony with Nature. Arcane force are reviled by them, and their natural attunement to the wilds lets them do battle with abusive magic-users on an equal footing.", "軟泥使將自己和正常文明割裂，讓自己與自然更加和諧。他們拒絕奧術能量，同時，與生俱來的自然和野性力量讓他們成爲了對抗魔法使用者的中堅力量。", "_t")
t("They can spawn oozes to protect and attack from a distance while also being adept at harnessing the power of mindstars and psiblades.", "他們能製造軟泥怪，來保護自己或遠距離攻擊對方，同時也能利用靈晶和心靈利刃來強化自己。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Willpower and Cunning", "他們最重要的屬性是：意志和靈巧。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +5 Willpower, +4 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +5 意志 , +4 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# -3", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# -3", "_t")
t("Max summons: %d", "最大召喚數： %d", "tformat")
t("Stone Warden", "岩石守衛", "birth descriptor name")
t([[The Spellblaze's scars may be starting to heal,
but little can change how the partisans feel.
Nature and arcane could bridge their divide -
and when it comes down to it, gold won't take sides...]], [[魔法大爆炸帶來的裂痕已經開始痊癒。
然而人們心中的偏見仍沒有消失。
奧術和魔法可以團結在一起——
在這兩者之間，金錢從不站隊……]], "_t")
t("Stone Wardens are dwarves trained in both the eldritch arts and the worship of nature.", "岩石守衛是那些同時訓練魔法技藝與自然力量的矮人。", "_t")
t("While other races are stuck in their belief that arcane forces and natural forces are meant to oppose, dwarves have found a way to combine them in harmony.", "在其他種族受困於自然和魔法天生對立的偏見時，矮人們已經找到方法讓這兩種力量和諧共存。", "_t")
t("Stone Wardens are armoured fighters, dual wielding shields to channel many of their powers.", "岩石守衛是身着重甲的戰士，雙持盾牌來施展技藝。", "_t")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength, Magic and Willpower", "他們最重要的屬性是：力量，魔法和意志", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Magic, +3 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 魔法 , +3 意志 , +0 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "_t")


