section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/races/giant.lua"

t("Giant", "巨人", "birth descriptor name")
t("Powerful beings that tower over all, but the bigger they are, the harder they fall...", "龐然的巨物傲視着渺小的生靈。然而須知，高處不勝寒，站得越高，跌得越慘……", "_t")
t("#{italic}#\"Giant\"#{normal}# is a catch-all term for humanoids which are typically over eight feet in height.  Their origins, cultures, and relationships to other races differ wildly, but they tend to live as refugees and outcasts, shunned by smaller sentient races who usually see them as a threat.", "#{italic}#\"巨人\"#{normal}# 是對那些身高超過八英尺的人型生物的統稱。他們的起源、文化和關係與其他種族迥異。他們被其他矮小的種族視爲威脅而躲避，作爲避難的流浪者而生存。", "_t")
t("Ogre", "食人魔", "birth descriptor name")
t([[Forged in the hatred of ages long passed,
made for a war that they've come to outlast.
Their forgotten birthplace lies deep underground,
its tunnels ruined so it wouldn't be found.
Past burglars have failed, but their data's immortal;
to start, look where halflings once tinkered with portals...]], [[他們鑄造於數千年的仇恨之中，
爲一場現在已經結束的戰爭而造。
他們被遺忘的誕生地深埋於地下，
那些隧道已經腐朽，無處尋覓。
過去的竊賊失敗了，但他們的數據將永遠保存；
要想找到他們，請尋找那些擺弄傳送門的半身人……]], "_t")
t("Ogres are an altered form of Human, created in the Age of Allure as workers and warriors for the Conclave.", "食人魔是變種人類，在厄流紀被孔克雷夫作爲工人和戰士而製造。", "_t")
t("Inscriptions have granted them magical and physical power far beyond their natural limits, but their dependence on runic magic made them a favored target during the Spellhunt, forcing them to take refuge among the Shalore.", "符文給他們超過自然界限的強大力量，但他們對符文魔法的依賴使之成爲獵魔行動絕佳的目標，而不得不依附於永恆精靈。", "_t")
t("Their preference for simple and direct solutions has given them an undeserved reputation as dumb brutes, despite their extraordinary talent with runes and their humble, dutiful nature.", "他們簡單的喜好與直接的方式令他們獲得了啞巴和野獸的蔑稱，儘管他們在法術和符文上有驚人的親和力。", "_t")
t("They possess the #GOLD#Ogric Wrath#WHITE# talent, which grants them critical chance and power, as well as resistance to confusion and stuns, when their attacks miss or are blocked.", "他們擁有 #GOLD#怒火中燒 #WHITE# 技能，能提供暴擊機率和傷害，並提供震懾定身免疫。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 Strength, -1 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +3 力量 , -1 敏捷 , +0 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 Magic, -2 Willpower, +2 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +2 魔法 , -2 意志 , +2 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# 13", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# 13", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Experience penalty:#LIGHT_BLUE# 15%", "#GOLD#經驗懲罰： #LIGHT_BLUE# 15%", "_t")
