t("Human", "人類", "birth descriptor name")
t("The Humans are one of the main races on Maj'Eyal, along with the Halflings. For many thousands of years they fought each other until events, and great people, unified all the Human and Halfling nations under one rule.", "人類與半身人一起是馬基·埃亞爾的主要種族，他們曾互相爭戰了幾千年，直到在領袖們的偉大領導下，人類和半身人的國度再度聯合起來。", "_t")
