t("One race, one mind, one way. Our oppression shall end, and we shall inherit Eyal. Do not presume we are weak - our way is true, and only those who help us shall see our strength.", "一個種族，一種思想，一種道路。我們的壓抑終於要終結，而我們將繼承埃亞爾，不要認爲我們很柔弱，只有那些幫助我們的人才能見識到我們的力量。", "_t")
t("Yeeks are a mysterious race native to the tropical island of Rel.", "奪心魔是一支神祕的種族，生活於熱帶島嶼瑞爾。", "_t")
t("Although they are now nearly unheard of in Maj'Eyal, they spent many centuries as secret slaves to the Halfling nation of Nargol.", "儘管他們在馬基·埃亞爾中幾乎不曾人們被提到過，他們已經作爲半身人王國納格爾的奴隸存在了數個世紀。", "_t")
t("They gained their freedom during the Age of Pyre and have since then followed 'The Way' - a unity of minds enforced by their powerful psionics.", "他們在派爾紀獲得了自由並在那個時候建立了維網——一個由他們靈能思維組成的網絡。", "_t")
t("They possess the #GOLD#Dominant Will#WHITE# talent which allows them to temporarily subvert the mind of a lesser creature. When the effect ends, the creature dies.", "他們天生掌握 #GOLD# 主導思維 #WHITE#，允許他們在短時間內控制一個較弱生物的思維。當效果結束時，被控制目標死亡。", "_t")
t("While Yeeks are not amphibians, they still have an affinity for water, allowing them to survive longer without breathing.", "雖然奪心魔不是兩棲生物，但他們天生對水有種特殊的親和力，允許他們屏息更長時間。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 屬性修正：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * -3 Strength, -2 Dexterity, -5 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * -3 力量 , -2 敏捷 , -5 體質", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +6 Willpower, +4 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +6 意志 , +4 靈巧", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# 7", "#GOLD# 每等級生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# 7", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Experience penalty:#LIGHT_BLUE# -15%", "#GOLD#經驗懲罰： #LIGHT_BLUE# -15%", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Confusion resistance:#LIGHT_BLUE# 35%", "#GOLD#混亂抗性:#LIGHT_BLUE# 35%", "_t")


