t("Maj'Eyal: The Age of Ascendancy", "馬基埃亞爾:卓越紀", "_t")
t("The people of Maj'Eyal: Humans, Halflings, Elves and Dwarves.", "馬基埃亞爾生活着人類、半身人、精靈和矮人。", "_t")
t("The known world has been at relative peace for over one hundred years, and people are prospering again.", "世界已經保持了超過一百年的和平，各大種族再次繁榮起來", "_t")
t("You are an adventurer, setting out to find lost treasure and glory.", "你是一位冒險者，出發去尋找失落的寶藏和榮耀。", "_t")
t("But what lurks in the shadows of the world?", "在世界的陰影之下究竟潛伏着什麼呢？", "_t")
t("Infinite Dungeon: The Neverending Descent", "無盡地下城：無盡的試煉", "_t")
t("Ever deeper, never ending, no reprieve, keep descending. In ruins old, through barred gate, once riddle solved, find thy fate.", "無盡深度，沒有終點，沒有重複，不斷深入，在古老的廢墟里，穿過關閉的大門，解開謎題，尋找你的宿命。", "_t")
t("Play as your favorite race and class and venture into the infinite dungeon.", "選擇你最喜歡的種族和職業，進入無盡地城冒險。", "_t")
t("The only limit to how far you can go is your own skill!", "能夠前進多遠取決於你的個人技術！", "_t")
t("Inside the infinite dungeon you will yourself be limitless. You can level up beyond level 50 and continue to gain stat and talent points (at a reduced rate).", "在無盡地城中你不受限制，你可以突破 50 級的等級上限並繼續獲得屬性和技能點數（以一個較低的比例獲得）。", "_t")
t("Every level after level 50 the maximum of stats will increase by one.", "級之後屬性最大值每級增加 1 點。", "_t")
t("Every 10 levels after level 50 the maximum points of each talent will increase by one.", "50 級之後每 10 級，技能的最大等級增加 1 點。", "_t")
t("The Arena: Challenge of the Master", "競技場：競技場主宰的挑戰", "_t")
t("Blood spilled on sand, only the strong survive. Prove yourself worthy to enter.", "血濺沙場，勇者生存，需證明你有進入的資格。", "_t")
t("Play as a lone warrior facing the Arena's challenge!", "孤身一人直面競技場的挑戰！", "_t")
t("You can use any class and race for it.", "你可以使用任何職業和種族。", "_t")
t("See how far you can go! Can you become the new Master of the Arena?", "看看你能前進多遠！你能成爲新的競技場主宰麼？", "_t")
t("If so, you will battle your own champion next time!", "如果這樣，下一場戰鬥你的對手就是你自己的冠軍角色！", "_t")


