section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-derth.lua"

t("Pfaugh. You're too late. %s has already finished. But I suppose it doesn't do any harm to take these and give you your undeserved reward.", "額哦……你來的太晚了，%s 已經完成了。不過這些東西給你也沒什麼壞處，雖然……你本不應該得到這些獎勵。", "tformat")
t("Ah, excellent. Hand them over, if you please. You should know that in your overlong absence, %s has managed to create a %s. I'll be most put out if he steals my rightful spot.", "啊，好極了，如果你願意，請交給我吧，要知道你離開的那麼長時間裏，%s 已經制造了 %s。如果他搶了我的位置，我估計我就要被解僱了。", "tformat")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A human robed in immaculate white satin opens the door and eyes you appraisingly.*#WHITE#
Ah, an adventurer. I was just thinking that I needed a new one.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一個穿着一塵不染白緞面長袍的人打開了門，他上下打量着你。*#WHITE#
啊，一個冒險者，我正好在考慮是不是要重新找個人幫忙。]], "_t")
t("That sounds promising. And ominous.", "聽上去不錯，但總有種不祥的預感……", "_t")
t("Indeed, it is both promising and ominous. I can reward you handsomely for your efforts, but they will lead you into deadly peril to which, I assume, the previous three fellows who went off on my errand never to return can attest.", "的確，你幫我完成這件事的話我會好好報答你，不過這個任務很危險。事實上，前面三個接受任務的人到目前爲止還沒有一個活着回來。", "_t")
t("What do you propose?", "那……你的建議呢？", "_t")
t("Good adventurer, I am an alchemist, and quite a good one. This year, for the first time, the great Brotherhood of Alchemists has invited my application to their number. I'll not try your patience with the details of the application process, but suffice to say that it is grueling. Fortunately, a mere three tasks now stand between me and acceptance.", "非常好，我是一個鍊金術師，水平很高超的那種。今年，煉金術士兄弟會第一次邀請我成爲他們的會員。加入的條件……我就不多囉嗦了，估計你也不想聽，反正複雜的很，我都快累死了。幸好，我現在就剩下三件事沒辦了。", "_t")
t("How can I help?", "我怎麼幫你？", "_t")
t("I require ingredients for three potent mixtures. Obviously, since I seek your aid, none of them is to be found by simply strolling to the local herbalist's. No, they will need to be forcibly parted from their owners who will, just as obviously, put up a fight. I've yet to encounter a naga who would be persuaded to hand over his tongue! Ha! Oh, I am droll at times.", "我需要一些材料來製作三瓶藥劑。很顯然，既然我找你幫忙，那麼，想簡單從那些草藥師那裏搞到這些材料是幾乎不可能的。沒錯，你得從這些材料的擁有者那裏強行搞來，當然你免不了一場大戰。我曾經試圖說服一位娜迦把它的舌頭給我……哈！我偶爾會開開玩笑。", "_t")
t("I specialize in separating vital body parts from monsters. What do you offer in return?", "對於從怪物身上把你要的東西給活剝下來，我可是個行家，但是我能得到什麼好處？", "_t")
t("Why, I will let you share in the fruits of my labors! Each of the three mixtures I shall produce in a quantity sufficient to create three doses: one for me, one for the Brotherhood and their confounded trial... and one for you. I must tell you that time is of the essence. I am not the only one who the Brotherhood invited this year, yet they will accept only one applicant-- the first to complete their trials. I know of at least three others laboring furiously to take my rightful place. Should your aid see me through, then I will reward you beyond even the remarkable elixirs. I've an ancient Lifebinding Emerald that grants great powers of health and healing when used properly. What say you?", "什麼？我會和你分享我的勞動成果！三瓶藥劑每個我都會製造三份：一份給自己，一份給煉金術士兄弟會交差，而另外一份給你。必須告訴你的是，時間非常緊迫，我不是今年煉金術士兄弟會邀請的唯一一個，只有第一個完成他們要求的人才會被接受。據我所知，至少還有三個人在搶我這個位置。如果你幫我成功入會的話，除了藥劑之外，我還有更好的東西回報你。我有一塊古老的生命寶石，合理使用可以大大增強你的治療能力。怎麼樣，有興趣麼？", "_t")
t("I accept.", "我接受了。", "_t")
t("I cannot aid you at this time.", "我現在沒空幫你。", "_t")
t("Excellent. Now then, I've three elixirs I'm working on. I'll burden you with only one at a time, since I've learned the hard way about the hazards of overloading an adventurer's brain. Here are your options: the elixir of the fox, which makes you as nimble and cunning as a fox; the elixir of avoidance, which sharpens your natural inclinations to get out of the way of incoming harm; or the elixir of precision, which grants intuitive understanding of an enemy's most sensitive spots. Which would you like to aid me with?", "好極了，那麼，我有三瓶藥劑要製造，不過每次我只給你一項任務，一次給你超負荷的任務對你可沒有任何好處。你自己選一個吧：狡詐藥劑，能讓你像一隻狐狸一般靈活；閃避藥劑，能提高你躲避傷害的能力；精準藥劑，能讓你對敵人的弱點了如指掌。你選擇哪一個？", "_t")
t("Here's a list of the ingredients I'm missing. Please attempt to not lose your life in their pursuit. I'll be most put out if I must wait another year. Oh, and I suppose I should tell you that I've already a handful of adventurers out scouring the unpleasant places of the world for these ingredients. Dally and one of them shall claim the prize while you're out.", "這裏有一張配方，上面寫着我目前缺少的材料。當心別丟了你的小命，要是我錯過這次機會就得等明年了。哦，我記得好像提醒過你，已經有幾個冒險者出發去幫我弄這些材料了，一會你出去之後達利或者他們之中的一個估計要來領取獎勵了。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*門鎖住了，沒人注意到你的敲門聲。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[Leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist opens his door.*#WHITE#
Ah, you again.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*鍊金師打開了門。*#WHITE#
啊，你回來了。]], "_t")
t("I've returned with the ingredients for the %s.", "我回來了，我找到了%s的材料。", "tformat")
t("I've come to offer more aid.", "我來接下一步任務。", "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits.]", "[給他材料。]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist grins and motions impatiently for the ingredients.*#WHITE#
Wonderful, absolutely wonderful! The final step! Here, let me have those!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*鍊金師看到材料有點急不可耐，他咧着嘴開心的笑了起來。*#WHITE#
好極了！簡直棒極了！這可是最後一步！來來來，把它們給我吧。]], "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits]", "[給他材料]", "_t")
t("Wait here while I perform my art. I'll have your reward within the hour.", "在這兒等着，我去製作藥劑，一小時內我會把東西弄好，當然還有你的獎勵。", "_t")
t("A final wait for you, my good adventurer, and then I shall return with both your rewards! Haha, complete at last!", "最後稍等一下，我的冒險家朋友，馬上我會帶着你的兩份獎勵回來，哈哈終於大功告成啦！", "_t")
t("[Wait]", "[等待]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns and hands you a small vial of fine glass.*#WHITE#
Enjoy your reward.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*鍊金師終於回來了，他遞給你一個精緻的小玻璃瓶。*#WHITE#
享用你的獎勵吧。]], "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns with a vial and a green gem.*#WHITE#
Enjoy the fruits of your labors, adventurer. I know I will. To show my appreciation, I shall name my firstborn after... er, what was your name, then? Haha, I jest. Oh, I do go on when I'm giddy. Fare you well.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*鍊金師終於回來了，手裏拿着一顆翡翠寶石和一個藥水瓶。*#WHITE#
盡情享用你的勞動成果吧，我的冒險家。爲了表示我的敬意，我準備給我的新作品取名爲……呃……你叫什麼名字？哈哈，開個玩笑，啊～在我被喜悅衝昏頭腦之前，我必須得繼續我的工作，那麼，再見了我的朋友。]], "_t")
t("Thank you. I'll be off.", "謝謝，我走了。", "_t")
t("Excellent. With which would you like to aid me?", "好極了，你準備幫我做哪一個？", "_t")
t("The %s.", "%s。", "tformat")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("Here's a list of the ingredients I'm missing. Please attempt to not lose your life in their pursuit. I'll be most put out if I must wait another year.", "這裏有一張配方，上面寫着我目前缺少的材料。當心別丟了你的小命，要是我錯過這次機會就得等明年了。", "_t")
t("I'll be off.", "我走了。", "_t")
t("Terribly sorry, but I've already made the elixir without your aid. I've no reward to give you, and no reason to do so if I did.", "非常抱歉，我已經自己把那些藥劑都做好了，我可沒理由再給你任何獎勵。", "_t")
t("Hrmph.", "哼。", "_t")


