section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-elvala.lua"

t("Too late! Argh, too late. %s has already finished. I'll make the elixir and reward you as promised, but only because the Brotherhood breaks the fingers of non-member alchemists who rook people. Members, on the other hand...", "太晚了！哎呀，太晚了。%s 已經完成了。我遵守諾言會幫你製作藥劑，不過是因爲，非會員的煉金術士如果欺騙他人的話，煉金術士兄弟會會折斷他們的手指，如果是會員的話，則另當別論……", "tformat")
t("Give them here. You took long enough; %s cooked up a %s in your absence. Be quicker about the next one lest I make a 'mistake' in brewing your reward.", "把材料給我，你的動作太慢了，%s 已經在你離開的時候製造了 %s 。下一次你最好動作快一點，免得我在給你製造獎品時“出錯”。", "tformat")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A shabbily-dressed elf opens the door, scratching his head in apparent puzzlement.*#WHITE#
Another adventurer? Or have we met? I can't tell people apart unless they wear brightly-colored headbands. You need to help me.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一個衣衫襤褸的精靈開了門，他的臉上帶着困惑的表情。*#WHITE#
又來了一個冒險者？我們碰過面麼？除非人們頭上扎一根顏色鮮明點的髮帶，要不然我就分不清楚誰是誰……你得幫我個忙。]], "_t")
t("I am indeed an adventurer. Go on.", "其實我是個冒險者，請繼續。", "_t")
t("Three elixirs stand between me and acceptance into the Brotherhood of Alchemists, unless I've been through that already. I'm never quite sure. But I think that's the case. Bring me the ingredients.", "必須製造三瓶藥劑我才能加入煉金術士兄弟會，我不是很確定，不過我覺得這是個麻煩，你得把材料給我。", "_t")
t("What elixirs? What ingredients?", "什麼藥劑？什麼材料？", "_t")
t("The ones that I need to get before the other alchemists get them. Can't have some lesser hack sneaking into the Brotherhood.", "必須在別的鍊金師之前弄到手，又不能潛入兄弟會裏偷。", "_t")
t("You're making little sense.", "你最好把話講明白些。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He raises his voice and gestures exaggeratedly, seemingly taking you for an idiot.*#WHITE#
Me need pieces of scary monsters for happy-making drink. You get me pieces. You probably get eaten by monsters, me have this conversation yet again with other bonehead.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他提高了嗓門，並做着誇張的手勢，似乎覺得你是一個白癡。*#WHITE#
我需要一些怪物的碎片來製作一些有趣的藥水，你得把那些碎片給我，你也許會被怪物吃掉，之前我和另外一個傻瓜也說過這些話。]], "_t")
t("I've been known to kill the occasional monster. Is there a reward in it for me?", "我知道要殺一些怪物，有什麼獎勵麼？", "_t")
t("It finally understands! You get a dose of every elixir you help me make. And if your help gets me into the Brotherhood, I've got half an Elixir of Invulnerability lying around that I'll give you. Don't try anything; I've already downed the other half.", "總算明白了！你每幫我做成一份藥劑我也會給你一瓶。要是你幫我加入煉金術士兄弟會，我這兒還有半瓶無敵藥水也給你，另外半瓶不用找了，因爲已經被我喝掉了。", "_t")
t("I accept.", "我接受了。", "_t")
t("I cannot aid you at this time.", "我現在沒空幫你。", "_t")
t("Three elixirs I need. I'll show you the ingredients to one at a time. Are you interested in the Elixir of Mysticism, the Elixir of the Savior, or the Elixir of Mastery?", "我需要三種藥劑，每次我會告訴你其中一個的配方。你對哪個比較感興趣？神祕藥劑？守護藥劑？還是掌握藥劑？", "_t")
t("Here's a list of the monster bits I need. I've already got a bunch of idiots out looking for these, by the way, so you best hurry up; they've got a head start on you and I'm not getting any saner here.", "這裏有一張記錄材料的紙，順便說一聲，之前我已經找了幾個傻瓜幫我去找這些東西了，所以你最好動作快點。他們已經走在你前面了，就是還沒找到個腦子聰明點的。", "_t")
t("So I see. I'll be off.", "瞭解，那我走了。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*門鎖住了，沒人注意到你的敲門聲。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[Leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The shabby elf opens his door.*#WHITE#
Do I know you?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個衣衫襤褸的精靈開了門。*#WHITE#
我們認識麼？]], "_t")
t("I've returned with the ingredients for the %s.", "我回來了，我找到了%s的材料。", "tformat")
t("I've come to offer more aid.", "我來接下一步任務。", "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits.]", "[給他材料。]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The elf claps his scarred hands together.*#WHITE#
Exceptional work, lackey! The final elixir awaits! Oh, yes. Membership will be mine. And revenge. Ohhhh yes.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個精靈拍着他那滿是傷疤的雙手。*#WHITE#
乾的好，我的冒險家！最後一份藥劑馬上就要完成了！對，沒錯，會員資格是我的了，然後我要報仇雪恨，嗯，沒錯！]], "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits]", "[給他材料]", "_t")
t("Contain your impatience while I prepare these. I'll have the elixir within the hour.", "我製造藥水的時候你得耐心點，一個小時後我會回來。", "_t")
t("Perfection. Wait here.", "好極了，在這兒等下。", "_t")
t("[Wait]", "[等待]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The elf finally returns and tosses you a small vial of fine glass.*#WHITE#
Side effects may include some slight mental imbalances.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個精靈終於回來了，丟給你一個精緻的小藥劑瓶。*#WHITE#
它會有點副作用，你會感到輕度的精神失衡。]], "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The alchemist finally returns with two vials.*#WHITE#
I have no idea who you are, but I'm pretty sure that I'm supposed to give these to somebody as a reward. If some adventurer kills you and takes them, then apparently you're not the fellow I'm looking for.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個鍊金師帶着兩個瓶子走了出來。*#WHITE#
我不知道你是誰，不過我要把這兩樣東西送給你作爲報答，要是有冒險者把你幹掉然後搶走了這兩瓶藥劑，那就算我找錯人了。]], "_t")
t("Thank you. I'll be off.", "謝謝，我走了。", "_t")
t("Which of the remaining elixirs interests you?", "剩下的藥劑，你對哪個感興趣？", "_t")
t("The %s.", "%s。", "tformat")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("Here's a list of the ingredients I'm missing. Please follow the directions carefully, or the resulting elixir could be more fatal than either of us would hope.", "這有一張配方，上面寫着我目前缺少的材料。你得按上面的指示小心行動，要不然做出的藥劑就會要人命了，我可不希望這樣。", "_t")
t("I'll be off.", "我走了。", "_t")
t("Already made it. Best pick up the pace next time, adventurer.", "我已經做好了，下次你動作最好快點，冒險者。", "_t")
t("Hrmph.", "哼。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-golem.lua"

t("Equipment(%s) <=> Inventory(%s)", "裝備(%s) <=> 道具欄(%s)", "tformat")
t("Change your golem's name", "改變傀儡的名字", "_t")
t("Name", "名稱", "_t")
t("%s (servant of %s)", "%s (%s的僕人)", "tformat")
t("I want to change your equipment.", "我想更換你的裝備。", "_t")
t("I want to change your talents.", "我想改變你的技能。", "_t")
t("I want to change your tactics.", "我想調整你的策略。", "_t")
t("I want to take direct control.", "我想直接操控你。", "_t")
t("#ROYAL_BLUE#The golem decides to change it's name to #{bold}#%s#{normal}#.", "#ROYAL_BLUE#傀儡決定將名字更改爲 #{bold}#%s#{normal}#.", "log")
t("Telos the Great and Powerful (reluctant follower of %s)", "偉大的泰勒斯大人 (%s不情願的隨從)", "tformat")
t("I want to change your name.", "我想改變你的名字。", "_t")
t("How is it that you speak?", "你居然能說話？", "_t")
t("I want to change your appearance (one-time only).", "我想要改變你的外觀(只能進行一次)。", "_t")
t("Nothing, let's go.", "沒事，走吧。", "_t")
t("What's the good of immortality if you can't even speak? No archmage worth his salt is going to concoct some immoral life-after-death scheme without including some sort of capacity for making his opinions known. And, by the way, your energy manipulation techniques are on the same level as those of my average pair of shoes. Though I guess you are making up for it with your golem crafting skills.", "如果你連說話都不能，就算得到永生還有什麼樂趣？任何一個稱職的大法師，在準備他們不道德的死後復活計劃的時候，都一定會計劃好確保在這種狀況下也能讓別人聽到自己的聲音。順帶一提，你操縱能量的技術連給我提鞋都不夠。雖然我猜，我正在用你的傀儡製作技能來彌補它。", "_t")
t("Change my name? I'm quite happy being 'Telos' thankyou. Though I wouldn't mind being 'Telos the Great and Powerful'. Do that actually. Yes!", "改變我的名字？我的名字就是“泰勒斯”，謝謝。當然，如果你叫我“偉大的泰勒斯大人”我也不介意。對，趕緊這麼做吧！", "_t")
t([[I'm a golem. How droll!
Oh, did you want something?]], [[我是個傀儡。真可笑！
哦，你想要點什麼嗎？]], "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The golem talks in a monotonous voice*#WHITE#
Yes master.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*傀儡用一個單調的聲音說：*#WHITE#
是，主人。]], "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-hermit.lua"

t("SON OF A RITCH! YOU SHOW UP TEN MINUTES AFTER I GET THE NEWS THAT SOME JACKASS ALREADY FINISHED THE ELIXIRS AND IS GETTING ACCEPTED BY THE BROTHERHOOD. WHAT THE HELL TOOK YOU SO LONG? MIRVENIA'S MAMMARIES, I'LL TAKE THESE AND MAKE YOU YOUR REWARD, BUT ONLY BECAUSE A CURSE WILL KILL ME IF I DON'T. AND IF IT TASTES LIKE PISS, THAT'S YOUR IMAGINATION, I'M SURE.", "見鬼！在我收到消息說某個蠢貨已經制成了藥劑並且加入了兄弟會之後10分鐘你居然出現了，到底什麼該死的事情花了你那麼長時間？！把你那些該死的材料給我，要不是有個詛咒說，如果我不這麼做的話我會被殺，我纔不會幫你做這該死的獎品。要是藥水味道嘗上去像馬尿一樣的話那肯定是你這混蛋造成的。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The halfling hands you a note that says, 'Heard %s managed to make a %s while you've been loafing. Hurry the hell up next time.*#WHITE#
		I STILL CAN'T HEAR A DAMNED THING. FORTUNATELY, YOU DON'T LOOK LIKE THE SORT THAT MAKES INTERESTING CONVERSATION.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個半身人遞給你一張紙條，上面寫着：聽說 %s 在你離開的時候製造了 %s 。下次動作快點。*#WHITE#
		我還是什麼都聽不見，幸運的是，看上去似乎和你聊天也沒什麼意思。]], "tformat")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*After a great deal of pounding, a halfling wrapped in charred, smoking robes opens the door. He looks irritated.*#WHITE#
IT'S NOT ENOUGH THAT I WORK ALL MORNING TO MAKE A POTION THAT ENDS UP NEARLY BLOWING MY ASS OFF, BUT NOW I'VE GOT IDIOTS BEATING DOWN MY DAMNED FRONT DOOR WITH WHAT SOUNDS LIKE A BATTERING RAM, AND YES, I HEARD IT, THOUGH I CAN HARDLY MAKE OUT A BLEEDING THING WITH THESE BLEEDING, CONCUSSED EARS. WHAT DO YOU WANT?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你敲了半天的門，終於有個穿着燒焦且冒着煙的長袍半身人開了門，他看上去很不高興。*#WHITE#
這一上午搞這天殺的藥劑差點搞的我屁股開花，我聽到有個白癡敲我家的門敲的跟攻城槌一樣，行了！我聽見了！雖然我的耳朵已經差不多快聾掉了！找我有什麼事麼？]], "_t")
t("Perhaps there's something that I can help you with.", "也許我能幫上什麼忙。", "_t")
t("SPEAK UP, HAMBRAIN. I'VE JUST GOTTEN MY EARDRUMS BLOWN OUT BY YET ANOTHER BY-THE-PYRE POTION GONE SOUTH, REMEMBER? THRICE-DAMNED THING WAS GOING PERFECTLY, TOO. TOKNOR'S TACKLE!", "說大聲點，笨蛋！我的耳膜最近在調製藥劑的時候被炸破了，謝天謝地，你最好將你的嗓門提高三倍！", "_t")
t("I SAID, MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING THAT I CAN HELP YOU WITH!", "我說，也許我能幫上什麼忙！！", "_t")
t("STILL CAN'T HEAR YOU, BUT LISTEN UP. THE BROTHERHOOD OF ALCHEMISTS IS ACCEPTING THE FIRST NEW APPLICANT TO DEMONSTRATE, AMONG OTHER THINGS, THREE VERY COMPLICATED ELIXIRS. I WOULDN'T BOTHER TRYING TO JOIN SUCH A BUNCH OF ADDLE-BRAINED DEGENERATES, BUT IT SO HAPPENS THAT THE BROTHERHOOD OF ALCHEMISTS HOLDS THE SECRET CURE FOR THE COMMON BLOWN-OFF ASS, WHICH IT SO HAPPENS IS OF SOME INTEREST TO ME.", "還是聽不見，不過聽着，煉金術士兄弟會最近會吸收最先做好三瓶指定藥劑的鍊金師作爲會員。我本來對那些呆瓜組成的團體沒什麼興趣，不過碰巧兄弟會有一種治療爛屁股的祕方，我對這個很感興趣。", "_t")
t("HOW CAN I HELP?", "我怎麼幫你？", "_t")
t("THE BROTHERHOOD KNOWS DAMNED WELL WHAT ADVANCES IN THE FIELD OF ALCHEMY WOULD DO FOR EVERY CIVILIZATION IN EXISTENCE, BUT THEY HOARD THEIR FEW WORTHWHILE SECRETS LIKE A GREAT BROWN WYRM SITTING ON ITS PILE OF CRAP. YOU KNOW WHAT? I DON'T EVEN WANT THE ASS-CURE FOR ME. I'M GOING TO STEAL EVERY SECRET THEY'VE GOT, WRITE THEM DOWN, MAKE A HUNDRED COPIES, AND NAIL ONE TO A TREE IN EVERY VILLAGE IN MAJ'EYAL.", "兄弟會精通該死的鍊金領域，而他們卻像一頭大棕龍坐在它的糞堆上一樣保守着他們的祕密！要知道，其實我纔不想要那什麼蛋疼的祕方，我準備把他們的祕密都偷出來，寫在紙上，抄上一百份，然後貼到馬基埃亞爾所有村莊的樹上去！", "_t")
t("THAT'S NOT A VERY HERMIT-LIKE ATTITUDE.", "這可不像一個隱士的態度。", "_t")
t("AND THEN WHAT WILL THEY DO? ONCE THEIR PRECIOUS SECRETS-- WHICH, IN ALL PROBABILITY, EITHER DON'T EXIST OR ARE THINGS LIKE RECIPES FOR ELIXIRS OF WHO-GIVES-A-FLYING-DUCK-- ARE OUT IN THE OPEN, THE BROTHERHOOD OF ASSWIPES WILL HAVE NOTHING TO HOLD IT TOGETHER BUT ELIXIRS OF THEIR TEARS AND WIDESPREAD DISDAIN FROM THE REST OF THE WORLD. SPEAK UP, THEN. ARE YOU IN OR OUT?", "AND 然後他們會怎麼樣？當他們的寶貝祕密，或許根本就不存在，或者就是些操蛋祕方公之於衆之後，除了用他們的淚水做藥劑和被大家鄙視之外，“基佬兄弟會”就沒什麼祕密可藏了。現在，說大聲點！你是接受任務還是拒絕？", "_t")
t("I'M IN.", "我接受！", "_t")
t("I CANNOT AID YOU AT THIS TIME.", "我沒空幫你！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He hands you a slip of paper with the names and properties of some elixirs on it.*#WHITE#
THE INGREDIENTS TO THESE SUCKERS ARE SORT OF A TRADE SECRET, SO I'LL TELL YOU ABOUT ONE AND WE'LL SEE HOW THAT GOES. OH, AND I'LL MAKE ENOUGH FOR YOU TO HAVE A SWIG WHEN I'M DONE, SO GOOD FOR YOU. WHICH ONE WILL IT BE? JUST POINT AT THE DAMNED LIST. I HAVEN'T HEARD A THING YOU'VE SAID YET. I HOPE TO HELL YOU'RE NOT STANDING THERE TRYING TO SELL ME SOMETHING.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他遞給你一張寫着藥劑材料的紙片。*#WHITE#
對它們來說藥劑配方是一個商業機密，所以一次我只給你一個，然後我會告訴你怎麼做。呃……等我做好以後一定會讓你喝個夠，這會令你大受裨益。好了，你現在選哪一個？你只要用手點一下這該死的列表就可以了，你說的話我一個字都沒聽見。但願你別再在這裏跟我說什麼了！]], "_t")
t("HERE'S A LIST OF THE STUFF I NEED. MOST OF IT WILL TRY TO KILL YOU, SO I HOPE YOU'RE NOT INCOMPETENT. I'VE GOT PLENTY OF INCOMPETENT HELP ALREADY. I HOPE FOR YOUR SAKE THAT YOU'RE SMARTER AND FASTER THAN THEM.", "這裏有一張我需要的材料清單，大多數材料擁有者可能會要了你的小命，但願你沒那麼挫，我已經有一票挫子幫手了。希望你比他們要聰明，動作麻利點！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*門鎖住了，沒人注意到你的敲門聲。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[Leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The halfling, still smoking, opens his door.*#WHITE#
I LIVE WAY THE HELL OUT HERE FOR A REASON, YOU PIECE OF... OH. IT'S YOU.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個半身人，身上還冒着煙，開了門。*#WHITE#
我呆在這坑爹的地方是有原因的，你TM…………哦，是你啊。]], "_t")
t("I'VE RETURNED WITH THE INGREDIENTS FOR THE %s.", "我回來了，我找到了%s的材料！", "tformat")
t("I'VE COME TO OFFER MORE AID.", "我來接下一步的任務！", "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits.]", "[給他材料。]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*For the first time you've seen, genuine pleasure lights up the halfling's soot-smeared face.*#WHITE#
GOOD WORK, WHOEVER YOU ARE. ALL OF MAJ'EYAL OWES YOU THEIR THANKS, EXCEPT FOR MEMBERS OF THE BROTHERHOOD OF ALCHEMISTS, WHO MIGHT TRY TO DO YOU BODILY HARM. FORTUNATELY FOR YOU, THEY'RE MOSTLY HARMLESS.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你第一次看到，半身人滿是煤灰的臉上綻放出了誠懇的笑容。*#WHITE#
乾的好！不管你是誰！整個馬基埃亞爾都應該感謝你，除了那些煉金術士兄弟會成員，他們想加害於你。不過幸運的是，那些貨通常來說根本傷不到你。]], "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits]", "[給他材料]", "_t")
t("WAIT HERE. THERE'S A GOOD CHANCE YOU'LL GET BLOWN INTO ADVENTURER KIBBLE IF YOU STEP INSIDE THIS BUILDING. MY ROBE OF MAD ALCHEMIST PROTECTION IS THE ONLY REASON I'M NOT VAPOUR.", "在這兒等着，這是一個不錯的機會，如果你進入這棟建築，你會有幸成爲冒險家牌肉鬆。由於我有這件強大的鍊金長袍保護，我纔沒變成粉蒸肉。", "_t")
t("GIVE ME AN HOUR, AND THINK UNPLEASANT THOUGHTS ABOUT THE BROTHERHOOD. IF ANYTHING EXPLODES, COME RESCUE ME, EVEN IF IT LOOKS LIKE THE BUILDING IS AN INFERNO OF POISONOUS SMOKE AND POLKA-DOT FLAMES.", "給我一小時時間，你在這等着，想想那可惡的兄弟會。要是聽到爆炸聲，你得來救我，不管什麼情況哪怕房子燒成窟窿，變成冒着毒煙的地獄你也得進來。", "_t")
t("[Wait]", "[等待]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Disaster fails to occur. The halfling finally returns and hands you a small vial of sooty glass.*#WHITE#
ENJOY, AND COME BACK ANY TIME IF YOU'RE INTERESTED IN SIMILAR WORK. I HAVEN'T WON YET. THE LONGER YOU WAIT, THE MORE LIKELY IT IS THAT YOU'LL RETURN TO A SMOKING CRATER AND ONE TRULY IRATE HALFLING.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*還好，沒發生任何不幸的事，那個半身人終於回來了，遞給你一個黑乎乎的玻璃瓶。*#WHITE#
喝吧！你要是喜歡這份工作的話隨時可以回來找我。我還沒贏呢！最好快點，你在這兒待的時間太長，下次迎接你的可就是一個冒着黑煙怒不可遏的半身人了！]], "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The halfling finally returns with a vial and a small pouch.*#WHITE#
YOUR DOSE OF THE ELIXIR, AS WELL AS SOMETHING ELSE. THIS INFUSION IS RARE AS HELL, SO DON'T GO WASTING IT.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個半身人終於拿着一個瓶子和一個袋子回來了。*#WHITE#
這是你那份藥劑，另外還有個東西給你。這個紋身可稀有了，千萬別浪費了！]], "_t")
t("THANK YOU. I'LL BE OFF.", "謝謝，我走了。", "_t")
t("WHICH ELIXIR DO YOU WANT TO HELP ME WITH? YOU ARE HERE TO DO JUST THAT, RIGHT? YOU'RE NOT SOME IMBECILE HERE LOOKING FOR A LOVE POTION?", "你選擇哪一個任務？你是來做任務的吧？我想你該不是那些來找春藥的蠢貨吧？", "_t")
t("[Indicate the %s.]", "[指向 %s.]", "tformat")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("TAKE THIS LIST OF INGREDIENTS, AND HURRY THE HELL UP.", "拿好配料清單，動作快點。", "_t")
t("I'LL BE OFF.", "我走了", "_t")
t("TOO SLOW, HAMBRAIN. ELIXIR'S MADE ALREADY, AND SOMEBODY ELSE WALKED OFF WITH THE REWARD. IF YOU'RE FEELING SORRY FOR YOURSELF, ASK WHETHER THIS IS MORE OR LESS PLEASANT THAN GETTING APPRECIABLE CHUNKS OF YOUR ANATOMY BLASTED CLEAN OFF YOUR BODY THIS MORNING. THAT'S RIGHT. BYE.", "太慢了，蠢蛋，藥劑我已經做好了。已經有人來拿走了獎勵。如果你覺得失望，告訴自己這是否比一早上被從你身上炸爛一大塊要好。就是這樣，再見！", "_t")
t("Hrmph.", "哼。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/alchemist-last-hope.lua"

t("Damn it all. You're too late. %s has already finished. But I suppose you did your best, so I'll take these and keep my end of the bargian.", "見鬼，你來的太晚了，%s 已經完成了，不過我想你已經盡力了，所以我還是會完成這樁交易，把材料給我吧。", "tformat")
t("Great work! And you're still in one piece, I see. Always nice. I feel the same way after safely brewing up a particularly tricky mixture. I've near blown my face clean off several times. Oh, while you were gone a little bird told me that %s has managed to create a %s. Don't let him finish before me!", "乾的好！而且你完好無損地回來了。很好，這和我費盡心思做好一瓶特效藥劑的感覺一樣好。我已經激動的不能自已了！哦對了，你不在的時候有一隻小鳥告訴我說 %s 已經制造了 %s 。別讓他超過我！", "tformat")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A dwarf in stained, battered mail armor opens the door.*#WHITE#
Say, you interested in dismembering stuff and getting paid?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一位穿着骯髒破舊鎖甲的矮人開了門。*#WHITE#
說！你是不是對收錢幫人蒐集材料感興趣？]], "_t")
t("Always.", "對！", "_t")
t("By the corpses of the gods, I love adventurers. Was about to become one myself when it suddenly hit me. And by \"it\" I mean \"my wife.\" Har!", "感謝上帝，我喜歡冒險者，我正準備自己也去當個冒險者時被它打了一下，呃……我說的“它”其實是指我老婆，哈！", "_t")
t("What do you propose?", "那……你的建議呢？", "_t")
t("I propose that I give you a list of monster parts to fetch, then you go and fetch them, then I make some blindingly amazing brews with said monster parts, then I get accepted into the Brotherhood of Alchemists.", "我的想法就是，我給你怪物物品清單，然後你給我把它們都找回來。然後我用這些材料做一些很炫的藥劑，之後我就可以加入煉金術士兄弟會了。", "_t")
t("Sounds like a plan.", "聽上去是一個不錯的計劃。", "_t")
t("I make excellent plans. And brews, which the Brotherhood will no doubt make me call 'elixirs' once I'm in. And I'll obey, because they have ways of getting what they want. Now, where were we?", "這可是一個極好的計劃，而這些藥劑，好吧，顯然如果我加入煉金術士兄弟會的話，他們一定會稱我的這些爲“萬能藥”，我會照他們說的話去做的，因爲他們自有他們的一套辦法讓我不得不服從他們的命令……那……我們剛說到哪兒了？", "_t")
t("Aiding you with getting into some Brotherhood. What's in it for me?", "幫你加入那個什麼什麼兄弟會……我能得到什麼回報？", "_t")
t("Oh, easy. You get a swig of each brew, of course. They'll put hair on your chest, and possibly your eyelids and fingernails. And, if your aid proves the deciding factor, then I've got a real treat for you: perhaps the last Taint of Purging left in Maj'Eyal.", "很簡單，每份藥劑我都會讓你先喝個痛快的。喝下這些藥劑會讓你長出有男子漢氣概的胸毛，可能還能長你臉上或者指甲蓋裏。而且，要是你的幫助能起決定性作用的話，我還會額外給你一件真正的寶物：傳說中馬基埃亞爾唯一的墮落印記——清除印記哦！", "_t")
t("I accept.", "我接受了。", "_t")
t("I cannot aid you at this time.", "我現在沒空幫你。", "_t")
t("One last thing. There's a few other fellows angling for the same slot in the Brotherhood that I am. They're not going to be sitting on their hands while we're at work here, so best move quick-like. Now, which of these do you want to help me with first: the Brew of Brawn, the Brew of Stoneskin, or the Brew of Foundations? Or Elixirs, rather. Not Brews. Best get in the habit now, I suppose.", "最後一件事，除我之外還有幾個傢伙對煉金術士兄弟會的這個會員資格虎視眈眈，他們肯定不希望我來坐這個位置的，因此你越快動身越好。現在，你選擇幫我完成哪個藥劑吧：蠻牛藥劑？石膚藥劑？還是領悟藥劑？最好馬上行動，我建議。", "_t")
t("Right, here's the list. Oh, one more thing. Got me some fellas already out hunting for this stuff, and I'll not play favorites. One of them brings me those ingredients before you do, and you're out of luck. Hurry back.", "OK，這裏是材料的清單。哦對了，另外還有一件事，有幾個傢伙已經出發幫我找這些材料了，我一視同仁，要是其中有人先把材料找到給我帶來的話，那你就只能自認倒黴了，動作快點吧。", "_t")
t([[Right, here's the list. Oh, one more thing. Got me some fellas already out hunting for this stuff, and I'll not play favorites. One of them brings me those ingredients before you do, and you're out of luck. Hurry back.

Oh, and one other last thing... if you have the time for another errand, though I've got no reward on this one.]], [[好的，這裏是材料的清單。哦對了，另外還有一件事，有幾個傢伙已經出發幫我找這些材料了，我一視同仁，要是其中有人先把材料找到給我帶來的話，那你就只能自認倒黴了，動作快點吧。

哦，對了，最後還有另外一件事……不知道你感不感興趣，不過這件事可沒有報酬的。]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The door is locked and nobody responds to your knocks*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*門鎖住了，沒人注意到你的敲門聲。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[Leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The mailed dwarf opens his door.*#WHITE#
Aha, my favorite adventurer.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個穿鎖甲的矮人打開了門。*#WHITE#
啊～我親愛的冒險家。]], "_t")
t("I've returned with the ingredients for the %s.", "我回來了，我找到了%s的材料。", "tformat")
t("I've come to offer more aid.", "我來接下一步任務。", "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits.]", "[給他材料。]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He gleefully claps you on the shoulder.*#WHITE#
Ha ha! This is the last one! Stire and Marus and that damned hermit can suck on my beard! And so can my wife! YES, I KNOW YOU CAN HEAR ME. Good work, friend. Let's have them.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他歡快地拍着你的肩膀。*#WHITE#
哈哈！這可是最後一件！斯泰爾和馬魯斯還有那個該死的隱士只能舔我的鬍子了，還有我老婆也是！對沒錯，我知道你能聽見！幹得好夥計，我們開始完成它吧。]], "_t")
t("[Give him the monster bits]", "[給他材料]", "_t")
t("Give me an hour or so to make with the alchemy. Don't go anywhere.", "別走開，給我一個小時的時間去做藥劑。", "_t")
t("I'd invite you inside while you wait, but the she-dwarf's in there, and I've grown fond of you.", "我本來想請你進來等的，不過我老婆在這裏所以……我發覺我有點喜歡你了。", "_t")
t("[Wait]", "[等待]", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The dwarf finally returns with a vial.*#WHITE#
Tastes like Urh'Rok's own piss, but it gets the job done.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個矮人回來了，手裏拿着個藥瓶。*#WHITE#
嘗上去像烏魯洛克的小便……不過總算完成了。]], "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The dwarf finally returns with a vial and a small pouch.*#WHITE#
I put a bit of the good stuff in this one, though it won't do you any favors tomorrow morning. And careful with that Taint of Purging, especially if the wife answers the door the next time you knock. Har!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個矮人終於回來了，手裏拿着一個藥瓶和一個小袋子。*#WHITE#
這裏面我給你帶來個好東西，儘管也許明天早上對你沒什麼用。小心使用這個“清除印記”,如果下次你敲門的時候，是我老婆開門的話，你可要小心點，哈！]], "_t")
t("Thank you. I'll be off.", "謝謝，我走了。", "_t")
t("Bless you adventurers. Which will it be?", "祝福你我的冒險家，你選擇哪一個？", "_t")
t("The %s.", "%s。", "tformat")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("Here's a list of the creature bits I need. Good luck with the murdering!", "這裏有材料清單，祝你好運！", "_t")
t("I'll be off.", "我走了。", "_t")
t([[Here's a list of the creature bits I need. Good luck with the murdering!

Oh, and one other last thing... if you have the time for another errand, though I've got no reward on this one.]], [[這裏有材料清單，祝你好運！

哦，對了，最後還有另外一件事……另外還有一件差事不知道你感不感興趣，不過這件事可沒有報酬的。]], "_t")
t("Well, I'll see if I can help.", "好吧，我看看我能不能幫上忙。", "_t")
t("I'm here for profit, not errands - I have the list and will work on it; sort your own sidejobs out.", "我可不白乾，不是給你做跑腿的，現在拿到材料清單了我會去搞定，別的事情就算了。", "_t")
t("Er, it seems that while you were out, somebody else managed to bring me the ingredients. I've got no reward for you! Sorry about that, but when time is of the essence, 'first come, first served' is the only sensible policy.", "呃，好像你不在的時候，已經有人把材料給我弄來了，我不會再給你獎勵了。很抱歉，不過時間纔是最重要的，“先來者先得”，你得記住這句話。", "_t")
t("Hrmph.", "哼。", "_t")
t([[Well, it's like this, one of my wife's friends has gone missing. A young alchemist in training, called Celia. Thing is, her husband died recently, and the grief done drove her mad. She used to go out to his grave every day, until one day she didn't come back. Personally I don't think she was able to live without him; the two were inseparable. If you get a chance on your travels, could you pass by the mausoleum to the east and check... well, you get the idea.

It's strange what death can do to people, how it can take over their minds. Sometimes they forget it's the living that matter... See she gets a proper burial - treated respectfully, eh?]], [[好吧，事情是這樣的，我老婆的一個朋友最近失蹤了。她是一個實習煉金術士，叫做塞莉婭。最近他丈夫去世了，這件事讓她悲痛欲絕。她每天會到她丈夫的墳墓那裏去，直到有一天她一去不回。我個人認爲她沒了她丈夫活不下去。她們兩人形影不離。要是你途經東邊的墓園的話你能不能去查看一下……你懂的。

我很奇怪死亡到底會對別人產生什麼影響，它又是怎樣佔據人的內心世界的。有時候他們甚至忘了那些活着的人才是最重要的……她丈夫的葬禮舉行的很莊重。]], "_t")
t("I'll do what I can.", "我會去盡力的。", "_t")
t("He points out the location of the graveyard on your map.", "他在你的地圖上指出墓地的位置。", "log")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/angolwen-leader.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A tall woman stands before you. Her fair skin radiates incredible power through her white robe.*#WHITE#
I am Linaniil of the Kar'Krul. Welcome to our city, @playerdescriptor.subclass@. What may I do for thee?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一位身材高大的女人站在你的面前，她白皙的皮膚透過她的白色長袍放射出一股驚人的力量。*#WHITE#
我是卡庫羅爾的萊娜尼爾。歡迎來到我們的城市。@playerdescriptor.subclass@有什麼需要幫忙的麼？]], "_t")
t("I require all the help I can get, not for my sake but for the town of Derth, to the northeast of here.", "我尋求一切能幫助我的力量，不是爲我自己，而是爲了東北地區的德斯小鎮。", "_t")
t("I am ready! Send me to Urkis!", "我準備好了，送我去厄奇斯！", "_t")
t("Urkis has been slain.", "厄奇斯被我幹掉了。", "_t")
t("Nothing for now. Sorry to have taken your time. Farewell, my lady.", "目前沒事，抱歉耽誤了你的時間，再見我的女士。", "_t")
t([[Yes, we have noticed the devastation that happened there. I have sent some friends thence to disperse the cloud, but the true threat lies not there.
He who created this abomination is Urkis. He is a Tempest, a powerful Archmage who channels the storms.
Years ago he went rogue, severing himself from Angolwen. At first he remained quiet, and thus we withheld action, but it seems we have no choice now.
Cleansing the skies will take much time. In the meanwhile, if thou art willing, we can send thee to Urkis' lair to face him.
I will not lie to thee: we can send thee thence, but this could be a death trap, and we have no means for thou to depart his lair, as he lives atop a tall peak in the Daikara mountains.]], [[是的，我們已經注意到了那裏發生的破壞。我已經派了幾個朋友去驅散那裏的烏雲，不過真正的威脅並不在那裏。
造成這場混亂的是厄奇斯。他是一個風暴術士，能夠操縱暴風雨的強大元素法師。
幾年前他叛逃安格利文獨自流浪。起初他保持低調，我們也就沒采取行動，不過現在看來我們沒有選擇了。
淨化天空需要花費不少時間，同時，假如你樂意的話，我們會傳送你到厄奇斯的老巢幫我們直接對付他。
坦白的說，我們送你去的地方，很可能就是一個死亡陷阱，而且我們沒有辦法再把你從他的巢穴裏傳送出去，因爲他的老巢在岱卡拉山脈的最高峯。]], "_t")
t("I need to prepare myself. I will be back soon.", "我要做些準備工作，我馬上就回來。", "_t")
t("I am ready. Send me. I will not let the good people of Derth down.", "我準備好了，傳送我過去吧。我不會再讓德斯人民遭受災難了。", "_t")
t("Good luck to thee. Thou hast the blessings of Angolwen.", "祝你好運，願安格利文的祝福與你同在。", "_t")
t("I see the storm is calmed.  Take this rune as a token of my appreciation.", "我看到風暴平息了。拿走這符文，作爲我的謝意。", "_t")
t("Thank you.", "謝謝。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/angolwen-staves-store.lua"

t("Welcome @playername@ to my shop.", "@playername@，歡迎來到我的商店。", "_t")
t("Let me see your wares.", "讓我看看你的商品吧。", "_t")
t("I am looking for staff training.", "我是來學習法杖格鬥的。", "_t")
t("Sorry, I have to go!", "抱歉，我要走了！", "_t")
t("I can teach you staff combat (talent category Spell/Staff combat).  Learning the basics costs 100 gold, while more intensive tutelage to gain proficiency costs 500 gold.  Once you're proficient, I can teach you more refined techniques for an additional 750 gold.", "我能教授你法杖格鬥(法術/法杖格鬥 技能樹)。學會基礎消耗100金幣，想學的更多就得花上500金幣。當你學會之後，只要750金幣，我就能傳授你一些進階技巧。", "_t")
t("Just give me the basics (reveals locked talent category) - 100 gold.", "只學習基礎（顯示帶解鎖的技能樹）- 100 金幣。", "_t")
t("The staff carver spends some time with you, teaching you the basics of staff combat.", "法杖商人花了一些時間，教授你法杖格鬥的基礎知識。", "logPlayer")
t("He is surprised at how quickly you are able to follow his tutelage.", "他對你學習速度之快感到驚訝。", "logPlayer")
t("Please teach me what I need to know (unlocks talent category) - %d gold.", "請教授我需要知道的一切（顯示已解鎖的技能樹）。 -%d 金幣。", "tformat")
t("The staff carver spends a substantial amount of time teaching you all of the techniques of staff combat.", "法杖商人花了大量時間，教授你法杖格鬥的全部知識", "logPlayer")
t("He is impressed with your mastery and shows you a few extra techniques.", "他對你的掌握程度表示驚訝，並對你展示了一些額外的技巧。", "logPlayer")
t("I'm already proficient, but I want to be an expert (improves talent mastery by 0.2) - 750 gold.", "我已經學會了，但我想成爲一名專家。(增加技能樹係數0.2) - 750 金幣。", "_t")
t(", including some esoteric techniques", "，包括一些祕密流傳的技巧。", "_t")
t("The staff carver spends a great deal of time going over the finer details of staff combat with you%s.", "法杖商人花了大量時間，教授你法杖格鬥的最終知識%s。", "tformat")
t("No thanks.", "不用了，謝謝。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/antimagic-end.lua"

t("\
\
#{italic}##LIGHT_GREEN#*As you drink the potion, your runes start to burn as they fade away, and a terrible agony seems to sink through your skin to your bones, muscles, and heart.  You black out from the pain, and come to a bit later, the runes gone forever.  You feel very ill, and yet...  cleansed.*#{normal}##WHITE#", "#{italic}##LIGHT_GREEN#*當你喝下藥水，你的符文逐漸燃燒着消失，一股可怕的痛苦感從你的皮膚逐漸滲透到骨骼、肌肉、心臟。在痛苦中，你感到一陣暈眩襲來。醒來後，你發現身上的符文永遠消失了。你感到無比疲憊……然而，你終於被自然的力量所淨化了。*#{normal}##WHITE#", "_t")
t([[Excellent! You truly prove that no mage-wrought flame or storm can stand against blade and arrow! Come, learn our ways. You are ready.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*he gives you a potion.*#WHITE#
Drink this. We extract it from a very rare kind of drake. It will grant you powers to fight and cancel magic, but never again will you be able to use magic.%s]], [[乾的好！你真正證明了那些魔法產生的火焰和風暴根本不是劍與矢的對手！來吧，加入我們的陣營，你已經準備好了。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*他給你一瓶藥劑。*#WHITE#
喝下它，這是我們從一種非常稀有的龍身上提取出來的。它會使你擁有反抗魔法和與魔法戰鬥的能力，不過你以後也不能使用魔法了。%s]], "tformat")
t("Thank you. I shall not let magic triumph! #LIGHT_GREEN#[you drink the potion]", "謝謝！我不會再讓魔法取得勝利了！ #LIGHT_GREEN#[你喝下了藥劑。]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ardhungol-end.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*As the monstrous spider falls you see something... moving in her belly until it explodes! A tall black man steps out of the spewed guts, surrounded by a golden light.*#WHITE#
By the Sun! I thought I would never again see a friendly face!
Thank you. I am Rashim, and I am in your debt.
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在巨大蜘蛛倒下之後你看到什麼東西……在它的胃裏蠕動！在它的胃炸開之後，一個高大黝黑的男子從炸碎的內臟裏走了出來，全身圍繞着金光。*#WHITE#
讚美太陽！我以爲我再也見不到一個友善的面孔了！
謝謝你，我是拉希姆，我欠你一份人情。
]], "_t")
t("I have been sent by your wife. She was worried for you.", "我是你妻子派來的，她很擔心你。", "_t")
t([[Ah, my dear heart!
Well, now that I am free I will create a portal to the Gates of Morning. I think I've seen enough spiders for the rest of my life.]], [[啊～我親愛的！
好吧，現在我自由了，我會開啓一個到晨曦之門的傳送門。我想我這輩子再也不想見到蜘蛛了。]], "_t")
t("Lead the way!", "請帶路！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ardhungol-start.lua"

t("Good day to you.", "你好啊！", "_t")
t("Good day to you too.", "你好！", "_t")
t("I have heard you are a great hero of the west. Could you help me, please?", "我聽說你是來自西部的英雄，你能幫我一個忙嗎？", "_t")
t("Maybe, what is it about?", "也許可以，是什麼事情呢？", "_t")
t("I have got enough problems sorry.", "我很忙，抱歉。", "_t")
t("Welcome back, @playername@.", "歡迎回來，@playername@。", "_t")
t("I have found your husband. I take it he made it home safely?", "我找到你的丈夫了，他安全回家了麼？", "_t")
t("I've got to go. Bye.", "我得走了，再見。", "_t")
t([[My husband, Rashim, is a Sun Paladin. He was sent to clear the spider lair of Ardhungol to the north of this town.
It has been three days now. He should be back by now. I have a feeling something terrible has happened to him. Please find him!
He should have a magical stone given by the Anorithil to create a portal back here, yet he did not use it!]], [[我丈夫，拉希姆，是一個太陽騎士。他被派去小鎮北部清除蜘蛛巢穴阿爾德胡格。
已經三天了，他應該回來了。我有種預感他肯定遇到了麻煩。請幫我找到他！
他應該有星月術士給他的魔法石，可以用來開啓返回這裏的傳送門的，到目前爲止他還沒用過！]], "_t")
t("I will see if I can find him.", "我會看看我是否能找到他的。", "_t")
t("Spiders? Eww, sorry, but he is probably dead now.", "蜘蛛？呃……抱歉，說不定他現在已經死了。", "_t")
t("Yes, yes he did! He said he would have died if not for you.", "是的，他回來了！他說要不是你幫忙他就死定了。", "_t")
t("It was nothing.", "小事一樁。", "_t")


