section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/command-staff.lua"

t("Greetings. How can I help you?", "你好，我能幫你什麼忙麼？", "_t")
t("Hurry up and make with the foe-blasting.", "快點，我們要去把敵人打爆。", "_t")
t("O wise wielder, instruct me that I may better serve you.", "智慧的長者，請指示我讓我更好的爲您服務。", "_t")
t("Make amends, magic-user, for the harm ye have wrought is beyond compare.", "贖罪吧，法師們，你們帶來了罄竹難書的危害。", "_t")
t("You really could have chosen a better home for me, you know. I was reasonably happy in my old crystal. This stick smells like armpit.", "要知道，你可以給我找個更好的環境。現在嘛，我還是留在我原來的舊水晶裏吧，這根法杖有一股狐臭的味道。", "_t")
t("Tremble before the might of Telos!", "在泰勒斯的強大力量下顫抖吧！", "_t")
t("It is not yet your place to command such a staff as this. To do so invites obliteration.", "你無法對其釋放掌控法杖。這樣做會帶來破壞。", "_t")
t("Call on which aspect of the staff?", "召喚哪種法杖的元素力量？", "_t")
t("Oh, I was once a mighty Eldritch Channeler. Mighty and absentminded, as it turns out. Had a bit of a mishap with an Inverted Kugala's Soul-infusion technique. Long story short, my soul is now stuck in this stick, and the soul I was working with... well, I don't rightly know where he got to. But I hope we never meet him.", "哦，我曾經是一個強大埃爾德里奇主宰者。事實證明，那時的我，強大而又不可一世。某次事故扭曲了古加拉的靈魂鑲嵌技術。長話短說吧，我的靈魂被困在了這根棍子裏——和我曾經研究的靈魂一起……好吧，我也不知道它從何處而來。但是我希望我們能和它永別。", "_t")
t("Argh! Bollocksed up a tricky bit of soul magic and the fool that I was supposed to be imprisoning for all eternity flitted away. My body, like all the targets of my spells, intended or otherwise, got reduced to elementary particles. Fortunately, I had this soul-cage of a staff all prepped and ready for a stray soul, so I'm not completely gone. But enough chit-chat. Let's fry somebody.", "哈！拜某次實驗事故和那個被永久囚禁的傻X靈魂所賜，我的身體，像所有其他被法術轟擊過的物體一樣，有意或無意，灰飛煙滅了。幸運的是，我還有這根可以容納靈魂的法杖容器，所以我沒有完全湮滅。好了，不多說了，讓我們去打爆敵人吧！", "_t")
t("My old master-- who, though a powerful enchanter, did not compare to you and your glory-- saw fit to imprison me in this fine staff to aid him in his work. Alas, he is long gone, but I despair not, for I have found a mighty new master.", "我的舊主人——雖然他的法術很強大，但卻比不上你和你的榮耀——他認爲，把我囚禁在這根法杖裏可以爲他更好的服務。唉，雖然他已經不復存在了，但我並不感到絕望，因爲我找到了一個強大的新主人。", "_t")
t("I am a portion of the very spirit of the world that was ripped free during the Spellblaze. I speak that I might enlighten those who bear me.", "我是在魔法大爆炸期間被撕裂靈魂的一部分。我可以教導給你所需的知識，只要你願意聆聽我。", "_t")
t("What's the good of immortality if you can't even speak? No archmage worth his salt is going to concoct some immoral life-after-death scheme without including some sort of capacity for making his opinions known. And, by the way, your energy manipulation techniques are on the same level as those of my average pair of shoes. Best study up if you don't want to die forgotten and incompetent.", "如果不能說話，那這樣的永生還有何意義？凡是想要達到永生不死的大法師，沒有一個留下一種方法讓自己的偉大知識永久流傳。而且，順便說一句，你的能量操縱水平只配給我提鞋，給我仔細的聽着，如果你不想因爲遺漏我說的話而死的不明不白。", "_t")
t("Of course. Which aspect?", "當然。哪一種？", "_t")
t("I highly recommend the mage aspect and the fire element. You're not going to find anything better for turning a piece of meat into a cloud of vapor.", "我強烈推薦術士類火焰元素。你不會找到比這更好的能讓一塊肉變成蒸汽的方法了。", "_t")
t("I live to serve-- though my use of the word 'live' is perhaps loose here.", "我畢生爲你效勞——雖然“畢生”在這裏對於我而言並不是那麼準確。", "_t")
t("Choose wisely. Powers beyond your comprehension will tolerate only so much interference in their carefully-laid natural order.", "明智地進行選擇。只有那些仔細維護自然秩序的人才會被那些超越你們理解的力量所容忍。", "_t")
t("Back in my day, we didn't need to go changing our staves around willy-nilly. We picked an element and stuck with it, by the gods.", "在我的時代，我們並不需要用棍子揮來揮去來施法。我們只需要抓取一種元素，就可以任意的使用它——像諸神一樣。", "_t")
t("error!", "錯誤！", "_t")
t("Certainly. You should be impressed, by the way, that I can do such a thing. Most lesser practitioners of my art would have difficulties with this. What shall I change?", "當然。順帶一提，我可以做的事情會讓你印象深刻。大多數較弱者實踐我的藝術時會感覺有困難。我要不要改變一下？", "_t")
t("Fine, as long as it leads to blasting something soon. What do you want me to change?", "很好，只要它能快速的引爆某物。你要我換成什麼？", "_t")
t("Choose different aspect", "選擇其他領域", "_t")
t("Call forth which element?", "召喚哪種元素", "_t")
t("staff", "法杖", "_t")
t("How is it that you speak?", "你居然能說話？", "_t")
t("I'd like you to bring forth a different aspect.", "我希望切換到其他領域。", "_t")
t("I'd like to alter your basic properties.", "我希望改變你的基礎屬性。", "_t")
t("Never mind.", "別介意。", "_t")
t("I see.", "我知道了", "_t")


