section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/corruptor-quest.lua"

t([[Wait, @playerdescriptor.subclass@!
I see you are a worthy opponent, powerful indeed. I can see, and feel, your mastery of the eldritch crafts.
We are the same.]], [[等等，@playerdescriptor.subclass@！
我看你是個有價值的對手，夠強力。我可以看到和感覺到，你對魔法技藝的熟練程度。
我們可是同行。]], "_t")
t("What do you mean 'the same'?", "“同行”是什麼意思？", "_t")
t("I am nothing like you. Die!", "誰跟你是同行，去死吧！", "_t")
t([[We both know the strength of the arcane; we both hunger for power. There is so much I have discovered, so much I could teach you.
This place is special. The veil of reality is thin here, forever shattered by the Spellblaze. We are taking advantage of this; we can draw on the power,
leeching from this place, to better ourselves, to bring forth the dominion of magic!]], [[我們都瞭解奧術的力量，我們也都渴求力量。我已經發現了很多東西，有很多我可以教你。
這個地方很特別。這裏與真理只隔着一層薄薄的面紗，已經被魔法大爆炸永久削弱了。我們可以利用它。
我們可以吸收力量，從這個地方吸取，來強大我們自身，使我們成爲魔法的主宰！]], "_t")
t("So be it. Die, and give me your power!", "如此的話。去死吧，把你的能量給我！", "_t")
t("The world suffered from the Spellblaze enough. Magic must serve people, not enslave them. I will not listen to you!", "魔法大爆炸已經給這個世界帶來了足夠的災難。魔法必須服務於人，而不是奴役別人。我不會聽你的！", "_t")
t("What do you propose, then?", "那你的建議呢？", "_t")
t([[Let us end this meaningless fight. Have you ever heard of a group of people called the Ziguranth?
These rambling madmen think magic should not be permitted to exist! They fear us; they fear our powers.
Let us join forces and crush the fools!]], [[讓我們停止這無畏的爭鬥。你有沒有聽說過一羣叫做伊格蘭斯的人？
這些瘋子認爲魔法不應該存在！他們害怕我們，害怕我們的力量。
讓我們聯合起來幹掉那些笨蛋！]], "_t")
t("Magic shall triumph!", "魔法必勝！", "_t")
t("Magic has a purpose. Those men are wrong, but you seem much worse.", "魔法自有它的用處。那些人想錯了，不過你比他們錯的更離譜。", "_t")
t("Then you must leave... THIS WORLD! DIE!", "那麼你必須離開……這個世界！死吧！", "_t")
t([[Good. Before your... untimely arrival we were preparing an attack on the Ziguranth main training camp, on the southern beach of the sea of Sash.
Come with us; let's destroy them!
I will open a portal to Zigur and the massacre shall begin!]], [[很好。在你到來之前，我們正準備攻擊伊格蘭斯在薩希之海南部沙灘的主要訓練營地。
和我們一起，去幹掉他們！
我會打開去伊格的傳送門，然後大屠殺就要開始了！]], "_t")
t("I am ready!", "我準備好了！", "_t")


