section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/derth-attack-over.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A Halfling comes forth from his hiding place.*#WHITE#
You killed them all? Are we safe now? Oh, please tell me this was a bad dream!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一個半身人從他的藏身地走了出來。*
#WHITE#你把它們都殺了？現在我們安全了麼？噢，真希望你告訴我這只是一場惡夢！]], "_t")
t("Be at ease. I have dispatched those monstrosities. Do you know where they came from or what they wanted?", "別害怕，我已經趕跑了那些怪物。你知道他們是從哪兒來的，想幹什麼嗎？", "_t")
t([[From nowhere! From the sky!
I do not know. I was tending my crop just outside the town when I heard screaming. As I entered the town, I saw the dark cloud over here. Those... those... things were coming from it in blasts of lightning!]], [[不知道從哪兒來的！從天上！
我真不知道。我當時正在農田裏照看我的莊稼，然後我聽到了哭喊聲。當我走進村子，我看到了天上的烏雲。那些……那些……東西正噴出一道道閃電！]], "_t")
t("It seems they have stopped coming for now. I will look for somebody who could help dispose of this nefarious cloud.", "好像它們現在不會再來了。我會找到人來幫我弄清楚這些邪惡烏雲的來龍去脈的。", "_t")
t([[Thank you! You have saved many people today!
I have heard of rumours of a reclusive town of wise and powerful men somewhere in the mountains. Maybe they could help? If they even exist...
There are also those Zigur-something people that claim to fight magic. Why are they not here?!]], [[多謝！你今天救了很多人！
我聽到有一個傳說，說在羣山中隱居着一羣足智多謀的賢士。也許他們能幫上忙？要是他們真的存在的話……
還有一羣被稱爲什麼伊格的號稱與魔法戰鬥的人，那些人怎麼不在這兒？！]], "_t")
t("You mean the Ziguranth. That would be me.", "你是指伊格蘭斯吧？我就是。", "_t")
t("I will not let you down.", "我不會讓你死的。", "_t")
t("Well then please do something about this evil magic!", "那就對這邪惡的魔法做點什麼吧！", "_t")
t("I will!", "我會的！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/dreadfell-ambush.lua"

t([[#VIOLET#*As you come out of the Dreadfell, you encounter a band of orcs*#LAST#
You! Give us the staff NOW and we might offer you a quick death!]], [[#VIOLET#*當你從恐懼王座裏出來的時候，你遭遇了一隊獸人。*
#LAST#你！馬上把你手上的法杖給我們！我們會讓你死的痛快一點！]], "_t")
t("What are you talking about?", "你說什麼？！", "_t")
t("Why would you want it?", "你們想要它幹什麼？", "_t")
t("Do not play dumb with Ukruk! ATTACK!", "你少裝蒜了，攻擊！", "_t")
t("That is not your concern! ATTACK!", "這和你無關，攻擊！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[Attack]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[攻擊]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/east-portal-end.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A robed Human is waiting for you when you step out of the portal.*#WHITE#
Well met, @playername@!
I am Meranas, Herald of Angolwen. I have come here at the request of King Tolak, who worried when you didn't return.
We have been watching Tannen for some time, and were pleased to see you reveal his true nature-- and stop him. For this we are grateful, and I think we can pay you back.
We have studied his portal research, and if you give me the components I will create the portal for you, here and now!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*當你走出傳送門時，一個穿着長袍的人正在那裏等着你。*
#WHITE#見到你很高興，@playername@!
我是馬雷納斯，安格利文的傳令官。我接到托拉克國王的命令在此等候你，他一直很擔心你。
我們已經觀察了泰恩一段時間，我們非常高興地看到你揭露了他的真面目並阻止了他。因此我們非常榮幸地請你回來。
我們已經分析了他關於傳送門的研究，如果你把那些相關的部件給我，我就可以立即給你創造一個傳送門，就是此時此刻。]], "_t")
t("Yes, Tannen was not exactly friendly. I thank you for your help. Here are the components. [hand him the diamond and the athame]", "是的，泰恩的確不是個好人。感謝你的幫助，這些就是傳送門的部件。[交給他寶石和祭祀匕首。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/eidolon-plane.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a humanoid shape filled with 'nothing'. It seems to stare at you.*#WHITE#
I am the Eidolon and you are not welcome here!
No matter how you came to this plane, #{bold}#DO NOT COME BACK!
NOW BEGONE!
#{normal}#
.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前的虛無之中站着一個人形的東西。它似乎在盯着你看。*#WHITE#
我是艾德隆，你在這裏不受歡迎!
不論你怎樣來到這裏, #{bold}#不要再來!
快滾!
#{normal}#
.]], "_t")
t("...", "……", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a humanoid shape filled with 'nothing'. It seems to stare at you.*#WHITE#
I have brought you here on the instant of your death. I am the Eidolon.
I have deemed you worthy of my 'interest'. I will watch your future steps with interest.
You may rest here, and when you are ready I will send you back to the material plane.
But do not abuse my help. I am not your servant, and someday I might just let you die.
As for your probable many questions, they will stay unanswered. I may help, but I am not here to explain why.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前的虛無之中站着一個人形的東西。它似乎在盯着你看。 *#WHITE#
在你死亡的瞬間我把你帶到這裏，我是艾德隆。
我一直在注視着你，觀察你的價值還有你的未來。
你可以在這裏休息一會，當你準備好時，我可以送你回到你原來所在的物質世界。
不過不要濫用我給你的幫助，我可不是你的僕人，也許有一天我也會讓你死去。
也許你有很多問題要問，不過我不會回答，我可以幫助你，但我不是來給你解釋爲什麼的。]], "_t")
t("Thank you. I will rest for a while.", "謝謝你，我在這裏休息一會。", "_t")
t("Thank you. I am ready to go back!", "謝謝你，我已經準備好回去了。", "_t")
t("Thank you, but I fear I will not survive anyway, can you send me back somewhere else please?", "謝謝你，不過我回去也是死，能不能送我到別的地方？", "_t")
t("Thank you, but I fear I will not survive anyway, can you send me back somewhere else on the level please?", "謝謝你，不過我回去也是死，能不能送我到這一層的別的地方？", "_t")
t("Thank you, I am ready to go back!", "謝謝你，我已經準備好回去了。", "_t")
t("Thank you, but I am weary of this life, I wish no more, please let me go.", "謝謝你，但是我厭倦了這樣的命運，請讓我安息吧。", "_t")
t([[It seems the threads of time and space have been disrupted...
I will try to send you to safety.]], [[似乎時間線和空間已經被打亂……
我會將你送到安全的地方。]], "_t")
t("Thanks.", "多謝。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*It seems to stare at you in weird way.*#WHITE#
I...had plans for you, but I cannot go against your free will. Know that you had a destiny waiting for you.
Are you sure?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*它看着你，對你的回答感到不可思議。*#WHITE#
我……本來爲你有別的安排，但是我不能違揹你的意願，要知道你還有使命沒有完成。
你確定嗎？]], "_t")
t("Just let me go please.", "請讓我死吧。", "_t")
t("asked the Eidolon to let %s die in peace", "請求艾德隆讓 %s 安息。", "tformat")
t("her", "她的", "_t")
t("him", "他", "_t")
t("brought down by Eidolon", "被艾德隆殺死", "_t")
t("No actually, perhaps life is still worth it!", "不，也許還是值得活下去的。", "_t")


