section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/elisa-orb-scrying.lua"

t("You immerse your mind in the Way and let knowledge flow in.", "你專注你的意志與維網取得鏈接，使信息傳輸進來。", "_t")
t("[You do not gain any knowledge.]", "[你沒有獲得任何信息。]", "_t")
t("You pause and recall past memories.", "你停了下來，開始回憶過去。", "_t")
t("[Images and knowledge flow in.]", "[圖像和知識涌現了出來。]", "_t")
t("[You do not recognize anything new.]", "[你沒想起什麼新東西。]", "_t")
t("Oh, hi @playername@, have you got something new to show me?", "啊，你好 @playername@ ，有什麼新東西給我看麼？", "_t")
t("Yes, Elisa, could you have a look at these objects please? [show her the items the orb could not identify]", "是的，埃莉薩，你能幫我看看這個物品麼？[給她看看水晶球無法辨識的物品。]", "_t")
t("Err, no... sorry, I just wanted to hear a friendly voice.", "呃，沒有……抱歉，我只想聽聽你甜美的聲音。", "_t")
t("Not yet sorry!", "沒事，抱歉！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*You hear something akin to a muffled giggle*#WHITE#
Oh, you are #{bold}#SOOOO#{normal}# cute!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你聽到捂着嘴巴咯咯笑的聲音*#WHITE#
呵，你實在#{bold}#太……#{normal}# 可愛了！]], "_t")
t("Goodbye, Elisa!", "再見，埃莉薩！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/elisa-shop.lua"

t([[Let's see what have you got here...
%s

That is very nice, @playername@!]], [[讓我看看你找到了什麼好東西……
%s

真是不錯，@playername@!]], "tformat")
t("Thank you, Elisa!", "謝謝你，埃莉薩！", "_t")
t("Hello friend, what can I do for you?", "你好朋友，我能幫你什麼忙麼？", "_t")
t("Could you have a look at these objects, please? [show her your unidentified items]", "你能幫我看看這些物品麼？[將未辨識的物品給她看。]", "_t")
t("Nothing, goodbye.", "沒事，再見。", "_t")
t([[Wait, @playername@, you seem to be quite the adventurer. Maybe we can help one another.
You see, I #{bold}#LOOOVVVEEEE#{normal}# learning new lore and finding old artifacts of power, but I am not exactly an adventurer and I would surely get killed out there.
So take this orb (#LIGHT_GREEN#*she gives you an orb of scrying*#WHITE#). You can use it to talk to me from anywhere in the world! This way you can show me your new shiny findings!
I get to see many interesting things, and you get to know what your items do. We both win! Isn't it sweet?
Oh yes, the orb will also identify mundane items for you, as long as you carry it.]], [[，你看上去像一個冒險家。也許你能幫助另外一個人。
你看，我#{bold}#熱愛#{normal}#學習新的手稿和蒐集擁有古老力量的物品。不過我自己並不是一個真正的冒險家，而且我如果出去冒險的話肯定會被殺掉。
所以拿着這個水晶球吧，(#LIGHT_GREEN#*她給了你一個辨識水晶*#WHITE#)。你可以在世界的任何一個角落用這個水晶球和我聯絡。要是你發現什麼閃閃發光的好東西，你就可以隨時隨地給我看了！
我可以看到有趣的東西，而你又能知道你所獲得的是什麼裝備，一舉兩得！聽上去應該不錯吧？
而且，你只要攜帶着它，它也會幫你辨認普通物品。]], "_t")
t("Woah, thanks, Elisa. This is really nice!", "哇～太好了，埃莉薩，這可太棒了！", "_t")


