section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/escort-quest.lua"

t([[At the last moment you invoke the power of nature.  The portal fizzles and transports @npcname@ to Zigur.
You can feel Nature thanking you.]], [[最後你召喚了自然之力，傳送門發出嘶嘶的響聲，將 @npcname@ 傳送到了伊格。
你可以感覺到自然對你的感激。]], "_t")
t([[Thank you, my friend. I do not think I would have survived without you.
Please let me reward you:]], [[謝謝你我的朋友，要是沒有你我就死定了。
請讓我報答你吧：]], "_t")
t("There you go. Farewell!", "那就這樣吧，再見！", "_t")
t("Thank you.", "謝謝。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/fallen-aeryn.lua"

t("%s grabs her amulet and disappears in a whirl of arcane energies.", "%s 抓住了她的項鍊在一股奧術漩渦中消失了。", "logPlayer")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*She lies nearly dead at your feet*#WHITE#
So, now you will kill me and complete the cycle of destruction?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*她倒在你的腳下，快要死了。*#WHITE#
那麼，現在你會殺死我然後完成毀滅法陣？]], "_t")
t("What are you talking about? Why did you attack me?", "你在說什麼？你爲什麼要攻擊我？", "_t")
t("Speak and I might spare you. Why did you attack me?", "說吧，也許我會饒恕你，你爲什麼要攻擊我？", "_t")
t([[You.. you do not know?
A few hours after you entered this place a raid of orcs fell upon us. They were not alone -- demons walked among them. We were overwhelmed! Utterly destroyed!
My land is no more! All because you could not stop them at the Charred Scar! You failed us! People died to protect you, and you failed!
#LIGHT_GREEN#*She starts to weep...*#WHITE#]], [[道？
你進入這個地方几個小時以後，獸人突襲了我們。他們不是單獨來的——還有大量惡魔跟隨着他們。我們寡不敵衆！被徹底擊敗了！
我的領地已經不復存在！全都是因爲你，沒能在灼燒之痕阻止他們！你背叛了我們！這麼多人爲你而死，而你卻背叛了我們！
#LIGHT_GREEN#*她開始哭泣……*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t("I know my mistakes and I intend to correct them. Please let me pass. I cannot save your people, but I can make their deaths mean something!", "我知道我所犯下的錯誤，我會設法彌補。請讓我通過這裏，我沒辦法拯救你的人民，但是我不會讓他們白白犧牲！", "_t")
t("[kill her]", "[殺了她]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/gates-of-morning-main.lua"

t("What may I do for you?", "我能幫你什麼忙麼？", "_t")
t("Lady Aeryn, at last I am back home! [tell her your story]", "艾琳女士，我終於回家了！[告訴她你的故事]", "_t")
t("Tell me more about the Gates of Morning.", "告訴我更多有關晨曦之門的事。", "_t")
t("Before I came here, I happened upon members of the Sunwall in Maj'Eyal. Do you know of this?.", "在我來這裏之前，我在馬基·埃亞爾遇到了太陽堡壘的成員。你知道這件事麼？", "_t")
t("I need help in my hunt for clues about the staff.", "我在蒐集法杖的線索，我需要你的幫助。", "_t")
t("I have destroyed the leaders of all the Orc Prides.", "我已經消滅了所有獸人部落的首領。", "_t")
t("I am back from the Charred Scar, where the orcs took the staff.", "我從灼燒之痕回來，獸人在那裏搶走了法杖。", "_t")
t("A dying paladin gave me this map; something about orc breeding pits. [tell her the story]", "一位瀕死的太陽騎士給了我這張地圖，關於獸人育種棚。[告訴她整個事情]", "_t")
t("Sorry, I have to go!", "抱歉，我要走了！", "_t")
t([[@playername@! We thought you had died in the portal explosion. I am glad we were wrong. You saved the Sunwall.
The news about the staff is troubling. Ah well, please at least take time to rest for a while.]], [[@playername@！我們以爲你在傳送門爆炸的時候死了，幸好我們想錯了，你拯救了太陽堡壘。
有關法杖的消息有點麻煩，那麼，至少請你休息一會兒吧。]], "_t")
t("I shall, thank you, my lady.", "我會的，謝謝你，我的女士。", "_t")
t([[There are two main groups in the population here, Humans and Elves.
Humans came here in the Age of Pyre. Our ancestors were part of a Mardrop expedition to find what had happened to the Naloren lands that sunk under the sea. Their ship was wrecked and the survivors landed on this continent.
They came across a group of elves, seemingly native to those lands, and befriended them - founding the Sunwall and the Gates of Morning.
Then the orc pride came and we have been fighting for our survival ever since.]], [[這裏主要有兩個種族，人類和精靈。
人類在派爾紀便來到了這裏。我們的祖先是馬卓普探險隊的一部分人員，他們是去調查沉入海底的納魯精靈大陸祕密的。他們的船失事沉沒，僥倖活下來的人就漂流到了這塊大陸。
他們碰到了一羣精靈，似乎是這塊大陸的原住民，他們成爲了朋友並一起生活，創建了太陽堡壘和晨曦之門。
後來獸人來到了這裏，從那時開始我們就一直與他們戰鬥。]], "_t")
t("Ahh, so they survived? That is good news...", "啊，那麼他們還活着，真是一個好消息……", "_t")
t("Go on.", "繼續。", "_t")
t("Well, actually...", "呃……事實上……", "_t")
t([[The people you saw are likely the volunteers of Zemekkys' early experiments regarding the farportals.
He is a mage who resides here in the Sunwall, eccentric but skilled, who believes that creation of a new farportal to Maj'Eyal is possible.
Aside from a few early attempts with questionable results, he hasn't had much luck. Still, it's gladdening to hear that the volunteers for his experiments live, regardless of their location. We are all still under the same Sun, after all.

Actually... maybe it would benefit you if you meet Zemekkys. He would surely be intrigued by that Orb of Many Ways you possess. He lives in a small house just to the north.]], [[你看到的那些人很可能是伊莫克斯關於遠古傳送門實驗的志願者。
他是居住在太陽堡壘的一個法師，脾氣古怪但是很有能力，他堅信可以創造一個遠古傳送門達到馬基·埃亞爾。
除了他早期的一些嘗試獲得了一點可疑的結論外，他並不算走運。不過還是很高興聽到他的實驗對象還活着的消息，儘管立場上我們不一致，不過畢竟是生活在同一片陽光下的人。

事實上……也許你去見伊莫克斯對你沒什麼好處。他一定會被你拿着的多元水晶球吸引住的。他就住在北面的小屋裏。]], "_t")
t("Maybe I'll visit him. Thank you.", "也許我會見見他，謝謝。", "_t")
t([[The news has indeed reached me. I could scarce believe it, so long have we been at war with the Pride.
Now they are dead? At the hands of just one @playerdescriptor.race@? Truly I am amazed by your power.
While you were busy bringing an end to the orcs, we managed to discover some parts of the truth from a captive orc.
He talked about the shield protecting the High Peak. It seems to be controlled by "orbs of command" which the masters of the Prides had in their possession.
He also said the only way to enter the peak and de-activate the shield is through the "slime tunnels", located somewhere in one of the Prides, probably Grushnak.
]], [[我的確已經得到了消息，真令人難以置信，我們和獸人已經戰鬥的太久了。
他們現在都死了麼？僅憑一個 @playerdescriptor.race@ 的力量？我對你的力量非常驚奇。
當你忙於解決那些獸人的時候，我們設法從那個獸人俘虜那裏獲得了一些線索。
他提起了有關巔峯保護罩的事。似乎那個護罩是受“指令水晶球”操控的，那些指令水晶就在獸人各大部落首領的手中。
他還說想要進入頂層並關閉護罩的唯一通道是“史萊姆通道”，位於某一個獸人部落內，有可能是格魯希納克的部落。
]], "_t")
t("Thanks, my lady. I have not been able to find all of the orbs of command in my travels; could you have some of your men search for me?", "謝謝，我的女士。我沒能找到所有的指令水晶球；請問你可以讓你們的人來幫我尋找一下嗎？", "_t")
t("Thanks, my lady. I will look for the tunnel and venture inside the Peak.", "謝謝，我的女士，我會尋找史萊姆通道，探尋前往巔峯的道路。", "_t")
t([[I have already sent parties to clear out the remainder of the prides as you progressed, and have instructed to keep a sharp eye out for any orbs of command you may have missed.
	Which do you not have? I can check with the parties if they found any. Our sources indicate that you should have four: one of Undeath, one of Destruction, one of Dragons, and one of Elemental might.]], [[我們已經派出部隊，清理那些被你所擊潰的部落的殘軍。我命令他們仔細搜查，確保找到可能落下的任何指令水晶球的蹤影。
	你缺少了什麼水晶球？我會去問問他們，看看他們有沒有找到什麼線索。我們得到情報，應該有四顆指令水晶球：亡靈水晶球，毀滅水晶球，巨龍水晶球，元素水晶球]], "_t")
t("The orb of Undeath.", "亡靈水晶球。", "_t")
t("The orb of Destruction.", "毀滅水晶球。", "_t")
t("The orb of Dragons.", "巨龍水晶球。", "_t")
t("The orb of Elements.", "元素水晶球。", "_t")
t("Thanks, my lady, that is all of them. I will look for the tunnel and venture inside the Peak.", "謝謝你，我的女士，看來我已經集齊了所有的水晶球。我會尋找史萊姆通道，打開通向巔峯的道路。", "_t")
t("Ah yes, my men have found that in Rak'Shor Pride. Here: ", "啊，是的，我們的人在拉克·肖部落找到了這個水晶球。給你：", "_t")
t("Ah yes, my men have found that in Vor Pride. Here: ", "啊，是的，我們的人在沃爾部落找到了這個水晶球。給你：", "_t")
t("Ah yes, my men have found that in Grushnak Pride. Here: ", "啊，是的，我們的人在格魯希納克部落找到了這個水晶球。給你：", "_t")
t("Ah yes, my men have found that in Gorbat Pride. Here: ", "啊，是的，我們的人在加伯特部落找到了這個水晶球。給你：", "_t")
t("Thank you, my lady.", "謝謝你，我的女士。", "_t")
t([[As much as I would like to help, our forces are already spread too thin; we cannot provide you with direct assistance.
But I might be able to help you by explaining how the Pride is organised.
Recently we have heard the Pride speaking about a new master, or masters. They might be the ones behind that mysterious staff of yours.
We believe that the heart of their power is the High Peak, in the center of the continent. But it is inaccessible and covered by some kind of shield.
You must investigate the bastions of the Pride. Perhaps you will find more information about the High Peak, and any orc you kill is one less that will attack us.
The known bastions of the Pride are:
- Rak'shor Pride, in the west of the southern desert
- Gorbat Pride, in a mountain range in the southern desert
- Vor Pride, in the northeast
- Grushnak Pride, on the eastern slope of the High Peak]], [[我真的很想幫助你，不過我們的軍隊已經十分分散而且薄弱，我們無法直接給你提供軍事援助。
但是我盡我所能，告訴你獸人部落的組成結構。
最近我們接到情報說獸人選舉了新的領袖，他們很有可能就是搶奪神祕法杖的幕後主使人。
我們相信，他們的力量中心就是巔峯，在這個大陸的中部區域。不過它被某種護罩保護無法進入。
你必須調查獸人部落的各個基地，或許你能找到更多有關巔峯的線索，而且你每殺死一個獸人，我們就少了一個攻擊我們的敵人。
已知的獸人部落有：
- 拉克·肖部落，在南部沙漠的西面。
- 加伯特部落，在南部沙漠的羣山之中。
- 沃爾部落，在東北方。
- 格魯希納克部落，在通往高塔之巔的東部山坡上。]], "_t")
t("I will investigate them.", "我會調查這些地方。", "_t")
t("Aeryn points to the known locations on your map.", "艾琳在你的地圖上指出了位置。", "logPlayer")
t([[One more bit of aid I might give you before you go. Your tale has moved me, and the very stars shine with approval of your relentless pursuit. Take their blessing, and let nothing stop you in your quest.
	#LIGHT_GREEN#*She touches your forehead with one cool hand, and you feel a surge of power*
	]], [[在你出發之前我還有一樣東西可以幫助你，我被你的故事所感動，閃耀的羣星將賜予你“無盡追蹤”的能力。帶上這個祝福，不要讓任何事物阻礙你的使命。
	#LIGHT_GREEN#*她用冰涼的手觸摸了你的額頭，你感覺到身上涌現出一股力量。*
	]], "_t")
t("I'll leave not a single orc standing.", "我會將那些獸人趕盡殺絕。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#You have learned the talent Relentless Pursuit.", "#VIOLET#你學會了無盡追蹤技能。", "logPlayer")
t("I have heard about that; good men lost their lives for this. I hope it was worth it.", "我已經聽說了，很多好人爲此犧牲了生命，但願這是值得的。", "_t")
t("Yes, my lady, they delayed the orcs so that I could get to the heart of the volcano. *#LIGHT_GREEN#Tell her what happened#WHITE#*", "是的，我的女士。他們拖住了敵人，使我能夠前進至火山中心。*#LIGHT_GREEN#告訴她發生的事。#WHITE#*", "_t")
t("I am afraid I was too late, but I still have some valuable information. *#LIGHT_GREEN#Tell her what happened#WHITE#*", "恐怕我太遲了，不過我還是帶來了有價值的消息。*#LIGHT_GREEN#告訴她發生的事。#WHITE#*", "_t")
t([[Sorcerers? I have never heard of them. There were rumours about a new master of the Pride, but it seems they have two.
Thank you for everything. You must continue your hunt now that you know what to look for.]], [[法師會？我從來沒聽說過他們。傳說部落有了一個新的領袖，看樣子現在應該有兩個。
感謝你所做的事，你必須進一步搜尋更多的消息，你知道你該去做什麼。]], "_t")
t([[Sorcerers? I have never heard of them. There were rumours about a new master of the Pride, but it seems they have two.
I am afraid with the power they gained today they will be even harder to stop, but we do not have a choice.]], [[法師會？我從來沒聽說過他們。傳說部落有了一個新的領袖，看樣子現在應該有兩個。
恐怕依他們現在所具有的力量我們更難阻止他們了，不過我們別無選擇。]], "_t")
t("I will avenge your men.", "我會替你的人報仇！", "_t")
t("Ah! This is wonderful! Finally a ray of hope amidst the darkness. I will assign my best troops to this. Thank you, @playername@ - take this as a token of gratitude.", "太好了！一線希望的曙光終於穿過了黑暗。我會派我最好的軍隊去那裏。多謝你了，@playername@——以此物來表示我們對你的感激。", "_t")
t("Good luck.", "祝你們好運。", "_t")
t("Aeryn gives you: %s", "艾琳給了你：%s", "logPlayer")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/gates-of-morning-welcome.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a beautiful woman clad in shining golden armour*#WHITE#
Stop! You are clearly a stranger! Where do you come from? The Gates of Morning are the last bastion of freedom in these lands, so who are you? A spy?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一位穿着金光閃閃鎧甲的美麗女士。*#WHITE#
站住！陌生人！你是從哪裏來的？晨曦之門是這塊大陸最後的自由聖地，你到底是誰？你是一個間諜麼？]], "_t")
t("My lady, I am indeed a stranger in these lands. I come from the west, from Maj'Eyal.", "我的女士，沒錯對於這個大陸來說我的確是一個陌生人，我來自西方，馬基·埃亞爾。", "_t")
t("Sorry, I have to go!", "抱歉，我要走了！", "_t")
t([[Maj'Eyal! For many years have we tried to contact your people. We always failed.
In any event, what is your purpose here?]], [[馬基·埃亞爾！我們的人民嘗試了很多年與你們取得聯繫，但都失敗了。
不管怎樣，你來這裏是幹什麼的？]], "_t")
t("It seems that I am stranded in these unfamiliar lands. #LIGHT_GREEN#*Tell her about your hunt for orcs and your encounter with Fillarel.*#WHITE#", "好像我在這塊陌生的大陸上迷路了。#LIGHT_GREEN#*告訴她關於你追殺獸人並遭遇了菲拉瑞爾的事。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Sun Paladins? What do you mean? We know of no such thing where I come from.", "太陽騎士？你是什麼意思？我並不知道我是從哪裏來的。", "_t")
t([[We are the mighty warriors of the Sunwall, channeling the power of the Sun and merging it with martial training.
For hundreds of years, we stood between the Orc Pride and the free people. Our numbers are diminishing, but we will stand firm until our last breath.]], [[我們是太陽堡壘裏強大的戰士，汲取太陽的力量，並將其注入到我們的軍事訓練中。
數百年來，我們一直爲了人民的自由與獸人戰鬥，我們的成員人數在不斷減少，不過我們會戰鬥至最後一刻。]], "_t")
t("You have a noble spirit, my lady.", "你的精神十分高貴，我的女士。", "_t")
t([[Orcs! Ah! Well then this is your lucky day. This whole continent is swarming with Orcs. They have united as the Orc Pride and, according to rumour, their masters are powerful.
They roam the lands freely, ever assaulting us.
@playername@, you have helped one of ours. I grant you access to the Gates of Morning and name you friend of the Sunwall.]], [[獸人！啊！那你非常走運，這個大陸到處都是獸人，他們組成了獸人部落，有傳言，他們的首領非常強大。
他們在這片大陸上四處劫掠，不斷襲擊我們。
@playername@，你已經幫了我們一個忙了，歡迎你來到晨曦之門，你是我們太陽堡壘的朋友。]], "_t")
t("Thank you, my lady.", "謝謝你，我的女士。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/golbug-explains.lua"

t([[#VIOLET#*As you open the door you notice a huge orc in the distance, covered in both flames and ice.*#LAST#
@playerdescriptor.race@! You should never have come! Your doom awaits!
The Orc Pride will never yield to anybody! They have their precious and there is nothing you can do.]], [[#VIOLET#*當你打開門，你注意到遠處一個巨大的獸人，同時被冰與火包圍着。*
#LAST#@playerdescriptor.race@！你不應該來這裏！你的死期到了！
獸人部落不會爲任何人讓步！他們有他們的榮耀，你什麼也做不了！]], "_t")
t("The Orc Pride obeys a master? I see... 'pride' indeed!", "整個獸人部落屈服於一個吸血鬼領主？我明白了……還真是“榮耀”啊！", "_t")
t("The Pride chooses its allies. It has no master! ATTACK!", "部落只會選擇自己的盟友，我們從不屈服於人！攻擊！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[Attack]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[攻擊]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/jewelry-store.lua"

t("Imbue which ring?", "鑲嵌哪枚戒指？", "_t")
t("Use which gem?", "使用哪顆寶石？", "_t")
t("%s failed to craft with %s and %s!", "%s將%s和%s融合的時候失敗了！", "logPlayer")
t("This costs %d gold, you need more gold.", "這將花費 %d 金幣，你需要更多金幣", "tformat")
t("This will cost you %s gold, do you accept?", "這將花費你 %s 金幣，你確認接受嗎？", "tformat")
t("%s %s ring", "%s %s戒指", "tformat")
t("weird", "奇怪的", "_t")
t("Imbue which amulet?", "鑲嵌哪個項鍊？", "_t")
t("Use which first gem?", "使用哪顆做第一個寶石？", "_t")
t("Use which second gem?", "使用哪顆做第二個寶石？", "_t")
t("#CRIMSON#Your timetravel has no effect on pre-determined outcomes such as this.", "#CRIMSON#你的時間穿越對這種已經預設好的結局沒有任何作用。", "_t")
t("Limmir needs more gold for the magical plating.", "利米爾需要更多錢用於鍍金工藝", "_t")
t("Not enough money", "金錢不足", "_t")
t("Imbue cost", "鑲嵌價格", "_t")
t("You need to use %s gold for the plating, do you accept?", "你需要花費 %s 金幣用於鍍金，你確認接受嗎？", "tformat")
t("Limmir's Amulet of the Moon", "利米爾的月亮吊墜", "_t")
t("%s creates: %s", "%s創造了：%s", "logPlayer")
t("Welcome, @playername@, to my shop.", "歡迎來我的商店，@playername@。", "_t")
t("Let me see your wares.", "讓我看看你的商品吧。", "_t")
t("I am looking for special jewelry.", "我在找一些特殊的珠寶。", "_t")
t("So you can infuse amulets in this place?", "據說你可以給項鍊附魔？", "_t")
t("I have found this tome; it looked important.", "我找到了這本手冊，看上去好像很重要。", "_t")
t("Sorry I have to go!", "抱歉，我必須得走了。", "_t")
t([[Then you are at the right place, for I am an expert jeweler.
If you bring me a gem and a ring, I can create a new ring imbued with the properties of the gem.  The original traits of the ring will be lost in the process but new ones of similar quality will be generated.
There is a small fee dependent on the level of the ring, and you need a quality ring to use a quality gem.]], [[你算找對地方了，我可是一個珠寶專家。
如果你給我找來一顆寶石和一枚戒指，我可以幫你把寶石的力量鑲嵌到戒指裏去。這顆戒指裏面原來所有的屬性會丟失掉，不過會也生成一些質量相似的新屬性。
不過根據不同戒指品質我要收取一小筆費用。你得尋找高品質的戒指來用於高品質的寶石。]], "_t")
t([[Yes! Thanks to you this place is now free from the corruption. I will stay on this island to study the magical aura, and as promised I can make you powerful amulets.
Bring me a an amulet and two different gems and I will turn them into a powerful amulet, though the original properties of the amulet will be lost.
I will not make you pay a fee for it since you helped me so much, but I am afraid the ritual requires a gold plating. This should be equal to about 1000 gold pieces.]], [[對！感謝你讓這個地方從腐化中脫離了出來。我會留在這個島上學習魔法光環，我會遵守我的諾言幫你製作一枚強力的項鍊。
給我帶來一條項鍊還有兩顆不同的寶石，我會利用它們給製作一枚強力的項鍊。
你幫了我那麼多，這次我不收任何費用。不過製作過程中需要鍍金工藝，這大約得花費1000金幣。]], "_t")
t("I need your services.", "我需要你的服務。", "_t")
t("Not now, thanks.", "暫時不用，謝了。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He quickly looks at the tome and looks amazed.*#WHITE# This is an amazing find! Truly amazing!
With this knowledge I could create potent amulets. However, it requires a special place of power to craft such items.
There are rumours about a site of power in the southern mountains. Old legends tell about a place where a part of the Wintertide Moon melted when it got too close to the Sun and fell from the sky.
A lake formed in the crater of the crash. The water of this lake, soaked in intense Moonlight for eons, should be sufficient to forge powerful artifacts!
Go to the lake and then summon me with this scroll. I will retire to study the tome, awaiting your summon.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他快速瀏覽了那本手冊，露出了驚訝的表情。*#WHITE# 這真是神奇的發現！太神奇了！
有了這些知識我就能製造更強大的項鍊了。不過這需要一個特殊的地方來完成製作過程。
傳言在南部山脈之中有個地方充滿能量。有個古老的傳說，當冬月與太陽距離太接近的時候它的一部分從空中掉落了下來並融入了大地，使那個地方充滿能量。
在墜落的地方形成了一個湖泊，湖水吸收了萬年月光的力量，應該有足夠的神力來製作這件藝術品。
去找到那個湖泊，然後使用這個卷軸將我召喚過去，從現在開始我要潛心研修你的這本手冊，等待你召喚我的那一刻。]], "_t")
t("I will see if I can find it.", "我看看能不能找到那個地方。", "_t")


