section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/keepsake-caravan-destroyed.lua"

t([[#VIOLET#*As the last member of the caravan lies dying, you look at him and see the hate that fills his eyes.*#LAST#
We should have finished you off that day. You deserved no mercy!]], [[#VIOLET#*作爲商隊最後的犧牲者，你看到他的雙眼中滿是仇恨。*#LAST#
我們那天應該殺了你。你不應該得到憐憫！]], "_t")
t("And I will show you no mercy. #LIGHT_GREEN#[Kill him]#LAST#", "那就讓我來告訴你什麼是無情。 #LIGHT_GREEN#[殺了他]#LAST#", "_t")
t("I am sorry. #LIGHT_GREEN#[Help him]#LAST#", "對不起。 #LIGHT_GREEN#[幫助他]#LAST#", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#*Before you can help him, he collapses to the ground and dies.*#LAST#", "#VIOLET#*你剛想扶起他時，發現他已經失去了最後一線生機。*#LAST#", "_t")
t("...", "……", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/keepsake-kyless-death.lua"

t([[#VIOLET#*Kyless lies dying on the floor. In his hand he holds a book.*#LAST#
Please! Before I die I have one request. Destroy the book. It wasn't me. The book brought this on us. It must be destoyed!]], [[#VIOLET#*克里斯躺在地板上奄奄一息。他的手裏還握着一本書。*#LAST#
求求你！在我死前我有一個請求！毀掉這本書。其實不是我，是這本書將災難帶給了我們。它必須被毀掉！]], "_t")
t("I will. #LIGHT_GREEN#[destroy the book]#LAST#", "好的。 #LIGHT_GREEN#[毀掉那本書]#LAST#", "_t")
t("I'm sorry but I need it. #LIGHT_GREEN#[keep the book]#LAST#", "對不起我需要它。#LIGHT_GREEN#[拿走這本書]#LAST#", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#*You destroy the book. When you finish you look up and see that Kyless is already dead.*#LAST#", "#VIOLET#*你毀掉了這本書。當你做完這一切後，你發現克里斯已經死了。*#LAST#", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#*You place the book in your pack. When you finish you look up and see that Kyless is already dead.*#LAST#", "#VIOLET#*你將這本書放到了揹包裏。當你做完這一切後，你發現克里斯已經死了。*#LAST#", "_t")
t("Goodbye, Kyless.", "再見，克里斯。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/last-hope-elder.lua"

t("Welcome, @playername@, to Last Hope. Traveler, please be quick as my time is precious.", "歡迎你，@playername@，歡迎來到最後的希望。旅行者，你最好抓緊時間，我的時間很寶貴。", "_t")
t("I have found a strange staff in my travels (#LIGHT_GREEN#*describe it in detail*#LAST#)  It looked very old and very powerful. I dared not use it.", "我在旅途中找到了一根法杖。(#LIGHT_GREEN#*詳細說明事情的來龍去脈*#LAST#) 它看上去很古老但擁有強大的力量。我不敢使用它。", "_t")
t("The hunt for the staff took me to a continent far to the east, accessible only by magic portal. I've recently returned by just such a portal, and I come bearing instructions on how to construct a similar portal here in Last Hope to make the return journey possible. I'm sure the Elves there would welcome trade with the west.", "追蹤這根法杖的時候我到達了遠東的一個大陸，只有通過魔法傳送門才能到達那兒。剛纔我就用這樣的一個傳送門返回這裏，我現在就是來告訴大家如何製造一個類似的傳送門從最後的希望通往遠東大陸，我相信那裏的精靈會很樂意同我們進行貿易往來。", "_t")
t("Nothing, excuse me. Bye!", "沒事，抱歉打擾了，再見！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He remains silent for a while*#WHITE# Indeed you were right to come here.
The staff you describe reminds me of an artifact of great power from ancient times. May I see it?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他沉默了一段時間*#WHITE# 的確你來這裏是對的。
你描述的法杖讓我想起了一件在古代有強大力量的神器，能讓我看一下麼？]], "_t")
t("Here it is. #LIGHT_GREEN#*Tell him about the encounter with the orcs*#LAST# You should keep it. I can feel its power and it would be safer if it were guarded by the armies of the kingdom.", "就是這個。 #LIGHT_GREEN#*告訴他有關被獸人部隊伏擊的事。*#LAST# 你應該拿着它。我能感受到它的力量，法杖在王國軍隊的保護下才是安全的。", "_t")
t("I am afraid I lost it. #LIGHT_GREEN#*Tell him about the encounter with the orcs*", "抱歉我沒能把它帶來。 #LIGHT_GREEN#*告訴他有關被獸人部隊伏擊的事。*", "_t")
t("I had it briefly but have lost it somehow.  It could have been some orcs I encountered ...", "我本來有它，但不知怎麼弄丟了。大概是被我遇到的獸人搶走了……", "_t")
t([[I am truly astonished by your strength; surviving that encounter was an epic feat.
As for the orcs, it is deeply troubling.  We have not seen any for eighty years... could they have come from the far east?
Anyway, thank you again, @playername@, for your help.]], [[我很驚訝你的力量，能在襲擊中活下來可是一項壯舉。
關於獸人，這就有點麻煩了。我們已經80年沒有見過他們了……難道他們是從遠東大陸過來的？
不管怎樣，還是非常感謝，@playername@, 感謝你的幫助。]], "_t")
t([[Orcs?! In the west?! This is deeply alarming! We have not seen any for nearly eighty years. They must have come from the far east...
But do not let me trouble you; you brought important news and you are lucky to be alive.]], [[獸人？在西部大陸？！這非常令人擔憂！我們幾乎已經80年沒有見到過獸人了，他們肯定是從遠東大陸來的……
不過你不必自責，你帶來了重要的消息，而且你還能活下來已經很幸運了。]], "_t")
t("Thank you, my lord.", "謝謝你，閣下。", "_t")
t([[We have heard rumours from the Dwarves that there may still be an orc presence deep in the old kingdom of Reknor, in the Iron Throne.
I know you have been through a lot, but we need somebody to investigate and determine if there is a connection with the staff.]], [[有來自矮人的傳說，在鋼鐵王座古王國瑞庫納深處可能仍有獸人的蹤跡。
我知道你已經經歷了很多事，不過我們還是需要一個人去調查一下，確認他們與法杖之間的聯繫。]], "_t")
t("I will check the mines.", "我會去礦坑那裏調查。", "_t")
t("That's extraordinary! I know a number of merchant princes who will salivate at the idea of new trade routes opening. But tell me, how fares your quest for the staff?", "真不可思議！對於新商路的開闢，我知道一些富商知道這個消息後肯定會高興的直流口水。不過你還沒告訴我，關於法杖的事情，進行的怎麼樣了？", "_t")
t("The staff is recovered and the culprits slain. They will trouble us no more. [tell him the whole story]", "法杖已經復原，罪犯已經被處決，他們不會再困擾我們了。[告訴他整個事情經過。]", "_t")
t("The hunt continues. The construction of this portal will be of great assistance in the staff's recovery.", "還在繼續調查，傳送門的建立對於法杖的修復會有極大的幫助。", "_t")
t("Excellent! Well then, concerning this fascinating portal, I'm afraid that men have largely forgotten whatever they once knew about the great magics of old. I know of only one man in these lands who might be able to help you, a wise man and recent arrival to Last Hope named Tannen. He claims to hail from Angolwen, a supposed haven for practitioners of magic and mysticism. He arrived just months ago with fabulous wealth and has already constructed his own tower in the northern part of the city. I know little of him, but if he is to be believed, then he is your best hope.", "太棒了！但是，關於這個有趣的傳送門，恐怕很多人早已將古老魔法遺忘了。我只知道在這個大陸上有一個人可能能夠幫助你，一個最近纔來到最後希望的智者。他的名字叫泰恩，他自稱他是從安格利文來的，那是傳說中的神祕魔法港灣，他幾個月前剛和一個富商來到這裏，他在城市北部邊境建造了他的塔樓。我對他了解不多，不過如果他是個可信之人的話，應該是最有可能幫上你的。", "_t")
t("In that case, let us proceed as quickly as possible. Now, concerning this fascinating portal. I'm afraid that men have largely forgotten whatever they once knew about the great magics of old. I know of only one man in these lands who might be able to help you, a wise man and recent arrival to Last Hope named Tannen. He claims to hail from Angolwen, a supposed haven for practitioners of magic and mysticism. He arrived just months ago with fabulous wealth and has already constructed his own tower in the northern part of the city. I know little of him, but if he is to be believed, then he is your best hope.", "那樣的話，我們就長話短說，關於這個有趣的傳送門，恐怕很多人早已將古老魔法遺忘了。我只知道在這個大陸上有一個人可能能夠幫助你，一個最近纔來到最後希望的智者。他的名字叫泰恩，他自稱他是從安格利文來的，那是傳說中的神祕魔法港灣，他幾個月前剛和一個富商來到這裏，他在城市北部邊境建造了他的塔樓。我對他了解不多，不過如果他是個可信之人的話，應該是最有可能幫上你的。", "_t")
t("Thank you.", "謝謝。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/last-hope-lost-merchant.lua"

t([[Ah, my #{italic}#good#{normal}# friend @playername@!
Thanks to you I made it safely to this great city! I am planning to open my most excellent boutique soon, but since I am in your debt, perhaps I could open early for you if you are in need of rare goods.]], [[啊, 我 #{italic}#親愛的#{normal}# 朋友 @playername@!
多虧了你我安全回到了這個偉大的城市！ 我的精品商店過些日子正打算開張營業。不過既然我欠你個人情，要是你需要一些稀有物品的話也許我可以爲你提前開張。]], "_t")
t("\
By the way, ", "順帶一提，", "_t")
t("during our escape I found the plans for an #YELLOW#Ambush Trap#LAST#", "在逃亡過程中我找到了個好點子—— #YELLOW#伏擊陷阱#LAST#", "_t")
t("\
You would not happen to be interested, by any chance?", "你應該會對它感興趣吧？", "_t")
t(" and while", "，同時在", "_t")
t(" organizing my inventory, I came across some #YELLOW#Smelly Toxin#LAST# that a colleague claimed could actually turn creatures to stone.  Truly exotic!", " 我整理貨物時, 我發現了一些 #YELLOW#石化毒劑#LAST# ，據說能把生物變成石頭。 真的很棒！", "_t")
t("while", "在", "_t")
t("\
I eventually plan to arrange a truly unique service for the most discerning of customers. If you come back later when I'm fully set up I shall be able to order for you something quite marvellous. For a perfectly #{italic}#suitable#{normal}# price, of course.", "\
我準備爲最有眼光的那位顧客提供一件真正獨特的服務。如果你過會兒回來，我將做好充分準備後給你一個大大的驚喜。而且價格絕對#{italic}#公道#{normal}#哦！當然！", "_t")
t("\
Oh my friend, good news! As I told you I can now request a truly #{italic}#unique#{normal}# object to be crafted just for you. For a truly unique price...", "噢我的好朋友，我告訴過你我可以爲你打造一件真正的 #{italic}#史詩#{normal}# 物品，專門爲你量身定做哦，而且價格非常公道……", "_t")
t("Yes please, let me see your wares.", "好吧，讓我看看你的貨物。", "_t")
t("What about the unique object?", "不如說說那個特殊物品？", "_t")
t("Ambush Trap?  Sounds useful.", "伏擊陷阱？聽上去很不錯", "_t")
t("Smelly Toxin?  What kind of smell?", "石化毒素？怎麼樣？", "_t")
t("Sorry, I have to go!", "抱歉，我要走了！", "_t")
t([[You know, I have asked here and there and it happens to be a very rare thing this contraption...
But since you have saved me, I'm willing to part from it for only 3000 gold pieces, a real bargain!]], [[你要知道，我問遍了每個地方都沒發現有相同的東西。
不過，既然你救了我的命，給我3000金幣我就把它轉讓給你。這可是很划算的！]], "_t")
t("Expensive, but I will take it.", "雖然很貴，不過我要了。", "_t")
t("...", "……", "_t")
t("Nice doing business with you my friend. There you go!", "和你做生意真愉快！", "_t")
t([[Ungrol told me this substance contains some exceedingly rare components.
"More Toxin than Medicine" he said.  Allas, he had not the funds to buy it.  On the other hand, because of our special relationship, I'm willing to let you have it #{italic}#at cost#{normal}# -- only 1500 gold pieces!]], [[溫格勒發現這種物質含有某些稀有成分，
“比毒藥還要毒” ，但他沒錢買下來。 基於我們的良好關係，我很願意賣給你，#{italic}#只需要#{normal}# -- 1500 金幣!]], "_t")
t("Fairly pricey, but seems useful.  We have a deal!", "有點貴，不過應該能派上用場。我要了！", "_t")
t("That price ... er stuff really stinks ...", "這個價格 ... 還是算了吧...", "_t")
t("Here you are.  Just be sure not to get any on yourself!", "給你了。別灑在自己身上了", "_t")
t("Thanks.", "多謝。", "_t")
t("I normally offer this service only for a truly deserved price, but for you my friend I am willing to offer a 20% discount - #{italic}#only#{normal}# 4000 gold to make an utterly unique item of your choice.  What do you say?", "對於這項服務，只有到了合理的價位我纔會願意提供給別人，不過對你，我的朋友，我準備給你打個20%的折扣—— #{italic}#只要#{normal}# 4000 金幣就可以打造一個真真正正你特有的裝備哦，怎麼樣？", "_t")
t("Why, 'tis a paltry sum - take my order, man, and be quick about it!", "什麼？這點小錢無所謂，趕緊給我弄出來吧！", "_t")
t("Yes, please!", "好的，請吧。", "_t")
t("HOW MUCH?! Please, excuse me, I- I need some fresh air...", "多少錢？！呃……抱歉，我……我得出去呼吸一下新鮮空氣……", "_t")
t("Not now, thank you.", "現在不用，再見。", "_t")
t("dragonbone wand", "龍骨魔杖", "_t")
t("dragonbone totem", "龍骨圖騰", "_t")
t("voratun torque", "沃瑞鉭項圈", "_t")
t("I've changed my mind.", "我決定不買了。", "_t")
t("#CRIMSON#Your timetravel has no effect on pre-determined outcomes such as this.", "#CRIMSON#你的時間穿越對這種已經預設好的結局沒有任何作用。", "_t")
t([[Do you want to name your item?
%s]], [[你想要命名你的物品嗎？
%s]], "tformat")
t("Yes, please.", "是的。", "_t")
t("Name", "名稱", "_t")
t("Name your item", "給你的裝備起名", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#The merchant carefully hands you: %s", "#LIGHT_BLUE#商人小心的交給了你：%s", "log")
t("No thanks.", "不用了，謝謝。", "_t")
t("Oh I am sorry, it seems we could not make the item your require.", "啊真抱歉，這東西我們可做不了。", "_t")
t("Oh, let's try something else then.", "好吧，我們試試別的東西。", "_t")
t("Oh well, maybe later then.", "好吧，以後再說。", "_t")
t("Which kind of item would you like ?", "你喜歡什麼類型的裝備？", "_t")
t("*This store does not appear to be open yet*", "*這個商店好像還沒開張。*", "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/last-hope-melinda-father.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A man talks to you from inside, the door half open. His voice is sad.*#WHITE#
Sorry, the store is closed.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*門半掩着，一個男人的聲音傳了出來，他的聲音聽上去很悲傷。*#WHITE#
抱歉……商店已經關門了……]], "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("@playername@! My daughter's savior!", "@playername@! 我女兒的救命恩人", "_t")
t("Hi, I was just checking in to see if Melinda is all right.", "你好，我就是來看望一下梅琳達的。", "_t")
t("Hi, I would like to talk to Melinda please.", "你好，我想和梅琳達談談。", "_t")
t("Sorry, I have to go!", "抱歉，我要走了！", "_t")
t("Please take this. It is nothing compared to the life of my child. Oh, and she wanted to thank you in person; I will call her.", "請帶上這個。沒什麼比我孩子的生命更重要了。哦，她想親自表達她對你的謝意。我去叫她出來。", "_t")
t("Melinda", "米琳達", "_t")
t("Thank you.", "謝謝。", "_t")
t("Melinda's father gives you: %s", "梅琳達的父親交給了你：%s", "logPlayer")
t("#CRIMSON#Your timetravel has no effect on pre-determined outcomes such as this.", "#CRIMSON#你的時間穿越對這種已經預設好的結局沒有任何作用。", "_t")
t("@playername@! #LIGHT_GREEN#*She jumps for joy and hugs you while her father returns to his shop.*#WHITE#", "@playername@! #LIGHT_GREEN#*當她父親返回商店時，她高興地跳了起來，給了你一個擁抱。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("I am glad to see you are fine. It seems your scars are healing quite well.", "看到你一切安好真是太好了。你的傷疤看上去也已經痊癒了。", "_t")
t("I am glad to see you well. Take care.", "很高興看到你沒事，多保重。", "_t")
t([[Yes it has mostly healed, though I still do have nightmares. I feel like something is still lurking.
Ah well, the bad dreams are still better than the fate you saved me from!]], [[是的，基本上好了，儘管晚上有時我還會做噩夢。我覺得心裏總不得安寧。
不過，這比起你救我之前的處境，確實好多了！]], "_t")
t("Should I come across a way to help you during my travels, I will try to help.", "如果在我的旅程中能幫到你的話，我會盡力的。", "_t")
t("Thank you, you are most welcome.", "謝謝，你真是個好人。", "_t")
t("Most certainly, so what are your plans now?", "那麼，你現在有什麼計劃麼？", "_t")
t("Hi @playername@! I am feeling better now, even starting to grow restless...", "你好 @playername@! 我感覺好多了，現在我甚至覺得精神煥發……", "_t")
t("So what are your plans now?", "那麼，你有什麼計劃麼", "_t")
t("About that, I was thinking that maybe you'd like to go out with me sometime ...", "呃，我覺得你也許喜歡和我出去走走……", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Melinda appears at the door and kisses you*#WHITE#
Hi my dear, I'm so happy to see you!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*梅琳達出現在門口，親吻了你*#WHITE#
親愛的，見到你真好！]], "_t")
t("I am still looking out for an explanation of what happened at the beach.", "我仍在爲那天在海灘的事情找個解釋。", "_t")
t("About what happened on the beach, I think I have found something.", "關於海灘那件事，我想我發現了什麼。", "_t")
t([[I do not know yet, my father won't let me out until I'm fully healed. I've always wanted to do so many things.
That is why I got stuck in that crypt, I want to see the world.
My father gave me some funds so that I can take my future into my own hands. I have some friends in Derth, maybe I will open my own little shop there. ]], [[我不知道，我的父親不會讓我出門的，除非我痊癒了。但我總想做許多事情。
這也許是我爲什麼會被關在地窖的原因吧，我想親眼看看這個世界。
我的父親給了我一些錢，這樣我就能掌握自己的未來。我在德斯鎮有幾個朋友，或許，我能在那裏開一家小商店]], "_t")
t("I have seen how you fought those corruptors, the way you destroyed their magic. I want to learn to do the same, so that such horrors never happen again. To anyone.", "我看到了你是怎樣對抗那些墮落法師的，看到了你摧毀他們的邪惡魔法的方法。我也想做同樣的事，這樣的話，這種噩夢就不會再上演了。", "_t")
t([[Or maybe, well I suppose I can trust you with this, I've always secretly dreamed of learning magic. Real magic I mean not alchemist tricks!
I've learnt about a secret place, Angolwen, where I could learn it.]], [[或許，呃，我可以相信你吧，我一直想學魔法。是真正的魔法，而不是煉金術士的小把戲！
我聽說過一個祕密的地方，叫做安格利文，在那裏我就能學習魔法。]], "_t")
t("Derth has its up and downs but I think they could do with a smart girl yes.", "德斯鎮有自己的起起落落，但我相信像你這樣的聰明女孩一定能生活下去。", "_t")
t("Thanks!", "謝謝！", "_t")
t("You wish to join our noble crusade against magic? Wonderful! I will talk to them for you.", "你希望加入我們高尚的反魔組織麼？太好了！我會和他們說的。", "_t")
t("I happen to be welcome among the people of Angolwen, I could say a word for you.", "我正巧在安格利文還比較受歡迎，我會幫你帶話的。", "_t")
t("That would be very nice!", "那真是太好了！", "_t")
t("What?!? Just because you rescued me from a moderately-to-extremely gruesome death, you think that entitles you to take liberties?!", "什麼？就因爲你救了我的命，我就得把自己給你？", "_t")
t("GIRL", "女孩", "_t")
t("GUY", "男孩", "_t")
t("Uhh, sorry I hear my father calling, see you.", "呃，不好意思，我聽到我的父親在喊我，再見。", "_t")
t("WHY AREN'T WOMEN ATTRACTED TO ME I'M A NICE %s.", "怎麼會有女人對我不感興趣呢？我可是個很好的%s。", "tformat")
t("Just a minute, I was just...", "等一會，我只是...", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*She looks at you cheerfully.*#WHITE#
Just kidding. I would love that!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*她興奮地看着你*#WHITE#
開玩笑的，我很喜歡!]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[walk away with her]#WHITE#What about a little trip to the south, from the coastline we can see the Charred Scar Volcano, it is a wonderous sight.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[朝她走了過去]#WHITE#我們去南邊旅行吧，從魔法大爆炸之痕的海岸開始，那是一段美好的風景。", "_t")
t("But... ok goodbye.", "但是……好吧，再見。", "_t")
t("Joke's on you really, goodbye!", "開什麼玩笑，再見了！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*You take Melinda in your arms and press her against you. The warmth of the contact lightens your heart.*#WHITE#
I feel safe in your arms. Please, I know you must leave, but promise to come back soon and hold me again.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你把梅琳達緊緊擁在懷裏，身體的接觸使你感受到她的體溫照亮了你的內心。*#WHITE#
在你的懷抱中我覺得很安全，我知道你要走了，求求你，答應我你會盡快回來看我，擁抱我。]], "_t")
t("I think I would enjoy that very much. #LIGHT_GREEN#[kiss her]#WHITE#", "我想我很樂意這麼做。#LIGHT_GREEN#[親吻她]#WHITE#", "_t")
t("That thought will carry me in the dark places I shall walk. #LIGHT_GREEN#[kiss her]#WHITE#", "對你的思念會伴隨我在黑暗中前行。#LIGHT_GREEN#[親吻她]]#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Oh, I am sorry. I think you are mistaken. I was only trying to comfort you.", "噢，抱歉，我想你誤會了。我只是想安慰你。", "_t")
t("Oh, sorry, I was not myself. Goodbye, then. Farewell.", "對不起，我失態了。那麼，再見吧。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Melinda looks worried*#WHITE#
Please tell me you can help!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*梅琳達面露憂愁*#WHITE#
請幫幫我!]], "_t")
t("Yes, I think so. Some time ago I assumed ownership of a very special home... #LIGHT_GREEN#[tell her the Fortress story]#WHITE#", "呃，不久前，我擁有了一座非常特別的房子... #LIGHT_GREEN#[告訴她關於堡壘的事]#WHITE#", "_t")
t([[An ancient fortress of a mythical race?! How #{bold}#exciting#{normal}#!
And you say it could cure me?]], [[一座神祕種族的古代堡壘#{bold}#真不可思議！#{normal}#!
你覺得那會治療我麼]], "_t")
t("The Fortress seems to think so. I know this might sound a bit .. inappropriate .. but you would need to come live there, at least for a while.", "堡壘應該是可以的。我知道，這聽上去有一點，呃，不太合適。不過，你應該到那裏去住上一小段時間。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*She looks at you cheerfully*#WHITE#
Ah the plan to sleep with me is finally revealed!
Shhh you dummy, I thought we were past such silliness, I will come, both for my health and because I want to be with you.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*She kisses you tenderly*#WHITE#]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*她興奮地看着你*#WHITE#
你的計劃終於暴露了！
傻瓜，兩個大傻瓜。我當然會去，不僅爲了我的健康，也爲了和你在一起。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*她溫柔地和你接吻*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t("Then my lady, if you will follow me. #LIGHT_GREEN#[take her to the Fortress]", "我的女士，如果你願意，就跟我來吧。#LIGHT_GREEN#[帶她去堡壘]", "_t")


