section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/mage-apprentice-quest.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a young man, a novice mage by his looks*#WHITE#
Good day to yo...#LIGHT_GREEN#*He stares at you and starts to run away fast!*#WHITE#
Do not kill me please!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一個年輕人，看上去像是一個法師學徒。*#WHITE#
你好……#LIGHT_GREEN#*他盯着你看了一會，然後撒腿就跑！*#WHITE#
請不要殺我！]], "_t")
t("...", "……", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a young man, a novice mage by his looks*#WHITE#
Good day to you, fellow traveler!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一個年輕人，看上去像是一個法師學徒。*#WHITE#
你好啊，旅行者！]], "_t")
t("What brings an apprentice mage out into the wilds?", "一個法師學徒在荒郊野外幹什麼？", "_t")
t("I found this artefact; it looks powerful and arcane infused. Maybe it would be enough?", "我發現了這件充滿奧術能量的神器，看上去很強大，應該夠了吧？", "_t")
t("So you have enough magical items now?", "你找到足夠的魔法物品了嗎？", "_t")
t("Sorry I have to go!", "抱歉，我必須得走了。", "_t")
t("Ahh, my story is a sad one... I should not trouble you with it, my friend.", "啊，我的故事說來讓人傷心……算了，我不應該打擾你的，我的朋友。", "_t")
t("It is no trouble at all! Please tell me!", "沒關係的，告訴我吧！", "_t")
t("Ok, bye then!", "好的，那麼再見。", "_t")
t([[Well, if you insist...
I am a novice mage, as you might have noticed, and my goal is to be accepted by the people of Angolwen and be taught the secrets of the arcane.]], [[好吧，假如你堅持的話……
我是個法師學徒，你可能已經看出來了。我的目標是被安格利文的人接納然後他們教給我奧術的祕密。]], "_t")
t("Who are the people of Angolwen?", "安格利文的人是誰？", "_t")
t("Ah yes, Angolwen, I have called it home for many years...", "啊，對的，安格利文，很多年來我一直稱呼它爲我的家……", "_t")
t("Well, good luck, bye!", "那麼，祝你好運，再見！", "_t")
t([[The keepers of ar... err, I do not think I am supposed to talk about them... sorry, my friend...
In any case, I must collect many items. I have some already but I am still looking for an arcane-infused artefact. You do not happen to have one, I imagine... Well, if you do, tell me please!]], [[他們是世界上僅存的法……唉呀，我好像說了什麼不該說的話……抱歉，我的朋友……
無論如何，我必須得蒐集些物品。這些都沒問題了，不過我還需要找到一件充滿奧術能量的神器。我想你不會恰巧有一件吧……當然如果你有的話，請告訴我！]], "_t")
t([[I hope I will too...
In any case, I must collect many items. I have some already but I am still looking for an arcane-infused artefact. You do not happen to have one, I imagine... Well, if you do, tell me please!]], [[我希望我也是……
無論如何，我必須得蒐集些物品。這些都沒問題了，不過我還需要找到一件充滿奧術能量的神器。我想你不會恰巧有一件吧……當然如果你有的話，請告訴我！]], "_t")
t("I will keep that in mind!", "好的，我記住了！", "_t")
t("No way, bye!", "算了吧，再見！", "_t")
t([[Let me examine it.
Oh yes, my friend, this is indeed a powerful artefact! I think that it should suffice to complete my quest! Many thanks!]], [[讓我試試看。
喔，是的，我的朋友，的確是一件強力神器！我想就憑這個我應該可以交差了！非常感謝！]], "_t")
t("Well, I cannot use it anyway.", "好的，對我來說沒什麼用。", "_t")
t([[Ah yes! I am so glad! I will be able to go back to Angolw...err... Oh well, I guess I can tell you; you deserve it for helping me.
During the dark years of the Spellhunt, many thousands of years ago, Linaniil, the great mage of the Kor'Krul, worried that magic might disappear with her generation and be lost to mortals should they need it again.
So she set a secret plan into action and built a secret place where magic would be kept alive.
Her plan worked and the group built a town called Angolwen in the western mountains. #LIGHT_GREEN#*He marks it on your map, along with a portal to access it*#WHITE#
Not many people are accepted there but I will arrange for you to be allowed inside.]], [[哦……對，我可以重新返回安格利…，呃……我想我現在可以告訴你了，你幫了我這麼多我應該告訴你。
在魔法狩獵的那些黑暗年代裏，幾千年前，萊娜尼爾，卡爾·庫爾的大法師，擔心魔法會在她們那一代人身上滅絕，人們需要的這些魔法會從這個世界上消失。
於是她祕密安置了一個隱祕的地方繼續傳承魔法。
她執行了她的計劃，她手下的人在西部的羣山之中建立了一個叫做安格利文的小鎮。#LIGHT_GREEN#*他在你的地圖上做了一個記號，然後爲你開啓了一個傳送門。*#WHITE#
只有少部分人會被那裏的人接受，我會想辦法讓你進去的。]], "_t")
t("Oh! How could such a place be kept secret for so long... This is interesting indeed. Thank you for your trust!", "哦！這個祕密的地方怎麼能保持隱祕這麼長時間，真的很有趣，謝謝你對我的信任。", "_t")
t([[Ah yes! I am so glad! I will be able to go back to Angolwen now, and perhaps we will meet there.
Please take this ring; it has served me well.]], [[哦……對！我太高興了！我終於可以回到安格利文了，也許我們會在那裏再次見面。
請收下這枚戒指，曾經它對我很有用。]], "_t")
t("Thanks, and best luck in your studies!", "謝謝，祝你好運！", "_t")


