section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/melinda-beach-end.lua"

t("What just happened?!", "剛纔發生了什麼？！", "_t")
t("I'm sorry I didn't manage to protect you and as you were about to die you... fired a powerful wave of blight.", "抱歉，剛纔我沒能保護住你，當你快死時，突然...你周圍產生了一道強大的法力衝擊波。", "_t")
t("But I have never cast a spell in my life!", "但我從來沒施過法啊！", "_t")
t("You are still tainted by that ... foul Demon! The taint is not all gone!", "你肯定被污染了...對,那個惡魔！污染還沒有被清除乾淨！", "_t")
t("There must be some of that demon's taint still inside you.", "你身體裏還存在着惡魔的污染。", "_t")
t("This is terrible! I assure you I had no idea this would happen. You must trust me!", "怎麼會！我發誓，什麼都不知道，你要相信我！一定要！", "_t")
t("I do. The Ziguranth are not raving zealots, you know. We will look for a way to cure you, as long as you reject the blight.", "我相信。伊格蘭斯不是殺人狂魔，我們會找到方法來治療你的，只要你拒絕接受這股枯萎能量。", "_t")
t("This is terrible! What is happening to me?!? You must help me!", "天啊!到底發生了什麼?!?你一定要幫我!", "_t")
t("I will. We will find a cure for this together.", "我當然會幫你。我們一起來想辦法。", "_t")
t("I'm a very lucky girl, am I not... This is the second time I've had you to save me now.", "我真是幸運的女孩，不是嗎... 這是你第二次拯救我了。", "_t")
t("Over the last weeks you've become very important to me, and I am glad to have you. This is certainly not the place to talk, though, let's go.", "最近的幾個星期裏，你對我非常重要，我很樂意這樣做。不過，這裏不是說話的地方，我們找個安全的地方吧。", "_t")
t("You're right, let's get out of here.", "你說得對！快點離開這。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[go back to Last Hope]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[回到最後的希望]", "_t")


