section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/melinda-beach.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The two of you spend some time relaxing on the beach.
The air is fresh, the sand shimmers, and the surf roars softly.*#WHITE#

This was such a lovely idea!
I have had a wonderful time with you today.

#LIGHT_GREEN#*She looks longingly into your eyes.*#WHITE#]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你們兩個在沙灘上放鬆一了陣子。
空氣清新無比，陽光照射在砂礫上，閃耀五顏六色的光芒，
耳邊傳來海浪輕柔地呼嘯。*#WHITE#

出來旅行真好！
今天和你玩得很開心啊。

#LIGHT_GREEN#*她直視着你，眼睛裏閃耀莫名的光芒。*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[Lean closer and kiss her]#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[你靠了過去，親吻了她]#WHITE#", "_t")
t([[Just before your lips touch, you sense that something is very wrong.
]], [[在你們倆嘴脣相碰之前，你注意到有什麼不對勁……
]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[Continue...]#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[繼續...]#WHITE#", "_t")


