section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/melinda-fortress.lua"

t("Hi, sweety!", "嗨親愛的！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[kiss her]#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[親吻她]#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Are you settling in fine?", "你過得好麼？", "_t")
t("I want to open my own little shop in Derth?", "我想在德斯鎮開店？", "_t")
t("I want to study magic at Angolwen?", "我想去安格利文學魔法？", "_t")
t("I want to train at Zigur?", "我想去伊格蘭斯訓練？", "_t")
t([[Well let me say that tank is #{bold}#dreadful#{normal}#, but that weird butler says it is the only way.
I do start to feel better too.
However I must say I get bored around here a little.
Do you remember, I once told you %s Maybe we could find a way to get me there during the day and return for my treatment during the night?]], [[好吧，那個通道確實有些#{bold}#可怕#{normal}#，不過那個長相奇怪的管家說那是唯一的路。
現在我覺得好多了。
不過，呆久了還是覺得有些無聊。
你還記得麼,我曾經說過“%s”，或許能想個辦法，白天出去，晚上再回來？]], "tformat")
t("Oh yes, I think we could arrange that. Shadow, would it be possible to create a portal for her?", "當然可以，我相信我們能做到。堡壘幻影，能爲她製造一個傳送門麼？", "_t")
t([[Yes Master. I will arrange for that right now.
She will be able to come and go unnoticed.]], [[是的，主人。我馬上做。
她將能夠無聲無息的來往於倆地之間。]], "_t")
t("That is perfect.", "很好。", "_t")
t("Oh this is great, thank you! My own secret lair, my own life.", "噢，太棒了！謝謝！屬於我自己的通道，屬於我自己的人生。", "_t")
t("I only wish your happiness, I am glad to provide.", "只要你過得幸福，我什麼都願意做。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Looking all glamorous she comes closer*#WHITE#
Now my sweet one, where were we the last time?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*看上去充滿魅力，梅琳達走近了你*#WHITE#
親愛的，我們上一次是什麼時候？]], "_t")
t("My memory fails me, care to help me remember? #LIGHT_GREEN#[smile playfully at her]", "我都忘了，你能幫我想起來麼？#LIGHT_GREEN#[你調皮地笑着]", "_t")


