section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/message-last-hope.lua"

t([[Well met, @playername@. I was sent with a message from King Tolak of Last Hope.
I followed the trail of bodies that you left - very impressive! We are lucky to have you on our side.
But enough talk; take this message. I must go now.
#LIGHT_GREEN#He gives you a sealed scroll and vanishes into the shadows.#LAST#]], [[終於見到你了，@playername@。我是最後的希望國王托拉克派來給你送信的。
我追隨你的足跡找到你，令人印象深刻！很榮幸你是站在我們這一邊的。
不聊了，信我已送到，我必須得走了。
#LIGHT_GREEN#他遞給你一個密封的卷軸，然後消失在陰影中。#LAST#]], "_t")
t("Thank you for your courage.", "感謝你的勇氣。", "_t")
t("The herald gives you %s.", "傳令官交給了你 %s 。", "logPlayer")


