section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/player-inscription.lua"

t("Buy a new slot with one #{bold}#talent category point#{normal}#.", "使用#{bold}#技能樹解鎖點#{normal}#開啓一個新的符文槽（最多5個）。", "_t")
t("Cancel", "取消", "_t")
t("You have too many of this type of inscription. You can only override an existing one. The old inscription will be lost.", "你擁有一個此類紋身了，你只能覆蓋掉現存的那一個。舊的紋身將消失。", "_t")
t([[You have reached your maximum number of inscriptions (infusions/runes).
If you have unassigned #{bold}#talent category points#{normal}# you can use one to create a new slot (up to 5).
You can replace an existing one or cancel.
The old inscription will be lost.]], [[你已經到達了你的符文/紋身上限。
如果你還有未使用的 #{bold}#技能樹解鎖點#{normal}# 你可以用它來開啓一個新的符文槽。
你可以替換掉一個現存的紋身，或者取消。
舊的紋身將消失。]], "_t")


