section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/point-zero-zemekkys.lua"

t("@playername@, nice to see you again! Or is this the first time that you have seen me?", "@playername@，很高興再次見到你！呃，我們以前見過面麼？", "_t")
t("Farewell, Grand Keeper.", "再見，偉大的守護者。", "_t")
t("Yes, this is our first meeting.", "是的，我們是第一次見面。", "_t")
t([[Ah, for you perhaps, but not for me.
Listen, someday you will encounter me again but it will not be me you see now. It will be younger me, if you will.
This is very important: do not tell my previous me about me. Understood?]], [[啊，對你來說也許是的，不過對我來說可不是。
聽着，某一天你會再次遇到我，不過那不是現在的我。如果你見到他，那他一定是過去的我。
記住這一點很重要：不要告訴那個以前的我有關現在的我的事，明白麼？]], "_t")
t("I think so...", "我想這……", "_t")
t("Yes, Grand Keeper.", "是，偉大的守護者。", "_t")


