section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/pre-charred-scar.lua"

t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#Suddenly a voice appears in your head.#WHITE#*
@playername@, this is High Sun Paladin Aeryn of the Sunwall. I am communicating with you by the power of the Anorithil.
I have some urgent information for you: the staff you were looking for has been located.]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#突然你的腦海中出現了一個聲音。#WHITE#*
@playername@，我是太陽堡壘的高階太陽騎士艾琳。我藉助星月術士的能力和你取得聯繫。
我有個非常緊急的消息要告訴你：我們已經知道你一直在尋找的法杖去向。]], "_t")
t("Where?!", "在哪裏？！", "_t")
t([[One of our patrols noticed some strange orc movements around the southern part of the continent, in the desert of Erúan.
A group of orcs were guarding something that looked like the staff you asked about.
You should go there to investigate. This might be your only chance.]], [[我們的一個巡邏隊在南部大陸艾露安沙漠注意到了一些獸人的奇怪行蹤。
一羣獸人在守衛着一件東西，看上去好像是你提到的那個法杖。
你應該去調查一下，這可能是你僅有的機會。]], "_t")
t("I will, right now!", "我馬上就去！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ring-of-blood-master.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a small humanoid creature with a disproportionate head.*#WHITE#
Ah, what have we here? @playerdescriptor.race@, I believe you have turned at the wrong corner.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一個矮小的人形生物，長着一個不成比例的腦袋。*#WHITE#
看，來了個什麼人，@playerdescriptor.race@, 我相信你一定走錯地方了。]], "_t")
t("So it would seem. What is going on here?", "有可能，這裏發生了什麼事？", "_t")
t([[This is my Ring of Blood! Listen, you have now two choices.
Since you do not look like slave fodder to me I will offer to let you pay to play the game.
If you feel you cannot take part in a slaver's game, I am afraid you will need to... disappear.]], [[這裏是鮮血之環！聽着，你現在有兩個選擇。
既然你看上去不像那些奴隸一樣的炮灰，我會給你一個機會來玩一個遊戲。
要是你不想參加這個奴隸遊戲，恐怕你得從我面前消失了。]], "_t")
t("Slavers? This is so wrong! [attack]", "奴隸？你沒搞錯吧！[攻擊]", "_t")
t("You think so? Die.", "你這樣認爲？去死吧。", "_t")
t("Game? I like playing, what's this about?", "遊戲？我喜歡，是個什麼樣的遊戲？", "_t")
t([[Well, you see, it's quite simple. I will mentally take control of various wild creatures or slaves while you use the orb of command on the other side of this room to take control of a slave.
Then we fight using our pawns for 10 rounds. If your slave survives you will win the Bloodcaller.]], [[你看，很簡單。我會精神控制一些野生怪物或者奴隸，你則用對面的指令水晶球來控制一個奴隸。
然後我們對戰10輪，如果你的奴隸還活着，那你會贏得了一個戒指，鮮血呼喚。]], "_t")
t("What if I lose?", "要是我輸了呢？", "_t")
t("Normally you would be taken as a slave, but you look like you would be more useful as a full-time player, so you can just try again.", "一般你自己會成爲我的奴隸，不過你看上去應該是個不錯的選手，你可以再次嘗試。", "_t")
t("Blood, death without self-harm risks? Great fun!", "鮮血和死亡，但自己卻不用冒生命危險，太有趣了！", "_t")
t([[Superb. Oh yes, before I forget, to use the orb you will need to pay the standard fee of 150 gold pieces.
I'm sure this is small money to an adventurer of your class.]], [[好極了，哦對了我差點忘了，每次使用水晶球你得支付150金幣。
對於你們這種冒險家來說我想肯定不過是九牛之一毛而已。]], "_t")
t("150 gold? Err... yes, sure.", "150金幣？呃……好吧當然。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ring-of-blood-orb.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*You place your hands on the orb.*#WHITE#
You must provide 150 gold to take part in the fight.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你把你的手放在水晶球上。*#WHITE#
你必須支付150金幣參加比賽！]], "_t")
t("[Pay 150 gold]", "[支付150金幣]", "_t")
t("[Leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("Let the fight start!", "比賽開始吧！", "_t")
t("Bring it on!", "儘管來吧！", "_t")


