section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ring-of-blood-win.lua"

t([[So, you tasted blood? Liked it? I am sure you did; you are just that kind of people.
Anyway, I suppose you deserve your reward.
You can always participate again for fun, if you've got the gold to spare.]], [[那……你嚐到了鮮血的滋味吧，怎麼樣喜歡麼？相信你一定喜歡，你就應該是這種人。
不管怎樣，你應該得到你的獎賞。
要是你願意花錢，你可以再來練習取樂。]], "_t")
t("Thanks, it was fun!", "謝謝，非常有趣！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/sage-kitty.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a cute little orange cat. It looks hungry and looks at you.*#WHITE#
Meowww?
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一隻可愛的小貓咪。它似乎餓了，眼淚汪汪地瞅着你。*#WHITE#
喵嗚...
]], "_t")
t("Oh kitty kitty!", "貓咪真可愛！", "_t")
t("No time for cats!", "我可沒時間浪費在貓身上!", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*It rubs up against your leg and purrs.*#WHITE#
Rrrrrrrrrrrr.
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*它輕輕地蹭着你的腿，咕嚕咕嚕地叫着。*#WHITE#
嗚嗚...
]], "_t")
t("Hey maybe you would like some of this delicious lookin troll intestines? #LIGHT_GREEN#[Feed him the intestines]#WHITE#", "小貓，你想吃點東西麼？我這裏正好有半截巨魔腸子，你要麼？ #LIGHT_GREEN#[餵給它吃]#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Sorry little fellow, I can't help you.", "小貓，抱歉，我幫不了你。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*It eats it all and looks happy. After a while it strolls away. Somehow you feel you have not seen the last of it.*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*它全部吃光了，看起來很開心。過了一會，它就跑開了。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[Leave]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[離開]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/shadow-crypt-yeek-clone.lua"

t("No time to talk fellow Wayist! ATTACK! FOR THE WAY!", "沒時間閒聊了，我的同胞！衝啊！爲了維網！", "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("The foolish cultist that created me is no more. What am I to do now...", "那個創造了我的愚蠢邪教徒已經死了。我現在應該做什麼呢…", "_t")
t("You are me, come with me!", "你就是我，和我一起走吧！", "_t")
t("You should head back to Irkkk.", "你應該回伊爾克去。", "_t")
t("I fear that would get confusing very fast. I think I will go back to Irkkk. Farewell my clone!", "我擔心這樣會讓我很困惑的。我覺得我應該回伊爾克去。再見了，我的克隆！", "_t")
t("Sure... if you prefer to think about it this way. We are all part of The Way anyway.", "啊……如果你願意這麼想也沒問題。反正，我們都是維網的一份子。", "_t")
t("I think so too, farewell my clone.", "我也是這麼想的，再見了，我的克隆。", "_t")
t("Clone? No you are the clone.", "克隆？不，你是我的克隆。", "_t")
t("Farewell.", "再見。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/shertul-fortress-butler.lua"

t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#The creature slowly turns to you. You hear its terrible voice directly in your head.#WHITE#*
Welcome, master.]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#那個生物慢慢向你走來，你的頭頂上響起一個可怕的嗓音。#WHITE#*
歡迎你，主人。]], "_t")
t("What are you, and what is this place?", "你是什麼東西？這是什麼地方？", "_t")
t("Master? I am not your mas...", "主人？我不是你的主……", "_t")
t("Why do I understand you? The texts are unreadable to me.", "我不明白，那些文字我看不懂。", "_t")
t("What can I do here?", "我能在這裏做什麼？", "_t")
t("What else can this place do?", "這裏還能做什麼？", "_t")
t("Would it be possible to improve my Cloak of Deception so I do not need to wear it to pass as a living being?", "可以幫我升級欺詐斗篷讓我可以直接通過而不必裝備它麼？", "_t")
t("You asked me to come, about a farportal?", "你叫我來，是爲了遠古傳送門？", "_t")
t("You asked me to come, about the rod of recall?", "你叫我來，是關於召回之杖？", "_t")
t("Would it be possible for my Transmogrification Chest to automatically extract gems?", "可以讓我的轉化之盒自動轉化寶石麼？", "_t")
t("Are there any training facilities?", "這裏是不是有一間訓練室？", "_t")
t("Can you use your magic to alter the appearance of my gear?", "你能用魔法改變我裝備的外形麼?", "_t")
t("I find your appearance unsettling. Any way you can change it?", "你的樣子看上去讓我不舒服，你可以改變外形麼？", "_t")
t("I have come upon a strange thing indeed. #LIGHT_GREEN#[tell him about Melinda]", "我到這裏來是爲了尋求幫助。 #LIGHT_GREEN#[告訴它梅琳達的事]", "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#The creature glares at you.#WHITE#*
You possess a control rod. You are the master.]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#那個生物瞪着你。#WHITE#*
你拿着控制魔杖，你就是我的主人。]], "_t")
t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#The creature glares at you.#WHITE#*
You are the master; you have the rod. I am created to speak to the master.]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#那個生物瞪着你。#WHITE#*
你擁有魔杖，你就是主人，我是被製造出來和主人對話的。]], "_t")
t("Err... ok.", "哦……好吧。", "_t")
t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#The creature glares at you with intensity. You 'see' images in your head.
You see titanic wars in an age now forgotten. You see armies of what you suppose are Sher'Tuls since they look like the shadow.
They fight with weapons, magic and other things. They fight gods. They hunt them down, killing or banishing them.
You see great fortresses like this one, flying all over the skies of Eyal - shining bastions of power glittering in the young sun.
You see the gods beaten, defeated and dead. All but one.
Then you see darkness; it seems like the shadow does not know what followed those events.

You shake your head as the vision dissipates, and your normal sight comes back slowly.
#WHITE#*
]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#那個生物集中精神注視着你，你“看到”了腦海中的影像。
你看到了已被人遺忘的泰坦之戰。你看到了夏·圖爾軍隊的陰影。
他們使用魔法、武器和其他東西戰鬥，他們和衆神戰鬥，將他們擊倒、殺死、驅散。
你看到巨大的類似這裏的堡壘飄浮在埃亞爾的上空，在陽光之下釋放出強大的能量光芒。
你看到衆神都被擊敗、殺死，除了一個。
然後你看到了黑暗，一些不知其名的陰影緊隨着出現。

你搖了搖驅散了腦海中的影像，你的眼前慢慢恢復了現實的景象。
#WHITE#*
]], "_t")
t("Those are Sher'Tuls? They fought the gods?!", "那是夏·圖爾？他們和衆神戰鬥？！", "_t")
t("They had to. They forged terrible weapons of war. They won.", "他們曾經是，他們鍛造了可怕的武器用於戰爭，並取得了勝利。", "_t")
t("But then where are they now if they won?", "他們是勝利了，但是現在他們又在哪裏呢？", "_t")
t("They are gone now. I cannot tell you more.", "他們已經消失，我不能告訴你更多了。", "_t")
t("But I am the master!", "我是你的主人！", "_t")
t("Fine.", "好吧。", "_t")
t([[*#LIGHT_GREEN#The creature glares at you.#WHITE#*
You are the master. You can use this place as you desire. However, most of the energies are depleted and only some rooms are usable.
To the south you will find the storage room.]], [[*#LIGHT_GREEN#那個生物瞪着你。#WHITE#*
你是主人，你可以隨意使用這個地方。不過，大多數這裏的能量已經耗竭，只有一些房間可以使用。
在南面你可以看到儲藏室。]], "_t")
t([[This Fortress is designed as a mobile base for the Godslayers - it can fly.
It is also equiped with various facilities: exploratory farportal, emergency containment field, remote storage, ...
However, the Fortress is badly damaged and has lain dormant for too long. Its energies are nearly depleted.
Take this Transmogrification Chest. It is linked by a permanent farportal to the Fortress. Any item you put inside will be sent to the power core and dismantled for energy.
There are, however, unwanted byproducts to this operation: the generation of a metal known as gold. It is of no use to the Fortress and thus will be sent back to you.]], [[這個堡壘是弒神者們的移動堡壘，它可以飛行。
它還裝備了其他設施：探險傳送門，緊急防護場，遠程存儲……
然而，堡壘已經嚴重損壞，而且已經休眠了太久了。它的能量幾近枯竭。
拿着這個轉化之盒。它與堡壘有永久鏈接，所有放進去的裝備都可以使用它分解，轉化爲堡壘的能量。
不過它還有這樣一個副作用：轉化物品會產生一種叫做金子的金屬，它們對於要塞是沒有用的，所以會變成金幣返還給你。]], "_t")
t("I will, thanks.", "我知道了，謝謝。", "_t")
t("I have already found such a chest in my travel. Will it work?", "我已經在我的旅途中找到了一個，它有發揮效用麼？", "_t")
t([[Yes, it will. I will attune it to this fortress.
Done.]], [[是的它會，我會把它和堡壘聯繫在一起。
好了。]], "_t")
t("Thanks.", "多謝。", "_t")
t([[Long ago the Sher'tuls used farportals not only for transportation to known locations, but also to explore new parts of the world, or even other worlds.
This Fortress is equipped with an exploratory farportal, and now has enough energy to allow one teleportation. Each teleportation will take you to a random part of the universe and use 45 energy.
Beware that the return portal may not be nearby your arrival point; you will need to find it. You can use the rod of recall to try to force an emergency recall, but it has high chances of breaking the exploratory farportal forever.
You may use the farportal; however, beware - I sense a strange presence in the farportal room.]], [[很久以前夏·圖爾們使用遠古傳送門，不僅是爲了傳送到那些已知的地方，也可以傳送的世界未知的角落，甚至是其他世界。
這個堡壘裝置有遠古傳送門，現在已經有足夠的能量開啓其中的一個了。每次傳送都會將你傳送到宇宙的一個隨機角落，每次耗費30能量。
注意返回的傳送門並不是就在你到達的那個地方，你需要自己去尋找。緊急情況下你可以使用召回之杖強制返回，不過這很有可能永久損壞遠古傳送門。
你可以使用遠古傳送門了，不過，當心，感覺到傳送門房間有異常的東西。]], "_t")
t("I will check it out, thanks.", "我會去檢查一下的，謝謝。", "_t")
t([[The rod of recall you possess is not a Sher'tul artifact, but it is based on Sher'tul design.
The Fortress now has enough energy to upgrade it. It can be changed to recall you to the Fortress.]], [[你所擁有的召回之杖並不是夏·圖爾的產物，不過是基於夏·圖爾的知識而製造的。
堡壘現在有足夠的能量來升級它的功能，可以使你傳送時返回到堡壘來。]], "_t")
t("I like it the way it is now. Thanks anyway.", "我喜歡保持原樣，不過還是謝謝了。", "_t")
t([[Yes master, a training facility is available to the north, but it is not yet powered on.
I will need to use 50 energy to do this.]], [[是的，主人。北方是有一間訓練室，不過它需要能量。
	我需要至少50能量來激活它。]], "_t")
t([[Yes master, the Mirror of Reflections is what you need. It is currently dormant but could be re-activated.
I will need to use 10 energy to do this.]], [[好的主人。反射之鏡能滿足您的需求。它目前處於休眠狀態，但可以重新激活。
它需要10點能量激活。]], "_t")
t("\
#{italic}##CRIMSON#This feature is purely cosmetic is available only to donators/buyers. You can unlock the room and use the preview but you will not be able to validate your choices.#{normal}#", "\
#{italic}##CRIMSON#此功能僅限捐贈者/購買者使用。您可以解鎖房間並使用預覽，但無法生效您的選擇。#{normal}#", "_t")
t("Maybe later.", "以後再說。", "_t")
t("That could be quite nice. Yes, please do it.", "非常好，就這麼做吧。", "_t")
t([[Ah yes, you seem to master the simple art of alchemy. I can change the chest to automatically use your power to extract a gem if the transmogrification of the gem would reward more energy.
However, I will need to use 25 energy to do this.]], [[嗯可以，你似乎掌握了基本的鍊金術，我可以使轉化之盒自動轉化寶石提供能量，
不過這需要耗費25能量值。]], "_t")
t("Maybe sometime later.", "以後再說。", "_t")
t("I can alter the Fortress holographic projection matrix to accomodate your racial tastes. This will require 60 energy, however.", "我可以通過堡壘改變我自身的結構以符合主人的口味，不過這得耗費60能量值。", "_t")
t("Can you try for a human female appearance please?", "請你變成一個女性人類的樣子吧？", "_t")
t("Can you try for a human male appearance please?", "請你變成一個男性人類的樣子吧？", "_t")
t("Please revert to your default appearance.", "請變回原來默認的樣子。", "_t")
t("Well, you do not look so bad actually. Let it be for now.", "好吧，其實你看上去沒那麼糟，就保持這個樣子吧。", "_t")
t([[Yes Master. I can use 10 energy to infuse your cloak. When you take it off the effect should still persist.
However, I suggest you still carry it with you in case something manages to remove it from you.]], [[是的主人，我可以耗費10能量來提升斗篷，使你脫下斗篷仍能保持它的特效。
不過，我建議你還是隨身攜帶，以備萬一特效被從你身上消除時使用。]], "_t")
t("Not now.", "暫時不用。", "_t")
t("That could be quite useful. Yes, please do it.", "這很有用。好，就這麼辦。", "_t")
t([[Demonic taint. Yes I have a way to help in the archives. However this is a long process, the subject will need to live here for a while.
She will have to spend 8 hours per day in the regeneration tank.]], [[惡魔的污染麼，是的，我有方法幫忙。不過這需要一段時間，目標生物必須在這裏住上一段時間。
她每天至少要在這裏呆上8小時。]], "_t")
t("This is great news! I will tell her at once.", "太好了！我馬上告訴她。", "_t")


