section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/slasul.lua"

t([[What is this? Why have you entered my temple and slain my followers?
Speak or die, for I am Slasul and you shall not disrupt my plans.]], [[怎麼回事？爲什麼你要闖入我的神廟殺死我的人？
說，要不然你就得死，我是薩拉蘇爾，你不應該打亂我的計劃。]], "_t")
t("I was sent by Ukllmswwik to stop your mad schemes to control all underwater life!", "我是烏克勒姆斯維奇派來的，阻止你試圖控制所有水下生物的瘋狂計劃。", "_t")
t([[I see. So the dragon sent you. He told you I am insane, I assume?
But which of us is truly evil? Myself, working to better my people, doing no harm to anyone, or you, who comes here to kill me, destroying my friends and planning to do the same to me?
Who is the insane one?]], [[我明白了，是那個龍人叫你來的，是他告訴你我瘋了，我圖謀不軌？
但我們到底誰纔是惡魔？我自己，爲人們做好事，對任何人都沒有傷害，而你，來這裏想要殺死我，殺死了我的朋友，現在還想連我一起幹掉？
誰纔是瘋子？]], "_t")
t("If you refuse to see reason, you leave me no choice!", "既然你不聽我解釋，那我別無選擇！", "_t")
t("Your feeble attempt to sway me from the side of good will not work. Pay for you sins!", "你想狡辯動搖的我立場麼？這可不起作用，爲你犯下的罪惡付出代價吧。", "_t")
t("Your words are... disturbing. Why should I spare you?", "你說的話讓我有點……搞不清楚了，但我爲什麼要寬恕你？", "_t")
t([[Spare me?#LIGHT_GREEN#*He laughs.*#WHITE#
Do not be so hasty to assume YOU are in a position to offer mercy to ME!
Yet I shall tell you my story. You surface dwellers do not know much about nagas, but let me tell you this: our current condition was not our choice.
When Nalore sank, many of us died, so we resorted to using the magic of this temple. It worked, it saved us, and yet we are cursed. Cursed in this form by the terrible magic.
If you do not believe anything else of what I say, please believe at least this: the Sher'Tul are hiding, not gone, and they are not benevolent entities.
Recently, that water dragon that sent you here started sending "agents" to secure the temple. I can only imagine his goals, but they are clearly not peaceful.]], [[寬恕我？#LIGHT_GREEN#*他笑了起來*#WHITE#
別用這種憐憫的態度對我！
我會告訴你我的故事，你們地面上的居民並不瞭解娜迦，讓我告訴你：我們目前的處境並不是我們自己的選擇。
當納魯大陸沉沒時，我們很多人死了，因此我們求助於這間神廟的魔法。它起作用了，它救了我們，但是我們受到了詛咒。在這種可怕的魔法下我們變成了現在這副模樣。
要是你不相信我所說的，至少你應該相信這個：夏·圖爾只是隱藏了起來，並沒有消失，而且它們並不是友善的種族。
現在，那個“水龍”派你來這裏，開始派代理人來保護神廟。我只能猜測他的真正目的，肯定不是出於善意。]], "_t")
t("You do not sound mad to me... could Ukllmswwik have lied?", "聽上去你不像是個瘋子，難道烏克勒姆斯維奇說謊了麼？", "_t")
t("As you wish. It did not have to come to this...", "如你所願吧，本來不至於如此……", "_t")
t("I will not be deceived by your lies! I will make your pay for your victims!", "我不會被你的謊言所欺騙，你必須爲你的犧牲者付出代價！", "_t")
t("Use this portal. It will bring you back to his cave; ask him the truth.", "使用這個傳送門，可以把你傳送回他的洞穴，去問他事情的真相吧。", "_t")
t("I will make him pay for his treachery.", "我會讓他的背叛付出代價。", "_t")
t("Thank you for listening to me.", "謝謝你聽我說完。", "_t")
t("The dragon was lying, I can feel it. I have decided to embrace your cause.", "那頭巨龍在說謊，我能看出來。我準備接受你的力量。", "_t")
t("Farewell, Slasul.", "再見，薩拉蘇爾。", "_t")
t("So be it... Die now!", "那好……你去死吧！", "_t")
t("[attack]", "[攻擊]", "_t")
t([[I secretly hoped you would.
Then let us seal this alliance. Share your lifeforce with me! So long you should live I shall not be killed!
In return let me offer you this powerful trident.]], [[我希望你能配合。
現在，讓我們開始履行同盟儀式。將你的生命與我同享！這樣只要你活着，我就永遠不死！
作爲回報，我會賜予你這柄強大的三叉戟。]], "_t")
t("I shall accept your offer, my liege.", "我接受你的饋贈，我的主人。", "_t")
t("LET US BE BOUND!", "我們合體吧！", "_t")
t("This sounds strange. I need to think about it.", "聽起來有點奇怪，我要考慮一下。", "_t")


