section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/sorcerer-end.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The two Sorcerers lie dead before you.*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*Their bodies vanish in a small cloud of mist, quickly fading away.*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*You feel the Way reaching out to you, the whole yeek race speaks to you.*#WHITE#
You have done something incredible %s! You also have created a unique opportunity for the yeek race!
The energies of those farportals are incredible, using them we could make the Way radiate all over Eyal, forcing it down on the other races, bringing them the same peace and happiness we feel in the Way.
You must go through the farportal and willingly sacrifice yourself inside. Your mind will embed itself into the farportal network, spreading the Way far and wide!
Even though you will die you will bring the world, and the yeeks, ultimate peace.
The Way will never forget you. Now go and make history!
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*兩個魔法師死在你面前。*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*他們的屍體化成了一縷青煙，很快消失了。*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*你感覺到維網和你發生了聯繫，整個奪心魔族在和你對話。*#WHITE#
你完成了令人難以置信的使命，%s！你也爲奪心魔族創造了千載難逢的機會！
遠古傳送門的能量強大到難以想象，我們可以利用這個能量擴展維網到整個埃亞爾，並進入其他種族，將我們從維網中得到的和平與幸福帶給他們。
你必須穿過傳送門，犧牲你自己，你的精神意志會使能量注入維網並使維網向遠處傳播。
雖然你會死去，但是你會給這個世界和奪心魔族帶來永久的和平。
維網永遠不會忘記你，現在，去創造歷史吧！
]], "tformat")
t("brother", "兄弟", "_t")
t("sister", "姐妹", "_t")
t("But... I did so much, I could do so much more for the Way by staying alive!", "但是……我已經做了那麼多，我活着一樣可以爲維網做那麼多！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*You feel the Way taking over your mind, your body.*#WHITE#
You will do as asked, for the good of all Yeeks! The Way is always right.
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你感到維網充斥了你的身心*#WHITE#
你會按照所要求的去做，爲了整個奪心魔族！維網總是正確的。
]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[sacrifice yourself to bring the Way to every sentient creature.]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[犧牲你自己，將維網傳播到所有智慧生命。]", "_t")
t("sacrificing %s to bring the Way to all", "%s犧牲自己，把維網傳播到全世界", "tformat")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[In a last incredible display of willpower you fight the Way for a few seconds, letting you project your thoughts to Aeryn.]#WHITE# High Lady! Kill me #{bold}#NOW#{normal}#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[在最後關頭你用意志抵抗了維網幾秒鐘，向艾琳傳遞了信息。]#WHITE# 艾琳女士，快殺了我！#{bold}#現在！#{normal}#", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Through your mind Aeryn sees what the Way is planning.*#WHITE#
You were a precious ally and a friend. The world will remember your last act of selfless sacrifice. I swear it.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*As she says this she pierces your body with a mighty thrust of her sword, ending the plans of the Way.*#WHITE#
]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*通過你的精神力量，艾琳明白了維網的計劃。*#WHITE#
你是一位偉大的盟友和罕見的夥伴。我發誓，整個世界都會銘記你的犧牲。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*一邊說，她一邊用劍刺入你的身體，終結了維網的計劃。*#WHITE#
]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#[slip peacefully into death.]", "#LIGHT_GREEN#[平靜地走向死亡。]", "_t")
t("sacrificing %s to stop the Way", "%s犧牲自己，阻止了維網。", "tformat")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The two Sorcerers lie dead before you.*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*Their bodies vanish in a small cloud of mist, quickly fading away.*#WHITE#
But the portal to the Void is already open. It must be closed before the Creator can come through or all will have been in vain!
After searching the remains of the Sorcerers you find a note explaining that the portal can only be closed with a sentient being's sacrifice.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*兩個魔法師死在你面前。*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*他們的屍體化成了一縷青煙，很快消失了。*#WHITE#
但是虛空傳送門仍然打開着，在造物主穿過之前必須得關閉，否則一切努力都白費了！
你搜索魔法師的屍體找到了一本筆記，上面寫道：想要關閉傳送門，只有犧牲一個生命才行。]], "_t")
t("Aeryn, I am sorry but one of us needs to be sacrificed for the world to go on. #LIGHT_GREEN#[sacrifice Aeryn for the sake of the world]", "艾琳，很抱歉我們之中得有一個人犧牲才能維持這個世界的存在。#LIGHT_GREEN#[爲了這個世界犧牲艾琳]", "_t")
t("I will close it. #LIGHT_GREEN#[sacrifice yourself for the sake of the world]", "我會關閉它。#LIGHT_GREEN#[爲了這個世界犧牲你自己。]", "_t")
t("sacrificing %s for the sake of the world", "%s爲了世界犧牲了自己", "tformat")
t([[I cannot believe we succeeded. I was prepared to die and it seems I will die, but at least I will do so knowing my sacrifice is not in vain.
Please, make sure the world is safe.]], [[真不敢相信我們成功了。我已經準備好去死了，至少我知道我的犧牲不會白費。
請你確保這個世界的和平。]], "_t")
t("You will never be forgotten.", "你會永遠被人銘記。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The two Sorcerers lie dead before you.*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*Their bodies vanish in some immaterial mist.*#WHITE#
You have won the game!
Both Maj'Eyal and the Far East are safe from the dark schemes of the Sorcerers and their God.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*兩個魔法師死在你面前。*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*他們的屍體化成了一縷青煙消失了。*#WHITE#
你贏得了這個遊戲！
馬基·埃亞爾和遠東大陸從法師會的黑暗計劃和他們的神手中獲救了。]], "_t")
t("Aeryn, are you well?", "艾琳，你還好麼？", "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t([[I cannot believe we succeeded. I was prepared to die and yet I live.
I might have underestimated you. You did more than we could have hoped for!]], [[真不敢相信我們成功了！我準備好去死了但我還活着。
我可能低估你了，你做了比我們預想的多的多的事情。]], "_t")
t("We both did.", "我們倆都是。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/sorcerer-fight.lua"

t("High Sun Paladin Aeryn appears next to you!", "高階太陽騎士艾琳在你的身邊出現了！", "logPlayer")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The two Sorcerers stands before you, shining like the Sun.*#WHITE#
Ah! Our guest is finally here. I take it you found the peak entertaining?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*兩個魔法師站在你面前，像太陽一樣閃閃發光。*#WHITE#
喔～！我們的客人終於來到了這裏。看來我們是到了舞會的高潮了，不是麼？]], "_t")
t("Spare me the small talk. I am here to stop you!", "我不是來和你們聊天的，我是來阻止你們的！", "_t")
t("Why are you doing all that? You were supposed to help people!", "你們爲什麼這麼做？你們本來是被期望幫助別人的！", "_t")
t([[Oh, but all we want is to help people. We have come to the self-evident conclusion that common people are just unfit to govern themselves, always bickering, arguing...
Since the last invasion of the orcs there has been no threat to unite them!]], [[唔～但是我們確實一直在幫助人們，我們得出了一個明確的結論，就是普通人根本不能管好自己，只會無休止的爭吵、爭鬥……
自從最後一波獸人入侵之後，人們就不再有別的威脅使他們聯合在一起了！]], "_t")
t("So you have decided to become the threat yourselves?", "所以你們想要使你們自己成爲人們新的威脅？", "_t")
t("Us? Ah, no, we are merely instruments for the Master. We have planned for His return.", "我們？哦，不是，我們不過是主人的工具。我們正在籌劃他的到來。", "_t")
t("And 'He' would be...?", "那他是……？", "_t")
t([[The Creator. The God who made this world, He who watched silently as the races fought and burnt the land.
He who felt great sorrow for this world. He who shall now shatter the barriers of this world to remake it, only better!
The staff has allowed us to drain enough energy from this world to open the portal to the Void and summon Him through!
It is already too late. He is coming through as we speak -- it is only a matter of hours!]], [[造物主，創造這個世界的神，他默默的看着你們這些種族在這個大陸上爭戰不休。
他對這個世界感到非常失望，它現在將要掃清這個世界所有的障礙，然後重新創造它，使它更美好！
法杖的力量使我們吸收了足夠的能量來開啓虛空傳送門召喚他的降臨！
已經太晚了！在我們說話的時刻他已經在穿越傳送門了！只需幾個小時的時間！]], "_t")
t([[The Creator. The God who made this world, He who watched silently as the races fought and burnt the land.
He who felt great sorrow for this world. He who shall now shatter the barriers of this world to remake it, only better!
The staff will allow us to drain enough energy from this world to open the portal to the Void and summon Him through!
You cannot stop us now!]], [[造物之主，創造這個世界的神，他默默的看着你們在這個大陸上爭戰不休。
他對這個世界感到非常失望，它現在將要掃清這個世界所有的障礙，然後重新創造它，使它更好！
法杖的力量使我們吸收了足夠的能量開啓虛空傳送門來召喚他的降臨！
你已經無法阻止我們了！]], "_t")
t("High Sun Paladin Aeryn", "太陽騎士艾琳", "_t")
t("I *WILL* stop you! The world will not end today!", "我要阻止你，世界不會在今天滅亡！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The air whirls at your side and suddenly High Sun Paladin Aeryn appears!*#WHITE#
Then you shall not fight alone! Together we shall stop them, or die trying!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*空氣在你身邊迴旋，突然高階太陽騎士艾琳出現了！*#WHITE#
你不是一個人在戰鬥！我們一起來阻止他們，戰鬥至最後一刻！]], "_t")
t("I am glad to have you at my side, my Lady. Let's hunt some wizards!", "很高興你能協助我，女士！我們來打敗這些巫師！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/tannen.lua"

t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*Nobody answers.*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*沒人回答。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*Nobody answers. Tannen is probably still busy studying the orb.*#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*沒人回答，泰恩估計還在忙着研究水晶球。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[leave]", "[離開]", "_t")
t("How may I be of service, good @playerdescriptor.race@?", "我能爲你提供什麼服務？我親愛的 @playerdescriptor.race@？", "_t")
t("[Relate to him the story of the staff and the Orb of Many Ways and the portals.]", "[告訴他關於法杖、多元水晶球和傳送門的事。]", "_t")
t("I have the diamond and the athame. [Hand over the Athame and Diamond]", "我有共鳴寶石和血符祭劍。[交給他血符祭劍和共鳴寶石]", "_t")
t("Thieving, murderous wretch. Prepare to die!", "竊賊，卑鄙的兇手，準備去死吧！", "_t")
t("How fares your research? Are we ready to create the portal?", "你研究的怎麼樣了？我們可以創造傳送門了麼？", "_t")
t("Nothing, excuse me. Bye!", "沒事，抱歉打擾了，再見！", "_t")
t("Astonishing! I have heard tell of this Orb in ancient texts and legends. Might I see it?", "真令人驚訝！我在古代的文獻和傳說中讀到過關於這個水晶球的資料。能讓我看看麼？", "_t")
t("[Show him the Orb of Many Ways]", "[給他看多元水晶球]", "_t")
t("Truly, it is the work of a great master. Perhaps Linaniil herself had a hand in its making. And you say you come bearing instructions in its usage?", "確實，這是一位傑出偉人的傑作。也許萊娜尼爾她自己也曾經參與過建造。你說你看不懂它的使用說明麼？", "_t")
t("I do. [Show him Zemekkys's scribbled notes]", "是的。[給他看伊莫克斯潦草的筆記]", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*He spends a few minutes reading*#WHITE# Ah! I see. I did not at first grasp this Zemekkys's methods, but I see now that they are sound, and it is simply his penmanship that needs improvement. We can manage to reproduce his work here, but, as he says, we will need the Blood-Runed Athame and a Resonating Diamond.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*他花了點時間閱讀筆記*#WHITE# 啊！我知道了。我一開始沒有看明白伊莫克斯的方法。現在我終於搞清楚了，是通過聲音來啓用的，他的字真得好好練一下。我們可以在這裏重複他的方法，不過，照他所說的話，我們還需要血符祭劍和共鳴寶石。", "_t")
t("Have you any idea where they might be found?", "你知道去哪裏尋找這兩樣東西麼？", "_t")
t("If the orcs created a portal in the depths of Reknor, they must have had access to such items. And if these items cannot pass through the portal they created, then it stands to reason that they must still be in Maj'Eyal. I would search Reknor, starting near the portal itself. Perhaps they did not move the Athame and Diamond far after its creation.", "假如獸人在瑞庫納深處製造了這樣一個傳送門的話，他們肯定有這兩樣東西。如果這些物品無法穿越他們所製造的傳送門的話，那麼就有理由相信這兩樣物品可能還在馬基·埃亞爾。必須得搜尋瑞庫納，從傳送門附近開始。或許在建造完傳送門之後，祭祀匕首和寶石仍然留在離這裏不遠的地方。", "_t")
t("I'll get searching. Thank you.", "我會去尋找的，謝謝你。", "_t")
t("One last thing. I will need to hold onto the Orb of Many Ways while you search. I lack the expertise this Chronomancer Zemekkys possesses, and have much learning on the subject to do if I am to follow in his footsteps.", "最後一件事，在你搜尋的時候我得研究一下多元水晶球。我缺少時空法師伊莫克斯所擁有的專業知識，如果我要重複他的工作我必須得花些時間研究這些內容。", "_t")
t("[Hand him the Orb] ", "[交給他水晶球] ", "_t")
t("I still require the Orb for now.", "我現在還需要水晶球", "_t")
t("Thank you. I will treat it with the utmost care.", "謝謝，我會小心謹慎使用的。", "_t")
t("Farewell. I'll return with the Athame and Diamond.", "再見，我會把血符祭劍和共鳴寶石帶回來的。", "_t")
t("Very well. There is no hurry. But I will need to spend a number of days studying it before we can create your portal.", "好極了，不用着急。要創造你需要的傳送門我還得花上幾天來學習一下呢。", "_t")
t("I understand. I'll return with the Athame and Diamond.", "我明白了，我會把血符祭劍和共鳴寶石帶回來的。", "_t")
t("Excellent. Return in a few days, and I'll have everything prepared. Oh, take this. #LIGHT_GREEN#*He hands you a key*#WHITE# It opens the ruins of Telmur, which the men of Sholtar sealed many years ago. If you happen to find a text in the ruins entitled \"Inverted and Reverted Probabilistic Fields,\" return with it and your odds of surviving our portal attempt will go up drastically.", "很好，幾天後你回來，我肯定把一切都準備好了。哦，帶上這個。#LIGHT_GREEN#*他交給你一把鑰匙。*#WHITE#他可以打開泰爾瑪廢墟,許多年以前肖塔人被封印在那裏。要是你在廢墟之中找到一份標題是《關於力場翻轉與回覆的可能性研究》的文獻請幫我帶回來，這樣可以使傳送門保留機會大大提高。", "_t")
t("Excellent. Are you yet willing to leave the Orb in my care for a time?", "太好了，那你同意把水晶球留給我研究一段時間了？", "_t")
t("I dare not let it out of my sight. I'm sorry.", "我可不希望它離開我的視線，抱歉。", "_t")
t("Here it is. Guard it carefully. I must return to the Far East soon.", "給你，小心保護好。我必須得返回遠東大陸了。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*The old man sighs*#WHITE# Very well. I suppose I must make do with a cursory examination under your supervision.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*那個老人嘆了口氣。*#WHITE# 好吧，那我只好在你的監督下來做一些粗略的試驗了。", "_t")
t("[Hand him the orb]", "[交給他水晶球]", "_t")
t("Thank you. Give me a few minutes. #LIGHT_GREEN#*He begins to pace back and forth absently, staring at the Orb.*#WHITE#", "謝謝，給我一點時間。#LIGHT_GREEN#*他開始心不在焉地前後踱着步，盯着水晶球。*#WHITE#", "_t")
t("[Wait]", "[等待]", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*He stops pacing and returns the Orb to you.*#WHITE# I believe I know most of what I need to. But I need a few details cleared up. You'll have to return to this Elven Chronomancer and ask him whether he meant an inverted probabilistic field or a reverted probabilistic field. I dare not guess, as the result could be quite unpleasant for you.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*他停下踱步，回到水晶球前來。*#WHITE# 我想我知道大多數我需要的東西，不過一些細節內容還得搞搞清楚。必須回去找到那個精靈時空法師，問問他到底是使用回覆力場還是反轉力場，我可不敢瞎猜，要不然結果很可能令你不太高興。", "_t")
t("I'll return with the answer.", "我會回去尋找答案的。", "_t")
t("Fear not. Return in a few days, and I'll have everything prepared. Oh, take this. #LIGHT_GREEN#*He hands you a key*#WHITE# It opens the ruins of Telmur, which the men of Sholtar sealed many years ago. If you happen to find a text in the ruins entitled \"Inverted and Reverted Probabilistic Fields\", return with it and your odds of surviving our portal attempt will go up drastically.", "別害怕，幾天後你回來，我肯定把一切都準備好了。哦，帶上這個。 #LIGHT_GREEN#*他交給你一把鑰匙。*#WHITE#他可以打開泰爾瑪廢墟,許多年以前肖塔人被封印在那裏。要是你在廢墟之中找到一份標題是《關於力場翻轉與回覆的可能性研究》的文獻請幫我帶回來，這樣可以使傳送門保留機會大大提高。", "_t")
t("Thank you, and farewell.", "謝謝，再見！", "_t")
t([[I think not, fool. Look down.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*You notice you're standing on an etched portal.*#WHITE#]], [[我可不這麼想，笨蛋，低頭看看。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*你注意到你正站在一個銘文傳送門上。*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t([[I am ready. You are not. Look down.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*You notice you're standing on an etched portal.*#WHITE#]], [[我準備好了，你還沒好，低頭看看。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*你注意到你正站在一個銘文傳送門上。*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t("What in the...", "我X…", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/tarelion-start-archmage.lua"

t("Wait a minute!", "等一下！", "_t")
t("Archmage Tarelion?", "大法師泰爾蘭？", "_t")
t([[Yes @playername@, I have heard you plan on going into the wild world, looking for some adventures of your own.
This is good, more of us should get out of here once in a while and actually help people out there.
Say, maybe you might want to get an adventure and help Angolwen?]], [[是的，@playername@，我聽說你計劃到野外，去尋求冒險。
這樣很好，我們應該多多出去到外面的世界，去幫助那裏的人們。
這麼說，也許你會想進行一場冒險，來幫助安格利文？]], "_t")
t("Perhaps, what do you need?", "也許吧，你想要什麼？", "_t")
t([[During the Spellblaze the world was torn apart - literally. A part of it, that we now call the Abashed Expanse, was ripped from the world and thrown into the void between the stars.
We managed to stabilize it and it is now orbiting Eyal. Recently we have noticed a disturbance there; if we do nothing it will crash onto Eyal, bringing much destruction in its wake.
Because it was once part of a land we know well we can teleport you there. You will need to stabilize three wormholes by firing any attack spells at them.
The instability is also to your advantage there, your simple phase door spell will be fully controllable.

So, you think you can help us ?]], [[魔法大爆炸把這個世界分裂成了幾個碎片。其中一部分，我們稱它爲次元浮島，從這個世界分離了出去，落入了羣星之中的無盡虛空。
我們試圖使它穩定下來，但是現在它正在向埃亞爾大陸飛來。最近我們在那兒也注意到一些騷動，如果我們任其發展它會撞向埃亞爾大陸造成極大的災難。
由於我們以前對那塊大陸比較熟悉，我們可以將你傳送至那裏，你需要向三個不穩定的蟲洞施放各種攻擊性法術使它們穩定下來。
雖然那裏的時空很不穩定，它同時也能給你帶來好處，你的相位之門法術在那裏可以變得完全受你控制。

那麼，你認爲你可以幫助我們麼？]], "_t")
t("Yes Archmage, send me there!", "是的大法師，把我送去那裏！", "_t")
t("No sorry, I need to go.", "不行，抱歉，我得走了。", "_t")
t("Good luck!", "祝你好運！", "_t")
t("[teleport]", "[傳送]", "_t")
t("Oh well, farewell on your trips. Now I need to find somebody else to go up there.", "那好吧，祝你旅途順風，我得找其他人幫我這個忙了。", "_t")
t("Bye.", "再見。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/tarelion.lua"

t([[I say, you there. Yes, you, young one!
You seem like the adventuring fare, up to all sorts of doo-daddle in the outside world, I imagine. Well, don't forget to pay patronage to our good library here in the city. The riches of the world are all well and good, but where would we be without the gift of knowledge? And all proceeds go towards the funding of further research. No greater cause, yes?]], [[我說，那邊那個，對對，就是你，年輕人！
你看上去像一個冒險者之類的，大不了算是一個在外面世界闖蕩的小子。好吧，別忘了爲這個城裏最好的圖書館捐點錢。這個世界的有錢人大多數是好人，但是要是我們沒有知識賜予力量怎麼辦？所有蒐集的資金都會直接用於進一步研究。沒有其他理由了，對麼？]], "_t")
t("Hold on! You... You're that apprentice mage I met in the wilds!", "打住！你……你不就是那個荒野之中的法師學徒麼？", "_t")
t("Why, well-spotted, whippersnapper! Indeed, when the mood takes me I sometimes travel under the guise of an apprentice. It permits me to traverse the land unnoticed in my research, and if I meet any I deem worthy and sympathetic to Angolwen's cause, then so much the better. And it does provide the odd chortle, I tell you!", "你說什麼？你這個傲慢的傢伙！的確我有時會心血來潮假扮成一個學徒到處旅行，這樣在我的研修旅行中就不會引人注意。我會蒐集一切對安格利文有價值的東西，多多益善。不過我告訴你，確實有人藉此來嘲笑我！", "_t")
t("Uh, yes, of course... I'll be moving on now.", "啊，是的，當然……我得繼續趕路了。", "_t")


