section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/temporal-rift-end.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A tall man, glowing like a star, appears out of nowhere.*#WHITE#
You destroyed *it* both? I am sorry for my harsh tone when we first met, but repairing time threads is stressful.
I cannot stay. I still have much to do. But take this-- it should help you.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*He disappears again before you can even reply. A rift opens, to Maj'Eyal... you hope.*#WHITE#]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一個高大的男人，全身像星星一樣閃耀着光芒，在你面前出現了。*#WHITE#
你把它們都摧毀了？真抱歉我們剛見面時候我對你有點刻薄，不過修復時間實在太緊迫了。
我不能留在這裏，我還有很多事情要做。帶上這個，它也許會對你有幫助。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*你剛想回答，他就又消失了。面前出現一道時空裂縫，希望是通往馬基埃亞爾的……*#WHITE#]], "_t")
t("Ok...", "好吧……", "_t")
t("The temporal warden gives you: %s.", "時間守衛給了你： %s", "log")


