section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/ukllmswwik.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@'s deep voice booms through the caverns.*#WHITE#
This is my domain, and I do not take kindly to intruders. What is your purpose here?]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@的低沉嗓音在山洞裏發出隆隆的迴響*#WHITE#
這裏是我的地盤，我會毫不客氣地對付任何入侵者，你到這裏想幹什麼？]], "_t")
t("I am here to kill you and take your treasures! Die, damned fish!", "我是來殺死你然後搶奪你的財寶的，死吧，該死的雜魚！", "_t")
t("I did not mean to intrude. I shall leave now.", "我無意闖入這裏，我會離開的。", "_t")
t([[Wait! You seem to be worthy, so let me tell you a story.
During the Age of Pyre the world was sundered by the last effects of the Spellblaze. A part of the continental shelf of Maj'Eyal was torn apart and thrown into the sea.
The Naloren Elves perished... or so the world thinks. Some of them survived; using ancient Sher'Tul magic they had kept for themselves, they transformed to live underwater.
They are now called the nagas. They live deep in the ocean between Maj'Eyal and the Far East.
One of them, Slasul, rebelled against his order and decided he wanted the world for himself, both underwater and above. He found an ancient temple, probably a Sher'Tul remain, called the Temple of Creation.
He believes he can use it to #{italic}#improve#{normal}# nagas.
But he has become mad and now looks upon all other intelligent water life as a threat, and that includes myself.
I cannot leave this sanctuary, but perhaps you could help me?
After all, it would be an act of mercy to end his madness.]], [[等下！你看上去有點價值，讓我告訴你一個故事。
在派爾紀，世界被魔法大爆炸的餘波撕裂，馬基·埃亞爾的一部分大陸架被撕裂出去漂向了海洋。
納魯精靈種族滅亡了……至少世界上的人都這麼認爲。事實上他們之中的一些人使用古代夏·圖爾的魔法存活了下來，他們轉而在水下生活。
他們現在被稱爲娜迦，他們生活在馬基·埃亞爾和遠東大陸之間的海洋深處。
他們中的一個，薩拉蘇爾，違抗了他的使命，妄圖控制整個水上和水下世界，他發現了一個有可能殘留有夏·圖爾遺蹟的古代神廟，叫做造物者神廟。
他相信可以利用它來#{italic}#進化#{normal}#娜迦。
但是他陷入了瘋狂，把一切水下智慧生物都視爲對他的威脅，包括我自己。
我不能離開這個聖所，但是也許你能幫我結果了他？
畢竟，算是對他瘋狂的一種寬恕吧。]], "_t")
t("DIE!", "去死！", "_t")
t("I would still rather kill you and take your treasure!", "我還是要殺了你，奪取你的財寶！", "_t")
t("I shall do as you say, but how do I find him?", "我會照着你的話去做，但是去哪兒找他呢？", "_t")
t("That seems... unwise. My apologies, but I must refuse.", "這似乎不是明智之舉，很抱歉，我必須拒絕。", "_t")
t("I can open a portal to his lair, far away in the western sea, but be warned: this is one-way only. I cannot bring you back. You will have to find your own way.", "我可以爲你打開一道傳送門，抵達他在西部海洋的巢穴，不過我提醒你：傳送是單程的，我沒法帶你回來，你必須自己去想辦法找到返回的路。", "_t")
t("I will.", "好的。", "_t")
t("This is a death trap! Goodbye.", "這是個陷阱！再見！", "_t")
t("Yes?", "嗯？", "_t")
t("TREACHERY!", "背叛者！", "_t")
t("I want your treasures, water beast!", "我需要你的財寶，水下怪物！", "_t")
t("Oh, is that so? Well, COME GET THEM!", "哦，你確定？好啊，來拿啊！", "_t")
t("I spoke with Slasul, and he did not seem hostile, or mad.", "我詢問過薩拉蘇爾，他貌似不是個壞人，也沒瘋。", "_t")
t("Farewell, dragon.", "告辭了，巨龍。", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@ roars!*#WHITE# You listen to the lies of this mad naga!
You are corrupted! TAINTED!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@ 發出了怒吼！*#WHITE# 你居然聽信這個瘋子娜迦的謊言！
你也一定也墮落了！]], "_t")
t("DO NOT MEDDLE IN THE AFFAIRS OF DRAGONS!", "不要管巨龍的閒事！", "_t")
t("[attack]", "[攻擊]", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*Shake your head.*#LAST#He swayed my mind! Please, I am not your enemy.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*你搖搖頭。*#LAST#好吧，我被他騙了，我不是你的敵人。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@ calms down!*#WHITE# Very well; he is indeed a trickster.  Now go finish your task, or do not come back!", "#LIGHT_GREEN#*@npcname@ 冷靜了下來！*#WHITE# 好吧，他的確是個騙子，那現在去完成你的任務吧，要不然就不要回來了！", "_t")
t("Thank you, mighty one.", "謝謝你，強大的巨龍。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/undead-start-game.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a Human clothed in black robes. He seems to be ignoring you.*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*You stand inside some kind of summoning circle, which prevents you from moving.*#WHITE#
Oh yes! YES, one more for my collection. My collection, yes. A powerful one indeed!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一個穿着黑色長袍的人類，他好像沒有注意到你。*#WHITE#
#LIGHT_GREEN#*你站在一個召喚法陣裏，沒法移動。*#WHITE#
啊，對！好！又一件我的收藏品，沒錯，的確是很強力的一個！]], "_t")
t("[listen]", "[聽他說話]", "_t")
t([[A powerful tool against my enemies. Yes, yes. They all hate me, but I will show them my power!
I will show them! SHOW THEM!]], [[一個對抗敵人的強力工具，對，沒錯，他們都仇恨我，我要讓他們嚐嚐我的厲害！
給他們點顏色看看！等着瞧！]], "_t")
t("I am not a tool! RELEASE ME!", "我不是你的工具！放開我！", "_t")
t([[You cannot talk. You cannot talk! You are a slave, a tool!
You are mine! Be quiet!
#LIGHT_GREEN#*As his mind drifts off you notice part of the summoning circle is fading. You can probably escape!*#WHITE#
]], [[你不可能說話，你不可能說話的啊！你是一個奴隸，一件工具！
你是我的，安靜點！
#LIGHT_GREEN#*當他的注意力開始分散時，你注意到召喚法陣正在消失，你可以逃跑了！*#WHITE#
]], "_t")
t("[attack]", "[攻擊]", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/undead-start-kill.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*He falls to his knees.*#WHITE#
Please spare me! I am pitiful. I will not stop you. Let me leave!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*他跪了下來*#WHITE#
饒恕我吧，饒了我這個可憐的人，我不會再阻止你了，讓我走吧！]], "_t")
t("No!", "不行！", "_t")
t([[But, but, you were my... you...
You need me! What do you think you will do on the surface? Everything you will meet will try to destroy you.
You are strong but you cannot resist them all!]], [[但……但……你是我的……你……
你還需要我！你想你到外面會怎麼樣？所有你見到的東西都會想摧毀你。
你雖然很強，但是你不可能對抗所有人！]], "_t")
t("So what do you propose?", "那你的建議呢？", "_t")
t("[kill him]", "[殺了他]", "_t")
t([[I can give you a cloak that will conceal your true nature!
With it all people will see when they look at you is a normal average Human. You can go about your business.
Please!]], [[我可以給你一件斗篷，讓別人認不出你的本來面目。
穿着它你的外形看上去就會像一個普通人一樣，不會引起別人的注意，這樣你就可以幹任何你想幹的事了。
求求你！]], "_t")
t("Thanks for the information. Now you may die. [kill him]", "謝謝你的幫忙，現在你可以死了。[殺了他]", "_t")
t("ARRGGggg... You are alone! You will be destroyed!", "啊啊啊啊噶……你孤身一人！註定走向毀滅！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/unremarkable-cave-bosses.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*A beautiful Elven woman in golden robes stands before you, facing an orc clad in mail.*#WHITE#
Fillarel: "Abandon this fight, orc! You cannot win: I stand with the power of the Sun and the shadows of the Moons."
Krogar: "Ha! It's only been one hour and you already look tired, my 'lady'."
#LIGHT_GREEN#*As you enter the room they notice you.*#WHITE#
Fillarel: "You! @playerdescriptor.race@! Help me defeat this monster or begone!"
Krogar: "Ah, looking for help? Bah. @playerdescriptor.race@, kill this wench for me and I shall reward you!"]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*一個穿着金色長袍的美麗精靈女子站在你面前，看着穿鎖甲的獸人。*#WHITE#
菲拉瑞爾：“投降吧，獸人！你不會贏的，我擁有太陽和月亮的神力。”
克羅格： "哈！才過了一個小時了，而你看上去已經很疲憊了，我的女士。"
#LIGHT_GREEN#*當你進入房間時他們注意到了你*#WHITE#
菲拉瑞爾： "你！ @playerdescriptor.race@!幫我幹掉這隻怪物，要不然給我滾開！"
克羅格： "哦？找人幫忙了？呸，@playerdescriptor.race@，給我幹掉這個臭婊子，我會報答你的！]], "_t")
t("[attack Krogar]", "[攻擊克羅格]", "_t")


