section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/unremarkable-cave-fillarel.lua"

t("Thank you, @playername@. I hate to admit it, but you saved my life.", "謝謝你，@playername@。不得不承認，你救了我的命。", "_t")
t("At your service. But may I ask what you were doing in this dark place?", "很榮幸，但你是否可以告訴我你在這個黑暗的地方幹什麼？", "_t")
t("At your service. I have been gone for months, but I can feel it, at last this is my homeland!", "很榮幸，我已經流浪幾個月了，不過我能夠感覺到，這裏就是我的故鄉！", "_t")
t([[I am an Anorithil, a mage of the Sun and Moons; we fight all that is evil. I was with a group of Sun Paladins; we came from the Gates of Morning to the east.
My companions were... were slaughtered by orcs, and I nearly died as well. Thank you again for your help.]], [[我是一位星月術士，操縱太陽和月亮的神力的法師。我和一羣太陽騎士一起對抗邪惡。我們來自東部的晨曦之門。
我的夥伴們…都被獸人殺死了，我也差點喪命，再次感謝你的幫助。]], "_t")
t("It was my pleasure. But may I ask a favor myself? I am not from these lands. I used a farportal guarded by orcs deep below the Iron Throne and was brought here.", "我的榮幸，不過我有個請求？我不是這個大陸的人，我使用了鋼鐵王座地下深處獸人保護的遠古傳送門，然後就到了這裏。", "_t")
t([[Yes, I noticed you were not from here. Your only hope is the Gates of Morning, the last bastion of freedom in this orc territory. When you leave the caves, head southeast; you cannot miss it.
Tell High Sun Paladin Aeryn that you met me. I'll send word to let you pass.]], [[是的，我也注意到了你不是這裏的人，晨曦之門，這座獸人領地中僅存的自由基地，將是你的唯一希望，當你離開洞穴，往東南方走就可以到達那裏。
告訴高階太陽騎士艾琳你碰到我的事，我會留下口信讓他們給你放行。]], "_t")
t("Thank you, I will talk with Aeryn.", "謝謝你，我會找艾琳談談的。", "_t")
t([[Gone? Wait, this face.. you are @playername@! We thought you died in the naga portal explosion!
Thanks to your courage the Gates of Morning still stand.
You should go there at once.]], [[流浪？等一下，你是……你是 @playername@！我們都以爲你在娜迦傳送門爆炸的時候死了！
感謝你的勇氣，晨曦之門能夠保存完好。
你應該馬上去那裏。]], "_t")
t("Sadly I am the bringer of bad news, the orcs are planning something. Good luck, my lady.", "恐怕我得告訴你一些壞消息，獸人正籌劃着什麼陰謀，祝你好運，我的女士。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/unremarkable-cave-krogar.lua"

t("@playerdescriptor.race@, you have helped me kill the Elf-wench. The Orc Pride thanks you... for now", "@playerdescriptor.race@，你幫我幹掉了那個精靈臭婊子，獸人部落感謝你的幫助。", "_t")
t("I hate Elves anyway...", "我討厭精靈……", "_t")


