section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/yeek-wayist.lua"

t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*Before you stands a creature about as tall as a Halfling, covered in small white fur and with a disproportionate head.
You also notice he does not wield his greatsword. It seems to float in the air, bound to his will.*#WHITE#
Why did you save me, stranger? You are not of the Way.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*在你面前站着一個和半身人一樣高的生物，擁有白色的毛髮和不成比例的腦袋。
你同時注意到他不是用手在握持一把長劍，而是把劍漂浮在空中，像是受他的意志控制一樣。*#WHITE#
你爲什麼救我，陌生人？你不是維網的人。]], "_t")
t("Well, you seemed to need help.", "好吧，你看上去似乎需要幫助。", "_t")
t("So I could rip your throat myself!", "這樣我可以親自割破你的喉嚨！", "_t")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*The greatsword floats to a less aggressive stance. He seems surprised.*#WHITE#
Then, on behalf of the Way, I thank you.]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*大劍在空中後退了些，顯得不那麼有敵意。他好像很吃驚。*#WHITE#
那麼我代表維網感謝你。]], "_t")
t("What is the Way, and what are you?", "維網是什麼東西，你是誰？", "_t")
t("The Way is enlightenment, peace and protection. I am a Yeek. I came through this tunnel to explore this part of the world that was closed to us for centuries.", "維網是啓迪、和平和守護，我是一個奪心魔。我穿過隧道來到這個和我們的世界隔絕了幾千年的世界來探險。", "_t")
t("Can you tell me more about the Way?", "你能告訴我更多有關維網的事麼？", "_t")
t("Select the party member to receive the mental shield:", "選擇接受精神豁免的隊伍成員：", "_t")
t("The contact with the Wayist mind has improved your mental shields. (+15 mental save, +10%% confusion resistance)", "與奪心魔的接觸提高了你的精神防禦。（+15精神豁免，+10%%混亂抵抗）", "logPlayer")
t("I am never alone. I have the Way.", "我不是一個人，我擁有維網。", "_t")
t("Farewell, then.", "那麼，再見。", "_t")
t([[I cannot, but I may show you a glimpse.
#LIGHT_GREEN#*He leans toward you. Your mind is suddenly filled with feelings of peace and happiness.*#WHITE#
This is the Way.]], [[不行，不過我可以讓你看一下。
#LIGHT_GREEN#*他靠向你，你的精神突然充滿和平和幸福的感覺。*#WHITE#
這就是維網。]], "_t")
t("Thank you for this vision. Farewell, my friend.", "謝謝你讓我看到這些，再見吧，我的朋友。", "_t")
t("Thank the Way. This... thing... would have killed me.", "感謝維網，這個……東西……差點殺了我。", "_t")
t("The Way sent me to explore this side of the tunnel.", "維網指引我來搜查這個隧道。", "_t")
t("Yes, me too. We should split up to cover more ground.", "是的我也是，我們應該分頭去探索這個大陸。", "_t")
t("Farewell. We are the Way, always.", "再見，維網和我們同在。", "_t")


