t("drem", "德瑞姆", "entity name")
t("A small faceless humanoid with vaguely Dwarven features.  Its waraxe and shield look battered, rusted, and generally in ill repair.", "身材矮小且擁有部分矮人特徵的人形怪物。它的戰斧和盾牌看起來又鏽又鈍，幾乎從未修理過。", "_t")
t("dremling", "德瑞姆亞種", "entity name")
t("A giant black-skinned humanoid covered in spikey scabrous deposits.  Its face is featureless; its eyesockets, empty and hollow.", "皮膚粗糙且長有角質骨刺的黑色巨人。它沒有明顯的臉部特徵，眼神空曠而呆滯。", "_t")
t("drem master", "德瑞姆領主", "entity name")
t("A disfigured humanoid with vaguely Dwarven features dressed in patched-together and rusted mail armor.  It seems to be in command of others, though its mouth is sewn shut.", "醜陋且具有部分矮人特徵的人形怪物，它裝備了一件破爛不堪的重甲。儘管它無法說話，但是它卻領導着其他矮人。", "_t")
t("brecklorn", "布瑞克隆", "entity name")
t("A giant hairless bat with the face of a Dwarf twisted into a constant scream.  Pustulant sores cover its malformed body, and your heart weakens as it nears.", "一隻巨大的無毛蝙蝠，它有着一張不停尖叫且扭曲的矮人臉。躁狂症症在它畸形的身體內蔓延，當它靠近時，你感覺心跳都快停止了。", "_t")
t("grannor'vor", "格蘭諾伏爾", "entity name")
t("A large sluglike creature that moves slowly, leaving a trail of acid in its wake.  Its head has strangely humanoid features.", "一隻長的類似蛞蝓的生物，當它緩慢經過時，會留下一灘酸性的蹤跡。它的頭部有着奇怪的人類特徵。", "_t")
t("grannor'vin", "格蘭諾文", "entity name")
t("A large sluglike creature with the face of a man.  Shadows seem to be drawn to its massive form, and your light dims as it approaches.", "一隻長有人臉的類似蛞蝓的生物。陰影似乎都被扯向了它厚重的身體，當它靠近你時，燈光似乎都模糊了。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/horror-undead.lua"

t("horror", "恐魔", "entity subtype")
t("undead", "亡靈", "entity type")
t("necrotic mass", "亡靈集合", "entity name")
t("This putrid mass of rotting flesh shifts and quivers, but shows no signs of intelligence or mobility.", "這塊腐爛的血肉不斷變形顫抖，不過似乎沒有智力和移動力。", "_t")
t("necrotic abomination", "亡靈憎惡", "entity name")
t("This monstrous form of putrid, torn flesh and chipped bone drags its mass towards you, spurting blood and viscera along the way.", "這塊腐爛的被切碎的血肉，掙扎着向你移動，在路上噴出的血液和內臟。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#As the necrotic abomination is destroyed you see the remaining bones and flesh reassembling in the form of new foes!", "#VIOLET#當亡靈憎惡被摧毀時，你發現它的剩餘部分重組爲新的敵人！", "logSeen")
t("bone horror", "骨靈恐魔", "entity name")
t("The massive ribcage in the middle beats with loud, audible cracks, as many a skeletal hand protrude forth, entwining, fusing, forming long skeletal appendages to support itself, while others crumble and collapse inward. During all this, somehow, it seems they grasp for you.", "中空的胸腔裏傳出巨大的破碎聲，似乎許多骷髏在裏面，突出，纏繞，融合，形成長長的骨架來支撐它，而其他部分倒塌向內。與此同時，似乎它們都想抓住你。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#As the bone horror is destroyed you see the remaining bones reassembling in the form of new foes!", "#VIOLET#當骨靈恐魔被摧毀時，你發現它的剩餘部分重組爲新的敵人！", "logSeen")
t("sanguine horror", "血紅恐魔", "entity name")
t("This pulsing, quivering form is a deep crimson, and appears to be composed entirely of thick, virulent blood. Waves rhythmically ripple across its surface, indicating a still beating heart somewhere in its body.", "這個不斷跳動不斷顫抖的物體是深紅色的，似乎完全由濃厚致命的血液組成。在其表面仍有富有節奏的波紋，也許在其身上的某個地方仍有心臟跳動", "_t")
t("animated blood", "活化血液", "entity name")
t("blood", "血", "entity subtype")
t("This crimson shape drips ceaselessly, spattering the nearby ground. The droplets seem to continue moving of their own volition.", "血紅色的物體不斷滴落液體，散落在地面上。滴落下來的血液似乎有着自己的意志。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/horror.lua"

t("horror", "恐魔", "entity type")
t("worm that walks", "蠕蟲合體", "entity name")
t([[A bulging rotten robe seems to tear at the seams, with masses of bloated worms spilling out all around the moving form.  Two arm-like appendages, each made up of overlapping mucous-drenched maggots, grasp tightly around the handles of bile-coated waraxes.
Each swing drips pustulant fluid before it, and each droplet writhes and wriggles in the air before splashing against the ground.]], "一件鼓鼓囊囊的長袍，長袍的縫隙裏不斷蠕動着浮腫的蠕蟲。它有着兩隻臂膀一樣的附屬物，每隻手都由重疊的蠕蟲組成，各握着一柄覆有膽汁的斧子。每次揮舞武器的時，它都會濺出屍僵毒液，每滴毒液在落到地面前都在沸騰和翻滾着。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_RED#A carrion worm mass has spawned from %s' wounds!", "#LIGHT_RED#一團腐肉蟲從%s的傷口了孵化了出來。", "logSeen")
t("bloated horror", "浮腫恐魔", "entity name")
t("A bulbous humanoid form floats here. Its bald, child-like head is disproportionately large compared to its body, and its skin is pock-marked with nasty red sores.", "這是一隻有着人頭的漂浮物。它的孩子似的光頭大的不成比例，並且它還有着滿身惡臭的膿瘡。", "_t")
t("nightmare horror", "夢魘恐魔", "entity name")
t("A shifting form of darkest night that seems to reflect your deepest fears.", "一隻漆黑的生物，它深邃的黑色身體反射出了你深深的恐懼。", "_t")
t("headless horror", "無頭恐魔", "entity name")
t("A headless, gangly humanoid with a large distended stomach.", "一個由閃光水晶構成的生物，它通體圍繞着球狀的光芒。", "_t")
t("#AQUAMARINE#As %s falls all its eyes fall to the ground!", "#AQUAMARINE#當%s倒下時它的眼睛掉落在了地上。", "logSeen")
t("eldritch eye", "艾爾德里奇之眼", "entity name")
t("A small bloodshot eye floats here.", "一隻小小的充血眼球，它遊蕩在這裏。", "_t")
t("#AQUAMARINE#As #Source# falls #Target# seems to weaken!", "#AQUAMARINE#當#Source#倒下時，#Target#似乎被削弱了！", "logCombat")
t("+Blind", "+致盲", "_t")
t("%s is blinded by the loss of all its eyes.", "%s 失去了它所有的眼睛，無法看見東西。", "logSeen")
t("luminous horror", "金色恐魔", "entity name")
t("A lanky humanoid shape composed of yellow light.", "一隻身材瘦長的怪物，它的身體由金色的光芒組成。", "_t")
t("radiant horror", "灼眼恐魔", "entity name")
t("A lanky four-armed humanoid shape composed of bright golden light.  It's so bright it's hard to look at, and you can feel heat radiating outward from it.", "一隻身材瘦長的四臂人形怪物，它的身體由金色的光芒組成。它的光芒令人無法直視，你可以感受到高溫從它身上不斷的向外輻射。", "_t")
t("devourer", "吞噬者", "entity name")
t("A headless, round creature with stubby legs and arms.  Its body seems to be all teeth.", "一隻無頭怪物，它有着圓潤的體型和又粗又短的四肢。它的牙齒似乎佔據了整個身體。", "_t")
t("blade horror", "刀鋒恐魔", "entity name")
t("Blades whirl in the air around this thin, floating figure. The air around it swirls with force, threatening to tear apart anything that approches, if the blades don't do it first.", "刀鋒環繞在這隻薄薄的漂浮着的恐魔周圍。它周圍的空氣中環繞着鋒利的能量，撕裂着靠近的任何東西。", "_t")
t("oozing horror", "黏液恐魔", "entity name")
t("A massive, amorphous blob of green slime crawls on the ground towards you. Eyes drift through the viscous mass, scanning for potential prey.", "一個巨大的有着綠色斑點的黏糊糊的物體從地上爬過來。在一堆黏糊糊中隱藏着的眼睛，尋找着潛藏的獵物。", "_t")
t("eldritch", "艾爾德里奇", "entity subtype")
t("umbral horror", "暗影恐魔", "entity name")
t("A dark shifting shape stalks through the shadows, blending in seamlessly.", "一個閃過黑暗的陰影，迅速遁入了無盡的黑暗。", "_t")
t("dreaming horror", "夢境恐魔", "entity name")
t([[A vaguely tentacled yet constantly changing form rests here apparently oblivious to your existence.
With each slow breath it takes reality distorts around it.  Blue twirls into red, green twists into yellow, and the air sings softly before bursting into a myriad of pastel shapes and colors.]], [[這是一隻混沌狀的觸手生物，它在這裏愜意的休息並不斷的變幻着顏色，顯然無視了你的存在。
它的每次呼吸都會使周圍的空間發生輕微的扭曲。在它身上氤氳着的光芒由藍轉紅、由綠轉黃，交織成一片五彩繽紛的和諧幻景。]], "_t")
t("It looks asleep and dreamy.", "它看上去沉浸在睡夢之中。", "_t")
t("It looks awake, beware!", "它醒來了，小心！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#A dream seed escapes %s's sleeping mind.", "#LIGHT_BLUE#一個夢境之種從%s的沉眠中釋放", "logSeen")
t([[A vaguely tentacled yet rapidly changing shape floats here.  With each breath you can feel reality twist, shatter, and break. 
Blue burns into red, green bursts into yellow, and the air crackles and hisses before exploding into a thousand fragments of sharp shapes and colors.]], "這是一隻混沌狀的觸手生物，它在這裏愜意的休息並不斷的變幻着顏色，顯然無視了你的存在。它的每次呼吸都會使周圍的空間發生輕微的扭曲。在它身上氤氳着的光芒由藍轉紅、由綠轉黃，交織成一片五彩繽紛的和諧幻景。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#The sleeper stirs...", "#LIGHT_BLUE#有人打擾了沉睡者的沉眠...", "logSeen")
t("dream seed", "夢境之種", "entity name")
t("A pinkish bubble floats here, reflecting the world not as it is, but as it would be in that surreal place that exists only in our dreams.", "這是一個漂浮着的粉紅色泡沫，它似乎能夠反映出世界的另一面，但是由於這虛幻的空間，它所反映的事物只可能存在於我們的夢境中。", "_t")
t("maelstrom", "靈能漩渦", "entity name")
t("This powerful vortex of ice and lightning somehow gives you the impression of claws, teeth and intense hunger...", "這個強大的靈能漩渦莫名其妙地給你一種利齒尖牙和飢餓的印象...", "_t")
t("parasitic horror", "寄生恐魔", "entity name")
t("You don't want to think about what sort of creature this lamprey-like horror was feeding on to grow so large.  Its skin pulsates and writhes, like things are moving underneath...", "你不想知道這個像七鰓鰻一樣的恐魔是吃什麼才能長這麼大的。它的皮膚不停的扭動，就像有東西在下面移動一樣...", "_t")
t("%s's severed flesh starts crawling!", "%s被切割的血肉開始爬行！", "logSeen")
t("mass of parasitic leeches", "大團寄生蟲", "entity name")
t("Dozens - hundreds maybe? - of blood-gorged worms, of varying shapes and sizes, making a writhing, ichor-soaked sea of tooth-lined maws and sickly green skin, ready to latch onto you and drink until they burst or your veins run dry.", "幾十個，也許幾百個？各種形狀和大小的血腥蠕蟲，形成一個扭動的，佈滿鋒利牙齒的血盆大口和生病的綠色皮膚組成的膿水海洋，隨時準備纏住你並吸你的血，直到它們脹破或着你的靜脈乾涸。", "_t")
t("Grgglck the Devouring Darkness", "格爾格勒克·黑暗吞噬者", "entity name")
t([[A horror from the deepest pits of the earth. It looks like a huge pile of tentacles all trying to reach for you.
You can discern a huge round mouth covered in razor-sharp teeth.]], "這是來自地底最深處的恐魔。看起來像是一團巨大觸手，它在不斷的向你靠近。你可以在它那血盆大口裏看到剃刀般的牙齒。", "_t")
t("Grgglck's Tentacle", "格爾格勒克的觸鬚", "entity name")
t("This is one of Grgglck's tentacles. It looks more vulnerable than the main body.", "這是格爾格勒克的一條觸鬚。它看起來比主體更加脆弱。", "_t")
t("#AQUAMARINE#With Grgglck's death its tentacle also falls lifeless on the ground!", "#AQUAMARINE#隨着格爾格勒克的死去它的那些觸手也毫無生機地倒在了地上！", "logSeen")
t("#AQUAMARINE#As #Source# falls you notice that #Target# seems to shudder in pain!", "#AQUAMARINE#當#Source#倒下時，你發現#Target#似乎因爲痛苦而顫抖!", "logCombat")
t("Ak'Gishil", "阿克·吉希爾", "entity name")
t("This Blade Horror has been infused with intense temporal magic, causing its power to increase dramatically. Rifts in space open around it constantly, summoning and banishing blades before vanishing as quickly as they appear.", "這隻刀鋒般的恐魔生於強大的能量漩渦中，並逐漸掌握了時空之核。它能夠不斷的撕裂空間，召喚出成羣的刀刃在其身周飛舞。", "_t")
t("Animated Sword", "次元之刃", "entity name")
t("Time seems to warp and bend around this floating weapon.", "時空在其周圍扭曲。", "_t")
t("#AQUAMARINE#A rift opens and a free floating blade emerges!", "#AQUAMARINE#時空裂縫打開了，裏面出現了一把浮空的刀刃!", "logSeen")
t("construct", "機關", "entity type")
t("weapon", "武器", "entity subtype")
t("Distorted Animated Sword", "極·次元之刃", "entity name")
t("This floating weapon shifts and shimmers, time and space warping and bending as it moves. It appears to vibrate, as if it may explode at any moment.", "時空在其周圍崩塌。", "_t")
t("#AQUAMARINE#A rift opens and a free floating blade emerges! It looks unstable...", "#AQUAMARINE#時空裂縫打開了，裏面出現了一把浮空的刀刃!它看起來很不穩定…", "logSeen")
t("#AQUAMARINE#The %s no longer seems to be controlled and clatters to the ground before vanishing into a rift.", "#AQUAMARINE#%s 似乎失去了控制，墜落在地面，消失在時空裂隙中。", "logSeen")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/horror_aquatic.lua"

t("aquatic", "水棲生物", "entity subtype")
t("horror", "恐魔", "entity type")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#%s explodes into a huge bubble of air!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#%s爆炸，成爲了一個巨大的氣泡!", "logSeen")
t("entrenched horror", "巨石恐魔 ", "entity name")
t("This massive stony structure shifts and pulsates, its many long, thin tentacles probing the nearby water for food.", "這個巨大的石狀生物有規律的震動着，它的觸手爲了水和食物正在四處遊走探測。", "_t")
t("swarming horror", "羣生恐魔", "entity name")
t("This tiny fish-like creature moves erratically, but is constantly surrounded by others of its kind.", "體型小的、象魚一樣的怪物，總是成羣出現。", "_t")
t("ravenous horror", "貪婪恐魔", "entity name")
t("A vile looking liquid flows from the teeth of this agile monster. It glides through the water towards you, spined fins jutting outwards.", "這個醜陋怪物的牙齒中不斷滴落邪惡的液體。", "_t")
t("boiling horror", "沸騰恐魔", "entity name")
t("This frothing ball of water rages with an intense heat.", "這個充滿泡沫的水球有着極高的溫度。", "_t")
t("swarm hive", "育種恐魔", "entity name")
t("This titanic mass of flesh pulsates and churns as tiny monsters burst from its orifices.", "巨大的肉塊在不斷振動、搖晃，從孔口處不斷涌現生物。", "_t")
t("abyssal horror", "深淵恐魔", "entity name")
t("This pitch black form is shrouded in darkness. All you can make out are a pair of deep red eyes, hidden behind a mass of tentacles.", "這個深黑的物體被黑暗圍繞，你只能認出一對猩紅的眼睛，藏在一堆觸手後面。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/horror_temporal.lua"

t("horror", "恐魔", "entity type")
t("dredgling", "墜靈恐魔", "entity name")
t("A small pink-skinned humanoid with large bulbous eyes.", "一隻小小的紅皮人型生物，它有着巨大的眼睛。", "_t")
t("dredge", "挖掘魔", "entity name")
t("A hulking pink-skinned creature with long arms as thick as tree trunks.  It drags its knuckles on the ground as it lumbers toward you.", "一隻灰色皮膚的生物，它的手臂像樹幹一樣粗壯有力。它拖動着膝關節，緩慢的向你爬過來。", "_t")
t("dredge captain", "挖掘魔首領", "entity name")
t("A thin pink-skinned creature with long spindly arms.  Half its body is old and wrinkly, and the other half appears quite young.", "一隻灰色皮膚的生物，它的手臂像樹幹一樣粗壯有力。它的半邊身體又老又皺，另外半邊身體則顯得格外年輕。", "_t")
t("temporal stalker", "時空獵手", "entity name")
t("A slender metallic monstrosity with long claws in place of fingers, and razor-sharp teeth.", "瘦長的金屬怪物，它有着金屬的爪子和鋒利的牙齒。", "_t")
t("temporal", "時空", "entity subtype")
t("void horror", "虛空靨魔", "entity name")
t("It looks like a hole in spacetime, but you get the impression it's somehow more than that.", "它乍一看像是時空中的一道縫隙，但你對它的印象遠遠不止於此。", "_t")
t("%s has collapsed in upon itself.", "%s自爆了。", "logSeen")


