section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/jelly.lua"

t("immovable", "靜態類", "entity type")
t("jelly", "果凍怪", "entity subtype")
t("A strange blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團奇怪膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("green jelly", "綠果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange green blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團綠色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("red jelly", "紅果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange red blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團紅色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("blue jelly", "藍果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange blue blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團藍色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("white jelly", "白果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange white blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團白色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("yellow jelly", "黃果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange yellow blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團黃色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("black jelly", "黑果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange black blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團黑色膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("Malevolent Dimensional Jelly", "惡毒次元果凍怪", "entity name")
t("A strange black blob on the dungeon floor; through it you seem to be able to see other times and places. As you stare you see things moving out of it.", "地板上的一團黑色膠狀物體。通過它的身體可以看到異次元，當你盯着它時，你發現有東西正從它身體裏冒出來。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/lich.lua"

t("undead", "亡靈", "entity type")
t("Only the most powerful spellcasters raised to unlife become liches. Doomed to haunt the world for an eternity, they have grown to hate all that breathes or trespasses on their domain. Unfortunately that includes you.", "只有最強大的法師，纔會被複活成爲巫妖。他們註定要永遠縈繞在這個世界上，他們憎恨所有在他們的領地上呼吸或侵入的人。不幸的是，這包括你在內。", "_t")
t("lich", "巫妖", "entity name")
t("Having thought to discover life eternal, these beings have allowed undeath to rob them of the joys of life. Now they seek to destroy it as well.", "爲了探索永恆的生命，這些人允許不死族剝奪他們的生趣。現在，他們同樣在毀滅生者。", "_t")
t("ancient lich", "遠古巫妖", "entity name")
t("An elder being from a now-forgotten age, filled and fueled by its hate and rage toward all things living, it seeks to deprive all others of a prize it cannot have... life.", "一位存活了不知多少歲月的巫妖，它對這個世界和生者充滿了仇恨，所以它試圖去剝奪生者所擁有而它所沒有的財富——生命。", "_t")
t("archlich", "高階巫妖", "entity name")
t("Blacker than the deepest night, this cold cruel form of darkness approaches.  Long ago it laid aside its mortality, but it has not forgotten its power; rather, its malice and hate have bent this undead entity on the destruction of all things living.", "從比漆黑的夜還要深邃的黑暗中，你感受到了一股冰冷的寒意。很久以前它放棄了生命，但卻沒忘記力量，相反，它被怨恨和邪念所強化，這隻扭曲的不死生物要毀滅所有的生者。", "_t")
t("blood lich", "血巫妖", "entity name")
t("The seething, pumping, disembodied blood of a horrendously powerful necromancer. To strike it is to bathe in the rivers of the Fearscape itself.", "來自一位非常強大的死靈法師的沸騰的、跳動的、有形的血液。跟它戰鬥等於要飽受惡魔空間的摧殘。", "_t")


