section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/major-demon.lua"

t("demon", "惡魔", "entity type")
t("major", "大惡魔", "entity subtype")
t("dolleg", "多雷格", "entity name")
t("A monstrous demon, covered in acidic thorns.", "一隻畸形的惡魔，身上長有酸性尖刺。", "_t")
t("dúathedlen", "多瑟頓", "entity name")
t("Under a shroud of darkness you discern an evil shape.", "在黑暗之霧的籠罩下，依稀可見惡魔的形態。", "_t")
t("uruivellas", "烏爾維拉斯", "entity name")
t([[This demon would look like a minotaur, if a minotaur had a fiery aura surrounding it and horns all over its body.
Oh, and it is twice as big, too.]], "這隻惡魔長的類似於一隻擁有熾焰光環的米諾陶斯，並且這隻米諾陶斯全身長滿了尖角。哦，還有兩倍大的體型……", "_t")
t("thaurhereg", "修爾希瑞格", "entity name")
t("This terrible demon is covered in blood, which flows *on* its skin in ever-changing patterns that disturb you simply when looking at it.", "這隻可怕的惡魔渾身是血，鮮血在它的身上以某種形式流淌。僅僅看了一眼，你就感到渾身不舒服。", "_t")
t("daelach", "達萊奇", "entity name")
t([[You can only guess at the real shape of this demon. Its body is surrounded by a cloud of fiery darkness.
It moves swiftly toward you, casting terrible spells and swinging its weapons at you.]], "你無法猜測這隻惡魔的真實形態。它的身體被一層熾熱的黑暗所籠罩。它向你發起快速的衝鋒，同時向你發射致命的法術。", "_t")
t("champion of Urh'Rok", "烏魯洛克的精英衛兵", "entity name")
t("One of Urh'Rok's own champions. A thousand nightmares made flesh and screaming steel tower before you in the form of a massive, armored humanoid.", "烏魯洛克精英衛隊的一員。千年的夢魘使血肉和被詛咒的鋼鐵融合爲一只鋼鐵怪物站在你面前。", "_t")
t("forge-giant", "鍛造巨人", "entity name")
t("A burning giant wielding a forge hammer of the underworld in each hand -- weapons imbued by Urh'Rok himself with the power to crush and shape felsteel. Enter their range at your peril.", "鍛造巨人的每隻手都有一柄地底鍛造巨錘——被烏魯洛克加持以鍛造魔鋼的巨錘。進入他們的領地是極度危險的事情。", "_t")
t("Khulmanar, General of Urh'Rok", "庫馬納·烏魯洛克之近衛將軍", "entity name")
t("This massive form, sheathed in dark flames, stands tall above a legion of lesser demons. In his hands he holds a massive blackened battleaxe, flames dancing around the blades.", "這個龐大的軀體籠罩在黑暗之炎中，他在一羣小惡魔中顯得鶴立雞羣。在他手裏握着一柄沉重的雙手斧，火焰在刀鋒處舞動。", "_t")


