section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/sandworm.lua"

t("vermin", "害蟲", "entity type")
t("sandworm", "沙蟲", "entity name")
t("A huge worm coloured as the sand it inhabits. It seems quite unhappy about you being in its lair.", "一隻僞裝成沙子顏色的巨大沙蟲。它很不高興你闖入它的地盤。", "_t")
t("sandworm destroyer", "沙蟲毀滅者", "entity name")
t("A huge worm coloured as the sand it inhabits. This particular sandworm seems to have been bred for one purpose only: the eradication of everything that is non-sandworm, such as... you.", "一隻僞裝成沙子顏色的巨大沙蟲。這隻特殊的沙蟲生來只有一個目標：消滅所有非沙蟲的異類，比如……你。", "_t")
t("sand-drake", "沙蜉蝣", "entity name")
t("dragon", "龍", "entity type")
t("sand", "沙", "entity subtype")
t("This unholy creature looks like a wingless dragon in shape, but it is sand-colored, making it all the more dangerous for its prey.", "這隻邪惡的生物從體型上看更像一隻短翼龍，並且和沙蟲一樣僞裝自己。", "_t")
t("gigantic sandworm tunneler", "巨大沙蟲挖掘者", "entity name")
t("The ground shakes as this huge worm burrows towards you, its gigantic mouth just as capable of devouring flesh as stone.", "這隻巨大的沙蟲挖地道靠近你時，大地在震顫。它的巨口似乎能吞下和石頭一樣硬的獵物。", "_t")
t("gigantic gravity worm", "巨大重力沙蟲", "entity name")
t("Space and time seem to bend around this huge worm.", "這隻沙蟲似乎扭曲了周圍的時空。", "_t")
t("gigantic corrosive tunneler", "巨大腐蝕挖掘者", "entity name")
t("This huge worm burrows through the earth using its powerful corrosive saliva.", "這隻巨大的沙蟲使用它腐蝕性的唾液挖掘泥土。", "_t")
t("%s explodes in an acidic cloud.", "%s 爆炸產生了一團酸霧。", "logSeen")


