section "game/modules/tome/data/general/npcs/skeleton.lua"

t("skeleton", "骷髏", "entity subtype")
t("undead", "亡靈", "entity type")
t("degenerated skeleton warrior", "腐化骷髏戰士", "entity name")
t("A haphazard collection of crumbling bones, with jerky movements that remind you of a child playing with a marionette.  It only has one arm, but that's all it needs to hold a sword.", "這具彷彿是死靈法師隨意收集而成的，搖搖欲墜的骨骸，生澀地從你的眼前走過，彷彿孩童手中玩弄的木偶。雖然它只有一條手臂，不過反正這對於拿一把劍也夠了，對吧。", "_t")
t("degenerated skeleton archer", "腐化骷髏弓箭手", "entity name")
t("A frail skeleton; just about the only bones that aren't cracked are its arms.  It's missing a hand, but a notch has been carved into its wrist to let it pull back a bowstring regardless.", "這具破爛不堪的骨架只有一根骨頭是好的：它手持長弓的手臂。儘管它缺少了一隻手，不過殘缺的骨骼上雕刻的凹槽剛好可以卡住弓弦拉弓上箭。", "_t")
t("skeleton mage", "骷髏法師", "entity name")
t("Given its condition, you're less inclined to think this skeleton knows proper spells, rather than simply disgorging its magical energy as it breaks down.  This doesn't make it much less dangerous to be around, mind you.", "看着它殘破的樣子，你與其相信這隻骷髏會釋放魔法，不如相信是在它身軀逐漸破碎的同時將奧術能量胡亂噴射出來。不過，這一點也沒有降低它的危險性，小心。", "_t")
t("skeleton warrior", "骷髏戰士", "entity name")
t("The forces binding this skeleton together are resilient enough to let it hold a shield and swing a weapon as well as it could have in life.  It's still wearing its old armor, in rusty but servicable condition.", "施展在這隻骷髏身上的魔法已經足夠靈活，足以讓它像還活着的時候那樣嚴陣以待，揮動武器。它仍然穿着它原來的那件老盔甲，鏽跡斑斑卻值得信賴。", "_t")
t("skeleton archer", "骷髏弓箭手", "entity name")
t("Nobody scavenged the high-quality bow from this archer before it was raised from the dead.  You're about to wish the world had more grave-robbers.", "在被複活之前，這位弓箭手的遺體上居然還保留着一張還不錯的弓。你開始覺得，世界上如果有更多的盜墓賊就好了。", "_t")
t("skeleton magus", "骷髏魔導師", "entity name")
t("This skeleton has been imbued with far more magical energy than normal, and serves as a conduit of its master's spellcasting prowess.", "這隻骷髏的身上充盈着更加豐沛的魔法力量，作爲它的主人強大魔力的明證。", "_t")
t("armoured skeleton warrior", "武裝骷髏戰士", "entity name")
t("It feels no pain.  It moves with fluidity and strength that would tear natural muscles apart.  It must be from a fresh corpse, since its bones, armor, and weapon are all in pristine condition.  And it's furious.", "這隻骷髏戰士沒有任何痛感，它的動作行雲流水，強大的揮斬足以將常人的肌肉撕裂。它一定是來自一具新鮮的屍體：它的骨頭、裝甲和武器還是嶄新的。並且，他彷彿怒不可遏。", "_t")
t("skeleton master archer", "骷髏弓箭手大師", "entity name")
t("This skeleton can fire arrows and nock new ones with blinding speed.  Arcane forces pull its bones with unnatural precision - its arms will never tremble or get tired.", "這隻骷髏可以飛速的拈弓射箭，奧術的力量使它的身軀達到了常人無法企及的精確度——它的射擊永遠不會顫動，也永遠不會疲累。", "_t")
t("skeleton assassin", "骷髏刺客", "entity name")
t("Most skeletons announce their presence with a chorus of rattling bones; this one's been charred black and has enough cartilage between its joints to muffle its approach.  The first you'll see of it will be the flash of its blade.", "普通骷髏骨節之間的吱嘎猛響會早早暴露他們的行蹤，但這隻骷髏的身軀被燒焦成暗夜的黑色，關節間的軟骨緩衝着骨節的轉動。當你看到它時，它銀光閃耀的刀刃已經出現在你的眼前。", "_t")


