t("anaconda", "巨蟒", "entity name")
t("You recoil in fear as you notice this gigantic snake.  It seeks to crush the life out of you.", "當你看到這隻10米長的龐然巨物時，本能的後退了一步。它在尋找突襲你的機會。", "_t")


