t("giant", "巨人", "entity type")
t("ice", "寒冰", "entity subtype")
t("snow giant", "雪巨人", "entity name")
t("snow giant thunderer", "閃電雪巨人", "entity name")
t("A towering creature, humanoid but huge. It wields a giant maul and does not look friendly. Lightning crackles over its body.", "一隻酷似人類卻很高大的生物。它手握一個巨錘，看起來不是很友好。閃電在它周身流動。", "_t")
t("snow giant boulder thrower", "雪巨人投石者", "entity name")
t("snow giant chieftain", "雪巨人酋長", "entity name")
t("A towering creature, humanoid but huge. It wields a giant maul and does not look friendly.", "一隻酷似人類卻很高大的生物。它手握一個巨錘，看起來不是很友好。", "_t")
t("Burb the snow giant champion", "雪巨人勇士巴布", "entity name")
t("A maddened, enraged snow giant that towers over his comrades. You've heard legends mentioning this particular monstrosity; they say that when he's not rampaging around frothing at the mouth, he sits, almost childlike, engraving stories and mysterious patterns on any flat stone surface he can find.", "一個被激怒的、遠遠高於其他雪巨人的勇士。你以前聽說過關於這個雪巨人的故事：據說，平時他不像現在這樣憤怒的口沫橫飛時，他會坐下來，像個孩子一樣，在他能找到的任何一塊平整的石頭表面雕刻難以理解的圖案。", "_t")


