t("spider", "蜘蛛", "entity subtype")
t("spiderkin", "蜘蛛", "entity type")
t("Arachnophobia...", "我有蜘蛛恐懼症……", "_t")
t("giant spider", "巨型蜘蛛", "entity name")
t("A huge arachnid, it produces even bigger webs.", "一隻巨大的蛛形綱動物，它可以織出更大的網。", "_t")
t("spitting spider", "吐毒蜘蛛", "entity name")
t("A huge arachnid, it sprays venom at its prey.", "一隻巨大的蛛形綱動物，它向獵物噴射毒液。", "_t")
t("chitinous spider", "硬殼蜘蛛", "entity name")
t("A huge arachnid with a massive exoskeleton.", "一隻巨大的蛛形綱動物，它有着厚重的外殼。", "_t")
t("gaeramarth", "蓋瑞麥斯", "entity name")
t("These cunning spiders terrorize those who enter the ever-growing borders of their lairs.  Those who encounter them rarely return.", "這些狡猾的蜘蛛威脅着進入它們地盤的生物。沒有人能從它們這生還。", "_t")
t("ninurlhing", "林爾荷", "entity name")
t("The air reeks with noxious fumes and the ground around it decays.", "在它周圍，毒霧散播，大地枯萎。", "_t")
t("faerlhing", "費爾荷", "entity name")
t("This spider seems to command the flow of mana, which pulses freely through its body.", "這隻蜘蛛善於控制法力流動，它可以使法力在它體內有節奏的跳躍。", "_t")
t("ungolmor", "阿格爾莫", "entity name")
t("Largest of all the spiderkin, its folds of skin seem nearly impenetrable.", "它是體型最大的蜘蛛，它褶皺的皮膚看起來牢不可破。", "_t")
t("losselhing", "盧瑟爾荷", "entity name")
t("The air seems to freeze solid around this frigid spider.", "這隻寒冷的蜘蛛似乎使周圍的空氣都凝固了。", "_t")
t("weaver young", "編織者幼體", "entity name")
t("A tiny arachnid that phases in and out of reality.", "一隻小小的蜘蛛，它在不斷的出入相位現實。", "_t")
t("weaver patriarch", "雄性編織者", "entity name")
t("A large blue arachnid with white markings on its thorax.  It shifts and shimmers as though only partially connected to the timeline.", "一隻胸部有着白色花紋的巨大藍蜘蛛。它不斷的移動和閃爍，好像它只有部分連接在時間線上。", "_t")
t("weaver matriarch", "雌性編織者", "entity name")
t("A large dark blue arachnid with a shifting yellow and white pattern on its thorax.  It shifts and shimmers as though only partially connected to the timeline.", "一隻胸部有着白色花紋的巨大黃蜘蛛。它不斷的移動和閃爍，好像它只有部分連接在時間線上。", "_t")
t("Ninandra, the Great Weaver", "妮娜卓·偉大的編織者", "entity name")
t("A huge blue and white spiderkin whose form shifts and shimmers in and out of reality.  She spins the threads of fate and binds the destiny of all within her web.", "一隻不斷移動和閃爍於相位現實間的巨大蜘蛛，身上有着藍黃相間的花紋。她可以編制命運之網並將獵物的命運捆綁在網上。", "_t")


