t("rogue sapper", "盜賊工兵", "entity name")
t("Stealthy tricksters that leave a wake of deadfalls and other hazards.  They really just make a mess of things.", "狡猾的騙子，他們會留下死亡陷阱和其他危險的東西。他們真的只會讓事態變得糟糕。", "_t")


