t("patchwork troll", "憎惡巨魔", "entity name")
t("A disgusting and mismatched construct of necromantically-enhanced troll bits and shattered weapons. Confused and furious, it rends and shatters its surroundings with impossible strength, moving with speed found nowhere in nature.", "一隻由死靈法術拼接而成的揮舞着武器的噁心巨魔。它用不可思議的力量摧毀周圍的一切，令人困惑的是，它的移動速度也世所罕見。", "_t")
t("Forest Troll Hedge-Wizard", "海哲·維薩德", "entity name")
t("This old-looking troll glares at you with malice. His muscles appear atrophied, but a certain power surrounds him nonetheless.", "這隻老邁的巨魔惡狠狠的盯着你。儘管它已經年老力衰，但是你仍能感受到一股強大的能量環繞着它。", "_t")


