t("Squeakkkkkkk??", "吱—嘎吱？？", "_t")
t("Squeeeeeeak!", "吱—嘎！", "_t")
t("spectral rat", "幽靈鼠", "entity name")
t("An eerie haze surrounds this translucent rat.", "怪異的煙霧環繞着這隻透明的老鼠。", "_t")
t("Eerie Squeak!", "可怕吱！", "_t")
t("Frightening Squeak??", "恐怖吱！", "_t")
t("vampire rat", "吸血鼠", "entity name")
t("Looks much like a normal rat. That is, other than the very large fangs.", "不談那大了一號的牙齒，它看起來還算比較正常的一隻老鼠。", "_t")
t("Squeak! Blood!", "吱！鮮血！", "_t")
t("gigantic bone rat", "巨型骨鼠", "entity name")
t("This massive beast appears to be a rat composed of countless bones fused together.", "這隻巨大的怪物看起來像是許多骨頭拼起來的老鼠。", "_t")
t("*SQUEAK*", "*嘎吱嘎*", "_t")
t("Rat Lich", "鼠巫妖", "entity name")
t("The master of the pit is before you. It squeaks with menace as it and a horde of minions approach you.", "這隻軍團的主人站在你面前。它吱吱叫着並指揮一大羣怪物接近你。", "_t")
t("#RED#Rising again, the Rat Lich's eyes glow with renewed energy!", "#RED#鼠巫妖再次復活，它的眼睛放射着全新能量的光輝！", "logSeen")
t("\
The Rat Lich's true power has been unveiled! Swirling with arcane energy, it stalks towards you uttering warsqueaks at its minions!", "\
鼠巫妖的真正力量展現出來了！它的身軀環繞着奧術能量，昂首闊步地帶領着它的僕從包圍着你，發出吱吱的戰吼！", "_t")
t("\"Squeak\" I say, yes .. \"Squeak!\"", "“吱吱”，我說，是的…“吱吱！”", "_t")
t("*squeak*", "*吱吱*", "_t")
t("SQUEAK!!!!!", "吱吱吱！！！", "_t")
t("Squeak!", "吱！", "_t")
t("Squeak??", "吱吱？？", "_t")


