t([[A terrible robed undead figure, this creature has existed in its unlife for many centuries by stealing the life of others.
It can summon the very shades of its victims from beyond the grave to come enslaved to its aid.]], [[這隻吸血鬼一副可怕的披長袍的不死族形象，它在漫長的歲月中偷取了許多他人的生命。
