section "game/modules/tome/data/general/objects/world-artifacts-far-east.lua"

t("tome", "書冊", "entity subtype")
t("Scroll of Summoning (Limmir the Jeweler)", "召喚卷軸（召喚珠寶匠利米爾）", "entity name")
t("summon Limmir the jeweler at the center of the lake of the moon", "在月之湖中心召喚珠寶匠利米爾", "_t")
t("Pendant of the Sun and Moons", "日月垂飾", "entity name")
t("a gray and gold pendant", "一個閃爍着金色灰色的垂飾", "_t")
t("This small pendant depicts a hematite moon eclipsing a golden sun and according to legend was worn by one of the Sunwall's founders.", "一個小小的垂飾，雕刻着紅月吞日的圖案。傳說其主人是太陽堡壘的建立者之一。", "_t")
t("All your damage is converted and split into light and darkness.", "你造成的所有傷害被轉化均分爲光系和暗影傷害。", "_t")
t("shimmering gold shield", "閃耀着金色光芒的盾牌", "_t")
t("Unsetting Sun", "永恆光輝", "entity name")
t("When Elmio Panason, captain of the Vanguard, first sought shelter for his shipwrecked crew, he reflected the last rays of the setting sun off his shield.  Where the beam hit they rested and built the settlement that would become the Sunwall.  In the dark days that followed the shield became a symbol of hope for a better future.", "當衝鋒隊隊長艾米奧·帕納森爲他的遇難船員們尋求庇護所的時候，他的盾牌反射着落日的光輝。他們在光輝照耀的地方休息宿營，之後太陽堡壘在那裏成立。在隨後那些暗無天日的日子裏，這面盾牌被人們當做美好未來希望的象徵。", "_t")
t("Glows brightly in the light of dawn.", "在黎明下閃耀光芒。", "_t")
t("Scorched Boots", "燒焦的長靴", "entity name")
t("pair of blackened boots", "一雙燻黑的靴子", "_t")
t("The master blood mage Ru'Khan was the first orc to experiment with the power of the Sher'Tul farportals in the Age of Pyre.  However, that first experiment was not particularly successful, and after the explosion of energy all that could be found of Ru'Khan was a pair of scorched boots.", "血魔導師魯·克漢是派爾紀第一個使用夏·圖爾遠程傳送門進行試驗的獸人。試驗不是很成功，能量爆炸後，只剩下了一雙燒焦的靴子。", "_t")
t("unearthly black stone", "神祕的黑色石頭", "_t")
t("Goedalath Rock", "高達勒斯之石", "entity name")
t("demonic", "惡魔", "entity subtype")
t("A small rock that seems from beyond this world, vibrating with a fierce energy.  It feels warped and terrible and evil... and yet oh so powerful.", "這塊小石頭看起來不是這個世界的，它不時產生着激烈的能量震動，讓人感到扭曲、可怕、邪惡……而又強大的能量。", "_t")
t("evil touch", "邪惡之觸", "_t")
t("Threads of Fate", "命運之弦", "entity name")
t("a shimmering white cloak", "一件閃着微光的白色斗篷", "_t")
t("Untouched by the ravages of time, this fine spun white cloak appears to be crafted of an otherworldly material that shifts and shimmers in the light.", "這件精緻的白色斗篷由異界材料製成，隨光線變化而閃爍，永恆如新。", "_t")
t("Blood-Edge", "飲血劍", "entity name")
t("red crystalline sword", "紅色的水晶劍", "_t")
t([[This deep red sword weeps blood continuously. It was born in the labs of the orcish corrupter Hurik, who sought to make a crystal that would house his soul after death. But his plans were disrupted by a band of sun paladins, and though most died purging his keep of dread minions, their leader Raasul fought through to Hurik's lab, sword in hand. There the two did battle, blade against blood magic, till both fell to the floor with weeping wounds. The orc with his last strength crawled towards his fashioned phylactery, hoping to save himself, but Raasul saw his plans and struck the crystal with his light-bathed sword. It shattered, and in the sudden impulse of energies the steel, crystal and blood were fused into one.
Now the broken fragments of Raasul's soul are trapped in this terrible artifact, his mind warped beyond all sanity by decades of imprisonment. Only the taste of blood calls him forth, his soul stealing the lifeblood of others to take on physical form again, that he may thrash and wail against the living.]], [[這把深紅色的劍不斷的向下滴血。它誕生於獸人墮落者胡裏克的實驗室。最初，胡裏克尋找了一枚水晶來製造他的命匣，但他的計劃很快被一羣太陽騎士打斷，儘管大部分騎士死於不死軍團的阻攔，但騎士團團長瑞蘇爾卻單槍匹馬殺入了胡裏克的實驗室。在那裏，兩位強者展開了對決，利劍與血魔法你來我往，直到他們都重傷倒地。獸人想拼盡最後一分力氣，拿到他的命匣，希望能拯救自己，但是瑞蘇爾識破了他的陰謀，將浸滿鮮血的利劍擲向了命匣。命匣破碎的瞬間，胡裏克的靈魂和利劍以及水晶融爲了一體。
現在，殘存的胡裏克靈魂被困在了這件可怕的武器中，他的思維因數十年的監禁而扭曲。只有鮮血的味道能引起他的興奮，他的靈魂在不斷的侵蝕他人的血肉，希望有朝一日能夠重組自我，擺脫這痛苦的存在形式。]], "_t")
t("15% chance to animate a bleeding foe's blood", "15%機率使處於流血狀態的敵人大出血", "_t")
t("animated blood", "活化血液", "_t")
t("A haze of blood, vibrant and pulsing through the air, possessed by a warped and cracked soul. Every now and then a scream or wail of agony garbles through it, telling of the mindless suffering undergone by its possessor.", [[這把深紅色的劍不斷的向下滴血。它誕生於獸人墮落者胡裏克的實驗室。最初，胡裏克尋找了一枚水晶來製造他的命匣，但他的計劃很快被一羣太陽騎士打斷，儘管大部分騎士死於不死軍團的阻攔，但騎士團團長瑞蘇爾卻單槍匹馬殺入了胡裏克的實驗室。在那裏，兩位強者展開了對決，利劍與血魔法你來我往，直到他們都重傷倒地。獸人想拼盡最後一分力氣，拿到他的命匣，希望能拯救自己，但是瑞蘇爾識破了他的陰謀，將浸滿鮮血的利劍擲向了命匣。命匣破碎的瞬間，胡裏克的靈魂和利劍以及水晶融爲了一體。
現在，殘存的胡裏克靈魂被困在了這件可怕的武器中，他的思維因數十年的監禁而扭曲。只有鮮血的味道能引起他的興奮，他的靈魂在不斷的侵蝕他人的血肉，希望有朝一日能夠重組自我，擺脫這痛苦的存在形式。]], "_t")
t("Summon", "召喚", "_t")
t("#GOLD#As the blade touches %s's spilt blood, the blood rises, animated!", "#GOLD#飲血劍接觸到%s噴出的血液，血液開始活化，動了起來!", "logSeen")
t("#GOLD#%s draws power from the spilt blood!", "#GOLD#%s從分出的血液汲取能量!", "logSeen")
t("Dawn's Blade", "黎明之刃", "entity name")
t("shining longsword", "閃光的長劍", "_t")
t("Said to have been forged in the earliest days of the Sunwall, this longsword shines with the light of daybreak, capable of banishing all shadows.", "傳說是在太陽堡壘成立之初打造，這把長劍閃耀着黎明破曉之光，可以破除一切黑暗。", "_t")
t("invoke dawn, inflicting %0.2f light damage in radius %d (based on Magic) and lighting the area within radius %d", "激發黎明的光芒，在半徑%d內造成%0.2f光系傷害（基於魔法），並照明%d碼。", "tformat", {2,1,3})
t("%s raises %s and sends out a burst of light!", "%s舉起%s，放出一陣光芒！", "logSeen")
t("#GOLD#You feel a swell of positive energy!", "#GOLD#你感受到正能量的波動！", "logPlayer")
t("If the sun doesn't set, dawn's power lasts forever.", "如果太陽永不落山，黎明的光輝將永恆。", "_t")
t("#GOLD#As you wield the sword and shield of the Sunwall, you feel the Sun's light radiating from your core.", "#GOLD#當你握住晨曦之門的劍與盾，你感覺到從你身體內部散發出太陽的光輝。", "logPlayer")
t("#GOLD#You feel the Sun's light vanish from within you.", "#GOLD#你感受到太陽的光輝從你的身體裏流失了。", "logPlayer")
t("Zemekkys' Broken Hourglass", "伊莫克斯的破沙漏", "entity name")
t("a broken hourglass", "壞掉的沙漏", "_t")
t("This small broken hourglass hangs from a thin gold chain.  The glass is cracked and the sand has long since escaped.", "這個壞掉的小沙漏系在一根金子做的細鏈上。沙漏的玻璃被打破了，裏面的沙子早就掉光了。", "_t")
t("Mandible of Ungolmor", "阿格爾莫的上顎", "entity name")
t("curved, serrated black dagger", "彎曲的鋸齒狀黑色匕首", "_t")
t("This obsidian-crafted, curved blade is studded with the deadly fangs of the Ungolmor. It seems to drain light from the world around it.", "這把黑曜石打造的利刃鑲嵌有阿格爾莫的致命毒牙。光明在它周圍消逝，無盡的黑暗纏繞着它。", "_t")
t("inflicts spydric poison dealing 200 damage over 3 turns and pinning the target", "使目標感染蜘蛛毒素，在3回合內造成200傷害，並定身目標。", "_t")
t("Kinetic Spike", "靈能釘刺", "entity name")
t("bladeless hilt", "短刃匕首", "_t")
t("A simple, rudely crafted stone hilt, this object manifests a blade of wavering, nearly invisible force, like a heat haze, as you grasp it. Despite its simple appearance, it is capable of shearing through solid granite, in the hands of those with the necessary mental fortitude to use it properly.", "看似只是簡單雕刻過的石柄，然而其前端顯現着一道搖晃的刀鋒。當你試圖去抓住刀鋒的時候，你感受到這是一股如熱氣般無形的力量。儘管外觀粗糙，但它在意志足夠堅強並且懂得使用它的人手裏卻可以削鐵如泥。", "_t")
t("fire a bolt of kinetic force (range %d), dealing 150%% (physical) weapon damage", "發射靈能之力，在距離%d範圍內造成150%%武器傷害。", "tformat")
t("The %s fires a bolt of kinetic force!", "%s發出一股動能衝擊！", "logSeen")
t("Rod of Sarrilon", "薩瑞倫之杖", "entity name")
t("ceremonial staff", "禮儀用的法杖", "_t")
t("A plain looking ceremonial rod. It has connections with Time that even chronomancers do not yet understand.", "看上去普普通通的法杖，但是它和時間的神祕聯繫連時空法師都不清楚。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/objects/world-artifacts-maj-eyal.lua"

t("Penitence", "懺悔", "entity name")
t("glowing staff", "通紅的法杖", "_t")
t("A powerful staff sent in secret to Angolwen by the Shaloren, to aid their fighting of the plagues following the Spellblaze. Its power is not to harm, but to heal and protect.", "永恆精靈密送到安格利文，用以對抗魔法大爆炸所引起災難的強大法杖。", "_t")
t("cure up to %d diseases or poisons (based on Magic)", "治癒至多%d項疾病和毒素。(基於魔法)", "tformat")
t("%s uses %s %s, curing %s afflictions!", "%s使用了%s%s，治療了%s項疾病！", "logSeen")
t("#DARK_GREEN#You feel the cleansing power of Penitence attune to you.", "#DARK_GREEN#你感受到懺悔法杖的淨化力量。", "logPlayer")
t("Lost Staff of Archmage Tarelion", "大法師泰爾蘭丟失的法杖", "entity name")
t("shining staff", "閃光的法杖", "_t")
t("Archmage Tarelion travelled the world in his youth. But the world is not a nice place and it seems he had to run fast.", "大法師泰爾蘭在年輕的時候曾環遊世界。但是這個世界並不是那麼美好以至於我們的大法師不得不飛速逃跑。", "_t")
t("Spellblaze Echoes", "魔法大爆炸迴響", "entity name")
t("deep black amulet", "深黑色的項鍊", "_t")
t("This ancient charm still retains a distant echo of the destruction wrought by the Spellblaze", "當你戴上這個古老的項鍊，似乎耳邊仍迴盪着魔法大爆炸的迴響。", "_t")
t("unleash a destructive wail, destroying terrain and dealing %0.2f physical damage (based on Magic) in a radius of %d", "釋放毀滅哀嚎，摧毀地形，造成 %0.2f 物理傷害 (基於魔法) 傷害半徑 %d", "tformat")
t("%s uses the %s!", "%s 使用了 %s！", "logSeen")
t("Daneth's Neckguard", "丹納斯的護頸", "entity name")
t("a thick steel gorget", "一個沉重的鋼製護頸", "_t")
t("A thick steel gorget designed to protect its wearer from fatal attacks to the neck.  This particular gorget was worn by the Halfling General Daneth Tendermourn during the pyre wars, and judging by the marks along its surface may have saved the General's life on more than one occasion.", "一個厚重的鋼護喉，旨在保護其穿着者頸部免受致命攻擊。這個特殊的護喉是半身人將軍丹納斯·坦德莫恩在派爾紀戰爭中佩戴過的，上面的各種傷痕表明其可能救過這位將軍不止一次。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#You feel invincible!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你感覺自己不可戰勝！", "logPlayer")
t("Thaloren-Tree Longbow", "精靈樹長弓", "entity name")
t("glowing elven-wood longbow", "光輝的精靈木長弓", "_t")
t("In the aftermath of the Spellblaze, the Thaloren had to defend their forests against foes and fires alike. Many of the trees died despite the efforts of the Elves to save them. Their wood was fashioned into a bow to be wielded against the darkness.", "在魔法大爆炸的餘波裏，自然精靈不得不從敵人和大火中保衛他們的森林。儘管精靈們奮力的搶救它們，許多樹還是死掉了。它們的遺體被打造成一張弓用來抵禦黑暗的侵襲。", "_t")
t("#DARK_GREEN#You understand this bow-and its connection to nature-in a way few can.", "#DARK_GREEN#你理解了這把弓——以及它和自然的聯繫——這是很多人無法理解的。", "logPlayer")
t("Corpsebow", "腐屍之弓", "entity name")
t("rotting longbow", "腐朽的長弓", "_t")
t("A lost artifact of the Age of Dusk, the Corpsebow is filled with a lingering essence of that era's terrible plagues. Those struck by arrows fired from its rotten string find themselves afflicted by echoes of ancient sickness.", "一件黃昏紀遺失的武器，腐屍之弓渾身纏繞着那個時代的瘟疫精華。被腐朽弓弦射出的箭所擊中的人，會因古老疾病在體內的共鳴而倍受折磨。", "_t")
t("#DARK_BLUE#You feel a kindred spirit in this bow...", "#DARK_BLUE#你在弓中感受到了共鳴的靈魂…", "logPlayer")
t("Spellblade", "魔宗利刃", "entity name")
t("glowing long sword", "光輝的長劍", "_t")
t("Mages sometimes have funny ideas. Archmage Varil once learned how to handle a sword and found he preferred wielding it instead of his staff.", "法師總是時不時冒出古怪的點子。大法師沃利爾曾學會了怎樣擎起一柄劍，同時發現自己對耍劍比玩法杖更感冒。", "_t")
t("Genocide", "獸人末日", "entity name")
t("pitch black blade", "漆黑的劍", "_t")
t("Farian was King Toknor's captain, and fought by his side in the great Battle of Last Hope.  However, when he returned after the battle to find his hometown burnt in an orcish pyre, a madness overtook him.  The desire for vengeance made him quit the army and strike out on his own, lightly armoured and carrying nought but his sword.  Most thought him dead until the reports came back of a fell figure tearing through the orcish encampments, slaughtering all before him and mercilessly butchering the corpses after.  It is said his blade drank the blood of 100 orcs each day until finally all of Maj'Eyal was cleared of their presence.  When the final orc was slain and no more were to be found, Farian at the last turned the blade on himself and stuck it through his chest.  Those nearby said his body shook with convulsions as he did so, though they could not tell whether he was laughing or crying.", "法瑞安曾是圖庫納國王的指揮官，在最後希望的偉大戰役中跟隨國王並肩作戰。然而，當戰爭結束，凱旋歸來之時，他卻發現故鄉處處燃燒着獸人的火焰，無邊的怒火吞噬了他。復仇的慾望使他離開軍隊，孤身一人踏上了征程，他除了護甲之外只帶了一柄劍。大多數人認爲他已經死了。直到有消息稱有一個毀滅者般的身影正在摧殘獸人的營地，他屠殺了所有見到的獸人並殘忍的肢解對方的屍體。據說他每天要用100個獸人的鮮血來祭刀直到殺光馬基埃亞爾的獸人。當最後一個獸人被殺死並且沒有發現更多的時候，法瑞安最終把利刃轉向了自己——那把劍刺穿了他的胸膛。那些在附近的目擊者說，當法瑞安這樣做的時候身體伴隨着陣陣痙攣，他們說不清他到底是哭是笑。", "_t")
t("Bolbum's Big Knocker", "鮑爾本的大門扣", "entity name")
t("thick staff", "一根厚重的法杖", "_t")
t("A thick staff with a heavy knob on the end.  It was said to be used by the grand alchemist Bolbum in the Age of Allure.  Much renowned is the fear of his students for their master, and the high rate of cranial injuries amongst them.  Bolbum died with seven daggers in his back and his much-cursed staff went missing after.", "這是一根末端有着厚重門扣的沉重法杖。據說是鍊金魔導師鮑爾本在厄流紀使用的法杖。它之所以聞名於世，大部分來源於鮑爾本的學生們對他的恐懼以及被它打傷腦袋的超高几率。鮑爾本被7把匕首插在後背而死，那根被衆人詛咒的法杖也從此消失不見。", "_t")
t("Guidance", "指引者", "entity name")
t("a softly glowing crystal", "一顆散發着柔和光芒的水晶", "_t")
t([[Said to have once belonged to Inquisitor Marcus Dunn during the Spellhunt this fist sized quartz crystal glows constantly with a soft white light and was rumoured to be a great aid in meditation, helping focus the mind, body, and soul of the owner as well as protecting them from the foulest of magics.
It seems somebody well versed in antimagic could use it to its fullest potential.]], [[曾經屬於魔法狩獵時期的檢察官瑪庫斯·丹。這個拳頭大小的石英晶體不斷散發出柔和的白光。而且據說對冥想有相當大的幫助，不但可以幫助集中精神、身體，還可以保護持有者的靈魂，並且保護他們免遭邪惡魔法的侵蝕。
似乎只有擁有反魔力量的人才能發揮它的全部潛能。]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#You feel a great hero guiding you!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你感到有個偉大的英雄在指引着你！", "logPlayer")
t("Eldoral Last Resort", "艾德瑞爾的最後手段", "entity name")
t("well-made sling", "精良的投石器", "_t")
t("A sling with an inscription on its handle: 'May the wielder be granted cunning in his fight against the darkness'.", "投石器的把手上有一段銘文：“願持有者於對抗黑暗之時被賜予神一般的機智。”", "_t")
t("When dropping below 30% max HP, you gain 20% attack speed, lose 100% fatigue, and your shots don't consume ammo for 5 turns. 30 turns cd.", "當你的生命降低到最大生命值30%的時候，在5回合內，你獲得20%攻擊速度，降低100%疲勞，且射擊不消耗彈藥。冷卻時間30回合。", "_t")
t("Orc Feller", "獸人砍伐者", "entity name")
t("shining dagger", "光輝的匕首", "_t")
t("During the invasion of Eldoral the Halfling Rogue Herah is said to have slain over one hundred orcs while defending a group of refugees.", "據說在艾德瑞爾戰爭中，半身人盜賊赫拉在保護一羣難民時殺死了100多個獸人。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#Herah's guile and luck is with you, her successor!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#Herah的狡詐和幸運與你同在，她的繼承人！", "logPlayer")
t("Nature's Vengeance", "自然的復仇", "entity name")
t("thick wooden mace", "木質粗權杖", "_t")
t("This thick-set mace was used by the Spellhunter Vorlan, who crafted it from the wood of an ancient oak that was uprooted during the Spellblaze.  Many were the wizards and witches felled by this weapon, brought to justice for the crimes they committed against nature.", "這把加粗的權杖曾屬於獵魔人沃爾蘭，他從一棵在魔法大爆炸中被連根拔起的古老橡樹中取材製造了它。衆多法師和女巫倒在了這把武器之下，他們對自然犯下的罪行得到了制裁。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#You feel nature defending you.", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你感覺自然在保衛你。", "logPlayer")
t("Fists of the Desert Scorpion", "沙蠍之拳", "entity name")
t("viciously spiked gauntlets", "有着鋒利尖刺的拳套", "_t")
t([[These wickedly spiked gauntlets belonged to an orc captain in the Age of Pyre who conquered the western sands, using them as a base to lay raids on Elvala to the south.  Known as The Scorpion, he seemed unconquerable in battle, able to pull enemies towards him with vicious mental force and lay down lethal blows on them.  Often a flurry of these yellow and black gauntlets would be the last thing great Shaloren mages would see before having the life crushed from them.

Finally The Scorpion was defeated by the alchemist Nessylia, who went to face the fiendish orc alone.  The captain pulled the elf towards him with a brutish cackle, but before he could batter the life from her flesh she tore off her robes, revealing eighty incendiary bombs strapped to her flesh.  With a spark from her fingers she triggered an explosion that could be seen for miles around.  To this day Nessylia is still remembered in song for the sacrifice of her immortal life to protect her people.]], "這隻有着鋒利尖刺的拳套屬於一位派爾紀統治西部荒野的獸人領主，他依靠它們對埃爾瓦拉發動了數次襲擊。他外號沙蠍，在戰場上所向披靡，他可以用精神力量將敵人拉過來，也可以用拳套把箭矢擋下。通常永恆精靈法師們在死前看到的最後物品，便是這隻黃黑相間的拳套殘影。最終沙蠍在決鬥中，被鍊金術師奈瑟莉亞擊敗。當這副拳套的主人將精靈拉向他，還沒來得及將她撕成兩半時，精靈掀開了她的長袍——下面捆着的是八十多枚鍊金炸彈。精靈指尖的火花，引發了數裏外都能看到的大爆炸。直到今天，民間仍流傳着奈瑟莉亞爲保護她的子民而犧牲的詩歌。", "_t")
t("Wind's Whisper", "風之密語", "entity name")
t("flowing light cloak", "流彩斗篷", "_t")
t("When the enchanter Razeen was cornered by Spellhunters near the Daikara mountain pass she wrapped her cloak about her and fled down a narrow ravine.  The hunters fired volley after volley of arrows at her, but by miracle or magic they all missed.  Razeen was able to escape and flee to the hidden city in the west.", "當魔法師瑞茲恩被獵魔人在岱卡拉的山隘逼入絕境時，她用斗篷包裹着自己逃下了峽谷。獵手們接連不斷的把箭射向她，但由於奇蹟或是魔法，他們全部射空了。瑞茲恩得以逃生並躲進了西部的隱祕之城。", "_t")
t("glowing rod", "熾熱的魔杖", "_t")
t("Gwai's Burninator", "戈瓦的燃燒鬥志", "entity name")
t("Gwai, a Pyromanceress that lived during the Spellhunt, was cornered by group of mage hunters. She fought to her last breath and is said to have killed at least ten people with this wand before she fell.", "戈瓦，一個生活在魔法狩獵時的火焰術士，她被一羣獵魔人逼入了絕境。她戰鬥至最後一刻，據說在她流盡最後一滴血之前她用這把魔杖幹掉了至少十人。", "_t")
t("shoot a cone of flames (radius %d) for %0.2f fire damage (based on Magic)", "發射長度 %d 的錐形火焰，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害（基於魔法）。", "tformat")
t("%s activates %s %s!", "%s激活了%s%s!", "logSeen")
t("viciously sharp battle axe", "兇猛的鋒利戰斧", "_t")
t("Drake's Bane", "屠龍", "entity name")
t("The killing of Kroltar, mightiest of wyrms, took seven months and the lives of 20,000 dwarven warriors.  Finally the beast was worn down and mastersmith Gruxim, standing atop the bodies of his fallen comrades, was able slit its throat with this axe crafted purely for the purpose of penetrating the wyrm's hide.", "庫洛塔的噩夢，最強大的龍，7個月的時間她帶走了20，000矮人戰士的生命。這條猛獸的力氣最終被耗盡了，工匠大師格魯克西姆，站在同伴們屍體的頂端，他用這把精工打造的斧頭斬開了龍的鱗甲，剖開了龍的喉嚨。", "_t")
t("Blood-Letter", "血字", "entity name")
t("glacial hatchet", "冰冷的手斧", "_t")
t("A hand axe carved out of the most frozen parts of the northern wasteland.", "用北部荒原的寒冰之核雕成的手斧。", "_t")
t("scintillating white crystal", "閃耀的白水晶", "_t")
t("Telos's Staff Crystal", "泰勒斯的法杖水晶", "entity name")
t("multi-hued", "混晶石", "entity subtype")
t("A closer look at this pure white crystal reveals that it is really a plethora of colors swirling and scintillating.", "近距離欣賞這顆純淨的白水晶，你會發現很多種顏色在上面盤旋閃耀。", "_t")
t("combine with a staff", "安裝至法杖", "_t")
t("Fuse with which staff?", "和哪件護甲熔合？", "_t")
t("You fix the crystal on the %s and create the %s.", "你將水晶安裝在%s，製造了%s。", "logPlayer")
t("The fusing fails!", "熔合失敗了！", "logPlayer")
t("#CRIMSON#Telos's gem seems to flare and glows an unearthly colour.", "#CRIMSON#泰勒斯的寶石閃耀着，發出非自然的光輝。", "logSeen")
t("#CRIMSON#The unearthly glow fades away.", "#CRIMSON# 非自然的光芒消退了。", "logPlayer")
t("Telos Golem (reluctant follower of %s)", "泰勒斯傀儡 (%s不情願的追隨者)", "tformat")
t("#ROYAL_BLUE#The golem decides to change it's name to #{bold}#%s#{normal}#.", "#ROYAL_BLUE#傀儡決定將名字更改爲 #{bold}#%s#{normal}#.", "log")
t("I feel lost!", "我感覺迷失了！", "_t")
t("Voice of Telos", "泰勒斯之聲", "entity name")
t("scintillating white staff", "閃耀的白色法杖", "_t")
t("A closer look at this pure white staff reveals that it is really a plethora of colors swirling and scintillating.", "對這根純淨的白色法杖近距離欣賞會發現很多種顏色在上面盤旋閃耀。", "_t")
t("Rope Belt of the Thaloren", "自然精靈的繩索腰帶", "entity name")
t("short length of rope", "一截短繩", "_t")
t("The simplest of belts, worn for centuries by Nessilla Tantaelen as she tended to her people and forests. Some of her wisdom and power have settled permanently into its fibers.", "最樸素的腰帶，被奈希拉·坦泰蘭在領導她的人民和森林期間穿戴了幾個世紀。這條腰帶永久的保存了她的部分智慧和力量。", "_t")
t("#DARK_GREEN#Nessilla's belt seems to come alive as you put it on.", "#DARK_GREEN#當你穿上它時，奈希拉之腰帶似乎活過來了。", "logPlayer")
t("Neira's Memory", "尼耶拉的記憶", "entity name")
t("crackling belt", "發出異常聲音的腰帶", "_t")
t("Ages ago this belt was worn by Linaniil herself in her youth, using its power she shielded herself from the Spellblaze rain of fire, but naught could she do for her sister Neira.", "許多年前這根腰帶是年輕時的萊娜尼爾穿戴的，在魔法大爆炸的火焰之中它的力量保護了她，但卻保護不了她的姐妹尼耶拉。", "_t")
t("surround yourself with a magical shield (strength %d, based on Magic) for %d turns", "製造一層魔法護盾，(強度%d，基於魔法) ，持續%d回合。", "tformat")
t("%s invokes the memory of Neira!", "%s呼喚了尼耶拉的記憶!", "logSeen")
t("Nature's Blessing", "自然之賜", "entity name")
t("supple leather armour entwined with willow bark", "柔韌的皮甲被柳木條纏繞着", "_t")
t("Worn by Protector Ardon, who first formed the Ziguranth during the mage wars between the Humans and the Halflings.  This armour is infused with the powers of nature, and protected against the disruptive forces of magic.", "曾被守護者亞當穿著，他在魔法戰爭中首次於人類和半身人之間建立了伊格蘭斯。這件護甲被灌注了大自然的能量，並被用來對抗魔法破壞者。", "_t")
t("#DARK_GREEN#You feel especially blessed.", "#DARK_GREEN#你感覺自己被特別祝福了。", "logPlayer")
t("Plate Armor of the King", "國王的板甲", "entity name")
t("suit of gleaming voratun plate", "隱隱放光的沃瑞鉭板甲", "_t")
t("Beautifully detailed with images of King Toknor's defence of Last Hope. Despair fills the hearts of even the blackest villains at the sight of it.", "精細描繪着國王圖庫納爲最後的希望浴血的影像。即便是徹頭徹尾的惡棍看到它，心底也會充滿深深的絕望。", "_t")
t("Witch-Bane", "巫師毀滅者", "entity name")
t("an ivory handled voratun longsword", "象牙柄沃瑞鉭長劍", "_t")
t([[A thin voratun blade with an ivory handle wrapped in purple cloth.  The weapon is nearly as legendary as its former owner, Marcus Dunn, and was thought to have been destroyed after Marcus was slain near the end of the Spellhunt.
It seems somebody well versed in antimagic could use it to its fullest potential.]], [[一把沃瑞鉭長劍，象牙的劍柄被紫色的布包裹着。這把兵器的傳奇性跟它上一任擁有者瑪庫斯·丹差不多了，人們都以爲這把劍在魔法狩獵末期瑪庫斯被害的時候被摧毀了。
據說只有將全身心奉獻給反魔法事業的人才能充分發揮它的力量。]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#You feel a great hero watching over you!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你感到有位偉大的英雄正在注視着你！", "logPlayer")
t("Staff of Arcane Supremacy", "至尊法杖", "entity name")
t("silver-runed staff", "銀色符文法杖", "_t")
t([[A long slender staff, made of ancient dragon-bone, with runes emblazoned all over its surface in bright silver.
It hums faintly, as if great power is locked within, yet alone it seems incomplete.]], "一根又細又長的法杖，由遠古龍骨製成，它通體銘刻着銀色的符文。它會發出微弱的嗡嗡聲，似乎有一股強大的力量被鎖在了裏面，整體來看，它似乎是不完整的。", "_t")
t("A true understanding of the arcane is needed to release its full power.", "只有理解奧術才能完全使用它的力量。", "_t")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#You feel a swell of arcane energy.", "#STEEL_BLUE#你感受到一股奧術能量在膨脹。", "logSeen")
t("Hat of Arcane Understanding", "奧術理解之帽", "entity name")
t("silver-runed hat", "銀色符文帽子", "_t")
t([[A traditional pointed wizard's hat, made of fine purple elven-silk and decorated with bright silver runes. You sense it has been passed from ancient times, and has been born on the heads of great mages.
Touching the cloth you feel a sense of knowledge and power from bygone ages, yet it is partly sealed away, waiting for a trigger to release it.]], "一隻傳統巫師的尖帽子，由紫色的精靈絲綢製成，上面還有亮銀色的裝飾物。你意識到它來自遠古時代，一個擁有衆多偉大法師的時代。通過觸摸你可以感受到遠古的知識和能量，但仍有一部分被密封着，等待有緣人來釋放它。", "_t")
t("Only supremacy of the arcane can release its full power.", "只有奧術至尊才能完全發揮它的力量。", "_t")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#The arcane energies surrounding you dissipate.", "#STEEL_BLUE#圍繞着你的奧術能量消退了。", "logPlayer")
t("Mirror Shards", "鏡影碎片", "entity name")
t("mirror lined chain", "鑲有鎖鏈的鏡片", "_t")
t("Said to have been created by a powerful mage after his home was destroyed by a mob following the Spellblaze. Though he fled, his possessions were crushed, burned, and smashed. When he returned to the ruins, he made this amulet from the remains of his shattered mirror.", "據說是由一位強大的魔法師在他的家園被獵魔行動的暴民摧毀後製造。雖然他逃脫了追捕，但是他的財產都被破壞和燒燬殆盡。當他回去時，發現家裏已成廢墟，牆上的斑駁和地上的碎片說明了這裏曾遭到怎樣的劫難。最終，他撿起了其中一塊鏡子殘片，將其做成了這副項鍊。", "_t")
t("create a reflective shield (50%% reflection rate, %d strength, based on Magic) for %d turns", "製造反射護盾（50%%反射率，%d吸收量，基於魔法）持續%d回合。", "tformat")
t("%s activates %s, forging a reflective barrier!", "%s激活了%s，製造了一層反射護盾！", "logSeen")
t("Destala's Scales", "德斯塔拉之鱗片", "entity name")
t("green dragon-scale cloak", "綠色的龍鱗斗篷", "_t")
t("This cloak is made from the scales of an infamous Venom Drake that terrorized the country side towards the end of the Age of Dusk. It was slain by a party led by Kestin Highfin, who had this cloak fashioned personally.", "黃昏紀末年，一條不知名的毒龍威脅着鄉村，冒險家科斯汀·赫菲因率領的小隊殺死了這條惡龍，用它的鱗片製作了這件時尚的斗篷。", "_t")
t("Spellblaze Shard", "魔爆碎片", "entity name")
t("crystalline dagger", "水晶匕首", "_t")
t("This jagged crystal glows with an unnatural light. A strap of cloth is wrapped around one end, as a handle.", "這塊鋸齒狀的水晶放射出異常的亮光，它的一端綁着幾圈布條當作握把。", "_t")
t("Mercy", "慈悲", "entity name")
t("wickedly sharp dagger", "異常尖銳的匕首", "_t")
t("This dagger was used by a nameless healer during the Age of Dusk. The plagues that ravaged his town were beyond the ability of mortal man to treat, so he took to using his dagger to as an act of mercy when faced with hopeless patients. Despite his good intentions, it is now cursed with dark power, letting it kill in a single stroke against those already weakened.", "這柄匕首曾被黃昏紀一名無名的治療師使用。瘟疫襲擊了城鎮，而醫者終究是凡人，他只能用這柄匕首結束那些絕望的病人的痛苦。儘管初衷是好的，這柄匕首現在已經被黑暗力量污染，用它傷害虛弱的敵人威力更大。", "_t")
t("deals 60 physical damage increased by 1% for each 1% life the target has lost", "造成60物理傷害。敵人每失去1%生命值，傷害增加1%。", "_t")
t("Thalore-Wood Cuirass", "精靈木胸甲", "entity name")
t("thick wooden plate armour", "厚木板甲", "_t")
t("Expertly hewn from the bark of trees, this wooden armor provides excellent protection at a low weight.", "由樹皮製成，做工相當精巧，重量很輕，卻能提供很好的防護。", "_t")
t("#DARK_GREEN#The armor molds comfortably to one of its caretakers.", "#DARK_GREEN#護甲對看守者來說非常合身。", "logPlayer")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/general/objects/world-artifacts.lua"

t("windy gem", "微風環繞的寶石", "_t")
t("Windborne Azurite", "風之銅藍", "entity name")
t("blue", "藍寶石", "entity subtype")
t("Air currents swirl around this bright blue jewel.", "空氣在這塊亮藍色寶石周圍旋轉。", "_t")
t("Primal Infusion", "原初之紋身", "entity name")
t("This wild infusion has evolved.", "這個紋身已經進化了", "_t")
t("pulsing infusion", "有活力的紋身", "_t")
t("Prismatic Rune", "棱彩符文", "entity name")
t("Mirror Image Rune", "鏡像符文", "entity name")
t("Staff of Destruction", "毀滅之杖", "entity name")
t("darkness infused staff", "充滿黑暗氣息的法杖", "_t")
t("This unique-looking staff is carved with runes of destruction.", "這個品相獨特的法杖上刻印着毀滅符文。", "_t")
t("Vargh Redemption", "瓦爾弗的救贖", "entity name")
t("sea-blue ring", "海藍色的戒指", "_t")
t("This azure ring seems to be always moist to the touch.", "這個海藍色的戒指看上去總是水汪汪的。", "_t")
t("summon a radius %d tidal wave that expands slowly over %d turns, dealing %0.2f cold and %0.2f physical damage (based on Willpower) each turn, knocking opponents back, and lowering their stun resistance", "召喚緩慢擴張的半徑 %d 的潮汐，持續 %d 回合，每回合造成 %0.2f 寒冷和 %0.2f 物理傷害，擊退敵人，並降低他們的震懾抗性。", "tformat")
t("tidal wave", "潮汐", "_t")
t("%s brandishes %s, calling forth the might of the oceans!", "%s揮舞着%s，召喚了海洋的力量!", "logSeen")
t("Ring of the Dead", "亡者之戒", "entity name")
t("dull black ring", "黯淡的戒指", "_t")
t("This ring is imbued with powers from beyond the grave. It is said that those who wear it may find a new path when all other roads turn dim.", "這枚戒指充溢着墳墓的氣息。據說佩戴它的人會在走投無路時發現新的道路。", "_t")
t("Will bring you back from death, but only once!", "能將你從死亡邊緣拯救1次", "_t")
t("Elemental Fury", "元素之怒", "entity name")
t("multi-hued ring", "多彩戒指", "_t")
t("This ring shines with many colors.", "這枚戒指閃耀着多種不同的色彩。", "_t")
