t("This black hat once belonged to a powerful mage named Malslek, in the Age of Dusk, who was known to deal with beings from other planes. In particular, he dealt with many powerful demons, until one of them, tired of his affairs, betrayed him and stole his power. In his rage, Malslek set fire to his own tower in an attempt to kill the demon. This charred hat is all that remained in the ruins.", "這頂黑色的帽子曾屬於一名強大的法師馬斯拉克，在黃昏紀時以交遊位面之廣而著稱。值得一提的是，他還與許多惡魔進行了交易。直到某一天，一名惡魔厭煩了契約的約束而背叛了他並偷走了馬斯拉克的力量。馬斯拉克一氣之下燒燬了自己的高塔，意圖殺死這隻惡魔。最終，廢墟中只剩下了這頂帽子流傳至今。", "_t")
t("#RED#Malslek's hatred flows through you.", "#RED#馬斯拉克的仇恨在你體內流淌。", "logPlayer")
t("Fortune's Eye", "幸運之眼", "entity name")
t("golden telescope", "金色望遠鏡", "_t")
t([[This finely crafted telescope once belonged to the explorer and adventurer Kestin Highfin. With this tool in hand he traveled in search of treasures all across Maj'Eyal, and before his death it was said his collection was incredibly vast. He often credited this telescope with his luck, saying that as long as he had it, he could escape any situation, no matter how dangerous. It is said he died confronting a demon seeking revenge for a stolen sword.

His last known words were "Somehow this feels like an ending, yet I know there is so much more to find."]], "這副精緻的望遠鏡曾屬於一位著名的冒險家和探險家科斯汀·赫菲因。有此寶在手，赫菲因遍歷了整個馬基埃亞爾大陸，在他死前據說他蒐集了許多寶貴的財富。他相信這副望遠鏡能帶給他好運，有此物在手，無論面對任何險境，都能死裏逃生。相傳，他死於一名惡魔的報復，報復他偷走了惡魔私藏的一把劍。海風留給世間的最後遺言是——想要我的財富嗎？那就去找吧，我的一切都在那裏，大幕纔剛剛拉開。", "_t")
