t("This massive suit of plate boasts an enormous bulk and overbearing weight. Said to belong to a nameless soldier who safeguarded a passage across the bridge to his village, in defiance to the cohorts of invading orcs. After days of assault failed to fell him, the orcs turned back. The man however, fell dead on the spot - from exhaustion. The armor had finally claimed his life.", "這件結實碩大的板甲有着誇張的體積和難以想象的重量。相傳這件板甲屬於一位不知名的士兵，爲了抵禦洪水般的獸人軍團入侵他的家鄉，這名士兵守護在通向他村莊的大橋上。經過幾天幾夜慘烈的進攻，獸人沒能擊倒他，最終敵人撤退了。而這名傳奇般的士兵，也因爲精疲力竭當場倒斃，這件盔甲最終奪去了他的生命。", "_t")
t([[When your effective movement speed (global speed times movement speed) is less than 100%%, reduces all incoming damage by a percent equal to the speed detriment (up to 70%%).
Current reduction bonus: %d%%]], [[當你的有效移動速度（整體速度乘移動速度）小於100%%的時候，降低所有傷害，比例相當於當前移動速度和100%%的差距，但最大不超過70%%。
當前減傷比例：%d%%]], "tformat")
t("slow the movement speed of all creatures (including yourself) within range 5 by 40% for 3 turns", "將範圍5內所有生物的移動速度（包括你自己）降低40%，持續3回合。", "_t")
t("%s rebalances the bulky plates of %s %s, and things slow down a bit.", "%s重新組合了%s%s的重型裝甲板，放慢了速度。", "logSeen")
t("The Face of Fear", "恐懼之顏", "entity name")
t("bone mask", "骨質面具", "_t")
t("This mask appears to be carved out of the skull of a creature that never should have existed, malformed and distorted. You shiver as you look upon it, and its hollow eye sockets seem to stare back into you.", "這件面具似乎用某種不明生物的頭骨製成的，那是一種本不應該存在於世間的可怕生物，畸形並且扭曲。每當你盯着這個面具時，它那空洞的眼窩似乎也在注視着你，令你感到發自內心的顫慄。", "_t")
t("flame coated sandals", "一雙被火焰覆蓋的草鞋", "_t")
t("Cinderfeet", "餘燼之足", "entity name")
t("A cautionary tale tells of the ancient warlock by the name of Caim, who fancied himself daily walks through Goedalath, both to test himself and the harsh demonic wastes. He was careful to never bring anything back with him, lest it provide a beacon for the demons to find him. Unfortunately, over time, his sandals drenched in the soot and ashes of the fearscape and the fire followed his footsteps outside, drawing in the conclusion of his grim fate.", "這是一個警示故事，講的是有個叫凱姆的古代術士，爲了勘查地獄般的惡魔荒原，也爲了考驗自己，自命不凡的認爲可以在惡魔的老巢高達勒斯天天散步。他每次從惡魔位面歸來都小心翼翼地不敢帶回任何東西，生怕成爲惡魔找到他的指引。不幸的是，來回很多次以後，他的草鞋浸滿了恐懼之地的煙塵和灰燼。地獄之焰隨他的腳步被帶到了世間，同時也註定了他悲慘的命運。", "_t")
t("Each step you take leaves a burning trail behind you lasting 5 turns that deals %d fire damage (based on Spellpower) to foes who enter it.", "你每踏出一步會在腳下留下一條持續5回合的燃燒痕跡，對所有經過的生物造成 %d 火焰傷害 (基於法術強度)", "tformat")
t("fire trail", "火焰尾跡", "_t")
t("Cuirass of the Dark Lord", "黑暗領主胸甲", "entity name")
t("black, spiked armor", "一件黑色的尖刺鎧甲", "_t")
t("Worn by a villain long forgotten, this armor was powered by the blood of thousands of innocents. Decrepit and old, the dark lord died in solitude, his dominion crumbled, his subjects gone. Only this cuirass remained, dying to finally taste fresh blood again.", "這件胸甲屬於一個早已被人遺忘的暴君，成千上萬無辜死者的鮮血強化了這件鎧甲。黑暗領主最終在衰老與虛弱中孤獨的死去，他的統治分崩離析，他的人民四散而去。只有這件胸甲被保留了下來，渴望着再次品嚐鮮血的味道。", "_t")
t("drain blood from all creatures within range 5, causing them to bleed for %0.2f physical damage over 4 turns (based on your Physicalpower). For each creature drained (up to 10), the armor gains strength, which fades over 10 turns if it is not fed", "吸收半徑5內所有生物的血液，令其在 4 回合內受到 %0.2f 點物理傷害。每吸收一個生物（至多10），護甲的屬性增加。 10回合後復原。", "tformat")
t("%s revels in the bloodlust of %s %s!", "%s激發了%s%s的嗜血渴望!", "logSeen")
t("Blood Charges: %d", "鮮血吸收：%d", "tformat")
t("Decayed Visage", "墮落視覺", "entity name")
t("mask of mummified skin", "木乃伊皮面罩", "_t")
t("A desiccated mask of human skin, all that remains of a necromancer from the Age of Pyre who failed to achieve lichdom.  The transformative process partially succeeded, leaving him unable to die as his body slowly rotted from the inside out over several years.  Now his spirit resides within this last bit of mummified flesh, still hungering for eternal life.", "一小片人皮面具，是派爾紀一位死靈法師的遺物。他試圖變成巫妖，但是沒有成功。他的身體逐漸腐爛，但由於未成功的法術而不能死去，就這樣過了數年。現在，他的靈魂仍藏身於這小塊皮膚中，渴求着永恆的生命。", "_t")
t("Dream Malleus", "夢境之槌", "entity name")
t("keening hammer", "發光木錘", "_t")
t("A large shimmering maul that seems to produce a ringing in your ears.  It is both as malleable as thought and as hard as the strongest steel.", "一個閃閃發光的大木槌,你的耳朵裏似乎能聽到它發出的聲音.它既像思想一樣有可塑性也像最強的鋼鐵那樣堅硬.", "_t")
t("Cloud Caller", "喚雲者", "entity name")
t("broad brimmed hat", "寬邊帽", "_t")
t("This hat's broad brim protects you from biting colds and sudden storms.", "這頂帽子寬闊的帽檐保護您免受呼嘯的寒風和突如其來的暴風雨.", "_t")
t("A small storm cloud follows you, dealing 15 lightning damage to all enemies in a radius of 3 each turn.", "一團小小的風暴包圍着你，每回合對周圍3碼內的敵人造成15閃電傷害。", "_t")
t("charm", "護符", "entity type")
t("torque", "項圈", "entity subtype")
t("The Jolt", "震撼", "entity name")
t("tingling torque", "刺痛項圈", "_t")
t("This torque feels tingly to the touch, but seems to enhance your thinking.", "這項圈摸起來讓人覺得刺痛,但似乎增強了你的思考.", "_t")
t([[Your mind is attuned to electricity.
Any lightning damage you do that is more than 10% of the victim's maximum life will attempt to brainlock the target.
Upon taking lightning damage >10% of your max life, your mind fires back, dealing 30% of the original damage as mind and trying to brainlock the target.
Upon taking mind damage >10% of your max life, you reflexively trigger the jolt, sending an arc of dazing lightning toward the target (damage based on mindpower).
This item can have up to 2 charges, with each charge having 4 turn cooldown.]], [[你的精神與電力連接。
你對敵人造成的超過其最大生命值10%的閃電傷害時，會試圖附加思維封鎖效果。
當你受到相當於最大生命值10%的閃電傷害時，你的精神會發起反擊，對敵人造成30%的原傷害，並試圖附加思維封鎖效果。
當你受到相當於最大生命值10%的精神傷害時，你會快速啓動這個項圈，朝敵人射出一團震懾的閃電，傷害基於意志。
這個物品可以存儲兩次充能，每次充能冷卻時間4回合。]], "_t")
t("damp steel battle axe", "潮溼的鋼鐵戰斧", "_t")
