t("Crafted for a warlord who wanted to keep his subjects under a stralite grip. Dark thoughts went into the making of these gauntlets, literally.", "一個軍閥爲了永遠掌握他的臣民而製造的.黑暗的思想被真正的灌注進去這些手套裏.", "_t")
t("Icy Kill", "冰冷殺戮", "entity name")
t("sharpened icicle", "鋒利的冰柱", "_t")
t([[As any scryer knows, the link between the murderer and the murdered is the murder weapon, and a scryer can follow that link from the murdered to the weapon to the murderer.
One rather cold blooded killer thought of a way around this. By carving blades out of ice, they could kill as they wished and the link would just melt away.
Their killing spree ended when one of the victims got lucky and managed to stab the murderer in the heart with the icey blade. After being united with the cold heart that created it, the final ice blade has never melted.]], [[任何占卜師都知道，兇器乃是緝查兇手最重要的線索；他們往往順着這條線索順藤摸瓜，從人羣中找出兇手的真身。
然而，一個冷酷的殺手找到了一個辦法：他用寒冰鑄成了一把利刃，將其刺入受害者的胸口，讓其隨着受害者心臟的體溫漸漸融化，消失於無形。
最終，這名殺手仍然沒有逍遙於法外。一名受害者幸運地奪下了利刃，反身刺入了殺手的心臟裏。殺手冷酷的內心沒有溫度，而這把與其相融的利刃從此再也不會融化。]], "_t")
