section "game/modules/tome/data/ingredients.lua"

t("length of troll intestine", "較長的巨魔腸子", "ingredient name")
t("A length of troll intestines. Fortunately, the troll appears to have eaten nothing in some time.", "一截較長的巨魔腸子。幸運的是，這隻巨魔碰巧沒吃任何東西。", "_t")
t("Kindly empty it before returning.", " 在把它帶回來之前請把它清理乾淨。", "_t")
t("skeleton mage skull", "骷髏法師頭骨", "ingredient name")
t("The skull of a skeleton mage. The eyes have stopped glowing... for now.", "一顆骷髏法師的頭骨。現在……它的眼睛已經暗淡了。", "_t")
t("If the eyes are still glowing, please bash it around a bit until they fade. I'll not have another one of those coming alive and wreaking havoc in my lab.", " 如果它的眼睛仍然亮着，請猛擊它直到不再發光爲止。我不想再要一個會突然活過來並把我的實驗室搞的一塌糊塗的頭骨了。", "_t")
t("ritch stinger", "裏奇螫針", "ingredient name")
t("A ritch stinger, still glistening with venom.", "一隻裏奇的螫針，還殘留着許多粘稠的毒液。", "_t")
t("Keep as much venom in it as possible.", " 請儘可能多的保持螫針的毒液。", "_t")
t("orc heart", "獸人心臟", "ingredient name")
t("The heart of an orc. Perhaps surprisingly, it isn't green.", "一顆獸人的心臟。很驚訝吧，它不是綠色的。", "_t")
t("If you can fetch me a still-beating orc heart, that would be even better. But you don't look like a master necromancer to me.", " 如果你能給我一個新鮮的、跳動着的獸人心臟，那就太好了。但是在我看來，你不像是一個死靈魔導師。", "_t")
t("naga tongue", "娜迦舌頭", "ingredient name")
t("A severed naga tongue. It reeks of brine.", "一截娜迦的舌頭。它散發着海水的氣息。", "_t")
t("Best results occur with tongues never tainted by profanity, so if you happen to know any saintly nagas...", " 最好的結果便是從未被污言穢語褻瀆過的舌頭，所以如果你正好碰到那些聖者娜迦…… ", "_t")
t("vial of greater demon bile", "大惡魔的膽汁", "ingredient name")
t("A vial of greater demon bile. It hurts your sinuses even with the vial's stopper firmly in place.", "一瓶大惡魔的膽汁。儘管有着良好的阻隔，它仍刺激着你的鼻竇。", "_t")
t("Don't drink it, even if it tells you to.", " 不要去喝它，即使它誘惑着你…… ", "_t")
t("pouch of bone giant dust", "一袋骨巨人的骨灰", "ingredient name")
t("Once the magics animating the bone giant fled, its remains crumbled to dust. It might be your imagination, but it looks like the dust occasionally stirs on its own.", "當操縱骨巨人的魔法力量消散後，塵歸塵，土歸土。也許是你的幻覺，但是它似乎偶爾會自行移動起來。", "_t")
t("Never, ever to be confused with garlic powder. Trust me.", " 絕對絕對不要和大蒜粉搞混，相信我…… ", "_t")
t("ice ant stinger", "冰蟻的螫針", "ingredient name")
t("Wickedly sharp and still freezing cold.", "異乎尋常的鋒利且散發着陣陣寒氣。", "_t")
t("If you've the means to eliminate the little venom problem, these make miraculous instant drink-chilling straws.", " 如果你有方法消除小小的毒液問題，這些螫針可以成爲不可思議的冷凍吸管。", "_t")
t("minotaur nose", "米諾陶的鼻子", "ingredient name")
t("The severed front half of a minotaur snout, ring and all.", "一隻米諾陶的鼻子的前半部分，上面有圓環裝飾。", "_t")
t("You'll need to find one with a ring, preferably an expensive one.", " 你要尋找 1 個帶有圓環的，最好是比較貴的那個。", "_t")
t("vial of elder vampire blood", "一瓶高級吸血鬼的血液", "ingredient name")
t("Thick, clotted, and foul. The vial is cold to the touch.", "粘稠的、凝固的、邪惡的液體。瓶子摸起來很冷。", "_t")
t("Once you've gotten it, cross some moving water on your way back.", " 取得它之後，你最好在回去的路上用活水寫些十字。", "_t")
t("multi-hued wyrm scale", "多彩的龍鱗", "ingredient name")
t("Beautiful and nearly impregnable. Separating it from the dragon must have been hard work.", "美麗且異常堅固的龍鱗。把它從龍身上扒下來一定費了不少力氣。", "_t")
t("If you think collecting one of these is hard, try liquefying one.", " 如果你認爲收集一片龍鱗很困難，那麼去嘗試溶解它吧。", "_t")
t("giant spider spinneret", "巨蛛的絲腺", "ingredient name")
t("An ugly, ripped-out chunk of giant spider. Bits of silk protrude from an orifice.", "從巨型蜘蛛身上扯下的一大塊醜陋的器官，少量的絲線從某個洞中伸出。", "_t")
t("The spiders in your barn won't do. You'll know a giant spider when you see one, though they're rare in Maj'Eyal.", " 你家倉庫裏的蜘蛛是不行的。當你看到一隻時，你就會明白什麼是巨型蜘蛛，儘管在馬基埃亞爾這種蜘蛛很稀少。", "_t")
t("honey tree root", "蜜蜂樹的根", "ingredient name")
t("The severed end of one of a honey tree's roots. It wriggles around occasionally, seemingly unwilling to admit that it's dead... and a *plant*.", "蜜蜂樹的一根樹根。它偶爾會蠕動下，似乎不承認它已經死了，而且還是個“植物”。", "_t")
t("Keep a firm grip on it. These things will dig themselves right back into the ground if you drop them.", " 牢牢的抓住它，如果你不小心把它掉在地上，它會立刻挖地逃走。", "_t")
t("bloated horror heart", "浮腫的恐魔心臟", "ingredient name")
t("Diseased-looking and reeking. It seems to be decaying as you watch.", "病變且散發着熱氣的心臟，在你看它的這段時間裏，它似乎開始腐爛。", "_t")
t("Don't worry if it dissolves. Just don't get any on you.", " 不要擔心它的腐爛，只要不碰到你身上就沒事。", "_t")
t("electric eel tail", "電鰻尾巴", "ingredient name")
t("Slimy, wriggling, and crackling with electricity.", "油膩的、蠕動的尾巴，並且它能發出噼啪作響的電火花。", "_t")
t("I know, I know. Where does the eel stop and the tail start? It doesn't much matter. The last ten inches or so should do nicely.", " 我知道，我知道。你想問電鰻的尾巴是哪一段？沒有確切的答案。最後 10 英寸或許是最合適的。", "_t")
t("vial of squid ink", "一瓶烏賊墨汁", "ingredient name")
t("Thick, black and opaque.", "粘稠的黑色不透明墨汁。", "_t")
t("However annoying this will be for you to gather, I promise that the reek it produces in my lab will prove even more annoying.", " 不管你怎樣討厭它，都需要你去採集，我向你保證我在實驗室用它做出的東西會更加令人討厭。", "_t")
t("bear paw", "熊爪", "ingredient name")
t("Large and hairy with flesh-rending claws. It smells slightly of fish.", "巨大的多毛肉爪。它聞起來有點魚肉的味道。", "_t")
t("You'd think I could get one of these from a local hunter, but they've had no luck. Don't get eaten.", " 你認爲我可以從本地的獵戶手上取得它嗎？甭想了，他們沒那個運氣。不要被吃掉了。", "_t")
t("ice wyrm tooth", "冰霜巨龍的牙齒", "ingredient name")
t("This tooth has been blunted with age, but still looks more than capable of doing its job.", "這顆牙齒飽受歲月的侵蝕，但是仍然能勝任它的工作。", "_t")
t("Ice Wyrms lose teeth fairly often, so you might get lucky and not have to do battle with one. But dress warm just in case.", " 冰龍每隔一段時間會換齒，所以你幸運的話，可以撿到幾顆而不需要和它戰鬥。保險起見穿的暖和點…… ", "_t")
t("red crystal shard", "紅色水晶碎片", "ingredient name")
t("Tiny flames still dance ethereally inside this transparent crystal, though its heat seems to have faded... you hope.", "儘管熱度已去，小巧的火焰仍然在在這顆透明的水晶裏飛舞着。", "_t")
t("I hear these can be found in a cave near Elvala. I also hear that they can cause you to spontaneously combust, so no need to explain if you come back hideously scarred.", " 我聽說這些小傢伙可以在埃爾瓦拉附近的洞穴裏找到。我還聽說它們會使你自燃，所以當你高度燒傷回來的話，不要向我訴苦。", "_t")
t("vial of fire wyrm saliva", "一瓶火龍涎", "ingredient name")
t("Clear and slightly thicker than water. It froths when shaken.", "龍涎比水更加粘稠，和水一樣清澈，當你搖晃它時會有泡沫產生。", "_t")
t("Keep this stuff well away from your campfire unless you want me to have to find a new, more alive adventurer.", " 把這個瓶子離你的篝火遠一些，我可不想明天重新找一個活的冒險家。", "_t")
t("chunk of ghoul flesh", "腐爛的食屍鬼肉塊", "ingredient name")
t("Rotten and reeking. It still twitches occasionally.", "這塊肉腐爛且冒着熱氣，它時不時會抽搐兩下。", "_t")
t("Unfortunately for you, the chunks that regularly fall off ghouls won't do. I need one freshly carved off.", " 告訴你一個不幸的消息，平時從食屍鬼身上掉下來的肉是不行的。我需要新鮮的，剛切下來的肉。", "_t")
t("mummified bone", "木乃伊骨頭", "ingredient name")
t("Bits of dry flesh still cling to this ancient bone.", "在這個古代的骨頭上仍殘留着一點肉塊。", "_t")
t("That is, a bone from a corpse that's undergone mummification. Actually, any bit of the body would do, but the bones are the only parts you're certain to find when you kick a mummy apart. I recommend finding one that doesn't apply curses.", " 那就是，經過木乃伊化的屍體身上的骨頭。實際上，身體的任何部位都可以，只是從它們身上只能找到骨頭了。我推薦你去找一根沒有被詛咒的骨頭。", "_t")
t("sandworm tooth", "沙蟲之牙", "ingredient name")
t("Tiny, dark grey, and wickedly sharp. It looks more like rock than bone.", "這顆小巧的牙齒呈暗灰色且鋒利的嚇人。它看起來更像是一塊石頭而不是一顆牙齒。", "_t")
t("Yes, sandworms have teeth. They're just very small and well back from where you're ever likely to see them and live.", " 是的，沙蟲也有牙齒。它們只是很小，藏得很好，如果你把頭伸進去找它你就沒法活着回來了。", "_t")
t("black mamba head", "黑曼巴頭", "ingredient name")
t("Unlike the rest of the black mamba, the severed head isn't moving.", "不像這條蛇的其他部分，這顆頭一動不動。", "_t")
t("If you get bitten, I can save your life if you still manage to bring back the head... and if it happens within about a minute from my door. Good luck.", " 如果你被它咬到了，只要你堅持到把它帶回來我就可以拯救你……但是如果你不能及時帶回來，那麼，祝你好運。", "_t")
t("snow giant kidney", "雪巨人的腎臟", "ingredient name")
t("As unpleasant-looking as any exposed organ.", "像其他解剖的器官一樣，這個腎臟很難看。", "_t")
t("I suggest not killing the snow giant by impaling it through the kidneys. You'll just have to find another.", " 我建議你不要從雪巨人的腎臟部位刺死它，否則你不得不尋找另外一個。", "_t")
t("storm wyrm claw", "風暴之龍的爪子", "ingredient name")
t("Bluish and wickedly sharp. It makes your arm hair stand on end.", "這隻爪子泛着藍色光澤並且鋒利的嚇人，它使你汗毛豎立。", "_t")
t("I recommend severing one of dewclaws. They're smaller and easier to remove, but they've never been blunted by use, so be careful you don't poke yourself. Oh yes, and don't get eaten.", " 我建議你割斷其中一隻爪子，它們更小而且容易被割下。但是它們從來不會因使用而鈍化，所以當心點別劃傷你自己。哦，對了，還有別被吃掉。", "_t")
t("green worm", "翡翠蠕蟲", "ingredient name")
t("A dead green worm, painstakingly separated from its tangle of companions.", "一隻死掉的綠色蟲子，需要非常仔細才能把它從蠕蟲團中挑揀出來。", "_t")
t("Try to get any knots out before returning. Wear gloves.", " 在回來之前把打結在上面的其他蠕蟲統統清理掉。戴上手套。", "_t")
t("vial of wight ectoplasm", "一瓶屍妖的血漿", "ingredient name")
t("Cloudy and thick. Only by bottling it can you prevent it from evaporating within minutes.", "絮狀且粘稠的液體。只有把它裝入瓶中，才能阻止蒸發。", "_t")
t("If you ingest any of this, never mind coming back here. Please.", " 如果你不小心喝掉一點，請不要介意回到我這。", "_t")
t("xorn fragment", "索爾石碎片", "ingredient name")
t("Looks much like any other rock, though this one was recently sentient and trying to murder you.", "撇開最近這塊石頭對你的刺殺行爲外，它看起來和其他石頭一模一樣。", "_t")
t("Avoid fragments that contained the xorn's eyes. You've no idea how unpleasant it is being watched by your ingredients.", " 不要帶回包含着索爾石怪眼睛的碎片。你不知道被你的原材料盯着是多麼難受的一件事。", "_t")
t("warg claw", "座狼爪", "ingredient name")
t("Unpleasantly large and sharp for a canine's claw.", "對於一隻犬科動物來說，這隻爪子實在太大了。", "_t")
t("My usual ingredient gatherers draw the line at hunting wargs. Feel free to mock them on your way back.", " 我對原料的需求使我想到了獵殺座狼。在你回來的時候請弄一隻爪子回來。", "_t")
t("pouch of faeros ash", "法羅的灰燼", "ingredient name")
t("Unremarkable grey ash.", "不起眼的灰燼。", "_t")
t("They're creatures of pure flame, and likely of extraplanar origin, but the ash of objects consumed by their fire has remarkable properties.", " 它們是由純粹的火焰組成的生物，似乎來自另一個世界。然而，由它們的火焰燃燒成的灰燼有着非凡的功效。", "_t")
t("wretchling eyeball", "酸液樹魔之眼", "ingredient name")
t("Small and bloodshot. Its dead gaze still burns your skin.", "小而充血的眼球，它死亡時的眼神仍使你毛骨悚然。", "_t")
t("Evil little things, wretchlings. Feel free to kill as many as you can, though I just need the one intact eyeball.", " 邪惡的小惡魔，酸液樹魔。你可以盡情的殺戮它們，儘管我只需要一隻完整的眼球。", "_t")
t("faerlhing fang", "費爾荷毒牙", "ingredient name")
t("It still drips venom and crackles with magical energy.", "它仍殘留着一些毒液，並散發着陣陣魔法能量。", "_t")
t("I've lost a number of adventurers to this one, but I'm sure you'll be fine.", " 我已經在這個工作中失去了許多冒險者，但我確信你會安全歸來。", "_t")
t("vampire lord fang", "吸血鬼族長的毒牙", "ingredient name")
t("Brilliantly white, but surrounded by blackest magic.", "亮白色的牙齒，周身卻縈繞着黑色的魔法。", "_t")
t("You should definitely consider not pricking yourself with it.", " 你必須確保自己不會被它劃傷。", "_t")
t("hummerhorn wing", "半透明的昆蟲翅膀", "ingredient name")
t("Translucent and delicate-looking, but surprisingly durable.", "半透明的翅膀看起來很脆，實際上你會發現它異常的堅韌。", "_t")
t("If you've not encountered hummerhorns before, they're like wasps, only gigantic and lethal.", " 如果你以前沒看過殺人蜂，你可以想象下……它們像大黃蜂一樣，只不過變的巨大而致命。", "_t")
t("organic", "器官", "ingredient type")
t("pouch of luminous horror dust", "一袋金色恐魔的粉塵", "ingredient name")
