section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/blighted-ruins.lua"

t("Work on my glorious project has been delayed. This displeases me. The fools from the nearby village are starting to suspect my presence, and have begun guarding their graveyards and cemeteries closely. Whatever meagre remains I can steal away are often too rotted or insubstantial to use for my project, so I have no choice but to use them as sub-par minions instead. Perhaps they will sow enough conflict and discord so that new, fresher remains will become available...", [[我偉大的計劃被耽擱了。這真讓我不爽。
	附近村莊裏的傻瓜們開始懷疑我來此的目的了，並在墓地周圍豎起了防禦，其實我從墓地得來的那些殘渣早就腐爛不堪了，萬般無奈下我只能將它們當做備用品使用，也許讓這些傢伙的互相猜忌會產生更多新鮮的屍體供我驅使……]], "_t")
t("The cloak of deception is complete! Truly my finest work, not counting my project of course, it allows my minions to walk amongst the living without arousing their suspicions at all. Already I have taken a stroll to a nearby town alongside a ghoulish thrall, wrapped in the cloak... hah! The fools didn't even bat an eyelid! With this item, acquisition of components for my project shall be all the more simple.", "欺詐斗篷已經完成！這簡直是我偉大計劃以外的最高傑作，他能使我的僕人們輕易的穿梭於人羣而不會引起任何懷疑。我已穿着此袍大搖大擺地裹着一個食屍鬼僕從在周圍的一個小鎮晃盪了一圈, 鎮裏的傻瓜們眼皮都不擡一下! 有了這件袍子，我計劃所需的材料真是太容易獲得了……", "_t")
t("Fate smiles upon me. What did I come across today but the body of an unfortunate %s? Unfortunate indeed, but rather fortunate for me. The body displays next to no decomposition... it shall be perfect! With this new minion and the cloak of deception, the completion of my project is all but assured. I must prepare for the ritual... my dark menagerie shall soon have a new member.", "命運女神向我微笑，我今天發現了一具%s倒黴鬼的屍體？這個徹頭徹尾的倒黴鬼卻是我命中的福星。他的屍體還沒有完全腐爛……真是完美！自從有了欺詐斗篷，我腰不酸了腿不疼了跑步也能上五樓了，我偉大計劃的結晶也已變成囊中之物了。我必須儘快開始準備儀式……我的不死軍隊又將加入一名新成員。", "tformat")
t("blighted ruins", "荒蕪廢墟", "newLore category")
t("note from the Necromancer", "死靈法師的筆記", "_t")
t("My masterpiece walks! It is glorious, beautiful. While it remains unfinished, it is finished enough to serve in its purpose of protecting my lair. No would-be hero will be able to defeat it, and once it is complete it will be nigh invulnerable! Now all that remains is to animate my newest minion and bend it to my will... then they'll see. They'll ALL see. What can possibly stop me now, I ask? What?!", "我的大師之作！它閃耀着榮光，真是美極了。雖然它還沒有全部完成，但卻足以保護我的巢穴。絕對沒有任何英雄能擊敗它，當它成爲完全體時就是無敵的存在啊，那時我將成爲世界之主，誰能擋我，我大吼三聲誰來斬我！哇哈哈！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/daikara.lua"

t([[#{bold}#Relle, Cornac Fighter & Expedition Captain#{normal}#
Nothing but hatchlings so far. Honestly, if this keeps up we won't have enough dragonhide to cover a dragon, let alone cover our losses. I've really spared no expense this time as well: Gorran is one of the finest rangers I know, and Sodelost... his prices are exorbitant, but then what else would you expect from those money-grubbing dwarven Thronesmen? I must admit I don't know much about Xann. The locals say there's no finer wyrmic in the area, and I admit she is something special in combat. Now, if only she could turn her draconic talents to FINDING some dragons!]], [[#{bold}#探險隊隊長，戰士瑞麗#{normal}#
到現在爲止，到手的都是幼龍。老實說，如果這種情況繼續下去，我們都湊不夠一條龍的龍皮，更別說彌補我們的損失了。這次我可要傾家蕩產了：高嵐是我所知道的最棒的尋林客之一，而蘇達羅斯特……他要價太高了，但這些矮人王的部下財迷心竅也不是一天兩天了。我確實不是很瞭解希安。當地人稱她爲這個區域裏首屈一指的龍戰士，這傢伙打架確實有一手。但她要是在獵龍方面也如此出色的話，我就別無他求了！]], "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Sodelost, Dwarf Rogue#{normal}#
Can't believe I agreed to this expedition. I suppose it's because I've known Relle for a while. We've crossed paths many times at Derth's trading post. I even gave her a special rate for my services. Sentimental fool! All it's got me is boots filled with snow and a light coinpurse. I still don't understand why these Kingdom types are so enamoured with drakeskin... makes superior armour they say. Pah! If you can't handle metal armour, what business do you have even wearing armour? Leather has about as much use as a halfling tied to a... noises up ahead, must stop writing.]], [[#{bold}#矮人盜賊，蘇達羅斯特#{normal}#
不敢相信我居然同意了這次探險，也許是因爲我和瑞麗相熟的緣故吧。我們多次在德斯的交易站打過照面。她還擁有我的特殊折扣券。多愁善感的我真是愚蠢啊！現在落得口袋空空、滿靴積雪的下場……這些皇子皇孫們咋就這麼鍾愛龍皮…… 聽說這玩意能做很好的盔甲？靠！你要是穿不了金屬鎧甲，幹嘛還穿個毛線盔甲啊？皮能給你帶來的保護就像半身人嘗試……上面好吵，先擱筆了。]], "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Gorran, Cornac Archer#{normal}#
That snake. That addlepated beardling. That coin-hounding, blackhearted, stump-kneed dwarf! A scout he calls himself! The finest eyes of the Iron Throne, able to read the sign of the tavern in Last Hope from the tavern in Derth! Surely someone with such grandiose praise for his own eyesight would have spotted that cold drake waiting in ambush for us! Damnable thing, I'll be lucky if I can ever use my left arm again. I can't use my bow now ... I'm effectively dead wood to the team. I'm beginning to think that Sodelost has ulterior motives... I wouldn't put it past a dwarf to lead us up this forsaken mountain to die just so he could rifle through our pockets! I keep telling Relle, but she won't listen. The fool...]], [[#{bold}#弓箭手，高嵐#{normal}#
這個賊眉鼠眼的惡棍，財迷心竅的混蛋，黑心黑肺黑肚腸的小人，滿臉鬍鬚的蠢材，行動遲緩的矮子！他還有臉說自己是個哨兵，你就是個燒餅！鋼鐵王座最好的眼線，能一眼看穿從德斯到最後的希望發生的所有事情! 嘴上吹的這麼牛，眼力勁這麼好，你丫的就不能發現埋伏我們的冰龍嗎。無能的白癡，老子手臂以後還能用就謝天謝地了。該死的，現在我連弓都拉不開了……我現在就是個廢物…… 這傢伙是不是心懷鬼胎，想在這鬼地方整死我，好掏空我的口袋，洗劫我的屍體，我早就告誡過瑞麗，這傻女人就是不聽……]], "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Relle, Cornac Fighter & Expedition Captain#{normal}#
Sodelost is dead, and so is Gorran. The former by Gorran's hand, the latter by my hand. Even in these wastes I cannot abide such an act of mutiny. I was aware of Gorran's anger ever since the drake attack, but I never dreamed he would turn on Sodelost like he did. He had taken my longsword as I slept the previous night, strode up to Sodelost, unheeding of I and Xann watching him, ran him through and laughed. Simply laughed. There was nothing for it; I wrenched my sword from his hand and brought it down on his neck. The commotion seems to have stirred up a nearby drake's nest, and now I fear we don't have the strength to repel a concentrated attack. We may have to abandon this expedition.]], [[#{bold}#探險隊隊長，戰士瑞麗#{normal}#
蘇達羅斯特已經死了，高嵐步了他的後塵。高嵐幹掉了前者，我則搞定了後者。就算是損兵折將，我也絕不能容忍這樣的背叛。在飛龍突襲我們後，我就開始提防高嵐，防止他在背後捅刀子，但他居然真的對蘇達羅斯特下了手。這傢伙趁夜色偷走了我的長劍並一路奔向蘇達羅斯特，完全沒有留意我和希安笑着對他一路尾隨。可笑的蠢材，我一把扭住他的手，奪回我的劍並在他脖子上留了一道深深的口子。 這場暴亂似乎驚動了附近的一個飛龍巢，這可不妙，恐怕我們現在完全無法反抗成羣飛龍的侵襲。這次冒險看來要就此結束了。]], "_t")
t("expedition journal entry (daikara)", "探險隊日記（岱卡拉）", "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Xann, Shaloren Wyrmic#{normal}# (This entry was scrawled by an unsteady hand)
#{italic}#impudent fools treading upon dragon's ground. slaying my dear kin just for their skin they will pay they will pay. i called the drake, told it to be cunning, avoid the dwarf's gaze. i laughed as it bit into that ranger's arm ahaahaa. they're killing each other now, simple creatures, simple soft skinned creatures. not like dragons, so perfect, symbols of power, perfection... their captain still lives, but not for long. i will bring her to you to feast.

rantha i will see you soon#{normal}#]], [[#{bold}#永恆精靈龍戰士，希安#{normal}# (便條由顫抖的手潦草塗鴉而成)
#{italic}#愚蠢的傢伙，你們竟敢踏入龍的領地，殘害我們的子孫，剝取他們的皮毛，你們會付出代價的，慘痛的代價。我喚來了飛龍，親授一條狡猾的計策，讓它避開矮人的巡視，當它一口咬住獵人的手臂時我大笑不止。這些蠢貨肯定會自相殘殺，單純的生物，單純的軟皮生物，他們有哪點比的上我們龍類，我們是這麼完美，簡直就是美與力量的象徵……他們的領隊還活蹦亂跳着，等過一會我就會請她參加我的宴會——作爲主菜，哦哈哈哈！

蘭莎，一會見#{normal}#]], "_t")
t("Dragonsfire Trap", "龍火陷阱", "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Relle, Cornac Fighter and Expedition Leader#{normal}#
It knows we're here.  Xann's gone, and I have to assume the worst.  Too late to run.  One option left, a contraption Sodelost ensured us he'd be able to use to get the kill...  shame he didn't leave instructions behind with it, it's unclear how to arm it, and I don't want to add "being charred to a crisp" to my list of troubles today.
I might not know a great deal about artifice, but I know how wild animals work, and for all the praise they get, dragons are no better.  I don't need to know how to rig this device so it goes off when the beast steps on it - I just need to put it inside something it'll eat whole...
#{italic}#Judging from this note's intact state and delicate placement next to a sack covered in assorted animal viscera, the dragon not only avoided setting off the trap, but has kept it as a trophy.  Inside the sack is a disarmed trap featuring a few recognizable alchemical flasks, and a means of mixing them in the right proportion when a pressure plate is triggered to produce a blast of dragonsfire. Figuring out how to arm it is almost as easy as figuring out how to make more traps like it.#{normal}#]], [[#{bold}#探險隊隊長，戰士瑞麗#{normal}#
那些龍知道我們在這裏。希安自己一個人跑了，我必須承擔最壞的情況。逃跑已經來不及了，只剩下一個選擇了，蘇達羅斯特曾經跟我們說過這個小東西可以保證可以殺掉……該死，可惜他根本沒留下說明書，我根本不知道該怎麼用這玩意兒，而我可不想在今天遇到的這麼多麻煩中間再加上“被烤焦”一項。

我可能不太瞭解盜賊工具的原理，但我知道怎麼對付野生動物。儘管人們都說龍很厲害，但我可不覺得他們能比動物強多少。我不需要知道具體怎麼組裝這個裝置才能讓它在動物踩上去的時候啓動——我只要把它放到什麼東西里面，等到龍把它一口吞下的時候……
#{italic}#從這張紙條毫無破損的完整狀態，以及它正處在一個裝滿動物內臟的袋子旁邊這一微妙的位置來看，龍不僅避免了陷阱，而且還把這個東西收藏起來作爲戰利品。在袋子裏裝着一個已經被接觸的陷阱，裏面依稀可以辨認出一些鍊金瓶子。當壓力板被觸發的時候，這些鍊金材料可以混合起來，產生一股龍火的爆炸。你可以很容易地搞清楚如何組裝和製造更多這樣的陷阱。#{normal}#]], "_t")
t("daikara", "岱卡拉", "newLore category")
t("Freezing Trap", "冰凍陷阱", "_t")
t([[#{bold}#Relle, Cornac Fighter and Expedition Leader#{normal}#
It knows we're here.  Xann's gone, and I have to assume the worst.  Too late to run.  One option left, a contraption Sodelost ensured us he'd be able to use to get the kill...  shame he didn't leave instructions behind with it, it's unclear how to arm it, and I don't want to add "being frozen solid" to my list of troubles today.
I might not know a great deal about artifice, but I know how wild animals work, and for all the praise they get, dragons are no better.  I don't need to know how to rig this device so it goes off when the beast steps on it - I just need to put it inside something it'll eat whole...
#{italic}#Judging from this note's intact state and delicate placement next to a sack covered in assorted animal viscera, the dragon not only avoided setting off the trap, but has kept it as a trophy.  Inside the sack is a disarmed trap featuring a few recognizable alchemical flasks, and a means of mixing them in the right proportion when a pressure plate is triggered to produce a blast of ice. Figuring out how to arm it is almost as easy as figuring out how to make more traps like it.#{normal}#]], [[#{bold}#探險隊隊長，戰士瑞麗#{normal}#
那些龍知道我們在這裏。希安自己一個人跑了，我必須承擔最壞的情況。逃跑已經來不及了，只剩下一個選擇了，蘇達羅斯特曾經跟我們說過這個小東西可以保證可以殺掉……該死，可惜他根本沒留下說明書，我根本不知道該怎麼用這玩意兒，而我可不想在今天遇到的這麼多麻煩中間再加上“被凍僵”一項。

我可能不太瞭解盜賊工具的原理，但我知道怎麼對付野生動物。儘管人們都說龍很厲害，但我可不覺得他們能比動物強多少。我不需要知道具體怎麼組裝這個裝置才能讓它在動物踩上去的時候啓動——我只要把它放到什麼東西里面，等到龍把它一口吞下的時候……
#{italic}#從這張紙條毫無破損的完整狀態，以及它正處在一個裝滿動物內臟的袋子旁邊這一微妙的位置來看，龍不僅避免了陷阱，而且還把這個東西收藏起來作爲戰利品。在袋子裏裝着一個已經被接觸的陷阱，裏面依稀可以辨認出一些鍊金瓶子。當壓力板被觸發的時候，這些鍊金材料可以混合起來，產生一團極冷的冷氣。你可以很容易地搞清楚如何組裝和製造更多這樣的陷阱。#{normal}#]], "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/derth.lua"

t("derth", "德斯鎮", "newLore category")
t("Beam Trap", "射線陷阱", "_t")
t([[#{italic}#A villager runs up to you, carrying a hefty looking sack.#{normal}#
You've saved us from the storms!  We can't ever repay you enough, but, well...  Shortly after you stopped them, a witch approached us and offered us some...  magical #{italic}#things#{normal}# and said they would protect our town if anything like that happened again.
It's not that I don't trust her, not after you and they - mostly you! - saved us, but...  I just don't feel comfortable having all this arcane stuff around us all the time.  None of us do.  If you've got a use for these, you're more than welcome to them.
#{italic}#He hands you a sack, containing a few dozen of the same strange magical object; included is a guide to using them and producing more, written for users completely inexperienced with magic.  Apparently, they're designed to be mounted on walls and rooftops, and will try to non-lethally incapacitate outside invaders while sending a message of distress to Angolwen.  With a few tweaks, you can make them deadly instead (and avoid harassing Angolwen while you're at it).#{normal}#]], [[#{italic}#一個村民向你跑來，手裏拿着一個漂亮的麻袋。#{normal}#
你從風暴中救了我們！你的恩情我們無以爲報，不過，正好…在你阻止了風暴之後，一個女巫到我們這裏來，給了我們一些…有魔法的#{italic}#東西#{normal}#。她說，如果這種事情再發生的話，她們就會保護我們的城鎮。
這可不是我不信任她，更何況你和他們——主要是你的功勞！——你們救了我，但是…我總覺得在我們周圍放着這些奧術魔法的東西讓我們感到有些不舒服。我們都是這麼想的。如果你能更好地利用這些東西，那麼請你好好收下它們吧。
#{italic}#他遞給你一個麻袋，裏面裝着幾十個一模一樣的奇怪的魔法物品。裏面還包含了有關如何使用和製造它們的說明，說明清晰易懂，不會魔法的人也能理解。顯然，它們是用來安裝在牆上或者屋頂上，會自動用非致命的手段擊退入侵者，並向安格列文報告這裏遇到危險的信息。通過一些調整，你可以讓它們變得更加致命（而且你使用它們的時候也不會騷擾到安格列文的人了）。#{normal}#]], "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/dreadfell.lua"

t([[MINIONS: Perhaps you feel your Master has been lax or absent? Well, I shall amend that. I have been studying an object of great import. It is of much greater interest than your foolish unlives. But do not think that I will let you get away with things because of this.

Skeletons, you have been getting noticeably behind in your adventurer slaughtering quotas. The next skeleton archer I see drinking coffee and chatting with the wights shall be rent limb from limb and fed to the orcs. Also, as a punishment for your general laxness, 1,000 skeletons shall be remanded down to Kor'Pul as punishment. A further 250 shall be slaughtered. These orders to be carried out by myself tomorrow at 3am.]], [[奴才們：也許汝等覺得吾最近鬆懈了？是啊，吾會改進這點。最近吾一直醉心於研究一個重要的項目，它給吾帶來的好處可比汝等這些不死廢物要大多了。但汝等可不要指望能因此而偷懶。

骷髏衆，最近你們獵殺的冒險者可比指標低太多了。就是你，後排那個骷髏射手！吾看到你和冒險者喝酒吃肉拜把子稱兄弟來着，這些傢伙本該被切成碎片拿去喂獸人的。作爲對汝等懶惰的嚴懲，1000個骷髏兵將被髮配到卡·普爾充軍，指標上的人頭數提高250，明早3點吾將親自發布這項命令。]], "_t")
t([[MINIONS: Be aware, I your great Master have found an item. It is of extreme power, but not yet complete, at least for my purposes.

All hail your brilliant Master. Would you like to walk in the sun? Would you like to be free to roam green meadows and crush innocent children? Such are my wishes also. The reward to anyone who brings me any item that will help me bend this sta... item to my will shall be stupendous.

Also, any new minions who have magical research skills are wanted. Recruit them and you shall be rewarded. Though if they steal my secrets, your blood will be my wine and your heart my appetizer.]], [[奴才們：注意了，汝等偉大的主人吾發現了一個寶物，它蘊藏着巨大的力量，雖然它並不完整，至少還不夠完成吾的宏圖大業。

讚美汝主。汝等有沒有夢想着在廣袤的草原上自由的奔馳，光明正大的在太陽下漫步，隨興的捏死人類無辜的嬰兒，無需考慮無需猶豫，只要誰能爲吾找到能粘合這把法……咳咳，這件寶物的辦法，它的願望就能實現。

同時，任何能使用魔法的物種都是我眼中的人才，替吾僱傭他們，而汝亦將被吾嘉獎。但小心了，要是找回來個倒鉤泄露了吾的祕密，我就會食汝之肉，飲汝之血，寢汝之皮。]], "_t")
t([[MINIONS: Perhaps you are minor dens of foulness because you have nothing to aspire to? Perhaps you could be greater if you had a worse example before you? Consider Me! I began my long unlife as a foolish pipsqueak such as yourself. Why, there was a time before I had conquered even a pit let alone a level or a dungeon. Now, behold all that is Mine.

You must have aspirations. I am not content with just the rule of Dreadfell. No, soon I shall have more. Much more. My boots shall tread the surface of the earth! I shall explore and destroy the most beautiful mountains. All shall be mine once I can walk in the sun once more. Where will you be? Do you wish to be more than the wight I stepped on yesterday? I shall need great leaders to guide my armies across the land.]], [[奴才們：汝等是否覺得身爲孤魂野鬼而感到前途一片黑暗，汝等是否對未來失去了憧憬，是否對自身失去了信心？也許汝等需要的只是一點點激勵，和一個榜樣。汝等的榜樣就是眼前：汝等偉大的主人！我最初和你們一樣是雜兵，其貌不揚，無足輕重，但吾堅持日行一善：堅持不懈的屠殺新手迷宮的探險者，天長日久總算修成正果，雄霸一方了。

做骷髏要有抱負。吾的目標可不光是對恐懼王座的統治而已。不久吾就會擁有更多，更多啊！吾將再次踏足地表，羣山將爲吾折服，大地將因吾沉陷。而那時的汝等又身居何職，難道那時的汝甘心做一名默默無聞的屍妖而已嗎，吾期待汝等之中的傑出精英替我掌管妖鬼大軍，一馬平川橫掃大陸，成就吾千秋霸業啊……]], "_t")
t([[MINIONS: You are foolish sods. Have you heard of the great Kor'Pul? Perhaps not, because you know very little and he died long before you were so stupid as to be born. However, he was great and had the chance to be greater still. He let himself be cooped into a small hellhole and was destroyed when the right hero invaded it and destroyed his plaything. Now he is but a mere shade of his former glory.

I shall not make this mistake. Be ready, for soon we shall march out upon the lands. Soon we shall conquer as even he could not. Pity the fool who thinks he can keep me stuck in even the grandest of pits, Dreadfell.]], [[奴才們：愚鈍的汝等可曾聽過偉大的卡·普爾的故事? 也許沒有吧，因爲他傳奇的時代遠在閉塞又狹隘的汝等出生以前。他當時是那樣的不可一世的巫妖，並有機會變得更加偉大。但他居然作起了宅男，將自己龜縮在一個小小的迷宮之類，直到一名天命英雄侵入迷宮並摧毀了他的靈魂匣。現在它僅僅是徘徊在自己過去榮光中的陰影而已。

吾絕不能重蹈他的覆轍。磨亮汝等的刀，清空汝等的肚腩，不久汝等將隨吾以雷霆萬鈞之勢衝上地表，征服一切。讓吾等盡情鄙視那些佔山爲王的傢伙，哪怕他是窩在偉大的恐懼王座。]], "_t")
t("note from the Master", "主人的筆記", "_t")
t([[MINIONS: To my newest vampire: burn, foolish adventurer, burn! I bet you are sorry for that flame spell now, aren't you? Suffer as I revisit it upon you.

To the rest of you, there will be punishment. An adventurer got down to my bedroom and surprised me. I, Myself, was hurt and almost had to use My special power. All is well now and I am as dangerous as ever, but you shall suffer for letting him get so low. The next minion I see shall be toasted with my marshmallows. Where then were the special pits of doom I organized? Where were the poisons of my wights or the diseases of my ghouls? Indeed, I should slaughter all of you, and I would, but those who were most foully remiss were already slaughtered by the adventurer. The rest of you? Beware My wrath.]], [[奴才們，致吾新來的吸血鬼：燃燒吧，愚蠢的冒險者，燃燒吧！現在你一定後悔無禮對我釋放這法術了吧？在你自己的魔法烈焰裏被燒成灰燼吧。

至於汝等，汝等居然讓一個冒險者衝到了吾的寢宮來嚇了吾一跳，汝等將接受懲罰。而吾不但受驚了還差點被迫動用了吾的特殊能力。雖然吾一如既往的強大不可戰勝，但汝等將要承擔放他到如此深入的責任，下一個讓吾看到的傢伙，將被吾做成棉花糖。屍鬼汝的毒液噴吐哪，鬼魂汝的疾病之觸哪，吾費盡心血組建的禁衛隊哪，簡直是一堆廢物。奇恥大辱啊，吾真想把汝等全都碾成碎片，雖然汝等中最渣的一部分已被那個冒險者摧毀，但餘下的傢伙，小心吾的震怒。]], "_t")
t("A smudged poem chalked on a dark piece of slate", "一首寫在石板上的被弄髒的詩歌", "_t")
t([[Master of life, Master of death,
All fall to a word
From his dreaded breath!

Master of staff, Master of steel,
None can withstand
His ruthless zeal!

Master of magic, Master of fire,
Pity the fool
That stirs his great ire!

Master of strength, Master of will,
Dare not oppose him
Or your blood will spill!

Master of shadows beyond mortal thought,
Against undying death all are as naught.]], [[他是生命之主，死亡之主，
一切生靈都將在他的恐怖呼吸中消亡！

他是衆僕之主，鋼鐵之主，
無人能理解他對暴虐的狂熱！

他是魔法之主，火焰之主，
憐憫那些挑動他心火的人！

他是力量之主，法力之主，
違抗他者必將血濺當場！

他是暗影之主遠非凡人可知，
挑戰永恆死亡之人必將灰飛煙滅。]], "_t")
t("A poem written in scribbled, child-like writing", "像小孩子寫的潦草詩歌", "_t")
t([[Me like Master,
He's a real laster,
He is faster
than a caster,
Can bring disaster,
Need more'n a plaster
After his attackaster...

Alabaster... raster... pastor? Grr, need more brains...]], [[我愛我主
他是真正的永生不滅
行動起來勢如閃電
快的法師都看不見
帶來破壞震撼九天
如你想要與之周旋
小命不保無人可怨……

旋……圈……卷？呀，需要更多腦漿……]], "_t")
t("A poem written in an elegant Gothic script", "高雅的哥特體詩歌", "_t")
t([[No staff will save thee
Against the blindness of pride
Death will catch thee up]], [[高傲的無知者
沒人能拯救你的性命
死亡終將追上你]], "_t")
t("a note about undead poetry from the Master", "主人關於不死詩歌的筆記", "_t")
t("As an aside, I notice one of my skeletons has amused himself by writing a poem about me. Whilst my first reaction was to have his bones crunched into dust and what remained of his undead soul sent to the darkest depths of the abyss, I do now realise that there is some merit to this. Every great leader needs tales penned of his brilliant conquest. Therefore I now command you all to write more poetry in my honour, praising my amazing powers, unrivalled leadership, unconquerable strength, etc etc. Any that fail to produce works of sufficient standard shall be annihilated.", "說些題外話，今天吾發現吾的一隻小骷髏正在自娛自樂的寫一首關於吾的詩。吾一怒之下就將它挫骨揚灰了，並用吾強大的力量將它的靈魂打入了永恆的地域。但很快吾發現此舉欠妥，每個偉大的領導者都需要傳奇的故事來記載他史詩般的征服歷程。故吾現在命令汝等速速以吾的名義作上衆多詩歌來讚美吾驚人的力量，偉大的領導力，無人可比的強大。所有不合格的作品和不符標準者都將面對吾的憤怒。", "_t")
t("slain master", "殺死主人", "_t")
t("A powerful staff is grabbed from the Master's dead hands.", "一把從主人手上奪來的強力法杖。", "_t")
t("a letter to Borfast from the Master", "主人寫給波法斯特的信", "_t")
t([[Ah, my dear Borfast, welcome to your glorious undeath! Your armour a cage, your hopes despair, your axe enslaved to my will, your soul mine to feast upon. How does it feel? Rather lovely I like to imagine! You were a valiant opponent, and though you were little threat to me I do like to honour you with this special treatment. And you do like honour, don't you? I know you wished to honour your people by defeating me and destroying my tower, but I'm sure you realise now that it was a rather vain endeavour.

I apologise for what happened to that lovely suit of plate. I know it got a little... worn... during the treatment. But I'm afraid I really did need to find out the locations of your companion, and certain pressures had to be applied. You weren't very talkative, now were you? But I soon made you sing, oh yes. Of course, I could have just used a little divination magic to find out what I wanted, but I do so enjoy a good torture... And my, how joyous your screams were whenever the acid splashed against your beard! Hoh, we did chortle, did we not? But no matter, I've had my best skeletal smiths work on fixing your armour, fit to be worn by my new champion.

I hope you enjoy your new work. Approach it with gusto, that sort of thing. I know in life you always dreamed of being a mighty hero of legend. But, well, what can be more glorious than this? You will live forever as my servant, destined to defend my throne for all time! You will be the envy of all the lesser ghouls that shamble about my halls. Well, until you get slain by some dumb intruding adventurer, of course... But that's the beauty of you heroes - one comes in, makes a mess, and then I get a new plaything to toy with. I wonder who shall replace you, eh?

Until then, do enjoy the work, try to keep the place clean, and remember - I own you forever.

- The Master]], [[啊，吾親愛的波法斯特，來迎接這不朽的新生吧！汝的護甲成了汝的籠子，汝的希望支離破碎，汝的斧頭只能順從吾的意志，汝的靈魂吾會盡情享用。這滋味怎樣？吾喜歡看到這樣可愛的畫面！汝是一個值得尊敬的對手，雖然汝會對吾構成一點點威脅，吾還是決定賜予汝這特殊的榮耀。並且吾知道汝喜歡榮耀，是不？吾知道汝希望通過打敗吾並摧毀吾的高塔來獲得榮耀，但是吾肯定汝現在知道了這是多麼自命不凡的行爲。

吾爲汝那可愛的護甲所經歷的事感到抱歉。吾知道……在賜予汝這特殊的待遇過程中它受到了一點……輕微的……損傷。但是吾恐怕很需要找到汝同伴的位置，必要的手段還是要採取的。汝好像不是很健談，是嗎？不過很快吾就會讓汝唱歌，是的。當然吾也可以用一點占卜魔法來找出什麼是吾輩想要的，但吾更享受折磨人的快感……還有天哪，當硫酸濺到汝身上時，汝的尖叫聲聽起來是多麼的歡快啊！哈，吾應該哈哈大笑，不是嗎？但是沒關係，吾已經吩咐了最好的骷髏工匠去修補汝的護甲，使它可以用於吾的新成員。

吾希望汝喜歡汝的新工作。汝會愛死這份工作。吾知道，在汝活着的時候汝總是夢想成爲一個強大的史詩英雄。但是，好吧，還有什麼比這更加榮耀的？汝將會作爲吾的奴僕永生，爲吾輩的王座戰鬥不止！汝將會成爲所有食屍鬼們都夢寐以求的近身侍衛。恩，直到汝被某個蠢蛋冒險家弄死，當然……但那就是汝輩所謂的英雄啊——一個進來，把這邊弄的一團糟，然後吾就有了一個新的玩具。汝猜誰會代替汝呢，恩？

直到那一刻前，請享受汝的工作，保持此處的清潔，並且記住——汝永遠是我的了。

——主人]], "_t")
t("a letter to Aletta from the Master", "主人寫給阿蕾塔的信", "_t")
t([[Ah, sweet Aletta! How rich your blood tasted on my lips! I know it's not quite what you were expecting from the next step in our relationship, but aren't surprises the true joy of any romance?

I don't blame you for falling for me, you know, even to the point of betraying all your companions just for me. Women have always had a weakness for my brooding personality and sparkling wit. Even in life I was quite the charmer, and death only improves things, I assure you. I really do have the reputation as a heartbreaker, in more ways than one... Your heart shall now sit in a special place, next to the rest of the offal in my pits.

Thank you for telling me of Borfast's weaknesses - it shall make overcoming the dwarven grunt all the simpler. Your rogue friend remains more elusive, but he will be found and destroyed. You see I have a sort of persistent bloody-mindedness about this sort of thing. There is not a cockroach in this tower that does not obey my every whim and will, and I shall see to it that it remains that way.

You must feel a little betrayed of course. I promised you power beyond your imaginings, and instead I drained your blood, fed your flesh to my servants, and enthralled your soul to my bidding. Well, we all struggle to manage expectations sometimes, eh? At least be glad I let your tortured essence roam the cold fastness of my fortress, haunting anyone foolish enough to invade. And some power I will impart to you, and it is indeed beyond your imaginings, for your mind could never reach the dark places I can. But open your eyes now, for such dark places shall be with you till the end of time... Welcome, indeed, to the dark place of my heart.

- The Master]], [[哦，阿蕾塔甜心，吾的寶貝！汝的血液嚐起來是多麼的醇厚啊！吾知道這不是汝所期盼的進一步關係，但是汝難道沒有感受到一點點浪漫的真諦嗎？

吾不怪你愛上了我，知道嗎，即使你爲吾背叛了所有同伴。女人們總是傾慕吾的氣質和才華。即使在生前吾也是英俊瀟灑，死亡只會讓吾更加玉樹臨風，我保證。作爲一個愛情殺手，吾確實有必要承擔責任，辦法有很多……汝的心臟現在位於一個特殊的地方，和其他內臟一起放在吾的後廳裏。

謝謝你告訴吾波法斯特的弱點——這使得我更加容易對付那些矮人。汝的盜賊朋友還在潛逃，但他很快就會被抓住並撕裂。你看我總是對這類事情有種嗜血的衝動。即便是這座高塔裏的一隻蟑螂，都會完全遵循吾的意志，吾會看到它的一舉一動。

汝肯定會有一點被背叛的感覺。吾答應給汝的力量遠超汝的想象，相反吾抽乾了你的血液，將你的肉體賜予了吾的侍從，並且奴役你的靈魂。好吧，有時吾輩都曾向着期盼的那樣努力過，恩？至少汝應該感到高興的是，吾將你扭曲的靈魂放逐在要塞裏漫步，去獵食任何敢於侵入要塞的敵人。並且，吾將會賜予汝一些力量，同樣這也會遠超汝的想象，因爲汝永遠達不到吾所處的黑暗巔峯。但是，睜開汝的雙眼，汝會發現汝已經永墜黑暗……歡迎你，你來到了吾內心真正黑暗的世界。

——主人]], "_t")
t("dreadfell", "恐懼王座", "newLore category")
t("a letter to Filio from the Master", "主人寫給菲里奧的信", "_t")
t([[Oh Filio, what a fun game we have had of cat and mouse! Well, perhaps to you it was a life and death struggle, but for me this past three weeks of patiently hunting you through my halls has been the most entertaining of past-times. I have enjoyed extending the game so, letting you escape my clutches when I felt it most prudent, watching as you got ever more desperate. Alas, you have now degraded too much, and it was simply too embarrassing watching you eat your own faeces to survive. I had to put an end to it - I'm sure you understand.

But ah, it's not truly an end, for you get to experience the wonder of undead enslavement! Is it not most exciting? Do your bones not quiver with delight? It is just your bones now, since I have a certain fondness for skeletal servants, but I have been nice enough to pad your heels with leather so you can still sneak about quietly. How you did love to sneak! Now you may spend an eternity doing so, ensuring any future trespassers get quite the surprise wandering through my great keep.

I have let you keep your little sling, since I know you like to play with it. Such a quaint weapon... But this staff I found in your possession - my, what a treasure you have brought me! I do not know whence you stole this artifact, but you clearly were completely unaware of its value or power. It has a history beyond your very comprehension, and in my hands it shall change the future! Thank you kindly, my servant; already you have served your Master well. I'm sure we shall enjoy a great friendship over the many years to come. Well, not friendship exactly - it more involves eternal agony on your part, and a rise to ultimate power and majesty for me. Such is the fate of the weak and the strong, a lesson you have already learned well. What a great teacher I make...

- The Master]], [[哦，菲里奧，貓鼠遊戲多麼的有趣啊！好吧，也許對於汝來說這是生死掙扎，但是對於吾，卻是這三個星期以來打發無聊時光最有趣的遊戲。吾一直都在延長比賽時間，看着你苟延殘喘，看着你陷入絕望。不過，汝現在也太自甘墮落了，僅僅是看到汝靠吃自己的糞便生存都讓吾感到尷尬。吾決定華麗的終結這場遊戲——你懂的。

但是呢，這不是真正的結束，因爲汝可以充分體驗作爲不死奴隸的樂趣！難道這不是最令人興奮的嗎？汝的骨頭有沒有興奮的發顫呢？現在它們仍是汝的骨頭，雖然吾一直愛好骷髏侍從，但是吾也會很大方的將你的皮毛附上去，這樣汝還可以無聲無息的潛行。汝是多麼的喜歡潛行啊！現在汝可以花一輩子來做這件事，給每位闖入我宮殿的侵入者一個驚喜，一個可以使他們永遠沉默的驚喜。

吾還可以讓你保留你的投石索，因爲吾知道你喜歡用它。如此精巧的武器……但是吾在你包裏找到的這根法杖——天哪，你給我帶來了多麼好的財寶！吾真不知道你偷了這件神器，但吾也很清楚汝肯定不知道它的價值。它的存在遠在汝出生以前，在吾輩手裏它可以改變未來！謝謝你的慷慨，吾的侍衛，顯然你已經把主子我伺候的很好了。吾肯定我們將會在未來的許多年內保持良好的友誼。好吧，也不能算是友誼——對於汝是更多的痛苦和折磨，對於吾則是力量和威嚴的增長。這就是弱肉強食的命運，汝已經很好的學習了這一課。吾真是個偉大的老師……

——主人]], "_t")
