section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/fearscape.lua"

t("a fearsome sight", "一副恐怖的景象", "_t")
t([[You stand in a field of fire, the flames dancing back and forth like blaze-spawned corn waving in the wind. It licks your feet, your skin, your face, and writhes around in tiny shapes which tear across your flesh and crawl down your throat. It burns and blazes through your body, and crazed thoughts fill your mind. This is Goedalath they tell you, the Fearscape, and you have no rightful place here.

In the distance you see looming, demonic shapes of absolute darkness, towering above the blazing land like wardens of doom. The sky is black, but above your head hangs a round world that you recognise as Eyal. Across the burning plains gather armies of fiendish figures, and glowing eyes turn up with hateful glowers to your home world. Suddenly both you and it and seem small and frail. As the flames fill your body with pain your only thought is of escape.]], [[你所站立之處烈火燎原，火焰如地獄之風般來回舞動。你站在一片火海之中。火焰在前後舞動，像地獄之種隨風搖擺。火焰炙烤着你的腳、你的皮膚、你的臉，在血肉中蔓延，爬進你的喉嚨。它燃燒着你的身體。狂熱的思想強行侵入你的意志，告訴你這裏是高達勒斯——惡魔空間。這裏不歡迎你的到來。
在遠方，你看到陰森的，惡魔形狀的黑暗物質籠罩在這燃燒的大地上，如同毀滅守衛一般。漆黑的天空中懸掛着一個圓形的，是被你稱之爲埃亞爾的世界……在這燃燒着的平原上聚集了大批的惡魔戰士，他們的瞳孔中充滿了對你故鄉的憎恨。突然間，你和它都顯得如此渺小而脆弱。當火焰將痛苦注滿你的身體時，你唯一的想法就是——逃走。]], "_t")
t("fearscape", "惡魔空間", "newLore category")
t("sacrificial altar", "獻祭祭壇", "_t")
t([[You see a female human lying unconscious on a black altar, twisted sigils scored into her naked flesh.
Around her are several figures in dark robes.

As they notice you one calls out 'Intruder! Protect the seed of Kryl-Feijan!']], [[你發現一名人類女子躺在一座黑色的祭壇上昏迷不醒，扭曲的魔法銘文深深的烙入了她赤裸的身體。
在她周圍你發現了數名黑袍人。

當他們發現你時，其中一人大聲呼喊“入侵者！我們必須保護卡洛·斐濟之種！”]], "_t")


