section "game/modules/tome/data/lore/shertul.lua"

t("first mural painting", "第一幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[You see here a mural showing a dark and tortured world. Large, god-like figures with powerful auras fight each other, and the earth is torn beneath their feet.
There is some text underneath ]], [[你能在這壁畫上看到一個黑暗和痛苦的世界。有着強大領域的上古巨神們在互相廝殺，大地在他們腳下龜裂。
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'In the beginning the world was dark, and the petty gods fought over their broken lands.'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#'剛開始世界充滿了黑暗，衆神爲了各自的領土而競爭。'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Sho ch'zun Eyal mor donuth, ik ranaheli donoth trun ze.'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Sho ch'zun Eyal mor donuth, ik ranaheli donoth trun ze.'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("second mural painting", "第二幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[In this picture a huge god with glowing eyes towers above the land, and in his right hand he holds high the sun. The other gods are running from him, wincing from the light.
There is some text underneath ]], [[在這幅畫上有一位鐵塔一樣的巨神，他目光如炬，右手高舉着太陽。衆神逃離他，害怕他手中的光芒。
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'But AMAKTHEL came, and his might surpassed all else, and the petty gods fled before his glory. And he made the Sun from his breath and held it above the world and said, \"All that this light touches shall be mine, and this light shall touch all the world.'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#但阿馬克泰爾來了,他的勇武震懾了衆人,僞神們懾服於他的榮耀。他深呼吸後把太陽高舉到了世界之上，說：“陽光所至，即我所至，這光芒將照亮全世界。”#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Fa AMAKTHEL tabak, ik koru bazan tro yu, ik ranaheli tobol don schek ruun. Ik blana dem Soli as banafel ik goriz uf Eyal ik blod, \"Tro fasa goru domus asam, ik goru domit tro Eyal.\"'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Fa AMAKTHEL tabak, ik koru bazan tro yu, ik ranaheli tobol don schek ruun. Ik blana dem Soli as banafel ik goriz uf Eyal ik blod, \"Tro fasa goru domus asam, ik goru domit tro Eyal.\"'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("third mural painting", "第三幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[This picture shows the huge god holding some smaller figures in his hands and pointing out at the lands beyond. You imagine these figures must be the Sher'Tul.
There is some text beneath ]], [[這幅畫顯示了真神將一個小巧的遺蹟託在手心，並指向遠方的大陸。你猜這遺蹟也許就是夏·圖爾。
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'And AMAKTHEL made the SHER'TUL, and gave unto us the powers to achieve all that we set our will to, and said to us \"Go forth to where the light touches and take all for your own.\"'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#並且阿馬克泰爾製造了夏·圖爾，給予我們完成自我意志的力量，他對我們說：“走向世界，爲自己取得一切。”#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Ik AMAKTHEL cosio SHER'TUL, ik baladath peris furko masa bren doth benna zi, ik blod is \"Fen makel ath goru domus ik denz tro ala fron.\"'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Ik AMAKTHEL cosio SHER'TUL, ik baladath peris furko masa bren doth benna zi, ik blod is \"Fen makel ath goru domus ik denz tro ala fron.\"'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("fourth mural painting", "第四幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[You see a mural showing a huge metropolis made of crystal, with small islands of stone floating in the air behind it. In the foreground is sitting a Sher'Tul, with a hand stretched up to the sky.
There is some text beneath ]], [[你在壁畫上看到一個巨大的水晶之城，有數個浮空島懸浮在周圍。在畫面的最前端坐着的是夏·圖爾人，他向天空筆直的舉起手臂。
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'We conquered the world, and built for ourselves towering cities of crystal and fortresses that travelled the skies. But some were not content...'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#我們征服了世界，爲自己建造高樓大廈，水晶般夢幻的都市和懸浮天空的堡壘，但有些人還不滿足……#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Batialatoth ro Eyal, ik rinsi akan fronseth sumit kurameth ik linnet pora gasios aeren. Ach nen beswar goreg.'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Batialatoth ro Eyal, ik rinsi akan fronseth sumit kurameth ik linnet pora gasios aeren. Ach nen beswar goreg.'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("fifth mural painting", "第五幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[This mural shows nine Sher'Tul standing side by side, each holding aloft a dark weapon. Your eyes are drawn to a runed staff held by the red-robed figure in the centre. It seems familiar somehow...
There is some text beneath ]], [[這幅壁畫顯示了九個夏·圖爾人肩並肩站着，每人手裏都高舉着一件一模一樣的黑色武器。你的注意力集中在畫面中間——被紅袍者舉起的符文法杖上。它看起來很眼熟……
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'Of pride we accepted no equals, and of greed we accepted no servitude. We made for ourselves terrible weapons - the Godslayers - and nine were chosen to wield them.'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#我們無視那高傲的公平，我們拒絕那貪婪的奴役。我們給自己打造了強大的武器——弒神之刃，並選出了九名精英來使用它們。#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Zubadon koref noch hesen, ik dorudon koref noch pasor. Cosief maro dondreth karatu - Ranaduzil - ik jein belsan ovrienis.'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Zubadon koref noch hesen, ik dorudon koref noch pasor. Cosief maro dondreth karatu - Ranaduzil - ik jein belsan ovrienis.'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("sixth mural painting", "第六幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[You see images of epic battles, with Sher'Tul warriors fighting and slaying god-like figures over ten times their size.
There is some text underneath ]], [[你在這幅畫上看到一場史詩戰爭——夏·圖爾的戰士們在和10倍大於他們的神祗戰鬥。
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'The petty gods were hunted down and slain, and their spirits rent to nothing. The land became our own. But one god remained...'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#那些神祗被一個個擊敗，他們的靈魂化爲虛無。大陸終於爲我們所擁有。但是還有一位神祗存在……#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Ranaheli meth dondruil ik duzin, ik leisif konru as neremin. Eyal matath bre sun. Ach unu rana soriton...'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Ranaheli meth dondruil ik duzin, ik leisif konru as neremin. Eyal matath bre sun. Ach unu rana soriton...'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("seventh mural painting", "第七幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[You see the red-robed Sher'Tul striking the huge god with the dark, runed staff. Bodies litter the floor around them, and the golden throne behind is bathed in blood. The light in the god's eyes seems faded.
There is some text underneath ]], [[你看到紅袍夏·圖爾人用那根又黑又亮的法杖攻擊巨大的神祗。碎肉撒了一地，鮮血染遍了整個黃金王座。神祗眼中的神采似乎消散了……
下面有一行文字]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'The almighty AMAKTHEL was assaulted on his golden throne, and though many died before his feet, he was finally felled.'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#真神阿馬克泰爾最終倒在了他的黃金王座下，雖然數以千計的人死在他的腳下，他最終還是隕落了。#{normal}#", "_t")
t("which you do not understand: #{italic}#'Trobazan AMAKTHEL konruata as va aurin leas, ik mab peli zort akan hun, penetar dondeberoth.'#{normal}#", "不明意義的文字：#{italic}#'Trobazan AMAKTHEL konruata as va aurin leas, ik mab peli zort akan hun, penetar dondeberoth.'#{normal}#", "_t")
t("eighth mural painting", "第八幅壁畫", "_t")
t([[The large mural shows the great god spread on the ground, with the dark staff held against his chest. Sher'Tul surround him, some hacking off his limbs, cutting out his tongue, and binding him with chains. A burst of light flares up from where a tall Sher'Tul warrior is gouging his eye with a black-bladed halberd. In the background a Sher'Tul mage beckons to a huge chasm in the ground.
The text beneath says simply ]], [[這幅巨大的壁畫上，真神被攤開在地上，那根黑色的法杖穿透了他的胸口。夏·圖爾人圍繞着他，有的在切他的肢體，有的在割他的舌頭，還有的在用鎖鏈捆綁他。一位高個子夏·圖爾人對他的眼睛射出了一束激光，他在用鋒利的長戟切割真神的眼睛。遠處，一個夏·圖爾法師在地上召喚了一道溝壑。
下面有隻有一句]], "_t")
t("#{italic}#'The Great Sin.'#{normal}#", "#{italic}#罪惡之源。#{normal}#", "_t")
t("ninth mural painting", "第九幅壁畫", "_t")
t("This final mural has been ruined, with deep scores and scratches etched across its surface. All you can see of the original appears to be flames.", "最後的這塊壁畫似乎損壞的很嚴重，上面有深深的劃痕和腐蝕的痕跡。你所能看到的似乎是火焰的畫面。", "_t")
t("Yiilkgur raising toward the sky", "伊克格，飛向天空", "_t")
t("Yiilkgur, the Sher'Tul Fortress is re-activated and raises from the depths of Nur toward the sky.", "伊克格重新激活了夏·圖爾要塞，它從湖底伸向天空。", "_t")
t("a living Sher'Tul?!", "活着的夏·圖爾人?!", "_t")
t("You somehow got teleported to an other Sher'Tul Fortress, in a very alien location. There you saw a living Sher'Tul.", "不管怎樣，你傳送到了另一個異次元的夏·圖爾要塞。在那裏，你看到了一位活着的夏·圖爾人。", "_t")
t("sher'tul", "夏·圖爾", "newLore category")
t("lost farportal", "失落的傳送門", "_t")
t("%s boldly entering a Sher'Tul farportal.", "%s勇敢地進入了一個夏·圖爾傳送門。", "tformat")


