section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/anti-antimagic.lua"

t("The fall of Zigur", "伊格的陷落", "_t")
t("You decided to side with the Grand Corruptor and joined forces to assault the Ziguranth main base of power.", " 你決定與大腐化者並肩戰鬥，加入對伊格蘭斯的大本營的攻擊。", "_t")
t("The Grand Corruptor died during the attack before he had time to teach you his ways.", " 大腐化者還沒來得及教會你他的技巧，就在戰鬥中戰死了", "_t")
t("The defenders of Zigur were crushed, the Ziguranth scattered and weakened.", " 伊格城的防禦被擊潰了，伊格蘭斯的勢力瓦解衰落了。", "_t")
t("In the aftermath you turned against the Grand Corruptor and dispatched him.", " 最後，你背叛了大腐化者並殺死了他。", "_t")
t("Select the party member to receive the hexes generic talent tree:", "選擇接受邪術技能樹的隊伍成員：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#The Grand Corruptor gazes upon you. You feel knowledge flowing in your mind. You can now train some corruption powers.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#大腐化者凝視着你。你感覺到知識在你的腦海裏流動。你可以學習一些墮落能力了。", "_t")
t("Grand Corruptor", "大腐化者", "_t")
t("Victory is mine!", "勝利是屬於我的！", "_t")
t("While you were in the Far East, the Grand Corruptor was busy in Maj'Eyal.", "當你在遠東戰鬥的視乎，大腐化者正在馬基·埃亞爾忙碌着。", "_t")
t("With the fall of Zigur he was able to attack and take control of Elvala, the Shaloren capital city.", "在伊格隕落之後，他成功地進攻並佔領了埃爾瓦拉，永恆精靈的首都。", "_t")
