t("#RED#You aided various denizens of Maj'Eyal in their attempts to join the Brotherhood of Alchemists, though you did not prove the deciding factor for any. This year's new member is %s.#WHITE#", "#RED#你幫助了馬基·埃亞爾的許多人加入鍊金術師兄弟會，但是你沒有成爲任何一個決定性因素。今年的新成員是%s。#WHITE#", "tformat")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#Various alchemists around Maj'Eyal are competing to gain entry into the great Brotherhood of Alchemists, and one or more have enlisted your aid.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_BLUE#很多馬基埃亞爾的煉金術士想競爭加入強大的煉金術士兄弟會，其中有一個或者幾個人請求你的幫助。#WHITE#", "_t")
