section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/charred-scar.lua"

t("The Doom of the World!", "世界末日！", "_t")
t("You were sent to the Charred Scar at the heart of which lies a huge volcano. In the Age of Pyre it destroyed the old Sher'Tul ruins that stood there, absorbing much of their latent magic.", " 你被送到了灼燒之痕，其中部是一個巨大的火山，在派爾紀元這裏曾是夏·圖爾遺址的所在，吸收了大量潛藏的魔法。", "_t")
t("This place is still full of that power and the orcs intend to absorb this power using the Staff of Absorption!", " 這裏仍然充滿了那種能量，獸人打算用吸能法杖的力量來吸收這裏的能量。", "_t")
t("Whatever their plan may be, they must be stopped at all cost.", " 不管他們的目的是要幹什麼，必須不惜一切代價阻止他們。", "_t")
t("The volcano is attacked by orcs. A few Sun Paladins made it there with you. They will hold the line at the cost of their lives to buy you some time.", " 火山受到了獸人的攻擊，一些太陽騎士正頂在最前線用他們的生命來幫助你爭取一些時間。", "_t")
t("Honor their sacrifice; do not let the orcs finish their work!", " 向他們的獻身精神致敬！不要讓獸人們達成所願。", "_t")
t("You arrived too late. The place has been drained of its power and the sorcerers have left.", " 你來的太晚了，這裏的能量已經被吸乾，而那些法師已經離開了。", "_t")
t("You arrived in time and interrupted the ritual. The sorcerers have departed.", " 你終於及時趕來阻止了儀式，法師們被驅散了。", "_t")
t("Use the portal to go back to the Far East. You *MUST* stop them, no matter the cost.", " 使用傳送門到達遠東大陸，你必須阻止他們，不惜一切代價！ ", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#A portal activates in the distance. You hear the orcs shout, 'The Sorcerers have departed! Follow them!'", "#VIOLET#遠處一個傳送門被激活，你聽到獸人們吼道：“惡魔法師已經離開！跟上他們！”", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#The Sorcerers flee through a portal. As you prepare to follow them, a huge faeros appears to block the way.", "#VIOLET#惡魔法師從傳送門逃跑了，當你準備跟隨他們時，一個巨大的法羅擋住了去路。", "logPlayer")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/deep-bellow.lua"

t("From bellow, it devours", "地下吞噬者", "_t")
t("Your escape from Reknor got your heart pounding and your desire for wealth and power increased tenfold.", " 你從瑞庫納逃了出來，你覺得你的心臟狂跳不止，你對財富和力量的渴望增加了十倍～ ", "_t")
t("Maybe it is time for you to start an adventurer's career. Deep below the Iron Throne mountains lies the Deep Bellow.", " 也許是你開始冒險生涯的時候了，在鋼鐵王座山脈的深處有個無盡深淵地下城。", "_t")
t("It has been long sealed away but still, from time to time adventurers go there looking for wealth.", " 那裏已被塵封已久，但是還是不斷有冒險者前去尋找財寶。", "_t")
t("None that you know of has come back yet, but you did survive Reknor. You are great.", " 據你所知沒有一個人能活着回來，不過你從瑞庫納倖存了下來，你比較牛 X。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/dreadfell.lua"

t("The Island of Dread", "恐怖之島", "_t")
t("You have heard that near the Charred Scar, to the south, lies a ruined tower known as the Dreadfell.", " 你聽說在灼燒之痕南部有一個叫做恐懼王座的荒塔廢墟。", "_t")
t("There are disturbing rumors of greater undead, and nobody who reached it ever returned.", " 傳說那裏有強大的亡靈生物，凡是到達那裏的人都有去無回。", "_t")
t("Perhaps you should explore it and find the truth, and the treasures, for yourself!", " 也許你應該去那裏一探究竟，順便可以找到埋藏在那裏的財寶。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/east-portal.lua"

t("You have created a portal back to Maj'Eyal. You should try to talk to someone in Last Hope about establishing a link back.", " 你創造了一個回到馬基埃亞爾的傳送門，你應該試試找最後的希望的某個人談談關於這件事。", "_t")
t("You talked to the Elder in Last Hope who in turn told you to talk to Tannen, who lives in the north of the city.", " 你和最後的希望的長者交談，得知要去找城市北邊的泰恩 ", "_t")
t("You gave the Orb of Many Ways to Tannen to study while you look for the athame and diamond in Reknor.", " 你把多元水晶球交給了泰恩進一步研究，然後去瑞庫納繼續尋找血符祭劍和共鳴寶石。", "_t")
t("You kept the Orb of Many Ways despite Tannen's request to study it. You must now look for the athame and diamond in Reknor.", " 雖然泰恩要求拿來研究但是你還是把多元水晶球保留了下來，下一步你必須去瑞庫納尋找血符祭劍和共鳴寶石了。", "_t")
t("You brought back the diamond and athame to Tannen who asked you to check the tower of Telmur, looking for a text of portals, although he is not sure it is even there. He told you to come back in a few days.", " 你把血符祭劍和共鳴寶石帶回給泰恩，他告訴你去泰爾瑪之塔看看，尋找那裏的傳送密文，他告訴幾天之後再回去找他。", "_t")
t("You brought back the diamond and athame to Tannen who asked you to contact Zemekkys to ask some delicate questions.", " 你把血符祭劍和共鳴寶石帶回給 Tannen，他告訴你去找伊莫克斯問一些細節問題。", "_t")
t("You brought back the diamond and athame to Tannen who asked you to come back in a few days.", " 你把血符祭劍和共鳴寶石帶回給泰恩，他告訴你過幾天再去找他。", "_t")
t("Tannen has tricked you! He swapped the orb for a false one that brought you to a demonic plane. Find the exit, and get revenge!", " 泰恩把你耍了！他換了個錯的水晶球給你，把你傳送到了惡魔的空間，找到出口回去找他算賬！ ", "_t")
t("Tannen revealed himself as the vile scum he really is and trapped you in his tower.", " 泰恩暴露出了他的確是個卑鄙的人渣，他把你囚禁在他的塔牢裏。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* The portal to the Far East is now functional and can be used to go back.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 通向遠東的傳送門開始運作了，你可以用它來回去。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Tannen points to the location of Telmur on your map.", "泰恩在你的地圖上指出了泰爾瑪的位置。", "logPlayer")
t("A portal appears in the center of the tower!", "在塔的中間出現了一個傳送門!", "_t")
t("Back and there again", "穿越過去", "_t")
t("Meranas, Herald of Angolwen", "安格列文傳令官 梅拉納斯", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#You enter the swirling portal and in the blink of an eye you are back in Last Hope.", "#VIOLET#你進入了傳送漩渦，一眨眼的功夫你已經回到了最後的希望。", "logPlayer")


