section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/grave-necromancer.lua"

t("And now for a grave", "絕望的墳墓", "_t")
t("Ungrol of Last Hope asked you to look for his wife's friend Celia, who has been reported missing. She frequently visits her late husband's mausoleum, in the graveyard near Last Hope.", " 最後的希望的溫格洛要幫忙找她妻子失蹤的朋友希利婭，她經常去他亡夫的陵墓那裏，在最後的希望附近的墓地裏。", "_t")
t("You searched for Celia in the graveyard near Last Hope, and found a note. In it, Celia reveals that she has been conducting experiments in the dark arts, in an attempt to extend her life... also, she is pregnant.", " 你在最後的希望附近的目的搜尋希利婭的蹤跡，找到一個紙條。從紙條中寫的內容你得知，希利婭正在進行一些黑暗魔法儀式，試圖延長她的壽命，另外……她還有孕在身！ ", "_t")
t("You have tracked Celia to her husband's mausoleum in the graveyard near Last Hope. It seems she has taken some liberties with the corpses there.", " 你跟蹤希利婭到了她亡夫在最後的希望附近墓地的陵墓裏，似乎她在那裏復活了一些屍體。", "_t")
t("You have laid Celia to rest, putting an end to her gruesome experiments.", " 你埋葬了希利婭，終結了她陰森恐怖的實驗。", "_t")
t("You have laid Celia to rest, putting an end to her failed experiments. You have taken her heart, for your own experiments. You do not plan to fail as she did.", " 你埋葬了希利婭，終結了她失敗的實驗，你拿走了她的心臟爲自己的實驗做準備，你相信你不會重蹈她的覆轍。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/high-peak.lua"

t("Falling Toward Apotheosis", "拜倒在神的腳下", "_t")
t("You have vanquished the masters of the Orc Pride. Now you must venture inside the most dangerous place of this world: the High Peak.", " 你征服了獸人軍團的最高領袖，現在你必須向這個世界最危險的地方挺進：巔峯。", "_t")
t("Seek the Sorcerers and stop them before they bend the world to their will.", " 找到那些妄圖扭曲這個世界的法師並阻止他們。", "_t")
t("To enter, you will need the four orbs of command to remove the shield over the peak.", " 想要進去的話，你必須找到那四個指令水晶來移除塔頂的防護罩。", "_t")
t("The entrance to the peak passes through a place called 'the slime tunnels', probably located inside or near Grushnak Pride.", " 通往塔頂的路需要穿過一個地方，叫做“史萊姆通道”，就在格魯希納克部落裏面或者附近。", "_t")
t("You have reached the summit of the High Peak, entered the sanctum of the Sorcerers and destroyed them, freeing the world from the threat of evil.", " 你到達了巔峯的最高處，進入法師們的聖所並摧毀他們，把這個世界從惡魔的威脅之中解放出來吧。", "_t")
t("You have won the game!", " 你通關了！ ", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You encountered Sun Paladin Aeryn who blamed you for the loss of the Sunwall. You were forced to kill her.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你遭遇了太陽騎士艾琳，她把太陽堡壘陷落的責任歸咎在你的頭上，你不得不殺了它她。#LAST#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You encountered Sun Paladin Aeryn who blamed you for the loss of the Sunwall, but you spared her.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你遭遇了太陽騎士艾琳，她把太陽堡壘陷落的責任歸咎在你的頭上，但是你饒恕了她。#LAST#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You defeated the Sorcerers before the Void portal could open.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你在虛空傳送門打開之前擊敗了那些法師。#LAST#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You defeated the Sorcerers and Aeryn sacrificed herself to close the Void portal.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你擊敗了那些法師，艾琳犧牲了她自己關閉了虛空傳送門。#LAST#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You defeated the Sorcerers and sacrificed yourself to close the Void portal.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你擊敗了那些法師，並犧牲了自己關閉虛空傳送門。#LAST#", "_t")
t("Endgame", "遊戲結束", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_RED#As you enter the level you hear a familiar voice.", "#LIGHT_RED#當你進入地圖你聽到了一個熟悉的聲音。", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_RED#Fallen Sun Paladin Aeryn: '%s YOU BROUGHT ONLY DESTRUCTION TO THE SUNWALL! YOU WILL PAY!'", "#LIGHT_RED#墮落太陽騎士艾琳：“%s 你只給太陽堡壘帶來了毀滅！你會爲此付出代價！”", "logPlayer")
t("Ruins of the Gates of Morning", "晨曦之門的廢墟", "_t")
t("The Sunwall was destroyed while you were trapped in the High Peak.", "當你在巔峯被困的時候，太陽堡壘被摧毀了。", "_t")
t("Winner", "遊戲勝利", "_t")
t("#GOLD#Well done! You have won the Tales of Maj'Eyal: The Age of Ascendancy#WHITE#", "#GOLD#乾的好！你贏得了馬基埃亞爾的傳說：卓越紀#WHITE#", "_t")
t("The Sorcerers are dead, and the Orc Pride lies in ruins, thanks to your efforts.", " 那些法師死了，獸人部落被埋葬在廢墟之中，感謝你爲此付出的努力。", "_t")
t("Your sacrifice worked. Your mental energies were imbued with farportal energies. The Way radiated from the High Peak toward the rest of Eyal like a mental tidal wave.", " 你的犧牲起作用了，你的精神能量被原自傳送門的能量所感染，從巔峯通往埃亞爾的輻射狀維網形成了一股精神衝擊波。", "_t")
t("Every sentient being in Eyal is now part of the Way. Peace and happiness are enforced for all.", " 所有埃亞爾有感覺的生物都成爲了維網的一部分，和平和幸福被傳輸給大家。", "_t")
t("Only the mages of Angolwen were able to withstand the mental shock and thus are the only unsafe people left. But what can they do against the might of the Way?", " 只有安格利文的法師能夠抵制住這道精神衝擊，從而他們成爲了僅存的危險人類，不過他們又能對強大的維網怎麼樣呢？ ", "_t")
t("In the aftermath of the battle the Way tried to force you to act as a vessel to bring the Way to every sentient being.", " 在戰鬥結束後，維網試圖強迫你用你的身軀作爲通道將維網傳輸到所有知覺生物的身體中。", "_t")
t("Through an incredible display of willpower you resisted long enough to ask Aeryn to kill you.", " 然而，你強大的意志力讓你支撐下來，向艾琳發送了信息。", "_t")
t("She sadly agreed and ran her sword through you, enabling you to do the last sacrifice you could for the world.", " 她懷着悲痛的心情用長劍刺穿了你的身軀，你終於爲這個世界做出了最後的貢獻。", "_t")
t("You have prevented the portal to the Void from opening and thus stopped the Creator from bringing about the end of the world.", " 你阻止了虛空傳送門的開啓，並終止了世界末日的到來。", "_t")
t("In a selfless act, High Sun Paladin Aeryn sacrificed herself to close the portal to the Void and thus stopped the Creator from bringing about the end of the world.", " 高階太陽騎士艾琳非常無私的犧牲了她自己，阻止了虛空傳送門的開啓，解救了這個世界。", "_t")
t("In a selfless act, you sacrificed yourself to close the portal to the Void and thus stopped the Creator from bringing about the end of the world.", " 你非常無私的犧牲了你自己，阻止了虛空傳送門的開啓，解救了這個世界。", "_t")
t("The Gates of Morning have been destroyed and the Sunwall has fallen. The last remnants of the free people in the Far East will surely diminish, and soon only orcs will inhabit this land.", " 晨曦之門被摧毀了，太陽堡壘陷落了。遠東大陸倖存的人口比以前明顯減少，很快獸人會佔據整個大陸。", "_t")
t("The orc presence in the Far East has greatly been diminished by the loss of their leaders and the destruction of the Sorcerers. The free people of the Sunwall will be able to prosper and thrive on this land.", " 失去了惡魔法師和獸人首領的獸人部落人口急劇減少，太陽堡壘的人們得以這片大陸上繼續發展、繁榮。", "_t")
t("Maj'Eyal will once more know peace. Most of its inhabitants will never know they even were on the verge of destruction, but then this is what being a true hero means: to do the right thing even though nobody will know about it.", " 馬基埃亞爾再一次回覆了和平和寧靜，大多數居民也許並不知道他們到了差點毀滅的邊緣，不過這正是稱之爲一個真正的英雄：就算不會被人所知也要去維護正義。", "_t")
t("You may continue playing and enjoy the rest of the world.", " 你可以繼續在這個世界上探險。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/infinite-dungeon.lua"

t("The Infinite Dungeon", "無盡地下城", "_t")
t("You have entered the Infinite Dungeon. There is no going back now.", " 你進入了無限地下城。你已不能再走回頭路了。", "_t")
t("Go deep, fight, win or die in a blaze of glory!", " 深入地下城去戰鬥吧，勝利或者爲榮耀而死！ ", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/keepsake.lua"

t("Keepsake", "往昔信物", "_t")
t("You have begun to look for a way to overcome the curse that afflicts you.", " 你開始尋求方法以驅除一直困擾着你的詛咒。", "_t")
t("Your curse has changed the iron acorn which now serves as a cruel reminder of your past and present.", " 你的詛咒使鐵橡果成爲了使你回憶起殘酷過去和現實的信物。", "_t")
t("You have found a small iron acorn which you keep as a reminder of your past", " 你找到了一個小小的鐵質橡果，似乎可以讓你回想起以前的往事。", "_t")
t("Berethh is dead, may he rest in peace.", " 貝里斯已死，但願他能安息。", "_t")
t("Your curse has defiled the iron acorn which now serves as a reminder of your vile nature.", " 你的詛咒污濁了鐵橡果，它成爲了使你回想起你卑劣本性的信物。", "_t")
t("Kyless, the one who brought the curse, is dead by your hand.", " 克里斯，那個曾經爲你帶來詛咒的人，死在了你的手上。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#You need to find Berethh, the last person who may be able to help you.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#你得找到貝里斯，也許他是最後一個可以幫助你的人。", "_t")
t("You have destroyed the merchant caravan that you once considered family.", " 你摧毀了那個你曾經視作家人的商隊。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#Seek out Kyless' cave in the northern part of the meadow and end him. Perhaps the curse will end with him.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#找出位於草原北部的克里斯的洞穴，然後殺掉他，他的死也許會解除這個詛咒。", "_t")
t("You have found a small iron acorn which you keep as a reminder of your past.", "你找到了一個小小的鐵質橡果，似乎可以讓你回想起以前的往事。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#Discover the meaning of the acorn and the dream.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#搞清楚鐵橡果與這個夢境的含義。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#You may have to revist your past to unlock some secret buried there.", "#LIGHT_GREEN#你可以回憶一下過去來解開埋藏在這裏的祕密。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#The time has come to learn the true nature of your curse.", "#VIOLET#是時候搞清楚你詛咒的本質了。", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#You find yourself in a dream.", "#VIOLET#你發現你在一個夢境裏。", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#Your hate surges. You refuse to succumb to death!", "#VIOLET#你仇恨涌動，你不屈服於死亡！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#You have discovered a small iron acorn, a link to your past.", "#VIOLET#你發現了一個小鐵橡果，它和你的過去有關。", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#The merchant caravan from the past has appeared in your dream.", "#VIOLET#很久以前商隊的往事出現在你的夢裏。", "logPlayer")
t("Last of the Caravan", "商隊的最後一人", "_t")
t("secret path to the cave", "通向山洞的祕密通道", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#You have begun your hunt for Kyless!", "#VIOLET#你開始追殺克里斯！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#You have a marker to the entrance of Kyless' cave!", "#VIOLET#你在通往克里斯洞穴的入口上有一個記號！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#You have found the entrance to Kyless' cave!", "#VIOLET#你找到了通往克里斯洞穴的入口！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#You have found the entrance to a vault!", "#VIOLET#你找到了通往一個地下室的入口！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#The shadows have noticed you!", "#VIOLET#陰影注意到了你！", "logPlayer")
t("A Second Vault", "另一處寶庫", "_t")
t("You recoginize this door as the entrance to a second vault. There are some scuffling noises and heavy breathing coming from the other side of the door.", "你認出來這扇門是通向另一處寶庫的門戶。你可以聽到門的另一邊有拖曳的腳步聲和沉重的呼吸聲", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#You have found Kyless. You must destroy him.", "#VIOLET#你找到了克里斯，你必須殺死他。", "logPlayer")
t("Death of Kyless", "克里斯之死", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#Kyless is dead.", "#VIOLET#克里斯死了。", "logPlayer")
t("Berethh", "貝里斯", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#Berethh lies dead.", "#VIOLET#貝利斯死了。", "logPlayer")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/kryl-feijan-escape.lua"

t("The Sect of Kryl-Feijan", "卡洛·斐濟教派", "_t")
t("You discovered a sect worshipping a demon named Kryl-Feijan in a crypt.", " 你在一個地城內發現了一個膜拜惡魔的教派，卡洛·斐濟教派 ", "_t")
t("They were trying to bring it back into the world using a human sacrifice.", " 他們試圖用獻祭活人來召喚惡魔到這個世界上。", "_t")
t("You defeated the acolytes and saved the woman. She told you she is the daughter of a rich merchant of Last Hope.", " 你打敗了那些侍僧並救了這個女人的命。她告訴你她是最後的希望一個富商的女兒。", "_t")
t("You failed to protect her when escorting her out of the crypt.", " 你沒有能成功地將她護送出這個地穴。", "_t")
t("You failed to defeat the acolytes in time - the woman got torn apart by the demon growing inside her.", " 你沒能及時殺死那些侍僧，那個女人被從她體內召喚出的惡魔撕成了碎片。", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/lichform.lua"

t("From Death, Life", "起死回生", "_t")
t("The affairs of this mortal world are trifling compared to your true goal: To conquer death.", " 凡人世界的那些瑣事對於你的終極目標：超越死亡來說是微不足道的。", "_t")
t("Your studies have uncovered much surrounding this subject, but now you must prepare for your glorious rebirth.", " 你關於這個主題的研究已經令你發現了很多東西，現在，你必須準備你輝煌的重生儀式。", "_t")
t("You will need:", " 你需要：", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You are experienced enough.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你有足夠的經驗。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* The ceremony will require that you are worthy, experienced, and possessed of a certain amount of power (level 25, Magic over 50, Willpower over 25 and one prodigy point available).#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 儀式需要你有足夠的財富、經驗並擁有足夠的力量。（等級25，魔力值50，意志值25，具有1點覺醒點）。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have 'extracted' the heart of one of your fellow necromancers.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經取得了你死靈法師同類的心臟。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* The beating heart of a powerful necromancer.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 一個死靈法師跳動的心臟。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* Yiilkgur the Sher'tul Fortress is a suitable location.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 夏·圖爾堡壘伊克格是個合適的地方。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* Yiilkgur has enough energy.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 伊克格有足夠的能量。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You are now on the path of lichdom.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經做好了成爲巫妖的準備。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* Use the control orb of Yiilkgur to begin the ceremony.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 使用伊克格的控制水晶球來開啓儀式。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* Your lair must amass enough energy to use in your rebirth (40 energy).#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你的堡壘中必須積累足夠的能量才能開啓重生儀式。（40 能量）#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* The ceremony will require a suitable location, secluded and given to the channelling of energy#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 儀式必須在一個合適的地方進行，要足夠隱蔽但是又能傳輸能量。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#CRIMSON#* You have ascended to Lichdom!#WHITE#", "#CRIMSON#* 你完成了巫妖轉生！#WHITE#", "_t")
t("Lichform", "巫妖轉生", "_t")
t("The secrets of death lay open to you! You are to become a Lich upon your next death!", "死亡的祕密已經朝你打開了！你下一次死亡就會轉生爲巫妖！", "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/lightning-overload.lua"

t("Storming the city", "雷鳴之城", "_t")
t("As you approached Derth you saw a huge dark cloud over the small town.", " 當你接近德斯村時你看到一個巨大的黑色烏雲籠罩在小鎮上方。", "_t")
t("When you entered you were greeted by an army of air elementals slaughtering the population.", " 當你進入村莊時，你看到的景象：一羣空氣元素正在屠殺村民。", "_t")
t(" * You have dispatched the elementals but the cloud lingers still. You must find a powerful ally to remove it. There are rumours of a secret town in the mountains, to the southwest. You could also check out the Ziguranth group that is supposed to fight magic.", " * 你已經驅散了元素生物，但是天上烏雲並未就此散去。你需要尋找一位盟友來幫助你。傳說中，在西南方的山脈之中有一個神祕的小鎮，你也能順便調查一下伊格蘭斯這個反魔法軍團。", "_t")
t(" * You have learned the real threat comes from a rogue Archmage, a Tempest named Urkis. The mages of Angolwen are ready to teleport you there.", " * 你得知真正的威脅來自於一個叛逃的元素法師，名字叫厄奇斯，精通風暴法術，安格利文的法師已經準備好把你傳送到那裏去了。", "_t")
t(" * You have learned the real threat comes from a rogue Archmage, a Tempest. You have been shown a secret entrance to his stronghold.", " * 你得知真正的威脅來自於一個叛逃的元素法師，是一個風暴法師。你得知了通向它祕密據點的一條隱藏通道。", "_t")
t(" * You have slain Urkis.  Return to Angolwen or Zigur for a reward.", " * 你幹掉了厄奇斯。現在返回安格列文或者伊格領取獎勵吧。", "_t")
t(" * Urkis has been dealt with. Permanently.", " * 厄奇斯被永遠解決掉了。", "_t")
t("Scared Halfling", "驚恐的半身人", "_t")
t([[You step out on unfamiliar grounds. You are nearly on top of one of the highest peaks you can see.
The storm is raging above your head.]], [[你進入了一個不熟悉的地方。你幾乎站在了你能看到的最高峯位置。
風暴在你的頭頂肆虐。]], "_t")
t([[As you arrive in Derth you notice a huge dark cloud hovering over the town.
You hear screams coming from the town square.]], [[當你到達德斯鎮時你注意到小鎮上空有一大團黑壓壓的烏雲。
你聽到小鎮廣場上傳來的尖叫聲。]], "_t")
t("Danger...", "小心……", "_t")
t([[It seems the Ziguranth have kept their word.
Derth is free of the storm cloud.]], [[似乎伊格蘭斯們遵守了他們的諾言。
德斯鎮的風暴威脅解除了。]], "_t")
t("Clear sky", "晴朗的天空", "_t")
t([[It seems the mages have kept their word.
Derth is free of the storm cloud.]], [[似乎法師們遵守了他們的諾言。
德斯鎮的風暴威脅解除了。]], "_t")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/lost-merchant.lua"

t("Trapped!", "陷阱！", "_t")
t("You heard a plea for help and decided to investigate...", " 你聽到了求救聲，決定去調查一下…… ", "_t")
t("Only to find yourself trapped inside an unknown tunnel complex.", " 結果落到了一個未知的複雜通道的陷阱裏。", "_t")
t("A stairway out appears at your feet. The Lord says: 'And remember, you are MINE. I will call you.'", "一道出去的樓梯在你的腳下出現了。強盜頭子說：“記住，你是我的，我會召喚你。”", "logPlayer")
