section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/paradoxology.lua"

t("The Way We Weren't", "穿越時空", "_t")
t([[You have met what seems to be a future version of yourself.
]], [[你看到了一個未來的自己。
]], "_t")
t([[You tried to kill yourself to prevent you from doing something, or going somewhere... you were not very clear.
]], [[你嘗試殺掉自己，以免他做什麼你不知道的事或者到某個……你也不清楚的地方。
]], "_t")
t([[You were killed by your future self, and thus this event never occured.
]], [[你被未來的自己殺掉了，這件事就像沒有發生過一樣。
]], "_t")
t([[You killed your future self. In the future, you might wish to avoid time-traveling back to this moment...
]], [[你殺死了未來的自己，在未來，你可不希望再穿越時空到這個時間點……
]], "_t")
t("%s the Paradox Mage", "時空法師%s", "tformat")
t("A later (less fortunate?) version of %s, possibly going mad.", "某個未來的（並且不太走運的？）%s，恐怕已經陷入了瘋狂。", "tformat")
t("but nobody knew why #sex# suddenly became evil", "但是沒有人知道爲什麼#sex#突然變得邪惡了", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#Killing your own future self does feel weird, but you know that you can avoid this future. Just do not time travel.", "#LIGHT_BLUE#殺死未來的自己貌似有點怪異，不過你知道你可以避免這樣的未來，穿越時空吧。", "logSeen")
t("Meet the guardian!", "去見時空守衛！", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#Your future self kills you! The timestreams are broken by the paradox!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你未來的自己殺死了你！時間流被混亂所打破！", "logSeen")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#All those events never happened. Except they did, somewhen.", "#LIGHT_BLUE#所有這些從來沒有發生過，除了他們在某個時候幹過。", "logSeen")
t("This rift in time has been created by the paradox. You dare not enter it; it could make things worse. Another Warden will have to fix your mess.", "這個時間裂隙是時空紊亂造成的。你不敢進入，事情可能會變得更糟，另外一個守衛將不得不前去修復混亂。", "log")


