section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/shertul-fortress.lua"

t("Sher'Tul Fortress", "夏·圖爾堡壘", "_t")
t("You found notes from an explorer inside the Old Forest. He spoke about Sher'Tul ruins sunken below the surface of the lake of Nur, at the forest's center.", " 在古老森林裏找到了一個探險者的筆記，裏面提到在森林中心的納爾湖底下有一個沉沒的夏·圖爾遺蹟。", "_t")
t("With one of the notes there was a small gem that looks like a key.", " 和筆記在一起被發現的還有個小小的寶石，樣子看上去像一把鑰匙。", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You used the key inside the ruins of Nur and found a way into the fortress of old.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你在納爾湖的底部使用這把鑰匙，進入了一個古老的堡壘。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* The Weirdling Beast is dead, freeing the way into the fortress itself.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 異形觸手死了，進入堡壘的道路被打開了。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have activated what seems to be a ... butler? with your rod of recall.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你用你的召回之杖激活了一個……管家？#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have bound the transmogrification chest to the Fortress power system.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你把轉化之盒連接到了堡壘的能量系統#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have upgraded the transmogrification chest to automatically transmute metallic items into gems before transmogrifying them.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你升級了轉化之盒，現在它會在轉化的時候自動把金屬物品轉化成寶石了。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have unlocked the training room.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你解鎖了訓練室。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have unlocked the hall of reflections.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你解鎖了反射之鏡的大廳。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have upgraded your rod of recall to transport you to the fortress.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你升級了你的召回之杖，可以使你傳送到這個堡壘。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#RED#* You have forced a recall while in an exploratory farportal zone. The farportal was rendered unusable in the process.#WHITE#", "#RED#* 你在探索遠古傳送門空間裏強制啓動了迴歸之杖，遠古傳送門因此變得不穩定了#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have entered the exploratory farportal room and defeated the horror lurking there. You can now use the farportal.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你進入實驗傳送門房間，並清除了那裏的恐魔。你現在可以使用遠古傳送門了。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* The fortress shadow has asked that you come back as soon as possible.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 堡壘之影希望你儘快回來。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have re-enabled the fortress flight systems. You can now fly around in your fortress!#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你重新激活了堡壘的飛行系統。你可以操控你的堡壘飛行了！#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* The fortress shadow has asked that you find an Ancient Storm Sapphire, along with at least 250 energy, to re-enable the fortress flight systems.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 堡壘之影需要你找到緣故風暴藍寶石，並需要 250 能量，才能重啓堡壘飛行系統。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("\
The fortress's current energy level is: #LIGHT_GREEN#%d#WHITE#.", "\
當前堡壘能量等級: #LIGHT_GREEN#%d#WHITE#。", "tformat")
t("Master, you have sent enough energy to improve your rod of recall. Please return to the fortress.", "主人，你已經收集了足夠升級迴歸之杖的能量。請儘快回到堡壘來。", "_t")
t([[Master, you have sent enough energy to activate the exploratory farportal.
However, there seems to be a disturbance in that room. Please return as soon as possible.]], [[主人，你已經收集了足夠啓動探索遠古傳送門的能量。
然而，在那個房間裏引發了一些騷動。請儘快回來。]], "_t")
t("The energy is too low. It needs to be at least 15.", "能量過低，至少需要15點能量。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#Your rod of recall glows brightly for a moment.", "#VIOLET#你的召回之杖閃了一下光。", "log")
t("Fortress Shadow", "堡壘之影", "_t")
t("The energy is too low. It needs to be at least 25.", "能量過低，至少需要25點能量。", "_t")
t("#VIOLET#Your transmogrification chest glows brightly for a moment.", "#VIOLET#你的轉化之盒閃了一下光。", "log")
t("The fortress is not found!", "找不到堡壘!", "log")


