t("#LIGHT_GREEN#Go at once to Last Hope to report those events!", "#LIGHT_GREEN#立刻到最後的希望彙報所發生的情況！", "_t")
t("In its remains, you found a strange staff. It radiates power and danger and you dare not use it yourself.", " 在他的屍體上，你發現了一根奇怪的法杖，它輻射出的力量和危險使你不敢使用它。", "_t")
t("You should bring it to the elders of Last Hope in the southeast.", " 你應該把它帶到最後的希望西南部的長者那裏給他看看。", "_t")
t("#00FFFF#You can feel the power of this staff just by carrying it. This is both ancient and dangerous.", "#00FFFF#你拿着法杖就可以感受到它的力量。它既古老又危險。", "logPlayer")
t("#00FFFF#It should be shown to the wise elders in Last Hope!", "#00FFFF#應該把它交給最後的希望的智慧長老看看！", "logPlayer")
t("#VIOLET#As you come out of the Dreadfell, you encounter a band of orcs!", "#VIOLET#當你走出恐懼王座，你遭遇了一隊獸人！", "logPlayer")
t([[You wake up after a few hours, surprised to be alive, but the staff is gone!
#VIOLET#Go at once to Last Hope to report those events!]], [[幾個小時以後，你醒了過來，驚訝地發現自己還活着，不過法杖已經不見了！
#VIOLET#立刻返回最後的希望報告這件事！]], "_t")
t("Ukruk the Fierce", "兇殘的烏克魯克", "_t")
t("Ambush", "伏擊", "_t")
t([[You are surprised to still be alive.
#VIOLET#Go at once to Last Hope to report those events!]], [[令人驚訝，你竟然活了下來！
#VIOLET#立刻返回最後的希望報告這件事！]], "_t")


