t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Trollmire and vanquished Prox the Troll.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了食人魔巢穴並擊敗了食人魔普洛克斯。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* You must explore the Trollmire and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你必須進入食人魔沼澤去調查那裏潛伏着什麼怪物並找到那裏的寶藏！#WHITE#", "_t")
