t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the ruins of Kor'Pul and vanquished the Shade.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你探索了卡·普爾廢墟並擊敗了暗影骷髏。#WHITE#", "_t")
