section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/start-dwarf.lua"

t("Reknor is lost!", "在瑞克納迷路了！", "_t")
t("You were part of a group of dwarves sent to investigate the situation of the kingdom of Reknor.", " 你是被指派到瑞庫納王國去調查情況的一個矮人小分隊的一員。", "_t")
t("When you arrived there you found nothing but orcs, well organized and very powerful.", " 當你到達那裏時，你受到了大量有組織的強力獸人的阻擊。", "_t")
t("Most of your team was killed there and now you and Norgan (the sole survivor besides you) must hurry back to the Iron Council to bring the news.", " 你隊伍中大多數人被殺死，現在你和諾爾甘 ( 除你以外的唯一倖存者 ) 必須趕緊突圍回到鋼鐵議會去彙報這裏的情況。", "_t")
t("Let nothing stop you.", " 不惜一切代價衝出去。", "_t")
t("Both Norgan and you made it home.", " 你和諾爾甘都回到了家。", "_t")
t("Norgan", "諾爾甘", "_t")


