section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/start-sunwall.lua"

t("Serpentine Invaders", "蛇形的侵略者", "_t")
t([[Nagas are invading the slazish fens. The Sunwall cannot fight on two fronts; you need to stop the invaders before it is too late.
 Locate and destroy the invaders' portal.]], [[ 娜迦正在攻擊斯拉伊什沼澤，太陽堡壘不能同時兩線作戰，你必須抓緊時間阻止那些侵略者，以免爲時過晚。 
 找到並摧毀侵略者的傳送門。]], "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have destroyed the naga portal. The invasion is stopped.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你摧毀了娜迦的傳送門，侵略者被阻止了。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You are back in Var'Eyal, the Far East as the people from the west call it.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你回到了瓦·埃亞爾——來自西方的人稱呼遠東大陸的名字。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* However, you were teleported to a distant land. You must find a way back to the Gates of Morning.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 然而，你被傳送到了一個遙遠的區域，你必須找到返回晨曦之門的方法。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* You must stop the nagas.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你必須阻止那些娜迦。#WHITE#", "_t")


