t([[The Thaloren forest is disrupted. Corruption is spreading. Norgos the guardian bear is said to have gone mad.
]], [[自然精靈森林陷入了混亂，到處肆虐着墮落。據說守護巨熊諾爾格斯已經陷入了瘋狂。
