t("#SLATE#* You must explore Norgos' Lair.#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你必須調查諾爾格斯的巢穴。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Heart of the Gloom and slain the Dreaming One.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了黑暗中心並殺死了夢境之眼。#WHITE#", "_t")
