t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Old Forest and vanquished Shardskin.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了古老森林並殺死了水晶樹精。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Old Forest and vanquished Wrathroot.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了古老森林並殺死了狂怒樹精。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* You must explore the Old Forest and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你應當探索古老森林，查清那裏潛伏的危險，並獲得那裏的寶藏！#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Maze and vanquished the Horned Horror.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了迷宮並殺死了長角恐魔。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Maze and vanquished the Minotaur.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了迷宮並殺死了米諾陶。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* You must explore the Maze and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你應當探索迷宮，查清那裏潛伏的危險，並獲得那裏的寶藏！#WHITE#", "_t")
