t("#SLATE#* You must explore the Sandworm Lair and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你應當探索沙蟲洞穴，查清那裏潛伏的危險，並獲得那裏的寶藏！#WHITE#", "_t")
