t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have explored the Daikara and vanquished the huge ice dragon that dwelled there.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你已經探索了岱卡拉並殺死了這裏的冰龍。#WHITE#", "_t")
t("#SLATE#* You must explore the Daikara and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你應當探索岱卡拉，查清那裏潛伏的危險，並獲得那裏的寶藏！#WHITE#", "_t")


