t("#LIGHT_GREEN#* You have sided with Slasul and killed Ukllmswwik.#WHITE#", "#LIGHT_GREEN#* 你選擇相信薩拉蘇爾並殺死了烏克勒姆斯維奇。#WHITE#", "_t")
