t("Equilibrium represents your standing in the grand balance of nature. The closer it is to 0 the more balanced you are. Being out of equilibrium will adversely affect your ability to use Wild Gifts.", "失衡值代表你大自然和諧的程度。失衡值越低，你和自然和諧的能力就越強。失衡值過高將會影響你使用自然系技能的能力。", "_t")
