t("Hate", "仇恨值", "_t")
t("Hate represents your soul's primal antipathy towards others.  It generally decreases whenever you have no outlet for your rage, and increases when you are damaged or destroy others.", "仇恨值代表你的靈魂對其他生物的憎惡。它會隨着你的怒氣消退而慢慢減少，在你受到傷害或攻擊敵人的時候會增加。", "_t")
t("Paradox", "紊亂值", "_t")
t("Paradox represents how much damage you've done to the space-time continuum. A high Paradox score makes Chronomancy less reliable and more dangerous to use but also amplifies its effects.", "紊亂值代表你對時空連續性造成的損害。較高的紊亂值會使時空法術變得更難控制，更加危險，但也會提升時空法術的效果。", "_t")
