section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/circles.lua"

t("Circle of Shifting Shadows", "暗影之陣", "talent name")
t([[Creates a circle of radius %d at your feet; the circle increases your defense and all saves by %d while dealing %0.2f darkness damage per turn to everyone else within its radius. The circle lasts %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在你的腳下創造一個 %d 碼半徑範圍的陣法，它會提高你 %d 近身閃避和所有豁免，並對周圍目標造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。 
		陣法持續 %d 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Circle of Sanctity", "聖潔之陣", "talent name")
t("Creates a circle of radius %d at your feet; the circle protects you from silence effects while you remain in its radius while silencing and dealing %d light damage to everyone else who enters. The circle lasts %d turns.", [[在你的腳下製造一個 %d 碼半徑範圍的法陣，當你在法陣內，它會使你免疫沉默效果，沉默進入此範圍內的敵人，並對其造成 %d 光系傷害。
		陣法持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Circle of Warding", "守護之陣", "talent name")
t([[Creates a circle of radius %d at your feet; the circle slows incoming projectiles by %d%% and attempts to push all creatures other than yourself out of its radius, inflicting %0.2f light damage and %0.2f darkness damage per turn as it does so.  The circle lasts %d turns.
		The effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在你的腳下製造一個 %d 碼半徑範圍的法陣，它會減慢 %d%% 拋射物速度並將除你外的其他生物推出去。 
		同時，每回合對目標造成 %0.2f 光系傷害和 %0.2f 暗影傷害。 
		法陣持續 %d 回合。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Celestial Surge", "天體潮涌", "talent name")
t([[Conjure a surge of celestial power through your circles. Any foe standing within one of your circles will be slowed by %d%% for %d turns and take %d light and %d darkness damage.
		Residual power from the surge will emanate from your circles for %d turns; each circle you stand in will increase your celestial resources.
		Shifting Shadows: +1 negative.
		Sanctity: +1 postive.
		Warding: +0.5 postive and negative.]], [[從你的法陣中召喚天體能量的潮涌。任何站在你的法陣中的敵人將會受到持續 %d 回合的 %d%% 減速效果，並受到 %d 光系和 %d 黑暗傷害。
		能量潮涌的殘餘力量將會從你的法陣中發出。在 %d 回合內，你每站在一個法陣中，都會獲得額外的天體能量恢復。
		暗影之陣：獲得 +1 負能量。
		聖潔之陣：獲得 +1 正能量。
		守護之陣：獲得 +0.5 正能量和負能量。]], "tformat", {2,1,3,4,5})


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/combat.lua"

t("Weapon of Light", "光明之刃", "talent name")
t([[Infuse your weapon with the power of the Sun, adding %0.1f light damage on each melee hit.
		Additionally, if you have a temporary damage shield active, melee hits will increase its power by %d once per turn.
		The damage dealt and shield bonus will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你的武器充滿太陽能量，每擊造成 %0.1f 光系傷害。 
		如果你同時打開了臨時傷害護盾，每回合一次，你的近戰攻擊命中可以增加護盾 %d 強度。
		傷害和護盾加成受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Wave of Power", "光明衝擊", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%sstrikes twice with Wave of Power!#NORMAL#", "#CRIMSON#%s使用光明衝擊打擊兩次r!#NORMAL#", "logSeen")
t([[In a pure display of power, you project a ranged melee attack, doing %d%% weapon damage.
		If the target is outside of melee range, you have a chance to project a second attack against it for %d%% weapon damage.
		The second strike chance (which increases with distance) is %0.1f%% at range 2 and %0.1f%% at the maximum range of %d.
		The range will increase with your Strength.]], [[你用光明力量釋放一次近程打擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。 
		如果目標在近戰範圍以外，有一定機率進行二次打擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		二次打擊機率隨距離增加，距離 2 時爲 %0.1f%% ，距離最大（ %d ）時機率爲 %0.1f%% 。
		攻擊距離受力量值加成。]], "tformat", {1,2,3,5,4})
t("Weapon of Wrath", "憤怒之刃", "talent name")
t([[Your weapon attacks burn with righteous fury, dealing %d%% of your lost HP as additional Fire damage (up to %d, Current:  %d).
		Targets struck are also afflicted with a Martyrdom effect that causes them to take %d%% of all damage they deal for 4 turns.
		The bonus damage can only occur once per turn.]], [[你使用武器攻擊時，造成相當於 %d%% 你已損失的生命值的火焰傷害 , 至多 %d 點,當前 %d 點 
		然後令目標進入殉難狀態，受到 %d%% 自己造成的傷害，持續 4 回合。
		每回合最多觸發一次額外傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Second Life", "第二生命", "talent name")
t("Any attack that would drop you below 1 hit point instead triggers Second Life, deactivating the talent, setting your hit points to 1, then healing you for %d.", "任何使你生命值降到 1 點以下的攻擊都會激活第二生命，自動中斷此技能並將你的生命值恢復到 1 點,然後受到 %d 點治療。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/crusader.lua"

t("Absorption Strike", "吸能一擊", "talent name")
t([[You strike your foe with your two handed weapon, dealing %d%% weapon damage.
		If the attack hits, all foes in radius 2 will have their light resistance reduced by %d%% and their damage reduced by %d%% for 5 turns.]], [[ 你用雙手武器攻擊敵人，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		如果攻擊命中，半徑 2 以內的敵人光系抗性下降 %d%% ，傷害下降 %d%% , 持續 5 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Mark of Light", "光之印記", "talent name")
t("You mark a target with light for 3 turns, causing all melee hits you deal to it to heal you for %d%% of the damage done.", "你用光標記目標 3 回合，你對它近戰攻擊時，將受到相當於 %d%% 傷害的治療。", "tformat")
t("Righteous Strength", "光明之力", "talent name")
t([[While wielding a two handed weapon, your critical strike chance is increased by %d%%, and your melee criticals instill you with righteous strength, increasing all physical and light damage you deal by %d%%, stacking up to 3 times.
		In addition, your melee critical strikes leave a lasting lightburn on the target, dealing %0.2f light damage over 5 turns and reducing opponents armour by %d.
		The damage increases with your Spellpower.]], [[ 當裝備雙手武器時，你的暴擊率增加 %d%% , 同時你的近戰暴擊會引發光明之力，增加 %d%% 物理和光系傷害加成，最多疊加 3 次。
		同時，你的近戰暴擊會在目標身上留下灼燒痕跡， 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 光系傷害，同時減少 %d 護甲。
		傷害受法強加成。]], "tformat")
t("Flash of the Blade", "閃光之刃", "talent name")
t("You require a two handed weapon to use this talent.", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Infuse your two handed weapon with light while spinning around.
		All creatures in radius one take %d%% weapon damage.
		In addition while spinning your weapon shines so much it deals %d%% light weapon damage to all foes in radius 2.
		At level 4 your spinning blade creates a shield that blocks all damage for 1 turn.]], [[ 旋轉一週，同時將光明之力充滿武器。
		半徑 1 以內的敵人將受到 %d%% 武器傷害，同時半徑 2 以內的敵人將受到 %d%% 光系武器傷害。
		技能等級 4 或以上時，在旋轉時你會製造一層護盾，吸收 1 回合內的所有攻擊。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/dark-sun.lua"

t("Collapse", "坍縮", "talent name")
t([[Open a radius 1 rift in spacetime at the targeted location for %d turns, increasing in radius by 1 each turn to a maximum of %d.
		All caught within the rift are pulled towards the center and take %0.2f gravity damage.
The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在目標地點開啓半徑1的時空裂縫，持續 %d 回合。每回合半徑增加1，最大 %d 。
		所有被裂縫波及的目標都會被朝中心牽引，受到 %0.2f 重力傷害。
傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Devourer Stance", "勢吞干戈", "talent name")
t([[Attune yourself to the endless hunger of distant dead suns.  For the next %d turns, your attacks will inflict an additional %0.2f gravity damage and attempt to pull enemies closer.  After three turns, you will recover half of all damage taken during this effect.
The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你將死星那無盡的飢餓賦予自己。在接下來的 %d 回合裏，你的攻擊造成額外 %0.2f 重力傷害並會試圖將敵人拉近。3回合之後，你獲得此效果期間所受傷害一半的回覆。
傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Singularity Armor", "星核護甲", "talent name")
t("Create a gravity field around you that converts %d%% of all damage you deal into physical damage, slows incoming projectiles by %d%%, and causes your gravity damage to reduce the target's knockback resistance by half for two turns.", "在你身邊製造一個重力場，將你造成傷害的 %d%% 轉化爲物理傷害，使向你發射的飛行物減速 %d%% ，並使你的重力傷害減半目標的擊退抗性兩回合。", "tformat")
t("Doom Spiral", "毀滅螺旋", "talent name")
t([[Infuse your weapon with overwhelming gravitational power while spinning around.
							All creatures within radius 2 take %d%% weapon damage as physical (gravity) and are pulled closer.
							Then, all adjacent creatures take %d%% weapon damage.  This second strike shields you for between %d and %d, increasing with more enemies hit.  The shield lasts for 2 turns.
The shield strength will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[旋轉一週，同時將毀滅性的重力注入武器。
							半徑2以內的生物受到 %d%% 物理（重力）武器傷害並被拉近。
							然後所有相鄰的生物受到 %d%% 武器傷害。這第二次攻擊給予你 %d 到 %d 的護盾，數值隨被擊中的敵人數量增大，持續2回合。
護盾量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/darkside.lua"

t("Brutalize", "暴行", "talent name")
t("%s resists the brutality!", "%s抵抗了暴行！", "logSeen")
t([[Hits the target with your weapon, doing %d%% damage. If the attack hits, the target is stunned for %d turns and has their bleed resistance reduced by 50%%.
The stun chance increases with your Physical Power.

#{italic}#It may not bleed, exactly, but you'll make it hurt.#{normal}#]], [[攻擊目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。如果命中，目標震懾 %d 回合且流血抗性降低 50%%。
震懾概率受物理強度加成。

#{italic}#或許不會出血，但絕對很疼。#{normal}#]], "tformat")
t("Lunacy", "錯亂", "talent name")
t([[Your curse feeds on the magic, which in turn is powered by the curse.
You gain a bonus to Spellpower equal to %d%% of your Willpower.
You gain a bonus to Mindpower equal to %d%% of your Magic.

#{italic}#Something is not quite right inside you.  Your solar spells are somehow twisted, but your bloody rites make things clear as day.#{normal}#]], [[你的詛咒汲取着魔法同時又驅動着魔法。
你獲得相當於 %d%% 意志的法術強度加值。
你獲得相當於 %d%% 魔法的精神強度加值。

#{italic}#你裏面有些不對勁。你的太陽法術被遮蔽了，但你血腥的行徑使得事物依然如同白晝一樣清晰。#{normal}#]], "tformat")
t("Flee the Sun", "陰走", "talent name")
t("%s's teleportation fizzles!", "%s的傳送失敗了!", "logSeen")
t("%s emerges from the darkness!", "%s從黑暗中現身了!", "logSeen")
t([[Fade into the darkness and reappear elsewhere within range %d.  When you emerge from the shadows, you are accompanied by a bright flash, dealing %0.2f light damage to enemies in radius 1.
						 The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[匿跡於黑暗之中並在距離 %d 碼範圍內的另一處重現。一道閃光會伴隨着你從陰影中現身，對半徑1碼範圍內的敵人造成 %0.2f 光系傷害。
						 傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Final Sunbeam", "夕陽烈暮", "talent name")
t([[Put all of your physical and magical might into one devastating attack.
Strike all adjacent enemies for %d%% weapon damage and daze them (using your highest power) for 3 turns.

Using this talent consumes all of your Positive Energy and prevents you from generating positive energy for 5 turns.
Every point of positive energy increases the damage by %.2f%%.
Every %d points of positive energy increase the radius by 1 (up to 10).]], [[將你所有的物理和魔法力量化作一次毀滅性的攻擊。
攻擊所有相鄰的敵人造成 %d%% 武器傷害並眩暈它們3回合（使用你最高的強度）。

使用此技能會耗盡你的正能量且5回合內你無法回覆正能量。
每一點正能量增加傷害 %.2f%% 。
每 %d 點正能量增加半徑1（最大10）。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/dirge.lua"

t("Dirge of Famine", "饑荒輓歌", "talent name")
t([[Sing a song of wasting and desolation which sustains you in hard times.

This dirge increases your health regeneration by %d.  The regeneration will increase with your level.]], [[爲荒廢和孤寂悲嘆一曲來支持困境中的你。

增加你的生命回覆%d。回覆量受等級加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dirge of Conquest", "征服輓歌", "talent name")
t([[Sing a song of violence and victory (mostly violence) and sustain yourself through cruelty.
Each time you deal a critical strike you gain 10%% of a turn (only once per turn).
Each time you kill a creature you gain %d%% of a turn (only once per turn).
]], [[爲暴力和（通過暴力取得的）勝利高歌一曲來支持殘酷的你。
你每次暴擊時獲得 10%% 個回合的時間（每回合限一次）。
你每次殺死一個生物時獲得 %d%% 個回合的時間（每回合限一次）。
]], "tformat")
t("Dirge of Pestilence", "瘟疫輓歌", "talent name")
t([[Sing a song of decay and defiance and sustain yourself through spite.
							Each time you suffer a detrimental effect, you gain a shield with strength %d, that lasts as long as the effect would.  This will add to and extend an existing shield if possible.
							This can only trigger once every %d turns]], [[爲腐敗和暴亂輕唱一曲來支持仇恨中的你。
							每次你受到負面狀態時你獲得 %d 的護盾，持續時間與那個狀態的持續時間相同。這可以強化你已有的傷害護盾。
							這一效果每 %d 回合只能觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Dirge Acolyte", "輓歌入門", "talent name")
t([[Even now, something compels you to sing.
			Dirge of Famine: Increases health regen by %d.
			Dirge of Conquest: Gives you part of a turn on critical (10%%) or kill (%d%%).
			Dirge of Pestilence: Shields you for %d when an enemy inflicts a detrimental effect on you (5 turn cooldown).
			You may only have one Dirge active at a time.]], [[每時每刻，都有什麼驅使着你歌唱。
			饑荒輓歌：增加生命回覆 %d 。
			征服輓歌：給予你暴擊時 10%% 回合或殺戮時 %d%% 回合的時間。
			瘟疫輓歌：敵人對你造成負面效果時獲得 %d 的護盾。
			你同時只能激活一種輓歌。]], "tformat")
t("Dirge Intoner", "悲慟之聲", "talent name")
t([[Your dirges carry the pain within you, which threatens to swallow those who come too close.  Anyone who hits you in melee suffers %0.2f mind damage.
							You, on the other hand, are steadied by the song.  Your dirges increase your resistance to stun and knockback by %d%%.
							The damage will increase with your Mindpower and your level.]], [[你的輓歌中寄寓着痛苦，過於接近你的生物可能會被這份痛苦吞噬。任何近戰擊中你的敵人會受到 %0.2f 精神傷害。
							而你則被這歌聲激勵着。輓歌增加你 %d%% 的震懾和擊退抗性。
							傷害受精神強度和等級加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dirge Adept", "輓歌專家", "talent name")
t([[Your dirges echo mournfully through the air.  When you end a dirge, you continue to gain its acolyte-level effects for %d turns.  You can only benefit from one such lingering dirge at a time.

Furthermore, you are given focus by the song.  Your dirges increase your resistance to confusion and fear by %d%%.]], [[你的輓歌在周圍迴盪着悲傷。當你結束輓歌時，你持續獲得其入門效果 %d 回合。你同時只能受到一種輓歌的餘音效果。

而且歌聲使得你更加專注。輓歌增加你 %d%% 的混亂和恐懼抗性。]], "tformat")
t("Dirge Nihilist", "虛無主義", "talent name")
t([[Your dirges deaden you to the outside world, reducing all incoming damage by %d.
The damage reduction will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的輓歌使你對外界變得遲鈍，減免所有傷害 %d 。
傷害減免受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/eclipse.lua"

t("Blood Red Moon", "血月喚醒", "talent name")
t("Increases your spell critical chance by %d%%.", "增加你 %d%% 法術暴擊率。", "tformat")
t("Totality", "日全食", "talent name")
t([[Increases your light and darkness resistance penetration by %d%% for %d turns, and reduces the cooldown of all Celestial skills by %d.
		The resistance penetration will increase with your Cunning.]], [[增加 %d%% 光系和暗影系抵抗穿透，持續 %d 回合。同時，減少你所有天空系技能冷卻時間 %d 回合至冷卻。 
		抵抗穿透受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Corona", "日冕", "talent name")
t([[Each time one of your spells criticals, you project a bolt of light or shadow at up to %d targets within radius %d, doing %0.2f light damage or %0.2f darkness damage per bolt.
		This effect costs 2 positive or 2 negative energy each time it's triggered, and will not activate if either your positive or negative energy is below 2.
		The damage scales with your Spellpower.
		This spell cannot crit.]], [[每當你的法術打出暴擊時，你會對 %d 碼內 %d 個目標發射一顆光球或暗影球，造成 %0.2f 光系或 %0.2f 暗影傷害。 
		每個球都會消耗 2 點正能量或負能量，當你的正能量或負能量低於 2 時不會觸發。 
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。
		該法術造成的傷害不能暴擊。]], "tformat", {2,1,3,4})
t("Darkest Light", "至暗之光", "talent name")
t("Shroud foes within radius %d in darkest light, dealing %0.2f light and %0.2f darkness damage per turn and converting %d%% of the damage they deal between light and darkness for %d turns.", "用無盡黑暗包圍半徑 %d 範圍內的所有敵人，每回合對其造成 %0.2f 光系和 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並將它們所造成的傷害的 %d%% 轉化爲光系和暗影傷害，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/glyphs.lua"

t("Glyphs", "聖印", "talent name")
t("glyph of sunlight", "日光聖印", "_t")
t("Deals %d light damage and heals the summoner for %d", "造成 %d 光系傷害，並恢復召喚者 %d 生命值。", "tformat")
t("glyph of moonlight", "月光聖印", "_t")
t("Deals %d darkness damage and saps the foes energy, reducing all damage dealt by %d%% for %d turns.", "造成 %d 暗影傷害，並吸收敵人的能量，使其造成的所有傷害降低 %d%% ，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("glyph of twilight", "暮光聖印", "_t")
t("trap", "陷阱", "_t")
t("Explodes knocking the enemy 1 space in a random direction and dealing %d light and %d darkness damage.", "爆炸將敵人向隨機方向擊退1格，造成 %d 光系和 %d 暗影傷害。", "tformat")
t([[When one of your spells goes critical, you bind glyphs in radius 1 centered on a random target in range %d at the cost of 5 positive and 5 negative energy.
		Glyphs last for %d turns and cause various effects when an enemy enters their grid.
		Glyphs will only spawn on enemies that aren't adjacent to an existing glyph.
		This can only happen every %d game turns.
		Glyph effects will scale with your Spellpower.

		Avalable glyphs are:
		#ffd700#Glyph of Sunlight#LAST#:  Bind sunlight into a glyph. When triggered it will release a brilliant light, dealing %0.2f light damage and healing you for %d.
		#7f7f7f#Glyph of Moonlight#LAST#:  Bind moonlight into a glyph. When triggered it will release a fatiguing darkness,  dealing %0.2f darkness damage and reducing the foes damage dealt by %d%% for %d turns.
		#9D9DC9#Glyph of Twilight#LAST#:  Bind twilight into a glyph. When triggered it will release a burst of twilight, dealing %0.2f light and %0.2f darkness damage and knocking the foe back %d tiles.
		]], [[每當你的法術暴擊時，你消耗 5 點正能量和負能量，在範圍 %d 內的隨機目標周圍 1 碼半徑的區域內放置隨機聖印。
		聖印持續 %d 回合，當敵人踩上時，會對其產生特殊效果。
		聖印只會在周圍沒有聖印的敵人周圍產生。
		每 %d 遊戲回合最多觸發一次該效果。
		聖印效果受法術強度加成。
		
		有以下幾種可用的聖印：
		#ffd700#日光聖印#LAST#——將陽光注入聖印。當其觸發時，將會釋放出明亮耀眼的光芒，造成 %0.2f 光系傷害，並恢復你 %d 生命值。
		#7f7f7f#月光聖印#LAST#——將月光注入聖印。當其觸發時，將會釋放出疲憊睏倦的黑暗，造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並使目標所造成的傷害減少 %d%% ，持續 %d 回合。
		#9D9DC9#暮光聖印#LAST#——將暮光注入聖印。當其觸發時，將會釋放出突然爆炸的暮光，造成 %0.2f 光系和 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並將目標擊退 %d 格。
		]], "tformat")
t("Glyphs of Fury", "憤怒之印", "talent name")
t([[Your glyphs are imbued with celestial fury; they last %d turns longer and when triggered they will deal damage.
		#ffd700#Glyph of Sunlight#LAST#:  Deals %0.2f light damage.
		#7f7f7f#Glyph of Moonlight#LAST#:  Deals %0.2f darkness damage.
		#9D9DC9#Glyph of Twilight#LAST#:  Deals %0.2f light and %0.2f darkness damage.]], [[你的聖印被注入了來自天空的怒火。
		它們的持續時間延長 %d 回合，並在觸發時造成額外傷害。
		#ffd700#日光聖印#LAST#：造成 %0.2f 光系傷害。
		#7f7f7f#月光聖印#LAST#：造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		#9D9DC9#暮光聖印#LAST#：造成 %0.2f 光系和 %0.2f 暗影傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Empowered Glyphs", "充能之印", "talent name")
t("Up to 3 times per turn when one of your glyphs triggers you feel a surge of celestial power, increasing your darkness and light resistance and affinity by 5%% for %d turns, stacking up to %d times.", "當你的聖印觸發時，天空能量的涌動讓你獲得暗影、光系抗性和傷害吸收各 5%% ，持續 %d 回合，最多疊加 %d 次。該效果每回合最多觸發 3 次。", "tformat")
t("Destabilize Glyphs", "激發聖印", "talent name")
t([[Destabilize your glyphs, triggering every glyph in radius 10 with an enemy standing on it.
		At talent level 2 glyphs triggered this way will leave a residue of themselves on the ground, dealing damage each turn for %d turns.
		#ffd700#Sunlight#LAST#:  %0.2f light damage.
		#7f7f7f#Moonlight#LAST#:  %0.2f darkness damage.
		#9D9DC9#Twilight#LAST#:  %0.2f light and %0.2f darkness damage]], [[激發所有聖印，10格內所有上方站着敵人的聖印將被觸發。
		技能等級2時，該效果觸發的聖印將在地面遺留能量，在 %d 回合內持續造成傷害。
		#ffd700#日光聖印#LAST#： %0.2f 光系傷害。
		#7f7f7f#月光聖印#LAST#： %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		#9D9DC9#暮光聖印#LAST#： %0.2f 光系和 %0.2f 暗影傷害。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/guardian.lua"

t("Shield of Light", "光能沁盾", "talent name")
t([[Infuse your shield with light, healing you for %0.2f each time you take damage at the expense of up to 2 positive energy.
		If you do not have any positive energy, the effect will not trigger.
		Additionally, once per turn successful melee attacks will trigger a bonus attack with your shield dealing %d%% light damage.
		The healing done will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你的盾牌充滿光系能量，每次受到攻擊會消耗 2 點正能量並恢復 %0.2f 生命值。 
		如果你沒有足夠的正能量，此效果無法觸發。 
		同時，每回合一次，近戰攻擊命中時會附加一次盾擊，造成 %d%% 光系傷害。
		恢復量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Brandish", "劍盾之怒", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Brandish without a shield!", "必須裝備一面盾牌！", "logPlayer")
t([[Hits the target with your weapon doing %d%% damage, and with a shield strike doing %d%% damage. If the shield strike connects, your shield will explode in a burst of light that inflicts %0.2f light damage on all targets except yourself within radius %d of the target, and light up all tiles in that radius.
		The light damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[用你的武器對目標造成 %d%% 傷害，同時盾擊目標造成 %d%% 傷害。如果盾牌擊中目標，則會產生光系爆炸，對範圍內除你以外的所有目標造成 %0.2f 光系範圍傷害（半徑 %d 碼）並照亮受影響區域。 
		光系傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Retribution", "懲戒之盾", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Retribution without a shield!", "必須裝備一面盾牌！", "logPlayer")
t("#RED#Absorb Remaining: %d", "#RED#剩餘吸收量：%d", "tformat")
t([[Retribution negates half of all damage you take while it is active. Once Retribution has negated %0.2f damage, your shield will explode in a burst of light, inflicting damage equal to the amount negated in a radius of %d and deactivating the talent.
		The amount absorbed will increase with your Spellpower.
		%s]], [[吸收你受到的一半傷害。一旦懲戒之盾吸收 %0.2f 傷害值，它會產生光系爆炸，在 %d 碼半徑範圍內造成等同吸收值的傷害並中斷技能效果。 
		傷害吸收值受法術強度加成。
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Crusade", "十字軍打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Crusade without a shield!", "使用十字軍打擊必須使用盾牌!", "logPlayer")
t([[You demonstrate your dedication to the light with a measured attack striking once with your weapon for %d%% Light damage and once with your shield for %d%% Light damage.
			If the first strike connects %d random talent cooldowns are reduced by 1.
			If the second strike connects you are cleansed of %d debuffs.]], [[你用武器攻擊造成 %d%% 光系傷害，再用盾牌攻擊造成 %d%% 光系傷害。
			如果第一次攻擊命中，隨機 %d 個技能冷卻時間減少1回合 。
			如果第二次攻擊命中，除去你身上至多 %d 個 debuff。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/hymns.lua"

t("Hymn of Shadows", "暗影聖詩", "talent name")
t([[Chant the glory of the Moons, gaining the agility of shadows.
		This increases your movement speed by %d%% and your spell speed by %d%%.
		You may only have one Hymn active at once.
		The effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[讚頌月之榮耀，使你獲得暗影之靈敏。
		移動速度增加 %d%% ，施法速度增加 %d%%
		同時只能激活一種聖詩。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn of Detection", "偵查聖詩", "talent name")
t([[Chant the glory of the Moons, granting you stealth detection (+%d power), and invisibility detection (+%d power).
		You may also attack creatures you cannot see without penalty and your critical hits do %d%% more damage.
		You may only have one Hymn active at once.
		The stealth and invisibility detection will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[讚美月之榮耀，使你能察覺潛行單位（ +%d 偵測等級）和隱形單位（ +%d 偵測等級）。 
		你攻擊不可見目標時無懲罰，同時暴擊造成 %d%% 額外傷害。 
		同時只能激活 1 個聖詩。 
		偵測等級和傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn of Perseverance", "堅毅聖詩", "talent name")
t([[Chant the glory of the Moons, granting you %d%% stun, blindness and confusion resistance.
		You may only have one Hymn active at once.]], [[讚美月之榮耀，增加你 %d%% 震懾、致盲和混亂抵抗。 
		同時只能激活 1 個聖詩。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn of Moonlight", "月光聖詩", "talent name")
t("#DARK_GREY#A shroud of shadow dances around %s!", "#DARK_GREY#陰影圍繞着%s起舞！", "logSeen")
t("%s's %s", "%s的%s", "tformat")
t("#DARK_GREY#The shroud of shadows around %s disappears.", "#DARK_GREY#圍繞着%s起舞的陰影消失了。", "logSeen")
t([[Chant the glory of the Moons, conjuring a shroud of dancing shadows that follows you as long as this spell is active.
		Each turn, a shadowy beam will hit up to %d of your foes within radius 5 for 1 to %0.2f damage.
		This powerful spell will drain %0.1f negative energy for each beam; no beam will fire if your negative energy is too low.
		You may only have one Hymn active at once.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[讚美月之榮耀，在技能激活時，在你身邊產生一片跟隨你的影之舞。 
		每回合隨機向附近 5 碼半徑範圍內的 %d 個敵人發射暗影射線，造成 1 到 %0.2f 傷害。 
		這個強大法術的每道射線會消耗 %0.1f 負能量，如果能量值過低則不會發射射線。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn Acolyte", "聖詩入門", "talent name")
t([[You have learned to sing the praises of the Moons, in the form of three defensive Hymns:

Hymn of Shadows: Increases your movement speed by %d%% and your spell casting speed by %d%%.

Hymn of Detection: Increases your ability to see stealthy creatures by %d and invisible creatures by %d, and increases your critical power by %d%%.

Hymn of Perseverance: Increases your resistance to stun, confusion and blinding by %d%%.

You may only have one Hymn active at a time.]], [[你學會了三種防禦聖詩，以此詠唱對月亮的讚頌：
		暗影聖詩：增加 %d%% 移動速度和 %d%% 施法速度。
		偵察聖詩：增加 %d 潛行偵察， %d 隱身偵察， %d%% 暴擊傷害 
		堅毅聖詩：增加 %d%% 震懾、混亂、致盲抗性。
		你同時只能激活一種聖詩。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn Incantor", "暗影臨近", "talent name")
t([[Your Hymns now focus darkness near you, which increases your darkness damage by %d%% and does %0.2f darkness damage to anyone who hits you in melee.
		These values scale with your Spellpower.]], [[聖詩讓暗影集中在你身邊，你的黑暗傷害增加 %d%% ，並對所有近戰攻擊你的敵人造成 %0.2f 暗屬性傷害。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn Adept", "聖詩專家", "talent name")
t([[Your skill in Hymns now improves your sight in darkness, increasing your infravision radius by %d.
		Also, when you end a Hymn, you will gain a buff of a type based on which Hymn you ended.
		Hymn of Shadows increases your movement speed by %d%% for one turn.
		Hymn of Detection makes you invisible (power %d) for %d turns.
		Hymn of Perseverance grants a damage shield (power %d) for %d turns.]], [[詠唱聖詩的嫺熟技藝讓黑暗不再阻礙你的視線，增加 %d 暗視半徑。
		每次你結束舊的聖詩時，你將獲得聖詩提供的增益效果。
		暗影聖詩：增加 %d%% 移動速度，持續 1 回合。 
		偵察聖詩：隱身 ( %d 強度) 持續 %d 回合。 
		堅毅聖詩：護盾 ( %d 強度) 持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Hymn Nocturnalist", "暗夜流光", "talent name")
t([[Your passion for singing the praises of the Moons reaches its zenith.
		Your Hymns now fire shadowy beams that will hit up to %d of your foes within radius 5 for 1 to %0.2f damage, with a 20%% chance of blinding.
		This powerful effect will drain %0.1f negative energy each time it fires at at least 1 target; no beam will fire if your negative energy is too low.
		These values scale with your Spellpower.]], [[詠唱聖詩歌頌月亮的熱情達到了頂峯。
		你的聖詩自動產生陰影射線攻擊周圍 5 格內至多 %d 個敵人，造成 1 到 %0.2f 傷害，同時有 20%% 機率觸發致盲效果。
		這項效果每產生一發射線並擊中至少一個目標將抽取 %0.1f 負能量，能量過低時無法產生射線。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/light.lua"

t("Healing Light", "治癒之光", "talent name")
t([[An invigorating ray of Sunlight shines upon you, healing your body for %d life.
		The amount healed will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[一束充滿活力的陽光照耀着你，治療你 %d 點生命值。 
		治療量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bathe in Light", "光之洗禮", "talent name")
t([[A magical zone of Sunlight appears around you, healing and shielding all within a radius of %d for %0.2f per turn and increasing healing effects on everyone within by %d%%. The effect lasts for %d turns.
		Existing damage shields will be added to instead of overwritten and have their duration set to 2 if it isn't higher.
		If the same shield is refreshed 20 times it will become unstable and explode, removing it.
		It also lights up the affected area.
		The amount healed will increase with the Magic stat]], [[陽光傾瀉在你周圍 %d 碼範圍內，每回合治療所有單位 %0.2f 生命值, 給予其等量的護盾 , 並增加此範圍內所有人 %d%% 治療效果。此效果持續 %d 回合。
		如果已經存在護盾，則護盾將會增加等量數值，如果護盾持續時間不足 2 回合，會延長至 2 回合。
		當同一個護盾被刷新 20 次後，將會因爲不穩定而破碎。
		它同時會照亮此區域。 
		治療量受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Barrier", "護盾術", "talent name")
t([[A protective shield forms around you that lasts for up to %d turns and negates %d damage.
 		The total damage the barrier can absorb will increase with your Spellpower and can crit.]], [[一個持續 %d 回合的保護性聖盾圍繞着你，可吸收 %d 點傷害。 
		 聖盾的最大吸收量受法術強度加成，該技能可以暴擊。]], "tformat")
t("Providence", "光之守護", "talent name")
t("Places you under the protection of a ray of sunlight. For %d turns, the light removes a single negative effect from you every turn.", "你位於陽光的保護下，每回合移除 1 種負面狀態，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/other.lua"

t("Glyph of Explosion", "爆炸聖印", "talent name")
t("You somehow fail to set the corrosive seed.", "你沒能設置腐蝕之種。", "logPlayer")
t("glyph of explosion", "爆炸聖印", "_t")
t("Explodes (radius 1) for %d light damage.", "爆炸 (範圍 1) 造成 %d 光系傷害。", "tformat")
t("test glyph", "測試聖印", "tformat")
t("Glyph of Paralysis", "麻痹聖印", "talent name")
t("glyph of paralysis", "麻痹聖印", "_t")
t("Dazes for %d turns.", "眩暈 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t([[You bind light in a glyph on the floor. All enemies walking over the glyph will be dazed for %d turns.
		The glyph is a hidden trap (%d detection and %d disarm power based on your Magic) and lasts for %d turns.]], [[你用光能在地上刻畫聖印。所有經過的目標會被眩暈 %d 回合。 
		聖印視爲隱藏陷阱（ %d 偵查強度 , %d 點解除強度 , 基於魔法）持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Glyph of Repulsion", "衝擊聖印", "talent name")
t("glyph of repulsion", "衝擊聖印", "_t")
t("Deals %d physical damage, knocking the target back.", "造成 %d 物理傷害，擊退目標。", "tformat")
t([[You bind light in a glyph on the floor. All enemies walking over the glyph will be hit by a blast that does %0.2f physical damage and knocks them back.
		The glyph is a hidden trap (%d detection and %d disarm power based on your Magic) and lasts for %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你用光能在地上刻畫聖印。所有經過的目標會受到 %0.2f 傷害並被擊退。 
		聖印視爲隱藏陷阱（ %d 偵查強度 , %d 點解除強度 , 基於魔法）持續 %d 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Glyph of Fatigue", "疲勞聖印", "talent name")
t("glyph of fatigue", "疲勞聖印", "_t")
t("trap", "陷阱", "_t")
t("Slows (%d%%) for 5 turns.", "減速 (%d%%) 5 回合。", "tformat")
t([[You bind light in a glyph on the floor. All enemies walking over the glyph will be slowed by %d%% for 5 turns.
		The glyph is a hidden trap (%d detection and %d disarm power based on your Magic) and lasts for %d turns.]], [[你用光能在地上刻畫聖印。所有經過的目標會減速 %d%% ，持續 5 回合。 
		聖印視爲隱藏陷阱（ %d 偵查強度 , %d 點解除強度 , 基於魔法）持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/radiance.lua"

t("Radiance", "光輝", "talent name")
t([[You are so infused with sunlight that your body glows permanently in radius %d, even in dark places.
		Your vision and body adapt to this glow, giving you %d%% blindness resistance, %d%% light resistance, and %d%% light affinity.
		The light radius overrides your normal light if it is bigger (it does not stack).
		]], [[你的體內充滿了陽光，你的身體會發光，半徑 %d 。
		你的眼睛和身體適應了光明，獲得 %d%% 目盲免疫， %d%% 光系抗性和 %d%% 光系傷害吸收。
		光照超過你的燈具時取代之，不與燈具疊加光照。
		]], "tformat")
t("Judgement", "裁決", "_t")
t([[Fire a glowing orb of light at each enemy within your Radiance.  Each orb will slowly follow its target until it connects, dealing %d light damage to anything else it contacts along the way.  When the target is reached the orb will explode dealing %d light damage in radius 1 and healing you for 50%% of the damage dealt.
		All targets struck by your Judgement will be blighted by light, reducing saves by %d, reducing critical power by %d%%, and causing light damage received to splash in radius 2 for %d%% damage against all hostile targets for 4 turns.]], [[在你的光輝中，向每一個敵人發射一個發光的球體。球體會緩慢追蹤會目標，直到擊中目標，對它沿途接觸到的其他物體造成 %d 點光系傷害。當到達目標時，球體將爆炸，在半徑 1 碼範圍內造成 %d 點光系傷害，並治療你 50%% 傷害量的生命值。
		所有被你的裁決擊中的目標都將受到光的照耀，降低 %d 全豁免，降低 %d%% 暴擊傷害，受到的光系傷害將會在 2 碼範圍內濺射，對敵對目標造成 %d%% 傷害，持續 4 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Searing Sight", "灼燒", "talent name")
t([[Your Radiance is so powerful it burns all foes caught in it, dealing %0.1f light damage to all foes caught inside every turn.
		Each enemy effected has a %d%% chance of being dazed and blinded by the light for 3 turns. The daze and blind can be applied to each enemy at most once every 7 turns.
		The damage increases with your Spellpower.]], [[你強大的光輝灼燒其中的目標，對裏面所有的敵人每回合造成 %0.1f 光系傷害。
		每個被這一效果影響的敵人會有 %d%% 機率被光震懾或致盲，持續 3 回合。震懾或致盲對單個敵人最多每 7 回合觸發一次。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Illumination", "照明", "talent name")
t([[The light of your Radiance allows you to see that which would normally be unseen and strike that which would normally be protected.
		All enemies in your Radiance aura have their invisibility and stealth power reduced by %d; all actors affected by illumination have their defense reduced by %d as well as all evasion bonuses from being unseen negated.
		In addition, your light damage is increased by %d%% and your strikes ignore %d%% of the light resistance of your targets.
		The invisibility, stealth power, and defense reductions increase with your Spellpower.]], [[光輝可以讓你看到平時無法見到的敵人，並攻擊被保護的敵人。
		在光輝光環的影響下的敵人，其隱形和潛行強度降低 %d 。所有被光照的目標，閃避值降低 %d ，且不受不可見帶來的閃避加成影響。
		此外，你的光系傷害降低 %d%% ，你的攻擊無視敵人 %d%% 的光系傷害抗性。
		隱形、潛行強度和閃避值降低效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/star-fury.lua"

t("Moonlight Ray", "月光射線", "talent name")
t([[Focuses the power of the Moon into a beam of shadows, doing %0.2f damage.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚月光的力量形成陰影射線，對目標造成 %0.2f 傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Blast", "陰影爆炸", "talent name")
t([[Invokes a blast of shadows that deals %0.2f darkness damage, and leaves a radius 3 field that does %0.2f darkness damage per turn for %d turns.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[引起一片暗影爆炸，對目標造成 %0.2f 點暗影傷害，並在 3 碼半徑範圍的區域內每回合造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害，持續 %d 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Twilight Surge", "光暗狂潮", "talent name")
t([[A surge of twilight pulses from you, doing %0.2f light and %0.2f darkness damage to all others within radius %d.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[一股洶涌的光暗狂潮圍繞着你，在你周圍 %d 碼半徑內造成 %0.2f 光系和 %0.2f 暗影範圍傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {3,1,2})
t("Starfall", "星沉地動", "talent name")
t([[A star falls on a radius %d area, doing %0.2f darkness damage on impact and stunning all within the area for 4 turns.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你搖落星辰，震懾 %d 碼半徑範圍內所有目標 4 回合，並造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/sun.lua"

t("Sun Ray", "陽光烈焰", "talent name")
t([[Calls forth a ray of light from the Sun, doing %0.1f Light damage to the target.
		At level 3 the ray will be so intense it will also blind the target and everyone in a radius 2 around it for %d turns.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 召喚太陽之力，形成一道射線，造成 %0.1f 點光系傷害。
		等級 3 時射線變得如此強烈，半徑 2 以內的敵人將被致盲 %d 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Path of the Sun", "陽光大道", "talent name")
t([[A path of sunlight appears in front of you for 5 turns. All foes standing inside take %0.1f Light damage per turn.
		While standing in the path, your movement takes no time and can not trigger traps.
		The damage done will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 在你面前出現一條陽光大道，持續 5 回合。任何站在上面的敵人每回合受到 %0.1f 點光系傷害。
		你站在上面行走不消耗時間, 也不會觸發陷阱。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sun's Vengeance", "陽光之怒", "talent name")
t([[Infuse yourself with the raging fury of the Sun, increasing your physical and spell critical chance by %d%%.
		Each time you crit with a physical attack or a spell you have %d%% chance to gain Sun's Vengeance for 2 turns.
		While affected by Sun's Vengeance, your Sun Ray will take no time to use and will deal 25%% more damage.
		If Sun Ray was on cooldown, the remaining turns are reduced by one instead.
		This effect can only happen once per turn.]], [[讓陽光的怒火充滿自身，增加 %d%% 物理和法術暴擊率。
		每次物理或法術暴擊時，有 %d%% 機率獲得陽光之怒效果，持續兩回合。
		當效果激活時，你的陽光烈焰變爲瞬間技能，同時傷害增加 25%% 。
		如果陽光烈焰處於冷卻中，則減少 1 回合冷卻時間。 
		該效果一回合至多觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Suncloak", "陽光護體", "talent name")
t([[You wrap yourself in a cloak of sunlight that empowers your magic and protects you for 6 turns.
		While the cloak is active, your spell casting speed is increased by %d%%, your spell cooldowns are reduced by %d%%, and you cannot take more than %d%% of your maximum life from a single blow.
		The effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 你將自己包裹在陽光中，保護你 6 回合。
		你的施法速度增加 %d%% ，法術冷卻減少 %d%% ，同時一次攻擊不能對你造成超過 %d%% 最大生命的傷害。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/sunlight.lua"

t("Searing Light", "灼熱之矛", "talent name")
t([[Calls the power of the Sun into a searing lance, doing %d damage to the target and leaving a radius 1 area of searing light on the ground for 4 turns that does %d light damage to all foes within it.
		The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你祈禱太陽之力形成一束灼熱的長矛，對目標造成 %d 點傷害，並在地上半徑爲 1 的範圍內留下灼熱光斑，每回合對其中的敵人造成 %d 光系傷害，持續 4 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sun Flare", "日珥閃耀", "talent name")
t([[Invokes the Sun to cause a flare within radius %d, blinding your foes for %d turns and lighting up the area.
		All enemies effected will take %0.2f light damage.
		At talent level 3 you gain %d%% light, darkness, and fire resistance for %d turns.
		The damage done and resistances will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[祈禱太陽之力，在 %d 碼半徑範圍內致盲目標，持續 %d 回合並照亮你的周圍區域。
		範圍內的敵人將會受到 %0.2f 光系傷害。
		等級 3 時，你將獲得 %d%% 光系、暗影和火焰傷害抗性，持續 %d 回合。
		傷害和抗性受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Firebeam", "陽炎噴射", "talent name")
t([[Call forth the Sun to summon a fiery beam that pierces to the farthest enemy dealing %d fire damage to all enemies hit.
		This spell will automatically cast again at the start of your next two turns.
		You will gain %0.2f positive energy each time firebeam or an instant damage proc caused by firebeam deals damage.
		The damage done will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[汲取太陽之力向目標射出一束太陽真火，射向最遠的敵人，對這條直線上的所有敵人造成 %d 火焰傷害。 
		這一技能將會每隔一個回合自動額外觸發一次，共額外觸發 2 次。
		每次射線發射或造成傷害時，你回覆 %0.2f 正能量。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sunburst", "日炎爆發", "talent name")
t("Release a burst of sunlight beams at %d random foes in radius %d, dealing %d damage to all foes hit and increasing your bonus light damage by %d%% of your bonus darkness damage for %d turns.", "對半徑 %d 範圍內最多 %d 個敵人射出一團太陽光線，對所有擊中的目標造成 %d 傷害，並使你的光系傷害加成增加相當於你暗影傷害加成 %d%% 的值，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat", {2,1,3,4,5})


