section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/celestial/twilight.lua"

t("Twilight", "黃昏", "talent name")
t([[You stand between the darkness and the light, allowing you to convert 15 positive energy into %d negative energy.
		The negative energy gain will increase with your Cunning.]], [[你處於黑暗和光明之間，能夠將 15 點正能量轉化爲 %d 負能量。 
		效果受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Jumpgate: Teleport To", "躍遷之門：傳送", "talent name")
t("You must sustain the Jumpgate spell to be able to teleport.", "你必須激活 躍遷之門 才能傳送。", "logPlayer")
t("Instantly travel to your jumpgate, as long as you are within %d tiles of it.", "在 %d 碼範圍以內你可以立即傳送至你的躍遷之門。", "tformat")
t("Jumpgate", "躍遷之門", "talent name")
t([[Create a shadow jumpgate at your current location. As long as you sustain this spell, you can use 'Jumpgate: Teleport' to instantly travel to the jumpgate, as long as you are within %d tiles of it.
		Note that any stairs underneath the jumpgate will be unusable while the spell is sustained, and you may need to cancel this sustain in order to leave certain locations.
		At talent level 4, you learn to create and sustain a second jumpgate.]], [[在你的位置製造 1 個陰影躍遷之門，當你激活這個技能時你可以使用躍遷之門：傳送技能將你傳送至此（躍遷之門必須在你 %d 碼範圍以內）。 
		注意：當此技能激活且樓梯位於躍遷之門下方時，樓梯將不可使用。你必須取消此技能方可使用樓梯離開該區域。 
		在等級 4 時，你可以製造 2 個躍遷之門。]], "tformat")
t("Mind Blast", "心靈震爆", "talent name")
t([[Let out a mental cry that shatters the will of your targets within radius %d, dealing %0.2f darkness damage and confusing (%d%% to act randomly) them for %d turns.
		The damage will improve with your spellpower and the duration will improve with your Cunning.]], [[在 %d 碼半徑範圍內釋放一股精神衝擊，摧毀目標的意志，對其造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並使其混亂 ( %d%% 機率隨機行動），持續 %d 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成，持續時間受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Simulacrum", "陰影幻象", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("You can't target summons!", "你不能選擇召喚物爲目標！", "logSeen")
t("You can't target allies!", "你不能選擇盟友爲目標！", "logSeen")
t("%s's shadow simulacrum", "%s的陰影幻象", "tformat")
t("A dark, shadowy shape whose form resembles the creature it was copied from. It is not a perfect replica, though, and it makes you feel uneasy to look at it.", "一團漆黑的陰影，模仿着被複制生物的外形。雖然複製並不完美，但直視它仍然讓人心悸。", "_t")
t([[Creates a shadowy copy of a hostile target. The copy will attack its progenitor immediately and lasts for %d turns.
		The duplicate has %d%% of the target's life, +50%% darkness resistance, -50%% light resistance, and deals 50%% less damage.
		The duration and life scale with your Cunning.]], [[用陰影複製一個敵對目標的幻象。這個幻象會立刻攻擊它的原型，持續 %d 回合。
		幻象擁有 %d%% 的目標生命， +50%% 暗影傷害抵抗， -50%% 光系傷害抵抗，造成 -50%% 的傷害。
		持續時間和幻象生命受你的靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Jumpgate Two", "躍遷之門II", "talent name")
t("jumpgate", "躍遷之門", "_t")
t("Create a second shadow jumpgate at your location. As long as you sustain this spell, you can use 'Jumpgate: Teleport' to instantly travel to the jumpgate, as long as you are within %d tiles of it.", "在你當前位置創造第 2 個躍遷之門，你可以使用躍遷之門：傳送技能將你傳送至這個位置，距離不超過 %d 碼。", "tformat")
t("Jumpgate Two: Teleport To", "躍遷之門：傳送II", "talent name")
t("You must sustain the Jumpgate Two spell to be able to teleport.", "你必須開啓躍遷之門II技能才能傳送。", "logPlayer")
t("Instantly travel to your second jumpgate, as long as you are within %d tiles of it.", "立即傳送你至先前創造的第 2 個躍遷之門，距離不超過 %d 碼。", "tformat")


