section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/age-manipulation.lua"

t("Turn Back the Clock", "時光倒流", "talent name")
t([[Projects a bolt of temporal energy that deals %0.2f temporal damage, and reduces the targets three highest stats by %d for 3 turns.
		The damage dealt will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[製造一束時空能量波造成 %0.2f 時空傷害並降低目標三項最高屬性值 %d 點，持續 3 回合。 
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Temporal Fugue Old", "時空神遊（舊）", "talent name")
t("Reverts the minds of all creatures in a radius %d cone to an infantile state, in effect confusing them (%d%% to act randomly) for %d turns.", "將 %d 碼錐形半徑範圍內敵人的心智降低到嬰兒水平，混亂目標 ( %d%% 強度) %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Ashes to Ashes", "塵歸塵", "talent name")
t([[You surround yourself with a radius %d distortion of time, which deals %0.2f stacking temporal damage over 3 turns to all other creatures.  The effect lasts %d turns.
		The damage dealt will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[時空扭曲光環圍繞着你（ %d 碼半徑範圍），在 3 回合內對範圍所有目標造成 %0.2f 累積時空傷害。效果持續 %d 回合。 
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Body Reversion", "返老還童", "talent name")
t([[You revert your body to a previous state, healing yourself for %0.2f life and removing %d physical status effects (both good and bad).
		The amount of life healed will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[你的身體回覆至先前狀態，治療自己 %0.2f 生命值並移除 %d 個物理狀態（增益狀態或負面狀態）。 
		受法術強度影響，生命回覆按比例加成。]], "tformat")


