t("@Source@ creates a bubble of slow time.", "@Source@製造出減速時間氣泡。", "_t")
t("Slows up to five targets in a radius %d ball by %d%%.", "讓半徑 %d 範圍內最多五個單位減速 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Anomaly Haste", "異常：加速", "talent name")
t("@Source@ creates a bubble of fast time.", "@Source@製造出加速時間氣泡。", "_t")
t("Increases global speed of up to five targets in a radius %d ball by %d%%.", "讓半徑 %d 範圍內最多五個單位增加整體速度 %d%% 。", "tformat")
