section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/blade-threading.lua"

t("Warp Blade", "扭曲靈刃", "talent name")
t([[Attack with your melee weapons for %d%% weapon damage as physical and temporal (warp) damage. If either attack hits you may stun, blind, pin, or confuse the target for %d turns.
		
		Blade Threading talents will freely swap to your dual-weapons when activated if you have them in your secondary slots.  Additionally you may use the Attack talent in a similar manner.]], [[使用你的近戰武器攻擊敵人，造成 %d%% 的物理和時空屬性的武器傷害。如果任意一次攻擊命中，你可以震懾、致盲、定身或者混亂目標 %d 回合。
		
		激活螺旋靈刃技能可以自由切換到你的雙持武器（必須裝備在副武器欄位上）。此外，當你使用近戰攻擊時也會觸發這個效果 ]], "tformat")
t("Blink Blade", "閃爍靈刃", "talent name")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t([[Teleport to the target and attack with your melee weapons for %d%% damage.  Then teleport next to a second random enemy, attacking for %d%% damage.
		Blink Blade can hit the same target multiple times.]], [[傳送到目標面前，並使用你的近戰武器攻擊目標，造成 %d%% 傷害。然後隨機傳送到第二個目標面前，攻擊並造成 %d%% 傷害。
		閃爍靈刃可以命中同一個目標多次。]], "tformat")
t("Blade Shear", "靈刃切變", "talent name")
t("You require two weapons to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s has been cut from the timeline!", "%s被從時間線中切除", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the temporal shear!", "%s 抵擋了靈刃切變！", "logSeen")
t([[Attack up to three adjacent targets for %d%% weapon damage.  If any attack hits you'll create a temporal shear dealing %0.2f temporal damage in a radius %d cone.
		Each target you hit with your weapons beyond the first increases the damage of the shear by 25%%.  Targets reduced below 20%% of maximum life by the shear may be instantly slain.
		The cone damage improves with your Spellpower.]], [[攻擊至多三個相鄰目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。任何一次攻擊命中將會製造一次時空切變，造成 %0.2f 時空傷害，攻擊半徑爲 %d 的錐形內的目標。		
		隨後的每次命中都將增加切變的傷害 25%% 。  被切變將血量減少到最大值 20%% 以下的目標將會立刻死亡。
		切變的傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blade Ward", "靈刃守衛", "talent name")
t("While dual-wielding you have a %d%% chance of completely parrying melee attacks made against you.", "雙持時你有 %d%% 機率格擋近戰攻擊。", "tformat")


