section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/bow-threading.lua"

t("Arrow Stitching", "重疊靈矢", "talent name")
t([[Fire an arrow for %d%% weapon damage and call up to 2 wardens, depending on available space, that will each fire a single arrow before returning to their timelines.
		The wardens are out of phase with normal reality and deal %d%% less damage but shoot through friendly targets. All your arrows, including arrows from Shoot and other talents, now phase through friendly targets without causing them harm.
		
		Bow Threading talents will freely swap to your bow when activated if you have one in your secondary slot. You may use the Shoot talent in a similar manner.]], [[發射一支靈矢造成 %d%% 武器傷害，並且根據可用空間，召喚最多兩個守衛，各自發射一枚靈矢然後回到他們自己的時間線中。
		守衛處在現實位面之外，靈矢的傷害減少 %d%% ，但能夠穿過友好目標。同時，你發射的所有來自射擊或者其他技能的箭矢，都可以穿透友軍並且不會造成傷害。
		
		激活螺旋靈弓技能可以自由切換到你的弓（必須裝備在副武器欄位上）。此外，當你使用遠程攻擊時也會觸發這個效果。]], "tformat")
t("Singularity Arrow", "奇點之矢", "talent name")
t("%s resists the knockback!", "%s抵抗了擊退！", "logSeen")
t("%s is drawn in by the singularity!", "%s 被拖向時空奇點！", "logSeen")
t([[Fire an arrow for %d%% weapon damage. When the arrow reaches its destination or hits a target it will draw in all other targets in a radius of %d and inflict %0.2f physical damage.
		Each target moved beyond the first increases the damage %0.2f (up to %0.2f bonus damage).
		Targets take reduced damage the further they are from the epicenter (20%% less per tile).
		The additional damage scales with your Spellpower.]], [[發射一支靈矢造成 %d%% 武器傷害。當靈矢到達目標地點或者擊中目標後，會牽引半徑 %d 並造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。
		從第二個單位起，每增加一個被牽引的單位，會使傷害增加 %0.2f (最多增加 %0.2f 額外傷害 ).
		目標離牽引中心的距離越遠受到的傷害就越低 (每格減少 20%% ).
		受法術強度影響，額外傷害有加成。]], "tformat")
t("Arrow Echoes", "靈矢回聲", "talent name")
t("You do not have line of sight.", "你沒有視線", "logSeen")
t([[Over the next %d turns you'll fire up to %d arrows at this target from this location, each dealing %d%% weapon damage to the target. 
		These shots do not consume ammo.]], [[在下面的 %d 回合中，你從當前所在位置對目標發射最多 %d 支靈矢，每支對目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。 
		這些射擊不消耗彈藥。]], "tformat")
t("Arrow Threading", "螺旋靈矢", "talent name")
t("Your arrows now tune your Paradox %0.2f points towards your preferred Paradox on hit.", "當你發射的箭矢命中時，將會使你的紊亂值向預設值調諧 %0.2f 點。", "tformat")


