section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/fate-weaving.lua"

t("Spin Fate", "命運之絲", "talent name")
t([[Each time you would take damage from someone else you gain one Spin, increasing your defense and saves by %d for three turns.
		This effect may occur once per turn and stacks up to three Spin (for a maximum bonus of %d).]], [[每當你要受到其他人造成的傷害時，你編織一層命運之絲，使你的閃避和豁免增加 %d ，持續三回合。
		這個效果每回合只能觸發一次，絲能疊加三層 ( 加成最多爲 %d ).]], "tformat")
t("Seal Fate", "命運封印", "talent name")
t([[Activate to Seal Fate for %d turns.  When you damage a target while Seal Fate is active you gain Spin and have a %d%% chance to increase the duration of one detrimental status effect on it by one turn.
		If you have Spin Fate active the chance will be increased by 33%% per Spin (for %d%% at three Spin.)
		The duration increase can occur up to %d times per turn and the bonus Spin once per turn.]], [[激活這個技能封印命運 %d 回合。
		在這個技能激活期間，每當你對目標造成傷害，你獲得一層命運之絲效果，並有 %d%% 機率延長目標的一個負面效果一回合。
		每層命運之絲將使負面狀態延長的概率增加 33%% ( 三層效果時增加 %d%% 。 )
		負面狀態延長每回合只能觸發 %d 次，該效果獲得的命運之絲每回合最多一層。]], "tformat")
t("Fateweaver", "命運編織", "talent name")
t("You now gain %d combat accuracy, physical power, spellpower, and mindpower per Spin.", "現在每層命運之絲使你獲得 %d 命中，物理、法術和精神強度。", "tformat")
t("Webs of Fate", "命運之網", "talent name")
t([[For the next %d turns you displace %d%% of any damage you receive onto a random enemy.
		While Webs of Fate is active you may gain one additional Spin per turn and your maximum Spin is doubled.]], [[接下來的 %d 回合中，你將受到的 %d%% 傷害轉移給隨機的敵人。
		當命運之網激活時，你每回合可以額外獲得一層命運之絲，同時你的命運之絲上限翻倍。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/flux.lua"

t("Induce Anomaly", "引導異常", "talent name")
t([[Create an anomaly, reducing your Paradox by %d.  This spell will never produce a major anomaly.
		Induced Anomalies may not be held by Twist Fate, nor do they cause held anomalies to trigger.  However upon learning Twist Fate you may target Induced Anomalies.
		The Paradox reduction will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[引發一次異常，減少你的紊亂值 %d 。這個技能不會引發重大異常。
		引導異常不會被扭曲命運延後，也不會觸發被延後的異變。 
		然而，當學會扭曲命運後，你可以選中引導異變作爲目標。
		紊亂值減少效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Reality Smearing", "彌散現實", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE##Source# converts damage to paradox!", "#LIGHT_BLUE##Source#將傷害轉化爲紊亂值!", "delayedLogMessage")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#(%d converted)#LAST#", "#LIGHT_BLUE#(%d 轉化)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[While active 30%% of all damage you take is converted into %0.2f Paradox per point.
		The Paradox is gained over three turns.]], [[當激活這個技能時，你受到傷害的 30%% 被轉化爲 %0.2f 的紊亂值。
		這些紊亂傷害會被分散到三個回合中。]], "tformat")
t("Attenuate", "湮滅洪流", "talent name")
t([[Deals %0.2f temporal damage over %d turns to all targets in a radius of %d.  Targets with Reality Smearing active will instead recover %d life over four turns.
		If a target is reduced below 20%% life while Attenuate is active it may be instantly slain.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[對範圍內所有單位造成 %0.2f 時空傷害，這些傷害會被分散到 %d 回合中。技能半徑爲 %d 格。
		帶有彌散現實效果的單位不會受到傷害，並在四回合中回覆 %d 生命值。
		如果目標的生命值被減低到 20%% 以下，湮滅洪流將會立刻殺死目標。
		傷害受到法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Twist Fate", "扭曲命運", "talent name")
t("You must have a twisted anomaly to cast this spell.", "你必須有被捕獲的異常來使用該法術。", "logPlayer")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#Casts %s.", "#STEEL_BLUE#釋放 %s.", "logPlayer")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#Targeting %s", "#STEEL_BLUE#瞄準%s", "saySimple")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#You take control of %s.", "#STEEL_BLUE#你控制了一次%s.", "logPlayer")
t([[If Twist Fate is not on cooldown minor anomalies will be held for %d turns, allowing your spell to cast as normal.  While held you may cast Twist Fate in order to trigger the anomaly and may choose the target area.
		If a second anomaly occurs while a prior one is held or the timed effect expires the first anomaly will trigger immediately, interrupting your current turn or action.
		Paradox reductions from held anomalies occur when triggered.
				
		Current Anomaly: %s
		
		%s]], [[當扭曲命運沒有進入冷卻時，微小異變將會被延後 %d 回合，允許你正常地使用法術。  你可以使用扭曲命運技能來選擇指定的區域來觸發被延後的異變。		如果在第一個異變被延後的回合中引發了第二個異變，那麼第一個異變將會立刻觸發，並且打斷你當前的回合或行動。
		當觸發被延後的異變時，可以立即減少紊亂值。
				
		當前異變： %s 
		
		%s ]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/gravity.lua"

t("Repulsion Blast", "排斥衝擊", "talent name")
t("%s slams into something solid!", "%s撞到了某個堅實的物體！", "logSeen")
t("%s is knocked back!", "%s 被擊退。", "logSeen")
t([[Sends out a blast wave of gravity in a radius %d cone, dealing %0.2f base physical (gravity) damage and knocking back targets caught in the area.
		Targets knocked into walls or other targets take 25%% additional damage and deal 25%% damage to targets they're knocked into.
		Closer targets will be knocked back further and the damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[在半徑 %d 碼的錐形範圍內釋放一股爆炸性的重力衝擊波，造成 %0.2f 物理 (重力 )傷害並擊退範圍內目標。
		被擊飛至牆上或其他單位的目標受到額外 25%% 傷害，並對被擊中的單位造成 25%% 傷害。
		離你越近的目標將會被擊飛得更遠。受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Gravity Spike", "重力釘刺", "talent name")
t("%s resists the knockback!", "%s抵抗了擊退！", "logSeen")
t("%s is drawn in by the singularity!", "%s 被拖向時空奇點！", "logSeen")
t([[Creates a gravity spike in a radius of %d that moves all targets towards the spell's center and inflicts %0.2f physical (gravity) damage.
		Each target moved beyond the first increases the damage by %0.2f (up to a maximum of %0.2f bonus damage).
		Targets take reduced damage the further they are from the epicenter (20%% less per tile).
		The damage dealt will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[在半徑 %d 範圍內製造一個重力釘刺，將所有目標牽引至法術中心，造成 %0.2f 物理 (重力 )傷害。
		從第二個單位起，每牽引一個單位將會使傷害增加 %0.2f (最多增加 %0.2f 額外傷害 )。
		離法術中心越遠，目標受到的傷害越少 (每格減少 20%%)。
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Gravity Locus", "重力核心", "talent name")
t([[Create a gravity field around you that converts %d%% all damage you deal into physical damage, slows incoming projectiles by %d%%, and protects you from all gravity damage and effects.
		Additionally, damage dealt by Repulsion Blast has a %d%% chance to reduce the target's knockback resistance by half for two turns.]], [[在你身邊製造一個重力場，將你造成傷害的 %d%% 轉化爲物理傷害，使向你發射的飛行物減速 %d%% ，並使你免受重力傷害和效果的影響。
		此外，排斥衝擊對目標造成傷害之後，有 %d%% 的機率將目標的擊退抗性減半兩回合。]], "tformat")
t("Gravity Well", "重力之井", "talent name")
t([[Increases local gravity in a radius of %d for %d turns, dealing %0.2f physical (gravity) damage as well as decreasing the global speed of all affected targets by %d%%.
		The damage done will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[增加半徑 %d 範圍內的重力 %d 回合，造成 %0.2f 物理 ( 重力 ) 傷害，並降低所有目標的整體速度 %d%% 。
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/guardian.lua"

t("Strength of Purpose", "意志之力", "talent name")
t([[Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using swords, axes, maces, knives, or bows.
		You now also use your Magic in place of Strength when equipping weapons and ammo as well as when calculating weapon damage.
		These bonuses override rather than stack with weapon mastery, dagger mastery, and bow mastery.]], [[當使用劍、斧、權杖、匕首或者弓箭時，增加武器傷害 %d%% ，物理強度30。
		當裝備武器、彈藥或者計算武器傷害時，你使用魔法取代你的力量屬性進行計算。
		這個技能的獎勵傷害取代武器掌握、匕首掌握和弓箭掌握的加成。]], "tformat")
t("Guardian Unity", "守衛融合", "talent name")
t("Guardian", "守衛", "_t")
t("#STEEL_BLUE##Source# shares damage with %s guardian!", "#STEEL_BLUE##Source#和%s的守衛共享傷害!", "delayedLogMessage")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#(%d shared)#LAST#", "#STEEL_BLUE#(%d 傷害共享)#LAST#", "tformat")
t("Not enough space to summon warden!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚守衛！", "logPlayer")
t([[When a single hit deals more than %d%% of your maximum life another you appears and takes %d%% of the damage as well as %d%% of all damage you take for the next %d turns.
		The clone is out of phase with this reality and deals 50%% less damage but its arrows will pass through friendly targets.
		This talent has a cooldown.]], [[當單次攻擊對你造成了最大生命值 %d%% 以上的傷害時，另一個你出現，吸收這次傷害的 %d%% ，並吸收 %d%% 你在接下來 %d 回合中的所有傷害。
		這個克隆體處於現實位面之外，因此只能造成 50%% 傷害，並且射出的箭矢可以穿過友軍。		這個技能有冷卻時間。]], "tformat")
t("Vigilance", "嚴陣以待", "talent name")
t("#ORCHID#%s has recovered!#LAST#", "#ORCHID#%s恢復了!#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[Improves your capacity to see invisible foes by +%d and to see through stealth by +%d.  Additionally you have a %d%% chance to recover from a single negative status effect each turn.
		Sense abilities will scale with your Magic stat.]], [[增強你的隱形偵測能力 +%d 以及潛行偵測能力 +%d 。  此外，每回合你有 %d%% 的機率從一個負面狀態中回覆。
		受魔法屬性影響，偵測能力按比例增加。]], "tformat")
t("Warden's Focus", "專注守衛", "talent name")
t("You require a weapon to use this talent.", "你需要武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You must pick a focus target.", "你必須選擇一個集中目標", "logPlayer")
t([[Attack the target with either your ranged or melee weapons for %d%% weapon damage.  For the next %d turns random targeting, such as from Blink Blade and Warden's Call, will focus on this target.
		Attacks against this target gain %d%% critical chance and critical strike power while you take %d%% less damage from all enemies whose rank is lower then that of your focus target.]], [[使用你的遠程或者近戰武器對目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。  在接下來的 %d 回合中，你的隨機目標技能，比如閃爍靈刃和守衛召喚將會集中命中目標。
		對這個目標的攻擊獲得 %d%% 額外的暴擊機率和暴擊加成，同時其他分級低於目標的單位對你造成的傷害減少 %d%% ]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/induced-phenomena.lua"

t("Cosmic Cycle", "宇宙圈", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#Your cosmic cycle expands.", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你的宇宙圈膨脹了。", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_RED#Your cosmic cycle contracts.", "#LIGHT_RED#你的宇宙圈收縮了。", "logPlayer")
t([[Tune yourself into the ebb and flow of spacetime.  When your Paradox crosses a 100 point threshold, your Cosmic Cycle gains or loses one radius.
		While Cosmic Cycle is expanding, your temporal resistance penetration will be increased by %d%%.  While it's contracting, your Willpower for Paradox calculations will be increased by %d%%.]], [[調整你自己進入時空的漲落。當你的紊亂值超過100點的臨界點時，你的宇宙輪迴會膨脹或收縮一個半徑。
		當宇宙圈膨脹時，你的時空抗性穿透將增加 %d%% 。當它收縮時，你計算紊亂值時的意志力將增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Polarity Shift", "奇點切換", "talent name")
t("You must have Cosmic Cycle active to use this talent.", "你必須開啓宇宙圈才能使用這一技能", "logPlayer")
t("Polarity Bolt", "奇點飛彈", "_t")
t([[Reverses the polarity of your Cosmic Cycle.  If it's currently contracting, it will begin to expand, firing a homing missile at each target within the radius that deals %0.2f temporal damage.
		If it's currently expanding, it will begin to contract, braiding the lifelines of all targets within the radius for %d turns.  Braided targets take %d%% of all damage dealt to other braided targets.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[逆轉你宇宙圈的極性。如果它正在收縮，它將開始膨脹，向半徑範圍內的每個目標發射一枚瞄準的飛彈，造成 %0.2f 時空傷害。
		如果它目前正在擴張，它將開始收縮，將半徑範圍內所有目標的生命線編織 %d 回合。被編織目標承受對其他編織目標造成的所有傷害的 %d%% 。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Reverse Causality", "逆轉因果", "talent name")
t([[When a creature enters your expanding Cosmic Cycle, you heal %d life at the start of your next turn.
		When a creature leaves your contracting Cosmic Cycle, you reduce the duration of one detrimental effect on you by %d at the start of your next turn.
		The healing will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[當一個生物進入你膨脹的宇宙圈時，你在下一回合開始時治療 %d 生命。
		當一個生物離開你收縮的宇宙圈時，你在下一回合開始時將對你造成一個負面效果的持續時間減少 %d 。
		治療量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Epoch", "亞伯契", "talent name")
t("%s resists the blindness!", "%s抵抗了致盲!", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the pin!", "%s抵抗了定身！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the confusion!", "%s抵抗了混亂！", "logSeen")
t([[While your cosmic cycle is expanding, creatures in its radius have a %d%% chance to suffer the effects of aging; pinning, blinding, or confusing them for 3 turns.
		While your cosmic cycle is contracting, creatures in its radius suffer from age regression; reducing their three highest stats by %d.
		The chance and stat reduction will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[當你的宇宙圈在擴展時，其半徑內的生物有 %d%% 的機會遭受老化的影響；定身、致盲或混亂它們3回合。
		當你的宇宙圈在收縮時，其半徑內的生物會遭受年齡退行的痛苦；它們的三個最高屬性會減少 %d 。
		機率和屬性降低效果受法術強度加成。
		]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/matter.lua"

t("Dust to Dust", "土歸土", "talent name")
t([[Fires a beam that turns matter into dust, inflicting %0.2f temporal damage and %0.2f physical (warp) damage.
		Alternatively you may target yourself, creating a field of radius %d around you that will inflict the damage over three turns.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[發射一道射線，令物質歸於塵土，造成 %0.2f 時空與 %0.2f 物理傷害。
		也可以以自己爲目標，製造一個圍繞自己 %d 碼的領域，在 3 回合內造成傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Matter Weaving", "物質編織", "talent name")
t([[Weave matter into your flesh, becoming incredibly resilient to damage.  While active you gain %d armour, %d%% resistance to stunning, and %d%% resistance to cuts.
		The bonus to armour will scale with your Magic.]], [[你的血肉被改變，對傷害的抗性提高。
		增加 %d 護甲， %d%% 震懾免疫， %d%% 流血免疫。
		護甲加成受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Materialize Barrier", "物質屏障", "talent name")
t("materialize barrier", "物質屏障", "_t")
t("a summoned wall of stone", "召喚的岩石牆壁", "_t")
t([[Create a tightly bound matter wall of up to a length of %d that lasts %d turns.
		If any part of this wall is dug out it will explode, causing targets in a radius of %d to bleed for %0.2f physical damage over six turns.]], [[製造一層堅實的物質牆，長度爲 %d ，持續 %d 回合。
		當牆壁被挖掘時，會產生半徑 %d 的爆炸，範圍內敵人會進入流血狀態， 6 回合內受到 %0.2f 物理傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Disintegration", "裂解", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's beneficial effect was stripped!#LAST#", "#CRIMSON#%s的有益效果被除去了！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[While active your physical and temporal damage has a %d%% chance to remove one beneficial physical or magical temporary effect (respectively) from targets you hit.
		Only one physical and one magical effect may be removed per turn from each target.
		Additionally your Dust to Dust spell now digs up to %d tiles into walls.]], [[你造成物理和時空傷害時，有 %d%% 機率除去一項物理或魔法增益效果。
		每個生物每回合只能被除去一項效果。
		同時，你的土歸土技能能挖至多 %d 格內的牆壁。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/other.lua"

t("Spacetime Tuning", "時空調諧", "_t")
t("What's your preferred paradox level?", "你希望將紊亂值調整到多少？", "_t")
t([[Use to set your preferred Paradox.  While resting or waiting you'll adjust your Paradox towards this number at the rate of %d per turn.
		Your Paradox modifier is factored into the duration and spellpower of all chronomancy spells.

		Preferred Paradox :  %d
		Paradox Modifier :  %d%%
		Spellpower for Chronomancy :  %d
		Willpower Paradox Modifier : -%d
		Paradox Sustain Modifier : +%d
		Total Modifed Paradox :  %d
		Current Anomaly Chance :  %d%%]], [[設置自己的紊亂值。
		休息或等待時，你每回合將自動調節 %d 點紊亂值趨向於你的設定值。
		你的紊亂值會修正所有時空法術的持續時間和法術強度。
		設定的紊亂值：%d
		紊亂值修正率：%d%%
		時空法術強度：%d
		意志修正數值：-%d
		紊亂維持數值：+%d
		修正後紊亂值：%d
		當前異常機率：%d%%]], "tformat")
t("Slow", "減速", "talent name")
t([[Creates a time distortion in a radius of %d that lasts for %d turns, decreasing global speed by %d%% for 3 turns and inflicting %0.2f temporal damage each turn to all targets within the area.
		The slow effect and damage dealt will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[在 %d 碼半徑範圍內製造 1 個時間扭曲力場，持續 %d 回合。同時減少 %d%% 目標整體速度，持續 3 回合，當目標處於此範圍內時每回合造成 %0.2f 時空傷害。 
		減速效果和傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Spacetime Mastery", "時空掌握", "talent name")
t("Your mastery of spacetime reduces the cooldown of Banish, Dimensional Step, Swap, and Temporal Wake by %d, and the cooldown of Wormhole by %d.  Also improves your Spellpower for purposes of hitting targets with chronomancy effects that may cause continuum destabilization (Banish, Time Skip, etc.), as well as your chance of overcoming continuum destabilization, by %d%%.", "你對時空的掌握讓你減少空間跳躍、時空放逐、、時空覺醒的冷卻時間 %d 個回合，減少蟲洞躍遷的冷卻時間 %d 個回合。同時當你對目標使用可能造成連續紊亂的技能（時空放逐、時間跳躍）時增加 %d%% 的法術強度。", "tformat")
t("Quantum Feed", "量子充能", "talent name")
t([[You've learned to boost your magic through your control over the spacetime continuum.  Increases your Magic and your Spell Save by %d.
		The effect will scale with your Willpower.]], [[你已經學會通過控制時空的流動來增強魔力。 
		增加 %d 點魔法和法術豁免。 
		效果受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Moment of Prescience", "預知之門", "talent name")
t([[You pull your awareness fully into the moment, increasing your stealth detection, see invisibility, defense, and accuracy by %d for %d turns.
		If you have Spin Fate active when you cast this spell, you'll gain a bonus to these values equal to 50%% of your spin.
		This spell takes no time to cast.]], [[你集中意識提升你的潛行偵測、隱形偵測、閃避和命中機率 %d 持續 %d 回合。 
		如果你已經激活了命運之網技能，你將得到一個基於 50%% 命運之網獲得提升點數的增益。 
		此技能不需要施法時間。]], "tformat")
t("Gather the Threads", "聚集螺旋", "talent name")
t([[You begin to gather energy from other timelines. Your Spellpower will increase by %0.2f on the first turn and %0.2f more each additional turn.
		The effect ends either when you cast a spell, or after five turns.
		Eacn turn the effect is active, your Paradox will be reduced by %d.
		This spell will not break Spacetime Tuning, nor will it be broken by activating Spacetime Tuning.]], [[你開始從其他時間線蒐集能量，初始增加 %0.2f 法術強度並且每回合逐漸增加 %0.2f 法術強度。 
		此效果會因爲使用技能而中斷，否則此技能會在 5 回合後結束。 
		當此技能激活時，每回合你的紊亂值會降低 %d 點。 
		此技能不會打斷時空調諧，激活時空調諧技能也同樣不會打斷此技能。]], "tformat")
t("Entropic Field", "熵光領域", "talent name")
t([[You encase yourself in a field that slows incoming projectiles by %d%%, and increases your physical resistance by %d%%.
		The effect will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[製造一個領域圍繞自己，減少所有拋射物 %d%% 的速度並增加 %d%% 物理傷害抵抗。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fade From Time", "時光凋零", "talent name")
t([[You partially remove yourself from the timeline for 10 turns.
		This increases your resistance to all damage by %d%%, reduces the duration of all detrimental effects on you by %d%%, and reduces all damage you deal by 20%%.
		The resistance bonus, effect reduction, and damage penalty will gradually lose power over the duration of the spell.
		The effects scale with your Spellpower.]], [[你將部分身體移出時間線，持續 10 回合.
		增加你 %d%% 所有傷害抵抗，減少 %d%% 負面狀態持續時間並減少 20%% 你造成的傷害。 
		抵抗加成、狀態減少值和傷害懲罰會隨法術持續時間的增加而逐漸減少。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("%s's Paradox Clone", "%s的無序克隆", "tformat")
t("The real %s... or so %s says.", "真正的%s... 或者%s這樣說。", "tformat")
t("Paradox Clone", "無序克隆", "_t")
t([[You summon your future self to fight alongside you for %d turns.  At some point in the future, you'll be pulled into the past to fight alongside your past self after the initial effect ends.
		This spell splits the timeline.  Attempting to use another spell that also splits the timeline while this effect is active will be unsuccessful.]], [[你召喚未來的自己和你一起戰鬥，持續 %d 回合。當技能結束後，在未來的某個時間點，你會被拉回到過去，協助你自己戰鬥。 
		這個法術會使時間線分裂，所以其他同樣能使時間線分裂的技能在此期間不能成功釋放。]], "tformat")
t("Displace Damage", "傷害轉移", "talent name")
t("#PINK##Source# displaces some damage onto #Target#!", "#PINK##Source#將部分傷害轉移至#Target#!", "delayedLogMessage")
t([[You bend space around you, displacing %d%% of any damage you receive onto a random enemy within range.
		]], [[空間在你身邊摺疊，轉移 %d%% 傷害到範圍內隨機 1 個敵人身上。
		]], "tformat")
t("Repulsion Field", "排斥之環", "talent name")
t([[You surround yourself with a radius %d distortion of gravity, knocking back and dealing %0.2f physical damage to all creatures inside it.  The effect lasts %d turns.  Deals 50%% extra damage to pinned targets, in addition to the knockback.
		The blast wave may hit targets more then once, depending on the radius and the knockback effect.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[你用 %d 碼半徑範圍的重力吸收光環圍繞自己，擊退所有單位並造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。此效果持續 %d 回合。對定身狀態目標額外造成 50%% 傷害。 
		這股爆炸性衝擊波可能會對目標造成多次傷害，這取決於攻擊半徑和擊退效果。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("Temporal Clone", "時空複製", "_t")
t([[Clones the target creature for up to %d turns.  The duration of the effect will be divided by half the target's rank, and the target will have have %d%% of its normal life and deal %d%% less damage.
		If you clone a hostile creature the clone will target the creature it was cloned from.
		The life and damage penalties will be lessened by your Spellpower.]], [[你複製目標，從其他時間線上召喚出複製體，持續 %d 回合。持續時間將會除以目標分級的一半，且複製體只擁有目標 %d%% 的生命，造成的傷害減少 %d%% 。
		如果你複製了一個敵人，複製體會立刻瞄準那個被你複製的敵人。 
		受法術強度加成，生命值和傷害懲罰按比例減小。]], "tformat")
t("Damage Smearing", "時空轉化", "talent name")
t("%s(%d smeared)#LAST#", "%s(%d 時空轉化)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[You convert %d%% of all non-temporal damage you receive into temporal damage spread out over %d turns.
		This damage will bypass resistance and affinity.]], [[你轉化所有受到的 %d%% 的非時空傷害爲持續 %d 回合的時空傷害釋放出去。 
		造成的傷害無視抗性和傷害吸收。]], "tformat")
t("Phase Shift", "相位切換", "talent name")
t("Phase shift yourself for %d turns; any damage greater than 10%% of your maximum life will teleport you to an adjacent tile and be reduced by 50%% (can only happen once per turn).", "切換你的相位 %d 回合；任何將會對你造成超過你最大生命值 10%% 傷害的攻擊會把你傳送到一個相鄰的格子裏，並且這次傷害減少50%%（每回合只能發生一次）。", "tformat")
t("Swap", "時空交換", "talent name")
t("%s resists the swap!", "%s抵抗了時空交換！", "logSeen")
t([[You manipulate the spacetime continuum in such a way that you switch places with another creature with in a range of %d.  The targeted creature will be confused (power %d%%) for %d turns.
		The spell's hit chance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你控制時間的流動來使你和 %d 碼範圍內的某個怪物交換位置。目標會混亂（ %d%% 強度） %d 回合。 
		法術命中率受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Temporal Wake", "時空甦醒", "talent name")
t("You do not have line of sight.", "你沒有視線", "logSeen")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the stun!", "%s抵抗了震懾！", "logSeen")
t([[Violently fold the space between yourself and another point within range.
		You teleport to the target location, and leave a temporal wake behind that stuns for %d turns and deals %0.2f temporal and %0.2f physical warp damage to targets in the path.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[暴力地摺疊你和另外一個點之間的空間。你傳送到目標地點並造成時空的甦醒，震懾路徑上的所有目標 %d 回合並造成 %0.2f 時空傷害和 %0.2f 物理（摺疊）傷害 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Carbon Spikes", "碳化釘刺", "talent name")
t([[Fragile spikes of carbon protrude from your flesh, clothing, and armor, increasing your armor rating by %d and inflicting %0.2f bleed damage over six turns on attackers.   Each time you're struck, the armor increase will be reduced by 1.  Each turn the spell will regenerate 1 armor up to its starting value.
		If the armor increase from the spell ever falls below 1, the sustain will deactivate and the effect will end.
		The armor and bleed damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[脆弱的碳化釘刺從你的肉體、衣服和護甲中伸出來，增加 %d 點護甲值。同時，在 6 回合內對攻擊者造成總計 %0.2f 點流血傷害。每次你受到攻擊時，護甲增益效果減少 1 點。每回合會自動回覆 1 點護甲增益至初始效果。 
		如果護甲增益降到 1 點以下，則技能會被中斷，效果結束。 
		護甲增益和流血傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Destabilize", "時空裂隙", "talent name")
t([[Destabilizes the target, inflicting %0.2f temporal damage per turn for 10 turns.  If the target dies while destabilized, it will explode, doing %0.2f temporal damage and %0.2f physical damage in a radius of 4.
		If the target dies while also under the effects of continuum destabilization, all explosion damage will be done as temporal damage.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[使目標所處的時空出現裂隙，每回合造成 %0.2f 時空傷害，持續 10 回合。如果目標在被標記時死亡，則會產生 4 碼半徑範圍的時空爆炸，造成 %0.2f 時空傷害和 %0.2f 物理傷害。 
		如果目標死亡時處於連續紊亂狀態，則爆炸產生的所有傷害會轉化爲時空傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Quantum Spike", "量子釘刺", "talent name")
t("%s has been pulled apart at a molecular level!", "%s 被分崩離析！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the quantum spike!", "%s抵抗了量子釘刺！", "logSeen")
t([[Attempts to pull the target apart at a molecular level, inflicting %0.2f temporal damage and %0.2f physical damage.  If the target ends up with low enough life (<20%%), it might be instantly killed.
		Quantum Spike deals 50%% additional damage to targets affected by temporal destabilization and/or continuum destabilization.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[試圖將目標分離爲分子狀態，造成 %0.2f 時空傷害和 %0.2f 物理傷害 , 技能結束後若目標生命值不足 20%% 則可能會被立刻殺死。 
		量子釘刺對受時空紊亂和/或連續紊亂的目標會多造成 50%%的傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


