section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/speed-control.lua"

t("Celerity", "迅捷", "talent name")
t("When you move you gain %d%% movement speed for %d turns.  This effect stacks up to three times but can only occur once per turn.", "當你移動時，你獲得 %d%% 移動速度，持續 %d 回合。  這個效果可以疊加三次，每回合只能觸發一次。", "tformat")
t("Time Dilation", "時間膨脹", "talent name")
t([[When you use a non-instant chronomancy spell you gain %d%% attack, spell, and mind speed for %d turns.  This effect stacks up to three times but can only occur once per turn.
		]], [[當你使用非瞬間時空系法術，你獲得 %d%% 戰鬥、施法和精神速度，持續 %d 回合。這個效果可以疊加三次，每回合只能觸發一次。
		]], "tformat")
t("Haste", "加速", "talent name")
t("Increases your global speed by %d%% for %d game turns.", "增加你的整體速度 %d%% ，持續 %d 遊戲回合。", "tformat")
t("Time Stop", "時間停止", "talent name")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#%s has stopped time!#LAST#", "#STEEL_BLUE#%s 停止了時間!#LAST#", "logSeen")
t("Gain %d turns.  During this time your damage will be reduced by %d%%.", "獲得 %d 個回合。在這段時間內，你造成的傷害減少 %d%% 。", "tformat")


