section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/spellbinding.lua"

t("Empower", "能量增幅", "talent name")
t([[Empowers the selected chronomancy spell, increasing spellpower when casting it by %d%%.
		Each spell can only be spellbound in one way at a time.
		
		Current Empowered Spell: %s]], [[強化指定的時空系法術，施放指定技能時法術強度增加 %d%% 。
		每個技能只能附加一種時空增效系效果。		
		當前強化法術： %s ]], "tformat")
t("Extension", "法術延展", "talent name")
t([[Extends the duration of the selected chronomancy spell by %d%%.
		Each spell can only be spellbound in one way at a time.
		
		Current Extended Spell: %s]], [[強化指定的時空系法術，延展指定法術的持續時間 %d%% 。
		每個技能只能附加一種時空增效系效果。				
		當前強化法術： %s ]], "tformat")
t("Matrix", "矩陣加速", "talent name")
t([[Reduces the cooldown of the selected chronomancy spell by %d%%.
		Each spell can only be spellbound in one way at a time.
		
		Current Matrix Spell: %s]], [[強化指定的時空系法術，減少指定法術的冷卻時間 %d%% 。
		每個技能只能附加一種時空增效系效果。	
		當前強化法術： %s]], "tformat")
t("Quicken", "迅捷施法", "talent name")
t("None", "無", "_t")
t([[Reduces the casting speed of the selected chronomancy spell by %d%%.
		Each spell can only be spellbound in one way at a time.
		
		Current Quickened Spell: %s]], [[強化指定的時空系法術，減少施放指定法術需要的時間 %d%% 。
		每個技能只能附加一種時空增效系效。
		
		當前強化法術： %s ]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/stasis.lua"

t("Spacetime Stability", "時空穩定", "talent name")
t([[You automatically adjust your Paradox %0.2f points towards your preferred Paradox each turn.
		While using Spacetime Tuning twice this value will instead be added to the amount you would normally tune.]], [[當時空調諧處於非激活狀態時，你的紊亂值每回合自動向設定值調整 %0.2f 點。
		處於激活狀態時，該效果加倍。]], "tformat")
t("Time Shield", "時間盾", "talent name")
t([[This intricate spell instantly erects a time shield around the caster, preventing any incoming damage and sending it forward in time.
		Once either the maximum damage (%d) is absorbed, or the time runs out (%d turns), the stored damage will return as a temporal restoration field over time (5 turns).
		Each turn the restoration field is active, you get healed for 10%% of the absorbed damage.
		While under the effect of Time Shield, all newly applied magical, physical and mental effects will have their durations reduced by %d%%.
		The shield's max absorption will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[這個複雜的法術會立刻在施法者身邊製造一個時空屏障，阻止受到的一切傷害，並將其送到將來。		一旦護盾吸收傷害達到最大值 ( %d )，或者持續時間結束 ( %d 回合 )，儲存的傷害將會返回變爲一個時空回覆場，持續五回合。
		每回合回覆場可以爲你回覆吸收傷害的 10%% 。
		當激活時光之盾時，所有新附加的魔法、物理和精神狀態的持續時間減少 %d%% 。
		護盾的最大吸收值受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stop", "時間靜止", "talent name")
t([[Inflicts %0.2f temporal damage, and attempts to stun all targets in a radius %d ball for %d turns.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[造成 %0.2f 時空傷害，並試圖震懾半徑 %d 碼範圍內所有目標 %d 回合。
		受法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Static History", "靜態歷史", "talent name")
t([[For the next %d turns you may not create minor anomalies.  You do not regain Paradox or lose the spell you're casting if a random anomaly would normally occur.
		This spell has no effect on major anomalies.]], [[接下來的 %d 回合中，你不會產生微小異變。  當隨機異變正常發生時，不會導致你獲得紊亂值或者施法失敗。
		這個技能對重大異變沒有影響。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/temporal-archery.lua"

t("Phase Shot", "相位射擊", "talent name")
t("You fire a shot that phases out of time and space allowing it to virtually ignore armor.  The shot will deal %d%% weapon damage as temporal damage to its target.", "你射出一枚在相位空間外的子彈，這使它可以忽視敵方護甲。此次射擊會對目標造成 %d%% 時空武器傷害。", "tformat")
t("Unerring Shot", "必中射擊", "talent name")
t("You focus your aim and fire a shot with great accuracy, inflicting %d%% weapon damage.  Afterwords your attack will remain improved for one turn as the chronomantic effects linger.", "你集中注意力射出極精準的一箭，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。接下來的一回合內，因時空延續，攻擊加成保留。", "tformat")
t("Perfect Aim", "完美瞄準", "talent name")
t([[You focus your aim, increasing your critical damage multiplier by %d%% and your physical and spell critical strike chance by %d%%
		The effect will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[集中你的注意力瞄準，增加你的暴擊加成 %d%% 並提高你的物理和法術暴擊率 %d%% 。
		受魔法影響，效果按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Quick Shot", "快速射擊", "talent name")
t([[You pause time around you long enough to fire a single shot, doing %d%% damage.
		The damage will scale with your Paradox and the cooldown will go down with more talent points invested.]], [[你暫停時間給你足夠的空閒射出一支箭，造成 %d%% 傷害。
		傷害受紊亂值影響，按比例加成，另外技能等級提高可以降低冷卻時間。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/temporal-combat.lua"

t("Fold Fate", "命運摺疊", "talent name")
t([[When you hit with Weapon Folding you have a %d%% chance of dealing an additional %0.2f temporal damage to enemies in a radius of %d.
		Affected targets may also have their physical and temporal resistance reduced by %d%% for %d turns.
		This effect has a cooldown.  If it triggers while on cooldown it will reduce the cooldown of Fold Gravity and Fold Warp by one turn.]], [[當你用武器摺疊命中時，有 %d%% 機率在半徑 %d 內造成額外 %0.2f 時空傷害。
		受影響的生物可能減少 %d%% 物理和時空抗性 %d 回合。
		這個效果有冷卻時間。當處於冷卻狀態被觸發時，會減少重力摺疊和扭曲摺疊 1 回合冷卻時間。]], "tformat", {1,3,2,4,5})
t("Fold Warp", "扭曲摺疊", "talent name")
t([[When you hit with Weapon Folding you have a %d%% chance of dealing an additional %0.2f physical and %0.2f temporal (warp) damage to enemies in a radius of %d.
		Each target hit may be stunned, blinded, pinned, or confused for %d turns.
		This effect has a cooldown.  If it triggers while on cooldown it will reduce the cooldown of Fold Gravity and Fold Fate by one turn.]], [[當你用武器摺疊命中時，有 %d%% 機率在半徑 %d 內造成額外 %0.2f 物理和 %0.2f 時空傷害。
		受影響的生物可能被震懾、致盲、定身或混亂 %d 回合。
		這個效果有冷卻時間。當處於冷卻狀態被觸發時，會減少重力摺疊和命運摺疊 1 回合冷卻時間。]], "tformat", {1,4,2,3,5})
t("Fold Gravity", "重力摺疊", "talent name")
t([[When you hit with Weapon Folding you have a %d%% chance of dealing an additional %0.2f physical (gravity) damage to enemies in a radius of %d.
		Affected targets may also be slowed, decreasing their global speed speed by %d%% for %d turns
		This effect has a cooldown.  If it triggers while on cooldown it will reduce the cooldown of Fold Fate and Fold Warp by one turn.]], [[當你用武器摺疊命中時，有 %d%% 機率在半徑 %d 內造成額外 %0.2f 物理( 重力) 傷害。
		受影響的生物可能被減速 %d%% ，持續 %d 回合。
		這個效果有冷卻時間。當處於冷卻狀態被觸發時，會減少扭曲摺疊和命運摺疊 1 回合冷卻時間。]], "tformat", {1,3,2,4,5})
t("Weapon Folding", "武器摺疊", "talent name")
t([[Folds a single dimension of your weapons (or ammo) upon itself, adding %0.2f temporal damage to your strikes.
		Additionally you have a %d%% chance to gain 10%% of a turn when your weapons hit.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[將時空摺疊在武器/彈藥上，造成額外 %0.2f 時空傷害。
		同時武器命中時你有 %d%% 機率獲得 10%% 回合的時間。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Invigorate", "鼓舞", "talent name")
t([[For the next %d turns, you recover %0.1f life and talents without fixed cooldowns will have their cooldowns refresh twice as fast as usual.
		The life regeneration will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[接下來的 %d 回合裏，你回覆 %0.1f 生命，同時不具有固定冷卻時間的技能會加倍冷卻速度。
		生命回覆受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Weapon Manifold", "多態武器", "talent name")
t([[You now have a %d%% chance to Fold Fate, Gravity, or Warp into your Weapon Folding damage.
		
		Fold Fate: Deals %0.2f temporal damage to enemies in a radius of %d.  Affected targets may lose %d%% physical and temporal resistance for %d turns.
		Fold Warp: Deals %0.2f physical and %0.2f temporal damage to enemies in a radius of %d.  Affected targets may be stunned, blinded, confused, or pinned for %d turns.
		Fold Gravity: Deals %0.2f physical damage to enemies in a radius of %d.  Affected targets will be slowed (%d%%) for %d turns.
		
		Each Fold has an eight turn cooldown.  If an effect would be triggered while on cooldown it will reduce the cooldown of the other two Folds by one turn.]], [[你現在有 %d%% 機率將命運、重力或扭曲之力摺疊進你的武器。
		命運：半徑 %d 內造成 %0.2f 時空傷害，並降低 %d%% 物理和時空抗性，持續 %d 回合。
		扭曲：半徑 %d 內造成 %0.2f 物理 %0.2f 時空傷害，並可能震懾、致盲、混亂或者定身 %d 回合。
		重力：半徑 %d 內造成 %0.2f 物理傷害，並減速（ %d%% ） %d 回合。
		每項效果有 8 回合冷卻時間。
		當處於冷卻中的效果被觸發時，將減少另外兩個效果的冷卻 1 回合。]], "tformat", {1,3,2,4,5,8,6,7,9,11,10,12,13})
t("Breach", "破滅", "talent name")
t("You require a weapon to use this talent.", "你需要武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Attack the target with either your ranged or melee weapons for %d%% damage.
		If the attack hits you'll breach the target's immunities, reducing armor hardiness, stun, pin, blindness, and confusion immunity by 50%% for %d turns.
		Breach chance scales with your Spellpower.]], [[ 使用遠程或近戰武器攻擊目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		如果攻擊命中，你將摧毀目標的防禦，對方的護甲強度，震懾、定身、致盲、混亂免疫降低 50%% ，持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/temporal-hounds.lua"

t("A trained hound that appears to be all at once a little puppy and a toothless old dog.", "一條受訓的獵犬，它的形態在小狗崽到掉牙的老狗之間來回切換", "_t")
t("temporal-hound", "時空守衛", "_t")
t("Temporal Hounds", "時空獵犬", "talent name")
t([[Upon activation summon a Temporal Hound.  Every %d turns another hound will be summoned, up to a maximum of three hounds. If a hound dies you'll summon a new hound in %d turns.  
		Your hounds inherit your increased damage percent, have %d%% physical resistance and %d%% temporal resistance, and are immune to teleportation effects.
		Hounds will get, %d Strength, %d Dexterity, %d Constitution, %d Magic, %d Willpower, and %d Cunning, based on your Magic stat.]], [[召喚一條時空獵犬。
		每隔 %d 回合召喚另一條時空獵犬，直至最多 3 條。
		當一條獵犬死去時，你將在 %d 回合內召喚一條新的獵犬。
		你獵犬繼承你的傷害加成，有 %d%% 物理和 %d%% 時空抗性，對傳送效果免疫。
		獵犬將擁有 %d 力量， %d 敏捷， %d 體質， %d 魔法， %d 意志和 %d 靈巧，基於你的魔法。]], "tformat")
t("Command Hounds: Blink", "閃爍命令", "talent name")
t("Temporal Hounds must be sustained to cast this spell.", "必須開啓時空獵犬來使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You do not have line of sight.", "你沒有視線", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t([[Command your Temporal Hounds to teleport to the targeted location.  If you target an enemy your hounds will set that enemy as their target.
		When you learn this talent, your hounds gain %d defense and %d%% resist all after any teleport.
		At talent level five, if you're not at your maximum number of hounds when you cast this spell a new one will be summoned.
		The teleportation bonuses scale with your Spellpower.]], [[命令你的時空獵犬傳送至指定位置。
		如果你指定敵人爲目標，獵犬們將視其爲目標攻擊。
		當你學會該技能後，你的獵犬在傳送後獲得 %d 閃避和 %d%% 全體抗性。
		技能等級 5 時，若獵犬數小於最大召喚數目，使用該技能時將召喚一條新獵犬。
		傳送加成受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Temporal Vigour", "時空活力", "talent name")
t([[Your hounds can now survive for up to %d turns after their hit points are reduced below 1.  While in this state they deal 50%% less damage but are immune to additional damage.
		Command Blink will now regenerate your hounds for %d life per turn and increase their global speed by %d%% for five turns.  Hounds below 1 life when this effect occurs will have the bonuses doubled.
		When you learn this talent, your hounds gain %d%% stun, blind, confusion, and pin resistance.
		The regeneration scales with your Spellpower.]], [[你的獵犬現在在生命值降至 1 以下後還能生存至多 %d 回合，免疫所有傷害但造成的傷害減少 50%% 。
		閃爍命令將能讓獵犬每回合回覆 %d 生命並整體速度提升 %d%%，持續 5 回合。生命 1 以下的獵犬將加倍該效果。
		當你學會該技能後，你的獵犬獲得 %d%% 震懾致盲混亂定身免疫。
		生命回覆受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Command Hounds: Breathe", "吐息命令", "talent name")
t("You must have temporal hounds to use this talent.", "你必須擁有時空獵犬來使用該技能", "logPlayer")
t([[Command your Temporal Hounds to breathe time, dealing %0.2f temporal damage and reducing the three highest stats of all targets in a radius %d cone.
		Affected targets will have their stats reduced by %d for %d turns.  You are immune to the breath of your own hounds and your hounds are immune to stat damage from other hounds.
		When you learn this talent, your hounds gain %d%% temporal damage affinity.]], [[命令獵犬們使用時光吐息，錐形範圍半徑 %d 範圍內造成 %0.2f 時空傷害並減少目標三項最高屬性值 %d 點 %d 回合。
		你免疫自己獵犬的吐息。自己的獵犬免疫其他獵犬的屬性降低效果。
		當你學會該技能後，獵犬們獲得 %d%% 時空傷害吸收。]], "tformat", {2,1,3,4,5})


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/threaded-combat.lua"

t("Thread Walk", "空間行走", "talent name")
t("range %d", "範圍 %d", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t("You cannot use Thread Walk without an appropriate weapon!", "你需要裝備合適的武器來使用該技能", "logPlayer")
t([[Attack with your bow or dual-weapons for %d%% damage.  If you shoot an arrow you'll teleport near the target location.  If you use your dual-weapons you'll teleport up to your bow's range away.
		Additionally you now go Out of Phase for five turns after any teleport, gaining %d defense and %d%% resist all.
		The Out of Phase bonuses will scale with your Magic stat.]], [[使用弓或雙持武器攻擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		如果使用弓箭，則你被傳送到目標附近。否則傳送到和目標距離等於弓的射程的位置。
		同時，你獲得傳送後加成：增加 %d 閃避和 %d%% 全體抗性。
		傳送後加成受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blended Threads", "混合螺旋", "talent name")
t([[Each time you hit with an arrow you reduce the cooldown of one Blade Threading talent on cooldown by one turn.
		Each time you hit with a melee weapon you reduce the cooldown of one Bow Threading talent on cooldown by one turn.
		This effect can only occur %d times per turn.]], [[每次你的箭命中時，減少一個螺旋靈刃系技能一回合的冷卻。
		每次你的近戰武器命中時，減少一個螺旋靈弓系技能一回合的冷卻。
		這個效果一回合最多觸發 %d 次。]], "tformat")
t("Thread the Needle", "針型聚焦", "talent name")
t("You require a weapon to use this talent.", "你需要武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Thread the Needle without an appropriate weapon!", "你需要裝備合適的武器來使用該技能", "logPlayer")
t("Attack with your bow or dual-weapons for %d%% damage.  If you use your bow you'll shoot all targets in a beam.  If you use your dual-weapons you'll attack all targets within a radius of one around you.", [[使用弓箭或者雙持武器攻擊造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		如果使用弓箭，你的箭將成爲具有穿透性的射線。
		如果使用雙持武器，則攻擊你周圍半徑 1 的所有目標。]], "tformat")
t("Warden's Call", "守衛呼喚", "talent name")
t("%s calls forth a temporal warden from another timeline.", "%s 從另一條時間線召喚出時空守衛。", "logSeen")
t([[When you hit with a melee or arrow attack, there is a %d%% chance that a warden will appear from another timeline to attack a random enemy.
		The summoned warden will attempt a melee attack if you made an arrow attack, or an arrow attack if you made a melee attack.
		These wardens are out of phase with your reality and deal %d%% less damage, and their arrows will pass through friendly targets.
		A warden can only be summoned this way once per turn and they return to their own timeline after attacking.]], [[當你用弓箭或近戰武器攻擊時，有 %d%% 機率讓一個時空守衛從另一個時空線穿越過來幫助你，攻擊或者射擊目標。
		守衛處於相位空間外，傷害減少 %d%% ，守衛的弓箭能穿過友方生物。
		這個效果每回合只能觸發一次，守衛在攻擊後會消失。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/timeline-threading.lua"

t("Rethread", "重組", "talent name")
t([[Rethread the timeline, dealing %0.2f temporal damage to the target before moving on to a second target.
		Rethread can hit up to %d targets up to 10 grids apart, and will never hit the same one twice; nor will it hit the caster.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[重組時間線，對一個目標造成 %0.2f 時空傷害。然後再對半徑 10 內的另一個目標造成等量傷害。
		重組能擊中至多 %d 個目標，不會重複擊中同一個目標，也不會擊中施法者。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Temporal Fugue", "時間複製", "talent name")
t("%s's Fugue Clone", "%s 的時間複製體", "tformat")
t("The real %s... or so %s says.", "真正的%s... 或者%s這樣說。", "tformat")
t("Fugue Clone", "時間複製", "_t")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t([[For the next %d turns two alternate versions of you enter your timeline.  While the effect is active all damage done by you or your copies is reduced by two thirds and all damage received is split between the three of you.
		Temporal Fugue does not normally cooldown while active.  You may take direct control of your clones, give them orders, and set their talent usage.
		Damage you deal to Fugue Clones or that they deal to you or each other is reduced to zero.]], [[接下來 %d 回合， 2 個你的鏡像進入你的時間線。
		當技能生效時，所有你或者你的鏡像造成的傷害會減少 2/3 ，所有你或者鏡像受到的傷害會由你們三者均分。
		開啓時該技能不會正常冷卻。你能直接控制你的鏡像，給他們指令，或者調整技能使用策略。
		你和鏡像不會互相傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Braid Lifelines", "生命線編織", "talent name")
t([[Your Rethread now braids the lifelines of all targets it hits for %d turns.  Braided targets take %d%% of all damage dealt to other braided targets.
		The amount of damage shared will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[你的重組技能將目標的生命線編織在一起 %d 回合。
		受影響的生物將受到其他受影響生物受到的 %d%% 傷害.
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Cease to Exist", "存在抹殺", "talent name")
t("The timeline is too fractured to do this now.", "目前的時間線過於破碎。", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#%s never existed, this never happened!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#%s 不存在，也不會發生！", "logSeen")
t("#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#%s tries to remove %sself from existance!", "#LIGHT_STELL_BLUE#%s試圖抹殺%s自己！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists!", "%s抵抗了效果！", "logSeen")
t([[Over the next %d turns, you attempt to remove the target from the timeline, lowering its resistance to physical and temporal damage by %d%%.
		If you manage to kill the target while the spell is in effect, you'll be returned to the point in time you cast this spell and the target will be slain.
		This spell splits the timeline.  Attempting to use another spell that also splits the timeline while this effect is active will be unsuccessful.
		The resistance penalty will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[接下來 %d 回合，你嘗試抹殺目標在當前時間線的存在，降低目標物理和時空抗性 %d%% 。
		如果你在法術生效期間擊殺了目標，你將會返回到你釋放該法術的時間點，而目標將被殺死。
		這個法術分離的時間線。法術生效期間，其餘分離時間線的法術將無法成功試用。
		抗性減少程度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/chronomancy/timetravel.lua"

t("Temporal Bolt", "時空之箭", "_t")
t([[Pull a bolt of temporal energy back through time.  The bolt will home in on your location, dealing %0.2f temporal damage to targets, and reducing the cooldown of one chronomancy talent on cooldown by one turn per enemy hit.
		The bolt gains 5%% damage each time it moves and the damage will scale with your Spellpower.
		At talent level five cooldowns are reduced by two.]], [[ 將一道時空之箭射入時間線中。
		時空之箭會返回你的位置，對路徑上目標造成 %0.2f 時空傷害。每飛行 1 格，傷害增加 5%% 。
		每命中一個目標，你隨機一個時空技能冷卻時間減少1回合。
		技能等級 5 時，改爲減少 2 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Time Skip", "時間跳躍", "talent name")
t("%s is immune!", "%s 免疫了!", "logSeen")
t("%s resists!", "%s抵抗了效果！", "logSeen")
t("Something has prevented the timetravel.", "某物阻止了時空旅行", "logPlayer")
t("temporal instability", "時間不穩定性", "_t")
t("%s has moved forward in time!", "%s的時間向前推移！", "logSeen")
t([[Inflicts %0.2f temporal damage.  If your target survives, it may be removed from time for %d turns.
		The damage will scale with your Spellpower.]], [[造成 %0.2f 時空傷害。如果你的目標存活，他將被從這個時空放逐 %d 回合。
		傷害受到法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Temporal Reprieve", "時空避難所", "talent name")
t("This talent cannot be used from within the reprieve.", "該技能不能在此時使用。", "logPlayer")
t("This talent cannot be used here.", "該技能不能在此處使用。", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles...", "法術失敗了...", "logPlayer")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#You time travel to a quiet place.", "#STEEL_BLUE#你時空旅行到了一個寂靜的地方。", "logPlayer")
t("Some rookie paradox mage is about to find out that the standard-issue Temporal Reprieve takes you to a random safe-zone, not a fixed one, and left the contents of their pack strewn about the place. Nearly all of it is equipment that your transmutation chest won't process and is unusable by anything with less than twelve limbs, so you kick most of it into the void, but a crumpled note catches your eye...", "有些新手時空法師還不知道，通常的時空避難所把你帶到的是一個隨機的安全的地方，而不是一個固定的地方，結果他們就把自己揹包裏的東西散落在了這裏。你發現這些裝備都是些十二隻腳的人才能用到的東西，並且你的轉化之盒也處理不了，就一腳把它們踢進了虛空之中，然而，一張殘破的筆記吸引了你的注意力…", "_t")
t("What the... ugh.", "這什麼鬼……額。", "_t")
t("Transport yourself to a safe place for %d turns.", "將自己傳送至安全的位置，停留 %d 回合.", "tformat")
t("Echoes From The Past", "往昔迴響", "talent name")
t([[Creates a temporal echo in a radius of %d around you.  Affected targets take %0.2f temporal damage, as well as up to %d%% of the difference between their current life and max life as additional temporal damage.
		The additional damage will be divided by the target's rank and the damage scales with your Spellpower.]], [[在半徑 %d 的範圍內製造一次時空迴響。
		範圍內的生物將受到 %0.2f 時空傷害，然後額外受到等於當前已損失生命值 %d%% 的傷害。
		額外傷害將被對面怪物的階級除。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/blight.lua"

t("Dark Ritual", "黑暗儀式", "talent name")
t([[Increases your spell critical damage multiplier by %d%%.
		The multiplier will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[增加 %d%% 法術暴擊倍率。 
		倍率受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Corrupted Negation", "能量腐蝕", "talent name")
t([[Project a corrupted blast of power that removes up to %d magical or physical effects or any type of sustain and deals %0.2f blight damage to any creatures caught in the radius 3 ball.
		For each effect, the creature has a chance to resist based on its spell save.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在 3 碼球形範圍內製造一個墮落能量球，移除範圍內任意怪物至多 %d 種魔法或物理效果或持續技能，並造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。 
		每除去一個效果時，基於法術豁免，目標都有一定概率抵抗。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Corrosive Worm", "腐蝕蠕蟲", "talent name")
t([[Infects the target with a corrosive worm for 6 turns that reduces blight and acid resistance by %d%% and feeds off damage taken.
		When this effect ends or the target dies the worm will explode, dealing %d acid damage in a 4 radius ball. This damage will increase by %d%% of all damage taken while infected.
		The damage dealt by the effect will increase with spellpower.]], [[用腐蝕蠕蟲感染目標 6 回合，降低目標 %d%% 酸性枯萎抗性。
		效果結束或者目標死亡時會產生爆炸，在 4 碼半徑內造成 %d 酸性傷害。同時，感染期內目標受到的傷害將以 %d%% 比例增加至爆炸傷害中。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Poison Storm", "劇毒風暴", "talent name")
t([[A furious storm of blighted poison rages around the caster in a radius of %d for %d turns.  Each creature hit by the storm takes %0.2f blight damage and is poisoned for %0.2f blight damage over 4 turns.
		At talent level 2 you have a chance to inflict Insidious Blight, which reduces healing by %d%%.
		At talent level 4 you have a chance to inflict Numbing Blight, which reduces all damage dealt by %d%%.
		At talent level 6 you have a chance to inflict Crippling Blight, which causes talents to have a %d%% chance of failure.
		Each possible effect is equally likely.
		The poison damage dealt is capable of a critical strike.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[一股強烈的劇毒風暴圍繞着施法者，半徑 %d 持續 %d 回合。風暴內的生物將進入中毒狀態，受到 %0.2f 枯萎傷害並中毒 4 回合受到額外 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。
		技能等級 2 時有機率觸發陰險毒素效果，降低 %d%% 治療係數。
		技能等級 4 時有機率觸發麻痹毒素效果，降低 %d%% 傷害。
		技能等級 6 時有機率觸發致殘毒素效果， %d%% 機率使用技能失敗。
		中毒機率在可能的毒素效果中平分。
		毒素傷害可以暴擊。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/blood.lua"

t("Blood Spray", "鮮血噴射", "talent name")
t([[You extract corrupted blood from your own body, hitting everything in a frontal cone of radius %d for %0.2f blight damage.
		Each creature hit has a %d%% chance of being infected by a random disease, doing %0.2f blight damage and weakening either Constitution, Strength or Dexterity for 6 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你從自身射出墮落之血，對前方 %d 碼半徑錐形範圍敵人造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。 
		每個受影響的單位有 %d%% 概率感染 1 種隨機疾病，受到 %0.2f 枯萎傷害，並且隨機弱化目標體質、力量和敏捷中的一項屬性，持續 6 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Grasp", "鮮血支配", "talent name")
t([[Project a bolt of corrupted blood, doing %0.2f blight damage and healing you for 20%% the damage dealt.
			50%% of the damage dealt will be gained as maximum life for 7 turns (before the healing).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[釋放一個墮落血球，造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害並恢復你 20%% 傷害值的生命。 
		造成的傷害的 50%% 會增加你的最大生命值，持續 7 回合。（這一效果發生在治療之前）
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Boil", "鮮血沸騰", "talent name")
t([[Make the impure blood of all creatures around you in radius %d boil.
				Each enemy afflicted by a disease, poison, or wound will have one removed at random dealing %0.2f blight damage, healing you for %d, and slowing them by %d%% for 5 turns.
			The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你周圍半徑 %d 內生物的不純淨的血液沸騰。
		被疾病、毒素或傷口影響的敵人將會隨機移除一個上述效果，受到 %0.2f 枯萎傷害，使你恢復 %d 生命值，並被減速 %d%% 5 回合。
		傷害受你的法術強度影響。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Fury", "鮮血狂怒", "talent name")
t([[Concentrate on the corruption you bring, increasing your spell critical chance by %d%%.
		Each time your spells go critical, you enter a blood rage for 5 turns, increasing your blight and acid damage by %d%%.
		The critical chance and damage increase will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[專注於你帶來的腐蝕，提高你 %d%% 法術暴擊率。 
		每當你的法術打出暴擊時，你進入嗜血狀態 5 回合，增加你 %d%% 枯萎和酸性傷害。 
		暴擊率和傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/bone.lua"

t("Bone Spear", "白骨之矛", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a spear of bones, doing %0.2f physical damage to all targets in a line.  Each target takes an additional %d%% damage for each magical debuff they are afflicted with up to a max of %d%% (%d).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 釋放一根骨矛，對一條線上的目標造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。這些目標每具有一個魔法負面效果，就額外受到 %d%% 的傷害，最多達到 %d%%（ %d ）。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bone Grab", "白骨之握", "talent name")
t("%s resists the pin!", "%s抵抗了定身！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists being teleported by Bone Grab!", "%s抵抗了骨矛的傳送!", "logSeen")
t([[Grab a target and teleport it to your side or if adjacent up to 6 spaces away from you, pinning it there with a bone rising from the ground for %d turns.
		The bone will also deal %0.2f physical damage.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[抓住目標將其傳送到你的身邊，或將身邊的目標丟到最多 6 格之外。從地上冒出一根骨刺，將其定在那裏，持續 %d 回合。
		骨刺同時也會造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bone Spike", "白骨尖刺", "talent name")
t([[Whenever you use a non-instant talent you launch a spear of bone at all enemies afflicted by 3 or more magical detrimental effects dealing %d physical damage to all enemies it passes through.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[每當你使用一個非瞬間的技能，你朝周圍所有具有 3 個或以上魔法負面效果的敵人射出骨矛，對一條直線上的敵人造成 %d 傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bone Shield", "白骨護盾", "talent name")
t("#SLATE#(%d to bones)#LAST#", "#SLATE#(%d 骨盾)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Bone shields start circling around you. They will each fully absorb one instance of damage.
		%d shield(s) will be generated when first activated.
		Then every %d turns a new one will be created if not full.
		This will only trigger on hits over %d damage based on Spellpower.]], [[製造一圈白骨護盾圍繞你。每個護盾能完全吸收一次攻擊傷害。
		啓動時製造 %d 個骨盾。
		如果你的骨盾數量不滿，每 %d 個回合將會自動補充一層骨盾。
		這一技能只會在攻擊傷害超過 %d 時觸發，閾值受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


