t("Harness the power of blood, both your own and your foes'.", " 操縱你和你目標鮮血的力量。", "_t")
t("blood", "血", "_t")
t("Bring corruption and decay to all who oppose you.", " 使任何敵對你的目標腐敗和衰弱。", "_t")
