section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/curses.lua"

t("Curse of Defenselessness", "衰竭詛咒", "talent name")
t([[Curses your target, decreasing its Defense and all saves by %d for 5 turns.  This cannot be saved against.
		The effects will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[詛咒目標，減少它 %d 點閃避和所有豁免，持續 5 回合。這一效果不能豁免。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Curse of Impotence", "虛弱詛咒", "talent name")
t([[Curses your target, decreasing all damage it does by %d%% for 10 turns.
		The effects will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[詛咒目標，減少它 %d%% 所有傷害，持續 10 回合。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Curse of Death", "死亡詛咒", "talent name")
t([[Curses your target, preventing normal life regeneration and dealing %0.2f darkness damage over 10 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[詛咒目標，阻止其生命值自然恢復，並在10回合內造成 %0.2f點暗影傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Curse of Vulnerability", "弱點詛咒", "talent name")
t([[Curses your target, decreasing all its resistances by %d%% for 7 turns.
		The effect will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[詛咒目標，減少其 %d%% 所有抵抗，持續 7 回合。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/hexes.lua"

t("Pacification Hex", "寧神邪術", "talent name")
t([[Hexes your target, dazing it and everything in a 2 radius ball around it for 3 turns and giving a %d%% chance to daze affected targets again each turn for 20 turns.
		The chance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[對目標施放邪術，眩暈它和 2 碼球形範圍內的一切，持續 3 回合。同時，每回合有 %d%% 概率再次眩暈目標，持續 20 回合。 
		概率受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Burning Hex", "燃燒邪術", "talent name")
t([[Hexes your target and everything within a radius 2 ball around it for 20 turns. Each time an affected target uses a resource (stamina, mana, vim, ...), it takes %0.2f fire damage.
		In addition, the cooldown of any talent used while so hexed is increased by %d%% + 1 turn.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[對目標施放邪術，詛咒它和 2 碼球形範圍內的一切，持續 20 回合。每次受影響的對象消耗資源（體力、法力、活力等）時，將會受到 %0.2f 點火焰傷害。 
		同時，對方使用的技能的冷卻時間延長 %d%% +1 個回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Empathic Hex", "轉移邪術", "talent name")
t([[Hexes your target and everything within a radius 2 ball around it. Each time they do damage, they take %d%% of the same damage for 20 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[對目標施放邪術，詛咒目標和 2 碼球形範圍內的一切。每當目標造成傷害時，它們也會受到 %d%% 相同傷害，持續 20 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Domination Hex", "支配邪術", "talent name")
t([[Hexes your target, forcing it to be your thrall for %d turns.
		If you damage the target, it will be freed from the hex.]], [[對目標施放邪術，使它成爲你的奴隸，持續 %d 回合。 
		如果你對目標造成傷害，則目標會脫離詛咒。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/plague.lua"

t("Virulent Disease", "劇毒瘟疫", "talent name")
t([[Whenever you deal non-disease blight damage you apply a disease dealing %0.2f blight damage per turn for 6 turns and reducing one of its physical stats (strength, constitution, dexterity) by %d. The three diseases can stack.
		Virulent Disease will always try to apply a disease the target does not currently have, and also one that will have the most debilitating effect for the target.
		This disease will try to prioritize being applied to an enemy with a high disease count near the target.
		The effect will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[每當你造成一個非疾病的枯萎傷害時，你將會對目標施加一項疾病，每回合造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害，持續 6 回合，並降低其一項物理能力值（力量、體質、敏捷） %d 。三種疾病可以疊加。
		劇毒瘟疫總是會使目標感染一項其所沒有的疾病，並試圖附加一項對目標有着最大負面效果的疾病。
		疾病會優先附加在目標周圍感染疾病數量最多的單位身上。
		疾病效果隨法術強度提升。]], "tformat")
t("Cyst Burst", "瘟疫爆發", "talent name")
t([[Make your target's diseases burst, doing %0.2f blight damage for each disease it is infected with.
		This will also spread any diseases to any nearby foes in a radius of %d with a minimum duration of 6.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使目標的疾病爆發，每種疾病造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。 
		同時會向 %d 碼半徑範圍內任意敵人散播衰老、虛弱、腐爛或傳染性疾病，疾病的持續時間最少爲6回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Catalepsy", "僵硬瘟疫", "talent name")
t("Diseases #DARK_GREEN#BURN THROUGH#LAST# %s!", "疾病在 %s 身上 #DARK_GREEN#燃燒#LAST# !", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the stun!", "%s抵抗了震懾！", "logSeen")
t("All your foes within a radius %d ball infected with a disease enter a cataleptic state, stunning them for %d turns and dealing %d%% of all remaining disease damage instantly.", "所有 %d 碼球形範圍內感染疾病的目標進入僵硬狀態，震懾它們 %d 回合並立即爆發 %d%% 剩餘所有疾病傷害。", "tformat")
t("Epidemic", "傳染病", "talent name")
t("The diseases of %s spread!", "%s的疾病在傳播！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the disease!", "%s抵抗了疫病！", "logSeen")
t([[Infects the target with a very contagious disease, doing %0.2f damage per turn for 6 turns.
		If any blight damage from non-diseases hits the target, the epidemic may activate and spread a random disease to nearby targets within a radius 2 ball.
		The chance to spread increases with the blight damage dealt and is 100%% if it is at least %d%% of the target's maximum life.
		Creatures suffering from that disease will also suffer healing reduction (%d%%) and diseases immunity reduction (%d%%).
		Epidemic is an extremely potent disease; as such, it fully ignores the target's diseases immunity.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower, and the spread chance increases with the amount of blight damage dealt.]], [[使目標感染 1 種傳染性極強的疾病，每回合造成 %0.2f 傷害，持續 6 回合。 
		如果目標受到非疾病造成的任何枯萎傷害，則感染者會自動向周圍 2 碼球形範圍目標散播一種隨機疾病。
		疾病傳播概率受造成的枯萎傷害影響，且當枯萎傷害超過最大生命值 %d%% 時傳播機率爲 100%% 。
		任何感染疾病單位同時會減少 %d%% 治療效果和 %d%% 疾病免疫。 
		傳染病是一種極強的疾病，以至於它可以完全忽略目標的疾病免疫。
		傷害受法術強度加成；傳染疾病的概率受枯萎傷害加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/reaving-combat.lua"

t("Corrupted Strength", "墮落力量", "talent name")
t([[Allows you to dual wield any type of one handed weapons, and increases the damage of the off-hand weapon to %d%%.
		Also, casting a spell (which uses a turn) will give a free melee attack at a random target in melee range for %d%% blight damage.]], [[允許你雙持單手武器並使副手武器傷害增加至 %d%% 。 
		同時每釋放 1 個法術（消耗 1 回合）會給予近戰範圍內的 1 個隨機目標一次附加攻擊，造成 %d%% 枯萎傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Bloodlust", "嗜血殺戮", "talent name")
t([[Each time you hit an enemy with a melee weapon you enter a bloodlust-infused frenzy, increasing your Spellpower by %0.1f.
		This effect stacks up to 10 times for a total Spellpower gain of %d.
		The frenzy lasts 3 turns.]], [[每當你使用近戰武器擊中一個目標，你進入嗜血狀態，增加你的法術強度 %0.1f 。
		這一效果最多疊加 10 層，共獲得 %d 法術強度。
		嗜血狀態持續 3 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Carrier", "攜帶者", "talent name")
t([[You gain a %d%% resistance to diseases, and each of your melee attacks have a %d%% chance to spread any diseases on your target.
		(As the Epidemic talent with the melee attack treated like blight damage.)]], "你增加 %d%% 疾病抵抗並有 %d%% 概率在近戰時散播你目標身上現有的疾病。", "tformat")
t("Acid Blood", "酸性血液", "talent name")
t([[Your blood turns into an acidic mixture. When you get hit, the attacker is splashed with acid.
		This deals %0.2f acid damage each turn for 5 turns, and reduces the attacker's Accuracy by %d.
		At level 3, it will also reduce Armour by %d for 5 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的血液變成酸性混合物。當你受傷害時，攻擊者會受到酸性濺射。 
		每回合濺射會造成 %0.2f 酸性傷害，持續 5 回合。 
		同時減少攻擊者 %d 點命中。 
		在等級 3 時，酸性濺射會減少目標 %d 點護甲持續 5 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/rot.lua"

t("Infectious Bite", "傳染性啃咬", "talent name")
t("@Source@ bites blight poison into @target@.", "@Source@將枯萎毒素注入 @target@。", "_t")
t([[Bite the target, dealing %d%% melee damage  
		If the attack hits you'll inject blight poison into the target, dealing %0.2f blight damage and a further %0.2f blight damage over 4 turns.
		The bonus damage improves with your Spellpower.]], [[啃咬目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。 
		如果攻擊擊中目標你會注入瘟疫病毒, 造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害並在 4 回合內造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("A worm spawned from a damaged horror.  Destroying it may have consequences.", "蟲子從受傷的恐魔身上產生，消滅它會帶來某些後果。", "_t")
t("%s exudes a corrupted gas as it dies.", "%s死亡時釋放出腐氣。", "logSeen")
t("Summon", "召喚", "_t")
t("Infestation", "侵擾", "talent name")
t([[Your body has become a mass of living corruption, increasing your blight and acid resistance by %d%% and blight affinity by %d%%.
On taking damage greater than 15%% of your maximum health, the damage will be reduced by %d%% and a carrion worm mass will burst forth onto a nearby tile, attacking your foes for 5 turns.
You can never have more than 5 worms active from any source at a time.
When a carrion worm dies it will explode into a radius 2 pool of blight for 5 turns, dealing %0.2f blight damage each turn and healing you for 33%% of that amount.]], [[你的身體已經腐敗 ,增加 %d%% 枯萎和酸性抗性 , %d%% 枯萎傷害吸收。
		每次生命值損失大於 15%% 時,傷害將減少 %d%% ，同時在相鄰的格子生成蠕蟲, 攻擊你的敵人 5 回合。
		你同時只能擁有 5 只蠕蟲。
		蠕蟲死亡時將爆炸，產生半徑 2 的枯萎毒池，持續 5 回合，造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害並治療你 33%% 傷害量。]], "tformat")
t("Worm Walk", "蠕蟲行走", "talent name")
t("You do not have line of sight to this location.", "你沒有這個位置的視野。", "logPlayer")
t("The worm walk fizzles!", "蠕蟲行走失敗了!", "logSeen")
t([[You disperse into a mass of carrion worms, reforming near the target location (%d teleport accuracy).
If used on a worm mass, you merge with it, moving to it's location, healing you for %d, restoring %d vim, and destroying the mass.]], [[你解體爲蠕蟲，並在目標處合併。（誤差 %d ）
如果對蠕蟲團使用，你和它合體，治療 %d 生命值 , 回覆 %d 活力。]], "tformat")
t("Pestilent Blight", "致命枯萎", "talent name")
t([[You have a %d%% chance on dealing blight damage to cause the target to rot away, silencing, disarming, blinding or pinning them for %d turns. This effect has a cooldown.
At talent level 4, this affects targets in a radius 1 ball.
Your worms also have a %d%% chance to blind, silence, disarm or pin with their melee attacks, lasting 2 turns.
The chance to apply this effect will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[每次造成枯萎傷害，有 %d%% 機率令目標腐爛，沉默、致盲、繳械或者定身 %d 回合。該效果有冷卻時間。
技能等級 4 時，該效果對半徑 1 內所有目標有效。
同時，你的蠕蟲在近戰攻擊中有 %d%% 機率附加沉默、致盲、繳械或定身效果，持續 2 回合。
負面狀態施加成功率受法術強度影響。]], "tformat")
t("Worm Rot", "腐肉蟲", "talent name")
t("%s resists the worm rot!", "%s抵抗了腐肉蟲！", "logSeen")
t([[Infects the target with parasitic carrion worm larvae for 5 turns.  Each turn the disease will remove a beneficial physical effect and deal %0.2f acid and %0.2f blight damage.
If not cleared after five turns it will inflict %0.2f blight damage as the larvae hatch, removing the effect but spawning a full grown carrion worm mass near the target's location.
Even if this disease is removed early, there is still a %d%% chance for the larvae to hatch.
You can never have more than 5 worms active from any source at a time.
The damage dealt will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使目標感染腐肉寄生幼蟲持續 5 回合。每回合會移除目標一個物理增益效果並造成 %0.2f 酸系和 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。 
		如果 5 回合後未被清除則幼蟲會孵化造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害，移除這個效果但是會在目標處成長爲一條成熟的腐肉蟲。
		即使這個疾病被移除了，腐肉蟲仍然有 %d%% 的機率腐化。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/sanguisuge.lua"

t("Drain", "枯萎吸收", "talent name")
t([[Fires a bolt of blight, doing %0.2f blight damage and replenishing 20%% of it as vim energy.
		The amount of vim regained depends on the target's rank (higher ranks give more vim).
		The effect will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[射出 1 枚枯萎之球，對目標造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。同時補充 20%% 傷害值作爲活力。 
		活力回覆量受目標分級影響（高級怪提供更多活力）。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bloodcasting", "血祭施法", "talent name")
t("The cost of using life instead of vim for talents is reduced to %d%%.", "使用生命值取代活力值釋放技能時，生命值消耗減少到 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Absorb Life", "生命吞噬", "talent name")
t([[Absorbs the life force of your foes as you kill them.
		As long as this talent is active, vim will decrease by 0.5 per turn and increase by %0.1f for each kill of a non-undead creature (in addition to the usual increase based on Willpower).]], [[當你殺死敵人時，你會吸收目標生命。 
		當此技能激活時，每回合會消耗 0.5 點活力；當你殺死一個非不死族單位時，會獲得 %0.1f 點活力（此外自然增長受意志影響）。]], "tformat")
t("Life Tap", "生命分流", "talent name")
t([[Feed on the pain you cause your foes.
			For 2 turns you gain %d%% lifesteal on all damage dealt.
			The lifesteal will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[從你對敵人的痛苦中汲取力量。
			在 2 回合內，你的所有傷害獲得 %d%% 的吸血。
			吸血比例受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/scourge.lua"

t("Virulent Strike", "撕裂", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Virulent Strike without two weapons!", "你需要兩把武器來使用撕裂技能！", "logPlayer")
t("Strike the target with both weapons dealing %d%% damage with each hit.  Each strike that hits will increase the duration of the lowest duration disease effect by %d.", "向目標揮舞兩把武器，每次攻擊造成 %d%% 傷害，每次攻擊將會使目標身上持續時間最短的疾病效果的持續時間延長 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Ruin", "毀傷", "talent name")
t([[Concentrate on the corruption you bring, enhancing each of your melee strikes with %0.2f blight damage (which also heals you for %0.2f each hit).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[專注於你帶來的瘟疫，每次近戰攻擊會造成 %0.2f 枯萎傷害（同時每擊恢復你 %0.2f 生命值）。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Acid Strike", "酸性打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Acid Strike without two weapons!", "你需要兩把武器來使用酸性打擊技能！", "logPlayer")
t([[Strike with each of your weapons, doing %d%% acid weapon damage with each hit.
		If at least one of the strikes hits, an acid splash is generated, doing %0.2f acid damage to all enemies in radius %d around the foe you struck.
		The splash damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[用每把武器打擊目標，每次攻擊造成 %d%% 酸性武器傷害。 
		如果有至少一次攻擊命中目標，則會產生酸系濺射，對 %d 範圍內的所有敵人造成 %0.2f 酸性傷害。 
		濺射傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {1,3,2})
t("Corrupting Strike", "黑暗連擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Corrupting Strike without two weapons!", "你需要兩把武器來使用黑暗連擊技能！", "logPlayer")
t("Corrupt the target reducing disease immunity by 100%% for 2 turns and stripping up to 2 nature sustains then strike with both your weapons dealing %d%% damage.", "腐化目標， 2 回合內降低其 100%% 的疾病免疫，並去除其 2 個自然持續效果。然後用你的兩把武器打擊敵人，造成 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/shadowflame.lua"

t("Wraithform", "鬼魂形態", "talent name")
t([[Turn into a wraith, allowing you to walk through walls and removing the need to breath for %d turns.
		Also increases your defense and armour by %d and %d, respectively.
		If you are still in a wall when the effect ends you will randomly teleport.
		]], [[轉化爲鬼魂，允許你穿牆且不需要呼吸，持續 %d 回合。 
		同時增加閃避 %d 和護甲值 %d 。 
		效果結束時若你處於牆內，你將被隨機傳送。
		增益效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Darkfire", "黑暗之炎", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a bolt of shadowflame that moves toward the target and explodes into a flash of darkness and fire, doing %0.2f fire damage and %0.2f darkness damage in a radius of %d.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[向目標發射一團黑暗之炎，產生爆炸並造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害和 %0.2f 暗影傷害（ %d 碼半徑範圍內）。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Flame of Urh'Rok", "烏魯洛克之焰", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the essence of the supreme demon overlord Urh'Rok to turn into a demon.
		While in demon form, you gain %d%% fire resistance, %d%% darkness resistance, and your global speed is increased by %d%%.
		The flames of the Fearscape will heal you while in demon form.
		The resistances and heal will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚偉大的惡魔領主烏魯洛克的實體，轉化爲惡魔。 
		當你處於惡魔形態時，你增加 %d%% 火焰抵抗， %d%% 暗影抵抗並且整體速度提升 %d%% 。 
		當你處於惡魔形態時，惡魔空間的火焰會治療你。 
		抵抗和治療量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fearscape", "惡魔空間", "talent name")
t("This spell cannot be used from within the Fearscape.", "該技能不能在惡魔空間使用。", "logPlayer")
t("This spell cannot be cast here.", "該技能不能在這裏使用。", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles...", "法術失敗了...", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_RED#You are taken to the Fearscape!", "#LIGHT_RED#你被帶到了惡魔空間！", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_RED#You are brought back from the Fearscape!", "#LIGHT_RED#你被帶回了惡魔空間！", "logPlayer")
t([[Summon a part of the Fearscape to intersect with the current level.
		You and your target are taken to the Fearscape, trapped there until you end the spell or until your target dies.
		While inside, a constant aura of flames will burn both of you for %0.2f fire damage (demons are healed instead) each turn.
		When the spell ends, only you and the target (if still alive) plus any loose objects are taken back to your home plane; all summons are left in the Fearscape.
		This powerful spell drains 5 vim per turn initially, increasing by +1 for each turn it has been active, and ends when your vim is depleted.
		It has no effect if cast from within the Fearscape.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚一部分惡魔空間與現有空間交叉。 
		你的目標和你自己都會被帶入惡魔空間，只有當你中斷技能或目標死亡時，限制解除。 
		在惡魔空間內，永恆之焰會燃燒你和目標，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，對惡魔則會改爲進行治療。
		當技能中斷時，你和目標（如果還活着），以及所有掉落物品會被帶回原來空間。
		這個強大的法術最初每回合消耗 5 點活力，活力值消耗每回合增加 1 點，當活力值歸零時技能終止。
		當你已處於惡魔空間時，此技能施放無效果。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/torment.lua"

t("Willful Tormenter", "施虐之心", "talent name")
t([[You set your mind toward a single goal: the destruction of all your foes.
		Increases the maximum amount of vim you can store by %d.]], [[你將精神集中於一個目標：摧毀所有敵人。 
		增加你 %d 點活力上限。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Lock", "鮮血禁錮", "talent name")
t("Reach out and touch the blood and health of your foes. Any creatures caught in the radius 2 ball will be unable to heal above their current life value (at the time of the casting) for %d turns.", "掌控敵人的血液和肉體。在 2 碼範圍內，任何被鮮血禁錮攻擊到的敵人的治療或回覆將不能超過當前生命值，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Overkill", "趕盡殺絕", "talent name")
t([[When you kill a creature, the remainder of the damage done will not be lost. Instead, %d%% of it will splash in a radius 2 as blight damage.
		The splash damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[當你殺死一個敵人後，多餘的傷害不會消失。 
		反之 %d%% 的傷害會濺落在 2 碼範圍內，造成枯萎傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Vengeance", "血之復仇", "talent name")
t("#RED#The powerful blow energizes %s reducing their cooldowns!#LAST#", "#RED#強大的攻擊使 %s 獲得能量，技能冷卻時間縮短了!#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[When you are dealt a blow that reduces your life by at least %d%%, you have a %d%% chance to reduce the remaining cooldown of all your talents by 1.
		Temporary life from Sanguine Infusion will not count against the damage threshold.
		The chance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[當你遭受到超過至少 %d%% 總生命值的傷害時，你有 %d%% 概率降低所有技能 1 回合冷卻時間。 
		鮮血灌注帶來的額外生命值，不會影響該技能的傷害閾值。
		概率受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/corruptions/vile-life.lua"

t("Blood Splash", "鮮血飛濺", "talent name")
t([[Inflicting pain and death invigorates you.
		Each time you deal a critical strike you gain %d life (this effect can only happen once per turn).
		Each time you kill a creature you gain %d life (this effect can only happen once per turn).]], [[製造痛苦和死亡讓你充滿活力。
		每次暴擊時回覆 %d 生命。
		每次殺死生物時回覆 %d 生命。
		每個效果每回合只能觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Elemental Discord", "元素狂亂", "talent name")
t([[Use elemental damage dealt to you to trigger terrible effects on the source:
		- Fire: burn for %0.2f fire damage over 5 turns
		- Cold: freeze for 3 turns with %d iceblock power
		- Acid: blind for %d turns
		- Lightning: daze for %d turns
		- Nature: %d%% slow for 4 turns
		This effect can only happen once every 10 turns per damage type.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 每次受到元素傷害時對造成傷害的生物觸發以下效果：
		- 火焰：灼燒目標 5 回合，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。
		- 寒冷：凍結目標 3 回合，冰塊強度 %d 。
		- 酸性：致盲 %d 回合。
		- 閃電：眩暈 %d 回合。
		- 自然：減速 %d%% 四回合。
		每種傷害類型的效果每 10 回合只能觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Healing Inversion", "治療逆轉", "talent name")
t([[You manipulate the vim of enemies in radius %d to temporarily invert all healing done to them (but not natural regeneration).
		For 5 turns all healing will instead damage them for %d%% of the healing done as blight.
		The effect will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你操控周圍%d碼範圍內目標的活力，臨時將他們所受到的所有治療轉化爲傷害（但生命值自然回覆除外）。
		在 5 回合內，他們受到的一切治療將會被轉化爲相當於治療量 %d%% 的枯萎傷害。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Vile Transplant", "邪惡移植", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON##Source# transfers an effect (%s) to #Target#!", "#CRIMSON##Source#將一項效果(%s)轉移至#Target#!", "tformat")
t([[You transfer up to %d physical or magical detrimental effects currently affecting you to a nearby creature at a cost of %d vim per effect.
		Specific effect immunities will not prevent the transfer.
		The chance to transfer each effect increases with your Spellpower.]], [[你將至多 %d 個物理與魔法負面狀態轉移給附近的一個生物，每轉移一個狀態消耗 %d 活力值。
		狀態免疫效果不會影響負面狀態的轉移。
		轉移每個狀態的成功率受法術強度影響。]], "tformat")


