%s
The effects depend on this talent's level.
Mastering a new tool places it (and its special effects, as appropriate) on cooldown.]], [[你成爲工具大師，能集中強化一件工具 (#YELLOW#當前選擇 %s#LAST#) 來改善其性能:

%s
效果取決於技能等級。
強化工具將使其進入冷卻。]], "tformat")
t("Hidden Blades", "隱匿刀鋒", "talent name")
t("#Source# strikes #target# with hidden blades!", "#Source#使用隱藏的刀片擊中了#target#!", "logCombat")
t("Melee criticals trigger an extra unarmed attack, inflicting %d%% damage. 4 turn cooldown.", "近戰暴擊觸發額外 %d%% 傷害徒手攻擊， 4 回合冷卻。", "tformat")
t([[You conceal spring loaded blades within your equipment. On scoring a critical strike, you follow up with your blades for %d%% damage (as an unarmed attack).
This talent has a cooldown.
#YELLOW#Prepared with: %s#LAST#]], [[你將刀片隱藏在裝備中，當你對臨近目標造成暴擊時，刀片自動彈出，造成 %d%% 徒手武器傷害。
該技能有冷卻時間。 
#YELLOW#準備於：%s#LAST#]], "tformat")
t("Assassinate", "暗殺", "talent name")
t("You must have Hidden Blades prepared to use this talent.", "你必須準備好隱藏刀片來使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("#Source# strikes at a vital spot on #target#!", "#Source#攻向#target#的要害!", "logCombat")
t("You prime your Hidden Blades to cause bleeding and facilitate the Assassinate ability, which allows you to strike twice for %d%% unarmed damage, hitting automatically while ignoring armor and resistance.", "你的隱匿刀鋒會觸發流血效果，同時強化暗殺技能，自動攻擊兩次造成 %d%% 徒手傷害，無視護甲與抗性。", "tformat")
t([[You strike your target with your Hidden Blades twice in a vital spot for %d%% unarmed (physical) damage.  You must be able to see your target to use this attack, but it always hits and ignores all armor and physical resistance.
In addition, your hidden blades now inflict a further %d%% of all damage dealt as bleeding over 5 turns.]], [[你用隱匿刀鋒攻擊兩次，每次造成 %d%% 徒手傷害。需要看見目標來使用該技能，該技能無視護甲和物理抗性。
此外，你的隱匿刀鋒在 5 回合內額外造成相當於傷害值 %d%% 的流血傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Rogue's Brew", "盜賊佳釀", "talent name")
t("%s is cured!", "%s 被治癒！", "logSeen")
t("Prepare a potion that restores %d life, %d stamina, and cures %d negative physical effects. 20 turn cooldown.", "準備藥劑，回覆 %d 生命, %d 體力, 解除 %d 項物理負面狀態。20 回合冷卻。", "tformat")
t([[Imbibe a potent mixture of energizing and restorative substances, restoring %d life, %d stamina and curing %d detrimental physical effects.  The restorative effects improve with your Cunning.
	#YELLOW#Prepared with: %s#LAST#]], [[製造強效恢復藥酒, 使用後回覆 %d 生命, %d 體力並解除 %d 項物理負面效果。該效果受靈巧加成。
	#YELLOW#準備於：%s#LAST#]], "tformat")
t("Rogue's Brew Mastery", "佳釀強化", "talent name")
t("Your Rogue's Brew fortifies you for 8 turns, preventing you from dying until you reach -%d life.", "調整配方，8 回合內生命底限增加 %d 。", "tformat")
t("Adjust your Rogue's Brew formulation so that it fortifies you for 8 turns, preventing you from dying until you reach -%d life.", "調整配方，8 回合內生命底限增加 %d 。", "tformat")
t("Smokescreen", "煙霧彈", "talent name")
t("Throw a smokebomb creating a radius 2 cloud of smoke, lasting %d turns, that blocks sight and reduces enemies' vision by %d. 15 turn cooldown.", "範圍 2 的煙霧彈，持續 %d 回合, 視野下降 %d 。15 回合冷卻。", "tformat")
t([[Throw a vial of volatile liquid that explodes in a radius %d cloud of smoke lasting %d turns.  The smoke blocks line of sight, and enemies within will have their vision range reduced by %d.
		Use of this talent will not break stealth, and creatures affected by the smokes can never prevent you from activating stealth, even if their proximity would normally forbid it.
		#YELLOW#Prepared with: %s#LAST#]], [[扔出煙霧彈，產生半徑 %d 的煙霧，持續 %d 回合。煙霧阻擋視野，所有煙霧中的敵人視野下降 %d 。
		使用該技能不解除潛行。被煙霧影響的生物不能阻止你潛行。
		#YELLOW#準備於：%s#LAST#]], "tformat")
t("Smokescreen Mastery", "強化煙霧彈", "talent name")
t("Your Smokescreen is infused with chokedust. Enemies in the smoke take %0.2f nature damage and may be silenced.", "你的煙霧彈中加入了窒息粉塵。每回合煙霧中的敵人將受到 %0.2f 自然傷害並有機率被沉默。", "tformat")
t("You infuse your smoke bomb with chokedust. Each turn, enemies in the smoke take %0.2f nature damage and are 50%% likely to be silenced.", "你的煙霧彈中加入了窒息粉塵。每回合煙霧中的敵人將受到 %0.2f 自然傷害並有 50%% 機率被沉默。", "tformat")
t("Dart Launcher", "飛鏢發射器", "talent name")
t("%s resists the sedation!", "%s抵抗了睡眠!", "logSeen")
t("Fire a poisoned dart dealing %0.2f physical damage that puts the target to sleep for 4 turns. 10 turn cooldown.", "發射毒鏢，造成 %0.2f 物理傷害，沉睡 4 回合。10 回合冷卻時間。", "tformat")
t([[Fire a poisoned dart from a silent, concealed launcher on your person that deals %0.2f physical damage and puts the target (living only) to sleep for 4 turns, rendering them unable to act. Every %d points of damage the target takes brings it closer to waking by 1 turn.
This can be used without breaking stealth.
#YELLOW#Prepared with: %s#LAST#]], [[從無聲發射器中發射毒鏢，造成 %0.2f 物理傷害，並催眠生物 4 回合。每受到 %d 點傷害，睡眠時間減少一回合。
使用該技能不解除潛行。
#YELLOW#準備於：%s#LAST#]], "tformat")
t("Dart Launcher Mastery", "毒鏢強化", "talent name")
t("Your darts ignore poison and sleep immunity and waking targets are slowed by %d%% for 4 turns.", "睡眠毒素無視免疫，且使目標醒來後減速 %d%% 4 回合。", "tformat")
t("The sleeping poison of your Dart Launcher becomes potent enough to ignore immunity, and upon waking the target is slowed by %d%% for 4 turns.", "睡眠毒素無視免疫，且使目標醒來後減速 %d%% 4 回合。", "tformat")
t("Grappling Hook", "鉤爪", "talent name")
t("You are too close to your target to swing your hook effectively!", "你距離目標太近了，不方便使用鉤爪！", "logPlayer")
t("#Source# throws a grappling hook at #target#!", "#Source#朝#target#扔出鉤爪!", "logCombat")
t("#Source#'s grappling hook latches onto #target#!", "#Source#的鉤爪命中了#target#!", "logCombat")
t("#Source# is dragged towards #target#!", "#Source#被拉向#target#!", "logCombat")
t("#Target# is dragged towards #source#!", "#Target#被拉向#source#!", "logCombat")
t("%s resists the pin!", "%s抵抗了定身！", "logSeen")
t("You cannot move!", "你無法移動!", "logPlayer")
t("You need more room to swing your hook effectively.", "你需要更多空間來使用鉤爪。", "logPlayer")
t("%s uses a grappling hook to pull %s %s!", "%s使用鉤爪來拉動%s向%s!", "logSeen")
t("You must anchor the hook to something solid.", "你需要將鉤爪固定在某個堅固的物體上", "logPlayer")
t("Throw a grappling hook up to range %d that drags you towards the target or the target towards you. 8 turn cooldown.", "發射長度 %d 的鉤爪，將你拉過去或者將對面拉過來。 8 回合冷卻。", "tformat")
t("not prepared", "沒有準備", "_t")
t([[Toss out a grappling hook to a target within range %d.  If this strikes either a wall or a creature that is immovable or larger than you, you will pull yourself towards it, otherwise, you will drag the target towards you.  Creatures struck by the hook will be pinned for 2 turns.
		Your grapple target must be at least 2 tiles from you.
#YELLOW#Prepared with: %s#LAST#]], [[朝 %d 格範圍內的目標發射鉤爪，如果目標是牆壁、目標不能移動或目標體型比你大，你將被拉過去，否則將目標拉過來。之後，目標將被定身 2 回合。
		鉤爪至少要發射到兩格外。
#YELLOW#準備於：%s#LAST#]], "tformat")
t("Grappling Hook Mastery", "鉤爪強化", "talent name")
t("Your grappling hook deals %d%% unarmed damage when it hits, plus a further %0.2f physical and %0.2f nature damage over 4 turns.", "被鉤爪擊中的生物受到 %d%% 徒手傷害 ,在 4 回合內受到 %0.2f 流血傷害和 %0.2f 自然毒素傷害。", "tformat")
t("Your grappling hook is tipped with vicious, venomous barbs. Creatures struck by it will be hit for %d%% unarmed damage, bleed for %0.2f physical damage and be poisoned for %0.2f nature damage over 4 turns.", "你的鉤爪上塗有毒素且裝有尖刺，被擊中的生物受到 %d%% 徒手傷害 ,在 4 回合內受到 %0.2f 流血傷害和 %0.2f 自然毒素傷害。", "tformat")


