		這個射擊將會穿過你和目標間的其他敵人。
		減速效果受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Kill Shot", "致命狙擊", "talent name")
t("#DARK_ORCHID##Source# snipes #Target# (%+d%%%%%%%% weapon bonus for range)!#LAST#", "#DARK_ORCHID##Source#狙擊了#Target#（%+d%%%%%%%% 遠程武器傷害加成）！#LAST#", "delayedLogMessage")
t([[Employ a specialized sniping shot at a target.
		This shot is focused on precision at long range and deals base %d%% ranged damage with a bonus that increases with distance.
		The ranged bonus is %d%% (penalty) at point blank range, while at your maximum range of %d it is %d%%.
		This shot will bypass other enemies between you and your target.]], [[對敵人進行一次特殊的射擊。
