		在零距離，傷害加成（懲罰）爲 %d%% ，在最大射程（ %d 格），傷害加成爲 %d%% 。
		這個射擊將會穿過你和目標間的其他敵人。]], "tformat")
t("Noggin Knocker", "爆頭連射", "talent name")
t("%s resists the stunning shot!", "%s抵抗了震懾。", "logSeen")
t([[Fire three shots in quick succession at a vulnerable point on the target (usually the head).
		Each shot deals %d%% Ranged damage and will try to stun or increase the target's stun duration by 1.
		These shots will bypass other enemies between you and your target.
		The chance to stun increases with your Accuracy.]], [[對敵人的脆弱部位（通常是頭部）迅速地連射三次。
		每次射擊造成 %d%% 遠程傷害並試圖震懾目標或增加震懾的持續時間 1 回合。
		這些射擊將會穿過你和目標間的其他敵人。
		受命中影響，震懾機率增加。]], "tformat")
t("Sling Sniper", "投石大師", "talent name")
t("Your mastery of called shots is unparalleled. and you gain %d%% bonus critical chance and %d%% critical damage with your Called Shots Talents. At rank 3 the cooldowns of all of your Called Shots Talents are reduced by 2 each. At rank 5 you gain %d%% Physical resistance penetration with all Called Shot attacks.", [[你對射擊的掌握程度無與倫比。你的精準射擊系技能獲得 %d%% 額外暴擊機率和 %d%% 額外暴擊傷害。 
		在第 3 級時，所有精準射擊系技能冷卻時間降低兩回合。
		在第 5 級時，你的精準射擊技能獲得 %d%% 物理抗性穿透]], "tformat")


