t("lethality", "致命攻擊", "_t")
t("Blending magic and shadows.", " 隱祕在陰影之中使用的祕密法術。", "_t")
t("shadow magic", "影之祕法", "_t")
t("Using darkness and a bit of magic, you manipulate the shadows.", "使用黑暗和魔法，操控陰影的力量。", "_t")
t("ambush", "伏擊", "_t")
t("The knowledge of the dangers of the world, and how to best avoid them.", " 讓你認識到世界中的各種危險，並學會如何有效避免它們。", "_t")
t("survival", "生存", "_t")
t("Tactical combat abilities.", " 戰鬥中使用的策略技巧。", "_t")
