section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/dirty.lua"

t("Dirty Fighting", "卑劣攻擊", "talent name")
t([[You make a low blow against a sensitive point on the target, dealing %d%% unarmed damage. If your attack hits, the target is left reeling and vulnerable, reducing their physical save by %d and their stun, blind, confusion and pin immunities to 50%% of normal for %d turns.
This effect bypasses saves.]], [[你攻擊目標的敏感部位，造成 %d%% 徒手傷害。如果攻擊命中，目標身受重創，物理豁免減少 %d ，震懾、致盲、混亂、定身免疫降低爲原來的 50%% ，持續 %d 回合。
該效果無視豁免。]], "tformat")
t("Backstab", "背刺", "talent name")
t([[Your quick wit gives you a big advantage against disabled targets, increasing your damage by %d%% for each disabling effect the target is under, to a maximum of %d%%.
For this purpose, disabling effects are stun, blind, daze, confuse, pin, disarm, cripple and silence.
In addition, for each disabling effect the target is under, your melee attacks have a %d%% (to a maximum of %d%%) chance to inflict a new effect on them (that they do not already have): either disarm, cripple (25%% power) or pin for 2 turns.
The chance to further disable the target increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你機智地利用敵人的傷殘，每項傷殘效果增加 %d%% 傷害，最多 %d%% 。
傷殘效果包括：震懾、致盲、眩暈、定身、繳械、致殘和沉默。
此外，每項傷殘效果使你的近戰攻擊有 %d%% 機率（最多疊加至 %d%% ）附加額外效果（不會重複）：繳械、致殘（25%% 強度）或者定身 2 回合。
附加效果成功率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blinding Powder", "致盲粉", "talent name")
t([[Throw a cloud of blinding dust in a radius %d cone. Enemies within will be blinded, as well as having their accuracy reduced by %d and movement speed decreased by %d%% for %d turns.
		The chance to inflict these effects increase with your Accuracy.]], [[撒出致盲粉，致盲前方 %d 格錐形範圍內的敵人。受影響的敵人命中減少 %d ，移動速度減少 %d%% ，持續 %d 回合。
		效果成功率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Twist the Knife", "扭曲刀刃", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's %s was extended!#LAST#", "#CRIMSON# %s的%s 被延長了！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's %s was stripped!#LAST#", "#CRIMSON# %s的%s 被解除了！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's %s was disrupted!#LAST#", "#CRIMSON# %s的%s 被幹擾了！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t("Make a painful strike dealing %d%% weapon damage that increases the duration of up to %d negative effect(s) on the target by %d turns. For each negative effect extended this way, the duration of a beneficial effect is reduced by the same amount, possibly canceling it.", "攻擊敵人造成 %d%% 武器傷害，並延長對方身上至多 %d 項負面效果持續時間 %d 回合。每延長一項負面效果，相應減少一項正面效果持續時間。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/lethality.lua"

t("Lethality", "刺殺掌握", "talent name")
t([[You have learned to find and hit weak spots. All your strikes have a %0.1f%% greater chance to be critical hits, and your critical hits do %0.1f%% more damage.
		Also, when using knives and throwing knives, you now use your Cunning instead of your Strength for bonus damage.]], "你學會尋找並打擊目標弱點。你的攻擊有 %0.1f%% 更大機率出現暴擊且暴擊傷害增加 %0.1f%% 。同時，當你使用匕首時，你的靈巧點數會代替力量影響額外傷害。", "tformat")
t("Expose Weakness", "弱點暴露", "talent name")
t([[Focus on a single target and perform a probing attack to find flaws in its defences, striking with your melee weapon(s) for %d%% damage.
		For %d turns thereafter, you gain %d armor penetration, %d accuracy, and %d%% all damage peneration.
		Learning this technique allows you to permanently gain %d armour penetration with all melee and archery attacks.
		The temporary armor penetration and accuracy bonuses increase with Cunning.]], [[集中精力試探目標，尋找其弱點 ,造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		在接下來的 %d 回合內，你獲得 %d 護甲穿透， %d 命中， %d%% 所有傷害穿透。
		學習這一技能還會使你的近戰和弓箭攻擊永久獲得 %d 護甲穿透。
		護甲穿透和命中加成受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blade Flurry", "劍刃亂舞", "talent name")
t([[Become a whirling storm of blades, increasing attack speed by %d%% and causing melee attacks to strike an additional adjacent target other than your primary target for %d%% weapon damage. 
This talent is exhausting to use, draining 4 stamina each turn.]], [[如疾風般揮舞武器，攻擊速度增加 %d%% ，每次攻擊追加一名目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
該技能每回合抽取 4 點體力。]], "tformat")
t("Snap", "靈光一閃", "talent name")
t("Your quick wits allow you to reset the cooldown of up to %d of your combat talents (cunning or technique) of tier %d or less.", "你的快速反應使你能夠重置至多 %d 個層級不超過 %d 的戰鬥技能（靈巧類或格鬥類）的冷卻時間。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/poisons.lua"

t("Apply Poison", "塗毒", "talent name")
t("%s resists the vile poison!", "%s抵抗了邪惡毒素!", "logSeen")
t([[Learn how to coat your melee weapons, throwing knives, sling and bow ammo with poison, giving your attacks a %d%% chance to poison the target for %d nature damage per turn for %d turns. Every application of the poison stacks, up to a maximum of %d nature damage per turn.
		The damage scales with your Cunning.]], [[學會如何在近戰武器、飛刀、彈藥上塗毒，命中後有 %d%% 機率使目標中毒，每回合受到 %d 自然傷害，持續 %d 回合。毒素效果可以疊加至 %d 傷害每回合。
		傷害受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Toxic Death", "致命毒素", "talent name")
t("#GREEN#Poison bursts out of %s's corpse!", "#GREEN#毒素從%s的屍體中爆發出來！", "logSeen")
t("When you kill a creature, all of your poisons affecting it will spread to foes in a radius of %d.", "當你殺死攜帶毒素的生物時，將毒素傳播至 %d 半徑內的敵人 .", "tformat")
t("Vile Poisons", "邪惡毒素", "talent name")
t([[Learn how to enhance your Deadly Poison, adding additional effects. Each level, you will learn a new kind of poison enhancement:
	Level 1: Numbing Poison
	Level 2: Insidious Poison
	Level 3: Crippling Poison
	Level 4: Leeching Poison
	Level 5: Volatile Poison
	New poison enhancements can also be learned from special teachers in the world.
	Also increases the effectiveness of your poisons by %d%%. (The effect varies for each poison.)
	Adjusting your weapon coating takes no time and does not break stealth.
	You may only have two poison enhancements active at once; applying a third will randomly cause one of the existing ones to be cancelled.]], [[你學會增強你致命毒素的效果。根據技能等級可以開啓新的效果： 
		等級 1 ：麻痹毒素 
		等級 2 ：陰險毒素 
		等級 3 ：致殘毒素 
		等級 4 ：吸血毒素 
		等級 5 ：傳染毒素 
		同時你還可以向世界上特定的人學習新毒素。 
		同時提高你 %d%% 的毒素效果。
		在你的武器上塗毒不會打破潛行狀態。 
		每次只能同時使用 2 種毒素效果。使用第三種毒素效果會隨機取消一種已啓用的效果。]], "tformat")
t("Venomous Strike", "毒素爆發", "talent name")
t("#GREEN#%s's %s is disrupted by crippling poison!", "#GREEN#%s 的%s被致殘毒素打斷了！", "logSeen")
t([[Numbing Poison - Reduces global speed by %d%% for 5 turns.
		Insidious Poison - Applies a standard poison that deals %0.2f nature damage over 5 turns.
		Crippling Poison - Places %d talents on cooldown for %d turns.
		Leeching Poison - Heals you for %d.
		Volatile Poison - Deals a further %0.2f nature damage to foes in a radius %d ball.
		]], [[麻痹毒素 - 整體速度減少 %d%% ，持續5回合。
		陰險毒素 - 在 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 自然傷害。
		致殘毒素 - 令 %d 個技能進入 %d 回合冷卻。
		吸血毒素 - 自己獲得 %d 治療。
		傳染毒素 - 額外 %0.2f 自然傷害，傷害半徑 %d 。
		]], "tformat")
t([[You strike your target with your melee or ranged weapon, doing %d%% weapon damage as nature and inflicting additional effects based on your active vile poisons:
		
		%s
		Learning this talent in addition to the Throwing Knives talent allows you to learn the Venomous Throw talent, which can be used to throw poisoned daggers at your foes, but is put on cooldown when this talent is used.
		]], [[你攻擊目標，造成 %d%% 自然武器傷害，並基於目標當前毒素觸發額外效果 :
		
		%s 
		學習該技能後，你能學習劇毒飛刀，但使用該技能會使其進入冷卻。
		]], "tformat")
t("Numbing Poison", "麻痹毒素", "talent name")
t("Enhances your Deadly Poison with a numbing agent, causing the poison to reduce all damage the target deals by %d%%.", "在你的武器上塗上麻痹毒素，中毒目標造成的傷害降低 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Insidious Poison", "陰險毒素", "talent name")
t("Enhances your Deadly Poison with an insidious agent, causing it to reduce the healing taken by enemies by %d%%.", "在你的武器上塗上陰險毒素，中毒目標受到的治療效果減少 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Crippling Poison", "致殘毒素", "talent name")
t("Enhances your Deadly Poison with a crippling agent, giving enemies a %d%% chance on using a talent to fail and lose a turn.", "在你的武器上塗上致殘毒素, 中毒目標每次使用技能都有 %d%% 概率失敗並流失 1 回合時間。", "tformat")
t("Leeching Poison", "吸血毒素", "talent name")
t("Enhances your Deadly Poison with a leeching agent, causing it to heal you for %d%% of the damage it does to its target.", "在你的武器上塗上吸血毒素, 你受到中毒傷害 %d%% 的治療。", "tformat")
t("Volatile Poison", "傳染毒素", "talent name")
t("Enhances your Deadly Poison with a volatile agent, causing the poison to deal %d%% increased damage to the victim and damage all of your enemies adjacent to it for 50%%.", "在你的武器上塗上傳染毒素, 毒素造成額外 %d%% 傷害，且會對周圍敵人造成 50%% 的傷害。", "tformat")
t("Vulnerability Poison", "脆弱毒素", "talent name")
t("Whenever you apply Deadly Poison, you also apply an unresistable magical poison dealing %0.2f arcane damage (based on your Magic) each turn. This poison reduces all damage resistance by 10%% and poison immunity by 50%%.", "在你的武器上塗上脆弱毒素，每回合造成每輪 %0.2f 點奧術傷害且所有傷害抗性將被減少 10%% ，毒素免疫減少 50%% 。", "tformat")
t("Stoning Poison", "石化毒素", "talent name")
t([[Enhance your Deadly Poison with a stoning agent.  Whenever you apply Deadly Poison, you afflict your target with an additional earth-based poison that inflicts %d nature damage per turn (stacking up to %d damage per turn) for %d turns.
		After either %d turns or the poison has run its course (<100%% chance, see effect description), the target will be turned to stone for %d turns.
		The damage scales with your Cunning.]], [[在你的武器上塗上石化毒素，額外造成每輪 %d 點自然傷害（可疊加至 %d ），持續 %d 回合。 
		%d 回合後或者毒素效果結束後（機率小於100%%，請參見效果介紹），目標將被石化 %d 回合。
		受靈巧影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/scoundrel.lua"

t("Lacerating Strikes", "撕裂揮擊", "talent name")
t("Your melee and ranged attacks have a %d%% chance to shred enemies inflicting an additional 100%% of the damage dealt as a bleed over 4 turns.", "你的近戰和遠程攻擊有 %d%% 的機率撕裂敵人，使其在 4 回合內受到 100%% 的額外流血傷害。", "tformat")
t("Scoundrel's Strategies", "街霸戰術", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's %s is disrupted by %s wounds!#LAST#", "#CRIMSON#%s 的 %s 被 %s 的傷口乾擾了！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[Your melee and ranged attacks inflict distracting wounds that reduce the target’s critical strike multiplier by %d%% for 5 turns. 
In addition, your attacks have a %d%% chance to inflict a painful wound that causes them to forget a random talent for %d turns.  The last effect cannot occur more than once per turn per target.
		]], [[你的近戰和遠程攻擊製造的傷口會使敵人分心，使目標的暴擊係數減少 %d%% ，持續 5 回合。
		此外，你的攻擊還有 %d%% 的機率造成痛苦的創傷，使敵人隨機遺忘一項技能，持續 %d 回合。這一效果每回合最多隻能觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Misdirection", "誤導", "talent name")
t("#ORANGE#%s redirects the effect '%s'!#LAST#", "#ORANGE#%s 誤導了 '%s' 效果！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[Your abilities in sowing confusion and chaos have reached their peak.  Whenever a foe attempts to apply a detrimental physical effect to you, they have a %d%% chance to fail. If there is an adjacent enemy to you, you misdirect your foe into applying it to them at %d%% duration.
You gain %d defense.
The chance to apply status effects increases with your Accuracy and the Defense with your Cunning.]], [[你製造混亂的技巧已趨於巔峯。現在，即便是你最簡單的動作也會迷惑敵人，使他們看不透你的行蹤。 
		敵人試圖對你施加物理負面狀態時，有 %d%% 機率失敗。此外，如果你周圍有敵人，這一效果將會被轉移到這個敵人身上，持續時間變爲 %d%% 。 
		你獲得 %d 閃避。
		施加負面狀態機率受命中影響。
		閃避加成受靈巧影響]], "tformat")
t("Fumble", "笨拙", "talent name")
t([[Your melee and ranged attacks leave your foes unable to focus on any complex actions, giving them a stacking 3%% chance of failure the next time they try to use a talent (to a maximum of %d%%).
		If any effect causes the target's turn to fail they fumble and injure themself, taking %0.2f physical damage.
		If the turn loss was caused by this effect then Fumble is removed.
		The damage dealt increases with your Cunning.
		]], [[你的近程和遠程攻擊會讓敵人難以集中精力於複雜的行動，在下一次使用技能時有 3%% 的機率失敗，這一效果可以疊加，最多疊加至 %d%% 。
		如果因任何原因，敵人技能使用失敗，對方將弄傷自己，造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。
		如果敵人是因笨拙效果而技能使用失敗，將會移除笨拙效果。
		傷害受靈巧加成。
	  ]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/shadow-magic.lua"

t("Shadow Combat", "影之格鬥", "talent name")
t([[Channel raw magical energy into your melee attacks; each blow you land will do an additional %.2f darkness damage.
		The damage will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[在你的武器上注入一股黑暗的能量，每次攻擊會造成 %.2f 暗影傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Cunning", "影之狡詐", "talent name")
t("Your preparations give you greater magical capabilities. You gain a bonus to Spellpower equal to %d%% of your Cunning (Current bonus: %d).", "你的充分準備提高了你的魔法運用能力。增加相當於你 %d%% 靈巧的法術強度。目前的法術強度加成： %d", "tformat")
t("Shadow Feed", "暗影充能", "talent name")
t([[You draw energy from the depths of the shadows.
		While sustained, you regenerate %0.2f mana per turn, and your physical and spell attack speed increases by %0.1f%%.]], [[你學會從暗影中汲取能量。 
		當此技能激活時，每回合回覆 %0.2f 法力值。 
		同時，你的攻擊速度和施法速度獲得 %0.1f%% 的提升。]], "tformat")
t("Shadowstep", "暗影突襲", "talent name")
t("You require to be able to move to use this talent.", "你無法移動，不能使用這一技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot do that currently.", "你現在不能使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You do not have line of sight.", "你沒有視線", "logSeen")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t("%s is not dazed!", "%s 未眩暈！", "logSeen")
t([[Step through the shadows to your target, dazing it for %d turns and hitting it with all your weapons for %d%% darkness weapon damage.
		Dazed targets are significantly impaired, but any damage will free them.
		To Shadowstep, you need to be able to see the target.]], [[通過陰影突襲你的目標，眩暈它 %d 回合並用你所有武器對目標造成 %d%% 暗影武器傷害。 
		被眩暈的目標受到顯著傷害，但任何對目標的傷害會解除眩暈。 
		當你使用暗影突襲時，目標必須在視野範圍內。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/stealth.lua"

t("Stealth", "潛行", "talent name")
t("You cannot be stealthy with such heavy armour on!", "你不能在身着重甲的情況下潛行！", "logPlayer")
t("You are being observed too closely to enter Stealth!", "你不能在周圍有怪物注視你的情況下潛行！", "logPlayer")
t(" (range %d in an unlit grid)", " (在黑暗地格範圍爲 %d )", "tformat")
t([[Enters stealth mode (power %d, based on Cunning), making you harder to detect.
		If successful (re-checked each turn), enemies will not know exactly where you are, or may not notice you at all.
		Stealth reduces your light radius to 0, increases your infravision by 3, and will not work with heavy or massive armours.
		You cannot enter stealth if there are foes in sight within range %d%s.
		Any non-instant, non-movement action will break stealth if not otherwise specified.

		Enemies uncertain of your location will still make educated guesses at it.
		While stealthed, enemies cannot share information about your location with each other and will be delayed in telling their allies that you exist at all.]], [[進入潛行模式（潛行點數 %d ，基於靈巧），讓你更難被偵測到。
		如果成功（每回合都重新檢查），敵人將不會知道你在哪裏，或者根本不會注意到你。
		潛行將光照半徑減小至 0，增加3點夜視能力，並且不能在裝備重甲或板甲時使用。
		如果敵人在半徑 %d %s 內，你不能進入潛行。
		除非特別說明，任何非瞬間非移動技能均會打破潛行。

		即使不知道你位置的敵人，仍然會猜測你可能在的位置。
		在潛行時，敵人無法分享有關你位置的信息，並且會一直相信你還在那裏。]], "tformat")
t("Shadowstrike", "影襲", "talent name")
t([[You know how to make the most out of being unseen.
		When striking from stealth, your attacks are automatically critical if the target does not notice you just before you land it.  (Spell and mind attacks critically strike even if the target notices you.)
		Your critical multiplier against targets that cannot see you is increased by up to %d%%. (You must be able to see your target and the bonus is reduced from its full value at range 3 to 0 at range 10.)
		Also, after exiting stealth for any reason, the critical multiplier persists for %d turns (with no range limitation).]], [[你充分發揮潛行優勢。
		潛行狀態下攻擊時，如果直到命中前你的目標都沒有發現你，你的攻擊將自動暴擊。（即使目標註意到你，你的法術和精神攻擊也會暴擊。）
		對於看不見你的目標，暴擊傷害增加 %d%% 。（你必須能夠看到你的目標，並且傷害獎勵隨距離降低：3 格內保持滿額，到 10 格時降低爲 0 ）、
		此外，由於任何原因脫離潛行後，暴擊傷害獎勵會持續存在 %d 回合（不受範圍限制）。]], "tformat")
t("Soothing Darkness", "黑暗親和", "talent name")
t([[You have a special affinity for darkness and shadows.
		When standing in an unlit grid, the minimum range to your foes for activating stealth or for maintaining it after a Shadow Dance is reduced by %d.
		While stealthed, your life regeneration is increased by %0.1f (based on your Cunning) and your stamina regeneration is increased by %0.1f.  The regeneration effects persist for %d turns after exiting stealth, with 5 times the normal rate.]], [[你對黑暗和陰影有特殊的親和力。
		站在黑暗地格中，激活潛行的最小範圍限制降低 %d 。
		當潛行時，你增加 %0.1f 的生命回覆速度（基於靈巧），同時你也增加 %0.1f 的體力回覆速度。該回復效果在退出潛行後仍能保持 %d 回合，並且回覆速度是正常的五倍。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Dance", "暗影之舞", "talent name")
t([[Your mastery of stealth allows you to vanish from sight at any time.
		You automatically enter stealth and cause it to not break from unstealthy actions for %d turns.]], [[你對潛行的精通讓你能夠隨時從視野中消失。
		你自動進入潛行模式，在 %d 回合內，你的行動不會使你主動顯形。]], "tformat")


