section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cunning/survival.lua"

t("Heightened Senses", "強化感知", "talent name")
t([[You notice the small things others do not notice, allowing you to "see" creatures in a %d radius even outside of light radius.
		This is not telepathy, however, and it is still limited to line of sight.
		Also, your attention to detail increases stealth detection and invisibility detection by %d, and you gain the ability to detect traps (+%d detect 'power').
		The detection abilities improve with Cunning.]], [[你注意到他人注意不到的細節，甚至能在陰影區域“看到”怪物， %d 碼半徑範圍。 
		注意此能力不屬於心靈感應，仍然受到視野的限制。 
		同時你的細緻觀察使你偵察潛行和隱身的能力增加 %d ，使你發現周圍的陷阱的能力增加 %d 。 
		陷阱偵查強度受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Device Mastery", "裝置掌握", "talent name")
t([[Your cunning manipulations allow you to use charms (wands, totems and torques) more efficiently, reducing their cooldowns and the power cost of all usable items by %d%%.
		In addition your knowledge of devices allows you to disarm known traps (%d disarm 'power', improves with Cunning).]], [[你靈活的頭腦，使你可以更加有效的使用裝置（魔杖、圖騰和項圈），減少 %d%% 飾品的冷卻時間。
		同時，你對裝置的知識讓你能夠解除被發現的陷阱（+ %d 解除強度，隨靈巧提升）。
		]], "tformat")
t("Track", "追蹤", "talent name")
t([[Sense foes around you in a radius of %d for %d turns.
		The radius will increase with your Cunning.]], [[感知範圍 %d 內的敵人，持續 %d 回合。
		範圍隨靈巧提升而提升。]], "tformat")
t("Danger Sense", "危機感知", "talent name")
t([[You have an enhanced sense of self preservation, and your keen intuition allows you to sense dangers others miss.
		Your ability to detect traps is enhanced (+%d detect 'power').
		Critical attacks against you have %0.1f%% reduced bonus damage, and damage bonuses attackers gain against you for being unseen are reduced by %d%%.
		You also gain an additional chance (at your normal save %+d, effective) to resist detrimental status effects that can be resisted.
		The detection and additional save chance improve with Cunning.]], [[你擁有了更高級的自我保護感知力，敏銳的直覺讓你察覺到他人會忽略的危險。
		你感知陷阱的能力提升了（ +%d 點偵察強度）。
		對你發動的攻擊的暴擊傷害降低 %0.1f%% ，同時潛行單位因未被發現而對你造成的額外傷害的倍率減小 %d%% 。
		你獲得一次機會重新抵抗未成功抵抗的負面效果，豁免爲正常豁免 %+d 。
		偵測點數和豁免隨靈巧提升。]], "tformat")
t("Disarm Trap", "解除陷阱", "talent name")
t("#CADET_BLUE#Disarm A Trap: (direction keys to select where to disarm, shift+direction keys to move freely)", "#CADET_BLUE#解除陷阱：（方向鍵選擇解除方向，Shift+方向鍵可以移動）", "log")
t("#CADET_BLUE#You don't have the skill to disarm traps.", "#CADET_BLUE#你沒有能解除陷阱的技能。", "logPlayer")
t("#CADET_BLUE#You cannot disarm traps in grids you cannot enter.", "#CADET_BLUE#你不能解除你無法到達的陷阱。", "logPlayer")
t("#CADET_BLUE#You don't see a trap there.", "#CADET_BLUE#你在這裏並沒有發現陷阱。", "logPlayer")
t([[You search a nearby grid for a hidden trap (%d detection 'power') and disarm it if possible (%d disarm 'power', based on your skill with %s).
		Disarming a trap requires at least a minimum skill level, and you must be able to enter the trap's grid to manipulate it, though you stay in your current location.  A failed attempt to disarm a trap may trigger it.
		Your skill improves with your your Cunning.]], [[你搜索周圍地格的陷阱（ %d 偵察強度），並嘗試解除 ( %d 解除強度，基於技能 %s)。
		解除陷阱有最低技能等級需求，且你必須能夠移動到陷阱的所在格，儘管你仍然留在你的當前位置。
		解除陷阱失敗可能會觸發陷阱。
		解除能力隨靈巧值提升。]], "tformat")


