t("Bladestorm Trap", "劍刃風暴陷阱", "talent name")
t("bladestorm trap", "劍刃風暴陷阱", "_t")
t("Construct attacks all adjacent enemies each turn for %d turns.", "每回合攻擊周圍生物，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Lay a trap that activates a lethal contraption of whirling blades, lasting %d turns.  This stationary construct is very durable, receives your damage bonuses, and automatically attacks all adjacent enemies each turn.", "放置一個陷阱，激活後產生致命的劍刃風暴，持續 %d 回合。這個臨時的結構體非常堅韌，獲得你的傷害加成，每回合自動攻擊相鄰敵人。", "tformat")
