When the marked enemy dies, the cooldown of this talent will be reduced by two turns for every turn the mark had remaining.

Each point in Bloodstained talents reduces the amount of damage you take from bleed effects by 2%%]], [[傳送至一個敵人面前，攻擊造成 100%% 武器傷害，使其在5回合裏受到 %d%% 流血傷害，並標記它6回合。如果目標已經在你身邊，則不會傳送。

被標記的敵人死亡時，標記每剩餘一回合此技能的冷卻減少2回合。

每一點血染系技能使你受到的流血傷害減少2%%。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Rage", "血腥暴怒", "talent name")
t([[Cut into an enemy and twist the blade, dealing %d%% damage and increasing the intensity of their existing bleed effects by %d%%.

Each point in Bloodstained talents reduces the amount of damage you take from bleed effects by 2%%]], [[將刀鋒切入敵人的身體然後旋轉，造成 %d%% 傷害並增加其流血強度 %d%% 。

每一點血染系技能使你受到的流血傷害減少2%%。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Bath", "血洗", "talent name")
t([[Your melee attacks also cause the target to bleed for %d%% of the damage dealt over five turns.

Each point in Bloodstained talents reduces the amount of damage you take from bleed effects by 2%%]], [[你的近戰攻擊還會使目標在5回合內受到所造成傷害 %d%% 流血傷害。

每一點血染系技能使你受到的流血傷害減少2%%。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Thirst", "嗜血狂魔", "talent name")
t([[Your hunger for violence and suffering sustains you.  All damage you do heals you for a portion of the damage done, from %d%% (at 0 Hate to) %d%% (at max Hate).  You can recover no more than 1/6 of your max life each turn this way.

Each point in Bloodstained talents reduces the amount of damage you take from bleed effects by 2%%]], [[你對於暴力和痛苦的渴求支撐着你。你造成的所有傷害都會治療你，依照 %d%% （0仇恨）至 %d%% （滿仇恨）的比例。你無法通過這種方式在一回合內回覆超過你最大生命1/6的量。

每一點血染系技能使你受到的流血傷害減少2%%。]], "tformat")


