section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/cursed-aura.lua"

t("Defiling Touch", "詛咒之觸", "talent name")
t("curse", "詛咒", "_t")
t("The %s lying nearby catches your attention. What draws you to it is not the thing itself, but something burning inside you. You feel contempt for it and all worldly things. This feeling is not new but the power of it overwhelms you. You reach out to touch the object, to curse it, to defile it. And you notice it begin to change. The colors of it begin to fade and are replaced with an insatiable hate. For a moment you hesitate. You know you must choose to resist this manifestation of your curse now and forever, or fall further into your madness.", "地上的%s引起了你的注意。吸引你的並不是物體本身，而是在你心底熊熊燃燒的憎恨之火。你對它充滿着憎恨，正如你憎恨着世間萬物一般。對你而言，這種感覺已經相當的熟悉，但是這一次，這股憎恨已經快要支配你了。你伸出手拾起了它 , 發自內心地詛咒它、污染它。緊接着，你發現它發生了變化。它的光澤開始暗淡，繼而充斥着無盡的憎恨。那一瞬間，你猶豫了。你知道命運的抉擇正放在面前，要麼從今天起抵抗身上的詛咒，並與之對抗終身；要麼繼續放縱自我，任由詛咒帶你墮入這瘋狂的深淵。", "tformat")
t("The %s lies defiled at your feet. An aura of hatred surrounds you and you now feel truly cursed. You have gained the Cursed Aura talent tree and 1 point in Defiling Touch, but at the cost of 2 Willpower.", "你的腳下躺着受詛咒的%s。一個詛咒光環籠罩了你，你感到自己被詛咒了。你獲得了詛咒光環技能樹和等級 1 的詛咒之觸，但是需永久消耗 2 點意志。", "tformat")
t("Cursed Fate", "被詛咒的命運", "_t")
t("The %s returns to normal and your hate subsides.", "這個%s變回原樣，你的仇恨消弭了。", "tformat")
t("Release your hate upon the object", "將你的憎恨釋放到物品上", "_t")
t("Suppress your affliction", "壓制你的憎恨之意", "_t")
t([[Your defiling touch permeates everything around you, permanently imparting a random curse on each item you find. When you equip a cursed item, you gain the effects of that curse (shown as a beneficial effect). Each item with the same curse that is equipped increases the curse's power.  Initially curses are harmful, but powerful benefits accumulate as the power of the curse increases.
		The Dark Gifts talent unlocks higher level curse effects and increases their power.
		Your aura permeates your equipment more thoroughly with talent level and can affect items as follows:
		Level 1  -- weapons
		Level 2  -- body armor and cloaks
		Level 3  -- shields and helmets
		Level 4  -- gloves, boots and belts
		Level 6  -- rings
		Level 7  -- amulets/necklaces
		Level 8  -- lites
		Level 9  -- tools/totems/torques/wands
		level 10 -- ammunition
		At level 5, you can activate this talent to surround yourself with an aura that adds 2 levels to a curse of your choosing. (%s chosen)
		Also, talent levels above 5 reduce the negative effects of your curses (currently %d%% reduction).]], [[		你的詛咒之觸瀰漫於你附近的所有東西，給予找到的每個物品 1 個隨機詛咒。當你穿戴 1 件詛咒裝備時，你增加那種詛咒的效果。最初詛咒是有害的，但是當裝備多件物品並且學到黑暗禮物時，詛咒會變的非常有益。 
		等級 1 ——詛咒武器
		等級 2 ——詛咒盔甲和斗篷
		等級 3 ——詛咒盾牌和頭盔
		等級 4 ——詛咒手套、靴子和腰帶
		等級 6 ——詛咒戒指
		等級 7 ——詛咒項鍊
		等級 8 ——詛咒燈具
		等級 9 ——詛咒工具/圖騰/項圈/魔棒
		等級 10 ——詛咒彈藥
		在等級 5 時，你可以激活此技能形成 1 個光環，增加 2 級你選擇的詛咒效果( 當前 %s)。 
		同時，技能等級在 5 以上時會減輕詛咒的負面效果（現在減少 %d%% ） ]], "tformat")
t("Dark Gifts", "黑暗禮物", "talent name")
t([[Your curses bring you dark gifts. Unlocks bonus level %d effects on all of your curses, allowing you to gain that effect when the power level of your curse reaches that level. At talent level 5, the luck penalty of cursed effects is reduced to 1.
		Talent levels above 5 add bonus power levels to your curses, increasing their effects (currently %0.1f).]], [[你的詛咒帶來黑暗的禮物。解鎖所有詛咒第 %d 層效果，並允許你在詛咒達到該等級時獲得此效果。 
		在等級 5 時，因詛咒帶來的幸運懲罰降到 1 。
		等級 5 以上時增加詛咒效果（當前增加 %0.1f ）]], "tformat")
t("Ruined Earth", "毀滅大地", "talent name")
t("Curse the earth around you in a radius of %d for %d turns. Any who stand upon it are weakened, reducing the damage they inflict by %d%%", [[詛咒你周圍 %d 碼半徑範圍的大地，持續 %d 回合。 
		任何站在大地上的目標將會被虛弱，減少它們 %d%% 的傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Choose Cursed Sentry", "選擇詛咒守衛", "talent name")
t("Which weapon will be your sentry?", "使用哪把武器作爲詛咒守衛？", "_t")
t("Choose a sentry to instill your affliction into.", "選擇你灌注恐懼的詛咒守衛。", "_t")
t("You cannot use %s without a weapon in your inventory!", "使用 %s 你的物品欄內必須得有裝備！", "logPlayer")
t("animated %s", "活化的%s", "tformat")
t("A weapon imbued with a living curse. It seems to be searching for its next victim.", "被詛咒喚醒的武器，似乎正在尋找下一名受害者。", "_t")
t("#ffa0ff#%s returns to your bags!", "#ffa0ff#%s 回到揹包中！", "logPlayer")
t("Your animated sentry struggles for a moment and then returns to your inventory inexplicably.", "你的詛咒守衛掙扎了一會，返回了你的物品欄。", "logPlayer")
t("Cursed Sentry", "詛咒護衛", "_t")
t([[Instill a part of your living curse into a weapon in your inventory, and toss it nearby. This nearly impervious sentry will attack all nearby enemies for %d turns. When the curse ends, the weapon will drop to the ground.
			Cursed Sentry attack speed (currently %d%%) will improve with talent level.
			When you first select a weapon, it will be remembered and used as long as it's in your inventory. Use Choose Cursed Sentry talent to alter your selection.
			At talent level 3, you get the ability to afflict powerful mundane objects (greater egos).
			At talent level 5, you can corrupt artifacts.]], [[將部分活性詛咒能量灌輸到你揹包裏的 1 把武器上，使其懸浮在空中。這個類似於詛咒護衛的武器會自動攻擊附近的敵人，持續 %d 回合。 
		攻擊速度： %d%% 。
		當你第一次選擇武器後，只要武器仍舊在揹包裏，就會被記住。使用“選擇詛咒護衛”技能來切換武器。
		技能等級 3 時，你能將具有高級詞綴的武器化爲守衛。
		技能等級 5 時，你能將神器化爲守衛。
		]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/cursed-form.lua"

t("Unnatural Body", "詛咒之體", "talent name")
t([[Your body's strength is fed by your hatred. This causes most forms of healing to be between 50%% effective (at 0 Hate) to 100%% effective (at 100+ Hate). In addition, after each kill, you store the waning life force to invigorate yourself, restoring %d life (limited by the foe's maximum life, up to a maximum of %d at any time).  You can heal no more than %0.1f life per turn this way, and it is not affected by your hatred level or other effects.
		Healing from kills improves with your Willpower.]], [[你的力量來源於心底的憎恨，這使得大部分治療效果減至原來的50%%（0仇恨）～100%%（100+仇恨）。
		另外，每次擊殺敵人你將存儲生命能量來治療自己，回覆 %d 點生命（受敵人最大生命值限制，任何時候不能超過 %d 點）。這個方式帶來的每回合回覆量不能超過 %0.1f 點生命，也不受仇恨等級或治療加成等因素影響。 
		通過殺死敵人獲得的治療量受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Relentless", "鮮血渴望", "talent name")
t("Your thirst for blood drives your movements. You gain +%d%% confusion, fear, knockback and stun immunity.", "對鮮血的渴望控制了你的行爲。增加 +%d%% 混亂、恐懼、擊退和震懾免疫。", "tformat")
t("Seethe", "狂熱沸騰", "talent name")
t("You have learned to hold onto your hate and use your suffering to fuel your body's rage. Every turn you take damage, the damage you inflict increases, until it reaches a maximum of +%d%% after 5 turns. Any turn in which you do not take damage will reduce the bonus.", [[你學會控制憎恨，並用你的痛苦燃燒心底的憤怒。 
		每當你受到傷害時，你的傷害會在 5 回合後增加至最大值 +%d%% 。 
		每個你不承受傷害的回合會降低該增益效果。]], "tformat")
t("Grim Resolve", "冷酷決心", "talent name")
t("You rise to meet the pain that others would inflict on you. Every turn you take damage, your Strength and Willpower increase until they reach a maximum of +%d after 5 turns. Any turn in which you do not take damage will reduce the bonus. While in effect, your body also has a %d%% chance to overcome poisons and diseases each turn.", [[你勇於面對其他人帶給你的痛苦。每回合當你承受傷害時，你將會增加你的力量和意志，直至在 5 回合後增加至最大值 +%d 。 
		每個你不承受傷害的回合會降低該增益效果。 
		當此效果激活時，每回合你有 %d%% 的概率抵抗毒素和疾病效果。]], "tformat")


