t("Crimson Templar", "赤紅守衛", "_t")
t("All the things in this dark world are contemptible.  Let yourself hate them and find the power therein.", "這個黑暗世界裏的一切都是可鄙的。仇恨他們，從中獲得力量。", "_t")
t("Hatred", "憎恨", "_t")
