section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/dark-figure.lua"

t("Radiant Fear", "恐懼輝耀", "talent name")
t("You are too far to from the target!", "你距離目標太遠了！", "logPlayer")
t("Fear radiates from your target in a radius of %d for %d turns driving all others away.", "恐懼 %d 碼半徑內的目標以驅逐他們，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Suppression", "詛咒抑制", "talent name")
t("The time you have spent suppressing the curse has taught you self control. The duration of most non-magical effects are reduced by %d%%.", "長年對抗詛咒的經歷使你能夠自我控制。大部分非魔法效果的持續時間減少 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Cruel Vigor", "殘酷活力", "talent name")
t("You are invigorated by the death around you. Each life you take grants %d%% speed for %d more turns.", "你被周圍的死亡所鼓舞。你每殺死一個單位提供你 %d%% 的速度，持續 %d 更多回合。", "tformat")
t("Pity", "憐憫", "talent name")
t("You hide your terrible nature behind a pitiful figure. Those that see you from a distance of %d will ignore you. If you attack or use a talent they will see you for what you are and pity will be deactivated.", [[你收起可怕的本質僞裝成可憐蟲。那些在 %d 碼外看到你的敵人將忽略你。 
		當你攻擊或使用技能時，它們會看穿你的本質，憐憫技能將失效。]], "tformat")


