section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/darkness.lua"

t("dark tendril", "黑暗觸鬚", "_t")
t("The dark tendrils dissipate.", "黑暗觸鬚消失了。", "logSeen")
t("The dark tendrils lash at %s.", "黑暗觸鬚攻擊了%s。", "logSeen")
t("Creeping Darkness", "黑暗之霧", "talent name")
t("%s's creeping dark", "%s的黑暗之霧", "tformat")
t([[Creeping dark slowly spreads from the target location and %d spots in a radius of %d around the targeted location. The dark deals %0.2f darkness damage each turn to anything in its area, and blocks the sight of any who do not possess Dark Vision or some other magical means of seeing.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower. You do +%d%% damage to anything that has entered your creeping dark.]], [[一股黑暗之霧蔓延在目標點和目標點附近 %d 碼範圍內最多 %d 格。黑暗之霧造成 %0.2f 點傷害，阻擋未掌握黑暗視覺或其他魔法視覺能力目標的視線。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。你對任何進入黑暗之霧的人造成 +%d%% 點傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Dark Vision", "黑暗視覺", "talent name")
t([[Your eyes penetrate the darkness to find anyone that may be hiding there. This allows you to see through creeping darkness out to a radius of %d. You can also find your way through the darkness with greater speed (+%d%% movement into creeping darkness).
		You do +%d%% damage to anything that has entered your creeping dark.]], [[你的眼睛穿過黑暗並發現隱藏在黑暗裏的敵人。 
		你的視線同樣可以穿過黑暗之霧看到 %d 的半徑範圍。同時黑暗之霧極大的提高你的步伐。 
		（在黑暗之霧中增加你 +%d%% 移動速度） 
		你對任何進入黑暗之霧的人造成 +%d%% 點傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Dark Torrent", "黑暗迸發", "talent name")
t([[Sends a torrent of searing darkness through your foes, doing %d damage. There is a 25%% chance the rushing darkness will blind them for 3 turns, and cause them to forget their target.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower. You do +%d%% damage to anything that has entered your creeping dark.]], [[向敵人發射一股灼熱的黑暗能量，造成 %d 點傷害。黑暗能量有 25%% 概率致盲目標 3 回合並使它們丟失當前目標。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。
		你對任何進入黑暗之霧的人造成 +%d%% 點傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Dark Tendrils", "黑暗觸手", "talent name")
t([[Send tendrils of creeping dark out to attack your target, and pin them in the darkness for %d turns. Creeping dark will trail behind the tendrils as they move. The darkness does %d damage per turn.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower. You do +%d%% damage to anything that has entered your creeping dark.]], [[伸出黑暗觸手攻擊你的敵人並使它們在黑暗裏定身 %d 回合。當黑暗觸手移動時，黑暗之霧會跟隨蔓延。 
		每回合黑暗會造成 %d 點傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。你對任何進入黑暗之霧的人造成 +%d%% 點傷害。]], "tformat")


