section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/endless-hunt.lua"

t("Stalk", "跟蹤", "talent name")
t("#F53CBE#You are having trouble focusing on your prey!", "#F53CBE#你無法集中注意力在你的目標身上！", "logPlayer")
t([[When you focus your attacks on a single foe and strike them in melee for two consecutive turns, your hatred of them overcomes you and you begin to stalk them with single-minded purpose. The effect will last for %d turns, or until your prey is dead. Stalking gives you bonuses against your foe that grow each turn you hit them, and diminish each turn you don't.
		Bonus level 1: +%d Accuracy, +%d%% melee damage, +%0.2f hate/turn prey was hit
		Bonus level 2: +%d Accuracy, +%d%% melee damage, +%0.2f hate/turn prey was hit
		Bonus level 3: +%d Accuracy, +%d%% melee damage, +%0.2f hate/turn prey was hit
		The accuracy bonus improves with your Willpower, and the melee damage bonus with your Strength.]], [[當你連續兩回合持續近戰攻擊同一個目標時，你將憎恨目標並追蹤目標，效果持續 %d 回合或直到目標死亡。 
		你每回合攻擊追蹤目標都將獲得可疊加增益效果，該效果在你不攻擊會減少 1 重效果。 
		1 重增益 ：+%d 命中， +%d%% 近戰傷害，當目標被擊中時，每回合增加 +%0.2f 仇恨值。
		2 重增益 ：+%d 命中， +%d%% 近戰傷害，當目標被擊中時，每回合增加 +%0.2f 仇恨值。
		3 重增益 ：+%d 命中， +%d%% 近戰傷害，當目標被擊中時，每回合增加 +%0.2f 仇恨值。
		命中受意志加成。 
		近戰傷害受力量值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Harass Prey", "痛苦折磨", "talent name")
t("#F53CBE#%s's %s is disrupted!", "#F53CBE#%s的%s中斷了！", "logSeen")
t([[Harass your stalked victim with two quick attacks for %d%% (at 0 Hate) to %d%% (at 100+ Hate) damage each. Each attack that scores a hit disrupts one talent, rune or infusion for %d turns. Your opponent will be unnerved by the attacks, reducing the damage they deal by %d%% for %d turns.
		Damage reduction increases with the Willpower stat.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[用兩次快速的攻擊折磨你追蹤的目標 , 每次攻擊造成 %d%% （0仇恨）～ %d%% （100+仇恨）的傷害。並且每次攻擊都將干擾目標某項技能、紋身或符文，持續 %d 回合。目標會因爲你的攻擊而氣餒，它的傷害降低 %d%% ，持續 %d 回合。
		傷害降低受意志加成。
		
		如果你裝備了盾牌，這一技能也會用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Beckon", "引誘思維", "talent name")
t([[The connection between predator and prey allows you to speak to the mind of your target and beckon them closer. For %d turns, they will try to come to you, even pushing others aside to do so. They will move towards you instead of acting %d%% of the time, but can save verses Mindpower to slow the effect. If they take significant damage, the beckoning may be overcome altogether. The effect makes concentration difficult for your target, reducing Spellpower and Mindpower by %d until they reach you.
		The Spellpower and Mindpower reduction increases with your Willpower.]], [[獵殺者和獵物之間的聯繫能讓你給予目標思想暗示 , 引誘他們更靠近你。 
		在 %d 回合內，目標會試圖接近你，甚至推開路徑上的其他單位。 
		每回合有 %d%% 的機率，它們會取消原有動作並直接向你走去。 
		目標受到致命攻擊時可能會打斷該效果，此效果會減少目標註意力，在它們到達你所在位置之前，降低其 %d 點法術強度和精神強度。 
		法術強度和精神強度的降低效果受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Surge", "殺意涌動", "talent name")
t([[Let hate fuel your movements. While active, you gain %d%% movement speed. The recklessness of your movement brings you bad luck (Luck -3).
		Cleave, Repel and Surge cannot be active simultaneously, and activating one will place the others in cooldown.
		Sustaining Surge while Dual Wielding grants %d additional Defense.
		Movement speed and dual-wielding Defense both increase with the Willpower stat.]], [[讓殺意激發你敏捷的身手 , 提高你 %d%% 移動速度。不顧一切的移動會帶給你厄運 (-3 幸運 )。 
		分裂攻擊、殺意涌動和無所畏懼不能同時開啓，並且激活其中一個也會使另外兩個進入冷卻。 
		雙持武器時，殺意涌動還會提高你 %d 的閃避。
		移動速度和雙持時的閃避增益受意志加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/fears.lua"

t("Instill Fear", "恐懼灌輸", "talent name")
t("%s resists the fear!", "%s抵抗了恐懼！", "logSeen")
t("#F53CBE#%s resists the fear!", "#F53CBE#%s抵抗了恐懼！", "logSeen")
t([[Instill fear in your foes within %d radius of a target location dealing %0.2f mind and %0.2f darkness damage and causing one of 4 possible fears that last for %d turns.
		The targets can save vs your Mindpower to resist the effect.
		Fear effects improve with your Mindpower.

		Possible fears are:
		#ORANGE#Paranoid:#LAST# Gives the target an %d%% chance to physically attack a nearby creature, friend or foe. If hit, their target will be afflicted with Paranoia as well.
		#ORANGE#Despair:#LAST# Reduces mind resist, mindsave, armour and defence by %d.
		#ORANGE#Terrified:#LAST# Deals %0.2f mind and %0.2f darkness damage per turn and increases cooldowns by %d%%.
		#ORANGE#Haunted:#LAST# Causes the target to suffer %0.2f mind and %0.2f darkness damage for each detrimental mental effect every turn.
		]], [[將恐懼注入目標 %d 半徑範圍內的敵人中，造成 %0.2f 精神和 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並隨機造成 4 種可能的恐懼效果之一，持續 %d 回合。
		目標可以與你的精神強度對抗，以抵抗恐懼效果。
		恐懼效果受精神強度加成。
		
		可能的恐懼效果如下所示：
		#ORANGE#妄想症:#LAST# 目標有 %d%% 機率使用物理攻擊附近的生物，不管它是敵對還是友方生物。如果擊中了目標，目標也會感染妄想症。
		#ORANGE#絕望:#LAST# 精神傷害抵抗，精神豁免，護甲值和閃避各降低 %d 。
		#ORANGE#驚懼:#LAST# 每回合受到 %0.2f 精神和 %0.2f 暗影傷害，技能冷卻時間增加 %d%% 。
		#ORANGE#惡靈纏身:#LAST# 目標每有一個負面精神效果，則每回合受到 %0.2f 精神和 %0.2f 暗影傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Heighten Fear", "恐懼加深", "talent name")
t([[Heighten the fears of those near to you. Any foe you attempt to inflict a fear upon and who remains in a radius of %d and in sight of you for %d (non-consecutive) turns, will take %0.2f mind and %0.2f darkness damage and gain a new fear that lasts for %d turns.
			This effect completely ignores fear resistance, but can be saved against.]], [[加深你周圍敵人的恐懼。所有被你灌注恐懼的目標若停留在你視野內，並且和你距離不超過 %d ，這樣累計達到 %d 回合時，受到 %0.2f 精神和 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並獲得一個新的持續 %d 回合的恐懼效果。
		這一效果無視恐懼免疫，但可以被豁免。]], "tformat")
t("Tyrant", "精神專制", "talent name")
t([[Impose your tyranny on the minds of those who fear you. When a foe gains a new fear, you have a %d%% chance to increase the duration of their heightened fear and one random existing fear effect by %d turns, to a maximum of 8 turns.
		Additionally, you gain %d Mindpower and Physical power for 5 turns every time you apply a fear, stacking up to %d times.]], [[提高對被你恐懼的目標的精神專制。當一個敵人獲得了一個新的恐懼效果，你有 %d%% 的機率增加這一效果和另一個隨機的已有恐懼效果的持續時間 %d 回合，最多 8 回合。
		此外，每當你恐懼一個目標，你獲得 %d 精神強度和物理強度，持續 5 回合，最多疊加 %d 層]], "tformat")
t("Panic", "驚慌失措", "talent name")
t("#F53CBE#%s ignores the panic!", "#F53CBE#%s無視驚恐！", "logSeen")
t("#F53CBE#%s resists the panic!", "#F53CBE#%s抵抗了驚恐！", "logSeen")
t("Panic your enemies within a range of %d for %d turns. Anyone who fails to make a mental save against your Mindpower has a %d%% chance each turn of trying to run away from you.", "使 %d 範圍內的敵人驚慌失措，持續 %d 回合，任何未通過精神豁免的敵人每回合將有 %d%% 概率從你身邊嚇走。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/force-of-will.lua"

t("Willful Strike", "偏執打擊", "talent name")
t("#Source# was blasted %d spaces into #Target#!", "#Source# 被推送%d格進入#Target#！", "logCombat")
t("#Source# was blasted into #Target#!", "#Source#撞向#Target#!", "logCombat")
t("%s was smashed back %d spaces!", "%s被擊退%d格！", "logSeen")
t("%s was smashed!", "%s被粉碎！", "logSeen")
t("%s was blasted back %d spaces!", "%s被擊退%d格！", "logSeen")
t([[Focusing your hate, you strike your foe with unseen force for %d damage and %d knockback.
		In addition, your ability to channel force with this talent increases all critical damage by %d%% (currently: %d%%)
		Damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[專注你的仇恨，你用無形的力量打擊敵人造成 %d 點傷害和 %d 碼擊退效果。 
		此外，你灌注力量的能力使你增加 %d%% 所有暴擊傷害。（當前： %d%% ） 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Deflection", "念力折射", "talent name")
t("Deflection (%d)", "念力折射 (%d)", "tformat")
t("You have deflected %d incoming damage!", "你偏轉了%d所受傷害。", "logPlayer")
t([[Create a barrier that siphons hate from you at the rate of 0.2 a turn. The barrier will deflect 50%% of incoming damage with the force of your will, up to %d damage. The barrier charges at a rate of 1/%d of its maximum charge per turn.
		In addition, your ability to channel force with this talent increases all critical damage by %d%% (currently: %d%%)
		The maximum damage deflected increases with your Mindpower.]], [[用你的意志力折射 50%% 的傷害。你可以折射最多 %d 點傷害，護盾值每回合回覆最大值的 1/%d 。（技能激活時-0.2仇恨值回覆）。
		你灌注力量的能力使你增加 %d%% 所有暴擊傷害。（當前： %d%% ） 
		最大傷害折射值受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blast", "怒火爆炸", "talent name")
t([[You rage coalesces at a single point, and then explodes outward, blasting enemies within a radius of %d in all directions. The blast causes %d damage and %d knockback at the center, that decreases with distance. Anyone caught in the explosion will also be dazed for 3 turns.
		In addition, your ability to channel force with this talent increases all critical damage by %d%% (currently: %d%%)
		Damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你將憤怒聚集在一點，然後向 %d 碼範圍內所有方向炸開。爆炸造成 %d 點傷害，在中心點處造成 %d 碼擊退效果，距離越遠效果越弱。 
		在爆炸範圍內的任何目標將會被眩暈 3 回合。 
		你灌注力量的能力使你每點增加 %d%% 所有暴擊傷害。（當前： %d%% ） 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Unseen Force", "無形之力", "talent name")
t([[Your fury becomes an unseen force that randomly lashes out at foes around you. For %d turns you strike %d (%d%% chance for %d) nearby target(s) within range %d doing %d damage and %d knockback. The number of extra strikes increases at higher talent levels.
		In addition, your ability to channel force with this talent increases all critical damage by %d%% (currently: %d%%)
		Damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你的憤怒變成一股無形之力，猛烈鞭笞你附近的隨機敵人。在 %d 回合內，你將攻擊 %d （ %d%% 概率攻擊 %d ）個半徑 %d 以內的敵人，造成 %d 點傷害並擊退 %d 碼。額外攻擊的數目隨技能等級增長。 
		你灌注力量的能力使你增加 %d%% 所有暴擊傷害。（當前： %d%% ） 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/gestures.lua"

t("Gesture of Pain", "痛苦手勢", "talent name")
t("You require two free or mindstar-equipped hands to use Gesture of Pain.", "你需要空手或雙持靈晶來激活痛苦手勢。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the Gesture of Pain.", "%s抵抗了痛苦手勢。", "logSeen")
t("#F53CBE#You revel in attacking a weakened foe! (+%d hate)", "#F53CBE#你沉醉於攻擊一個虛弱的敵人！（+%d 仇恨）", "logPlayer")
t([[Use a gesture of pain in place of a normal attack to assault the minds of your enemies, inflicting between %0.1f and %0.1f mind damage. If the attack succeeds, there is a %d%% chance to stun your opponent for 3 turns.
		This strike replaces your melee physical and checks your Mindpower against your opponent's Mental Save, and is thus not affected by your Accuracy or the enemy's Defense. The base damage (doubled) and the critical chance of any Mindstars equipped are added in when this attack is performed.
		This talent requires two free or mindstar-equipped hands and has a 25%% chance to inflict brainlock, which can critically hit. The damage will increase with your Mindpower.
		If attacking with two mindstars the attack will trigger their proc effects, if any.
		Mindstars bonuses from damage and physical criticals: (+%d damage, +%d critical chance)]], [[使用痛苦手勢來代替通常攻擊，對你的敵人的精神進行打擊，造成 %0.1f 到 %0.1f 點精神傷害。如果攻擊命中，有 %d%% 概率震懾你的目標 3 個回合。 
		這項攻擊採用你的精神強度而非物理強度，同時需檢查對方精神豁免。這項攻擊不受你的命中或對方閃避影響，也不會觸發任何當你的武器命中對方時觸發的效果。但是，你的靈晶提供的基礎傷害（按雙倍計算）和暴擊率會被計算入攻擊中。 
		這項技能需要你空手或雙持靈晶，同時有 25%% 概率觸發可暴擊的思維封鎖效果。
		如果用雙持靈晶攻擊，能夠觸發命中效果。
		傷害受精神強度加成。
		受靈晶影響，增加 %d 傷害和 %d 暴擊率。]], "tformat")
t("Gesture of Malice", "怨恨手勢", "talent name")
t([[Enhance your Gesture of Pain with a malicious curse that causes any victim that is struck to have all resistances lowered by %d%% for %d turns.
		]], [[使你的痛苦手勢充滿怨恨的詛咒，任何受到痛苦手勢攻擊的目標會降低 %d%% 所有抵抗，持續 %d 回合。
		]], "tformat")
t("Gesture of Power", "力量手勢", "talent name")
t([[Enhance your mental attacks with a single gesture. You gain +%d mindpower and +%d%% chance to inflict critical damage with mind-based attacks (current chance is %d%%).
		Requires two free or mindstar-equipped hands; does not require Gesture of Pain to be sustained.]], [[通過一個手勢來增強你的精神攻擊。你獲得 +%d 精神強度和 +%d%% 機率增加精神攻擊的暴擊率（當前機率爲 %d%% ）。 
		需要至少一隻空手或者裝備靈晶。不需要痛苦手勢持續激活。]], "tformat")
t("Gesture of Guarding", "守護手勢", "talent name")
t("#F53CBE##Source# lashes back at #Target#!", "#F53CBE##Source#反擊#Target#!", "logCombat")
t([[You guard against melee damage with a sweep of your hand. So long as you can use Gestures (Requires two free or mindstar-equipped hands), you deflect up to %d damage (%0.1f%% of your best free hand melee damage) from up to %0.1f melee attack(s) each turn (based on your cunning). Deflected attacks cannot be crits.
		If Gesture of Pain is active, you also have a %0.1f%% chance to counterattack.]], [[ 你通過手勢來防禦近戰傷害。只要你能使用手勢（要求空手或雙持靈晶），你最多偏移 %d 點傷害（你的單手最大傷害的 %0.1f%% ），每回合最多觸發 %0.1f 次（基於你的靈巧）。成功防禦的攻擊不會暴擊。
		如果痛苦手勢被激活，你將有 %0.1f%% 的概率造成反擊狀態。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/gloom.lua"

t("Gloom", "黑暗光環", "talent name")
t("#F53CBE#Your heart hardens as a powerful foe enters your gloom! (+%d hate)", "#F53CBE#當一個強力的敵人進入黑暗光環你的內心變得更加冷酷！（+%d 仇恨）", "logPlayer")
t([[A terrible gloom surrounds you, affecting all those who approach to within radius 3. At the end of each game turn, those caught in your gloom must save against your Mindpower, or have a %d%% chance to suffer from slowness (30%%), stun or confusion (30%%) for %d turns.
		The chance increases with your mind speed.
		This ability is innate, and carries no cost to activate or deactivate.
		Each point in Gloom talents increases your Mindpower (current total: %d).]], [[一個 3 碼半徑範圍的可怕黑暗光環圍繞你 , 影響附近的敵人。在每個遊戲回合結束時，光環內的每一個目標必須與你的精神強度進行豁免鑑定，未通過鑑定則有 %d%% 概率被減速30%% 、震懾或混亂(30%%)，持續 %d 回合。 
		機率受精神速度影響。
		這個能力是與生俱來的，激活或停止不消耗任何能量。
		黑暗光環樹下的每個技能都會增加你的精神強度（當前總計： %d ）。]], "tformat")
t("Weakness", "黑暗衰竭", "talent name")
t([[Each turn, those caught in your gloom must save against your Mindpower, or have a %d%% chance to be crippled by fear for %d turns, reducing damage they inflict by %d%%. The first time you melee strike a foe after they have been weakened will give you %d hate.
		The chance increases with your mind speed.
		Each point in Gloom talents increases your Mindpower (current total: %d).]], [[在黑暗光環裏的每一個目標每回合必須與你的精神強度進行豁免鑑定，未通過鑑定則有 %d%% 概率被恐懼而虛弱持續 %d 回合，降低 %d%% 傷害，你對被削弱目標的首次近戰攻擊能獲得 %d 點仇恨值。 
		機率受精神速度影響。
		黑暗光環樹下的每個技能都會增加你的精神強度（當前總計： %d ）。]], "tformat")
t("Mindrot", "思維腐蝕", "talent name")
t([[Every turn, all enemies in your gloom take %0.2f mind damage and %0.2f darkness damage.
		This damage is increased by your global speed but only happens ever game turn.
		The damage scales with your Mindpower.
		Each point in Gloom talents increases your Mindpower (current total: %d).]], [[所有在你黑暗光環內的敵人每回合會受到 %0.2f 精神傷害和 %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		傷害受整體速度加成，但每個遊戲回合最多觸發一次。
		傷害受精神強度影響。
		黑暗光環樹下的每個技能都會增加你的精神強度（當前總計： %d ）。]], "tformat")
t("Sanctuary", "庇護光環", "talent name")
t([[Your gloom has become a sanctuary from the outside world. Damage from any attack that originates beyond the boundary of your gloom is reduced by %d%%.
		Each point in Gloom talents increases your Mindpower (current total: %d).]], [[你的黑暗光環成爲獨立於外界的避難所，任何光環外的目標對你的傷害降低 %d%% 。 
		黑暗光環樹下的每個技能都會增加你的精神強度（當前總計： %d ）。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/one-with-shadows.lua"

t("Shadow Senses", "陰影感知", "talent name")
t([[Your awareness extends to your shadows.
		You always know exactly where your shadows are and can perceive any foe within %d tiles of their vision.]], [[ 你的意識延伸到陰影上。
		你能清晰的感知到陰影的位置，同時還能感知到陰影視野 %d 碼範圍內的敵人。]], "tformat")
t("Shadows Empathy", "陰影鏈接", "talent name")
t([[You empathy with your shadows causes the line between you and your shadows to blur.
		You lose %d%% light resistance, but gain %d%% darkness resistance and affinity. You also gain %0.2f%% all resistance for each shadow in your party.]], [[你與你的陰影鏈接，你和你的陰影之間的界限漸漸模糊。
		你失去 %d%% 光系傷害抗性，獲得 %d%% 暗影傷害抗性和傷害吸收。你的隊伍裏每有一個陰影，就獲得 %0.2f%% 所有傷害抗性。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Transposition", "陰影換位", "talent name")
t([[Observers find it difficult to tell you and your shadows apart.
		You can target a shadow in radius %d and instantly trade places with it.
		%d random negative physical or magical effects are transferred from you to the chosen shadow in the process.]], [[ 現在，其他人很難分清你和陰影。 
		 你能選擇半徑 %d 範圍內的一個陰影並和它交換位置。
		同時至多 %d 個隨機負面物理或魔法效果會被轉移至選擇的陰影身上。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Decoy", "陰影誘餌", "talent name")
t("#GOLD#(%d decoy)#LAST#", "#GOLD#(%d 陰影誘餌)#LAST#", "tformat")
t("#GOLD#%d decoy#LAST#", "#GOLD#%d 陰影誘餌#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Your shadows guard you with their lives.
		When you would receive a fatal blow, you instantly transpose with a random shadow that takes the blow instead, putting this talent on cooldown.
		For the next 4 turns you only die if you reach -%d life.
		Effect increases with Mindpower.]], [[你的陰影用生命來守護你。
		當你受到致命攻擊時，你將立刻和隨機一個陰影換位，讓它代替承受攻擊，並將此技能打入冷卻。
		在接下來的 4 個回合，除非你的生命降至 -%d 下，否則你不會死去。
		效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/predator.lua"

t("Predator", "獵殺者", "talent name")
t("Improve your predation by learning from past hunts. You gain %0.2f accuracy and %0.2f armor penetration against foes for each foe of that type you have previously slain, to a maximum of %d accuracy and %d apr.", "你從過去的殺戮中汲取知識，強化你獵殺的能力。你過去每殺死過該類型的一個生物，就獲得 %0.2f 命中和 %0.2f 護甲穿透，最多 %d 命中和 %d 護甲穿透。", "tformat")
t("Savage Hunter", "兇殘獵手", "talent name")
t("%s's cursed miasma", "%s的詛咒瘴氣", "tformat")
t([[Upon making a critical melee attack the savagery of your predation causes a Cursed Miasma to begin permeating your hunting grounds.
		The miasma will seep from %d locations, including your own, within radius %d, deals %0.2f damage split between Darkness and Mind and blocks sight.
		Prey lost within your miasma have a %d%% chance to lose track of you and may mistake friends for foe.
		Savage Hunter costs #ffa0ff#8 Hate#LAST# on trigger and does not trigger when you're in Cursed Miasma.]], [[每當你造成一次近戰暴擊，你兇殘的捕獵慾望在你的狩獵場中產生一股詛咒瘴氣。
		瘴氣會試圖擴散到半徑 %d 碼內的 %d 格內，包括你自己所在的位置，對敵人交替造成 %0.2f 暗影或精神傷害，並阻擋視線。
		迷失在你瘴氣中的獵物有 %d%% 的機率失去你的位置，並有可能攻擊自己的盟友。
		兇殘獵手觸發時會消耗 #ffa0ff#8 點仇恨值 #LAST# ，不會當你位於詛咒瘴氣中時觸發。]], "tformat")
t("Shrouded Hunter", "障壁獵手", "talent name")
t([[While shrouded in cursed miasma you gain stealth (%d power) and %d physical power.
		The stealth power and physical power will increase with your mindpower.]], [[當你被包裹在詛咒瘴氣中時，你獲得潛行 (%d 強度) ，並獲得 %d 物理強度。
		潛行強度和物理強度受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Mark Prey", "獵殺標記", "talent name")
t("Focus your predation on the most worthy prey. Upon entering a level for the first time, up to %d foes are marked as your prey. You gain vision of them, wherever they are. Additionally, all damage you receive from their subtype is reduced by %d%%.", "將你的獵殺慾望集中在最重要的獵物身上。當你第一次走入某張地圖，你會將最多 %d 個敵人標記成你的獵物。無論它們在哪裏，你可以獲得它們的視野。此外，對於所有它們所屬的子分類的敵人，你從它們那裏受到的傷害降低 %d%% 。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/primal-magic.lua"

t("Arcane Bolts", "奧術飛彈", "talent name")
t([[Each turn for 4 turns you fire a bolt of arcane energy at your nearest enemy inflicting %d damage.
		The damage will increase with the Magic stat.]], [[連續4個回合向你最近目標發射奧術能量彈，造成 %d 傷害。
		傷害受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Displace", "位移", "talent name")
t("Selects a displacement location...", "選擇一個轉移目標...", "logPlayer")
t("Your attempt to displace fails!", "你嘗試置換術但是失敗了！", "logSeen")
t("Instantaneously displace yourself within line of sight up to 3 squares away.", "瞬間將你移動至視線內3碼以外。", "tformat")
t("Primal Skin", "原始皮膚", "talent name")
t([[Years of magic have permeated your skin leaving it resistant to the physical world. Your armor is increased by %d.
		The bonus will increase with the Magic stat.]], [[魔法滲透進你的皮膚，增加你的物理抗性，提高你的護甲值 %d 。
		增益效果受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Vaporize", "蒸發", "talent name")
t([[Bathes the target in raw magic inflicting %d damage. Such wild magic is difficult to control and if you fail to keep your wits you will be confused for 4 turns.
		The damage will increase with the Magic stat.]], [[蒸騰你的目標造成 %d 傷害。這個魔法難以駕馭，如果施放失敗你會被混亂4回合。
		傷害受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/punishments.lua"

t("Reproach", "意念懲罰", "talent name")
t([[You unleash your hateful mind on any who dare approach you, inflicing %d mind damage. The attack will hit multiple targets, but each additional target will further reduce damage by %d%%.
		25%% chance to brainlock. The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你對任何敢於靠近的敵人釋放意念懲罰，造成 %d 精神傷害。攻擊可能會指向多個目標，但是每個目標會減少 %d%% 傷害。 
		25%% 概率附加思維封鎖效果。傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hateful Whisper", "憎恨私語", "talent name")
t([[Send a whisper filled with hate to spread throughout your foes. When the whisper is first heard, they will suffer %d mind damage and feed you %d hate. For the first %d turns, the whisper will travel from the original victim to a new one within a range of %0.1f. Every victim of the whisper has a %d%% chance of spreading it to another victim every turn.
		25%% chance to brainlock. The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你向周圍的敵人發出充滿憎恨的私語。第 1 個聽到的敵人會受到 %d 點精神傷害並提供你 %d 仇恨值。在最初的 %d 回合裏私語會從目標身上傳播到 %0.1f 碼半徑範圍新的敵人身上。 
		每個目標在每回合有 %d%% 機率將私語傳播向另一個目標。 
		25%% 概率附加思維封鎖效果。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Agony", "極度痛苦", "talent name")
t([[Unleash agony upon your target. The pain will grow over the course of %d turns. The first turn will inflict %d damage, and slowly increase to %d on the last turn (%d total).
		25%% chance of brainlock. The damage will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[對你的目標釋放極大的痛苦。痛苦會在 %d 回合內逐漸增加。第一回合會造成 %d 點傷害並在最後 1 回合增加至 %d 點傷害（總計 %d ）。 
		25%% 概率附加思維封鎖效果。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Madness", "絕望", "talent name")
t("Every time you inflict mind damage, there is a %d%% chance that your foe must save against your Mindpower or go mad. Madness can cause them to become confused, slowed or stunned for 3 turns, and lowers resistance to mind damage by %d%%.", "每次你造成精神傷害時，有 %d%% 概率你的敵人必須用精神抵抗抵消你的精神強度，否則會崩潰。精神崩潰會使它們在短時間內被混亂、減速或震懾 3 回合，並且降低它們 %d%% 對精神傷害的抵抗。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/rampage.lua"

t("Rampage", "暴走", "talent name")
t("You are already rampaging!", "你已經在暴走狀態！", "logPlayer")
t([[You enter a terrible rampage for %d turns (up to a maximum of %d turns), destroying everything in your path. Starting a rampage is instantaneous. You may also enter a rampage (50%% chance) when you are hit for more than 8%% of your max life. 
		Any talent, rune or infusion you use while rampaging becomes a distraction, and reduces the duration of the rampage by 1. Your first movement while rampaging increases the rampage duration by 1.
		Rampage Bonus: +%d%% movement speed.
		Rampage Bonus: +%d%% attack speed.
		Rampage Bonus: +%d%% mind speed.]], [[你進入暴走狀態 %d 回合（最多 %d 回合），摧毀在你路徑上的所有東西。主動進入暴走狀態不需要時間，同時也有 50%% 機率在你受到 8%% 最大生命值以上的傷害時自動激活。暴走狀態下你使用任何技能、符文或紋身都無法專心使得技能效果持續時間縮短 1 回合，暴走狀態下的第一次移動可延長暴走效果 1 回合。
		暴走加成： +%d%% 移動速度。 
		暴走加成： +%d%% 攻擊速度。
		暴走加成： +%d%% 精神速度。]], "tformat")
t("Brutality", "無情", "talent name")
t([[You attack with mindless brutality. The first critical hit inflicted while rampaging increases the rampage duration by 1.
		Rampage Bonus: Your physical damage increases by %d%%.
		Rampage Bonus: Your Physical Save increases by %d and Mental Save increases by %d.]], [[使你的暴走更加無情，暴走狀態下的第一次暴擊可延長暴走效果 1 回合。 
		暴走加成：你的物理傷害增加 %d%% 。 
		暴走加成：你的物理豁免增加 %d ，精神豁免增加 %d 。]], "tformat")
t("Tenacity", "不屈不撓", "talent name")
t([[Nothing will stop your rampage.
		Rampage Bonus: You shrug off up to %d damage each turn during your rampage. If you shrug off more than %d damage, the rampage duration increases by 1.
		The amount of damage you can shrug off improves with your Strength.]], [[你的暴走變得勢不可擋。 
		暴走加成：暴走狀態下每回合你最多可以無視 %d 傷害，當你無視超過 %d 傷害時，暴走效果延長 1 回合。 
		受力量加成，你無視的傷害有額外加成。]], "tformat")
t("Slam", "猛力抨擊", "talent name")
t("You must be rampaging to use this talant.", "只有在暴走狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("#F53CBE#%s slams %s!", "#F53CBE#%s 猛擊了 %s ！", "logSeen")
t("#F53CBE#%s resists the stunning blow!", "#F53CBE#%s抵抗了震懾一擊！", "logSeen")
t("#F53CBE#Your rampage is invigorated by the collosal slam! (+1 duration)", "#F53CBE#你的暴走受到鼓舞！（+1 持續時間）。", "logPlayer")
t([[While rampaging, you slam up to %d adjacent opponents, stunning them for %d turns and damaging them for between %d and %d physical damage. Your first slam of at least two opponents increases the rampage duration by 1.
		Damage increases with your Physical Power.]], [[暴走狀態中，你可以攻擊到最多 %d 個鄰近目標，震懾他們 %d 回合，並造成 %d ～ %d 物理傷害，首次同時對兩個以上目標造成的攻擊可以延長暴走效果 1 回合。 
		傷害受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/self-hatred.lua"

t("Self-Sacrifice", "自我犧牲", "talent name")
t("You can only use this while in combat", "你只能在戰鬥中使用此技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[At the start of each turn, if you're bleeding, you gain %d hate.

You can activate this talent to use your own life for power, bleeding yourself for a small portion of your maximum life (%0.2f damage) over the next 5 turns. This bleed cannot be resisted or removed, but can be reduced by Bloodstained.]], [[每回合開始時，如果你正在流血，你獲得 %d 仇恨。

你可以主動使用此技能，使用你的生命值換取力量，使你在5回合裏受到最大生命值一小部分的流血傷害（ %0.2f 傷害）。此流血效果不能被抵抗，無法被移除，但可以被血染系技能減少。]], "tformat")
t("Self-Loathing", "自憤", "talent name")
t([[Increases critical chance by %d%% (at all times) and critical strike power by up to %d%% (based on hate).

#{italic}#Anger makes you strong. And you're always angry.#{normal}#]], [[增加 %d%% 暴擊率（始終）並增加最多 %d%% 暴擊傷害（基於當前仇恨值）。

#{italic}#憤怒使你更強，而你始終憤怒。#{normal}#]], "tformat")
t("Self-Destruction", "自毀", "talent name")
t("tore themself apart", "把自己撕成碎片", "_t")
t([[Call upon your deepest reserves of strength to win no matter the cost. 
Immediately upon activation and every turn while this talent is active, your detrimental effects expire and your talents cool down as if an extra turn had passed. 
This bonus cooldown occurs even if your talents would not normally cool down.
This talent deactivates automatically upon rest.
This strength comes at a cost: you lose %d%% of your maximum life every turn.  This can kill you.

#{italic}#If you're lucky, this will take everything you've got.#{normal}#]], [[喚起你保留在最深處的力量，以不顧一切代價取勝。
使用這一技能的瞬間，和之後這一技能持續開啓的每一回合，你的負面效果持續時間和技能冷卻時間都會額外減少一回合。
即使你的技能冷卻時間本來不會降低，這一效果也可以降低其冷卻時間。
這一技能在休息時自動關閉。
這一力量的代價是你每回合損失 %d%% 的最大生命。這一效果可以殺死你。

#{italic}#如果你走運，代價就是你的一切。#{normal}#]], "tformat")
t("Self-Judgement", "自裁", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON##Target# suffers from %s from #Source#, mitigating the blow!#LAST#.", "#CRIMSON##Target# 承受了來自#Source#的 %s , 降低了傷害!#LAST#.", "logCombat")
t("%s(%d bled out#LAST#%s)#LAST#", "%s(%d 減免#LAST#%s)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Any direct damage that exceeds %d%% of your maximum life has the excess damage converted to a shallow wound that bleeds over the next %d turns. This bleed cannot be resisted or removed, but can be reduced by Bloodstained. Extremely powerful hits (more than %d%% of your max life) are not fully converted.

#{italic}#You can't just die. That would be too easy.#{normal}#]], [[任何超過你最大生命 %d%% 的傷害中的額外部分會變成一道淺表傷口，在接下來的 %d 回合中造成流血傷害。此流血效果不能被抵抗或去除，但強度可以被血染系技能降低。極其強力的攻擊（超過 %d%% 最大生命）無法被完全轉化。

#{italic}#你不能就這麼死了。這太輕鬆了。#{normal}#]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/shadows.lua"

t("Fade", "消隱", "talent name")
t("You fade from sight, making you invulnerable until the beginning of your next turn.", "你從視線中消失並無敵，直到下一回合開始。", "tformat")
t("Phase Door", "相位之門", "talent name")
t("Teleports you within a small range.", "在小範圍內傳送你自己。", "tformat")
t("Blindside", "閃電突襲", "talent name")
t("With blinding speed you suddenly appear next to a target up to %d spaces away and attack for %d%% damage.", "你以難以置信的速度閃現至附近 %d 碼的一個目標身邊並造成 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")
t("Shadow Lightning", "暗影閃電", "talent name")
t([[Strikes the target with a spark of lightning doing %0.2f to %0.2f damage (%0.2f average).
		The damage will increase with the Magic stat]], [[用閃電打擊目標造成 %0.2f 到 %0.2f 傷害 (平均 %0.2f 傷害)。
		傷害受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Flames", "暗影之火", "talent name")
t([[Bathes the target in flames doing %0.2f damage
		The damage will increase with the Magic stat]], [[用火焰灼燒你的目標造成 %0.2f 傷害。 
		傷害受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Reform", "重組", "talent name")
t("When a shadow is hit and killed, there is a %d%% chance it will reform unhurt.", "當陰影受到傷害或被殺死，有 %d%% 機率重組並免受傷害。", "tformat")
t("Call Shadows", "召喚陰影", "talent name")
t("Your hate is too low to call another shadow!", "你的仇恨值不足，無法召喚陰影。", "logPlayer")
t("Summon", "召喚", "_t")
t([[While this ability is active, you will continually call up to %d level %d shadows to aid you in battle. Each shadow costs 5 hate to summon. Shadows are weak combatants that can: Use Arcane Reconstruction to heal themselves (level %d), Blindside their opponents (level %d), and Phase Door from place to place.
		Shadows ignore %d%% of the damage dealt to them by their master.]], [[當此技能激活時，你可以召喚 %d 個等級 %d 的陰影幫助你戰鬥。每個陰影需消耗 6 點仇恨值召喚。 
		陰影是脆弱的戰士，它們能夠：使用奧術重組治療自己（等級 %d ），使用靈異打擊突襲目標（等級 %d ），使用相位之門進行傳送。
		陰影無視 %d%% 主人造成的傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Warriors", "陰影戰士", "talent name")
t("Instill hate in your shadows, strengthening their attacks. They gain %d%% extra Accuracy and %d%% extra damage. The fury of their attacks gives them the ability to try to Dominate their foes, increasing all damage taken by that foe for 4 turns (level %d, %d%% chance at range 1). They also gain the ability to Fade when hit, avoiding all damage until their next turn (%d turn cooldown).", [[將仇恨注入你的陰影，強化他們的攻擊。他們獲得 %d%% 額外命中和 %d%% 額外傷害加成。 
		他們瘋狂的攻擊可以令他們支配對手，提高被支配目標所受到的所有傷害 4 回合（等級 %d ， %d%% 機率 1 碼範圍）。 
		它們同時擁有消隱的能力，免疫所有傷害直到下一回合開始（ %d 回合冷卻時間）。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Mages", "陰影法師", "talent name")
t([[Infuse magic into your shadows to give them fearsome spells. Your shadows receive a bonus of %d to their Spellpower.
		Your shadows can strike adjacent foes with Lightning (level %d, %d%% chance at range 1).
		At level 3 your shadows can sear their enemies from a distance with Flames (level %d, %d%% chance at range 2 to 6).
		At level 5 when your shadows are struck down they will attempt to Reform, becoming whole again (50%% chance).]], [[灌輸魔力給你的陰影使它們學會可怕的法術。你的陰影獲得 %d 點法術強度加成。 
		你的陰影可以用閃電術攻擊附近的目標（等級 %d ， %d%% 機率 1 碼範圍）。 
		等級 3 時你的陰影可以遠距離使用火焰術灼燒你的敵人（等級 %d ， %d%% 機率 2 到 6 碼範圍）。 
		等級 5 時你的陰影在被擊倒時有一定機率重組並重新加入戰鬥（50%% 機率）。]], "tformat")
t("Focus Shadows", "聚集陰影", "talent name")
t("#PINK#The shadows converge on #Target#!", "#PINK#陰影被集中至 #Target# ！", "logCombat")
t("There are no shadows to heed the call!", "沒有陰影可以召喚！", "logPlayer")
t("#PINK#The shadows form around #Target#!", "#PINK#陰影被集中至 #Target# ！", "logCombat")
t("Their are no shadows to heed the call!", "沒有陰影可以召喚！", "logPlayer")
t([[Focus your shadows on a single target. Friendly targets will be defended for %d turns. Hostile targets will be attacked, with a %d%% chance the shadows will blindside the target.
		If you have less than maximum shadows available, they will automatically be summoned before focusing.
		This talent has no cost.]], [[將你的陰影聚集至單一目標。如果目標爲友善則保護目標 %d 回合。如目標爲敵對則有 %d%% 機率使用靈異打擊攻擊目標。 
		如果你的陰影數目少於最大值，將在聚集前召喚出來。
		該技能不消耗任何能量。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/slaughter.lua"

t("Slash", "削砍", "talent name")
t([[You slash wildly at your target for %d%% (at 0 Hate) to %d%% (at 100+ Hate) damage.
		At level 3, any wound you inflict with this carries a part of your curse, reducing the effectiveness of healing by %d%% for %d turns. The effect will stack.
		The damage multiplier increases with your Strength.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[野蠻的削砍你的目標造成 %d%% （0仇恨）至 %d%% （100+仇恨）傷害。
		等級 3 時攻擊附帶詛咒，降低目標治療效果 %d%% 持續 %d 回合，效果可疊加。 
		傷害比例受力量值加成。
		如果你裝備了盾牌，這一技能也會用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Frenzy", "狂熱", "talent name")
t("You require a mainhand weapon to use this talent.", "你需要裝備主手武器來使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Assault nearby foes with 4 fast attacks for %d%% (at 0 Hate) to %d%% (at 100+ Hate) damage each. Stalked prey are always targeted if nearby.
		At level 3 the intensity of your assault overwhelms anyone who is struck, reducing their Defense by %d for 4 turns.
		The damage multiplier and Defense reduction increase with your Strength.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[對附近目標進行 4 次攻擊每個目標造成 %d%% （0仇恨值）至 %d%% （100+仇恨值）。附近被追蹤的目標會被優先攻擊。
		等級 3 時你的猛烈攻擊會同時降低目標 %d 的閃避，持續 4 回合。 
		傷害加成和閃避減值受力量值加成。
		如果你裝備了盾牌，這一技能也會用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Reckless Charge", "魯莽衝撞", "talent name")
t("#Source# knocks back #Target#!", "#Source#擊退了#Target#！", "logCombat")
t("#Target# blocks #Source#!", "#Target# 格擋了 #Source#！", "logCombat")
t("Charge through your opponents, attacking anyone near your path for %d%% (at 0 Hate) to %d%% (at 100+ Hate) damage. %s opponents may be knocked away from your path. You can attack a maximum of %d times, and can hit targets along your path more than once.", "衝過你的目標，途經的所有目標受到 %d%% （0仇恨）至 %d%% （100+仇恨）傷害。 %s 體型的目標會被你彈開。你最多可以攻擊 %d 次，並且你對路徑上的敵人可造成不止 1 次攻擊。", "tformat")
t("Cleave", "分裂攻擊", "talent name")
t("#Source# cleaves through #Target#!", "#Source#劈中了#Target#！", "logCombat")
t([[While active, every swing of your weapon strikes strikes other adjacent enemies for %d%% (at 0 hate) to %d%% (at 100 hate) physical damage. The recklessness of your attacks brings you bad luck (luck -3).
		Cleave, Repel and Surge cannot be active simultaneously, and activating one will place the others in cooldown.
		Cleave will deal 25%% additional damage while using a two-handed weapon.
		The Cleave damage increases with your Strength.]], [[當激活時，你的每一次武器攻擊都會攻擊一個臨近的目標，造成 %d%% （0仇恨值）到 %d%% （100+仇恨值）的物理傷害。不顧一切的殺戮會帶給你厄運（-3 幸運）。
		分裂攻擊、殺意涌動和無所畏懼不能同時開啓，並且激活一個也會使另外兩個進入冷卻。
		當使用雙手武器時，分裂攻擊會造成 25%% 的額外傷害。
		分裂攻擊傷害受力量值加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/strife.lua"

t("Dominate", "壓制", "talent name")
t([[Turn your attention to a nearby foe, and dominate them with your overwhelming presence. If the target fails to save versus your Mindpower, it will be unable to move for %d turns and vulnerable to attacks. They will lose %d Armour, %d Defense and your attacks will gain %d%% resistance penetration. If the target is adjacent to you, your domination will include a melee attack.
		Effects will improve with your Willpower.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[將注意力轉移到附近目標並用你強大的氣場壓制它。如果目標未能通過精神強度豁免鑑定，目標 %d 回合內將無法移動並受到更多傷害。目標降低 %d 點護甲值、 %d 點閃避，並且你對目標的攻擊會增加 %d%% 抵抗穿透。如如果目標與你相鄰 , 那麼此技能會附加一次近戰攻擊。 
		效果受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Preternatural Senses", "第七感覺", "talent name")
t([[Your preternatural senses aid you in your hunt for the next victim. You sense foes in a radius of %0.1f. You will always sense a stalked victim in a radius of 10.
		Also increases stealth detection by %d and invisibility detection by %d.
		Stealth and invisibility detection improves with your Willpower]], [[你的第 7 感能讓你能在狩獵中發現下個犧牲品。 
		你能感覺到 %0.1f 碼半徑範圍內的敵人。 
		在 10 碼半徑範圍內你總能看見被追蹤的目標。
		同時增加你的偵測潛行等級 %d ，偵測隱形等級 %d 。
		偵測強度受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blindside", "閃電突襲", "talent name")
t("The blindside fizzles!", "閃電突襲失敗了！", "logSeen")
t([[With blinding speed, you suddenly appear next to a target up to %d spaces away and attack for %d%% (at 0 Hate) to %d%% (at 100+ Hate) damage. Your sudden appearance catches everyone off-guard, giving you %d extra Defense for 1 turn.
		The Defense boost improves with your Strength.]], [[你閃電般的出現在 %d 碼範圍內的敵人身邊，造成 %d%% （0仇恨）～ %d%% （100+仇恨）的傷害。
		你閃電般的突襲使敵人沒有提防，增加 %d 點額外閃避，持續 1 回合。 
		閃避值受力量值加成。
		如果你裝備盾牌的話，這一技能也可以使用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Repel", "無所畏懼", "talent name")
t([[Rather than hide from the onslaught, you face down every threat. While active you have a %d%% chance of repelling a melee attack. The recklessness of your defense brings you bad luck (Luck -3).
		Cleave, Repel and Surge cannot be active simultaneously, and activating one will place the others in cooldown.
		Repel chance increases with your Strength and by 20%% when equipped with a shield.]], [[在猛烈的攻擊面前，你選擇直面威脅而不是躲藏。 
		當技能激活時，你有 %d%% 概率抵擋一次近程攻擊。不顧一切的防禦會帶給你厄運（-3幸運）。
		分裂攻擊，殺意涌動和無所畏懼不能同時開啓，並且激活其中一個也會使另外兩個進入冷卻。 
		抵擋概率受力量加成。
		裝備盾牌時，抵擋概率增加 20%% ]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/cursed/traveler.lua"

t("Hardened", "堅韌", "talent name")
t("Your travels have hardened you. You gain +%d armor.", "你的經歷使你的護甲值增加 +%d 。", "tformat")
t("Wary", "謹慎", "talent name")
t("You have become wary of danger in your journeys. You have a %d%% chance of not triggering traps.", "你的行動變得更加謹慎，有 %d%% 機率不會觸發陷阱。", "tformat")
t("Weathered", "風化", "talent name")
t("You have become weathered by the elements. Your Cold and Fire resistance is increased by %d%%", "你更適應元素攻擊，增加你火焰和寒冷抵抗 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Savvy", "領悟", "talent name")
t("You have become a keen observer in your travels. Each kill gives you %d%% more experience.", "你在旅途中逐漸成長爲一個敏銳的觀察者，殺死敵人獲得 %d%% 更多經驗值。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/antimagic.lua"

t("Resolve", "分解", "talent name")
t([[You stand in the way of magical damage. That which does not kill you will make you stronger.
		When you are hit by hostile non-physical, non-mind damage you gain %d%% resistance to that element for 7 turns.
		At talent level 3, the bonus resistance may apply to 3 elements, refreshing the duration with each element added.
		Additionally, each time you take non-physical, non-mind damage, your equilibrium will decrease and stamina increase by %0.2f.
		The effects will increase with the greater of your Mindpower or Physical power and the bonus resistance can be a mental crit.]], [[你選擇了站在魔法的對立面。那些未能殺死你的磨難將使你更加強大。 
		每次你從敵對目標那裏受到一種非物理、非精神時，你能增加 %d%% 對該類型傷害的抵抗，持續 7 回合。 
		在技能等級 3 時，你可以獲得對 3 種類型的抵抗，每增加一種類型時都會刷新持續時間。
		此外，每當你被非物理，非精神傷害擊中時，你會降低 %0.2f 失衡值並增加等量體力值。
		技能效果受精神或物理強度較高者加成。
		抗性加成效果可以觸發精神暴擊。]], "tformat")
t("Antimagic Zone", "反魔領域", "talent name")
t("%s resists the silence!", "%s抵抗了沉默！", "logSeen")
t([[Let out a burst of sound that silences for %d turns all those affected in a radius of %d.
		Each turn for %d turns the effected area will cause %0.2f manaburn damage to all creatures inside.
		For each creature silenced your equilibrium is reduced by %d (up to 5 times).
		The damage and apply power will increase with the greater of your Mindpower or Physical power.

		Learning this talent will let your Nature damage and penetration bonuses apply to all Manaburn damage regardless of source.]], [[發出一次音波衝擊，沉默周圍目標 %d 回合，有效範圍 %d 碼。 
		在 %d 回合內，受影響的區域裏的所有生物受到 %0.2f 法力燃燒傷害。
		每沉默一個目標，你回覆 %d 失衡值，至多 5 次。
		沉默機率受精神或物理強度較高者加成。
		
		學會這個技能，也會讓你的自然傷害加成和傷害穿透屬性，對所有法力燃燒傷害生效，不管這一傷害的來源是什麼。]], "tformat")
t("Antimagic Shield", "反魔法護盾", "talent name")
t("#GREEN#The antimagic shield of %s crumbles.", "#GREEN#%s的反魔法護盾消失了。", "logSeen")
t([[Surround yourself with a shield that will absorb at most %d non-physical, non-mind element damage per attack.
		Each time damage is absorbed by the shield, your equilibrium increases by 1 for every 30 points of damage and a standard Equilibrium check is made. If the check fails, the shield will crumble and Antimagic Shield will go on cooldown.
		The damage the shield can absorb will increase with your Mindpower or Physical power (whichever is greater).]], [[給你增加一個護盾，每次被攻擊吸收最多 %d 點非物理、非精神元素傷害。 
		每吸收 30 點傷害都會增加 1 點失衡值，並進行一次失衡值鑑定，若鑑定失敗，則護盾會破碎且技能會進入冷卻狀態。 
		護盾的最大傷害吸收值受精神或物理強度較高者加成。]], "tformat")
t("Mana Clash", "奧術對撞", "talent name")
t("\
#GREEN#Antimagic Adept:  #LAST#4 magical sustains from the target will be removed.", "\
#GREEN#反魔專家： #LAST#你的奧術對撞技能還會從目標身上移除 4 個持續魔法技能。", "_t")
t([[Drain %d mana, %d vim, %d positive and negative energies from your target, triggering a chain reaction that explodes in a burst of arcane damage.
		The damage done is equal to 100%% of the mana drained, 200%% of the vim drained, or 400%% of the positive or negative energy drained, whichever is higher. This effect is called a manaburn.
		The effect will increase with your Mindpower or Physical power (whichever is greater).
		%s]], [[從目標身上吸收 %d 點法力， %d 點活力， %d 點正負能量，並觸發一次鏈式反應，引發一次奧術對撞。 
		奧術對撞造成相當於 100%% 吸收的法力值或 200%% 吸收的活力值或 400%% 吸收的正負能量的傷害，按最高值計算（稱爲法力燃燒）。 
		效果受精神或物理強度較高者加成。
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Antimagic Adept", "反魔專家", "talent name")
t("Your Mana Clash talent also removes 4 magical sustains from the target.", "你的奧術對撞技能還會從目標身上移除 4 個持續魔法技能。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/call.lua"

t("Meditation", "冥想", "talent name")
t("@Source@ #GREEN#meditates#LAST# on nature.", "@Source@進入了自然#GREEN#冥想#LAST#狀態。", "_t")
t("@Source@ interrupts @hisher@ #GREEN#meditation#LAST#.", "@Source@停止了@hisher@#GREEN#冥想#LAST#。", "_t")
t([[Meditate on your link with Nature.
		While meditating, your equilibrium decreases by %0.2f per turn, your Mental Save is increased by %d, and your healing factor increases by %d%%.
		Your deep meditation does not let you deal damage correctly, reducing the damage you and your summons deal by 50%%.
		Also, any time you are resting (even with Meditation not sustained) you enter a simple meditative state that decreases your equilibrium by %0.2f per turn.
		The activated effects increase with your Mindpower.]], [[你進入冥想，與大自然進行溝通。 
		冥想時每回合你能回覆 %0.2f 失衡值，你的精神豁免提高 %d ，你的治療效果提高 %d%% 。 
		冥想時你無法集中精力攻擊，你和你的召喚物造成的傷害減少 50 %%。 
		另外，你在休息時（即使未開啓冥想）會自動進入冥想狀態，使你每回合能回覆 %0.2f 點失衡值。 
		激活時效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Nature's Touch", "自然之觸", "talent name")
t([[Touch a target (or yourself) to infuse it with Nature, healing it for %d (this heal does not work on undead).
		The amount healed will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[對你自己或某個目標註入大自然的能量，治療 %d 點生命值（對不死族無效）。 
		治療量受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Earth's Eyes", "大地之眼", "talent name")
t([[Using your connection to Nature, you can see your surrounding area in a radius of %d.
		Also, while meditating, you are able to detect the presence of creatures around you in a radius of %d.]], [[利用你與大自然的聯繫，你可以查看自身周圍 %d 碼半徑範圍的區域。 
		同時，當你處於冥想狀態時，你還可以查看自身周圍 %d 碼半徑範圍中怪物的位置。]], "tformat")
t("Nature's Balance", "自然平衡", "talent name")
t("Your deep link with Nature allows you to reset the cooldown of %d of your wild gifts of tier %d or less.", "你與大自然間的深刻聯繫，使你能夠立刻冷卻 %d 個技能層次不超過 %d 的自然系技能。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/cold-drake.lua"

t("Ice Claw", "冰爪", "talent name")
t([[You call upon the mighty claw of a cold drake and rake a wave of freezing cold in front of you, doing %d%% weapon damage as Ice damage in a cone of radius %d. Ice damage gives a chance of freezing the target.
		Every level in Ice Claw additionally raises your Physical Save by 2.
		Each point in cold drake talents also increases your cold resistance by 1%%.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[你召喚強大的冰龍之爪，在半徑 %d 範圍內造成 %d%% 寒冰武器傷害，有一定機率凍結目標。
		同時，該技能每等級增加物理豁免 2 點。 
		每一點冰龍系技能同時也能增加你的寒冷抵抗 1%% 。
		如果你裝備了盾牌，這一技能也會用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat", {2,1})
t("Icy Skin", "冰膚術", "talent name")
t([[Your skin forms icy scales and your flesh toughens, increasing your Maximum Life by %d%% and your Armour by %d.
		You also deal %0.2f cold damage to any enemies that physically strike you.
		Each point in cold drake talents also increases your cold resistance by 1%%.
		The life increase will scale with your Talent Level, and your Armour and retaliation cold damage will scale with Mindpower.]], [[你的皮膚上覆蓋了寒冰，血肉更加堅硬。增加 %d%% 最大生命與 %d 護甲值。
		同時，你對近戰命中你的目標造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		每一點冰龍系技能同時也能增加你的寒冷抵抗 1%% 。
		生命加成受技能等級影響，護甲和傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Ice Wall", "冰牆術", "talent name")
t("ice wall", "冰牆", "_t")
t("a summoned, transparent wall of ice", "被召喚來的一堵透明冰牆。", "_t")
t([[Summons an icy wall of %d length for %d turns. Ice walls are transparent, but block projectiles and enemies.
		Ice walls also emit freezing cold, dealing %0.2f damage for each ice wall within radius %d of an enemy, and with each wall giving a 25%% chance to freeze an enemy. This cold cannot hurt the talent user or their allies.
		Each point in cold drake talents also increases your cold resistance by 1%%.]], [[召喚一條長度 %d 的冰牆，持續 %d 回合。冰牆是透明的，但能阻擋拋射物和敵人。
		冰牆會釋放極度寒氣，每格牆壁對半徑 %d 內的敵人造成 %0.2f 傷害，並有 25%% 機率凍結。寒氣不會傷害釋放者及其召喚物。
		每一點冰龍系技能同時也能增加你的寒冷抵抗 1%% 。]], "tformat", {1,2,4,3})
t("Ice Breath", "冰息術", "talent name")
t("@Source@ breathes ice!", "@Source@呼出寒冰!", "_t")
t("%s resists the freeze!", "%s抵抗了凍結！", "logSeen")
t([[You breathe ice in a frontal cone of radius %d. Any target caught in the area will take %0.2f cold damage and be frozen for 3 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Strength, the critical chance is based on your Mental crit rate, and the Freeze apply power is based on your Mindpower.
		Each point in cold drake talents also increases your cold resistance by 1%%.]], [[向前方 %d 碼範圍施放一個錐形冰凍吐息，範圍內所有目標受到 %0.2f 寒冷傷害，並被凍結3回合。
		傷害受力量值加成。技能暴擊率基於精神暴擊值計算，凍結機率受精神強度影響。 
		每一點冰龍系技能同時也能增加你的寒冷抵抗 1%% 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/corrosive-blades.lua"

t("Acidbeam", "酸性射線", "talent name")
t([[Channel acid through your psiblades, extending their reach to create a beam doing %0.1f Acid damage (which can disarm them).
		The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[ 在你的心靈利刃裏充填酸性能量，延展攻擊範圍, 形成一道射線，造成 %0.1f 點酸性繳械傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Corrosive Nature", "自然腐蝕", "talent name")
t([[You gain %d%% Acid resistance.
		When you deal Nature damage to a creature, you gain a %0.1f%% bonus to Acid damage for %d turns.
		This damage bonus will improve up to 4 times (no more than once each turn) with later Nature damage you do, up to a maximum of %0.1f%%.
		The resistance and damage increase improve with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你的酸性抗性增加 %d%% 。
		當你造成自然傷害時，你的酸性傷害增加 %0.1f%% ，持續 %d 回合。
		傷害加成能夠積累到最多4倍（1回合至多觸發1次），最大值 %0.1f%% 。
		抗性和傷害加成受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("trap", "陷阱", "_t")
t("Corrosive Seeds", "腐蝕之種", "talent name")
t("You somehow fail to set the corrosive seed.", "你沒能設置腐蝕之種。", "logPlayer")
t([[You focus on a target zone of radius 2 to make up to %d corrosive seeds appear.
		The first seed will appear at the center of the target zone, while others will appear at random spots.
		Each seed lasts %d turns and will explode when a hostile creature walks over it, knocking the creature back and dealing %0.1f Acid damage within radius 1.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你集中精神於某塊半徑 2 的區域，製造出 %d 個腐蝕之種。 
		第一個種子會產生於中心處，其他的會隨機出現。
     每個種子持續 %d 回合，
		當一個生物走過腐蝕之種時，會在半徑 1 的區域內引發一場爆炸，擊退對方並造成 %0.1f 點酸性傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Acidic Soil", "酸化大地", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with natural forces, ignoring %d%% acid resistance of your targets.
		In addition, the acid will nourish your bloated oozes, giving them an additional %0.1f life regeneration per turn.]], [[ 你的周圍充滿了自然力量，忽略目標 %d%% 的酸性傷害抵抗。
		同時酸性能量會治療你的浮腫軟泥怪，增加他們每回合 %0.1f 的生命回覆。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/dwarven-nature.lua"

t("Earthen Missiles", "岩石飛彈", "talent name")
t([[Conjures %d missile-shaped rocks that you target individually at any target or targets in range.  Each missile deals %0.2f physical damage, and an additional %0.2f bleeding damage every turn for 5 turns.
		At talent level 5, you can conjure one additional missile.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[釋放出 %d 個岩石飛彈射向任意射程內的目標。每個飛彈造成 %0.2f 物理傷害和每回合 %0.2f 流血傷害，持續 5 回合。 
		在等級 5 時，你可以額外釋放一個飛彈。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Elemental Split", "元素分裂", "talent name")
t("Crystaline Half (%s)", "水晶分身 (%s)", "tformat")
t("A crystaline structure that has taken the form of %s.", "有着%s的形象的水晶分身。", "tformat")
t("Crystaline Half", "水晶分身", "_t")
t("Stone Half (%s)", "岩石分身 (%s)", "tformat")
t("A stone structure that has taken the form of %s.", "有着%s的形象的岩石分身。", "tformat")
t("Stone Half", "岩石分身", "_t")
t([[Reach inside your dwarven core and summon your stone and crystaline halves to fight alongside you for %d turns.
		Your Crystaline Half will attack your foes with earthen missiles.
		Your Stone Half will taunt your foes to protect you.
		This power can not be called upon while under the effect of Deeprock Form.
		]], [[深入你的矮人血統，召喚岩石和水晶分身爲你作戰，持續 %d 回合。
		水晶分身會使用飛彈攻擊敵人。
		岩石分身會嘲諷敵人來保護你。
		處於深巖形態時，該技能不能使用。
		]], "tformat")
t("Power Core", "能量核心", "talent name")
t([[Your halves learn new talents.
		Crystaline Half: Rain of Spikes - A massive effect that makes all nearby foes bleed.
		Stone Half: Stone Link - A protective shield that will redirect all damage against nearby allies to your Stone Half.
		The level of those talents is %d.]], [[你的分身學會新的技能。
		水晶分身 ：尖刺之雨——被動技能，令周圍敵人流血。
		岩石分身 ：岩石鏈接——一層保護護盾，將周圍友方受到的所有傷害轉移至岩石分身。
		技能等級爲 %d 。]], "tformat")
t("Dwarven Unity", "矮人的團結", "talent name")
t([[You call upon the immediate help of your Halves.
		Your Stone Half will trade places (if in sight) with you and all creatures currently targetting you in a radius of %d will target it instead.
		Your Crystaline Half will instantly fire a volley of level %d earthen missiles at all foes near the stone half (or you if the stone half is dead) in radius %d.
		In addition, as passive effect, your halves now also learn your level of Combat Accuracy.]], [[你呼喚你的分身的幫助。
		岩石分身將和你交換位置，同時原位置半徑 %d 內的敵人將會轉爲以岩石分身爲目標。
		水晶分身將立即發射等級 %d 的岩石飛彈，目標是岩石分身（如死亡，則改爲你自己）半徑 %d 周圍的敵人。]], "tformat")
t("Mergeback", "重吸收", "talent name")
t([[Merges your halves back into you, cleansing your body of %d detrimental magical, mental or physical effects.
		Each half also heals you for %d and releases a shockwave dealing %0.2f Nature damage in a radius 3.]], [[重吸收你的分身，清除合計至多 %d 個負面狀態。
		每個分身將治療你 %d 生命值，並在半徑 3 的範圍內造成 %0.2f 點自然傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Link", "岩石鏈接", "talent name")
t("Creates a shield of radius %d that redirects all damage done to friends inside it to you for 5 turns.", "製造一層半徑 %d 的護盾，將友方受到的傷害轉移過來，持續 5 回合。", "tformat")
t("Rain of Spikes", "巖刺之雨", "talent name")
t([[Fires spikes all around you, making your foes within radius %d bleed for %0.2f damage over 6 turns.
		Damage and chance to apply the effect increase with Willpower.]], [[ 在身邊發射尖刺，半徑 %d 內的敵人在 6 回合內流血 %0.2f 點。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/earthen-power.lua"

t("Stoneshield", "岩石堅盾", "talent name")
t([[The first time you take damage each turn, you regenerate %d%% of the damage dealt as mana (up to a maximum of %0.2f) and %d%% as equilibrium (up to %0.2f).
		Increases Physical Power by %d, increases damage done with shields by %d%%, and allows you to dual-wield shields.
		Also, all of your melee attacks will perform a shield bash in addition to their normal effects.]], [[每回合第一次承受傷害時，你將 %d%% 的傷害轉化爲法力 ( 至多 %0.2f 點 ) ， %d%% 的傷害轉化爲失衡值 ( 至多回復 %0.2f )。
		增加物理強度 %d , 增加盾牌傷害 %d%% , 並讓你能夠雙持盾牌。
		同時，你的近戰攻擊附帶一次盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Fortress", "岩石壁壘", "talent name")
t([[When you use your Resilience of the Dwarves racial power your skin becomes so tough that it even absorbs damage from non-physical attacks.
		Non-physical damage is reduced by %d%% of your total armour value (ignoring hardiness).
		While this effect is not active, half of it is still applied against foes entangled by your stone vines.]], [[當你使用鋼筋鐵骨時，你的皮膚會變得非常堅硬，甚至能吸收非物理攻擊。
		所有非物理傷害減免 %d%% 護甲值（無視護甲強度）。
		鋼筋鐵骨沒有啓用的時候，被你岩石藤蔓纏繞的敵人對你的攻擊也會獲得一半的傷害減免效果。]], "tformat")
t("Shards", "岩石碎片", "talent name")
t([[Sharp shards of stone grow from your shields.
		When you are hit in melee, you will get a free attack against the attacker with the shards doing %d%% shield damage (as Nature).
		This effect can only happen once per turn and is not affected by counterstrike.]], [[尖銳的岩石碎片從盾牌生長出來。
		每次你承受近戰攻擊時，你能利用這些碎片反擊攻擊者，造成 %d%% 自然盾牌傷害。
		每回合只能反擊一次，且無法觸發格擋反擊。]], "tformat")
t("Eldritch Stone", "岩石護盾", "talent name")
t([[Creates a shield of impenetrable stone around you for %d turns, absorbing up to %d damage.
		Your equilibrium will increase by twice the damage absorbed.
		When the effect ends, all equilibrium above minimum will be converted to mana in a storm of arcane energy and the cooldown of your Block is reset.
		The storm inflicts Arcane damage equal to the converted equilibrium (maximum %d) against everyone around you in a radius %d.
		Also while resting you will passively regenerate %0.2f mana each turn.
		The shield strength will increase with Willpower]], [[製造一層持續 %d 回合的岩石護盾，吸收至多 %d 點傷害。
		你的失衡值將會上升兩倍傷害吸收量。 
		護盾破碎時，所有超過最小值的失衡值將被轉化爲法力值，同時釋放奧術能量風暴 , 造成等同於轉化失衡值的奧術傷害（至多 %d 點），傷害半徑 %d 。
		你的格擋技能的冷卻時間也會被重置。
		同時，你休息時獲得每回合 %0.2f 回魔速度。
		護盾值受意志度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/earthen-vines.lua"

t("Stone Vines", "岩石藤蔓", "talent name")
t(" and %0.1f Arcane", " 和 %0.1f 奧術傷害", "tformat")
t([[From the ground around you, you form living stone vines extending from your feet.
		Each turn, the vines will attempt to seize a random target within radius %d.
		Affected creatures are pinned to the ground and take %0.1f nature%s damage each turn for %d turns.
		A creature entangled by the vines will have a chance to break free each turn, and will automatically succeed if it is more than %d grids away from you.
		The chance to affect targets and damage increase with talent level and Willpower.]], [[你周圍的地面開始生成岩石藤蔓。
		每回合藤蔓將試圖抓住半徑 %d 內的一個隨機目標。
		受影響的目標將被定身，同時每回合受到 %0.1f 自然傷害 %s, 持續 %d 回合。
		被岩石藤蔓抓住的生物每回合有一定機率逃脫，如果距離你超過 %d 碼則自動逃脫。 
		定身機率和傷害受法術強度與技能等級加成。]], "tformat")
t("Eldritch Vines", "奧術藤蔓", "talent name")
t([[Each time one of your stone vines deals damage to a creature it will restore %0.1f equilibrium and %0.1f mana.
		Your vines also become infused with eldritch energies, dealing an additional %0.1f arcane damage.]], [[每次藤蔓造成傷害時，你回覆 %0.1f 點失衡值與 %0.1f 點法力值。
		同時藤蔓會附加 %0.1f 奧術傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Rockwalk", "岩石漫步", "talent name")
t([[Merge with one of your stone vines, traversing it to emerge near an entangled creature (maximum range %d).
		Merging with the stone is beneficial for you, healing %0.2f life (increases with Willpower).
		This will not break Body of Stone.]], [[吸收一條岩石藤蔓，並將自己拉到被困住的怪物附近（最大半徑 %d ）。
		吸收岩石藤蔓會治療你 %0.2f 點生命值。
		使用這個技能不會打破岩石身軀。]], "tformat")
t("Rockswallow", "岩石吞噬", "talent name")
t([[Merge your target (within range %d) with one of your stone vines that has seized it, forcing it to traverse the vine and reappear near you.
		Merging with the stone is detrimental for the target, dealing %0.1f nature damage.
		The damage will increases with your Willpower.]], [[將半徑 %d 內的目標連同岩石藤蔓一起拉過來，造成 %0.1f 自然傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/eyals-fury.lua"

t("Reclaim", "沙化", "talent name")
t([[You focus the inexorable pull of nature against a single creature, eroding it and allowing it to be reclaimed by the cycle of life.
		This deals %0.1f Nature and %0.1f Acid damage to the target, and is particularly devastating against undead and constructs, dealing %d%% more damage to them.
		The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你將自然無情的力量集中於某個目標上，腐蝕他並讓他重歸生命輪迴。
		造成 %0.1f 點自然傷害， %0.1f 點酸性傷害，對不死族和構裝生物有 %d%% 傷害加成。
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Nature's Defiance", "自然的反抗", "talent name")
t([[Your devotion to nature has made your body more attuned to the natural world and resistant to unnatural energies.
		You gain %d Spell save, %0.1f%% Arcane resistance, and %0.1f%% Nature damage affinity.
		You defy arcane forces, so that any time you take damage from a spell, you restore %0.1f Equilibrium each turn for %d turns.
		The effects increase with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你對自然的貢獻讓你的身體更親近自然世界，對非自然力量也更具抵抗力。
		你獲得 %d 點法術豁免， %0.1f%% 奧術抗性，同時將受到的 %0.1f%% 的自然傷害轉化爲治療。
		由於你和奧術力量對抗，每次你受到法術傷害時，你回覆 %0.1f 點失衡值，持續 %d 回合。
		效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Acidfire", "酸火", "talent name")
t("Acidfire cloud", "酸火毒雲", "_t")
t([[You call upon the earth to create a blinding, corrosive cloud in an area of radius %d for %d turns.
		Each turn, this cloud deals %0.1f acid damage to each foe with a 25%% chance to blind and a %d%% chance of burning away one magical sustain or beneficial magical effect.
		The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你召喚酸雲覆蓋半徑 %d 的地面，持續 %d 回合。酸雲具有腐蝕性，能致盲敵人。
		每回合，酸雲對每個敵人造成 %0.1f 點酸性傷害，25%% 機率致盲，同時有 %d%% 機率除去一個有益的魔法效果或魔法持續技能。
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("#CRIMSON#%s drains magical energy!", "#CRIMSON#%s 吸收了魔法能量！", "tformat")
t("Eyal's Wrath", "埃亞爾之怒", "_t")
t([[You draw deeply from your connection with nature to create a radius %d storm of natural forces around you for %d turns.
		This storm moves with you and deals %0.1f Nature damage each turn to all foes it hits.
		In addtion, it will drain up to %d Mana, %d Vim, %d Positive, and %d Negative energy from each enemy within it's area every turn, while you restore Equilibrium equal to 10%% of the amount drained.
		The damage and drain increase with your Mindpower.]], [[ 你在自己周圍半徑 %d 的範圍內製造自然力量風暴，持續 %d 回合。
		風暴會跟隨你移動，每回合對每個敵人造成 %0.1f 點自然傷害。
		此外，它並抽取 %d 點法力， %d 點活力， %d 點正能量和 %d 點負能量，同時你的失衡值會回覆你抽取能量的 10%% 。
		傷害和吸取量受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/fire-drake.lua"

t("Wing Buffet", "龍翼颶風", "talent name")
t([[You summon a powerful gust of wind, knocking back your foes within a radius of %d up to 3 tiles away and hitting them for %d%% weapon damage.
		Every level in Wing Buffet additionally raises your Physical Power and Accuracy by 2, passively.
		Each point in fire drake talents also increases your fire resistance by 1%%.

		This talent will also attack with your shield, if you have one equipped.]], [[你召喚一陣強風，擊退半徑 %d 碼內的敵人至多 3 格，並造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		同時，每個技能等級增加你的物理強度和命中 2 點。
		每點火龍系的技能可以使你增加火焰抵抗 1%% 。
		如果你裝備了盾牌，這一技能也會用你的盾牌攻擊。]], "tformat")
t("Bellowing Roar", "怒意咆哮", "talent name")
t("@Source@ roars!", "@Source@發出咆哮!", "_t")
t([[You let out a powerful roar that sends your foes in radius %d into utter confusion (power: %d%%) for 3 turns.
		The sound wave is so strong, your foes also take %0.2f physical damage.
		The damage improves with your Strength.
		Each point in fire drake talents also increases your fire resistance by 1%%.]], [[你發出一聲咆哮使 %d 碼半徑範圍內的敵人陷入徹底的混亂（強度 %d%% ），持續 3 回合。 
		如此強烈的咆哮使你的敵人受到 %0.2f 物理傷害。 
		傷害受力量值加成。 
		每點火龍系的技能可以使你增加火焰抵抗 1%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Devouring Flame", "火焰吞噬", "talent name")
t([[Spit a cloud of flames, doing %0.2f fire damage in a radius of %d each turn for %d turns.
		The flames will ignore the caster, and will drain 10%% of the damage dealt as the flames consume enemies life force and transfer it to the user.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower, and can critical.
		Each point in fire drake talents also increases your fire resistance by 1%%.]], [[你噴出一片火焰，範圍內的目標每回合會受到 %0.2f 火焰傷害（影響半徑 %d ），持續 %d 回合。 
		火焰會無視使用者，並吸收 10%% 傷害治療自身。
		傷害受精神強度加成。技能可暴擊。 
		每點火龍系的技能可以使你增加火焰抵抗 1%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Fire Breath", "火焰吐息", "talent name")
t("@Source@ breathes fire!", "@Source@噴出火焰!", "_t")
t([[You breathe fire in a frontal cone of radius %d. Any target caught in the area will take %0.2f fire damage over 3 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Strength and the critical chance is based on your Mental crit rate.
		Each point in fire drake talents also increases your fire resistance by 1%%.]], [[你在前方 %d 碼錐形範圍內噴出火焰。此範圍內的目標會在 3 回合內受到 %0.2f 火焰傷害。
		傷害受力量值加成，暴擊機率基於你的精神暴擊率。 
		每點火龍系的技能可以使你增加火焰抵抗 1%% 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/fungus.lua"

t("Wild Growth", "野性生長", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with a myriad of tiny, nearly invisible, reinforcing fungi.
		You gain %d maximum life and %d life regeneration.
		The effects will increase with your Willpower.]], [[使你自身周圍環繞無數微不可見、有治療作用的孢子。
		你獲得 %d 最大生命值， %d 生命回覆。
		效果受意志值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fungal Growth", "真菌生長", "talent name")
t([[The fungus on your body allows regeneration effects to last longer.
		Each time you gain a beneficial effect with the regeneration subtype you increase its duration by %d%% + 1 rounded up.
		The effect will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[你身上的孢子讓回覆效果更加持久。
		每當你獲得一個回覆類的增益效果，你會讓它的持續時間增加 %d%% +1，向上取整。
		技能效果受意志值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Ancestral Life", "原始生命", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_GREEN##Source# gains %d%%%% of a turn from Ancestral Life.#LAST#", "#LIGHT_GREEN##Source#從原始生命處獲得%d%%%%回合。#LAST#", "logCombat")
t([[Your fungus reaches into the primordial ages of the world, granting you ancient instincts.
		Each time you receive non-regeneration healing you gain %0.1f%% of a turn per 100 life healed.  This effect can't add energy past 2 stored turns and overhealing is not counted.
		Also, regeneration effects on you will decrease your equilibrium by %0.1f each turn.
		The turn gain increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你的孢子可以追溯到創世紀元，你可以傳承來自遠古的天賦。 
		每當你獲得一個非回覆的治療效果，每治療 100 點生命值，你獲得 %0.1f%% 個回合。
		這一效果最多獲得 2 個回合。
		同時，每當你受到回覆作用時，每回合你的失衡值將會減少 %0.1f 。 
		增益回合受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sudden Growth", "瘋狂成長", "talent name")
t("A wave of energy passes through your fungus, making it release immediate healing energies on you, healing you for %d%% of your current life regeneration rate (#GREEN#%d#LAST#).", "一股強大的能量穿過你的孢子，使其立刻對你釋放治癒性能量，治療你 %d%% 當前生命回覆值（#GREEN# %d #LAST#）。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/gifts.lua"

t("Be at one with nature.", " 與大自然的融爲一體。", "_t")
t("call of the wild", "自然召喚", "_t")
t("Nature heals and cleans you.", " 利用大自然的力量治療你受到的創傷、清潔你的身體。", "_t")
t("harmony", "自然協調", "_t")
t("The way to combat magic, or even nullify it.", " 你選擇終生與魔法對抗並試圖永遠終結它。", "_t")
t("antimagic", "反魔法", "_t")
t("The art of calling creatures adept in melee combat to your aid.", " 召喚近戰生物來協助你戰鬥的藝術。", "_t")
t("summoning (melee)", "召喚(近戰)", "_t")
t("The art of calling creatures adept in elemental destruction to your aid.", " 召喚遠程元素攻擊類生物來協助你戰鬥的藝術。", "_t")
t("summoning (distance)", "召喚(遠程)", "_t")
t("The art of calling versatile creatures to your aid.", " 召喚輔助類生物來協助你戰鬥的藝術。", "_t")
t("summoning (utility)", "召喚(通用)", "_t")
t("The art of manipulating the lifespan and location of your summons.", " 操縱召喚物壽命和位置的戰鬥藝術。", "_t")
t("summoning (augmentation)", "召喚(增益)", "_t")
t("The art of improving the quality of your summons.", " 增強召喚物的戰鬥藝術。", "_t")
t("summoning (advanced)", "高級召喚", "_t")
t("Through dedicated consumption of slime mold juice, you have gained an affinity with slime molds.", " 通過對史萊姆的研究使你學會了一些史萊姆技能。", "_t")
t("slime", "史萊姆", "_t")
t("By covering yourself in fungus, you better your healing.", " 利用真菌環繞周身，增強你的治療能力。", "_t")
t("fungus", "真菌", "_t")
t("Take on the defining aspects of a Sand Drake.", " 化身成爲土龍形態使你能使用土龍技能。", "_t")
t("sand drake aspect", "土龍形態", "_t")
t("Take on the defining aspects of a Fire Drake.", " 化身成爲火龍形態使你能使用火龍技能。", "_t")
t("fire drake aspect", "火龍形態", "_t")
t("Take on the defining aspects of a Cold Drake.", " 化身成爲冰龍形態使你能使用冰龍技能。", "_t")
t("cold drake aspect", "冰龍形態", "_t")
t("Take on the defining aspects of a Storm Drake.", " 化身成爲雷龍形態使你能使用雷龍技能。", "_t")
t("storm drake aspect", "雷龍形態", "_t")
t("Take on the defining aspects of a Venom Drake.", " 化身成爲毒龍形態使你能使用毒龍技能。", "_t")
t("venom drake aspect", "毒龍形態", "_t")
t("Take on the aspects of aged and powerful dragons.", " 繼承遠古真龍的力量使你能使用強大的龍族技能。", "_t")
t("higher draconic abilities", "高等龍族", "_t")
t("Learn to channel your mental power through mindstars, forming powerful psionic blades.", " 學會將你的精神能量灌注於靈晶中，產生心靈利刃。", "_t")
t("mindstar mastery", "靈晶掌握", "_t")
t("Cover the floor with natural mucus.", " 用粘液覆蓋地面。", "_t")
t("mucus", "粘液", "_t")
