t("You learn to control moss, making it grow at will to help you on the battlefield.", " 你學會控制苔蘚生長，幫助戰鬥。", "_t")
t("moss", "苔蘚", "_t")
t("Your body's anatomy is starting to blur.", "你身體的解剖結構開始模糊。", "_t")
t("malleable body", "可塑形體", "_t")
t("You channel ooze through your psiblades.", " 你向心靈利刃裏灌注軟泥能量。", "_t")
t("oozing blades", "軟泥利刃", "_t")
t("You channel acid through your psiblades.", " 你向心靈利刃裏灌注酸性能量。", "_t")
