t("#PINK#You can manage a maximum of %d summons at any time. You need %d Cunning to increase your limit.", "#PINK#你能同時擁有最多 %d 名召喚物。你需要 %d 靈巧來提升上限。", "logPlayer")
t("Summon", "召喚", "_t")


