section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/slime.lua"

t("Slime Spit", "史萊姆噴吐", "talent name")
t([[Spit slime at your target doing %0.1f nature damage and slowing it down by 30%% for 3 turns.
		The slime can bounce from foe to foe, hitting up to a total of %d target(s).
		Additional targets must be within 6 tiles of each other and the slime loses %0.1f%% damage per bounce.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower]], [[向你的目標噴吐酸液造成 %0.1f 自然傷害並減速目標 30%% 3 回合。 
		酸液球可彈射到附近的某個敵方單位 %d 次。 
		彈射距離最多爲 6 碼，同時每彈一次會減少 %0.1f%% 傷害。
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Poisonous Spores", "毒性孢子", "talent name")
t("@Source@ releases poisonous spores at @target@.", "@Source@朝@target@釋放毒素孢子。", "_t")
t([[Releases poisonous spores at an area of radius %d, infecting the foes inside with a random poison doing %0.1f Nature damage over 10 turns.
		This attack can crit and deals %d%% additional critical damage.
		The damage and critical bonus increase with your Mindpower.]], [[向 %d 碼半徑範圍釋放毒性孢子，使範圍內的敵方單位感染隨機類型的毒素，造成 %0.1f 自然傷害，持續 10 回合。
		這個攻擊能夠暴擊，造成額外 %d%% 暴擊傷害。
		傷害和暴擊加成受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Acidic Skin", "酸性皮膚", "talent name")
t("The skin of @Source@ starts dripping acid.", "@Source@的皮膚開始滴落酸液。", "_t")
t([[Your skin drips with acid, damaging all that hit you for %0.1f disarming acid damage.
		The damage increases with your Mindpower.]], [[你的皮膚浸泡着酸液，對所有攻擊你的目標造成 %0.1f 酸性繳械傷害。
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Slime Roots", "史萊姆觸手", "talent name")
t([[You extend slimy roots into the ground, follow them, and re-appear somewhere else in a range of %d with error margin of %d.
		Doing so changes your internal structure slightly, taking %d random talent(s) off cooldown.]], [[你延伸史萊姆觸手進入地下，然後在 %d 碼範圍內的指定位置出現（ %d 碼誤差）。
		釋放此技能會導致你的身體結構發生輕微的改變，使 %d 個技能冷卻完畢。]], "tformat")


