section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/summon-melee.lua"

t("Jelly Spread", "果凍散佈", "talent name")
t("@source@ oozes over the ground!!", "@source@在地上散佈!!", "_t")
t("Ooze over the floor, spreading caustic jelly in a radius of 1 lasting %d turns and dealing %d nature damage per turn to hostile creatures caught within.", "在 1 碼範圍內的地板上散佈腐蝕性的粘液，持續 %d 回合，對上面所有的敵對生物造成 %d 自然傷害。", "tformat")
t("Mitotic Split", "有絲分裂", "talent name")
t("%d%% chance to split upon taking a single hit dealing at least %d%% of your maximum life.", "當受到最大生命值 %d%% 的攻擊的時候，有 %d%% 的機率分裂。", "tformat")
t("War Hound", "契約：戰爭獵犬", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a War Hound!", "@Source@召喚了一隻戰爭獵犬!", "_t")
t([[Summon a War Hound for %d turns to attack your foes. War hounds are good basic melee attackers.
		It will get %d Strength, %d Dexterity and %d Constitution.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		The hound's Strength and Dexterity will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻戰爭獵犬來攻擊敵人，持續 %d 回合。 
		戰爭獵犬是非常好的基礎近戰單位。 
		它擁有 %d 點力量， %d 點敏捷和 %d 點體質。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		獵犬的力量和敏捷受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Jelly", "契約：果凍怪", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a Jelly!", "@Source@召喚了一隻果凍怪!", "_t")
t("A strange blob on the dungeon floor.", "地板上的一團奇怪膠狀物體。", "_t")
t("#GREEN##Target# absorbs some damage. #Source# is closer to nature.", "#GREEN##Target#吸收了傷害， #Source#更貼近自然了。", "delayedLogMessage")
t([[Summon a Jelly for %d turns to attack your foes. Jellies do not move, but your equilibrium will be reduced by 10%% of all damage received by the jelly.
		It will get %d Constitution and %d Strength.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		The jelly's Constitution will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻果凍怪來攻擊敵人，持續 %d 回合。 
		果凍怪不會移動。 
		它擁有 %d 點體質和 %d 點力量。 
		每當果凍怪受到傷害時，你降低等同於它受到傷害值的 10 %%失衡值。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		果凍怪的體質受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Minotaur", "契約：米諾陶", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a Minotaur!", "@Source@召喚了一隻米諾陶!", "_t")
t("It is a cross between a human and a bull.", "它擁有人類和牛的特徵。", "_t")
t([[Summon a Minotaur for %d turns to attack your foes. Minotaurs cannot stay summoned for long, but they deal high damage.
		It will get %d Strength, %d Constitution and %d Dexterity.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		The minotaur's Strength and Dexterity will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻米諾陶來攻擊敵人，持續 %d 回合。米諾陶不會呆很長時間，但是它們會造成極大傷害。 
		它擁有 %d 點力量， %d 點體質和 %d 點敏捷。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		米諾陶的力量和敏捷受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Golem", "契約：岩石傀儡", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a Stone Golem!", "@Source@召喚了一隻岩石傀儡!", "_t")
t("You cannot summon; you are suppressed!", "你不能召喚，你被壓制了！", "logPlayer")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("It is a massive animated statue.", "一座巨型活化傀儡。", "_t")
t("%s (wild summon)", "%s (野性召喚)", "tformat")
t([[Summon a Stone Golem for %d turns to attack your foes. Stone golems are formidable foes that can become unstoppable.
		It will get %d Strength, %d Constitution and %d Dexterity.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		The golem's Strength and Dexterity will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻岩石傀儡來攻擊敵人，持續 %d 回合。岩石傀儡是可怕的敵人並且不可阻擋。 
		它有 %d 點力量， %d 點體質和 %d 點敏捷。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		傀儡的力量和敏捷受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


