section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/gifts/summon-utility.lua"

t("Taunt", "嘲諷", "talent name")
t("Forces all hostile foes in radius %d to attack you.", "強制 %d 碼範圍內的所有敵對目標攻擊你。", "tformat")
t("Shell Shield", "甲殼護盾", "talent name")
t("Under the cover of your shell, gain %d%% all resistance for %d turns", "隱藏在你的甲殼下，增加 %d%% 全體傷害抗性，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Web", "蜘蛛之網", "talent name")
t("Spread a web and throw it toward your target. If caught, it won't be able to move for %d turns.", "朝你的目標投擲一個網，若目標被擊中則被困在原地 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Turtle", "契約：烏龜", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a Turtle!", "@Source@召喚了一隻烏龜!", "_t")
t([[Summon a Turtle for %d turns to distract your foes. Turtles are resilient, but not very powerful. However, they will periodically force any foes to attack them, and can protect themselves with their shell.
		It will get %d Constitution, %d Dexterity and 18 willpower.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		Their Constitution will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻烏龜來吸引敵人攻擊，持續 %d 回合。 
		烏龜具有很強的生命力，並不能造成很多傷害。 
		然而，它們會週期性的嘲諷敵人並用龜殼保護自己。
		它擁有 %d 點體質， %d 點敏捷和 18 點意志。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		烏龜的體質受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Spider", "契約：蜘蛛", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons a Spider!", "@Source@召喚了一隻蜘蛛!", "_t")
t("You cannot summon; you are suppressed!", "你不能召喚，你被壓制了！", "logPlayer")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("%s (wild summon)", "%s (野性召喚)", "tformat")
t([[Summon a Spider for %d turns to harass your foes. Spiders can poison your foes and throw webs to pin them to the ground.
		It will get %d Dexterity, %d Strength, 18 Willpower and %d Constitution.
		Your summons inherit some of your stats: increased damage%%, resistance penetration %%, stun/pin/confusion/blindness resistance, armour penetration.
		Their Dexterity will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[召喚一隻蜘蛛來擾亂敵人，持續 %d 回合。 
		蜘蛛可以使敵人中毒並向目標撒網，將目標固定在地上。 
		它擁有 %d 點敏捷， %d 點力量， 18 點意志和 %d 點體質。 
		你的召喚物繼承你部分屬性：增加百分比傷害、抗性穿透、震懾/定身/混亂/致盲抵抗和護甲穿透。
		蜘蛛的敏捷受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Frantic Summoning", "瘋狂召喚", "talent name")
t([[You focus yourself on nature, allowing you to summon natural creatures much faster (%d%% of a normal summon time) and with no chance to fail from high equilibrium for %d turns.
		When activating this power, a random summoning talent will come off cooldown.
		Each time you summon, the duration of the frantic summoning effect will reduce by 1.]], [[你專注於自然，使你的自然召喚速度提升（ %d%% 的正常召喚時間），並且即使在高自然失衡值下也不會失敗，持續 %d 回合。 
		當此技能激活時，某個隨機的召喚天賦會冷卻。 
		每次你進行召喚，瘋狂召喚的效果會減少 1 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Pheromones", "信息素", "talent name")
t([[Mark a creature with pheromones, signalling to all of your summons within %d tiles to shift aggression towards the marked creature for %d turns. Marked targets will receive %d%% increased damage from your summons and your summons will change target to it.
		The increased damage from your summons will increase with your Mindpower]], [[用信息素標記一個生物，向它周圍 %d 碼範圍內的所有召喚獸發出信號，將攻擊目標轉移到被標記的生物身上，持續 %d 回合。被標記的目標從你的召喚物那裏受到的傷害增加 %d%% ，你的召喚物也會集火它。
		你召喚物的傷害增加效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


