t([[A nasty bite that hits for %d%% weapon damage, reduces the targets healing by %d%%, and causes the target to bleed for %d%% weapon damage over 5 turns.
		Only usable while frenzied.]], [[撕咬目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。減少目標治療效果 %d%% 並造成 %d%% 武器傷害的流血傷害持續 5 回合。 
		只有在狂亂狀態下可以使用。]], "tformat")
t("Frenzied Leap", "狂亂跳躍", "talent name")
t("@Source@ leaps forward in a frenzy!", "@Source@在狂熱中向前跳躍！", "_t")
t([[Leaps toward a target within range.
		Only usable while frenzied.]], [[跳向範圍內目標。
		只有在狂亂狀態下可以使用。]], "tformat")
t("Gnashing Teeth", "咬牙切齒", "talent name")
t("@Source@ tries to bite @Target@ with razor sharp teeth!", "@Source@嘗試用尖銳的牙齒咬 @Target@ ！", "_t")
t("The scent of blood sends the %ss into a frenzy!", "鮮血的氣味使得%s們變得狂熱！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the cut!", "%s抵抗了流血！", "logSeen")
t([[Bites the target for %d%% weapon damage, potentially causing it to bleed for %d%% weapon damage over five turns.
		If the target is affected by the bleed it will send the devourer into a frenzy for %d turns (which in turn will frenzy other nearby devourers).
		The frenzy will increase global speed by %d%%, physical crit chance by %d%%, and prevent death until -%d%% life.]], [[ 咬傷目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害，可能讓目標進入流血狀態，在五回合內造成 %d%% 武器傷害。 
		如果目標進入流血狀態，吞噬者會進入狂熱狀態 %d 回合（也會讓周圍的其他吞噬者進入狂熱狀態）。
		狂熱狀態會增加整體速度 %d%% , 物理暴擊率 %d%% , 同時降至 -%d%% 生命時纔會死去。]], "tformat")
t("Abyssal Shroud", "墮入深淵", "talent name")
t("Creates a shroud of darkness over a radius 3 area that lasts %d turns.  The shroud causes %0.2f darkness damage each turn, reduces light radius by %d, and darkness resistance by %d%% of those within.", "製造一個 3 碼範圍的黑暗深淵持續 %d 回合。深淵會造成每回合 %0.2f 黑暗傷害並降低 %d 光照範圍，同時使其中生物的暗影抵抗減少 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Echoes From The Void", "虛空迴響", "talent name")
t("@Source@ shows @Target@ the madness of the void.", "@Source@向 @Target@ 展示了虛空的瘋狂。", "_t")
t("Shows the target the madness of the void.  Each turn for 6 turns the target must make a mental save or suffer %0.2f mind damage as well as resource damage (based off the mind damage and nature of the resource).", " 釋放虛空的混亂，使目標每回合強制進行精神豁免鑑定，持續 6 回合，未通過豁免則在原傷害基礎上造成 %0.2f 精神傷害（由精神和自然傷害基礎傷害決定）。", "tformat")
t("Void Shards", "虛空碎片", "talent name")
t("@Source@ summons void shards.", "@Source@召喚出虛空碎片。", "_t")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("void shard", "虛空碎片", "_t")
t("It looks like a small hole in the fabric of spacetime.", "看起來像空間中的一小塊破洞。", "_t")
t("Summons %d void shards.  The void shards come into being destabilized and will suffer %0.2f temporal damage each turn for five turns.  If they die while destabilized they'll explode for %0.2f temporal and %0.2f physical damage in a radius of 4.", "召喚 %d 個虛空碎片。碎片會進入不穩定狀態，造成每回合 %0.2f 時空傷害持續 5 回合。它們在不穩定狀態下死亡會發生爆炸造成 4 碼範圍 %0.2f 時空和 %0.2f 物理傷害。", "tformat")
t("Knife Storm", "刀刃風暴", "talent name")
t([[Summon a storm of swirling blades to slice your foes, inflicting %d physical damage and bleeding to anyone who approaches for %d turns.
		The damage and duration will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[ 召喚旋轉劍刃風暴將敵人切成碎片，對進入風暴的敵人造成 %d 點物理傷害並令其流血 %d 回合。 
		傷害和流血持續時間受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Psionic Pull", "念力牽引", "talent name")
t("%s is pulled in!", "%s 被拉了進去！", "logSeen")
t([[Pull all foes toward you in radius 5 while dealing %d physical damage.
The damage will increase with your mindpower.]], [[將 5 碼範圍內的目標拉向你並造成 %d 物理傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Razor Knife", "刀鋒之刃", "talent name")
t([[Launches a knife with intense power doing %0.2f physical damage to all targets in line.
		The damage will increase with Mindpower]], [[對一條直線目標發射一把鋒利的刀刃造成 %0.2f 物理傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Slime Wave", "史萊姆衝擊波", "talent name")
t([[A wall of slime oozes out from the caster with radius 1, increasing once every two turns to a maximum eventual radius of %d, doing %0.2f slime damage for %d turns.
		The damage and duration will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[在 1 碼範圍內形成一個史萊姆牆，每隔 2 回合範圍會擴大，直至 %d 碼，造成 %0.2f 史萊姆傷害持續 %d 回合。 
		傷害及持續時間受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Tentacle Grab", "觸鬚之握", "talent name")
t("%s resists the grab!", "%s抵抗了抓取！", "logSeen")
t([[Grab a target and drag it to your side, holding it in place and silencing non-undead and creatures that need to breathe for %d turns.
		The grab will also deal %0.2f slime damage per turn.
		The damage will increase with your Mindpower.]], [[抓住一個目標並將其拉至身邊，並抓取 %d 回合。需要呼吸的非亡靈類生物還會被窒息。
		同時每回合造成 %0.2f 史萊姆傷害。 
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Ooze Spit", "凝膠噴射", "talent name")
t([[Spit slime at your target doing %0.2f nature damage and slowing it down by 30%% for 3 turns.
		The damage will increase with the Dexterity stat]], [[向目標噴射毒液造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並降低其 30%% 移動速度持續 3 回合。 
		傷害受敏捷值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Slime Roots", "史萊姆觸手", "talent name")
t("You extend slimy roots into the ground, follow them, and re-appear somewhere else in a range of %d with error margin of %d.", "變成史萊姆遁入地下，並在 %d 至 %d 範圍內重新出現。", "tformat")
t("Animate Blade", "虛空利刃", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to invoke!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚！", "logPlayer")
t("Open a hole in space, summoning an animated blade for 10 turns.", "在空間中打開一個孔洞，召喚一個次元之刃10回合。", "tformat")
t("Drench", "浸溼", "talent name")
t([[Blast a wave of water all around you with a radius of %d, making all creatures Wet for 10 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在你身邊 %d 範圍內製造水流，令所有生物溼潤。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Suckers", "吸血者", "talent name")
t("@Source@ tries to latch on and suck blood!", "@Source@嘗試抓住目標吸血！", "_t")
t([[Latch on to the target and suck their blood, doing %0.2f physical and %0.2f acid damage per turn.
		After 5 turns of drinking, drop off and gain the ability to Multiply.
		Damage scales with your level.
		]], [[抓住目標，吸取他們的血液，每回合造成 %0.2f 物理和 %0.2f 酸性傷害。
		5 回合後脫落並繁殖。
		傷害隨等級上升。
		]], "tformat")


