		寒冰同時會解除你受到的一個負面精神狀態。]], "tformat")
t("%d cold damage", "%d 寒冰傷害", "tformat")
t("Rune: Heat Beam", "符文：熱能射線", "talent name")
t([[Activate the rune to fire a beam of heat, doing %0.2f fire damage over 5 turns
		The intensity of the heat will also remove one random detrimental physical effect from you.]], [[激活這個符文發射一束射線，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害持續 5 回合。 
		高溫同時會解除你受到的一個負面物理狀態。]], "tformat")
t("%d fire damage", "%d 火焰傷害", "tformat")
t("Rune: Speed", "符文：加速", "talent name")
t("Activate the rune to increase your global speed by %d%% for %d turns.", "激活這個符文提高整體速度 %d%% 持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("speed %d%% for %d turns", "提速 %d%% 持續 %d 回合", "tformat")
t("Rune: Vision", "符文：視野", "talent name")
t([[Activate the rune to get a vision of the area surrounding you (%d radius) and to allow you to see invisible and stealthed creatures (power %d) for %d turns.
		Your mind will become more receptive for %d turns, allowing you to sense any %s around.]], [[激活這個符文可以使你查看周圍環境（ %d 有效範圍）使你你查看隱形生物（ %d 偵測隱形等級）持續 %d 回合。 
		你的精神更加敏銳，能感知到周圍的 %s ，持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat", {1,2,3,5,4})
t("radius %d; dur %d; see %s", "範圍 %d; 持續 %d; 感知 %s", "tformat")
t("Rune: Phase Door", "符文：相位之門", "talent name")
t([[Activate the rune to teleport randomly in a range of %d.
		Afterwards you stay out of phase for %d turns. In this state all new negative status effects duration is reduced by %d%%, your defense is increased by %d and all your resistances by %d%%.]], [[激活這個符文會使你在 %d 碼範圍內隨機傳送。 
		之後，你會出入現實空間 %d 回合，所有新的負面狀態持續時間減少 %d%% ，閃避增加 %d ，全體傷害抗性增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("range %d; power %d; dur %d", "範圍 %d; 強度 %d; 持續 %d", "tformat")
t("Rune: Controlled Phase Door", "符文：可控相位之門", "talent name")
t("The targetted phase door fizzles and works randomly!", "目標傳送門故障，隨機傳送！", "logPlayer")
t("Activate the rune to teleport in a range of %d.", "激活這個符文，傳送至 %d 碼內的指定位置。", "tformat")
t("range %d", "範圍 %d", "tformat")
t("Rune: Lightning", "符文：閃電", "talent name")
t([[Activate the rune to fire a beam of lightning, doing %0.2f to %0.2f lightning damage.
		Also transform you into pure lightning for %d turns; any damage will teleport you to an adjacent tile and ignore the damage (can only happen once per turn)]], [[激活這個符文發射一束閃電打擊目標，造成 %0.2f 至 %0.2f 閃電傷害。 
		同時會讓你進入閃電形態 %d 回合：受到傷害時你會瞬移到附近的一格並防止此傷害，一回合只能觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("%d lightning damage", "%d 閃電傷害", "tformat")
t("Infusion: Insidious Poison", "紋身：陰險毒素", "talent name")
t([[Activate the infusion to spit a bolt of poison doing %0.2f nature damage per turn for 7 turns, and reducing the target's healing received by %d%%.
		The sudden stream of natural forces also strips you of one random detrimental magical effect.]], [[激活這個紋身會發射一個毒氣彈造成每回合 %0.2f 自然傷害持續 7 回合，並降低目標治療效果 %d%% 。
		突然涌動的自然力量會除去你受到的一個負面魔法效果。]], "tformat")
t("%d nature damage, %d%% healing reduction", "%d 自然傷害， %d%% 治療下降", "tformat")
t("Rune: Invisibility", "符文：隱身", "talent name")
t([[Activate the rune to become invisible (power %d) for %d turns.
		As you become invisible you fade out of phase with reality, all your damage is reduced by 40%%.
		]], [[激活這個符文使你變得隱形（ %d 隱形等級）持續 %d 回合。 
		由於你的隱形使你從現實相位中脫離，你的所有傷害降低 40%% 。
		]], "tformat")
t("power %d for %d turns", "強度 %d 持續 %d 回合", "tformat")


