	需要在某個星球的空中飛行。]], "_t")
t("High Planetary Orbit", "高空軌道", "talent name")
t([[Activate the powerful flight engines of the Fortress, propelling it fast into high planetary orbit.
	Requires being in flight above the ground of a planet.]], [[啓動堡壘強大的飛行引擎，將其快速推入行星高空軌道。
