t("Hide in Plain Sight", "強制潛行", "talent name")
t("You cannot be stealthy with such heavy armour on!", "你不能在身着重甲的情況下潛行！", "logPlayer")
t([[You have learned how to be stealthy even when in plain sight of your foes.  You may attempt to enter stealth regardless of how close you are to your enemies, but success is more likely against fewer opponents that are farther away.
		Your chance to succeed is determined by comparing %0.2f times your stealth power (currently %d) to the stealth detection of all enemies (reduced by 10%% per tile distance) that have a clear line of sight to you.
		You always succeed if you are not directly observed.
		This resets the cooldown of your Stealth talent, and, if successful, all creatures currently following you will lose track of your position.
		You estimate your current chance to hide as %0.1f%%.]], [[即使在你的敵人面前，你也學會了如何隱身。不管你與敵人有多近，你都可以嘗試潛行，但敵人越少，距離越遠陳功率越高。
		你的成功率取決於你潛行強度的%0.2f倍（當前值 %d ），以及所有能在視野裏看到你敵人的偵測潛行能力（離你距離每有一格則下降10%%）。
		如果沒有敵人能看到你，你一定會潛行成功。
		這一技能會重置潛行技能的冷卻時間。如果使用成功的話，所有敵人都會失去對你位置的感知。
		你估計你目前使用這一技能的成功率爲%0.1f%%。]], "tformat")
t("Unseen Actions", "行動如風", "talent name")
t([[You are able to perform usually unstealthy actions (attacking, using objects, ...) without breaking stealth.	 When you perform such an action while stealthed, you have a chance to stay hidden.
		Success is more likely against fewer opponents and is determined by comparing %0.2f times your stealth power (currently %d) to the stealth detection (reduced by 10%% per tile distance) of all enemies that have a clear line of sight to you.
		Your base chance of success is 100%% if you are not directly observed, and good or bad luck may also affect it.
		You estimate your current chance to maintain stealth as %0.1f%%.]], [[你學會在潛行狀態下使用一些通常會打破潛行的技能（如攻擊，使用物品……）當你在隱身狀態下這麼做的時候，你有一定概率不會打破潛行狀態。
		你的成功率取決於你潛行強度的%0.2f倍（當前值 %d ），以及所有能在視野裏看到你敵人的偵測潛行能力（離你距離每有一格則下降10%%）。
		當你不在敵人的視野內時，基礎成功率爲 100%% ，這一機率還受你的運氣影響。
		你估計當前成功率爲 %0.1f%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Hack'n'Back", "燕回斬", "talent name")
t("You hit your target, doing %d%% damage, distracting it while you jump back %d squares away.", "你打擊目標造成 %d%% 傷害，分散它的注意力並往回跳 %d 碼。", "tformat")
t("Mobile Defence", "輕裝防禦", "talent name")
t("Whilst wearing leather or lighter armour, you gain %d%% Defense and %d%% Armour hardiness.", "當你裝備皮甲或輕甲時，你會增加 %d%% 近身閃避和 %d%% 護甲強度。", "tformat")
t("Light of Foot", "踏雪無痕", "talent name")
t([[You are light on your feet, handling your armour better. Each step you take regenerates %0.2f stamina, and your fatigue is permanently reduced by %0.1f%%.
		At level 3 you are able to walk so lightly that you never trigger traps that require pressure.]], [[你的步伐很輕快，使你能更好的適應盔甲的重量。每移動一步你可以回覆 %0.2f 體力，並且你的疲勞值永久減少 %0.1f%% 。
		在等級3時你的腳步非常輕快，以至於你不會觸發壓力式陷阱。]], "tformat")
t("Strider", "凌波微步", "talent name")
t("You literally dance around your foes, increasing your movement speed by %d%% and reducing the cooldown of Hack'n'Back, Rush, Disengage and Evasion by %d turns.", "你在敵人周圍跳起華麗的舞蹈，增加 %d%% 移動速度並減少燕回斬、衝鋒、逃脫和迴避技能 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Charm Mastery", "飾品掌握", "talent name")
t("Your cunning manipulations allow you to use charms (wands, totems and torques) more efficiently, reducing their cooldowns by %d%%.", "你靈活的頭腦，使你可以更加有效的使用飾品（魔杖、圖騰和項圈），減少 %d%% 飾品的冷卻時間。", "tformat")
t("Piercing Sight", "洞察視界", "talent name")
t([[You look at your surroundings with more intensity than most people, allowing you to see stealthed or invisible creatures.
		Increases stealth detection by %d and invisibility detection by %d.
		The detection power increases with your Cunning.]], [[你比大多數人都更加註意仔細觀察周圍的動靜，使你能發覺隱形和潛行的生物。
		提升偵測潛行等級 %d 並提升偵測隱形等級 %d 。
		你的偵查強度受靈巧加成。]], "tformat")
t("Precision", "弱點打擊", "talent name")
t("You require two weapons to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Precision without dual wielding!", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[You have learned to hit the right spot, increasing your armor penetration by %d when dual wielding.
		The Armour penetration bonus will increase with your Dexterity.]], [[你已經學會打擊弱點位置，雙持時增加你 %d 點護甲穿透。
		護甲穿透受敏捷值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Momentum", "急速切割", "talent name")
t("You require two melee weapons to use this talent.", "你需要雙持武器才能使用這個技能", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Momentum without dual wielding melee weapons!", "你只有雙持武器的時候纔可以使用急速切割！", "logPlayer")
t("When dual wielding, increases attack speed by %d%%, but drains stamina quickly (-6 stamina/turn).", "當你雙持武器時，增加 %d%% 攻擊速度，快速消耗體力（-6體力/回合）。", "tformat")
t("Defensive Throw", "閃身投擲", "talent name")
t("#Source# slams #Target# into the ground!", "#Source#將#Target#掀翻在地！", "logCombat")
t("#Source# throws #Target# to the ground!", "#Source#將#Target#扔到地上！", "logCombat")
t("#Source# misses a defensive throw against #Target#!", "#Source#對#Target#的反擊沒有命中!", "logCombat")
t([[When you avoid a melee blow while unarmed, you have a %d%% chance to throw the target to the ground.  If the throw lands, the target will take %0.2f damage and be dazed for 2 turns, or %0.2f damage and be stunned for 2 turns if the target is grappled.  You may attempt up to %0.1f throws per turn.
		The chance of throwing increases with your Accuracy, the damage scales with your Physical Power, and the number of attempts with your Strength and Dexterity.]], [[當你閃避一次近戰攻擊時，如果你沒有裝備武器你有 %d%% 概率將目標摔到地上。
		如果目標被成功摔倒，則會造成 %0.2f 傷害且目標被眩暈2回合或承受 %0.2f 傷害。同時目標若被抓取，則會被震懾2回合。
		每回合至多觸發 %0.1f 次。
		受命中和物理強度影響，摔投概率和傷害按比例加成。
		觸發次數受力量和敏捷影響。]], "tformat")
t("Roundhouse Kick", "迴旋踢", "talent name")
t([[Attack your foes in a frontal arc with a roundhouse kick, which deals %0.2f physical damage and knocks your foes back 4 grids. This will break any grapples you're maintaining
		The damage improves with your Physical Power.]], [[施展迴旋踢攻擊前方敵人，造成 %0.2f 物理傷害並擊退目標4格。這項攻擊會取消你的抓取效果。
		傷害受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bone Nova", "白骨新星", "talent name")
t([[Fire bone spears in all directions, hitting all foes within radius %d for %0.2f physical damage, and inflicting bleeding for another %0.2f damage over 5 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[向所有方向射出骨矛，對 %d 碼範圍內所有敵人造成 %0.2f 物理傷害,同時在 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 流血傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Ambush", "暗影伏擊", "talent name")
t([[You reach out with shadowy vines toward your target, pulling it to you and silencing it for %d turns and dazing it for 2 turns.
		The chance to hit improves with your Accuracy.]], [[你向目標甩出 1 道影之繩索，將目標拉向你並沉默它 %d 回合，同時眩暈目標 2 回合。 
		技能命中率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Ambuscade", "影分身", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to invoke your shadow!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚陰影。", "logPlayer")
t("A dark shadowy form in the shape of %s.", "一團黑暗的形體模仿了%s的形態。", "tformat")
t("Shadow of %s", "%s的影子", "tformat")
t([[You take full control of your own shadow for %d turns.
		Your shadow possesses your talents and stats, has %d%% life and deals %d%% damage, -30%% all resistances, -100%% light resistance and +100%% darkness resistance.
		Your shadow is permanently stealthed (%d power), and all melee damage it deals is converted to darkness damage.
		The shadow cannot teleport.
		If you release control early or if it leaves your sight for too long, your shadow will dissipate.]], [[你在 %d 回合內完全控制你的影子。 
		你的影子繼承了你的天賦和屬性，擁有你 %d%% 的生命值並造成等同於你 %d%% 的傷害， -30%% 所有抵抗， -100%% 光屬性抵抗並增加 100%% 暗影抵抗。 
		你的影子處於永久潛行狀態（ %d 潛行強度）並且它所造成的所有近戰傷害均會轉化爲暗影傷害。 
		如果你提前解除控制或者它離開你的視野時間過長，你的影分身會自動消失。]], "tformat")
t("Shadow Leash", "暗影束縛", "talent name")
t("%s resists the shadow!", "%s抵抗了陰影！", "logSeen")
t([[For an instant, your weapons turn into a shadow leash that tries to grab the target's weapon, disarming it for %d turns.
		The chance to hit improves with your Accuracy.]], [[使你的武器立刻轉化爲暗影之縛形態，奪取目標武器，繳械目標 %d 回合。 
		技能命中率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dismay", "黑暗痛苦", "talent name")
t("Each turn, those caught in your gloom must save against your Mindpower or have an %0.1f%% chance of becoming dismayed for %d turns. When dismayed, the first melee attack against the foe will result in a critical hit.", "在黑暗光環裏的每一個目標每回合必須與你的精神強度進行豁免鑑定，未通過鑑定則有 %0.1f%% 概率受到黑暗痛苦持續 %d 回合，你對受黑暗痛苦折磨的目標進行的首次近戰攻擊必定暴擊。", "tformat")
t("Shadow Empathy", "陰影鏈接", "talent name")
t([[You are linked to your shadows for %d turns, diverting %d%% of all damage you take to a random shadow.
		Effect increases with Mindpower.]], [[ 你連接到你的陰影，持續 %d 回合，將你受到的傷害的 %d%% 轉移至隨機某個陰影上。
		效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Circle of Blazing Light", "熾焰之陣", "talent name")
t([[Creates a circle of radius %d at your feet; the circle lights up affected tiles, increases your positive energy by %d each turn and deals %0.2f light damage and %0.2f fire damage per turn to everyone else within its radius.  The circle lasts %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在你的腳下製造一個 %d 碼半徑的法陣，它會照亮範圍區域，每回合增加 %d 正能量並造成 %0.2f 光系傷害和 %0.2f 火焰傷害。 
		陣法持續 %d 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blur Sight", "模糊視覺", "talent name")
t([[The caster's image blurs, granting a %d bonus to Defense.
		The bonus will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[施法者的形象變的模糊不清，增加 %d 點閃避。 
		閃避受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Cold Flames", "骨靈冷火", "talent name")
t("cold flames", "冷火", "_t")
t([[Cold Flames slowly spread from %d spots in a radius of %d around the targeted location. The flames deal %0.2f cold damage, and have a chance of freezing.
		Damage improves with your Spellpower.]], [[冰冷的火焰從目標點向 %d 個方向擴散，有效範圍 %d 碼半徑。火焰會造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害並有機率冰凍目標。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Quicken Spells", "快速施法", "talent name")
t("Reduces the cooldown of all spells by %d%%.", "減少 %d%% 所有法術冷卻時間。", "tformat")


