t("Block", "格擋", "talent name")
t("You require a shield to use this talent.", "你需要一面盾牌來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("None", "無", "_t")
t(" and ", "和", "_t")
t(" Increases your spell save by %d for that turn.", " 那回合增加 %d 點法術豁免.", "tformat")
t(" Reflects all blocked damage back to the source.", " 反彈所有格擋的傷害。", "_t")
t(" All blocked damage heals the wielder.", " 所有格擋的傷害值會治療玩家。", "_t")
t([[Raise your shield into blocking position for 2 turns reducing all non-Mind damage by %d. If you block all of an attack's damage, the attacker will be vulnerable to a deadly counterstrike (the next weapon attack will instead deal 200%% damage) for one turn.
			Counterstrike can normally only effect one enemy per block.
			If any damage was successfully blocked this effect will be removed at the start of your turn.
			If the shield has damage resistance to the blocked damage type the block value is increased by 50%%.
			
			Current Bonuses:  %s%s%s%s]], [[舉起你的盾牌進入防禦姿態 2 回合，減少所有非精神攻擊傷害 %d 。如果你完全格擋了一次攻擊，攻擊者將遭到一次致命的反擊（一次普通攻擊將造成 200%% 傷害），持續 1 回合。 
		每次格擋通常只能反擊一個敵人。
		如果有任何傷害被成功格擋，此效果將在回合開始時移除。
		如果盾牌對格擋傷害類型有傷害抗性，則格擋值增加50%% 。
		
		當前加成：%s%s%s%s]], "tformat")
t("Bloom Heal", "夏花之愈", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the power of nature to regenerate your body for %d life every turn for 6 turns.
		The life healed will increase with the Willpower stat.]], [[呼喚自然的力量每回合恢復你 %d 生命值持續 6 回合。 
		恢復量受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("Destroy Magic", "禁魔", "talent name")
t("%s's animating magic is disrupted!", "%s 的魔法力量被幹擾了！", "logSeen")
t("The target has a %d%% chance (stacking to a maximum of %d%%) to fail to cast any spell.  At level 2 magical effects may be disrupted, at level 3 magical sustains may be disrupted, and at level 5 magical constructs and undead may be stunned.", " 目標有 %d%% 概率（最大疊加至 %d%% ）施法失敗率。等級 2 時魔法效果可能會被打斷。等級 3 時持續性法術可能會被打斷。等級 5 時魔法生物和不死族可能會被震懾。", "tformat")
t("Battle Trance", "戰意勃發", "talent name")
t("You overdose on the honeyroot sap!", "你嗑藥過量，混亂了！", "logPlayer")
t([[You enter into a fighting trance, gaining 15%% resist all, losing 15 mindpower, but gaining 20 mental save. However, each turn after the fifth that this talent is active, there is a chance that you will be overcome and become confused.
This does not take a turn to use.]], [[你進入了戰鬥狂熱狀態，獲得 15%% 全體傷害抗性，減少 15 點精神強度並獲得 20 點精神豁免。技能激活 5 回合後，每回合你都有一定機率疲勞，終止技能並進入混亂狀態。
使用這一技能不消耗回合]], "tformat")
t("Soul Purge", "解放靈魂", "talent name")
t("Remove any talent Morrigor has absorbed.", "除去 Morrigor 吸收的所有技能。", "tformat")
t("Dig", "挖掘", "talent name")
t("You require a digger to dig.", "挖掘需要裝備鋤頭。", "logPlayer")
t("digging", "正在挖掘", "_t")
t("dug", "挖掘了", "_t")
t("You have been interrupted!", "你被打斷！", "logPlayer")
t([[Dig/cut a tree/...
		Digging takes %d turns (based on your currently best digger available).]], " 挖掘消耗 %d 回合 ( 基於你攜帶的最好鋤頭 )。", "tformat")
t("Shivgoroth Form", "西弗格羅斯形態", "talent name")
t("You are already a Shivgoroth!", "你已經是寒冰元素了！", "logPlayer")
t([[You absorb latent cold around you, turning into an ice elemental - a shivgoroth - for %d turns.
		While transformed, you do not need to breathe, gain access to the Ice Storm talent at level %d, gain %d%% resistance to cuts and stuns, gain %d%% cold resistance, and all cold damage heals you for %d%% of the damage done.
		The power will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你吸收周圍的寒冰圍繞你，將自己轉變爲純粹的冰元素——西弗格羅斯，持續 %d 回合。 
		轉化成元素後，你不需要呼吸並獲得等級 %d 的冰雪風暴，獲得 %d%% 切割和震懾抵抗， %d%% 寒冰抗性 ,所有冰冷傷害可對你產生治療，治療量基於傷害值的 %d%% 。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Mental Refresh", "振作精神", "talent name")
t("Reset up to 3 wild gift, psionic or cursed talents.", "刷新至多 3 個自然，靈能或詛咒系技能。", "tformat")
t("Dagger Block", "匕首格擋", "talent name")
t([[Raise your dagger into blocking position for one turn, reducing the damage of all physical melee attacks against you by %d. If you block all of an attack's damage, the attacker will be vulnerable to a deadly counterstrike (a normal attack will instead deal 200%% damage) for one turn and be left disarmed for 3 turns.
		The blocking value will increase with your Dexterity and Cunning.]], [[ 舉起你的匕首來格擋攻擊一回合，減少所有物理傷害 %d 點。如果你完全格擋了一次攻擊的傷害，攻擊者將進入致命的被反擊狀態（對其進行的一次攻擊傷害增加到 200%% ）一回合併被繳械三回合。
		格擋值受敏捷值和靈巧值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shieldsmaiden Aura", "女武神之守護", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%s's shield deflects the blow!", "#CRIMSON#%s的盾牌讓攻擊發生了偏斜！", "logSeen")
t("Can block up to 1 hit per 10 turns.", "每 10 回合能自動抵抗一次攻擊。", "tformat")
t("Psionic Maelstrom", "靈能風暴", "talent name")
t("For the next 8 turns, powerful blasts of psionic energies will erupt from you, doing %d damage.", "接下來 8 回合內，強大的靈能能量在你身邊爆發，造成 %d 傷害。", "tformat")
t("Melee retaliation", "近戰報復", "talent name")
t("Intermediary for melee retaliation.", "近戰反傷的中介。", "tformat")


