section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/misc/races.lua"

t("higher", "高等人類", "_t")
t("Wrath of the Highborn", "高等人類之怒", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the power of the Highborn, increasing all damage by %d%% and reducing all damage taken by %d%% for 5 turns.
		The bonus will increase with your Magic.]], [[召喚高等人類的力量，增加所有傷害 %d%% ，減少受到的所有傷害 %d%% ，持續5回合。
		增益效果受魔力值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Overseer of Nations", "遠見卓識", "talent name")
t([[While Highers are not meant to rule other humans - and show no particular will to do so - they are frequently called to higher duties.
		Their nature grants them better senses than other humans.
		Increase blindness immunity by %d%%, maximum sight range by %d, and increases existing infravision, and heightened senses range by %d.
		At talent level 5, each time you hit a target you gain telepathy to all similar creatures in radius 15 for 5 turns.]], [[雖然高等人類的高貴血統並不意味着統治他人——他們也沒有特別的意願去那樣做——但是他們經常承擔更高的義務。 
		他們的本能使得他們比別人有更強的直覺。 
		增加 %d%% 目盲免疫 , 提高 %d 點最大視野範圍並提高 %d 光照、夜視及感應範圍。
		技能等級 5 時，每次你命中目標，你將獲得 15 格範圍內同類型生物感知能力，持續 5 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Born into Magic", "魔法親和", "talent name")
t([[Highers were originally created during the Age of Allure by the human Conclave. They are imbued with magic at the very core of their being.
		Increase spell save by %d and arcane resistance by %d%%.
		Also, when you cast a spell dealing damage, you gain a 20%% bonus to the damage type for 5 turns. (This effect has a cooldown.)]], [[高等人類們最初是在厄流紀由孔克雷夫創造的。他們天生具有魔法天賦。 
		提高 %d 點法術豁免和 %d%% 奧術抵抗。
		每次釋放傷害法術時， 5 回合內該傷害類型獲得 20%% 傷害加成。（該效果有冷卻時間。）]], "tformat")
t("Highborn's Bloom", "生命綻放", "talent name")
t([[Activate some of your inner magic, using it to power your abilities.  For the next %d turns all active talents will be used without resource cost.
		Your resources must still be high enough to initially power the talent and failure rates (etc.) still apply.
		]], [[激活你的內在潛力，以提高你的能力。 
		在接下來 %d 回合中可無消耗使用技能。 
		你的能量值仍需要滿足使用這些技能的最低能量需求，且技能仍有機率會失敗。]], "tformat")
t("shalore", "永恆精靈", "_t")
t("Grace of the Eternals", "不朽的恩賜", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the grace of the Eternals to increase your global speed by %d%% for 5 turns.
		The speed bonus will increase with your Dexterity or Magic (whichever is higher).]], [[召喚不朽的恩賜之力來增加你 %d%% 的整體速度，持續 5 回合。 
		受敏捷和魔法中較高一項影響，速度會有額外的提升。]], "tformat")
t("Magic of the Eternals", "不朽的魔法", "talent name")
t([[Reality bends slightly in the presence of a Shaloren due to their inherent magical nature.
		Increases critical chance by %d%% and critical strike power by %d%%.]], [[因爲永恆精靈的自然魔法，現實發生了輕微的扭曲。 
		提高 %d%% 的暴擊概率和 %d%% 暴擊傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Secrets of the Eternals", "不朽的祕密", "talent name")
t([[As the only immortal race of Eyal, Shaloren have learnt over the long years to use their innate inner magic to protect themselves.
		%d%% chance to become invisible (power %d) for 5 turns when hit by a blow doing at least 10%% of your total life.]], [[作爲埃亞爾僅存的古老種族，永恆精靈在漫長的歲月裏學習到如何用他們與生俱來的精神魔法保護自己。 
		%d%% 的概率使自身進入隱形狀態（ %d 點隱形等級），當承受至少 10%% 總生命值的傷害時觸發，持續 5 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Timeless", "超越永恆", "talent name")
t([[The world grows old as you stand through the ages. To you, time is different.
		Reduces the time remaining on detrimental effects by %d, most cooling down talents by %d, and increases the time remaining on beneficial effects by %d (up to 2 times the current duration).]], [[世界在不斷的變老，而你似乎永恆不變。對於你來說，時間是不同尋常的。 
		減少 %d 回合負面狀態的持續時間，減少技能 %d 回合冷卻時間直至冷卻並增加 %d 回合增益狀態的持續時間（至多延長爲剩餘時間的兩倍）。]], "tformat")
t("thalore", "自然精靈", "_t")
t("Gift of the Woods", "森林的恩賜", "talent name")
t([[Call upon nature to regenerate your body for %d life every turn and increase healing mod by %d%% for 8 turns.
		The life healed will increase with your Willpower or Constitution (whichever is higher).]], [[召喚自然的力量，每回合恢復 %d 生命值，治療係數增加 %d%% ，持續 8 回合。
		生命恢復量受意志值或體質值中較高一項加成。]], "tformat")
t("Verdant", "親近自然", "talent name")
t([[Thaloren have an affinity for natural elements, allowing them to heal for a portion of damage taken from them.
		You gain %d%% Nature and Acid damage affinity.]], [[自然精靈對自然元素有親和力，這讓它們在受到傷害時可以獲得一定的治療。
		獲得 %d%% 自然和酸性傷害吸收。]], "tformat")
t("Guardian of the Wood", "森林守護", "talent name")
t([[Thaloren are part of the wood; it shields them from corruption.
		Increase disease immunity by %d%%, blight resistance by %0.1f%%, and all resistances by %0.1f%%.]], [[自然精靈是森林的一部分，森林保護他們免受侵蝕。 
		提高 %d%% 疾病抵抗、 %0.1f%% 枯萎抵抗和 %0.1f%% 所有抵抗。]], "tformat")
t("Nature's Pride", "自然的驕傲", "talent name")
t("treant", "樹人", "_t")
t("A very strong near-sentient tree.", "一棵非常強大而有感知能力的樹。", "_t")
t([[Nature is with the Thaloren; they can always feel the call of the woods.
		Summons two elite Treants to your side for 8 turns.
		The treants have a global resistance equal to your blight resistance and can stun, knockback, and taunt foes.
		Your Willpower (%d) will be added to all of their non-Magic primary stats and their talent levels will increase with your Nature's Pride talent level.
		Your increased damage, damage penetration, and many other stats will be inherited.]], [[自然與自然精靈同在，你他們可以時刻感受到森林的召喚。 
		召喚 2 個精英樹人，持續 8 回合。 
		樹人的所有抵抗取決於你的枯萎抵抗，並且可以震懾、擊退並嘲諷你的敵人。 
		你的意志值 ( %d ) 將會被加到它們的所有非魔法主要屬性值上，他們的技能等級受到你自然的驕傲技能等級的加成。
		你的傷害加成，傷害穿透和其他許多屬性會被繼承。]], "tformat")
t("dwarf", "矮人", "_t")
t("Resilience of the Dwarves", "鋼筋鐵骨", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the legendary resilience of the Dwarven race to increase armour (+%d), armour hardiness (+%d%%), spell (+%d) and physical (+%d) saves for 8 turns.
		The bonuses will increase with your Constitution.]], [[召喚矮人一族的傳奇血統來增加你 +%d 點護甲值， +%d%% 護甲強度， +%d 點法術豁免和 +%d 物理豁免，持續 8 回合。 
		此效果受你的體質加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stoneskin", "石化皮膚", "talent name")
t([[Dwarf skin is a complex structure; it can automatically react to physical blows and harden itself.
		When you are hit in melee, you have a 15%% chance to increase your armour total by %d for 5 turns and fully ignore the attack triggering it.
		There is no cooldown to this effect; it can happen while already active.]], [[矮人皮膚是一種複雜的結構，它可以在受到打擊後自動硬化。 
		當你被近戰攻擊擊中時有 15%% 的概率增加 %d 點護甲值，持續 5 回合，同時無視觸發該效果的攻擊。
		該效果無冷卻時間，可重複觸發。]], "tformat")
t("Power is Money", "金錢就是力量", "talent name")
t([[Money is the heart of the Dwarven Empire; it rules over all other considerations.
		Increases Physical, Mental and Spell Saves based on the amount of gold you possess.
		+1 save every %d gold, up to +%d. (currently +%d)]], [[金錢是矮人王國的心臟，它控制了所有其他決策。 
		基於你的金幣持有量，增加物理、精神和法術抵抗。 
		+1 豁免值每 %d 單位金幣，最大 +%d (當前 +%d )。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Walking", "穿牆術", "talent name")
t([[While the origins of the dwarves remain clouded in mystery to the other races, it is obvious that they share strong ties to the stone.
		You can target any wall and immediately enter it, appearing on the other side.
		This can pass through up to %d tiles (increases with Constitution and talent level).]], [[雖然矮人的起源對其他種族來說始終是不解之謎，但是很顯然他們的起源與石頭密不可分。 
		你可以指定任何一堵牆並立刻穿過它，出現在另一側。 
		穿牆距離最大 %d 碼（受體質和分類天賦等級影響有額外加成）]], "tformat")
t("halfling", "半身人", "_t")
t("Luck of the Little Folk", "小不點的幸運", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the luck and cunning of the Little Folk to increase your critical strike chance by %d%% and your saves by %d for 5 turns.
		The bonus will increase with your Cunning.]], [[召喚小不點的幸運和機智來提高你 %d%% 暴擊率和 %d 豁免 5 回合。 
		受靈巧影響，此效果有額外增益。]], "tformat")
t("Duck and Dodge", "閃避", "talent name")
t([[Halfling's incredible luck always kicks in at just the right moment to save their skin.
		Whenever you take %d%% or more of your life from a single attack, you gain %d%% Evasion and %d additional defense for the next %d turns. The defense increases based on your luck and other defensive stats.]], [[半身人強大的人品在關鍵時刻總能保他們一命。 
		每當一次攻擊對你造成 %d%% 生命值或更多傷害時，你可以獲得額外 %d%% 閃避率和 %d 點閃避（基於幸運和其他閃避相關數值），持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Militant Mind", "好鬥精神", "talent name")
t([[Halflings have always been a very organised and methodical race; the more foes they face, the more organised they are.
		If two or more foes are in sight your Physical Power, Physical Save, Spellpower, Spell Save, Mental Save, and Mindpower are increased by %0.1f per foe (up to 5 foes).]], [[半身人曾是一個有組織紀律的種族，敵人越多他們越團結。 
		如果有 2 個或多個敵人在你的視野裏，每個敵人都會使你的所有強度和豁免提高 %0.1f 。（最多 5 個敵人）]], "tformat")
t("Indomitable", "不屈意志", "talent name")
t([[Halflings have one of the most powerful military forces in the known world and have been at war with most other races for thousands of years.
		Removes %d stun, daze, or pin effects and grants immunity to stuns, dazes and pins for %d turns.]], [[半身人以驍勇善戰聞名於世，他們曾經在戰場上對抗其他種族上千年。 
		立刻移除 %d 種震懾、眩暈和定身狀態，並使你對震懾、眩暈和定身免疫 %d 回合。
		使用此技能不消耗回合。]], "tformat")
t("orc", "獸人", "_t")
t("Orcish Fury", "獸族之怒", "talent name")
t([[Summons your lust for blood and destruction; especially when the odds are against you.  
		You increase your damage by 10%% + %0.1f%% per enemy you can see in line of sight of you (maximum 5 enemies, %0.1f%% bonus) for 3 turns.
		The damage bonus will increase with your Constitution.]], [[激活你對殺戮和破壞的渴望，尤其是當你孤軍奮戰之時。
		你視野中每有一個敵人，增加所有傷害 10 %% + %0.1f%% （最多5個敵人， %0.1f%% ），持續 3 回合。
		增益受體質值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hold the Ground", "獸族忍耐", "talent name")
t("#CRIMSON#%s roars with rage shaking off %d mental debuffs!", "#CRIMSON#%s憤怒地咆哮，擺脫了%d項精神負面效果！", "logSeen")
t([[Orcs have been the prey of the other races for thousands of years, with or without justification. They have learnt to withstand things that would break weaker races.
		When your life goes below 50%% your sheer determination cleanses you of %d mental debuff(s) based on talent level and Willpower.  This can only happen once every %d turns.
		Also increases physical save by %d.]], [[其他種族對獸族的獵殺持續了上千年，不管是否正義。你們已經學會忍受那些會摧毀弱小種族的災難。 
		當你的生命值降低到 50%% 以下，你強大的意志移除你身上最多 %d 個精神狀態（基於技能等級和意志）。該效果每 %d 回合最多觸發一次。
		額外增加 %d 物理豁免。]], "tformat")
t("Skirmisher", "散兵", "talent name")
t([[Orcs have seen countless battles, and won many of them.
		You revel in the defeat of your foes, gaining %d%% damage resistance for 2 turns each time you kill an enemy.
		The resistance will scale with talent level and your Constitution.
		Additionally, passively increase all damage penetration by %d%%.]], [[獸人們經歷了許多次戰爭，並獲勝了許多次。 
		你陶醉於殺戮你的敵人，每次殺死敵人你將獲得 %d%% 的傷害抗性，持續 2 回合。
		增加的抗性基於你的技能等級和意志。
		被動增加 %d%% 所有傷害穿透。]], "tformat")
t("Pride of the Orcs", "獸族榮耀", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the will of all of the Orc Prides to survive this battle.
		You remove up to %d detrimental effect(s) then heal for %d life.
		The healing will increase with talent level and your Willpower.]], [[呼喚獸族榮耀來和敵人拼搏。 
		移除 %d 個負面狀態並治療 %d 生命值。
		治療量受意志加成。]], "tformat")
t("yeek", "奪心魔", "_t")
t("Dominant Will", "主導意志", "talent name")
t("%s is immune to instakill and mind control effects!", "%s免疫即死和精神控制效果！", "logSeen")
t("%s must be below 80%% of their max life to be controlled!", "%s無法在超過80%%最大生命的情況下被控制！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the mental assault!", "%s抵抗了精神攻擊！", "logSeen")
t([[Shatter the mind of your victim, giving you full control of its actions for %s turns (based on your Willpower).
	When the effect ends, you pull out your mind and the victim's body collapses, dead.
	Targets with ranks at or above rare must be below 80%% of their maximum life to be controlled, will be invulnerable for the duration, and will break free of the effect without dying after 3 turns.
	This effect cannot be saved against but checks instakill immunity.]], [[粉碎目標的意志，使你可以完全控制它的行動 %s 回合。（受你的意志值加成） 
		當技能結束時，你的意志會脫離而目標會因大腦崩潰而死亡。 
		稀有等級即以上的目標必須要在其最大生命值的 80%% 以下才能被控制，在持續時間內不會受到傷害，並且在 3 回合後不會死亡 ,而會脫離控制。
		這一效果無法被豁免，但需要通過即死免疫。]], "tformat")
t("Unity", "強化思維", "talent name")
t([[Your mind becomes more attuned to the Way, and is shielded from outside effects.
		Increase confusion and silence immunities by %d%% and Mental Save by %d.]], [[你的思維和維網變的更加協調並且增強對負面效果的抵抗。 
		增加 %d%% 混亂和沉默抵抗並增加你 +%d 點精神豁免。]], "tformat")
t("Quickened", "迅捷", "talent name")
t("#RED#%s reacts immediately after taking severe wounds!#LAST#", "#RED#%s受傷後反應迅速！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[Yeeks live fast, think fast, and sacrifice fast for the Way.
		Your global speed is increased by %0.1f%%.
		If your life drops below 30%% you gain 1.5 turns.  This effect can only happen once every %d turns.]], [[基於“維網”，奪心魔新陳代謝很快，思維很快並且獻祭也很快。 
		你的整體速度增加 %0.1f%% 。
		當你的生命值降低到 30%% 以下時，你獲得 1.5 個回合。該效果每 %d 回合最多觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Wayist", "快速支援", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("yeek mindslayer", "奪心魔心靈殺手", "_t")
t("A wayist that came to help.", "趕來幫忙的維網幫手。", "_t")
t([[Reach through the collective psionic gestalt of the yeeks, the Way, to call for immediate help.
		Summons up to 3 yeek mindslayers to your side for 6 turns.
		All their primary stats will be set to %d (based on your Willpower and Talent Level).
		Your increased damage, damage penetration, and many other stats will be inherited.]], [[通過奪心魔的維網，迅速召集幫手。 
		在你周圍召喚 3 個奪心魔精英，持續 6 回合。
		他們的所有主要屬性會被設置爲 %d (基於你的意志值和技能等級）
		你的傷害加成，傷害穿透和許多其他屬性都會被繼承。]], "tformat")
t("Knowledge of the Way", "維網的力量", "talent name")
t([[You merge your mind with the rest of the Way for a brief moment; the sum of all yeek knowledge gathers in your mind
		and allows you to identify any item you could not recognize yourself.]], [[你將精神與維網鏈接，能暫時獲得你們一族所有的知識
		讓你能鑑定所有物品。]], "tformat")
t("The various racial bonuses a character can have.", " 多種多樣的種族天賦。", "_t")
t("ogre", "食人魔", "_t")
t("race", "種族技能", "talent category")
t("Ogric Wrath", "食人魔之怒", "talent name")
t([[You enter an ogric wrath for %d turns, increasing your stun and pinning resistances by 20%% and all damage done by 10%%.
		In addition, whenever you use an infusion or rune, miss a melee attack, or any damage you deal is reduced by a damage shield (or similar effect) you gain a charge of Ogre Fury (up to 5 charges total, each lasting 7 turns).
		Each charge grants 20%% critical damage power and 5%% critical strike chance.
		You lose a charge each time you deal a critical strike.
		The duration will increase with your Strength.]], [[你進入憤怒狀態 %d 回合，獲得 20%% 震懾和定身免疫，全體傷害增加 10%% 。
		同時，每當你使用符文或紋身、攻擊未命中或傷害被護盾等效果削減時，你獲得一層食人魔之怒效果，持續 7 回合，效果可疊加至最多 5 層。
		每層提供 20%% 暴擊傷害和 5%% 暴擊率。
		每次暴擊時減少一層食人魔之怒效果。
		持續時間受力量加成。]], "tformat")
t("Grisly Constitution", "強大體魄", "talent name")
t([[An ogre's body is acclimated to spells and inscriptions.
		Increases spell save by %d and improves the contribution of primary stats on infusions and runes by %d%%.
		At level 5 your body is so strong you can use a two handed weapon in your main hand while still using an offhand item.
		When using a two handed weapon this way you suffer a 20%% accuracy, physical power, spellpower and mindpower penalty, decreasing by 5%% per size category above #{italic}#big#{normal}#; further, all damage procs from your weapons are reduced by 50%%.]], [[食人魔的身體對法術和符文親和力很強。
		增加 %d 法術豁免，增加紋身和符文的屬性加成效果 %d%% 。
		技能等級 5 時，你的身體變得如此強壯，能在主手持有雙手武器的同時，副手持有其他副手武器。
		這樣做的話，你的命中、物理、法術、精神強度會下降 20%% ，體型超過#{italic}#'較大'#{normal}#時，每增加一體型，懲罰減少 5%% 。同時你的武器附加傷害減少 50%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Scar-Scripted Flesh", "血肉傷痕", "talent name")
t([[When you crit you have a %d%% chance to reduce by 1 the remaining cooldown of one of your inscriptions and of any saturations effects.
		This effect can only happen once per turn.]], [[每次暴擊時有 %d%% 機率減少隨機一個紋身或符文 1 回合冷卻時間，或減少符文紊亂或紋身紊亂 1 回合持續時間。
		該效果每回合最多觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Writ Large", "符文親和", "talent name")
t("#PURPLE#Your mastery over inscriptions is unmatched! One more inscriptions slot available to buy.", "#PURPLE#你對紋身的掌握無人能及！你可以消耗一個大系點進一步解鎖一個紋身位", "logPlayer")
t([[Instantly removes runic and infusion saturations.
		For %d turns your inscriptions cool down twice as fast.
