section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/psi-archery.lua"

t("Guided Shot", "導引箭", "talent name")
t("Fire and guide an arrow to its target with precise telekinetic nudges. Does normal damage, but accuracy and crit chance are increased by %d.", "射出一支導引箭精確的飛向敵人。造成普通傷害，但是命中和暴擊率提高 %d 。", "tformat")
t("Augmented Shot", "強力射擊", "talent name")
t("Use telekinetic forces to greatly augment the durability and tension of your bow in order to fire an arrow with velocity unmatched by even the mightiest mundane archers. Increases armor penetration by %d, and deals %d%% damage.", "使用精神靈能以增強弓的耐久和張力，使射出的箭具有無與倫比的威力。增加 %d 點護甲穿透並造成 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")
t("Thought-quick Shot", "意念射擊", "talent name")
t("Ready and release an arrow with a flitting thought. This attack does not use a turn, and increases in talent level reduce its cooldown.", "用飛翔的思緒射出一支箭矢。此攻擊不消耗回合數。隨着技能等級提高，冷卻時間縮短。", "tformat")
t("Masterful Telekinetic Archery", "靈能射擊掌握", "talent name")
t("You cannot do that without a telekinetically-wielded bow.", "你沒有靈能持握弓箭，無法這麼做。", "logPlayer")
t([[You temporarily set aside a part of you mind to direct your telekinetically-wielded bow. It will automatically attack the nearest target each turn for %d turns.
			The telekinetically-wielded bow uses Willpower in place of Strength and Cunning in place of Dexterity to determine attack and damage.
			You are not telekinetically wielding anything right now.]], [[你暫時分出一部分精神去控制念動之弓。它會在 %d 回合內自動攻擊1個目標。
			念動弓使用意志和靈巧來代替力量和敏捷決定攻擊。
			你暫時還沒有裝備任何念動武器。]], "tformat")
t([[You temporarily set aside a part of you mind to direct your telekinetically-wielded bow. It will automatically attack a target each turn for %d turns.
			The telekinetically-wielded bow uses Willpower in place of Strength and Cunning in place of Dexterity to determine attack and damage.
		Combat stats:
		Accuracy: %d
		Damage: %d
		APR: %d
		Crit: %0.2f
		Speed: %0.2f]], [[你暫時分出一部分精神去控制念動之弓。它會在 %d 回合內自動攻擊1個目標。
		念動弓使用意志和靈巧來代替力量和敏捷決定攻擊。
		戰鬥屬性：
		命中：%d
		傷害：%d
		護甲穿透：%d
		暴擊率：%0.2f
		攻擊速度：%0.2f]], "tformat")


