t("Slumber", "催眠", "talent name")
t("%s resists the sleep!", "%s抵抗了睡眠！", "logSeen")
t([[Puts the target into a deep sleep for %d turns, rendering it unable to act.  Every %d points of damage the target suffers will reduce the effect duration by one turn.
		When Slumber ends, the target will suffer from Insomnia for a number of turns equal to the amount of time it was asleep (up to ten turns max), granting it %d%% sleep immunity for each turn of the Insomnia effect.
		The damage threshold will scale with your Mindpower.]], [[目標進入持續 %d 回合的深睡眠，使其無法進行任何動作。目標每承受 %d 傷害，睡眠的持續時間減少一回合。 
		當催眠結束時，目標會飽受失眠的痛苦，持續回合等於已睡眠的回合數（但最多 5 回合），失眠狀態的每一個剩餘回合數會讓目標獲得 %d%% 睡眠免疫。 
		傷害臨界點受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Restless Night", "不眠之夜", "talent name")
t([[Targets you have slept take %0.2f mind damage each turn for five turns upon waking.
		The damage will scale with your Mindpower.]], [[被你沉睡的目標在醒來時每行走一回合將承受 %0.2f 精神傷害，持續 5 回合。 
		受精神強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sandman", "睡魔", "talent name")
t([[Increases the amount of damage you can deal to sleeping targets before reducing the effect duration by %d%%, and reduces the sleep immunity of your Insomnia effects by %d%%.
		These effects will be directly reflected in the appropriate talent descriptions.
		The damage threshold bonus will scale with your Mindpower.]], [[增加 %d%% 你對被睡眠目標在睡眠回合減少前所能造成的傷害，並且減少 %d%% 你造成的失眠效果所增加的睡眠免疫。 
		這些效果將即時反映在技能描述中。 
		受精神強度影響，傷害臨界點的增益效果按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dreamscape", "夢境空間", "talent name")
t("You feel it unwise to travel to the dreamscape in such a fragile form.", "你感覺在夢境空間裏使用如此脆弱的形態非常不明智", "logPlayer")
t("This talent cannot be used from within the Dreamscape.", "該技能不能在夢境空間中使用。", "logPlayer")
t("This talent cannot be used here.", "該技能不能在此處使用。", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles...", "法術失敗了...", "logPlayer")
t("Your target must be sleeping in order to enter its dreamscape.", "要進入夢境空間，目標必須處於睡眠狀態。", "logPlayer")
t("You can't cast this on friendly targets.", "該技能不能對友軍釋放。", "logPlayer")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#You are taken to the Dreamscape!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#你進入了夢境空間！", "logPlayer")
t([[Enter a sleeping target's dreams for %d turns.  While in the Dreamscape, you'll encounter the target's invulnerable sleeping form as well as dream projections that it will spawn every other turn to defend its mind.
		Projections inflict 50%% less damage than the original, unless the target has Lucid Dreamer active.
		When the Dreamscape ends, for each projection destroyed, the target's life will be reduced by 10%% and it will be brainlocked for one turn.
		In the Dreamscape, your damage will be improved by %d%%.
		The damage bonus will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[進入某個睡眠狀態目標的夢境中，持續 %d 回合。 
		當你位於夢境空間中時，你將會遇到目標無敵的睡眠形態，每 4 回合它會製造出 1 個夢境守衛來保護它的心靈。 
		除非目標激活了清晰夢境，否則夢境守衛造成的普通傷害只有 50 %%。 
		當夢境空間的效果結束時，你每摧毀一個夢境守衛，目標生命值會減少 10 %%，並且受到持續 1 回合的思維封鎖效果（可疊加）。 
		在夢境空間中時，你的傷害會提高 %d%% 。 
		傷害增益受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/solipsism.lua"

t("Solipsism", "唯我論", "talent name")
t([[You believe that your mind is the center of everything.  Permanently increases the amount of psi you gain per level by 5 and reduces your life rating (affects life at level up) by 50%% (one time only adjustment).
		You also have learned to overcome damage with your mind alone, and convert %d%% of all damage you receive into Psi damage and %d%% of your healing and life regen now recovers Psi instead of life.
		Converted Psi damage you take will be further reduced by %0.1f%% (%0.1f%% from character level with the remainder further reduced by %0.1f%% from talent level).
		The first talent point invested will also increase the amount of Psi you gain from Willpower by 0.5, but reduce the amount of life you gain from Constitution by 0.25.
		The first talent point also increases your solipsism threshold by 20%% (currently %d%%), reducing your global speed by 1%% for each percentage your current Psi falls below this threshold.]], [[你相信你的心靈是世間萬物的中心。 
		每級永久性增加你 5 點靈能值，並減少你 50%% 的生命成長（影響升級時的生命增益，但只在學習此技能時永久影響一次）
		同時你學會用心靈來承受傷害，轉化 %d%% 生命削減爲靈能值削減，並且 %d%% 的治療值和回覆值會轉化爲靈能值的增長。 
		轉化成的靈能值削減將進一步被減少 %0.1f%% （ %0.1f%% 來自於人物等級， %0.1f%% 來自於技能等級。） 
		學習此技能時，（高於基礎值 10 的）每點意志會額外增加 0.5 點靈能值上限，而（高於基礎值 10 的）每點體質會減少 0.25 點生命上限（若低於基礎值 10 則增加生命上限）。 
		學習此技能時，你的唯我臨界點會增加 20 %%（當前 %d%% ），你的靈能值每低於這個臨界點 1 %%，你的所有速度減少 1 %%。]], "tformat")
t("Balance", "唯我論：均衡", "talent name")
t([[You now substitute %d%% of your Mental Save for %d%% of your Physical and Spell Saves throws (so at 100%%, you would effectively use mental save for all saving throw rolls).
		The first talent point invested will also increase the amount of Psi you gain from Willpower by 0.5, but reduce the amount of life you gain from Constitution by 0.25.
		Learning this talent also increases your solipsism threshold by 10%% (currently %d%%).]], [[你現在使用 %d%% 精神豁免值來替代 %d%% 物理和法術豁免（即 100 %%時精神豁免完全替代所有豁免）。 
		學習此技能時，（高於基礎值 10 的）每點意志會額外增加 0.5 點靈能值上限，而（高於基礎值 10 的）每點體質會減少 0.25 點生命上限（若低於基礎值 10 則增加生命上限）。 
		學習此技能也會增加你 10 %%唯我臨界點（當前 %d%% ）。]], "tformat")
t("Clarity", "唯我論：明晰", "talent name")
t([[For every percent that your Psi pool exceeds %d%%, you gain 1%% global speed (up to a maximum of %+d%%).
		The first talent point invested will also increase the amount of Psi you gain from Willpower by 0.5, but reduce the amount of life you gain from Constitution by 0.25 and will increase your solipsism threshold by 10%% (currently %d%%).]], [[當你的靈能值超過 %d%% 時，每超過 1%% 你增加 1%% 整體速度（最大值 %+d%% ）。
		學習此技能時，（高於基礎值 10 的）每點意志會額外增加 0.5 點靈能值上限，而（高於基礎值 10 的）每點體質會減少 0.25 點生命上限（若低於基礎值 10 則增加生命上限），增加你 10%% 唯我臨界點（當前 %d%% ）。]], "tformat")
t("Dismissal", "唯我論：豁免", "talent name")
t("#TAN##Source# mentally dismisses some damage!", "#TAN##Source#精神上豁免了部分傷害!", "delayedLogMessage")
t("#TAN#(%d dismissed)#LAST#", "#TAN#(%d 唯我論：豁免)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Each time you take damage, you roll %d%% of your mental save against it.  A successful saving throw can crit and will reduce the damage by at least 50%%.
		The first talent point invested will also increase the amount of Psi you gain from Willpower by 0.5, but reduce the amount of life you gain from Constitution by 0.25.
		The first talent point also increases your solipsism threshold by 10%% (currently %d%%).]], [[每當你受到傷害時，你會使用 %d%% 精神豁免來鑑定。鑑定時精神豁免可能暴擊，至少減少 50%% 的傷害。 
		學習此技能時，（高於基礎值 10 的）每點意志會額外增加 0.5 點靈能值上限，而（高於基礎值 10 的）每點體質會減少 0.25 點生命上限（若低於基礎值 10 則增加生命上限）。 
		學習此技能也會增加你 10 %%唯我臨界點（當前 %d%% ）。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/telekinetic-combat.lua"

t("Telekinetic Assault", "靈能打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot do that without a weapon in your hands.", "你必須裝備一把武器施展該技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Assault your target with all weapons, dealing two strikes with your telekinetically-wielded weapon for %d%% damage followed by an attack with your physical weapon for %d%% damage.
		This physical weapon attack uses your Willpower and Cunning instead of Strength and Dexterity to determine Accuracy and damage.
		Any active Aura damage bonusses will extend to your main weapons for this attack.]], [[用你的所有武器打擊目標，使用你的靈能武器打擊兩次，造成 %d%% 傷害，然後使用你的物理武器打擊一次，造成 %d%% 傷害。
		物理武器將會使用意志值和靈巧值代替力量值和敏捷值決定命中和傷害。
		在這次攻擊中，所有啓用的光環傷害加成效果也會適用到你的主武器上。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/thermal-mastery.lua"

t("Transcendent Pyrokinesis", "卓越熱能", "talent name")
t([[For %d turns your pyrokinesis transcends your normal limits, increasing your Fire and Cold damage by %d%% and your Fire and Cold resistance penetration by %d%%.
		In addition:
		The cooldowns of Thermal Shield, Thermal Leech, Thermal Aura, Thermal Strike and Pyrokinesis are reset.
		Thermal Aura effects will have their radius increased by 1.
		Your Thermal Shield will have 100%% absorption efficiency and will absorb twice the normal amount of damage.
		Pyrokinesis will inflict Flameshock.
		Thermal Leech will reduce enemy damage by %d%%.
		Thermal Strike will have its secondary cold/freeze explode in radius 1.
		The damage bonus and resistance penetration scale with your Mindpower.
		Only one Transcendent talent may be in effect at a time.]], [[在 %d 回合中你的熱能突破極限，增加你的火焰和寒冷傷害 %d%% ，火焰和寒冷抗性穿透 %d%% 。
		額外效果：
		重置熱能護盾，熱能吸取，熱能光環和意念風暴的冷卻時間。
		根據情況，熱能光環獲得其中一種強化：熱能光環的半徑增加爲 2 格。你的所有武器獲得熱能光環的傷害加成。
		你的熱能護盾獲得 100%% 的吸收效率，並可以吸收兩倍傷害。
		意念風暴附帶火焰衝擊效果。
		熱能吸取將會降低敵人的傷害 %d%% 。
		熱能打擊的第二次寒冷/凍結攻擊將會產生半徑爲 1 的爆炸。
		傷害和抗性穿透受精神強度加成
		同一時間只有一個靈能系技能產生效果。]], "tformat")
t("Brainfreeze", "鎖腦極寒", "talent name")
t([[Quickly drain the heat from your target's brain, dealing %0.1f Cold damage.
		Affected creatures will also be brainlocked for 4 turns, putting a random talent on cooldown, and freezing cooldowns.
		The damage and chance to brainlock increase with your Mindpower.]], [[迅速的抽取敵人大腦的熱量，造成 %0.1f 寒冷傷害。
		受到技能影響的生物將被思維封鎖四回合，隨機技能進入冷卻，並凍結冷卻時間。
		傷害和思維封鎖機率受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Heat Shift", "熱能轉移", "talent name")
t([[Within radius %d, transfer heat from a group of enemies bodies to their equipment, freezing them to the floor while the excess heat disables their weapons and armor.
		Those afflicted will be dealt %0.1f Cold and %0.1f Fire damage, and be pinned (Frozen Feet) and disarmed for %d turns.
		Targets suffering both types of damage will also have have their Armour and saves reduced by %d.
		The chance to apply the effects and the duration increase with your Mindpower.]], [[在半徑 %d 範圍內，將所有敵人身上的熱量轉移到武器上，把敵人凍僵在地面，多餘的熱量則令他們無法使用武器和盔甲。 
		造成 %0.1f 寒冷傷害和 %0.1f 火焰傷害，並對敵人施加定身（凍足）和繳械狀態，持續 %d 回合。
		受到兩種傷害影響的單位也會降低 %d 護甲和豁免。
		施加狀態的機率和持續時間受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thermal Balance", "熱能平衡", "talent name")
t([[You seek balance between fire and cold based on your current Psi level.
		You blast your foes with %0.1f Fire damage based on your current Psi, %0.1f Cold damage based on your max Psi minus your current Psi, in a radius %d ball.
		This sets your current Psi to half of your maximum Psi.
		The damage scales with your Mindpower.]], [[根據當前的意念力水平，你在火焰和寒冷中尋求平衡。
		你對敵人施放一次爆炸，根據當前的意念力造成 %0.1f 火焰傷害，根據意念力最大值與當前值的差值造成 %0.1f 寒冷傷害，爆炸半徑爲 %d 。
		這個技能會使你當前的意念力變爲最大值的一半。
		傷害受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/thought-forms.lua"

t("thought-form", "精神體", "_t")
t("Thought-Form: Bowman", "具象之弧：弓箭手", "talent name")
t("thought-forged bowman", "精神體弓箭手", "_t")
t("A thought-forged bowman.  It appears ready for battle.", "一位身穿皮甲的精神體弓箭手。他時刻準備着戰鬥。", "_t")
t([[Forge a bowman, clad in leather armor, from your thoughts.  The bowman learns Bow Mastery, Combat Accuracy, Steady Shot, Crippling Shot, and Rapid Shot as it levels up, and has +%d Strength, +%d Dexterity, and +%d Constitution.
		Activating this talent will put all other thought-forms on cooldown.
		The stat bonuses will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[你從腦海裏召喚出一位身穿皮甲的精神體弓箭手。當精神體弓箭手到達對應等級時可習得弓術掌握、強化命中、穩固射擊、致殘射擊和急速射擊，並且可增加 %d 點力量、 %d 點敏捷和 %d 體質。 
		激活此技能會使其他具象之弧系技能進入冷卻。 
		屬性增益受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thought-Form: Warrior", "具象之弧：狂戰士", "talent name")
t("thought-forged warrior", "精神體狂戰士", "_t")
t("A thought-forged warrior wielding a massive battle-axe and clad in heavy armor.  It appears ready for battle.", "一位身穿重甲的精神體狂戰士。他時刻準備着戰鬥。", "_t")
t([[Forge a warrior wielding a battle-axe from your thoughts.  The warrior learns Weapon Mastery, Combat Accuracy, Berserker, Death Dance, and Rush as it levels up, and has +%d Strength, +%d Dexterity, and +%d Constitution.
		Activating this talent will put all other thought-forms on cooldown.
		The stat bonuses will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[你從腦海裏召喚出一位手持戰斧的精神體狂戰士。當精神體狂戰士到達對應等級時可習得武器掌握、強化命中、嗜血、死亡之舞和衝鋒，並且可增加 %d 點力量、 %d 點敏捷和 %d 體質。 
		激活此技能會使其他具象之弧系技能進入冷卻。 
		屬性增益受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thought-Form: Defender", "具象之弧：盾戰士", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to summon!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚。", "logPlayer")
t("thought-forged defender", "精神體盾戰士", "_t")
t("A thought-forged defender clad in massive armor.  It wields a sword and shield and appears ready for battle.", "一位身穿重甲的精神體盾戰士。他手持劍盾，時刻準備着戰鬥。", "_t")
t([[Forge a defender wielding a sword and shield from your thoughts.  The solider learns Armor Training, Weapon Mastery, Combat Accuracy, Shield Pummel, and Shield Wall as it levels up, and has +%d Strength, +%d Dexterity, and +%d Constitution.
		Activating this talent will put all other thought-forms on cooldown.
		The stat bonuses will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[你從腦海裏召喚出一位手持劍盾的精神體盾戰士。當精神體盾戰士到達對應等級時可習得護甲掌握、武器掌握、強化命中、盾牌連擊和盾牆，並且可增加 %d 點力量、 %d 點敏捷和 %d 體質。 
		激活此技能會使其他具象之弧系技能進入冷卻。 
		屬性增益受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thought-Forms", "具象之弧", "talent name")
t([[Forge a guardian from your thoughts alone.  Your guardian's primary stat will be improved by %d, its two secondary stats by %d, and it will have Magic, Cunning, and Willpower equal to your own.
		At talent level one, you may forge a mighty bowman clad in leather armor; at level three a powerful warrior wielding a two-handed weapon; and at level five a strong defender using a sword and shield.
		Thought forms can only be maintained up to a range of %d, and will rematerialize next to you if this range is exceeded.
		Only one thought-form may be active at a time, and the stat bonuses will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[你從腦海裏召喚出一位強大的守護者。 
		你的守護者主屬性會增加 %d ，他的兩項副屬性會增加 %d ，同時他的力量、靈巧和意志屬性等同於你的屬性值。 
		在等級 1 時，你會召喚出身着皮甲的弓箭手大師； 
		在等級 3 時，你會召喚出手持雙手武器的精英狂戰士； 
		在等級 5 時，你會召喚出手持劍盾的精英盾戰士。 
		精神體只能存在於 %d 碼範圍內，若超出此範圍，則精神體會回到你身邊。 
		在同一時間內只有一種具象之弧可以激活。 
		屬性增益受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Transcendent Thought-Forms", "具象之弧：卓越", "talent name")
t("Your thought-forms now know Lucid Dreamer, Biofeedback, and Psychometry at talent level %d.", "你的精神體習得技能等級爲 %d 的清晰夢境、生物反饋和共鳴之心。", "tformat")
t("Over Mind", "具象之弧：支配", "talent name")
t("You must have an active Thought-Form to use this talent!", "你必須開啓具象之弧來使用該技能！", "logPlayer")
t([[Take direct control of your active thought-form, improving its damage, attack speed, and maximum life by %d%%, but leaving your body a defenseless shell.
		At talent level 1, any Feedback your Thought-Forms gain will be given to you as well. At level 3, your Thought-Forms gain a bonus to all saves equal to your Mental Save. At level 5, they gain a bonus to all damage equal to your bonus mind damage.
		The secondary bonuses apply whether or not this talent is currently active.
		The life, damage, and speed bonus will improve with your Mindpower.]], [[直接控制當前的精神體，增加其 %d%% 傷害、攻速以及最大生命值，但是此時你的身體會處於比較脆弱的狀態。 
		在等級 1 時，你的守護者所獲得的任何反饋值也會傳遞給你。 
		在等級 3 時，你的守護者會獲得所有豁免的增益效果，數值等同你精神豁免的大小。 
		在等級 5 時，它們會獲得傷害增益，增益值基於你的額外精神傷害。 
		等級 3 的增益爲被動效果，無論此技能是否激活均有效。 
		增益效果受精神強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thought-Form Unity", "具象之弧：共鳴", "talent name")
t([[You now gain %d%% mind speed while Thought-Form: Bowman is active, %d Mindpower while Thought-Form: Warrior is active, and %d%% resist all while Thought-Form: Defender is active. 
		These bonuses scale with your Mindpower.]], [[現在，當具象之弧：弓箭手激活時，你提升 %d%% 精神速度； 
		當具象之弧：狂戰士激活時，你提升 %d 精神強度； 
		當具象之弧：盾戰士激活時，你提升 %d%% 所有抵抗。 
		受精神強度影響，增益效果按比例加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/trance.lua"

t("Trance of Purity", "淨化之幻", "talent name")
t([[Activate to purge negative status effects (100%% chance for the first effect, -%d%% less chance for each subsequent effect).  While this talent is sustained all your saving throws are increased by %d.
		The chance to purge and saving throw bonus will scale with your mindpower.
		Only one trance may be active at a time.]], [[激活以清除負面狀態（100%% 清除第一個狀態，-%d%% 機率清除後續狀態）。當此技能激活時，你的所有豁免值增加 %d 。
		受精神強度影響，淨化機率和豁免增益按比例加成。
		同一時間只有一種迷幻系技能可以激活。]], "tformat")
t("Trance of Well-Being", "治療之幻", "talent name")
t([[Activate to heal yourself for %0.2f life.  While this talent is sustained your healing modifier will be increased by %d%% and your life regen by %0.2f.
		The effects will scale with your mindpower.
		Only one trance may be active at a time.]], [[激活以治療你 %0.2f 生命值。當此技能激活時，你的治療量會增加 %d%% ，同時你的生命回覆會提高 %0.2f 點。
		受精神強度影響，增益按比例加成。
		同一時間只有一種迷幻系技能可以激活。]], "tformat")
t("Trance of Focus", "集中之幻", "talent name")
t([[Activate to increase your critical strike damage by %d%% for 10 turns.  While this talent is sustained your critical strike chance is improved by +%d%%.
		The effects will scale with your mindpower.
		Only one trance may be active at a time.]], [[激活以增加你 %d%% 暴擊傷害，持續10回合。當此技能激活時，你的暴擊率會增加 +%d%% 。
		受精神強度影響，增益按比例加成。
		同一時間只有一種迷幻系技能可以激活。]], "tformat")
t("Deep Trance", "深度幻想", "talent name")
t([[When you wield or wear an item infused by psionic, nature, or arcane-disrupting forces you improve all values under its 'when wielded/worn' field %d%%.
		Note this doesn't change the item itself, but rather the effects it has on your person (the item description will not reflect the improved values).]], [[當你穿戴由靈能、自然或反魔力量灌注的裝備時，你增加 %d%% "當使用或裝備時:"的增益屬性。
		注意此技能不會改變裝備屬性，它的效果只作用於你自身。（此技能的增益也不會在裝備描述上反映出來）。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/psionic/voracity.lua"

t("Kinetic Leech", "動能吸取", "talent name")
t("%s resists the sleep!", "%s抵抗了睡眠！", "logSeen")
t([[You draw kinetic energy from your surroundings to replenish your Psi.
		This will slow all targets within radius %d by %d%% (max %d%%) for four turns, draining %0.1f (max %0.1f) stamina from each.
		You replenish %d (max %d) Psi from the first target, with each additional target restoring 20%% less than the one before it.
		The strength of these effects increases as your Psi depletes and with your Mindpower.]], [[你從周圍吸取動能，來增加自己的靈能值。
		減少 %d 碼半徑範圍內的敵人 %d%% (最多 %d%% )速度，同時每個目標吸取 %0.1f (最多 %0.1f )點體力。
		從第一個目標處你獲得 %d (最多 %d ) 靈能值，之後每個目標減少20%%.
		當靈能值減少時，技能效果會加強。]], "tformat")
t("Thermal Leech", "熱能吸取", "talent name")
t([[You draw thermal energy from your surroundings to replenish your Psi.
		This will freeze all targets within radius %d for %d (max %d) turns, and deal %0.1f (max %0.1f) Cold damage.
		You replenish %d (max %d) Psi from the first target, with each additional target restoring 20%% less than the one before it.
		The damage and the strength of these effects increases as your Psi depletes and with your Mindpower.]], [[你從周圍吸取熱能，來增加自己的靈能值。
		凍結 %d 碼半徑範圍內的敵人 %d （最多 %d ）回合，同時對每個目標造成 %0.1f （最多 %0.1f ）點寒冷傷害。
		從第一個目標處你獲得 %d （最多 %d ）靈能值，之後每個目標減少20%%.
		當靈能值減少時，技能效果會加強。]], "tformat")
t("Charge Leech", "電能吸取", "talent name")
t([[You draw electical potential energy from your surroundings to replenish your Psi.
		This deals %0.1f (max %0.1f) Lightning damage to all targets around you within radius %d, and has a %d%% (max %d%%) chance to daze them for 3 turns.
		You replenish %d (max %d) Psi from the first target, with each additional target restoring 20%% less than the one before it.
		The strength of these effects increases as your Psi depletes and with your Mindpower.]], [[你從周圍吸取電能，來增加自己的靈能值。
		對 %d 碼半徑範圍內的敵人造成 %0.1f (最多 %0.1f ）點閃電傷害，同時有 %d%% （最多 %d%% ）機率使之眩暈 3 回合。
		從第一個目標處你獲得 %d (最多 %d )靈能值，之後每個目標減少20%%.
		當靈能值減少時，技能效果會加強。]], "tformat", {3,1,2,4,5,6,7})
t("Insatiable", "貪得無厭", "talent name")
t("Increases your maximum energy by %d. You also gain %0.1f Psi for each kill and %0.1f Psi for each mind critical.", "增加靈能值上限 %d 。 每次殺死敵人獲得 %0.1f 靈能值，每次精神暴擊獲得 %0.1f 靈能值。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/acid-alchemy.lua"

t("Acid Infusion", "酸液充能", "talent name")
t([[When you throw your alchemist bombs, you infuse them with explosive acid that can blind.
		In addition all acid damage you do is increased by %d%%.
		You cannot have more than one alchemist infusion sustain active at once.]], [[ 將酸性能量填充至鍊金炸彈，能致盲敵人。
		你造成的酸性傷害增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Caustic Golem", "酸化傀儡", "talent name")
t([[While Acid Infusion is active, your bombs coat your golem in acid for %d turns when they hit it.
		While coated, any melee hit against your golem has a %d%% chance to trigger a radius 4 cone of acid towards the attacker that does %0.1f Acid damage to all caught inside. (This can only happen once per turn.)
		The effects increase with your talent level and with the Spellpower and damage modifiers of your golem.]], [[當你的酸性充能激活時，若你的炸彈擊中了你的傀儡，酸液會覆蓋傀儡 %d 回合。
		當傀儡被酸液覆蓋時，任何近戰攻擊有 %d%% 概率產生一次範圍 4 的錐形酸液噴射，造成 %0.1f 點傷害（每回合至多一次）。

		效果受法術強度、技能等級和傀儡傷害加成。]], "tformat")
t("Caustic Mire", "腐蝕之地", "talent name")
t([[A radius %d pool of acid spawns at the target location, doing %0.1f Acid damage each turn for %d turns.
		All creatures caught in the mire will also suffer a %d%% slowness effect.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 一小塊酸液覆蓋了目標地面，散落在半徑 %d 的範圍內，每回合造成 %0.1f 點酸性傷害，持續 %d 回合。
		受影響的生物同時會減速 %d%% 。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dissolving Acid", "酸液溶解", "talent name")
t([[Acid erupts all around your target, dealing %0.1f acid damage.
		The acid attack is extremely distracting, and may remove up to %d physical or mental temporary effects or mental sustains (depending on the Spell Save of the target).
		The damage and chance to remove effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 酸液在目標周圍爆發，造成 %0.1f 點酸性傷害。
		酸性傷害具有腐蝕性，有一定概率除去至多 %d 個物理/精神狀態效果或是精神持續效果。
		受法術強度影響，傷害和機率額外加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/advanced-golemancy.lua"

t("Life Tap", "生命分流", "talent name")
t("Having an Alchemist Golem", "有一個鍊金傀儡", "_t")
t("You tap into your golem's life energies to replenish your own. Drains %d life.", "你汲取傀儡的生命能量來恢復自己。恢復 %d 點生命。", "tformat")
t("Gem Golem", "寶石傀儡", "talent name")
t([[Insert a pair of gems into your golem, providing it with the gem bonuses and changing its melee attack damage type. You may remove the gems and insert different ones; this does not destroy the gems you remove.
		Gem level usable: %d
		Gem changing is done in the golem's inventory.]], [[在傀儡身上鑲嵌 2 顆寶石，它可以得到寶石加成並改變近戰攻擊類型。你可以移除並鑲嵌不同種類的寶石，移除行爲不會破壞寶石。 
		可用寶石等級： %d
		寶石會在傀儡的物品欄中改變成功。]], "tformat")
t("Supercharge Golem", "超載傀儡", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to supercharge!", "沒有足夠的空間來超載傀儡！", "logPlayer")
t("Your golem is currently inactive.", "你的傀儡當前尚未被激活。", "logPlayer")
t([[You activate a special mode of your golem, boosting its regeneration rate by %0.2f life per turn for %d turns.
		If your golem was dead, it is instantly brought back to life with %d%% life.
		While supercharged, your golem is enraged and deals 25%% more damage.]], [[你激活傀儡的特殊模式，提高它每回合 %0.2f 生命回覆速度，持續 %d 回合。 
		如果你的傀儡死亡，它會立刻復活，復活時保留 %d%% 生命值。 
		此技能激活時你的傀儡處於激怒狀態，可增加 25%% 傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Runic Golem", "符文傀儡", "talent name")
t([[Increases your golem's life, mana and stamina regeneration rates by %0.2f.
		At level 1, 3 and 5, the golem also gains a new rune slot.
		Even without this talent, Golems start with three rune slots.]], [[增加傀儡 %0.2f 生命、法力和耐力回覆。 
		在等級 1 、 3 、 5 時，傀儡會增加 1 個新的符文孔。 
		即使沒有此天賦，傀儡默認也有 3 個符文孔。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/aegis.lua"

t("Arcane Reconstruction", "奧術重組", "talent name")
t([[Imbues your body with arcane forces, reconstructing it to a default state, healing for %d life.
		The life healed will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你的身體充滿奧術能量，將其重組爲原始狀態，治療 %d 點生命值。 
		治療量受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shielding", "強化護盾", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with strengthening arcane forces.
		Every damage shield, time shield, displacement shield, and disruption shield affecting you has its power increased by %d%%.
		At level 5, it also increases the duration of all shields by 1 turn.
		The shield value will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你的周身圍繞着強烈的奧術能量。 
		你的每個傷害護盾、時間護盾、轉移護盾、干擾護盾的強度上升 %d%% 。 
		在等級 5 時，它會增加 1 回合所有護盾的持續時間。 
		護盾強度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Arcane Shield", "奧術護盾", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with protective arcane forces.
		Each time you receive a direct heal (not a life regeneration effect), you automatically gain a damage shield equal to %d%% of the heal value for 3 turns.
		This will replace an existing damage shield if the new shield value and duration would be greater than or equal to the old.
		The shield value will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使你的周身圍繞着保護性的奧術能量。 
		每當你獲得一個直接治療時（非持續恢復效果）你會自動獲得一個護盾，護盾強度爲治療量的 %d%% ，持續 3 回合。 
		如果新護盾的量和持續時間比當前護盾大或相等，將會取代之。
		護盾強度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Aegis", "守護印記", "talent name")
t([[Release arcane energies into most magical shields currently protecting you.
		It will affect at most %d shield effects.
		Damage Shield, Time Shield, Displacement Shield:  Increase the damage absorption value by %d%%.
		Disruption Shield: Tap into the stored energies to restore the shield (at a rate of 2 energy per 1 shield power). Any leftover energy is converted back into mana at a rate of %0.2f energy per mana.
		The charging will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[釋放奧術能量充滿當前保護你的魔法護盾，進一步強化它。
		它會影響最多 %d 種護盾效果。 
		傷害護盾，時間護盾，轉移護盾：提高 %d%% 最大傷害吸收值。 
		干擾護盾：將儲存的能量轉化爲護盾值（比例爲2:1）。剩餘能量將以 %0.2f 的比例轉化爲法力值。
		充能強度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/aether.lua"

t("trap", "陷阱", "_t")
t("Aether Beam", "以太螺旋", "talent name")
t("You somehow fail to set the aether beam.", "你沒能設置以太螺旋。", "logPlayer")
t("aether beam", "以太螺旋", "_t")
t([[You focus the aether into a spinning beam of arcane energies, doing %0.2f arcane damage and having 25%% chance to silence the creatures it pierces.
		The beam will also damage its epicenter each turn for 10%% of the damage (but it will not silence).
		The beam spins with incredible speed (1600%%) and can only hit the same target up to 3 times inbetween their turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你凝聚以太能量，釋放出一個以太螺旋，對周圍目標造成 %0.2f 奧術傷害並且有 25 %%機率沉默目標。 
		以太螺旋每回合也會對中心點造成 10 %%的傷害（但是不會沉默目標）。 
		螺旋會以難以置信的速度旋轉。（1600 %%基礎速度），對每個單位最多一個回合擊中3次。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Aether Breach", "以太裂隙", "talent name")
t([[Rupture reality to temporarily open a passage to the aether, triggering %d random arcane explosions in the target area.
		Each explosion does %0.2f arcane damage in radius 2, and will each trigger at one turn intervals.
		Subsequent casts will stack but the explosions will still only occur once per turn and will be centered at the last area targeted.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[撕裂位面，暫時產生通往以太空間的裂隙，在目標區域造成 %d 個隨機魔法爆炸。 
		每個爆炸在 2 碼範圍內造成 %0.2f 奧術傷害，並且每回合只能觸發一次爆炸。 
		在上一次爆炸尚未完全結束時，再次釋放該技能將累計爆炸次數並相應更改爆炸區域。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Aether Avatar", "以太之體", "talent name")
t("#VIOLET#%s loses 50 mana from using a non-Arcane talent!#LAST#", "#VIOLET#%s 由於使用非奧術技能，流失了50點法力值!#LAST#", "logSeen")
t("#LAST# and #AQUAMARINE#", "#LAST#和#AQUAMARINE#", "_t")
t("At level %d: #AQUAMARINE#%s#LAST#", "等級%d: #AQUAMARINE#%s#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Infuse your body with untethered aether forces for %d turns.
		While active, the cooldown for Arcane and Aether spells is divided by 3, your arcane damage and penetration is increased by 25%%, your Disruption Shield radius is increased to 10, and your maximum mana is increased by 33%%.
		Using non arcane based spells in this state is hard and makes you lose 50 mana each time (up to once per turn).
		
		Spells considered arcane for the purpose of not-losing mana are:
		%s]], [[在你的身體中注入無羈的奧術能量，持續 %d 回合。
		當此技能激活時，你的奧術系和以太系技能冷卻時間除以 3 ，你的奧術傷害加成和抗性穿透增加 25%% ，你的干擾護盾的半徑增加到 10 ，你的最大法力值增加 33%% 。
		在這種狀況下使用非奧術的法術是很困難的，你每次使用會失去 50 點法力值（每回合最多一次）。

		不會扣減魔法的奧術法術如下所示：
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Pure Aether", "以太掌握", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with Pure Aether, increasing all your arcane damage by %0.1f%% and ignoring %d%% arcane resistance of your targets.
		At level 5 casting Aether Avatar removes up to %d magical or physical detrimental effects.]], [[純淨的以太能量環繞着你，增加 %0.1f%% 奧術傷害並且無視目標 %d%% 奧術抵抗。 
		在等級 5 時，使用以太之體會移除 %d 個魔法或物理負面效果。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/age-of-dusk.lua"

t("Dire Plague", "恐怖瘟疫", "talent name")
t([[You unleash the glorious vision of the past when the continent was filled with death and plagues.
		All foes in range %d catch a dire plague for 5 turns, dealing %0.2f darkness damage each turn.
		The Dire Plague is considered a disease but is not prevented by disease immunity.
		Every turn there is a %d%% chance of a piece of the soul to be ripped away, increasing your souls by 1.
		]], [[你釋放出過往的光輝景象，大地充滿瘟疫和死亡。
		範圍 %d 碼內的敵人感染 5 回合恐怖瘟疫，每回合受到 %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		這種瘟疫是可怕的疾病，無法被疾病免疫阻擋。
		此外，該瘟疫每回合有 %d%% 機率剝離目標部分靈魂，使你獲得 1 個靈魂。
		]], "tformat")
t("Crepuscule", "黃昏降臨", "talent name")
t("%s resists the crepuscule!", "%s 抵抗了黃昏降臨！", "logSeen")
t([[You call upon an eerie night to aid you for %d turns.
		Each turn you automatically fire a beam of darkness towards a random foe (prioritizing the ones further away) that deals %0.2f darkness damage and has 25%% chance to blind any foes caught inside for 4 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你呼喚黃昏降臨，持續 %d 回合。
		每回合隨機發射一束暗影光線（優先攻擊最遠的敵人），造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害，並有 25%% 機率致盲敵人 4 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("The End of All Hope", "希望終結", "talent name")
t([[Whenever one of your Dire Plague rips a soul it feels the inescapable coming of the end.
		When this happens the darkness damage of the plague is a critical hit and all Dire Plagues in radius %d around it (including itself) have their durations increased by %d turns.
		The duration increase may happen only once per turn.
		If Crepuscule is currently active it fires an additional free beam at the target.
		In addition the chance to rip a soul by Dire Plague increases by %d%%.
		]], [[每當你的恐怖瘟疫撕裂靈魂，受難者將感受到死亡降臨，無以逃避。
		該效果觸發時，瘟疫造成的暗影傷害自動暴擊，且目標周圍 %d 碼範圍內（包括它自己）的恐怖瘟疫將會延長 %d 回合。
		每回合最多觸發 1 次延長效果。
		如果黃昏降臨處於激活狀態，還會額外朝目標發射一道光線。
		此外，你的恐怖瘟疫撕裂靈魂的機率提升 %d%% 。
		]], "tformat")
t("Golden Age of Necromancy", "死靈法術的黃金時代", "talent name")
t([[You recall the age long gone where necromancers had free reign over the world.
		Increases all saves by %d, confusion and teleport resistances by %d%%.
		At level 5 any time you cross the 1 life threshold you become invulnerable for 1 turns.]], [[你回憶起久遠的黃金時代，死靈法師自由支配這個世界。
		獲得 %d 全體豁免， %d%% 混亂和傳送抗性。
		技能等級 5 時，每當你穿越 1 生命值的界線，無敵 1 回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/air.lua"

t("Lightning", "閃電術", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up mana into a powerful beam of lightning, doing %0.2f to %0.2f damage (%0.2f average)
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[用魔法召喚一次強力的閃電造成 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 傷害（平均 %0.2f ）。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Chain Lightning", "連鎖閃電", "talent name")
t([[Invokes a forking beam of lightning doing %0.2f to %0.2f damage (%0.2f average) and forking to another target.
		It can hit up to %d targets up to 10 grids apart, and will never hit the same one twice; nor will it hit the caster.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚一次叉狀閃電造成 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 傷害（平均 %0.2f ）並連鎖到另外一個目標。 
		它最多可以連鎖 10 碼範圍內 %d 個目標並且不會對同一目標傷害 2 次，同樣它不會傷害到施法者。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Feather Wind", "風之羽翼", "talent name")
t([[A gentle wind circles around the caster, increasing carrying capacity by %d, defense against projectiles by %d, pin immunity by %d%% and stun immunity by %d%%.
		At level 4 it also makes you levitate slightly above the ground, allowing you to ignore some traps.
		At level 5 it also grants %d%% movement speed and removes %d fatigue.]], [[一股溫柔的風圍繞着施法者，增加 %d 點負重能力，增加 %d 點對拋射物的閃避，獲得 %d%% 定身免疫和 %d%% 震懾免疫。 
		在等級 4 時，它會使你輕微的漂浮在空中，可忽略部分陷阱。 
		在等級 5 時，同時還會提升你 %d%% 的移動速度並且移除 %d 點疲勞。]], "tformat")
t("Thunderstorm", "閃電風暴", "talent name")
t("#0080FF#A furious lightning storm forms around %s!", "#0080FF#一道強烈的閃電風暴圍繞着%s！", "logSeen")
t("#0080FF#The furious lightning storm around %s calms down and disappears.", "#0080FF#圍繞着%s的閃電風暴沉寂了下來並消失了。", "logSeen")
t([[Conjures a furious, raging lightning storm with a radius of 6 that follows you as long as this spell is active.
		Each turn, a random lightning bolt will hit up to %d of your foes for 1.00 to %0.2f damage (%0.2f average) in a radius of 1.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[當此技能激活時，在 6 碼半徑範圍內召喚一陣強烈的閃電風暴跟隨你。 
		每回合閃電風暴會隨機傷害 %d 個敵方單位，對 1 碼半徑範圍造成 1.00 ～ %0.2f 傷害（平均 %0.2f ）。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/animus.lua"

t("Soul Leech", "靈魂吸取", "talent name")
t([[Each time you or your undead minions deal damage to a creature you apply Soul Leech to them.
		If a creature dies with this effect active, you steal its soul.
		Strong creatures and bosses are so overflowing with soul power that you steal a fragment of their soul every few turns:
		%s- rare: at most every %d turns
		%s- unique: at most every %d turns
		%s- boss: at most every %d turns
		%s- elite boss: at most every %d turns#WHITE#

		Also increases your maximum souls capacity by %d .
		]], [[每當你或你的不死隨從對敵人造成傷害，將會對其附加靈魂吸取效果。
		如果敵人在靈魂吸取狀態下死去，你將會偷取它的靈魂。
		強大的敵人和Boss的靈魂力量如此強大，你可以每隔幾個回合從它們的身上偷取一個靈魂：
		%s- 稀有：每 %d 回合偷取一個靈魂
		%s- 史詩：每 %d 回合偷取一個靈魂
		%s- Boss：每 %d 回合偷取一個靈魂
		%s- 精英Boss：每 %d 回合偷取一個靈魂#WHITE#
		
		此外，增加你的最大靈魂儲量 %d 。
		]], "tformat")
t("Consume Soul", "消耗靈魂", "talent name")
t([[Consume a soul whole to rebuild your body, healing you for %d and generating %d mana.
		If used below 1 life the surge increases your spellpower by %d for 10 turns.
		The heal and mana increases with your Spellpower.]], [[消耗一個靈魂，用來修復你的身體，恢復 %d 生命值，獲得 %d 法力值。
		如果你當前生命值在 1 以下，這股力量還將會提升你的法術強度 %d ，持續 10 回合。
		治療量和法力值受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Torture Souls", "折磨靈魂", "talent name")
t([[Unleash dark forces to all foes in sight that are afflicted by Soul Leech, dealing %0.2f frostdusk damage to them and tearing apart their souls.
		This returns up to %d souls to you (one for each foe hit).
		The damage increases with your Spellpower.]], [[朝視野內所有被靈魂吸收影響的敵人放出黑暗能量，對其造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害，並撕裂它們的靈魂。
		這將會讓你獲得最多 %d 個靈魂（每擊中一個獲得一個）。
		傷害受法術強度提升。
		]], "tformat")
t("Reaping", "靈魂收割", "talent name")
t([[You draw constant power from the souls you hold within your grasp.
		If you hold at least 2, your mana regeneration is increased by %0.1f per turn.
		If you hold at least 5, your spellpower is increased by %d.
		If you hold at least 8, all your resistances are increased by %d.]], [[你從掌握的靈魂中持續汲取力量，根據當前靈魂數量獲得以下效果：
		2 個以上： 你的每回合法力值恢復速度增加 %0.1f 。
		5 個以上： 你的法術強度增加 %d 。
		8 個以上： 你的全體傷害抗性增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/arcane.lua"

t("Manathrust", "奧術射線", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up mana into a powerful bolt doing %0.2f arcane damage.
		At level 3, it becomes a beam.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[製造出一個強大的奧術之球對目標造成 %0.2f 奧術傷害。 
		在等級 3 時，它會有穿透效果。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Arcane Power", "奧術能量", "talent name")
t("Your mastery of magic allows you to enter a state of deep concentration, increasing your Spellpower by %d and arcane resistance by %d%%.", "你對魔法的理解使你進入精神集中狀態，增加 %d 點法術強度和 %d%% 奧術抗性。", "tformat")
t("Arcane Vortex", "奧術漩渦", "talent name")
t([[Creates a vortex of arcane energies on the target for 6 turns. Each turn the vortex will look for another foe in sight and fire a manathrust doing %0.2f arcane damage to all foes in line.
		If no foes are found, the target will take 50%% more arcane damage.
		If the target dies, the vortex explodes, releasing all remaining damage in a radius 2 ball of arcane force.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在目標身上放置一個持續 6 回合的奧術漩渦。 
		每回合，奧術漩渦會隨機尋找視野內的另一個敵人，並且釋放一次奧術射線，對一條線上的所有敵人造成 %0.2f 奧術傷害。 
		若沒有發現其他敵人，則目標會承受 150 %%額外奧術傷害。 
		若目標死亡，則奧術漩渦爆炸並釋放所有的剩餘奧術傷害，在 2 碼半徑範圍內形成奧術爆炸。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Disruption Shield", "干擾護盾", "talent name")
t("#VIOLET#%s's disruption shield collapses and then explodes in a powerful manastorm!", "#VIOLET#%s的干擾護盾破碎並爆炸產生了一股強力的法力風暴！", "logSeen")
t("#SLATE#(%d absorbed)#LAST#", "#SLATE#(%d 護盾吸收)#LAST#", "tformat")
t("#PURPLE#(%d mana)#LAST#", "#PURPLE#(%d 法力值)#LAST#", "tformat")
t("%s restores Disruption Shield (+%d) and gains %d mana with Aegis!", "%s使用守護印記復原了干擾護盾(+%d)並獲得%d法力值！", "logSeen")
t("%s restores Disruption Shield (+%d) with Aegis!", "%s使用守護印記復原了干擾護盾(+%d)！", "logSeen")
t([[Surround yourself with arcane forces, disrupting any attempts to harm you by creating a shield of pure aether which can absorb %d damage.
		In combat, the mental focus required to maintain and monitor the shield is too much and you let it run on its own. In this state once the shield power is depleted it will start using your mana to absorb hits, at a ratio of %0.2f mana per damage.
		Whenever mana is used by the shield it stores a remnant of this energy (up to %d max). When the shield is deactivated any stored energy is released in a radius %d arcane storm that lasts 5 turns, dealing 20%% of the total stored damage each turn.
		Outside of combat the shield regenerates 10%% of its power each turn and stored energy quickly dissipates.
		Dropping below 50%% mana or reaching max energy storage will automatically deactivate this talent.
		The shield power improves with your Spellpower.
		The maximum energy storage is based on your total mana (ignoring sustained spells), with a limit at %d effective mana.

		Current shield power: %d
		Current stored energy: %d]], [[你的身邊充滿奧術力量，製造出一層能吸收 %d 傷害的護盾。
		在戰鬥中你無法集中精力持續維持這層護盾，一旦護盾值消耗歸零，則會使用你的法力值來吸收傷害，比例爲 %0.2f 法力值吸收一點傷害。
		每當法力值被該效果消耗時，護盾會儲存一定能量（最多 %d ）。當護盾關閉時，這些儲存的能量將轉化爲在你身邊 %d 格的奧術風暴，在5回合內每回合造成 20%% 累計吸收傷害的傷害。
		戰鬥外該護盾每回合回覆 10%% ，同時儲存的能量迅速消散。
		當你法力值下降到 50%% 以下，或者達到最大能量存儲量，護盾會自動關閉。
		護盾值受法術強度加成。
		最大儲存能量受原始法力值上限加成（無視已經啓用的維持技能），在 %d 法力值的時候達到上限。

		當前護盾值：%d
		當前儲能：%d]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/conveyance.lua"

t("Phase Door", "相位之門", "talent name")
t("The targeted phase door fizzles and works randomly!", "相位之門定位失敗了，變爲隨機傳送!", "logPlayer")
t([[Teleports you randomly within a small range of up to %d grids.
		At level 4, it allows you to specify which creature to teleport.
		At level 5, it allows you to choose the target area (radius %d).
		If the target area is not in line of sight, there is a chance the spell will partially fail and teleport the target randomly.
		The range will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在 %d 碼範圍內隨機傳送你自己。 
		在等級 4 時，你可以傳送指定生物（怪物或被護送者）。 
		在等級 5 時，你可以選擇傳送位置（半徑 %d ）。 
		如果目標位置不在你的視線裏，則法術有可能失敗，變爲隨機傳送。 
		影響範圍受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Teleport", "傳送", "talent name")
t("Select a target to teleport...", "選擇目標傳送...", "logPlayer")
t("The spell fizzles!", "法術失敗了!", "logSeen")
t("Select a teleport location...", "選擇傳送位置...", "logPlayer")
t("The targetted teleport fizzles and works randomly!", "傳送定位失敗了，變爲隨機傳送!", "logPlayer")
t([[Teleports you randomly within a large range (%d).
		At level 4, it allows you to specify which creature to teleport.
		At level 5, it allows you to choose the target area (radius %d).
		If the target area is not in line of sight, there is a chance the spell will partially fail and teleport the target randomly.
		Random teleports have a minimum range of %d.
		The range will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在 %d 碼範圍內隨機傳送。 
		在等級 4 時，你可以傳送指定生物（怪物或被護送者）。 
		在等級 5 時，你可以選擇傳送位置（半徑 %d ）。 
		如果目標位置不在你的視線裏，則法術有可能失敗，變爲隨機傳送。 
		隨機傳送的最小半徑爲 %d 。
		影響範圍受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Displacement Shield", "偏轉護盾", "talent name")
t([[This intricate spell erects a space distortion around the caster that is linked to another distortion, placed around a target.
		Any time the caster should take damage, there is a %d%% chance that it will instead be warped by the shield and hit the designated target.
		Once the maximum damage (%d) is absorbed, the time runs out (%d turns), or the target dies, the shield will crumble.
		The max damage the shield can absorb will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[這個複雜的法術可以扭曲施法者周圍的空間，此空間可連接至範圍內的另外 1 個目標。 
		任何時候，施法者所承受的傷害有 %d%% 的概率轉移給指定連接的目標。 
		一旦吸收傷害達到上限（ %d ），持續時間到了（ %d 回合）或目標死亡，護盾會破碎掉。 
		護盾的傷害最大吸收值受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Probability Travel", "次元移動", "talent name")
t([[When you hit a solid surface, this spell tears down the laws of probability to make you instantly appear on the other side.
		Teleports up to %d grids.
		After a successful probability travel you are left unstable, unable to do it again for a number of turns equal to %d%% of the number of tiles you blinked through.
		The range will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[當你擊中一個固體表面時，此法術會撕裂位面將你瞬間傳送至另一面。 
		傳送最大距離爲 %d 碼。 
		在一次成功的移動後，你將進入不穩定狀態，在基於你傳送碼數的 %d%% 回合內，無法再次使用該技能。 
		傳送距離受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/death.lua"

t("Rigor Mortis", "屍僵症", "talent name")
t("%s resists the Rigor Mortis!", "%s 抵抗了屍僵症！", "logSeen")
t([[Press your advantage when your foes are starting to crumble.
		For every detrimental effect on the target you deals %0.2f frostdusk damage (with diminishing returns) and reduce its global speed by 25%% for one turn per effect (up to a maximum of %d).
		The diminishing returns on damage bonus works this way:
		- 2 effects: %0.2f
		- 5 effects: %0.2f
		- 10 effects: %0.2f
		- 15 effects: %0.2f
		And so on...
		Damage increases with your Spellpower.
		]], [[利用敵人的痛楚打擊敵人。
		目標每具有一個負面效果，造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害（有收益衰減），並降低其整體速度 25%% （最大降低 %d ）。
		傷害加成的收益衰減如下面所示：
		- 2 個效果： %0.2f 傷害
		- 5 個效果： %0.2f 傷害
		- 10 個效果： %0.2f 傷害
		- 15 個效果： %0.2f 傷害
		以此類推。
		傷害受法術強度加成。
		]], "tformat")
t("Drawn To Death", "黃泉之路", "talent name")
t([[Every time you or one of your minions kill a creature you create a temporary link to the place of death.
		For %d turns afterwards you can instantly and accurately teleport to it (if it is in sight).
		]], [[每當你或你的隨從殺死一個生物，你可以創建一個通向它死亡的地方的臨時通道。
		 %d 回合內，你可以瞬間、準確地傳送到視野內的那個位置。
		]], "tformat")
t("Grim Shadow", "冷酷陰影", "talent name")
t("#GREY#Darkness pulsates around %s!", "#GREY#黑暗從%s身上散發出來！", "logSeen")
t([[Your body starts to radiate shadows, increasing your darkness resistance by %d%%, armour by %d and defence by %d.
		Any time you absorb a soul the shadows pulse outward, dealing %0.2f frostdusk damage to all foes in range %d and knocking them back 3 tiles.
		This can only happen once per turn.
		The damage increases with your Spellpower.]], [[你的身體開始散發暗影，獲得 %d%% 暗影抗性， %d 護甲值和 %d 閃避值。
		每當吸收靈魂，你體內的黑暗會放射出來，對範圍 %d 內所有敵人造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害，並將其擊退 3 格。
		這一效果每回合最多觸發一次。
		傷害受法術強度提升。]], "tformat", {1,2,3,5,4})
t("Utterly Destroyed", "徹底毀滅", "talent name")
t([[Whenever a creature is killed by yourself or a minion you feast on its essence, gaining %0.1f mana.
		At level 3 the thrill of the death invigorates you, granting a movement speed bonus of 50%% for %d turns.]], [[每當你或你的隨從殺死一個敵人，你吞噬它的精華，獲得 %0.1f 法力值。
		技能等級 3 時，對死亡的渴望還會激勵你，讓你獲得 50%% 移動速度加成，持續 %d 回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/deeprock.lua"

t("Deeprock Form", "深巖形態", "talent name")
t(", Arcane damage by %0.1f%% and Arcane damage penetration by %0.1f%%", ", 增加 %0.1f%% 奧術傷害和 %0.1f%% 奧術抗性穿透", "tformat")
t(", Nature damage by %0.1f%% and Nature damage penetration by %0.1f%%", ", 增加 %0.1f%% 自然傷害和 %0.1f%% 自然抗性穿透", "tformat")
t(" and %d%% bleeding, poison, disease, and stun immunity", " 和 %d%% 流血、毒素、疾病和震懾免疫", "tformat")
t([[You call upon the very core of the world, harnessing its power to transform your body.
		For %d turns you become a Deeprock Elemental, gaining two size categories%s.
		This increases your Physical damage by %0.1f%% and Physical damage penetration by %0.1f%%%s, and armour by %d.%s
		The effects increase with spellpower.]], [[你呼喚世界深層的核心之力，用來改造自己的身體。
		%d 回合內，你將變成深巖元素形態，增加 2 點體型 %s 。
		同時，你將增加 %0.1f%% 物理傷害和 %0.1f%% 物理抗性穿透 %s ，並獲得 %d 點護甲。 %s
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("\
In addition, you use your physical resistance versus all damage against you.", "\
另外，你用你的物理抗性對抗所有對你的傷害。", "_t")
t("Volcanic Rock", "火山熔岩", "talent name")
t([[When you turn into a Deeprock elemental your Arcane damage is increased by %0.1f%%, Arcane damage penetration by %0.1f%% and you gain the power to invoke volcanos:
		%s]], [[當你進入深巖元素形態時，增加 %0.1f%% 奧術傷害和 %0.1f%% 奧術抗性穿透，同時獲得激發火山的能力:
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Boulder Rock", "岩石投擲", "talent name")
t([[When you turn into a Deeprock elemental your Nature damage is increased by %0.1f%%, Nature damage penetration by %0.1f%% and you gain the power to throw boulders:
		%s]], [[當你進入深巖元素形態時，增加 %0.1f%% 自然傷害和 %0.1f%% 自然抗性穿透，同時獲得投擲巨石的能力:
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Mountainhewn", "山崩地裂", "talent name")
t([[While in deeprock form, you become indomitable, granting you %d%% resistance to cuts, poisons, diseases and stuns.
		At level 5 and higher, while Deeprock Form is active, all incoming damage is applied against physical resistance instead of the normal resistance type.]], [[當你進入深巖元素形態時，你獲得 %d%% 流血、毒素、疾病和震懾免疫。
		技能等級 5 或以上時，在深巖元素形態下，你將用物理抗性取代其他傷害抗性。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/divination.lua"

t("Arcane Eye", "奧術之眼", "talent name")
t([[Summons an ethereal magical eye at the designated location that lasts for %d turns.
		The eye cannot be seen or attacked by other creatures, and possesses magical vision that allows it to see any creature in a %d range around it.
		It does not require light to do so, but it cannot see through walls.
		Casting the eye does not take a turn.
		Only one arcane eye can exist at any given time.
		At level 4, if cast on a creature it will follow it until it expires, or until the creature dies.
		At level 5, it will place a magical marker on the creatures, negating invisibility and stealth effects.]], [[召喚 1 個奧術之眼放置於指定地點，持續 %d 回合。 
		此眼睛不會被其他生物看見或攻擊，它提供魔法視覺，可看到它周圍 %d 碼範圍的怪物。 
		它不需要燈光去提供能量，且它的視線無法穿牆。 
		召喚奧術之眼不消耗回合。 
		同時只能存在 1 個奧術之眼。 
		在等級 4 時，可以在怪物身上放置奧術之眼，持續時間直到技能結束或怪物死亡。 
		在等級 5 時，它可以在怪物身上放置一個魔法標記並無視隱形和潛行效果。]], "tformat")
t("Keen Senses", "敏銳直覺", "talent name")
t([[You focus your senses, getting information from moments in the future.
		Improves your capacity to see invisible foes by +%d, to see through stealth by +%d, and to perform a critical spell cast by +%d%%.
		The effects will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[你集中精神，通過直覺獲取未來的信息。 
		增加偵測隱形等級 +%d
		增加偵測潛行等級 +%d
		增加法術暴擊機率 +%d%%
		此效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Vision", "探測", "talent name")
t("Form a map of your surroundings in your mind in a radius of %d", "通過意念探測周圍地形，有效範圍： %d 碼。", "tformat")
t("Premonition", "預感", "talent name")
t("#OLIVE_DRAB#Your premonition allows you to raise a shield just in time!", "#OLIVE_DRAB#你的預知能力是你及時獲得一個護盾！", "logPlayer")
t([[Echoes of the future flash before your eyes, allowing you to sense some incoming attacks.
		If the attack is not physical, you will erect a temporary shield that reduces all damage of this type by %d%% for 5 turns.
		This effect can only happen once every 5 turns, and happens before damage is taken.
		The bonus will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的眼前會閃爍未來的景象，讓你能夠預知對你的攻擊。 
		如果攻擊是元素類或魔法類的，那麼你會創造一個臨時性的護盾來減少 %d%% 所有此類攻擊傷害，持續 5 回合。 
		此效果每隔 5 回合只能觸發一次，且在承受傷害前被激活。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/dreadmaster.lua"

t("Dread", "夢魘", "talent name")
t([[Summon a Dread of level %d that will annoyingly blink around, hexing your foes.
		It knows the following spells:
		- Burning Hex at level %d
		- Empathic Hex at level %d
		- Pacification Hex at level %d
		- Blur Sight at level %d
		- Phase Door at level %d
		]], [[召喚一個等級 %d 的夢魘。夢魘會四處傳送，並對敵人釋放邪術。
		它會使用以下技能：
		- 燃燒邪術等級 %d
		- 轉移邪術等級 %d
		- 寧神邪術等級 %d
		- 模糊視覺等級 %d
		- 相位之門等級 %d
		]], "tformat")
t("Souleater", "噬魂者", "talent name")
t("#GREY#%s has fed on enough minions and starts to randomly hex foes!", "#GREY#%s吸取了足夠多的隨從，開始隨機對敵人釋放邪術！", "logSeen")
t([[Any time one of your minions dies or expires, and even if it is resurrected by a boneyard, the dread feeds on it.
		Each time it feeds it gets healed for %d and reduces remaining cooldown of its spells by %d.
		Every 10 minion deaths it casts a random hex on up to %d foes at once, instantly and without triggering a cooldown.]], [[每當你的一個死靈隨從死亡或超時的時候，夢魘會吸收它的能量，即使它被大墓地復活了仍然會如此。
		每當夢魘吸收一個隨從，它會恢復 %d 生命值，並降低其法術剩餘冷卻時間 %d 。
		每當它吸收 10 個死亡的隨從，它會立刻朝最多 %d 個敵人釋放邪術，不消耗時間，也不會觸發技能冷卻。]], "tformat")
t("Neverending Peril", "不滅災厄", "talent name")
t("In an effort to make your dread more annoying you focus a shell of darkness around it, rendering it fully invincible for %d turns.", "你使用一層暗影包裹你召喚的夢魘，以便最大限度給敵人帶來擾亂。夢魘在 %d 回合內進入無敵狀態。", "tformat")
t("Dreadmaster", "夢魘之王", "talent name")
t([[You now summon a Dreadmaster instead of a Dread.
		Dreadmasters learn to cast silence, disperse magic and mind disruption, making them the ultimate annoyance tool.
		It learns them at talent level %d.]], [[你改爲召喚夢魘之王取代夢魘。
		夢魘之王可以釋放技能等級 %d 的沉默、驅散和精神干擾，是擾亂敵人的強大力量。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/earth.lua"

t("Pulverizing Auger", "粉碎鑽擊", "talent name")
t([[Fire a powerful beam of stone-shattering force, digging out any walls in its path up to %d range.
		The beam continues to a range of %d, affecting any creatures in its path, dealing %0.2f physical damage to them.
		If any walls are dug, you gain %d%% physical damage bonus for 6 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[射出一道能擊碎岩石的強有力的射線，在其路徑上擊碎 %d 碼距離內的所有牆壁。
		射線會繼續前進直到 %d 碼距離處，對路徑上的所有生物造成 %0.2f 點物理傷害。 
		如果有牆壁被擊碎，你在 6 回合內獲得 %d%% 物理傷害加成。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Skin", "石化皮膚", "talent name")
t([[The caster's skin grows as hard as stone, granting a %d bonus to Armour.
		Each time you are hit in melee, you have a %d%% chance to reduce the cooldown of an Earth or Stone spell by 2 (this effect can only happen once per turn).
		The bonus to Armour will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[施法者的皮膚變的和岩石一樣堅硬，提高 %d 點護甲。 
		每次你被近戰攻擊擊中，你有 %d%% 機率減少一個土系或石系法術 2 回合冷卻（一回合最多一次）。
		護甲受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Mudslide", "山崩地裂", "talent name")
t([[Conjures a mudslide, dealing %0.2f physical damage in a radius of %d. Any creatures caught inside will be knocked back 8 spaces.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚一次山崩對敵人造成 %0.2f 點物理傷害（ %d 碼錐形範圍）。 
		範圍內的任何敵人都將被擊退。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stone Wall", "岩石堡壘", "talent name")
t("stone wall", "石牆", "_t")
t("a summoned wall of stone", "召喚的岩石牆壁", "_t")
t([[Entomb yourself in a wall of stone for %d turns.
		At level 4, it becomes targetable.
		Any hostile creature caught in the radius will also suffer %0.2f physical damage.
		Duration and damage will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚岩石堡壘環繞着你，持續 %d 回合。 
		在等級 4 時，它可以環繞其他目標。
		範圍內的任何敵對生物將受到 %0.2f 點物理傷害。 
		持續時間和傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/eldritch-shield.lua"

t("Eldritch Blow", "奧術盾擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Eldritch Blow without a shield!", "沒有盾牌，無法使用奧術盾擊!", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the stun!", "%s抵抗了震懾！", "logSeen")
t([[Channel eldritch forces into a melee attack, hitting the target with your weapon and shield for %d%% arcane damage.
		If either attack hits, the target will be stunned for %d turns and you automatically Block.
		The chance for the attack to stun increases with your Physical Power, but it is considered a magical attack and thus is resisted with spell save, rather than physical save.
		Damage increases with Spellpower.]], [[調用奧術能量，激發近戰攻擊，使用武器和盾牌攻擊目標造成 %d%% 奧術武器傷害。
		只要有一次命中，將震懾目標 %d 回合，並且你會進入格擋狀態。
		由於這次攻擊視爲魔法攻擊，震懾成功率由己方物理強度和目標法術豁免（非物理豁免）決定。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Eldritch Infusion", "奧術充能", "talent name")
t("You require a shield to use this talent.", "你需要一面盾牌來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Imbues your shields with arcane power, dealing %0.2f arcane damage with each melee strike and %0.2f arcane damage when hit.
		Your shields radiate with eldritch forces, imbuing you back with %d spellpower and mindpower per tier of your shields (offhand counts for half). Current bonus is %d.
		Allows counterstrikes after incomplete blocks and the cooldown of Block is reduced by %d turns.
		The damage will increase with Spellpower.]], [[用奧術能量給盾牌充能，每次近戰攻擊附加 %0.2f 奧術傷害，同時每次受到近戰攻擊時反擊 %0.2f 點奧術傷害。
		你的盾牌放射出埃爾德里奇能量，盾牌每材質等級獲得 %d 法術和精神強度（副手盾牌加成減半）。當前加成爲 %d 。
		當你不完全格擋時，也可以進行反擊。格擋技能的冷卻時間降低 %d 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Eldritch Fury", "奧術連擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Eldricth Fury without a shield!", "必須裝備一面盾牌！", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the dazing blows!", "%s抵抗了眩暈打擊!", "logSeen")
t([[Channel eldritch forces into a ferocious melee attack, hitting the target three times with your shields doing %d%% Nature damage.
		If any of the attacks hit, the target will be dazed for %d turns and your Block cooldown is reset.
		The chance for the attack to daze increases with you Physical Power, but it is considered a magical attack and thus is resisted with spell save, rather than physical save.]], [[調用奧術能量，激發近戰攻擊，用盾牌攻擊目標三次，造成 %d%% 自然武器傷害。
		只要有一次命中，將眩暈目標 %d 回合，你的格擋技能冷卻將會被重置。
		由於這次攻擊視爲魔法攻擊，震懾成功率由己方物理強度和目標法術豁免（非物理豁免）決定。]], "tformat")
t("Eldritch Slam", "奧術猛擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Eldritch Slam without a shield!", "必須裝備一面盾牌！", "logPlayer")
t([[Slam your shield on the ground creating a shockwave.
		You perform a melee attack for %d%% arcane damage against everyone within radius %d.
		Any creature hit by the attack will be submitted to a Counterstrike effect for 3 turns, as if you had blocked against them.
		At level 5 your Block cooldown is reset.]], [[用盾牌猛擊地面，製造衝擊波。
		對半徑 %d 內的生物造成 %d%% 奧術武器傷害。
		所有被擊中的目標將會進入可以反擊的狀態 3 回合，就像你格擋了它們的攻擊那樣。
		在等級 5 時，你的格擋技能冷卻也會被重置。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/eldritch-stone.lua"

t("Stone Spikes", "岩石尖刺", "talent name")
t("poisoned for %0.1f Nature damage over 6 turns (%d%% healing reduction)", "中毒 6 回合受到合計 %0.1f 點自然傷害（同時減少 %d%% 治療效果） ", "tformat")
t(", blasted for %0.1f Arcane damage (and silenced for %d turns),", ", 受到 %0.1f 點奧術傷害（同時沉默 %d 回合）,", "tformat")
t(" impaled for %0.1f Physical damage (and disarmed for %d turns),", " 受到 %0.1f 點物理傷害（同時繳械 %d 回合）,", "tformat")
t([[Stony spikes erupt from the ground in a radius %d cone.
		Creatures caught in the area will be %scut for %0.1f Physical damage dealt over 6 turns.
		The damage increases with your Spellpower, and the chance to apply the detrimental effect(s) improves with Spellpower or Physical Power, whichever is greater.]], [[在半徑 %d 的錐形範圍內，從地下爆發岩石尖刺。
		範圍內的生物將 %s 在 6 回合內受到 %0.1f 物理傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成，負面狀態附加機率受法術強度和物理強度較高一項影響。]], "tformat")
t(" and ", "和", "_t")
t("Poisoned Spikes", "劇毒尖刺", "talent name")
t([[Coats your stone spikes with insidious poison, dealing %0.1f total nature damage over 6 turns while reducing all healing by %d%%.
		The damage increases with Spellpower and the chance to poison and healing reduction increases with either Spellpower or Physical Power, whichever is greater.]], "用毒素覆蓋岩石尖刺，使生物中毒 6 回合，造成合計 %0.1f 自然傷害，並減少 %d%% 治療效果。", "tformat")
t("Eldritch Spikes", "奧術尖刺", "talent name")
t([[Imbues your stone spikes with arcane forces, dealing %0.1f Arcane damage and silencing each target hit for %d turns.
		The damage increases with Spellpower and the chance to silence increases with either Spellpower or Physical Power, whichever is greater.]], "用奧術能量填充岩石尖刺，造成 %0.1f 奧術傷害，並沉默 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Impaling Spikes", "穿透尖刺", "talent name")
t([[Your stone spikes grow in length, instantly dealing %0.1f Physical damage and disarming targets hit for %d turns.
		The damage increases with Spellpower and the chance to disarm increases with either Spellpower or Physical Power, whichever is greater.]], "強化你的岩石尖刺，造成 %0.1f 物理傷害，並繳械 %d 回合。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/energy-alchemy.lua"

t("Lightning Infusion", "閃電充能", "talent name")
t([[When you throw your alchemist bombs, you infuse them with lightning damage that can daze your foes.
		In addition all lightning damage you do is increased by %d%%.
		You cannot have more than one alchemist infusion sustain active at once.]], [[ 將閃電能量填充至鍊金炸彈，能眩暈敵人。
		你造成的閃電傷害增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Dynamic Recharge", "動態充能", "talent name")
t("%s is energized by the attack, reducing some talent cooldowns!", "%s被這次攻擊充能，減少了部分技能冷卻時間。", "logSeen")
t([[While Lightning Infusion is active, your bombs energize your golem.
		All talents on cooldown on your golem have %d%% chance to be reduced by %d.]], [[ 當閃電充能開啓時，你的炸彈會給傀儡充能。
		你的傀儡的所有冷卻中技能有 %d%% 概率減少 %d 回合冷卻時間。]], "tformat")
t("Thunderclap", "閃電霹靂", "talent name")
t("You need to ready alchemist gems in your quiver.", "需要裝備鍊金寶石。", "logPlayer")
t([[By crushing an alchemist gem you generate a thunderclap in a cone of radius %d dealing %0.2f physical damage and %0.2f lightning damage.
		All creatures caught inside are knocked back and disarmed for %d turns.
		The duration and damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 粉碎一顆鍊金寶石，製造一次閃電霹靂，在半徑 %d 的錐形區域內造成 %0.2f 點物理傷害和 %0.2f 點閃電傷害。
		範圍內的生物將會被擊退並被繳械 %d 回合。
		傷害和持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Living Lightning", "閃電之體", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#%s is energized by all the damage taken!", "#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#%s從承受的傷害中獲得了能量！", "logSeen")
t("%s's %s", "%s的%s", "tformat")
t([[Infuse your body with lightning energy, bolstering your movement speed by +%d%%.
		Each turn, a foe within range %d will be struck by lightning and be dealt %0.1f Lightning damage.
		In addition, damage to your health will energize you.
		At the start of each turn in which you have lost at least %d life (20%% of your maximum life) since your last turn, you will gain %d%% of a turn.
		The effects increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 將閃電能量填充到身體中，增加 %d%% 移動速度。
		每回合半徑 %d 內的一個生物將會被閃電擊中，造成 %0.1f 點閃電傷害。
		另外，對你的傷害會激活你。
		每次你的回合開始時，如果自從上個回合結束你受到至少 %d 點傷害（20%% 最大生命值），你將獲得 %d%% 個額外回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/enhancement.lua"

t("Arcane Strike", "奧術打擊", "talent name")
t("You require a weapon to use this talent.", "你需要武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Strike twice with your mainhand weapon dealing %d%% Arcane damage.
		If either of these attacks hit you gain %d mana.
		The mana gain will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使用你的主手武器打擊兩次目標，造成 %d%% 奧術傷害。
		如果任何一擊命中目標，你獲得 %d 法力值。
		法力值恢復受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fiery Hands", "燃燒之手", "talent name")
t([[Engulfs your hands (and weapons) in a sheath of fire, dealing %0.2f fire damage per melee attack and increasing all fire damage dealt by %d%%.
		Each hit will also regenerate %0.2f stamina.
		The effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的雙手籠罩在火焰中，每次近戰攻擊會造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害並提高所有火焰傷害 %d%% 。 
		每次攻擊同時也會回覆 %0.2f 體力值。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shock Hands", "閃電之觸", "talent name")
t([[Engulfs your hands (and weapons) in a sheath of lightning, dealing %d lightning damage with a chance to daze (25%%) per melee attack and increasing all lightning damage dealt by %d%%.
		Each hit will also regenerate %0.2f mana.
		The effects will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的雙手籠罩在雷電中，每次近戰攻擊會造成 %d 閃電傷害（25%% 機率眩暈敵人），並提高 %d%% 所有閃電系傷害。
		每次攻擊同時也會回覆 %0.2f 法力值。 
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Inner Power", "心靈之力", "talent name")
t([[You concentrate on your inner self, increasing your Strength, Dexterity, Magic, and Cunning by %d.
		Additionally, you gain a shield absorbing %d damage before you take damage every %d turns.
		The stat increase and shield will improve with your Spellpower.]], [[你專注於你的內心，增加你 %d 點力量，敏捷，魔法和靈巧。
		在你受到傷害前，你會產生一個吸收 %d 傷害的護盾，該效果最多每 %d 回合觸發一次。
		屬性值增長和護盾強度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/eradication.lua"

t("Boneyard", "大墓地", "talent name")
t("#GREY#%s is resurrected by the boneyard!", "#GREY#%s被大墓地復活了！", "logSeen")
t([[Spawn a boneyard of radius %d around you that lasts for 8 turns.
		Any foes inside gain the brittle bones effect, reducing their physical resistance by %d%% and making all cooldowns %d%% longer.
		When one of your minions stands in the boneyard they gain %d more physical and spell power.
		At level 5 when a minion dies inside the boneyard it has a %d%% chance to resurrect instantly. This effect may only happen once per minion.
		]], [[在你周圍 %d 碼範圍內召喚大墓地，持續 8 回合。
		範圍內的敵人獲得脆骨效果，降低 %d%% 物理傷害抗性，並延長 %d%% 技能冷卻時間。
		大墓地中的死靈隨從會獲得額外 %d 物理和法術強度。
		技能等級 5 時，在大墓地中死亡的隨從有 %d%% 機率原地復活。每個隨從只能這樣復活一次。
		]], "tformat")
t("To The Grave", "葬身之所", "talent name")
t("%s resists the call of the boneyard!", "%s抵抗了大墓地的召喚！", "logSeen")
t([[Teleport all foes in radius %d to your boneyard, as close to its center as possible.
		Up to %d ghouls or skeletons are created around them by the boneyard, without any additional soul cost, but they only last 5 turns.
		]], [[將 %d 碼範圍內的所有敵人傳送到大墓地內，並儘可能拖入大墓地的中央。
		然後，在它們的周圍製造最多 %d 個食屍鬼或骷髏，召喚它們不會額外消耗靈魂，但是隻能留存 5 回合。
		]], "tformat")
t("Impending Doom", "災厄降臨", "talent name")
t([[Your target's doom draws near. Its healing factor is reduced by 80%%, and will take %d%% of its remaining life (or %0.2f, whichever is lower) over 10 turns as frostdusk damage.
		This spell is so powerful that every 3 turns it tears a part of the target's soul, generating one soul for you.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你使目標厄運臨頭。10回合內，目標的治療加成減少 80%% ， 並累計受到 %d%% 剩餘生命值（至多 %0.2f 點）霜暮傷害。
		這個法術的力量是如此強大，每 3 回合它會撕裂目標靈魂的一部分，使你獲得一個靈魂。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Eternal Night", "永恆之夜", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with Frostdusk, increasing all your darkness and cold damage by %0.1f%%, and ignoring %d%% of the darkness and cold resistance of your targets.
		At the end of each turn if you are under 1 life you are healed for %d%% of all damage you dealt.]], [[使用霜暮的力量覆蓋全身，增加 %0.1f%% 暗影和寒冷傷害，並無視目標 %d%% 的暗影和寒冷抗性。
        此外，若你生命值少於1點，你造成的傷害會在回合結束時以 %d%% 比例治療自身。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/explosives.lua"

t("Throw Bomb", "炸彈投擲", "talent name")
t("You need to ready alchemist gems in your quiver.", "需要裝備鍊金寶石。", "logPlayer")
t([[Imbue an alchemist gem with an explosive charge of mana and throw it.
		The gem will explode for %0.1f %s damage.
		Each kind of gem will also provide a specific effect.
		The damage will improve with better gems and with your Spellpower.]], [[向一塊鍊金寶石內灌輸爆炸能量並扔出它。 
		寶石將會爆炸並造成 %0.1f 的 %s 傷害。 
		每個種類的寶石都會提供一個特殊的效果。 
		傷害受寶石品質和法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Alchemist Protection", "鍊金保護", "talent name")
t([[Grants %d%% protection to you, your golem and other friendly creatures against the elemental damage of your own bombs, and against external elemental damage (fire, cold, lightning and acid) by %d%%.
		At talent level 5 it also protects against all side effects of your bombs.]], [[提高你和其他友好生物對自己炸彈 %d%% 的元素傷害抵抗，並增加 %d%% 對外界的元素傷害抵抗。 
		在等級 5 時它同時會保護你免疫你的炸彈所帶來的特殊效果。]], "tformat")
t("Explosion Expert", "爆破專家", "talent name")
t([[Your alchemist bombs now affect a radius of %d around them.
		Explosion damage may increase by %d%% (if the explosion is not contained) to %d%% if the area of effect is confined.]], [[鍊金炸彈的爆炸半徑現在增加 %d 碼。
		增加 %d%% （地形開闊）～ %d%% （地形狹窄）爆炸傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Shockwave Bomb", "烈性炸彈", "talent name")
t("You need to ready at least two alchemist gems in your quiver.", "至少需要裝備兩枚鍊金寶石。", "logPlayer")
t([[Crush together two alchemist gems, making them extremely unstable.
		You then throw them to a target area, where they explode on impact, dealing %0.2f physical damage and knocking back any creatures in the blast radius.
		Each kind of gem will also provide a specific effect.
		The damage will improve with better gems and with your Spellpower.]], [[將 2 顆鍊金寶石壓縮在一起，使它們變的極度不穩定。 
		然後，你將它們扔到指定地點，爆炸會產生 %0.2f 物理傷害並擊退爆炸範圍內的任何怪物。 
		每個種類的寶石都會提供一個特殊的效果。 
		傷害受寶石品質和法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/fire-alchemy.lua"

t("Flame Infusion", "火焰充能", "talent name")
t([[When you throw your alchemist bombs, you infuse them with flames that burn for a few turns.
		In addition all fire damage you do is increased by %d%%.
		You cannot have more than one alchemist infusion sustain active at once.]], [[給鍊金炸彈附加火焰能量, 使敵人進入灼燒狀態
		此外，你造成的所有火焰傷害增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Smoke Bomb", "煙霧彈", "talent name")
t([[Throw a smoke bomb, blocking everyone's line of sight. The smoke dissipates after %d turns.
		If a creature inside is victim of fire burns the smoke will consume instantly, replicating the burns on all foes and increasing its duration by %d turns.
		Duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[投擲一枚煙霧彈，遮住一條直線的視野。 %d 回合後煙霧會消失。 
		若煙霧中存在處於引燃狀態的生物，則會將煙霧消耗一空並在所有目標身上附加引燃效果，持續時間增加 %d 回合。 
		持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fire Storm", "火焰風暴", "talent name")
t("firestorm", "火焰風暴", "_t")
t([[A furious fire storm rages around the caster, doing %0.2f fire damage in a radius of 3 each turn for %d turns.
		You closely control the firestorm, preventing it from harming your party members.
		The damage and duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[製造一片激烈的火焰風暴，每回合對施法者周圍 3 碼範圍內的目標造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，持續 %d 回合。 
		你精確的操控火焰風暴，阻止它傷害你的隊友。 
		傷害和持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Body of Fire", "火焰之軀", "talent name")
t("#FF8000#%s turns into pure flame!", "#FF8000#%s完全成爲了火焰！", "logSeen")
t("#FF8000#The raging fire around %s calms down and disappears.", "#FF8000#圍繞%s的憤怒火焰沉寂了下來並消失了。", "logSeen")
t([[Turn your body into pure flame, increasing your fire resistance by %d%%, burning any creatures striking you in melee for %0.2f fire damage, and randomly launching up to %d slow-moving fire bolt(s) per turn at targets in sight, each dealing %0.2f fire damage.
		The projectiles safely go through your friends without harming them.
		The damage and resistance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[將你的身體轉化爲純淨的火焰，增加你 %d%% 火焰抵抗。對任何進展攻擊你的怪物造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害並向附近目標每回合隨機射出 %d 個緩慢移動的火焰球，每個火球造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。 
		傷害和火焰抵抗受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/fire.lua"

t("Flame", "火球術", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a bolt of fire, setting the target ablaze and doing %0.2f fire damage over 3 turns.
		At level 5, it will create a beam of flames.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[製造一個火球，使目標進入灼燒狀態並在 3 回合內造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。 
		在等級 5 時，火焰會有穿透效果。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Flameshock", "火焰衝擊", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a cone of flame with radius %d. Any targets caught in the area will suffer Burning Shock, stunning them and dealing %0.2f fire damage over %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在你前方製造一片 %d 碼半徑錐形範圍的火焰。 
		任何在此範圍的目標會被燃燒的火焰衝擊，共受到 %0.2f 點火焰傷害，持續 %d 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fireflash", "爆裂火球", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a bolt of fire that moves toward the target and explodes into a flash of fire, doing %0.2f fire damage in a radius of %d.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[向你的目標發射一枚爆裂火球，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，有效範圍 %d 碼。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Inferno", "地獄火", "talent name")
t([[Raging flames burn foes and allies alike, doing %0.2f fire damage in a radius of %d each turn for %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[向地上釋放一片火焰，每回合可對敵我雙方造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，半徑 %d 碼，持續 %d 回合。
		受法術強度影響，傷害有額外加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/frost-alchemy.lua"

t("Frost Infusion", "冰霜充能", "talent name")
t([[When you throw your alchemist bombs, you infuse them with cold damage that can freeze your foes.
		In addition all cold damage you do is increased by %d%%.
		You cannot have more than one alchemist infusion sustain active at once.]], [[將寒冰能量填充至鍊金炸彈，能冰凍敵人。
		你造成的寒冰傷害增加 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("Ice Armour", "寒冰護甲", "talent name")
t([[While Frost Infusion is active, your bombs deposit a layer of ice on your golem for %d turns when they hit it.
		This ice provides your golem with %d additional armour, melee attacks against it deal %0.1f Cold damage to the attacker, and 50%% of its damage is converted to Cold.
		The effects increase with your talent level and with the Spellpower and damage modifiers of your golem.]], [[當你的寒冰充能激活時，若你的炸彈擊中了你的傀儡，冰霜會覆蓋傀儡 %d 回合。
		冰霜會增加傀儡 %d 點護甲，同時受到近戰攻擊時，會反擊攻擊方 %0.1f 點寒冷傷害，同時傀儡造成的傷害的 50%% 轉化爲寒冰傷害。
		效果受法術強度、技能等級和傀儡傷害加成。]], "tformat")
t("Flash Freeze", "極速凍結", "talent name")
t([[Invoke a blast of cold all around you with a radius of %d, doing %0.1f Cold damage and freezing creatures to the ground for %d turns.
		Affected creatures can still act, but cannot move.
		The duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 在半徑 %d 的範圍內激發寒冰能量，造成 %0.1f 點寒冷傷害，同時將周圍的生物凍結在地面上 %d 個回合。 
		受影響的生物能夠行動，但不能移動。
		持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Ice Core", "冰霜之軀", "talent name")
t([[Turn your body into pure ice, increasing your Cold damage affinity by %d%% and your physical resistance by %d%%.
		You have a %d%% chance to shrug off all direct critical hits (physical, mental, spell).
		The effects increase with your Spellpower.]], [[ 將你的身體轉化爲純淨的寒冰體，你受到的寒冰傷害的 %d%% 會治療你，同時你的物理抗性增加 %d%% 。
		你有 %d%% 機率擺脫暴擊傷害（物理，精神，法術）。
		效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/glacial-waste.lua"

t("Hiemal Shield", "寒冬護盾", "talent name")
t("#GREY#Your hiemal shield does not have enough resources!", "#GREY#你的寒冬護盾資源不夠！", "logPlayer")
t("#GREY#Your hiemal shield regenerates to full!", "#GREY#你的寒冬護盾恢復到滿了！", "logPlayer")
t("#SLATE#(%d absorbed)#LAST#", "#SLATE#(%d 護盾吸收)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Conjure a shield of ice around you that can absorb a total of %d damage.
		Anytime it does it retaliates by sending a bolt of ice at the attacker, dealing %0.2f cold damage (this can only happen once per turn per creature).
		When you are above 1 life it only affects 66.6%% of the damage, letting through the rest.
		When you are under 1 life it affects 100%% of the damage and also reduces the damage of critical hits by %d%%.
		10 turns after leaving combat the shield will consume its mana and soul cost again to fully regenerate if needed. if that cost can not be matched, it unsustains.
		The shield strength will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使用冰塊在你的身邊形成一道護盾，吸收最多 %d 點傷害。
		每當其受到傷害，它會對攻擊者發射一團冰球，造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害（每個生物每回合最多觸發一次）
		當你的生命值在 1 以上的時候，護盾只吸收 66.6%% 的傷害。
		當你的生命值在 1 以下時，護盾吸收 100%% 傷害，還會降低你受到的暴擊傷害 %d%% 。
		當你脫離戰鬥 10 回合後，護盾將會試圖消耗魔法和靈魂，將其恢復到滿。如果不能滿足這一條件，護盾會解除。
		護盾強度受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Desolate Waste", "荒蕪之地", "talent name")
t([[Every time your shield loses %d%% of its original value a circle of desolate waste will spawn under you, lasting 6 turns, and dealing %0.2f cold damage per turn to foes within radius %d.
		If a creature is hit by your hiemal shield's retribution bolt while on the waste, the shield feeds of the wasteland to regenerate %0.1f%% of its original value.
		No more than %d desolate wastes can trigger per shield activation.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[每當你的寒冰護盾損失 %d%% 原始護盾值，在你周圍 %d 碼範圍內的大地會變成荒蕪的極寒之地，對敵人在 6 回合內造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		如果一個生物在荒蕪之地上被寒冬護盾的冰球擊中，護盾將會吸收荒蕪之地的能量，恢復 %0.1f%% 原始護盾值。
		每次護盾最多觸發 %d 次荒蕪之地效果。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {1,3,2,4,5})
t("Crumbling Earth", "破碎大地", "talent name")
t([[Your desolate wastes are now rapidly crumbling.
		Any foe moving through them is likely to get cut, taking %0.2f cold damage and bleeding over 4 turns (stacking) while reducing its movement speed by 15%%.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的荒蕪大地開始破碎。
		在荒蕪大地上移動的敵人有機率被冰劃傷流血受傷，受到 %0.2f 寒冷傷害，流血 4 回合（可以疊加），並降低移動速度 15%% 。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bleak Guard", "冰寒守衛", "talent name")
t([[Your hiemal shield is stronger, taking %d%% less damage from all attacks.
		When under 1 life this effect is increased to %d%%.]], [[你進一步強化寒冬護盾的效果，所受所有傷害降低 %d%% 。
		當生命值在 1 以下時，這一效果提升 %d%% 。]], "tformat")


