section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/golem.lua"

t("Knockback", "擊退", "talent name")
t("%s resists the knockback!", "%s抵抗了擊退！", "logSeen")
t([[Your golem rushes to the target, dealing %d%% damage and knocking it back.
		Knockback chance will increase with talent level.
		While rushing the golem becomes ethereal, passing harmlessly through creatures on the path to its target.]], [[你的傀儡衝向目標，將其擊退並造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		擊退機率受技能等級加成。]], "tformat")
t("Taunt", "嘲諷", "talent name")
t("#Source# provokes #Target# to attack it.", "#Source#強制#Target#攻擊它", "logCombat")
t("The golem taunts targets in a radius of %d, forcing them to attack it.", "你的傀儡嘲諷 %d 碼半徑範圍的敵人，強制他們攻擊傀儡。", "tformat")
t("Crush", "壓碎", "talent name")
t("%s resists the crushing!", "%s抵抗了壓碎", "logSeen")
t([[Your golem rushes to the target, crushing it into the ground for %d turns and doing %d%% damage.
		Pinning chance will increase with talent level.
		While rushing the golem becomes ethereal, passing harmlessly through creatures on the path to its target.]], [[你的傀儡衝向目標，將其推倒在地持續 %d 回合，造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		受技能等級影響，定身機率有加成。]], "tformat")
t("Pound", "敲擊", "talent name")
t("Your golem cannot do that currently.", "你的傀儡現在不能使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the dazing blow!", "%s抵抗了眩暈打擊！", "logSeen")
t([[Your golem rushes to the target and creates a shockwave with radius 2, dazing all foes for %d turns and doing %d%% damage.
		Daze chance increases with talent level.
		While rushing the golem becomes ethereal, passing harmlessly through creatures on the path to its target.]], [[你的傀儡衝向目標，踐踏周圍 2 碼範圍，眩暈所有目標 %d 回合並造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		眩暈機率受技能等級加成。]], "tformat")
t("Eye Beam", "眼睛光束", "talent name")
t([[Your golem fires a beam from his eyes, doing %0.2f fire damage, %0.2f cold damage or %0.2f lightning damage.
		The beam will always be the maximun range it can be and will not harm friendly creatures.
		The damage will increase with your golem's Spellpower.]], [[從你的眼睛中發射一束光束，造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害， %0.2f 冰冷傷害或 %0.2f 閃電傷害。 
		該射線永遠具有最大範圍，並不會傷害友方單位。
		傷害受傀儡的法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Reflective Skin", "反射皮膚", "talent name")
t([[Your golem's skin shimmers with eldritch energies.
		Any damage it takes is partly reflected (%d%%) to the attacker.
		The golem still takes full damage.
		Damage returned will increase with your golem's Spellpower.]], [[你的傀儡皮膚閃爍着艾爾德里奇能量。 
		所有對其造成的傷害有 %d%% 被反射給攻擊者。 
		傀儡仍然受到全部傷害。 
		傷害反射值受傀儡的法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Arcane Pull", "奧術牽引", "talent name")
t("#Target# is pulled toward #Source#!", "#Target#被拉向#Source#!", "logCombat")
t("Your golem pulls all foes within radius %d toward itself while dealing %0.2f arcane damage.", "你的傀儡將 %d 碼範圍內的敵人牽引至身邊，並造成 %0.2f 奧術傷害。", "tformat")
t("Molten Skin", "熾熱皮膚", "talent name")
t([[Turns the golem's skin into molten rock. The heat generated sets ablaze everything inside a radius of 3, doing %0.2f fire damage in 3 turns for %d turns.
		Burning is cumulative; the longer they stay within range, they higher the fire damage they take.
		In addition the golem gains %d%% fire resistance.
		Molten Skin damage will not affect friendly creatures.
		The damage and resistance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使傀儡的皮膚變成灼熱岩漿，發出的熱量可以將 3 碼範圍內的敵人點燃，在 3 回合內每回合造成 %0.2f 灼燒傷害持續 %d 回合。 
		灼燒可疊加，他們在火焰之中持續時間越長受到傷害越高。 
		此外傀儡獲得 %d%% 火焰抵抗。 
		熾熱皮膚不能影響傀儡的主人。 
		傷害和抵抗受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Self-destruction", "自爆", "talent name")
t([[The golem self-destructs, destroying itself and generating a blast of fire in a radius of %d, doing %0.2f fire damage.
		This spell is only usable when the golem's master is dead.]], [[傀儡引爆自己，摧毀傀儡併產生一個火焰爆炸， %d 碼有效範圍內造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。 
		這個技能只有傀儡的主人死亡時能夠使用。]], "tformat")
t("Armour Configuration", "護甲掌握", "talent name")
t("Decreases", "降低", "_t")
t("Increases", "增加", "_t")
t([[The golem automatically reconfigures heavy mail and massive armours designed for living creatures to protect its own vital areas.
	%s armour value by %d, armour hardiness by %d%%, and provides %d%% critical hit reduction when wearing heavy mail or massive armour.]], [[傀儡學會重新組裝重甲和板甲，以便更加適用於傀儡。
	當裝備重甲或板甲時， %s護甲強度 %d 點 , 護甲韌性 %d%% ，並且減少 %d%% 暴擊傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Poison Breath", "毒性吐息", "talent name")
t("@Source@ breathes poison!", "@Source@呼出毒素！", "_t")
t([[Breathe poison on your foes, doing %d damage over a few turns.
		The damage will increase with your Magic.]], " 對你的敵人噴吐毒霧，在幾個回合內造成 %d 點傷害。傷害受魔力值加成。", "tformat")


