section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/golemancy.lua"

t("Golem has no master", "傀儡沒有主人", "_t")
t("Master must know the Gem Golem talent", "主人必須擁有寶石傀儡技能", "_t")
t("impossible to use this gem", "無法使用該寶石", "_t")
t("Master's Gem Golem talent too low for this gem", "主人寶石傀儡等級過低，無法使用該寶石", "_t")
t("Your golem is out of sight; you cannot establish direct control.", "你的傀儡在視線外，你無法直接控制它。", "logPlayer")
t("drolem", "龍傀儡", "_t")
t("Interact with the Golem", "檢查傀儡", "talent name")
t([[Interact with your golem to check its inventory, talents, ...
		Note: You can also do that while taking direct control of the golem.]], "和你的傀儡交互，檢查它的物品、技能等。", "tformat")
t("Refit Golem", "改裝傀儡", "talent name")
t("Golem", "傀儡", "_t")
t("%s (servant of %s)", "%s (%s的僕人)", "tformat")
t("refitted", "配置了", "_t")
t("refitting", "正在配置", "_t")
t("You have been interrupted!", "你被打斷！", "logPlayer")
t("You need to ready 2 alchemist gems in your quiver to heal your golem.", "你至少在你的彈藥欄內裝備2枚鍊金寶石，才能夠修理你的傀儡。", "logPlayer")
t("You need to ready 15 alchemist gems in your quiver to heal your golem.", "你至少在你的彈藥欄內裝備15枚鍊金寶石，才能夠修理你的傀儡。", "logPlayer")
t("Not enough space to refit!", "沒有足夠的空間改裝！", "logPlayer")
t([[Take care of your golem:
		- If it is destroyed, you will take some time to reconstruct it (this takes 15 alchemist gems and 20 turns).
		- If it is alive but hurt, you will be able to repair it for %d (takes 2 alchemist gems). Spellpower, alchemist gem and Golem Power talent all influence the healing done.]], [[與你的傀儡進行交互： 
		- 如果它被摧毀，你將耗費一些時間重新安裝傀儡（需要 15 個鍊金寶石）。 
		- 如果它還存活，你可以修整它使其恢復 %d 生命值。（耗費 2 個鍊金寶石）。法術強度、鍊金寶石和強化傀儡技能都會影響治療量。]], "tformat")
t("Golem Power", "強化傀儡", "talent name")
t("Improves your golem's proficiency with weapons, increasing its attack and damage.", "提高傀儡的武器熟練度，增加其命中和傷害。", "_t")
t("Improves your golem's proficiency with weapons, increasing its Accuracy by %d, Physical Power by %d and damage by %d%%.", "提高傀儡的武器熟練度，增加它 %d 點命中、 %d 物理強度和 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")
t("Golem Resilience", "堅韌傀儡", "talent name")
t("Improves your golem's armour training, damage resistance, and healing efficiency.", "提高傀儡護甲熟練度、傷害抵抗和治療係數。", "_t")
t([[Improves your golem's armour training, damage resistance, and healing efficiency.
		Increases all damage resistance by %d%%; increases Armour value by %d, Armour hardiness by %d%%, reduces chance to be critically hit by %d%% when wearing heavy mail or massive plate armour, and increases healing factor by %d%%.
		The golem can always use any kind of armour, including massive armours.]], [[提高傀儡護甲熟練度、傷害抵抗和治療係數。
		增加 %d%% 所有傷害抵抗；增加 %d 點護甲和 %d%% 護甲韌性；當裝備 1 件鎖甲或板甲時，減少 %d%% 被暴擊率；增加 %d%% 治療效果。 
		傀儡可以使用所有類型的護甲，包括板甲。]], "tformat")
t("Invoke Golem", "傀儡召返", "talent name")
t("Not enough space to invoke!", "沒有足夠的空間召喚！", "logPlayer")
t("You invoke your golem to your side, granting it a temporary melee power increase of %d for 5 turns.", "你將傀儡拉到你身邊，使它暫時性增加 %d 點近戰物理強度，持續 5 回合。", "tformat")
t("Golem Portal", "傀儡傳送", "talent name")
t("Your golem is currently inactive.", "你的傀儡當前尚未被激活。", "logPlayer")
t("#Target# focuses on #Source#.", "#Target# 將注意力集中到 #Source#。", "logCombat")
t("Teleport to your golem, while your golem teleports to your location. Your foes will be confused, and those that were attacking you will have a %d%% chance to target your golem instead.", [[使用此技能後，你和傀儡將會交換位置。 
		你的敵人會被混亂，那些之前攻擊你的敵人將有 %d%% 概率轉而攻擊傀儡。]], "tformat")


