section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/grave.lua"

t("Black Ice", "黑冰", "talent name")
t([[Summon an icy spike directly on a foe, impaling it for %0.2f cold damage.
		At level 5 it hits all foes in range 1 around the target.
		Any creature hit will take %d%% more damage from your necrotic minions for 3 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚冰刺刺穿敵人，造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		技能等級 5 時，冰刺會擊中目標周圍 1 碼範圍內的所有敵人。
		在接下來的 3 回合內，你的死靈隨從對冰刺擊中的敵人造成額外 %d%% 傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Chill of the Tomb", "極寒墳墓", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a bolt of cold that moves toward the target and explodes into a chilly circle of death, doing %0.2f cold damage in a radius of %d.
		Necrotic minions caught in the blast do not take damage but are instead coated with a thin layer of ice, reducing all damage they take by %d for 4 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[發射出一團極寒的冰球，在目標位置爆炸，在 %d 碼範圍內造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		被爆炸擊中的死靈隨從不會受到傷害，而是被一層厚冰覆蓋， 4 回合內受到的傷害減少 %d 點。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {2,1,3})
t("Corpselight", "陰燃鬼火", "talent name")
t([[You summon a corpselight that radiates cold for 7 turns in radius %d.
		Every turn all foes inside take %0.2f cold damage.
		Anytime you cast a spell inside your corpselight's area it grows by one stack, each stack giving +1 radius and +10%% damage.
		The corpselight can gain at most %d stacks and the radius will never extend beyond 10.
		If cast while under 1 life it spawns with 3 stacks.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你召喚一個半徑爲 %d 的鬼火，散發出刺骨的屍寒，持續 7 回合。
		在每個回合內，每個被鬼火覆蓋的敵人會受到 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		每當你在鬼火的範圍內施放法術，它會強化一層，每一層增長半徑 1，傷害增加 10%% 。
		鬼火最多可以疊加強化 %d 層，且半徑最大爲 10 。
		如果在生命值爲 1 以下時使用技能，鬼火初始強度爲 3 層。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Grave Mistake", "墓光之災", "talent name")
t("#STEEL_BLUE#The corpselight implodes!", "#STEEL_BLUE#鬼火爆炸了!", "logSeen")
t([[Upon expiring the corpselight implodes, pulling in all foes towards its center and dealing %0.2f cold damage.
		The damage is increased by +10%% per stack.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.

		#PURPLE#Learning this spell will make Corpselight cost two souls to use instead of one.]], [[你的鬼火消失時會發生爆炸，將所有敵人拖向中心位置，並造成 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		鬼火每疊加一層，傷害增加 10%% 。
		傷害受法術強度加成。

		#PURPLE#學習這一技能會把你陰燃鬼火消耗的靈魂數量從 1 增加到 2 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/ice.lua"

t("Freeze", "凍結", "talent name")
t([[Condenses ambient water on a target, freezing it for %d turns and damaging it for %0.2f.
		If this is used on a friendly target the cooldown is reduced by 33%%.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[凝聚周圍的水凍結目標 %d 回合並對其造成 %0.2f 傷害。 
		如果目標爲友好生物，冷卻時間減少 33%% 。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Frozen Ground", "凍結大地", "talent name")
t([[Blast a wave of cold all around you with a radius of %d, doing %0.2f cold damage and freezing creatures to the ground for 4 turns.
		Affected creatures can still act, but cannot move.
		For each affected creature that is also wet the cooldown of Shatter decreases by 2.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[製造一股冷空氣圍繞着你，在 %d 碼半徑範圍內對目標造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害並凍結它們的雙腳 4 回合。 
		被凍結雙腳的單位可以動作但無法移動。 
		該技能每擊中一個處於溼潤狀態的目標，將會減少寒冰破碎的技能冷卻時間 2 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shatter", "寒冰破碎", "talent name")
t("%s shatters!", "%s 粉碎了！", "logSeen")
t([[Shatter all frozen targets in your line of sight, doing %0.2f cold damage.
		Depending on the target's rank, there will also be an additional effect:
		* Critters will be instantly killed
		* +50%% critical chance against Normal rank
		* +25%% critical chance against Elites or Bosses
		All affected foes will get the wet effect.
		At most, it will affect %d foes.
		If you are yourself Frozen, it will instantly be destroyed.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[打破視線範圍內所有已凍結目標，造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害。 
		基於目標品級，有額外效果： 
		* 動物類會被立刻殺死 
		* 對普通單位增加 50%% 暴擊率 
		* 對精英單位增加 25%% 暴擊率 
		所有受影響單位將進入溼潤狀態。
		它最多可影響 %d 個敵方單位。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Uttercold", "絕對零度", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with Uttercold, increasing all your cold damage by %0.1f%% and ignoring %d%% cold resistance of your targets
		In addition you pierce through iceblocks easily, reducing damage absorbed from your attacks by iceblocks by %d%%.]], [[使你周圍的溫度驟降，增加你 %0.1f%% 冰系傷害並無視目標 %d%% 冰冷抵抗。 
		同時，你的破冰動作變的更加容易，減少 %d%% 冰層對你的攻擊傷害格擋值。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/master-necromancer.lua"

t("Aura of Undeath", "不死光環", "talent name")
t([[Your mastery of necromancy becomes so total that an aura of undeath radiates around you in radius %d.
		Any undead minion standing inside of it is protected, increasing all their resistances by %d%%.
		In addition when you create new minions they inherit %d%% of your spellpower (applied to any powers), spell crit chance (applied to any crit chances), saves, resists and damage increases (applied to all elements).
		]], [[你對死靈法術的掌握是如此強大，你可以在周圍 %d 碼範圍內放射出不死能量的光環。
		所有在光環內的不死隨從會被光環保護，增加 %d%% 全體傷害抗性。
		另外，當你創造不死隨從的時候，它們會繼承你 %d%% 法術強度（附加於所有強度），法術暴擊率（附加於所有暴擊率），豁免，抗性和傷害加成效果（附加於所有傷害加成）。
		]], "tformat")
t("Surge of Undeath", "不死狂潮", "talent name")
t([[Sends out a surge of undeath energies into your aura.
		All minions inside gain 25%% speed for %d turns
		All non-ghoul minions are healed by %d%%.
		If you know Call of the Mausoleum, the time remaining to the next free ghoul is reduced by %d.
		if you know Corpse Explosion or Putrescent Liquefaction the duration of those effects are increased by %d.
		All non-undead foes caught inside are dazed for %d turns.]], [[在你的光環中放出一股不死能量。
		所有隨從獲得 25%% 速度，持續 %d 回合。
		所有非食屍鬼的隨從被治療 %d%% 。
		如果你掌握陵墓召喚技能，到下一個免費食屍鬼的時間降低 %d 。
		如果你掌握奪命屍爆或腐爛液化技能，這些效果的持續時間延長 %d 。
		所有非不死生物的敵人都會被眩暈 %d 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Recall Minions", "召回隨從", "talent name")
t([[Tighten the ethereal leash to some of your minions currently within your aura of undeath, pulling them to you and swapping place with any eventual foes in the way.
		Up to %d minions are affected.
		When recalling a minion the spell tries to prioritize a spot where there is already a foe, to push it away.]], [[拉緊你與不死光環內的死靈隨從的虛幻連接，將它們拉到你的身邊，並與路徑上的敵人換位。
		最多召回 %d 個隨從。
		當你召回隨從的時候，會優先選擇周圍有敵人的格子，將敵人推開。]], "tformat")
t("Suffer For Me", "替死鬼", "talent name")
t("#GREY#(%d to minion: %s)#LAST#", "#GREY#(%d 到不死隨從: %s)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[By creating an arcane link with your minion army you are able to redirect parts of any damage affecting you to them.
		Anytime you take damage %d%% of it is instead redirected to a random minion without your aura of undeath.
		The minion takes 300%% damage from that effect.
		The damage redirected percent depends on your Spellpower.]], [[你與你的不死大軍之間建立奧術連接，將你所收到的任何傷害轉移到他們的身上。
		每當你受到傷害的時候， %d%% 的傷害轉移到到隨機一個不死光環內的隨從身上。
		那個隨從將會受到 3 倍傷害。
		傷害轉移比例受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/master-of-bones.lua"

t("Call of the Crypt", "墓穴召喚", "talent name")
t([[Call upon the battlefields of old, collecting bones, fusing them with souls, and forging them into skeletal minions.
		Up to %d skeleton warriors of level %d are summoned, and up to %d skeletons can be controlled at once.
		At level 3 the summons become armoured skeletons warriors.
		At level 5, for every 3 skeleton warriors, a skeleton mage or archer will also be created without costing any souls. If this makes you go over your skeleton limit, a normal skeleton will be removed and its soul refunded.

		#GREY##{italic}#Skeleton minions come in fewer numbers than ghoul minions but are generally more durable.#{normal}#
		]], [[從古戰場中收集白骨，將靈魂附着在白骨上，將其轉化爲你的骷髏隨從。
		使用技能將會召喚 %d 個等級 %d 的骷髏戰士。最多同時掌控 %d 個骷髏戰士。
		技能等級 3 時，你將會改爲召喚武裝骷髏戰士。
		技能等級 5 時，每當你召喚 3 個骷髏戰士，將會額外召喚一個骷髏法師或骷髏弓箭手，不消耗靈魂。如果這超過了你的骷髏數量上限，會移除一個普通骷髏，並返還其靈魂消耗。

		#GREY##{italic}#骷髏的數量一般來說比食屍鬼更少，但是它們一般來說更加強韌。#{normal}#
		]], "tformat")
t("Shattered Remains", "粉碎骸骨", "talent name")
t("#GREY#%s shatters!", "#GREY#%s 粉碎了！", "logSeen")
t([[Any time one of your skeleton or bone giant dies, it shatters in radius %d, making any foe bleed for %0.2f physical damage over 5 turns.
		If any other skeleton or bone giant minion is in the radius it will pickup some of the bones to enhance itself, increasing maximum and current life by %d, armour by %d and gain %0.2f physical melee retaliation for 20 turns.
		This talent never works when you kill your own minions.
		]], [[每當你的骷髏或骨巨人死去時，它會在半徑 %d 碼範圍內粉碎，使敵人受到 %0.2f 物理流血傷害，持續 5 回合。
		如果範圍內有其他骷髏或骨巨人，它們會使用這些骸骨強化自己，增加最大和當前生命值 %d ，護甲值 %d ，並獲得 %0.2f 物理近戰報復效果，持續 20 回合。
		如果你殺死自己的隨從，這一效果不會觸發。
		]], "tformat")
t("Assemble", "亡靈組合", "talent name")
t("A towering creature, made from the bones of dozens of dead bodies. It is covered by an unholy aura.", "像鐵塔一樣的生物，由數不清的骨頭構成。它全身圍繞着邪惡的氣息。", "_t")
t("A towering creature, made from the bones of hundreds of dead bodies. It is covered by an unholy aura.", "像鐵塔一樣的生物，由數不清的骨頭構成。它全身圍繞着邪惡的氣息。", "_t")
t([[Every army of undead minions needs its spearhead. To that end you combine 3 skeleton minions into a bone giant of level %d.
		The minions used are selected from the weakest first, and a Lord of Skulls will never be used. 
		At level 3 an eternal bone giant is created instead.
		At level 6 a heavy bone giant is created instead.
		Only one bone giant may be active, and casting this spell while one already exists will destroy it and create a new one.
		]], [[任何亡靈軍隊需要領袖。爲此，你將 3 個骷髏隨從合成成一個等級爲 %d 的骨巨人。
		優先選擇最弱的不死隨從，且不會使用骷髏王作爲合成材料。
		在等級 3 時，會改爲製造 1 個永恆骨巨人。 
		在等級 6 時，會改爲製造 1 個重型骨巨人。 
		任何時候最多隻能有一個骨巨人，如果你在有骨巨人的時候使用這一技能，會摧毀原有的骨巨人，並用新的骨巨人取代它。
		]], "tformat")
t("Lord of Skulls", "骷髏之王", "talent name")
t([[Consume a soul to empower one of your skeleton, making it into a Lord of Skulls.
		The Lord of Skulls gains %d more life and is instantly healed to full.
		There can be only one active Lord of Skulls, casting this spell on another skeleton removes the effect from the current one.
		It also gains a new talent if high enough:
		At level 2 Warriors learn Giant Leap, a powerful jump attack that deals damage and dazes on impact and frees the skeleton from any stun, daze and pin effects they may have
		At level 3 Archers learn Vital Shot, a devastating attack that can stun and cripple their foes
		At level 5 Mages learn Meteoric Crash, a destructive spell that crushes and burns foes in a big radius for multiple turns and stuns them
		At level 6 Bone Giants learn You Shall Be My Weapon!, a massive attack that deals high damage, knockbacks foes and stuns them
		]], [[消耗一個靈魂，強化你的一個骷髏，使其成爲骷髏王。
		骷髏王具有 %d 額外生命值，且生命值立刻恢復到滿。
		同時只能存在一個骷髏王，在其他骷髏身上使用這個技能會消除掉原有骷髏王的效果。
		技能等級足夠高時，骷髏王獲得額外技能：
		- 等級2時，戰士將學會戰爭踐踏，一個強大的跳躍攻擊，可以造成傷害，眩暈敵人，並解除自身的眩暈、定身和震懾效果。
		- 等級3時，弓箭手將學會要害射擊，一個毀滅性的射擊攻擊，可以震懾和殘廢敵人。
		- 等級5時，法師將學會落星，一個強大的法術，可以壓碎敵人，並在大範圍內造成多回合的持續傷害。
		- 等級6時，骨巨人將學會化作星星吧！！，一個強力的攻擊，可以造成高額傷害，擊退並震懾敵人。
		]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/master-of-flesh.lua"

t("Call of the Mausoleum", "陵墓召喚", "talent name")
t("\
#DARK_SEA_GREEN#Next free ghoul in %d turn(s).\
#LAST#", "\
#DARK_SEA_GREEN#下一個免費食屍鬼在 %d 回合後出現。\
#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[You control dead matter around you, lyring in the ground, decaying.
		When you enter combat and every %d turns thereafter a ghoul of level %d automatically raises to fight for you.
		At level 3 you can forcefully activate this spell to summon up to %d ghasts around you.
		At level 5 every 4 summoned ghouls or ghasts a ghoulking is summoned for free.
		Ghouls, ghasts and ghoulkings last for %d turns.
		%s
		#GREY##{italic}#Ghoul minions come in larger numbers than skeleton minions but are generally more frail and disposable.#{normal}#
		]], [[你操控大地上的死亡血肉，讓其腐爛。
		你進入戰鬥時，以及之後每隔 %d 個回合，將會自動召喚一個等級 %d 的食屍鬼來爲你而戰。
		技能等級 3 時，你可以主動激活該技能，在身邊召喚最多 %d 個妖鬼。
		技能等級 5 時，你每召喚 4 個食屍鬼或妖鬼，將會額外召喚一個食屍鬼王。
		食屍鬼，妖鬼和食屍鬼王持續 %d 個回合。
		%s
		#GREY##{italic}#食屍鬼通常數量比骷髏更多，但是它們是相對更加脆弱，容易被擊倒的消耗品。#{normal}#
		]], "tformat")
t("Corpse Explosion", "奪命屍爆", "talent name")
t([[Ghouls are nothing but mere tools to you, for %d turns you render them bloated with dark forces.
		Anytime a ghoul or ghast is hit it will explode in a messy splash of gore, dealing %0.2f frostdusk damage to all foes in radius %d of it.
		Any creature caught in the blast also receives a random disease that deals %0.2f blight damage over 6 turns and reduces one attribute by %d.
		Only one ghoul may explode per turn. The one with the least time left to live is always the first to do so.
		The damage and disease power is increased by your Spellpower.
		]], [[對你來說，食屍鬼只是可以隨地丟棄的工具。在 %d 回合內，你讓它們的體內充滿黑暗的能量。
		在此期間，每當一個食屍鬼或妖鬼被擊中，它會爆炸成爲一團碎肉，對 %d 碼範圍的所有敵人造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害。
		所有被爆炸擊中的敵人也會感染持續 6 回合的隨機疾病，某一項屬性值降低 %d 點，並且每回合受到 %0.2f 枯萎傷害。
		每回合內最多隻能有一個食屍鬼爆炸。你會優先讓剩餘時間最短的食屍鬼爆炸。
		傷害和疾病強度受法術強度加成。
		]], "tformat", {1,3,2,5,4})
t("Putrescent Liquefaction", "腐爛液化", "talent name")
t("#GREY#%s dissolves into the cloud of gore.", "#GREY#%s化爲一團血肉的雲霧。", "logSeen")
t([[Shattering up to %d ghouls or ghasts you create a putrescent swirling cloud of radius %d that follows you around for 3 turns per dead ghoul plus one turn. Oldest ghouls are prioritized for destruction.
		Any ghoul or ghast dying or expiring within this cloud increases its duration by %d turn and every two absorbed ghoul/ghast your gain back one soul.
		The cloud deals %0.2f frostdusk damage to any foes caught inside.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.
		]], [[你粉碎最多 %d 個食屍鬼或妖鬼，在身邊創造出半徑 %d 碼的腐敗雲霧，持續時間爲殺死的食屍鬼數量乘 3 再加一回合。你會優先選擇最老的食屍鬼。
		每個在雲霧中死去的食屍鬼或妖鬼會增加它的持續時間 %d 回合，每死亡2個食屍鬼或妖鬼會恢復1點靈魂。
		雲霧會對其中的所有敵人造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。
		]], "tformat")
t("Discarded Refuse", "李代桃僵", "talent name")
t("%s sacrifices a ghoul to avoid being affected by %s!", "%s犧牲了一個食屍鬼，避免了陷入%s狀態！", "logSeen")
t([[Whenever you would be affected by a detrimental physical effect you instead transfer it instantly to one of your ghouls.
		The ghoul dies from the process.
		While under 1 life it also affects magical and mental effects.
		At most %d effects can be affected per turn.
		Cross-tier effects are never affected.]], [[當你即將受到一個物理負面效果時，你自動將其轉移到你的食屍鬼身上。
		這一食屍鬼會在這個過程中立刻死亡。
		當你的生命值低於 1 時，你也會轉移魔法和精神負面效果。
		每回合最多轉移 %d 個效果。
		不會轉移越層負面效果（失去平衡，法術衝擊和思維封鎖）。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/meta.lua"

t("Disperse Magic", "驅散", "talent name")
t([[Removes up to %d magical effects (good effects from foes, and bad effects from friends) from the target.
		At level 3, it can be targeted.
		]], [[驅散目標身上的 %d 種魔法效果（敵方單位的增益狀態和友方單位的負面狀態）。 
		在等級 3 時可以選擇目標。]], "tformat")
t("Spellcraft", "法術親和", "talent name")
t([[You learn to finely craft and tune your spells, reducing all their cooldowns by %d%%.
		In doing so you can also carve a hole in spells that affect an area to avoid damaging yourself.  The chance of success is %d%%.
		In addition, you hone your damaging spells to spellshock their targets. Whenever you deal damage with a spell you attempt to spellshock them with %d more Spellpower than normal. Spellshocked targets suffer a temporary 20%% penalty to damage resistances.]], [[你學會巧妙控制和調諧你的法術，降低 %d%% 法術冷卻時間。
		此外，你可以控制自己的攻擊性魔法，嘗試在攻擊範圍中留出空隙，避免傷及自身。成功概率爲 %d%% 。 
		如果你的法術強度等級超過目標法術豁免等級，你的攻擊法術將會對目標產生法術衝擊。此技能將會在判定目標是否會被你法術衝擊，使用法術強度對抗敵人法術豁免的時候，使這一判定獲得 %d 額外法術強度加成。被法術衝擊目標暫時減少 20%% 傷害抗性。]], "tformat")
t("Energy Alteration", "能量轉化", "talent name")
t([[Your mastery over magic is so great that you can alter the energy of all damaging spells to suit your needs.
		Whenever you deal damage with a spell you attune to the element of that spell for 6 turns, converting %d%% of any damage you deal into that element.
		This effect will not override itself and will only trigger from spells directly cast by you, not from damage over time or ground damage effects.]], [[你對魔法的掌握是如此精巧，你可以調節任何傷害技能的能量，來爲你所用。
		每當你使用法術造成傷害的時候，你將法術調諧到這一元素，持續 6 回合，你造成的所有傷害中的 %d%% 將會轉化爲該元素。
		這一效果不會覆蓋自身，只會被你直接釋放的技能觸發，不會因持續傷害或地面傷害效果而觸發。]], "tformat")
t("Metaflow", "奧術流動", "talent name")
t([[Your mastery of arcane flows allow you to reset the cooldown of up to %d of your spells (that don't have a fixed cooldown) of tier %d or less.
		In addition for %d turns you are overflowing with energy; all known spells are considered one talent level higher when casting them.]], [[你對奧術的精通使你能重置法術的冷卻時間，重置至多 %d 個法術的冷卻（對固定冷卻時間的技能無效），對技能層次 %d 或更低的技能有效。
		此外，在接下來的 %d 回合內，你充滿能量，釋放法術的時候，技能等級視爲額外增加 1 級]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/necrosis.lua"

t("Blurred Mortality", "模糊死亡", "talent name")
t([[The line between life and death blurs for you.
		You can only die when you reach -%d life but your maximum life is reduced by %d.
		When you are below 1 life you gain %d%% to all resistances.
		The life amount is based on your Constitution attribute.]], [[對你來說，生命和死亡的界線開始變得模糊。
		只有生命值到達 -%d 時你纔會死亡，同時你的最大生命值降低了 %d 。
		當你的生命值低於 1 時，獲得 %d%% 全體傷害抗性。
		生命值變化受體質值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Across the Veil", "穿越死亡", "talent name")
t("#GREY#%s unleashes a blast of frostdusk as %s crosses the veil!", "#GREY#%s穿越死亡邊緣，在%s身邊放出了一股霜暮爆炸！", "logSeen")
t([[As you learn to tiptoe across the veil of death you learn to master the dark forces.
		Each time you cross the 1 life threshold you automatically unleash a blast of %0.2f frostdusk damage in radius %d.
		For each creature that takes damage from the blast one of your talent's cooldown is reduced by %d turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你對黑暗能量的掌握，讓你學會了在死亡的邊緣起舞。
		無論是受到傷害還是被治療，每當你的生命值穿越 1 的界線的時候，你會自動在周圍 %d 碼範圍內放出爆炸，造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害，
		這一爆炸每對一個敵人造成傷害，你的一個隨機技能的冷卻時間降低 %d 回合。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {2,1,3})
t("Runeskin", "符文皮膚", "talent name")
t("effects disabled because of an infusion", "由於紋身，效果被禁用", "_t")
t("effects disabled because of no rune", "由於沒有符文，效果被禁用", "_t")
t("%d runes active", "有 %d 個符文", "tformat")
t([[As you continue to attune your body to undeath you reject nature as a whole.
		As long as you have no natural infusion on your skin, each rune on it increases your minimum negative life by -%d and your spells critical chance by %0.1f%%.

		Currently: %s]], [[你拒絕自然，讓自己的身體離不死越來越近。
		如果沒有自然紋身，你身上的每個符文提供 -%d 生命底線和 %0.1f%% 法術暴擊率。

		當前: %s]], "tformat")
t("Spikes of Decrepitude", "破碎尖刺", "talent name")
t([[Each turn you unleash dark powers through your runeskin.
		For each rune you have a random foe in sight will be hit by a spike of decrepitude, dealing %0.2f frostdusk damage.
		A foe can only be hit by one spike per turn.
		If your life is below 1, the spikes also reduce all damage done by the targets by %d%%.]], [[你每回合都從符文皮膚中釋放出黑暗能量。
		你每擁有一個符文，就會用破碎尖刺攻擊視野內的一名隨機敵人，造成 %0.2f 霜暮傷害。
		每個敵人每回合只會被尖刺攻擊一次。
		如果你的生命值在 1 以下，尖刺還會使目標造成的傷害減少 %d%% 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/nightfall.lua"

t("Invoke Darkness", "黑夜降臨", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a beam of darkness, doing %0.2f darkness damage.
		At level 5, the beam widens to hit foes on each side.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[發射出黑暗的射線，對目標造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		技能等級 5 時，射線會變寬，可以擊中兩側的目標。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Night Sphere", "暗夜籠罩", "talent name")
t([[Dark fumes erupt from the ground in radius %d for 5 turns. Any creature entering the circle will receive either a bane of confusion or a bane of blindness.
		Only one bane can affect a creature.
		Banes last for %d turns, and also deal %0.2f darkness damage.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[黑暗之霧籠罩 %d 碼範圍的地面 5 回合。任何生物走進去都會受到混亂災禍或致盲災禍的影響。
		同一個生物同時只會被一種災禍效果影響。 
		災禍效果持續 %d 回合，造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Erupting Shadows", "暗影噴發", "talent name")
t([[Shadows engulf your foes, anytime you deal darkness damage to a creature affected by a bane, the bane's duration is increased by 1 turn and the shadows erupt, dealing an additional %0.2f darkness damage.
		The damage can only happen once per turn per creature, the turn increase however always happens.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[暗影吞噬你的敵人。每當你對災禍影響下的敵人造成暗影傷害時，災禍會被延長 1 回合，並且觸發一次暗影噴發，造成 %0.2f 額外暗影傷害。
		每回合對同一個生物最多觸發一次傷害，但持續時間可以被延長任意多次。
		傷害受法術強度提升。]], "tformat")
t("River of Souls", "靈魂之河", "talent name")
t([[You summon a river of tortured souls to launch an onslaught of darkness against your foes.
		Every turn for 5 turns you launch a projectile towards the designated area that explodes in radius %d, dealing %0.2f darkness damage.
		Each projectile consumes a soul and the spell ends when it has sent 5 projectiles or when you have no more souls to use.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你召喚冥河中受折磨的靈魂，對敵人發起暗夜強襲。
		接下來 5 回合裏，每回合向目標區域發射一個靈魂，產生 %d 碼範圍的爆炸，造成 %0.2f 暗影傷害。
		每次發射會消耗一個靈魂；累計發射 5 個靈魂，或者沒有剩餘靈魂的時候，法術會結束。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/phantasm.lua"

t("Illuminate", "照明術", "talent name")
t([[Creates a globe of pure light within a radius of %d that illuminates the area and deals %0.2f damage to all creatures.
		At level 3, it also blinds all who see it (except the caster) for %d turns.]], [[製造一個發光的球體，照亮 %d 碼半徑範圍區域，並對所有生物造成 %0.2f 點光系傷害。
		在等級 3 時，它同時可以致盲看到它的人（施法者除外） %d 回合。 ]], "tformat")
t("Phantasmal Shield", "幻象護盾", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with a phantasmal shield of pure light.
		Whenever you would take damage there is %d%% chance to become ethereal for an instant and fully ignore it.
		If you do get hit, the shield glows brightly, sending triggering a flash of light on the attacker, dealing %0.2f light damage in radius %d around it and dazzling any affected creature (deal 10%% less damage) for 5 turns. This can only happen every %d turns.
		The damage and ignore chance will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[使用純淨的光構成幻象護盾，保護你自己。
		每當你受到傷害時，你有 %d%% 的機率瞬間變得虛無，完全無視這一傷害。
		如果你觸發了這一效果，護盾會向攻擊你的敵人發出明亮的閃光，在其周圍 %d 碼範圍內造成 %0.2f 光系傷害，並炫目所有受到傷害的敵人（減少 10%% 的傷害），持續 5 回合。這一效果最多每 %d 回合觸發一次。
		光系傷害和無視傷害機率受法術強度加成。]], "tformat", {1,3,2,4})
t("Invisibility", "隱形", "talent name")
t([[Weave a net of arcane disturbances around your body, removing yourself from the sight of all, granting %d bonus to invisibility for 7 turns.
		While invisible all damage you deal against blinded or dazzled foes is increased by %d%% (additive with other damage increases).
		The invisibility bonus will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你在身體周圍編織一個奧術能量的干擾網，讓你消失在敵人的視野中，獲得 %d 強度的隱形效果，持續 7 回合。
		當隱形時，你對致盲或炫目的敵人造成的傷害增加 %d%% （與其他傷害加成效果加法疊加）
		隱形強度隨法術強度提升。]], "tformat")
t("Mirror Image", "鏡像", "talent name")
t("You cannot summon; you are suppressed!", "你不能召喚，你被壓制了！", "logPlayer")
t("Mirror Image (%s)", "鏡像 (%s)", "tformat")
t("A blurred image.", "一個模糊的鏡像。", "_t")
t("Summon", "召喚", "_t")
t([[Create a perfect lookalike of your own form made out of pure light near a creature.
		This image has %d life and can never take more than 1 damage per creature per turn and is immune to any non direct damage (ground effects, damage over time, ...).
		Whenever you cast a spell your mirror image will try to duplicate it at the same target for 66%% less damage, if possible. If it can it will loose 1 life, if not it will instead taunt a creature to focus its attention on itself.
		While the image exists you receive the damage bonus from the Invisibility spell as if you were invisible.
		This spell can not be cast while a Mirror Image already exists and only in combat. It will disappear after a few turn when outside of combat.
		]], [[在某個生物的身旁，召喚一個由純粹的光線構成的，與你完全相似的完美複製體。
		這一鏡像具有 %d 生命值，每回合從每個生物身上最多受到 1 點傷害，且免疫任何非直接傷害（地面效果，持續傷害，等等）
		當你釋放任何法術的時候，鏡像也會試圖對同一目標釋放這一法術，造成的傷害降低 66%% 。如果它這麼做了，它會流失 1 點生命值。如果不能的話，它則會嘲諷一個生物，將它的注意力集中在自己身上。
		只要鏡像持續存在在戰場上，你就會獲得隱形技能所基於的隱形傷害加成，無論你是否隱形。
		這一技能無法在場上已經有鏡像的時候釋放，且只能在戰鬥中釋放。鏡像在脫戰後快速消失。
		]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/rime-wraith.lua"

t("Rime Wraith", "遠古冰魂", "talent name")
t([[You summon a Rime Wraith inside of you, an intangible creature, that haunts both foes and allies for %d turns.
		Every turn the wraith will select a new target and jump to it.
		When the wraith enters a creature they are covered in hoarfrost for 3 turns:
		- if friendly: increases cold resistance by %d%%, converts all damage done to cold and increases cold damage by %d%%.
		- if hostile: reduces cold resistance by %d%% and move %d%% slower
		When selecting a target the wraith prefers one that is not affected by hoarfrost if possible.
		]], [[你在體內召喚遠古冰魂，這是一種無形的生物，可以對敵人和盟友造成影響，持續 %d 回合。
		每一回合，冰魂會選擇一個新的目標，然後跳向那個目標。
		當冰魂進入一個生物體內，那個生物將會被寒霜覆蓋，持續 3 回合。
		- 友方目標：獲得 %d%% 寒冷傷害抗性，所造成的所有傷害轉化成寒冷傷害，增加寒冷傷害 %d%% 。
		- 敵對目標：降低 %d%% 寒冷傷害抗性，移動速度降低 %d%% 。
		冰魂會優先選擇沒有被寒霜覆蓋的目標。
		]], "tformat")
t("Frigid Plunge", "寒流涌動", "talent name")
t([[When switching targets your rime wraith now always prefers the one farther away if possible.
		Any creatures on the path of the wraith while it travels are affected:
		- if friendly: they are healed for %d
		- if hostile: they take %0.2f cold damage, because the wraith is inside the creature the damage fully ignores any damage shield
		The damage and healing will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[當冰魂選擇目標的時候，它會優先選擇儘可能遠的目標。
		在冰魂轉移的時候，所有在路徑上的生物將會受到以下影響：
		- 友方目標：治療 %d 生命值
		- 敵對目標：受到 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。因爲冰魂在敵人體內，這一效果穿透傷害護盾。
		傷害和治療效果受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Gelid Host", "霜寒宿主", "talent name")
t([[By crushing one more soul you reinforce your existing rime wraith, duplicating it out of its current host.
		The new wraith will exist for %d turns and cannot be used for another cast of Gelid Host.
		When it is created the current host and all foes in radius %d are blasted for %0.2f cold damage.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你粉碎一個靈魂，強化你當前的冰魂，將其從當前的宿主身上覆製出來。
		複製的新冰魂持續 %d 回合，不能被再次複製。
		當新冰魂創建後，其原來的宿主和周圍 %d 碼範圍內的所有敵人會受到 %0.2f 寒冷傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Permafrost", "永凍極寒", "talent name")
t([[Hoarfrost now has additional effects:
		- if friendly: magical and physical saves increased by %d, at level 5 healing factor is also increased by 15%%.
		- if hostile: magical and physical saves reduced by %d, at level 5 all talents cool down 15%% slower.
		]], [[寒霜覆蓋效果獲得以下額外效果：
