section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/storm.lua"

t("Nova", "閃電新星", "talent name")
t([[Lightning emanates from you in a circular wave with radius %d, doing %0.2f to %0.2f lightning damage (%0.2f average) and possibly dazing anyone affected (75%% chance).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[一圈閃電從你身上放射出來，在 %d 碼範圍內對目標造成 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 閃電傷害（平均 %0.2f ）並有 75%% 概率眩暈敵人。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shock", "閃電之擊", "talent name")
t([[Conjures up a bolt of lightning, doing %0.2f to %0.2f damage (%0.2f average) and dazing the target for 3 turns.
		If the target resists the daze effect it is instead shocked, which halves stun/daze/pin resistance, for 5 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚一個閃電球對目標造成 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 閃電傷害（平均 %0.2f ）並眩暈目標 3 回合。 
		如果目標免疫了眩暈，則 5 回合內震懾和定身抗性減半。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hurricane", "風暴之怒", "talent name")
t([[Each time one of your lightning spells dazes a target, it has a %d%% chance to creates a chain reaction that summons a mighty Hurricane that lasts for 10 turns around the target with a radius of %d.
		Each turn, the afflicted creature and all creatures around it will take %0.2f to %0.2f lightning damage (%0.2f average).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[每次你的閃電法術眩暈目標時，它會有 %d%% 的概率發生連鎖反應，生成一個圍繞目標 %d 碼半徑範圍的颶風，持續 10 回合。 
		每回合該單位附近的所有生物會承受 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 閃電傷害（平均 %0.2f ）。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Tempest", "無盡風暴", "talent name")
t([[Surround yourself with a Tempest, increasing all your lightning damage by %d%% and ignoring %d%% lightning resistance of your targets.
		Your Lightning and Chain Lightning spells also gain a %d%% chance to daze, and your Thunderstorm spell gains a %d%% chance to daze.]], [[在你周圍生成一股風暴，增加你 %d%% 閃電傷害並無視目標 %d%% 閃電抵抗。 
		你的閃電術和連鎖閃電同時會增加 %d%% 眩暈機率，並且閃電風暴也會增加 %d%% 眩暈機率。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/temporal.lua"

t("Congeal Time", "時間凝固", "talent name")
t("Project a bolt of time distortion, decreasing the target's global speed by %d%% and all projectiles it fires by %d%% for 7 turns.", "製造一個扭曲時間的力場，減少目標 %d%% 的整體速度，目標所釋放的拋射物減速 %d%% ，持續 7 回合。", "tformat")
t("Temporal Shield", "時光之盾", "talent name")
t([[This intricate spell instantly erects a time shield around the caster, preventing any incoming damage and sending it forward in time.
		Once either the maximum damage (%d) is absorbed, or the time runs out (%d turns), the stored damage will return as a temporal restoration field over time (5 turns).
		Each turn the restoration field is active, you get healed for 10%% of the absorbed damage (Aegis Shielding talent affects the percentage).
		The shield's max absorption will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[這個複雜的法術在施法者周圍立刻製造一個時間屏障，吸收你受到的傷害。 
		一旦達到最大傷害吸收值（ %d ）或持續時間（ %d 回合）結束，存儲的能量會治療你，持續 5 回合，每回合回覆總吸收傷害的 10%% ( 強化護盾技能會影響該係數 )。  
		最大吸收值受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Time Prison", "時光牢籠", "talent name")
t([[Removes the target from the flow of time for %d turns. In this state, the target can neither act nor be harmed.
		Time does not pass at all for the target, no talents will cooldown, no resources will regen, and so forth.
		The duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[將目標從時光的流動中移出，持續 %d 回合。 
		在此狀態下，目標不能動作也不能被傷害。 
		對於目標來說，時間是靜止的，技能無法冷卻，也沒有能量回復…… 
		持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Essence of Speed", "時間加速", "talent name")
t("Increases the caster's global speed by %d%%.", "增加施法者 %d%% 整體速度。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/thaumaturgy.lua"

t("Orb of Thaumaturgy", "奇術之球", "talent name")
t([[You create an orb attuned to thaumaturgy for %d turns.
		While it lasts, any beam spell you cast will be duplicated and also cast for free at the orb for %d%% of the normal damage.
		]], [[你放出一個奇術之球，持續 %d 回合。
		在這個球持續期間，你釋放的射線類法術將會被複制一次，指向奇術之球，並造成 %d%% 原傷害。
		]], "tformat")
t("Multicaster", "多重施法", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#%s [known, eligible]#LAST#", "#LIGHT_BLUE#%s [已學會, 可觸發]#LAST#", "tformat")
t("#YELLOW#%s [known]#LAST#", "#YELLOW#%s [已學會]#LAST#", "tformat")
t("#GREY#%s [unknown]#LAST#", "#GREY#%s [未學會]#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[Casting beam spells has become so instinctive for you that you can now easily weave in other spells at the same time.
		Anytime you cast a beam spell there is a %d%% chance to automatically cast an offensive spell that you know.
		Beam spells duplicated by the Orb of Thaumaturgy can also trigger this effect.
		This can only happen once (or twice with Orb of Thaumaturgy) per turn.
		The additional cast will cost mana but no turn, will not active its cooldown and can trigger on spells currently on cooldown.
		During Aether Avatar only compatible spells are used.

		Eligible spells: %s]], [[釋放射線類法術對你來說如此自然，以至於可以和其他法術穿插釋放。
        每當釋放射線類法術時，你有 %d%% 機率自動釋放一個已習得的其他攻擊類法術。
        奇術之球複製的射線類法術也能觸發這一效果。
        該效果一回合只能觸發一次（使用奇術之球可以觸發兩次），且不能觸發處於冷卻中的法術。
        額外釋放的法術仍然會消耗法力值，但不會消耗時間，也不會使該法術進入冷卻。
        以太之體狀態下，只會釋放以太之體下能釋放的技能。

        可觸發法術：%s]], "tformat")
t("Slipstream", "能量滑流", "talent name")
t("#PURPLE#Your Slipstream does not have enough resources!", "#PURPLE#你的能量滑流魔力不足了", "logPlayer")
t("#PURPLE#Your Slipstream regenerates to full!", "#PURPLE#的能量滑流充能滿了！", "logPlayer")
t([[By weaving arcane triggers around you feet you can use the residual energies of your beam spells for free movement.
		Each time you cast a beam spell you can move right afterwards without spending a turn.
		This spell has %d charges. Once all charges are spent it unsustains.
		If you exit combat with some charges left it will after 10 turn regenerates its charges, if you have enough mana.]], [[你將奧術力量編織於雙腳，可以使用射線類法術來進行免費移動。
		每當你釋放一個射線類法術，你可以立刻移動一次，不需要消耗時間。
		這一法術有 %d 次充能。當充能耗盡時，這一法術將會解除持續。
		脫離戰鬥10 回合內將會消耗法力值補充充能。]], "tformat")
t("Elemental Array Burst", "元素陣爆發", "talent name")
t([[Using your near-perfect knowledge of beam spells you combine them all into a powerful 3-wide beam of pure energy.
		The beam deals %0.2f thaumic damage and always goes as far as possible.
		Thaumic damage can never be resisted by anything but "Resistance: All", always uses your highest resistance penetration and highest damage type bonus and can never be altered into other damage types.
		It can trigger Burning Wake and Hurricane.
		It is affected by the wet status (+30%% damage) if you are in Shivgoroth Form.
		It has a 25%% chance to either stun or freeze the targets for 3 turns (if Crystalline Focus or Uttercold are active, respectively).
		Each time you deal damage with a beam spell, the remaining cooldown is reduced by 1 (this can happen only once per turn).
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的射線類法術已臻化境，可以將各種元素合併起來，發射出純粹能量構成，寬度爲3的強力射線。
		射線造成 %0.2f 奇術傷害，且必定發射到最遠距離。
		奇術傷害無法被“全體抗性”之外的任何抗性阻擋，使用你最高的抗性穿透屬性和最高的傷害加成屬性，且無法被變爲其他傷害類型。
		這一技能可以觸發無盡之炎和風暴之怒。
		如果你處在西弗格羅斯形態下，對潮溼目標傷害增加 30%% 。
		在開啓水晶力場或絕對零度的情況下，技能分別有 25%% 機率震懾或凍結目標 3 回合。
		每當你使用射線類技能造成傷害，這一技能的冷卻時間降低 1 回合（這一效果每回合最多觸發一次）。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Thaumaturgy Unlock Checker", "奇術解鎖檢測", "talent name")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/war-alchemy.lua"

t("Heat", "加熱", "talent name")
t([[Turn part of your target into fire, burning the rest for %0.2f fire damage over 8 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[將你的敵人化爲火焰，在8回合內造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/water.lua"

t("Ice Shards", "寒冰箭", "talent name")
t([[Hurl ice shards at the targets in the selected area. Each shard travels slowly and does %0.2f ice damage, hitting all adjacent targets on impact with 25%% chance to freeze them.
		If the target resists being frozen, it instead get wet.
		If the target is wet the damage increases by 30%% and the ice freeze chance increases to 50%%.
		This spell will never hit the caster.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[朝指定地點所有目標射出寒冰箭。每根寒冰箭緩慢移動，造成 %0.2f 冰系傷害，有25%%機率使其凍結。
		如果目標抵抗了凍結，則會使其溼潤。
		如果目標處於溼潤狀態，傷害增加 30%% ，同時冰凍率上升至 50%% 。
		此法術不會傷害施法者。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Glacial Vapour", "寒霜冰霧", "talent name")
t([[Glacial fumes rise from the ground, doing %0.2f cold damage in a radius of 3 each turn for %d turns.
		Creatures that are wet will take 30%% more damage and have 15%% chance to get frozen.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[在 3 碼半徑範圍內升起一片寒冷的冰霧，每回合造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害，持續 %d 回合。 
		處於溼潤狀態的生物承受額外 30%% 傷害，並有 15%% 機率被凍結。
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Tidal Wave", "潮汐", "talent name")
t("A #LIGHT_BLUE#wave of icy water#LAST# erupts from the ground!", "一股 #LIGHT_BLUE#冰冷的水流#LAST# 從地面上涌現!", "logSeen")
t([[A wall of water rushes out from the caster with an initial radius of 1, increasing by 1 per turn to a maximum radius of %d, doing %0.2f cold damage and %0.2f physical damage to all inside, as well as knocking back targets each turn.
		The tidal wave lasts for %d turns.
		All creatures hit gain the wet effect, which reduces their stun/freeze immunity by half and interacts with other cold spells.
		The damage and duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[以施法者爲中心，在 1 碼半徑範圍內生成一股巨浪，每回合增加 1 碼半徑範圍，最大 %d 碼。 
		對目標造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害和 %0.2f 物理傷害，同時擊退目標，持續 %d 回合。 
		所有受影響的生物進入溼潤狀態，震懾抗性減半。
		傷害和持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Shivgoroth Form", "西弗格羅斯形態", "talent name")
t("You are already a Shivgoroth!", "你已經是寒冰元素了！", "logPlayer")
t([[You absorb latent cold around you, turning into an ice elemental - a shivgoroth - for %d turns.
		While transformed, you do not need to breathe, gain access to the Ice Storm talent at level %d, gain %d%% resistance to cuts and stuns, gain %d%% cold resistance, and all cold damage heals you for %d%% of the damage done.
		The power will increase with your Spellpower.

		#AQUAMARINE#Ice storm:#LAST#
		%s]], [[你吸收周圍的寒冰圍繞你，將自己轉變爲純粹的冰元素——西弗格羅斯，持續 %d 回合。 
		轉化成元素後，你不需要呼吸並獲得等級 %d 的冰雪風暴，獲得 %d%% 震懾和流血抵抗， %d%% 寒冷傷害抗性。所有寒冷傷害可對你產生治療，治療量基於傷害值的 %d%% 。 
		效果受法術強度加成
		#AQUAMARINE#冰雪風暴:#LAST#
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Ice Storm", "冰雪風暴", "talent name")
t([[A furious ice storm rages around the caster, doing %0.2f cold damage in a radius of 3 each turn for %d turns.
		It has a 25%% chance to freeze damaged targets.
		If the target is wet the damage increases by 30%% and the freeze chance increases to 50%%.
		The damage and duration will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[召喚一股激烈的暴風雪圍繞着施法者，在 3 碼範圍內每回合對目標造成 %0.2f 冰冷傷害，持續 %d 回合。 
		它有 25%% 概率冰凍受影響目標。 
		如果目標處於溼潤狀態，傷害增加 30%% ，同時凍結率上升至 50%% 。
		傷害和持續時間受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/wildfire.lua"

t("Blastwave", "火焰新星", "talent name")
t([[A wave of fire emanates from you with a radius of %d, knocking back anything caught inside and setting them ablaze, doing %0.2f fire damage over 3 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[從你身上釋放出一波 %d 碼半徑範圍的火焰，擊退範圍內所有目標並使它們進入 3 回合灼燒狀態，共造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Burning Wake", "無盡之炎", "talent name")
t([[Your Flame, Flameshock, Fireflash and Blastwave spells leave a burning wake on the ground, burning all within for %0.2f fire damage for 4 turns.
		The damage will increase with your Spellpower.]], [[你的火球術、火焰衝擊、爆裂火球和火焰新星都會在地上留下燃燒的火焰，每回合對經過者造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，持續 4 回合。 
		傷害受法術強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Cleansing Flames", "淨化之焰", "talent name")
t([[When you stand in your Burning Wake or Inferno ground effect, you can self immolate to trigger Cleansing Flames for %d turns.
		While the effect lasts you will take %0.2f fire damage per turn.
		Each turn there is a %d%% chance for any creature taking damage from Burning Wake, Inferno or Cleansing Flames to remove a status effect (physical or magical).
		If the target is hostile, it will remove a beneficial effect.
		If the target is friendly, it will remove a detrimental effect.]], [[當你站在你的無盡之焰或地獄火地面效果上的時候，你可以用淨化之焰引燃自己，持續 %d 回合。
		在這一效果持續的時候，你會每回合受到 %0.2f 火焰傷害。
		在每一回合內，對於每個從無盡之焰，地獄火或淨化之焰中受到傷害的生物，將會有 %d%% 機率移除一個物理或魔法狀態。
		如果目標是敵人，則移除其增益狀態。 
		如果目標時友方單位，則移除其負面狀態。]], "tformat")
t("Wildfire", "野火燎原", "talent name")
t("Surround yourself with Wildfire, increasing all your fire damage by %0.1f%%, ignoring %d%% fire resistance of your targets and reducing self-inflicted fire damage by %d%%.", [[使身上纏繞火焰，增加 %0.1f%% 所有火系傷害並無視目標 %d%% 火焰抵抗。 
		同時，減少 %d%% 對自己造成的火焰傷害。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/2h-assault.lua"

t("Stunning Blow", "震懾打擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists the stunning blow!", "%s抵抗了震懾打擊。", "logSeen")
t([[Hit the target twice with your two-handed weapon, doing %d%% damage. Each hit will try to stun the target for %d turns.
		The stun chance increases with your Physical Power.]], [[用你的雙手武器攻擊目標兩次並造成 %d%% 傷害。每次攻擊都會試圖震懾目標 %d 回合。 
		受物理強度影響，震懾概率有加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fearless Cleave", "無畏跳斬", "talent name")
t("You must be able to move to use this talent.", "你必須處於可以移動的狀態才能使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("Take a step toward your foes then use the momentum to cleave all creatures adjacent to you for %d%% weapon damage.", "向前跳一步，用這股力量對周圍的目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。", "tformat")
t("Death Dance", "死亡之舞", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Death Dance without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Spin around, extending your weapon in radius %d and damaging all targets around you for %d%% weapon damage.
		At level 3 all damage done will also make the targets bleed for an additional %d%% damage over 5 turns]], [[原地旋轉，伸展你的武器，傷害你周圍半徑 %d 範圍內的所有目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		等級 3 時，所造成的傷害會引發額外 %d%% 流血傷害，持續 5 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Execution", "致命斬殺", "talent name")
t("You require a two handed weapon to use this talent.", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Takes advantage of a wounded foe to perform a killing strike.  This attack is an automatic critical hit that does %0.1f%% extra weapon damage for each %% of life the target is below maximum.
		(A victim with 30%% remaining life (70%% damaged) would take %0.1f%% weapon damage.)
		If an enemy dies from this attack then two of your talent cooldowns are reduced by 2 turns and Execution's cooldown is reset.]], [[試圖斬殺目標。目標每損失 1%% 生命，你造成額外 %0.1f%% 武器傷害。
		（對於剩餘 30%% 生命（即損失了 70%% 生命）的敵人造成 %0.1f%% 武器傷害）
		該攻擊必定暴擊。
		如果這一攻擊殺死了敵人，你的兩個技能的冷卻時間減少兩個回合，致命斬殺技能的冷卻時間歸零。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/2hweapon.lua"

t("Death Dance", "死亡之舞", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Death Dance without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("Spin around, extending your weapon and damaging all targets around you for %d%% weapon damage.", "原地旋轉，伸展你的武器，傷害你周圍所有的目標，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。", "tformat")
t("Berserker", "狂戰士", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Berserker without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[You enter an aggressive battle stance, increasing Accuracy by %d and Physical Power by %d, at the cost of -10 Defense and -10 Armour.
		While berserking, you are nearly unstoppable, granting you %d%% stun and pinning resistance.
		The Accuracy bonus increases with your Dexterity, and the Physical Power bonus with your Strength.]], [[進入狂暴的戰鬥狀態，以減少 10 點閃避和 10 點護甲的代價增加 %d 點命中和 %d 點物理強度。 
		開啓狂暴時你無人能擋，增加 %d%% 震懾和定身抵抗。 
		命中受敏捷值加成； 
		物理強度受力量值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Warshout", "戰爭怒吼", "talent name")
t("@Source@ uses Warshout.", "@Source@發出戰吼.", "_t")
t("@Source@ uses Warsqueak.", "@Source@發出吱吱的戰吼.", "_t")
t("You cannot use Warshout without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("Shout your warcry in a frontal cone of radius %d. Any targets caught inside will be confused (power %d%%) for %d turns.", "在你的正前方大吼形成 %d 碼半徑的扇形戰爭怒吼。任何在其中的目標會被混亂（強度 %d%%) %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Death Blow", "致命打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Death Blow without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s feels the pain of the death blow!", "%s 感受到了死亡一擊的疼痛！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the death blow!", "%s抵抗了死亡一擊！", "logSeen")
t([[Tries to perform a killing blow, doing %d%% weapon damage and dealing an automatic critical hit. If the target ends up with low enough life (<20%%), it might be instantly killed.
		At level 4, it drains half your remaining stamina, and uses it to increase the blow damage by 100%% of it.
		The chance to instantly kill will increase with your Physical Power.]], [[試圖施展一次致命打擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害，本次攻擊自動變成暴擊。 
		如果打擊後目標生命值低於 20%% 則有可能直接殺死。 
		在等級 4 時會消耗剩餘的耐力值的一半並增加 100%% 所消耗耐力值的傷害。 
		目標即死的概率受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Stunning Blow", "震懾打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Stunning Blow without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the stunning blow!", "%s抵抗了震懾打擊。", "logSeen")
t([[Hits the target with your weapon, doing %d%% damage. If the attack hits, the target is stunned for %d turns.
		The stun chance increases with your Physical Power.]], [[用你的武器攻擊目標並造成 %d%% 傷害。如果此次攻擊命中，則目標會震懾 %d 回合。 
		震懾概率受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Sunder Armour", "破甲", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Sunder Armour without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("#CRIMSON#%s shatters %s shield!", "#CRIMSON#%s粉碎了%s的護盾!", "logSeen")
t([[Hits the target with your weapon, doing %d%% damage. If the attack hits, the target's armour and saves are reduced by %d for %d turns.
		Also if the target is protected by a temporary damage shield there is %d%% chance to shatter it.
		Armor reduction chance increases with your Physical Power.]], [[用你的武器攻擊目標並造成 %d%% 傷害。如果此次攻擊命中，則目標護甲和豁免會減少 %d 持續 %d 回合。 
		同時，如果目標被臨時傷害護盾保護，有 %d%% 機率使之破碎。
		受物理強度影響，護甲減值有額外增加。]], "tformat")
t("Sunder Arms", "破刃", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Sunder Arms without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Hits the target with your weapon, doing %d%% damage. If the attack hits, the target's Accuracy is reduced by %d for %d turns.
		Accuracy reduction chance increases with your Physical Power.]], [[用你的武器攻擊目標並造成 %d%% 傷害。如果此次攻擊命中，則目標命中會減少 %d 持續 %d 回合。 
		命中減值受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Blood Frenzy", "血之狂暴", "talent name")
t("You require a two handed weapon to use this talent.", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Blood Frenzy without a two-handed weapon!", "你需要裝備一把雙手武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Enter a blood frenzy, draining stamina quickly (-2 stamina/turn). Each time you kill a foe while in the blood frenzy, you gain a cumulative bonus to Physical Power of %d.
		Each turn, this bonus decreases by 2.]], [[進入血之狂暴狀態，快速消耗體力（ -4 體力/回合）。每次你在血之狂暴狀態下殺死一個敵人，你可以獲得 %d 物理強度增益。
		每回合增益減 2 。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/acrobatics.lua"

t("Vault", "撐杆跳", "talent name")
t("You cannot land in that space.", "你不能在這個位置落地。", "logPlayer")
t("You must vault over someone adjacent to you.", "你只能用撐杆跳跳過某個鄰近的目標。", "logPlayer")
t("#Source# #YELLOW#vaults#LAST# over #target#!", "#Source##YELLOW#撐杆跳過#LAST# #target#!", "logCombat")
t([[Use an adjacent friend or foe as a springboard, vaulting over them to another tile within range.
		This maneuver grants you a burst of speed from your momentum, allowing you run %d%% faster (movement speed bonus) in the same direction you vaulted for 3 turns.
		The increased speed ends if you change directions or stop moving.
		]], [[利用相鄰的友軍或敵人作爲跳板，從他們頭上跳入技能範圍內的另外一格中。
		這個伎倆使你藉助彈跳的力量提高你的速度，讓你在跳躍的方向上的移動速度增加 %d%% 三回合。
		如果你改變方向或者停止移動，速度加成將會消失。
		]], "tformat")
t("Tumble", "翻筋斗", "talent name")
t("@Source@ tumbles to a better position!", "@Source@翻筋斗到更優的位置！", "_t")
t("You cannot move!", "你無法移動!", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot tumble to that space.", "你不能翻筋斗到這個地點。", "logPlayer")
t([[Move to a spot within range, bounding around, over, or through any enemies in the way.
		This maneuver can surprise your foes and improves your tactical position, improving your physical critical chance by %d%% for 1 turn.]], [[從敵人的側面、上空或者胯下移動到技能範圍內的指定位置。
		這個伎倆可以驚嚇你的敵人讓你獲得更有利的戰術位置，增加你的暴擊機率 %d%% 1 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Trained Reactions", "特種訓練", "talent name")
t([[While this talent is sustained, you anticipate deadly attacks against you.
		Any time you would lose more than %d%% of your maximum life in a single hit, you instead duck out of the way and assume a defensive posture.
		This reduces the triggering damage and all further damage in the same turn by %d%%.
		You need %0.1f Stamina and an adjacent open tile to perform this feat (though it does not cause you to move).]], [[當這個技能被激活的時候，你能夠預見到致命的傷害。
		每當你遭受一次大於 %d%% 生命值的攻擊時，你閃身躲避這個攻擊並擺出防禦姿勢。
		這個技能降低本次傷害和接下來本回合的所有傷害 %d%% 。
		你需要 %0.1f 體力和相鄰的無人空地來觸發技能效果（儘管你不會因爲躲避而移動）。]], "tformat")
t("Superb Agility", "身輕如燕", "talent name")
t([[You gain greater facility with your acrobatic moves, lowering the cooldowns of Vault, Tumble, and Trained Reactions by %d, and their stamina costs by %0.1f.
		At Rank 3 you also gain 10%% global speed for 1 turn after Trained Reactions activates. At rank 5 this speed bonus improves to 20%% and lasts for 2 turns.]], [[你使用雜耍系技能更加得心應手，降低撐杆跳、翻滾和求生本能的冷卻時間 %d 回合，降低技能的體力消耗 %0.1f 。
		在等級 3 時，每當求生本能觸發，你獲得 10%% 的整體速度 1 回合。
		在等級 5 時，速度加成變爲 20%% ，持續 2 回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/agility.lua"

t("Agile Defense", "敏捷防禦", "talent name")
t("%s(%d deflected)#LAST#", "%s(%d 敏捷防禦)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[You are trained in an agile, mobile fighting technique combining sling and shield. This allows shields to be equipped, using Dexterity instead of Strength as a requirement.
While you have a shield equip and your Block talent is not on cooldown, you have a %d%% chance to deflect any incoming damage, reducing it by 50%% of your shield’s block value.]], [[你學會了在戰鬥中靈敏使用投石索和盾牌的技巧。允許你裝備盾牌，用敏捷代替力量需求。
當你裝備盾牌，且格擋技能未進入冷卻時，有 %d%% 機率抵擋攻擊，減免 50%% 格擋值的傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Vault", "撐杆跳", "talent name")
t("You require a shield to use this talent.", "你需要一面盾牌來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the daze!", "%s抵抗了眩暈!", "logSeen")
t([[Leap onto an adjacent target with your shield, striking them for %d%% damage and dazing them for 2 turns, then using them as a springboard to leap to a tile within range %d.
The shield bash will use Dexterity instead of Strength for the shield's bonus damage.
At talent level 5, you will immediately enter a blocking stance on landing.]], [[用盾牌踩在臨近目標上，造成 %d%% 傷害並眩暈 2 回合，之後將其做爲跳板躍向 %d 格內的空地。
盾襲將使用敏捷代替力量決定盾牌傷害。
技能等級 5 時，你將在落地後立刻進入格擋狀態。]], "tformat")
t("Bull Shot", "衝鋒射擊", "talent name")
t("You are too close to build up momentum!", "離開目標太近無法施展！", "logPlayer")
t([[You rush toward your foe, readying your shot. If you reach the enemy, you release the shot, imbuing it with great power.
		The shot does %d%% weapon damage and knocks back your target by %d.
		The cooldown of this talent is reduced by 1 each time you move.
		This requires a sling to use.]], [[你衝向敵人，同時準備射擊。當你接近敵人時，立刻射擊，釋放強大的威力。
		射擊造成 %d%% 武器傷害並擊退目標 %d 格.
		每次你移動時，該技能的冷卻時間減少 1 回合。
		該技能需要投石索。]], "tformat")
t("Rapid Shot", "速射姿態", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Rapid Fire without a bow or sling!", "你需要一把弓或者投石索來施放這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[Enter a fluid, mobile shooting stance that excels at close combat. Your ranged attack speed is increased by %d%% and each time you shoot you gain %d%% increased movement speed for 2 turns.
Ranged attacks against targets will also grant you up to %d%% of a turn. This is 100%% effective against targets within 3 tiles, and decreases by 20%% for each tile beyond that (to 0%% at 8 tiles). This cannot occur more than once per turn.
Requires a sling to use.]], [[進入流暢而靈活的射擊姿勢，更適用於近戰。你的遠程攻擊速度增加 %d%% ，每次射擊令你在兩回合內移動速度增加 %d%% 。
命中敵人的遠程攻擊將給你帶來 %d%% 額外回合，該效果對三格以內的目標有 100%% 效果，每增加 1 格距離，效果降低 20%% ( 8 格降爲 0 %% )。該效果每回合只能生效一次。
該技能需要投石索。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/archery.lua"

t("Shoot", "射擊", "talent name")
t("@Source@ shoots!", "@Source@射擊!", "_t")
t("Shoot your bow, sling or other missile launcher!", "使用弓箭，投石索或者導彈發射器射擊！", "tformat")
t("Steady Shot", "穩固射擊", "talent name")
t([[Fire a steady shot, doing %d%% damage with a %d%% chance to mark the target.
If Steady Shot is not on cooldown, this talent will automatically replace your normal attacks (and trigger the cooldown).]], [[穩固地射擊，造成 %d%% 傷害，同時有 %d%% 機率標記目標。
如果穩固射擊沒有進入冷卻狀態，將自動代替普通攻擊，並進入冷卻。]], "tformat")
t("Pin Down", "強力定身", "talent name")
t([[You fire a shot for %d%% damage that attempts to pin your target to the ground for %d turns, as well as giving your next Steady Shot or Shoot 100%% increased chance to critically hit and mark (regardless of whether the pin succeeds).
		This shot has a 20%% chance to mark the target.
		The chance to pin increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你朝目標發射定身攻擊，造成 %d%% 傷害，並嘗試將目標定身 %d 回合。
		你對目標的下一發射擊或者穩固射擊將增加 100%% 暴擊率與標記機率。
		此次攻擊有 20%% 機率標記目標。
		定身機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Fragmentation Shot", "爆裂射擊", "talent name")
t([[Fires a shot that explodes into a radius %d ball of razor sharp fragments on impact, dealing %d%% weapon damage and leaving targets crippled for %d turns, reducing their attack, spell and mind speed by %d%%.
		Each target struck has a %d%% chance to be marked.
		The status chance increases with your Accuracy.]], [[發射命中後爆裂成 %d 格半徑球型範圍碎片的彈藥, 造成 %d%% 武器傷害並致殘目標 %d 回合，降低 %d%% 攻擊、施法和精神速度。
		每個被擊中的目標有 %d%% 機率被標記。
		致殘機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Scatter Shot", "分散射擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists the scattershot!", "%s抵抗了分散射擊!", "logSeen")
t([[Fires a wave of projectiles in a radius %d cone, dealing %d%% weapon damage. All targets struck by this will be knocked back to the maximum range of the cone and stunned for %d turns.
		Each target struck has a %d%% chance to be marked.
		The chance to knockback and stun increases with your Accuracy.]], [[射出彈藥化爲 %d 格錐形衝擊波，造成 %d%% 傷害，被擊中的單位將被擊退至範圍外，並被震懾 %d 回合。
		每個被擊中的目標有 %d%% 機率被標記。
		擊退與震懾機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Headshot", "爆頭", "talent name")
t([[Fire a precise shot dealing %d%% weapon damage, with 100 increased accuracy. This shot will bypass other enemies between you and your target.
Only usable against marked targets, and consumes the mark on hit.]], [[瞄準目標頭部發射穿透性彈藥，造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
此次攻擊額外獲得 100 命中，且能穿透目標以外單位。
只能對被標記的單位使用，使用將消耗掉標記。]], "tformat")
t("Volley", "齊射", "talent name")
t([[You fire countless shots into the sky to rain down around your target, inflicting %d%% weapon damage to all within radius %d.
If the primary target is marked, you consume the mark to fire a second volley of arrows for %d%% damage at no ammo cost.]], [[你向天空發射無數彈藥，如箭雨般落向目標，造成 %d%% 傷害，殺傷半徑 %d 格。
如果中心目標被標記，你將消耗其標記，不消耗彈藥發射額外齊射一輪，造成 %d%% 傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Called Shots", "精準射擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists the silence!", "%s抵抗了沉默！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the disarm!", "%s抵抗了繳械!", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the slow!", "%s抵抗了減速!", "logSeen")
t([[You fire a disabling shot at a target's throat (or equivalent), dealing %d%% weapon damage and silencing them for %d turns.
If the target is marked, you consume the mark to fire two secondary shots at their arms and legs (or other appendages) dealing %d%% damage, reducing their movement speed by 50%% and disarming them for the duration.
The status chance increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你朝目標的喉嚨（或者類似部位）射擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害並沉默 %d 回合。
如果目標被標記，則消耗標記並額外向目標的手臂與大腿（或者類似部位）射擊兩次，造成 %d%% 傷害 , 降低其 50 %% 移動速度，同時使其不能使用武器。
狀態效果機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bullseye", "靶心", "talent name")
t("Each time you consume a mark, you gain %d%% increased attack speed for 2 turns and the cooldown of %d random techniques are reduced by %d turns.", "每次消耗標記時，獲得 %d%% 攻擊速度 2 回合，並減少 %d 個戰鬥技巧系技能冷卻時間 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Relaxed Shot", "寧神射擊", "talent name")
t([[You fire a shot without putting much strength into it, doing %d%% damage.
		That brief moment of relief allows you to regain %d stamina.]], [[你射出放鬆的一箭, 造成 %d%% 傷害，同時回覆 %d 體力。
		]], "tformat")
t("Crippling Shot", "致殘射擊", "talent name")
t([[You fire a crippling shot, doing %d%% damage and reducing your target's speed by %d%% for 7 turns.
		The status power and status hit chance improve with your Accuracy.]], [[你射出致殘一箭 ,造成 %d%% 傷害，並降低目標 %d%% 速度 7 回合。
		狀態效果受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Pinning Shot", "定身射擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists!", "%s抵抗了效果！", "logSeen")
t([[You fire a pinning shot, doing %d%% damage and pinning your target to the ground for %d turns.
		The pinning chance increases with your Dexterity.]], [[你射出定身一箭 , 造成 %d%% 傷害，並定身目標 %d 回合。
		定身機率受敏捷加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/assassination.lua"

t("Coup de Grace", "致命一擊！", "talent name")
t("You require two weapons to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Coup de Grace without dual wielding!", "你需要雙持武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("#Source# delivers a Coup de Grace against #Target#!", "#Source#對#Target#發起致命一擊!", "logCombat")
t("%s resists the Coup de Grace!", "%s抵抗了致命一擊！", "logSeen")
t("#GREY#%s slips into shadow.", "#GREY#%s 潛入陰影。", "logSeen")
t([[Attempt to finish off a wounded enemy, striking them with both weapons for %d%% increased by 50%% if their life is below 30%%.  A target brought below 20%% of its maximum life must make a physical save against your Accuracy or be instantly slain.
		You may take advantage of finishing your foe this way to activate stealth (if known).]], [[嘗試終結一名受傷的敵人，用雙持武器攻擊對方，造成 %d%% 武器傷害，如果對方的生命值在30%% 以下，傷害還會增加50%% 。 20%% 生命以下的目標將用物理豁免對抗你的命中，若未通過則會被立刻秒殺。
		如果該技能殺死敵人，且你學會了潛行技能，你將進入潛行狀態。]], "tformat")
t("Terrorize", "致命恐懼", "talent name")
t([[When you exit stealth, you reveal yourself dramatically, intimidating foes around you. 
		All foes within radius %d that witness you leaving stealth will be stricken with terror, which randomly inflicts stun, slow (40%% power), or confusion (50%% power) for %d turns.
		The chance to terrorize improves with your combat accuracy.]], [[每次你脫離潛行狀態，你戲劇般的顯形令周圍的敵人聞風喪膽。 
		%d 範圍內看到你脫離潛行狀態的敵人將陷入恐懼，隨機觸發震懾、減速(40%%)、或者混亂 (50%%) 狀態，持續 %d 回合。
		恐懼機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Garrote", "絞殺", "talent name")
t("#Target# avoids a garrote from #Source#!", "#Target#避免了被#Source#勒住喉嚨!", "logCombat")
t([[When attacking from stealth, you slip a garrote over the target’s neck (or other vulnerable part).  This strangles for %d turns and silences for %d turns.  Strangled targets are pinned and suffer an automatic unarmed attack for %d%% damage each turn. 
		Your chance to apply the garrote increases with your Accuracy and you must stay adjacent to your target to maintain it.
		This talent has a cooldown.]], [[每次在潛行狀態下發起進攻時，你嘗試絞殺目標。目標將被勒住 %d 回合，沉默 %d 回合。被勒住的目標不能移動，每回合受到一次 %d%% 傷害的徒手攻擊。 
		勒住的機率受命中加成，你必須待在目標身邊以保持該狀態。
		該技能有冷卻時間。]], "tformat")
t("Marked for Death", "死亡標記", "talent name")
t([[You mark a target for death for 4 turns, causing them to take %d%% increased damage from all sources. When this effect ends they will immediately take physical damage equal to %0.2f plus %d%% of all damage taken while marked.
		If a target dies while marked, the cooldown of this ability is reset and the cost refunded.
		This ability can be used without breaking stealth.
		The base damage dealt will increase with your Dexterity.]], [[你爲目標打上死亡標記，持續 4 回合 , 使其受到的傷害增加 %d%% 。該效果結束時，額外造成 %0.2f 追加等於標記期間受到的傷害的 %d%% 的物理傷害。
		目標在標記期間死亡時，該技能立刻冷卻完成，同時返還消耗。
		使用該技能不消耗潛行。
		傷害受敏捷加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/battle-tactics.lua"

t("Greater Weapon Focus", "專注打擊", "talent name")
t([[Concentrate on your blows; for %d turns, each strike you land on your target in melee range has a %d%% chance to trigger another, similar strike.
		This works for all blows, even those from other talents and from shield bashes, but you can gain no more than one extra blow with each weapon during a turn.
		The chance increases with your Dexterity.]], [[專注於你的攻擊，每次攻擊有 %d%% 概率對目標造成一次類似的附加傷害，持續 %d 回合。 
		此效果對所有攻擊，甚至是技能攻擊或盾擊都有效果，但每回合每把武器最多獲得一次額外攻擊。 
		概率受敏捷值加成。]], "tformat", {2,1})
t("Step Up", "步步爲營", "talent name")
t([[After killing a foe, you have a %d%% chance to gain a 1000%% movement speed bonus for 1 game turn.
		The bonus disappears as soon as any action other than moving is done.
		Note: since you will be moving very fast, game turns will pass very slowly.]], [[每殺死 1 個敵人你有 %d%% 概率增加 1000%% 移動速度，持續一個標準遊戲回合。 
		此效果在你執行除移動外其他動作後立刻結束。 
		注意：由於你的移動非常迅速，遊戲回合會過的很慢。]], "tformat")
t("Bleeding Edge", "撕裂鞭笞", "talent name")
t([[Lashes at the target, doing %d%% weapon damage.
		If the attack hits, the target will bleed for %d%% weapon damage over 7 turns, and all healing will be reduced by %d%%.]], [[割裂目標並造成 %d%% 武器傷害。 
		如果攻擊命中目標，則目標會持續流血 7 回合， 
		造成總計 %d%% 武器傷害。在此過程中，任何對目標的治療效果減少 %d%% 。]], "tformat")
t("True Grit", "剛毅", "talent name")
t([[Take a defensive stance to resist the onslaught of your foes.
		While wounded, you gain all damage resistance equal to %d%% of your missing health.
		(So if you have lost 70%% of your life, you gain %d%% all resistance.)
		In addition, your all damage resistance cap increases %0.1f%% closer to 100%%.
		This consumes stamina rapidly the longer it is sustained (%0.1f stamina/turn, increasing by 0.3/turn).
		The resist is recalculated each time you take damage.]], [[採取一個防守姿態並抵抗敵人的猛攻.
		當你受傷後，你獲得相當於 %d%% 損失生命值百分比的全體傷害抗性。
		例如：當你損失 70%% 生命時獲得 %d%% 抗性。
		同時，你的全體傷害抗性上限相比於 100%% 的差距將減少 %0.1f%% 。
		該技能消耗體力迅速，體力值基礎消耗 %0.1f ，每回合增加 0.3 。
		抗性效果在每回合開始時刷新。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/bloodthirst.lua"

t("Mortal Terror", "致命恐懼", "talent name")
t("%s resists the terror!", "%s抵抗了恐懼！", "logSeen")
t([[Your mighty blows inspire utter terror on your foes. Any melee strike you do that deals more than %d%% of the target's total life puts them in a mortal terror, dazing them for 5 turns.
		Your critical strike chance also increase by %d%%.
		The daze chance increase with your Physical Power.]], [[你強力的攻擊引發敵人深深的恐懼。 
		任何你對目標造成的超過其 %d%% 總生命值的近身打擊會使目標陷入深深的恐懼中，眩暈目標 5 回合。 
		你的暴擊率同時增加 %d%% 。 
		眩暈概率受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bloodbath", "浴血", "talent name")
t([[Delight in spilling the blood of your foes.  After scoring a critical hit, your maximum hit points will be increased by %d%%, your life regeneration by %0.2f per turn, and your stamina regeneration by %0.2f per turn for %d turns.
		The life and stamina regeneration will stack up to five times, for a maximum of %0.2f and %0.2f each turn, respectively.]], [[沐浴着敵人的鮮血令你感到興奮。 
		在成功打出一次暴擊後，會增加你 %d%% 的最大生命值、 %0.2f 每回合生命回覆點數和 %0.2f 每回合體力回覆點數持續 %d 回合。 
		生命與體力回覆可以疊加 5 次直至 %0.2f 生命和 %0.2f 體力回覆/回合。]], "tformat")
t("Bloody Butcher", "血之屠夫", "talent name")
t([[You delight in the inflicting of wounds, providing %d physical power.
		In addition when you make a creature bleed its physical damage resistance is reduced by %d%% (but never below 0%%).
		Physical power depends on your Strength stat.]], [[你沉醉於撕裂傷口的興奮中，增加 %d 物理強度。
		同時，每次你讓敵人流血時，它的物理抗性下降 %d%% （但不會小於 0%% ）
		物理強度加成受力量影響。]], "tformat")
t("Unstoppable", "勢不可擋", "talent name")
t([[You enter a battle frenzy for %d turns. During that time, you can not use items, healing has no effect, and your health cannot drop below 1.
		At the end of the frenzy, you regain %d%% of your health per foe slain during the frenzy.
		While Unstoppable is active, Berserker Rage critical bonus is disabled as you lose the thrill of the risk of death.]], [[你進入瘋狂戰鬥狀態 %d 回合。 
		在這段時間內你不能使用物品，並且治療無效，此時你的生命值無法低於 1 點。 
		狀態結束後你每殺死一個敵人可以回覆 %d%% 最大生命值。
		當進入無雙狀態時，由於你失去了死亡的威脅，狂戰之怒不能提供暴擊加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/bow.lua"

t("Bow Mastery", "弓術專精", "talent name")
t([[Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using bows.
		Also, increases your reload rate by %d.]], [[當使用弓時，增加 %d%% 弓箭傷害，提高 30 物理強度。
		同時，增加 %d 裝填效果。]], "tformat")
t("Piercing Arrow", "穿透箭", "talent name")
t("You fire an arrow that cuts right through anything, piercing multiple targets if possible with nigh infinite armor penetration, doing %d%% damage.", "你射出一支能穿透任何東西的箭，可以穿透多個目標並對目標造成 %d%% 無視護甲的穿透傷害。", "tformat")
t("Dual Arrows", "雙重射擊", "talent name")
t([[You fire two arrows at your target, hitting it and a nearby foe if possible, doing %d%% damage
		This talent does not use any stamina.]], [[你向目標同時射出 2 支箭，對目標及其周圍的一個敵人造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		此技能不消耗體力值。]], "tformat")
t("Volley of Arrows", "箭雨", "talent name")
t("You must wield a bow!", "你必須裝備一把弓！", "logPlayer")
t("You fire multiple arrows at an area of %d radius, doing %d%% damage with each arrow.", "你向 %d 碼半徑區域內射出多支箭，每隻箭造成 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/buckler-training.lua"

t("Buckler Expertise", "盾牌訓練", "talent name")
t([[Allows shields to be equipped, using Cunning instead of strength as a requirement.
			When you are attacked in melee, you have a %d%% chance to deflect the attack with your shield, completely evading it.
			In addition, as long as you are wearing armour no heavier than leather, you gain %d Armour and %d%% Armour hardiness.
			The chance to deflect increases with your Cunning.]], [[允許你裝備盾牌，使用靈巧作爲屬性需求。
		當你受到近戰攻擊，你有 %d%% 的機率用盾牌使這次攻擊偏斜，並完全躲避它。
		另外，若你沒有裝備重甲，你獲得 %d 護甲值和 %d%% 護甲強度。
		受到靈巧影響，偏斜機率有加成。]], "tformat")
t("Bash and Smash", "擊退射擊", "talent name")
t("You require a ranged weapon and a shield to use this talent.", "你必須裝備一把遠程武器和一面盾牌。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the knockback!", "%s抵抗了擊退！", "logSeen")
t("Bash an enemy in melee range with your shield (twice for talent level 5 or more), doing %d%% damage and knocking them back %d squares. You may then follow with a deadly short-range sling attack, dealing %d%% damage. The shield bash will use Dexterity instead of Strength for the shield's bonus damage.", [[用盾牌重擊近戰範圍內的一名敵人（當技能等級在 5 級或更高時重擊 2 次），造成 %d%% 傷害並擊退 %d 格。緊接着用投石索發動一次致命的攻擊，造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		盾牌攻擊使用敏捷取代力量來計算盾牌傷害加成。]], "tformat")
t("Buckler Mastery", "格擋大師", "talent name")
t(" At talent level 5, your Bash and Smash shield hits are guaranteed criticals.", "技能等級 5，你的擊退射擊必定暴擊。", "_t")
t(" At talent level 5, your Bash and Smash shield hit is a guaranteed critical.", "技能等級 5 時，你的擊退射擊必定暴擊。", "_t")
t("When you are hit by a projectile, physical or otherwise, you have a %d%% chance to deflect it up to %d squares away.%s", "當你被拋射物攻擊時，不論是否爲物理類型，你有 %d%% 的機率使其偏斜最多 %d 格。%s", "tformat")
t("Counter Shot", "以牙還牙", "talent name")
t("#ORCHID##Source# follows up with a countershot.#LAST#", "#ORCHID##Source#啓動了反擊射擊.#LAST#。", "logCombat")
t([[Any time you block an attack with Buckler Expertise or Buckler Mastery you instantly counterattack with your sling for %d%% damage  This can only occur up to %d time(s) per turn.
			]], [[每當你的格擋專家或者格擋大師技能擋住攻擊時，你立刻使用投石索發動一次傷害 %d%% 的反擊。每回合最多隻能發動 %d 次反擊。
			]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/combat-techniques.lua"

t("Rush", "衝鋒", "talent name")
t("@Source@ rushes out!", "@Source@衝了出去!", "_t")
t("You can only rush to a creature.", "你只能衝向生物。", "logPlayer")
t("You are too close to build up momentum!", "離開目標太近無法施展！", "logPlayer")
t([[Rush toward a target enemy with incredible speed and perform a melee attack for 120%% weapon damage that can daze the target for 3 turns if it hits.
		You must rush from at least 2 tiles away.]], [[快速衝向敵人，並造成 120%% 基礎武器傷害。如果此次攻擊命中，那麼目標會被眩暈 3 回合。 
		你必須從至少 2 碼以外開始衝鋒。]], "tformat")
t("Precise Strikes", "精準打擊", "talent name")
t([[You focus your strikes, reducing your attack speed by %d%% and increasing your Accuracy by %d and critical chance by %d%%.
		The effects will increase with your Dexterity.]], [[你集中精神攻擊，減少你 %d%% 攻擊速度並增加你 %d 點命中和 %d%% 暴擊率。 
		此效果受敏捷值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Perfect Strike", "完美打擊", "talent name")
t("You have learned to focus your blows to hit your target, granting +%d accuracy and allowing you to attack creatures you cannot see without penalty for the next %d turns.", "你已經學會專注你的攻擊來命中目標，增加 %d 命中並使你在攻擊你看不見的目標時不再受到額外懲罰，持續 %d 回合。", "tformat")
t("Blinding Speed", "急速", "talent name")
t("Through rigorous training, you have learned to focus your actions for a short while, increasing your speed by %d%% for 5 turns.", "通過嚴格的訓練你已經學會在短時間內爆發你的速度，提高你 %d%% 速度 5 回合。", "tformat")
t("Quick Recovery", "快速恢復", "talent name")
t("Your combat focus allows you to keep your hatred burning (%0.1f hate refunded after spending hate on a talent)", "你專注於戰鬥，使你每次消耗仇恨後，恢復 %0.1f 仇恨。", "tformat")
t("Your combat focus allows you to regenerate stamina faster (+%0.1f stamina/turn).", "你專注於戰鬥，使得你可以更快的回覆體力（ +%0.1f 體力/回合）。", "tformat")
t("Fast Metabolism", "快速代謝", "talent name")
t("Your combat focus allows you to regenerate life faster (+%0.1f life/turn).", "你專注於戰鬥，使你可以更快的回覆生命值（ +%0.1f 生命值/回合）。", "tformat")
t("Spell Shield", "法術抵抗", "talent name")
t("Rigorous training allows you to be more resistant to some spell effects (+%d spell save).", "嚴格的訓練使得你對某些法術效果具有更高的抗性（ +%d 法術豁免）。", "tformat")
t("Unending Frenzy", "無盡怒火", "talent name")
t("You revel in the death of your foes, regaining %0.1f additional hate with each death you cause.", "你陶醉在敵人的死亡中，每殺死一個敵人回覆額外 %0.1f 仇恨值。", "tformat")
t("You revel in the death of your foes, regaining %0.1f stamina with each death you cause.", "你陶醉在敵人的死亡中，每殺死一個敵人回覆 %0.1f 體力值。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/combat-training.lua"

t("Thick Skin", "硬化皮膚", "talent name")
t("Your skin becomes more resilient to damage. Increases resistance to all damage by %0.1f%%.", "你的皮膚變的更加堅硬。增加所有傷害抵抗 %0.1f%% 。", "tformat")
t("Heavy Armour Training", "重甲訓練", "talent name")
t("You cannot use your %s anymore.", "你不能使用你的%s了。", "logPlayer")
t("(Note that brawlers will be unable to perform many of their talents in massive armour.)", "(請注意，格鬥家在身穿板甲的時候，無法使用大部分技能。)", "_t")
t("(Note that wearing mail or plate armour will interfere with stealth.)", "(請注意，身穿重甲或板甲的時候不可以潛行。)", "_t")
t([[You become better at using your armour to deflect blows and protect your vital areas. Increases Armour value by %d, Armour hardiness by %d%%, and reduces the chance melee or ranged attacks critically hit you by %d%% with your current body armour.
		(This talent only provides bonuses for heavy mail or massive plate armour.)
		At level 1, it allows you to wear heavy mail armour, gauntlets, helms, and heavy boots.
		At level 2, it allows you to wear shields.
		At level 3, it allows you to wear massive plate armour.
		%s]], [[ 你使用防具來偏轉攻擊和保護重要部位的能力加強了。 
		根據現有防具，提高 %d 護甲值和 %d%% 護甲韌性，並減少 %d%% 被暴擊機率。 
		( 這項技能只對重甲或板甲提供加成。 ) 
		在等級 1 時，能使你裝備鎖甲、金屬手套、頭盔和重靴。 
		在等級 2 時，能使你裝備盾牌。 
		在等級 3 時，能使你裝備板甲。
		%s]], "tformat")
t("Light Armour Training", "輕甲訓練", "talent name")
t([[You learn to maintain your agility and manage your combat posture while wearing robes or light armour.  When wearing armour no heavier than leather in your main body slot, you gain %d Defense, %d%% Armour hardiness, and %d%% reduced Fatigue.
		In addition, when you step adjacent to a (visible) enemy, you use the juxtaposition to increase your total Defense by %d for 2 turns.
		The Defense bonus scales with your Dexterity.]], [[你學會在身着輕甲和布甲時保持敏捷。你獲得 %d 閃避， %d%% 護甲強度，減少 %d%% 疲勞。
		此外，每當你進入和（可見的）敵人相鄰的位置時，你獲得 %d 閃避，持續 2 回合。
		閃避受敏捷加成。]], "tformat")
t("Combat Accuracy", "強化命中", "talent name")
t("Increases the accuracy of unarmed, melee and ranged weapons by %d.", "增加你的徒手、近身和遠程武器命中 %d 點。", "tformat")
t("Weapons Mastery", "武器掌握", "talent name")
t("Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using swords, axes or maces.", "使用劍、斧、狼牙棒時，增加 %d%% 傷害，增加 30 物理強度。", "tformat")
t("Dagger Mastery", "匕首掌握", "talent name")
t("Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using daggers.", "使用匕首時，增加 %d%% 傷害，增加 30 物理強度。", "tformat")
t("Exotic Weapons Mastery", "特殊武器掌握", "talent name")
t("Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using exotic weapons.", "使用特殊武器時，增加 %d%% 傷害，增加 30 物理強度。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/conditioning.lua"

t("Vitality", "活力", "talent name")
t([[You recover faster from poisons, diseases and wounds, reducing the duration of all such effects by %d%%.  
			Whenever your life falls below 50%%, your life regeneration increases by %0.1f for %d turns (%d total). This effect can only happen once every %d turns.
		The regeneration scales with your Constitution.]], [[你受中毒、疾病和創傷的影響較小，減少 %d%% 此類效果的持續時間。 
		此外在生命值低於 50%% 時，你的生命回覆將會增加 %0.1f ，持續 %d 回合，共回覆 %d 生命值，但每隔 %d 回合才能觸發一次。
		生命回覆受體質值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Unflinching Resolve", "頑強意志", "talent name")
t("#ORCHID#%s has recovered!#LAST#", "#ORCHID#%s恢復了!#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[You've learned to recover quickly from effects that would disable you. Each turn, you have a %d%% chance to recover from a single stun effect.
		At talent level 2 you may also recover from Blindness, at level 3 Confusion and Pins, and level 4 Disarms and Slows.
		Effects will be cleansed with the priority order Stun > Blind > Confusion > Pin > Disarm > Slow.
		Only one effect may be recovered from each turn, and the chance to recover from an effect scales with your Constitution.]], [[你學會從負面狀態中快速恢復。 
		每回合你有 %d%% 機率從震懾效果中恢復。 
		在等級 2 時，也可以從致盲效果中恢復。 
		在等級 3 時，也可以從混亂和定身效果中恢復。 
		在等級 4 時，也可以從繳械和減速效果中恢復。 
		解除負面狀態的優先級是 震懾 > 致盲 > 混亂 > 定身 > 繳械 > 減速
		每回合你只能擺脫 1 種狀態。 
		受體質影響，恢復概率按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Daunting Presence", "望而生畏", "talent name")
t([[Enemies are intimidated by your very presence.
		Enemies within radius %d have their Physical Power, Mindpower, and Spellpower reduced by %d.
		The power of the intimidation effect improves with your Physical power]], [[敵人因你的存在而恐懼。 
		半徑 %d 碼範圍內的敵人的物理強度，精神強度和法術強度會降低 %d 。
		受物理強度影響，威脅效果有加成。]], "tformat")
t("Adrenaline Surge", "腎上腺素", "talent name")
t([[You release a surge of adrenaline that increases your Physical Power by %d for %d turns. While the effect is active, you may continue to fight beyond the point of exhaustion.
		You may continue to use stamina based talents while at zero stamina at the cost of life.
		The Physical Power increase will scale with your Constitution.
		Using this talent does not take a turn.]], [[你激活腎上腺素來增加 %d 物理強度持續 %d 回合。 
		此技能激活時，你可以不知疲倦地戰鬥，若體力爲 0 ，可繼續使用消耗類技能，代價爲消耗生命。 
		物理強度受體質值加成。 
		使用本技能不會消耗額外回合。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/dualweapon.lua"

t("Dual Weapon Training", "雙持專精", "talent name")
t("Increases the damage of your off-hand weapon to %d%%.", "副手武器傷害增加至 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Dual Weapon Defense", "抵擋訓練", "talent name")
t([[You have learned to block incoming blows with your offhand weapon.
		When dual wielding, your defense is increased by %d.
		Up to %0.1f times a turn, you have a %d%% chance to parry up to %d damage (based on your your offhand weapon damage) from a melee attack.
		A successful parry reduces damage like armour (before any attack multipliers) and prevents critical strikes.  Partial parries have a proportionally reduced chance to succeed.  It is difficult to parry attacks from unseen attackers and you cannot parry with a mindstar.
		The defense and chance to parry improve with Dexterity.  The number of parries increases with Cunning.]], [[你已經學會用你的武器招架攻擊。當你雙持時，增加 %d 點近身閃避。
		每回合最多 %0.1f 次，你有 %d%% 概率抵擋至多 %d 點傷害（基於副手傷害）。 
		抵擋的減傷類似護甲，且被抵擋的攻擊不會暴擊。很難抵擋未發現的敵人的攻擊，且不能使用靈晶抵擋攻擊。
		受敏捷影響，閃避增益按比例加成。 
		抵擋次數受靈巧加成。
		]], "tformat")
t("Close Combat Management", "近戰訓練", "talent name")
t("You must dual wield to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You must dual wield to manage contact with your target!", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t([[You have learned how to carefully manage contact between you and your opponent.
		When striking in melee with your dual wielded weapons, you automatically avoid up to %d damage dealt to you from each of your target's on hit effects.  This improves with your Dexterity, but is not possible with mindstars.
		In addition, while this talent is active, you redirect %d%% of the damage you avoid this way back to your target.]], [[你近戰格鬥的技巧更加精湛了。
		用雙持武器命中對手時，你每命中一個敵人獲得 %d 傷害減免（受敏捷加成，靈晶無效）。
		此外，該技能開啓時，你能反彈 %d%% 傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Offhand Jab", "副手猛擊", "talent name")
t("You must dual wield to perform an Offhand Jab!", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the surprise strike!", "%s抵抗了這次打擊！", "logSeen")
t([[With a quick shift of your momentum, you execute a surprise unarmed strike in place of your normal offhand attack.
		This allows you to attack with your mainhand weapon for %d%% damage and unarmed for %d%% damage.  If the unarmed attack hits, the target is confused (%d%% power) for %d turns.
		The chance to confuse increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你迅速移動，用徒手攻擊敵人。
		造成 %d%% 主手武器傷害， %d%% 徒手傷害。
		若徒手攻擊命中，敵人將被混亂（ %d%% 強度） %d 回合。
		混亂機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Dual Strike", "雙持打擊", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Dual Strike without dual wielding!", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the stunning strike!", "%s抵抗了震懾打擊！", "logSeen")
t([[Attack with your offhand weapon for %d%% damage. If the attack hits, the target is stunned for %d turns, and you hit it with your mainhand weapon doing %d%% damage.
		The stun chance increases with your Accuracy.]], [[用副手武器造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		如果攻擊命中，目標將會被震懾 %d 回合並且你會使用主武器對目標造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		震懾概率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Flurry", "疾風連刺", "talent name")
t("You cannot use Flurry without dual wielding!", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("Lashes out with a flurry of blows, hitting your target three times with each weapon for %d%% damage.", "對目標進行快速的連刺，每把武器進行 3 次打擊，每次打擊造成 %d%% 的傷害。", "tformat")
t("Heartseeker", "追心刺", "talent name")
t("Swiftly leap to your target and strike at their vital points with both weapons, dealing %d%% weapon damage. This attack deals %d%% increased critical strike damage.", "迅速躍向目標，用兩把武器發動一次強力的突刺攻擊，造成 %d%% 武器傷害，該次攻擊暴擊傷害係數增加 %d%% 。", "tformat")
t("Whirlwind", "旋風斬", "talent name")
t("You require two weapons to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("The target location must be within range and within view.", "目標區域需要在視野內、技能範圍內。", "logPlayer")
t("There is no open space in which to land near there.", "目標周圍沒有空餘空間。", "logPlayer")
t("%s becomes a whirlwind of weapons!", "%s 化作武器的旋風！", "logSeen")
t("You quickly move up to %d tiles to arrive adjacent to a target location you can see, leaping around or over anyone in your way.  During your movement, you attack all foes within one grid of your path with both weapons for %d%% weapon damage, causing those struck to bleed for 50%% of the damage dealt over 5 turns.", "你迅速跳躍至 %d 格內的敵人身邊並在移動中用 2 把武器對路徑周圍的所有敵人造成 %d%% 傷害，並使其流血 5 回合受到額外 50%% 傷害。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/duelist.lua"

t("Dual Weapon Mastery", "雙持掌握", "talent name")
t([[Your offhand weapon damage penalty is reduced to %d%%.
		Up to %0.1f times a turn, you have a %d%% chance to parry up to %d damage (based on your offhand weapon damage) from a melee or ranged attack.  The number of parries increases with your Cunning.  (A fractional parry has a reduced chance to succeed.)
		A successful parry reduces damage like armour (before any attack multipliers) and prevents critical strikes.  It is difficult to parry attacks from unseen attackers and you cannot parry with a mindstar.]], [[你的副手武器懲罰減少至 %d%% .
		每回合最多 %0.1f 次，你有 %d%% 概率抵擋至多 %d 點傷害（基於副手傷害）。 
		抵擋的減傷類似護甲，且被抵擋的攻擊不會暴擊。很難抵擋未發現的敵人的攻擊，且不能使用靈晶抵擋攻擊。
		]], "tformat")
t("Tempo", "節奏", "talent name")
t([[The flow of battle invigorates you, allowing you to press your advantage as the fight progresses.
		Up to once each per turn, while dual wielding, you may:
		Riposte -- If a melee or archery attack misses you or you parry it, you instantly restore %0.1f stamina and gain %d%% of a turn.
		Recover -- On performing a critical strike with your offhand weapon, you instantly restore %0.1f stamina.]], [[戰鬥鼓舞着你，讓你在戰鬥中獲得優勢。
		每回合一次，若你雙持武器，你將：
		反擊 -- 如果你閃避或抵擋了近戰或弓箭攻擊，你立刻回覆 %0.1f 體力並獲得 %d%% 額外回合。
		回覆 -- 副手武器暴擊時回覆 %0.1f 體力。]], "tformat")
t("Feint", "佯攻", "talent name")
t("You must be able to move to use this talent.", "你必須處於可以移動的狀態才能使用該技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s cannot move!", "%s 無法移動！", "logPlayer")
t("Terrain prevents #Source# from switching places with #Target#.", "地形阻止了#Source#與#Target#的換位.", "logCombat")
t([[Make a cunning feint that tricks your target into swapping places with you.  While moving, you take the opportunity to trip them, pinning and dazing them for 2 turns.
		Switching places distracts your foes and allows you to improve your defenses:  For %d turns, Dual Weapon Mastery yields one extra parry each turn and you are %d%% less likely to miss your parry opportunities.
		The chance to pin and to daze increases with your Accuracy]], [[假裝攻擊敵人，欺騙敵人和你換位。在移動時趁機削弱敵人，使其定身並眩暈 2 回合。
		換位令你的敵人分心，使你的閃避得到強化： %d 回合內，雙持掌握提供額外一次抵擋攻擊機會，你錯失抵擋機會的機率下降 %d%% 。
		定身與眩暈機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Lunge", "刺擊", "talent name")
t("You require two weapons to use this talent.", "你只有在雙持狀態下才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("You cannot use Lunge without dual wielding!", "你需要雙持武器來施展這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("%s resists the blow!", "%s抵抗了攻擊！", "logSeen")
t([[Exploiting a gap in your target's defenses, you make a lethal strike with your offhand weapon for %d%% damage that causes them to drop their weapon, disarming them for %d turns.
		Tempo will reduce the cooldown of this talent by 1 turn each time it is triggered defensively.
		The chance to disarm increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你攻其不備，用副手發起致命打擊，造成 %d%% 傷害並使其武器脫落，繳械 %d 回合。
		節奏技能被觸發時，該技能的冷卻時間減少 1 回合。
		繳械機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/excellence.lua"

t("Shoot Down", "強制擊落", "talent name")
t("#Source# shoots down '#Target#'!", "#Source#擊落了'#Target#'！", "logCombat")
t([[Your reflexes are lightning-fast, if you spot a projectile (arrow, shot, spell, ...) you can instantly shoot at it without taking a turn to take it down.
		You can shoot down up to %d projectiles.]], [[ 你的反射神經像閃電一樣快。當你瞄準拋射物（箭矢、彈藥、法術等）時，你能馬上擊落它而不消耗時間。 
		你最多能擊落 %d 個目標。]], "tformat")
t("Bull Shot", "衝鋒射擊", "talent name")
t("You are too close to build up momentum!", "離開目標太近無法施展！", "logPlayer")
t([[You rush toward your foe, readying your shot. If you reach the enemy, you release the shot, imbuing it with great power.
		The shot does %d%% weapon damage and knocks back your target by %d.]], " 你衝向你的敵人，並準備好射擊。如果你接觸到敵人，你將射出你準備好的箭矢/ 彈藥，給予其強勁的力量。射擊造成 %d%% 傷害並擊退對手 %d 碼。", "tformat")
t("Intuitive Shots", "直覺射擊", "talent name")
t("%s %s the attack!", "%s %s攻擊", "logSeen")
t("fails to intercept", "未能攔截", "_t")
t("intercepts", "攔截了", "_t")
t([[Activating this talent enhances your reflexes to incredible levels.  Each time you are attacked in melee, you have a %d%% chance get a defensive shot off in time to intercept the attack, fully disrupting it (including extra blows from certain talents), dealing %d%% archery damage, and knocking the attacker back %d tiles.
		Activating this talent will not interrupt reloading.]], " 激活該技能會大幅強化你的反射神經。每次你受到近戰攻擊，你有 %d%% 的機率進行一次防禦性射擊來中止對方這次攻擊，並造成 %d%% 傷害，同時擊退對方 %d 碼。激活這項技能不會中斷裝填彈藥。", "tformat")
t("Strangling Shot", "沉默射擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists the strangling shot!", "%s抵抗了沉默射擊！", "logSeen")
t([[You fire a shot at your target's throat, mouth, or equivalent body part, doing %d%% damage and silencing it for %d turns.
		The silence chance increases with your Accuracy.]], " 你瞄準目標的喉嚨、嘴巴或相關部位，造成 %d%% 傷害，並沉默對方 %d 個回合。沉默機率隨命中增長。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/field-control.lua"

t("Heave", "前踢", "talent name")
t("%s resists the knockback!", "%s抵抗了擊退！", "logSeen")
t([[A mighty kick that pushes your target away %d grids.
		If another creature is in the way, it will also be pushed away.
		The Knockback chance increases with your Accuracy or your Physical Power, whichever is greater.]], [[一次強力的前踢使你的目標被擊退 %d 碼。 
		如果有另外一個怪物擋在路上，它也會被推開。 
		擊退概率受敏捷或物理強度（取較大值）加成。]], "tformat")
t("Slow Motion", "子彈時間", "talent name")
t("Your great dexterity allows you to see incoming projectiles (spells, arrows, ...), effectively slowing them down by %d%%.", "你敏捷的身手允許你看見飛來的拋射物（法術、箭矢……），減慢它們 %d%% 速度。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/finishing-moves.lua"

t("Uppercut", "上鉤拳", "talent name")
t("@Source@ throws a finishing uppercut.", "@Source@打出終結性的上勾拳。", "_t")
t("%s resists the stun!", "%s抵抗了震懾！", "logSeen")
t([[A finishing uppercut that deals %d%% damage, and attempts to stun your target for %d to %d turns, depending on the amount of combo points you've accumulated.
		The stun chance will improve with your Physical Power.
		Using this talent removes your combo points.]], [[一次終結的上鉤拳，對目標造成 %d%% 傷害並可能震懾目標 %d 到 %d 回合（由你的連擊點數決定）。 
		震懾概率受物理強度加成 
		使用此技能會消耗當前的所有連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Concussive Punch", "震盪拳", "talent name")
t("@Source@ throws a concussive punch.", "@Source@打出震盪拳。", "_t")
t([[A powerful concussive punch that deals %d%% weapon damage to your target. If the punch hits, all targets in a radius of %d will take %0.2f to %0.2f damage, depending on the amount of combo points you've accumulated.
		The area damage will scale with your Strength, and the radius will increase by 1 per combo point.
		Using this talent removes your combo points.]], [[一次強力的衝擊，對目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害。如果此次攻擊命中，則會對 %d 碼半徑內所有目標造成 %0.2f ～ %0.2f 物理傷害（由你的連擊點數決定）。 
		受力量影響，範圍傷害按比例加成，每 1 點連擊點範圍上升 1 碼。 
		使用此技能會消耗當前所有連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Butterfly Kick", "蝴蝶踢", "talent name")
t([[You spin into a flying leap and deliver a powerful kick dealing %d%% weapon damage to all enemies in a radius of 1 as you land. The range will increase by 1 per combo point and total damage will increase by 10%% per combo point.
		Using this talent removes your combo points and you must have at least 1 combo point to use it.]], [[你旋轉着飛踢過去，對半徑 1 內的敵人造成 %d%% 武器傷害。
		每一點連擊點增加 1 點攻擊範圍和 10%% 傷害。
		使用該技能需要至少一點連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Haymaker", "致命重拳", "talent name")
t("@Source@ throws a wild haymaker!", "@Source@打出狂暴的重拳!", "_t")
t("%s feels the pain of the death blow!", "%s 感受到了死亡一擊的疼痛！", "logSeen")
t("%s resists the death blow!", "%s抵抗了死亡一擊！", "logSeen")
t([[A vicious finishing strike that deals %d%% damage increased by 20%% per combo point you have up to a max of %d%%. If the target ends up with low enough life (<20%%), it might be instantly killed.
		Killing a target with Haymaker will instantly restore %d%% to %d%% of your maximum stamina, depending on the amount of combo points you've accumulated.
		Using this talent removes your combo points.]], [[一次強烈的終結追擊，對目標造成 %d%% 傷害，每 1 點連擊點額外造成 20%% 的傷害，至多 %d%% 。 
		如果目標生命低於 20%% ，則會被立刻殺死。 
		用此技能殺死目標會立刻回覆你 %d%% 到 %d%% 最大體力值（由你的連擊點數決定）。 
		使用此技能會消耗當前所有連擊點。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/grappling.lua"

t("Grappling Stance", "抓取姿態", "talent name")
t([[Increases your Physical Save by %d and your Physical Power by %d.
		The bonuses will scale with your Strength.]], [[增加你的物理豁免 %d 和你的物理強度 %d 。 
		受力量影響，增益按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Clinch", "關節技：鎖鉗", "talent name")
t([[Make a melee attack for %d%% damage and then attempt to grapple a target up to one size category larger than yourself for %d turns. A grappled opponent will be unable to move, take %d damage each turn, and %d%% of the damage you receive from any source will be redirected to them as physical damage.
		Any movement from the target or you will break the grapple. Maintaining a grapple drains %d stamina per turn.
		You may only grapple a single target at a time, and using any targeted unarmed talent on a target that you're not grappling will break the grapple.]], [[對目標造成 %d%% 武器傷害並抓取目標（可抓取目標的身材最多比你大 1 級）持續 %d 回合。 1 個被鉗住的對手將無法移動,每回合受到 %d 傷害，同時你受到的傷害的 %d%% 將轉移至它身上。 
		任何目標或你的移動將會打破抓取。維持抓取每回合消耗 %d 體力。 
		同時你只能抓取 1 個目標，並且對任意 1 個你沒有抓取的目標使用非抓取徒手技能均會打破抓取。]], "tformat")
t("Crushing Hold", "關節技：折頸", "talent name")
t([[Enhances your grapples with additional effects. All additional effects will apply to every grapple with no additional save or resist check.
		#RED#Talent Level 1:  Reduces physical power by %d
		Talent Level 3:  Silences
		Talent Level 5:  Reduces global action speed by %d%%]], [[增強你的抓取，獲得額外效果，所有效果不需通過其他豁免或抵抗鑑定。
		#RED# 等級 1 ：減少 %d 物理強度
		等級 3 ：沉默 
		等級 5 ：目標減速 %d%% ]], "tformat")
t("Take Down", "關節技：抱摔", "talent name")
t([[Rushes forward and attempts to take the target to the ground, making a melee attack for %d%% damage then attempting to grapple them. If you're already grappling the target you'll instead slam them into the ground creating a radius 5 shockwave for %d physical damage and breaking your grapple.
		The grapple effects and duration will be based off your grapple talent, if you have it, and the damage will scale with your Physical Power.]], [[衝向目標，試圖將他掀翻在地，造成 %d%% 傷害然後抓取之。如果已經抓取，則將他掀翻，製造衝擊波，在半徑 5 的範圍內造成 %d 物理傷害並解除抓取。
		抓取效果和持續時間基於抓取技能。傷害受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Hurricane Throw", "關節技：颶風投", "talent name")
t("You must be grappling something to use this talent.", "你必須處於抓取中才能使用這個技能。", "logPlayer")
t("Your grapple victim must be able to move to use this talent.", "要使用這個技能，你抓取的目標必須可以移動。", "logPlayer")
t("#RED#%s is shaken by the collision and loses a turn!#LAST#", "#RED#%s 被衝擊波擊中，失去一回合行動機會！#LAST#", "logSeen")
t([[In a mighty show of strength you whirl your grappled victim around and throw them into the air causing %d%% damage to them and enemies in radius %d on landing.  
			If at least 1 other enemy is hit the thrown enemy will be shaken by the impact losing a full turn.
			You can only throw enemies that could move normally.]], [[你使出全力將抓取的目標扔到空中，對他和着陸點周圍半徑 %d 的生物造成 %d%% 傷害。
		如果至少有一個敵人被擊中，被投擲的敵人將會因爲衝擊而失去一個回合。
		你只能投擲那些可以移動的敵人。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/magical-combat.lua"

t("Arcane Combat", "奧術武器", "talent name")
t([[				
				Currently selected spell: %s]], [[				
				目前選擇的法術: %s]], "tformat")
t([[				
				Currently selected spell: Random]], [[				
				目前選擇的法術：隨機]], "_t")
t([[Allows you to use melee weapons to focus your spells, granting a %d%% chance per melee attack to cast an offensive spell as a free action on the target.
		Delivering the spell this way will not trigger a spell cooldown.
		You may select an allowed spell to trigger this way, or choose to have one randomly selected for each attack.
		While dual wielding or using a shield the chance is halved.
		The chance increases with your Cunning.

		Allowed spells: %s %s]], [[允許你使用近戰武器附魔法術。在你每次的近戰攻擊中都有 %d%% 概率附加一次火球術、閃電術或岩石飛彈。 
		你可以選擇觸發某一種法術，或者選擇隨機觸發任意一種法術。
		當雙持或持有盾牌時，每把武器觸發概率減半。
		通過這種方式觸發的法術不會造成對應技能進入冷卻。
		觸發概率受靈巧加成。
		允許法術： %s %s]], "tformat")
t("Arcane Cunning", "奧術靈巧", "talent name")
t("The user gains a bonus to Spellpower equal to %d%% of your Cunning (Current bonus: %d).", "增加相當於你 %d%% 靈巧的法術強度。目前的法術強度加成： %d", "tformat")
t("Arcane Feed", "奧術充能", "talent name")
t("Regenerates %0.2f mana per turn, and increases physical and spell critical chance by %d%% while active.", "當技能激活時，每回合恢復 %0.2f 法力值並提高 %d%% 物理及法術爆擊機率。", "tformat")
t("Arcane Destruction", "奧術毀滅", "talent name")
t([[Raw magical damage channels through the caster's weapon, increasing raw Physical Power by %d%% of your Magic (current bonus: %d).
		Each time you crit with a melee blow, you will unleash a radius %d ball of arcane damage, doing %0.2f.
		The bonus scales with your Spellpower and talent level.
		If you are using a shield this will only occur 50%% of the time.
		If you are dual wielding this will only occur 50%% of the time.
		At level 5 the ball becomes radius 2.
		]], [[通過你的武器來傳送原始的魔法傷害。增加相當於你 %d%% 魔法屬性值的物理強度（當前值： %d ）。
		每當你近戰攻擊暴擊時，你會釋放一個半徑爲 %d 碼的奧術屬性的魔法球，造成 %0.2f 的傷害。 
		受法術強度影響，增益按比例加成。
		當使用盾牌時，只有50%% 的機率觸發。
		當雙持武器時，只有50%% 的機率觸發。
		技能等級 5 時，魔法球的半徑變成 2。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/marksmanship.lua"

t("Master Marksman", "射擊精通", "talent name")
t([[Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using bows or slings, as well as your reload rate by %d.
		In addition, your Shoot has a %d%% chance to mark targets on hit.
The mark lasts for 5 turns, grants you visibility of the target (even through walls and other concealment), and causes them to become vulnerable to Headshot, Volley and Called Shots.]], [[使用弓和投石索時 %d%% 武器傷害， 30物理強度和 %d 填彈速度。
		射擊技能有 %d%% 機率標記目標。
		標記持續 5 回合，令你能感知到目標，同時讓他們面對爆頭、齊射和精巧射擊更脆弱。]], "tformat")
t("First Blood", "第一滴血", "talent name")
t([[You take advantage of unwary foes (those at or above 90%% life). Against these targets, Shoot, Steady Shot and Headshot bleed targets for %d%% additional damage over 5 turns and have a 50%% increased chance to mark (if capable of marking).
In addition, your Steady Shot, Shoot and Headshot now restore %0.1f stamina on hit.]], [[你趁敵人尚未防備（90%% 血量以上）施展攻擊，射擊、穩固射擊和爆頭使敵人流血 5 回合造成額外 %d%% 傷害，標記概率增加 50%% 。
此外，你的射擊、穩固射擊和爆頭回復 %0.1f 體力。]], "tformat")
t("Flare", "閃光彈", "talent name")
t([[Fire a shot at the target tile that blinds enemies for %d turns, marks them for 2 turns and illuminates the area within radius %d for %d turns. Enemies within the illuminated area lose %d defence and stealth power and cannot benefit from concealment.
		The status chance increases with your Accuracy, and the defense reduction with your Dexterity.]], [[發射閃光彈，致盲敵人 %d 回合, 標記他們 2 回合並照亮 %d 格範圍 %d 回合。範圍內的敵人降低 %d 閃避和潛行強度，不能從隱匿技能得到任何加成。
		狀態效果機率受命中加成，閃避削減受敏捷加成。]], "tformat")
t("Trueshot", "專注射擊", "talent name")
t("Enter a state of heightened focus for %d turns. While in this state your ranged attack speed is increased by %d%%, your shots do not consume ammo, and all shots capable of marking have their chance to mark increased by %d%%.", "進入專注狀態 %d 回合，遠程攻擊速度增加 %d%% ，射擊不消耗彈藥，標記概率增加 %d%% 。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/mobility.lua"

t("Disengage", "後跳", "talent name")
t("You must be able to move to use %s!", "要使用 %s ，你必須能夠移動!", "logPlayer")
t("You must disengage directly away from your target in a straight line.", "你必須以接近直線的軌跡後跳。", "logPlayer")
t("You must land in an empty space.", "你必須着陸於空地。", "logPlayer")
t("Your Disengage was partially blocked.", "你的後跳被部分阻擋了。", "logPlayer")
t("You are not able to Disengage in that direction.", "你不能朝這個方向後跳。", "logPlayer")
t([[Jump back up to %d grids from your target, springing over any creatures in your way. 
		You must disengage in a nearly straight line directly away from your target (which you must be able to see).
		After moving, you gain %d%% increased movement speed for 3 turns (which ends if you take any actions other than movement), and you may reload your ammo (if any).
		The extra speed and maximum distance you can move are reduced by your Fatigue level.]], [[指定目標，向後跳躍 %d 格，可以躍過途中所有生物。
		你必須選擇可見目標，必須以近乎直線的軌跡後跳。
		落地後，你獲得 3 回合 %d%% 移動速度加成，採取除移動外的行動會提前終止。
		移動速度和跳躍距離會受疲勞值影響。]], "tformat")
t("Evasion", "閃避", "talent name")
t([[Your quick wit and reflexes allow you to anticipate attacks against you, granting you a %d%% chance to evade melee and ranged attacks and %d increased defense for %d turns.
		The chance to evade and defense bonus increase with your Dexterity.]], [[你的戰鬥技巧和反射神經讓你能迅速躲閃攻擊，獲得 %d%% 機率躲閃近戰與遠程攻擊，閃避增加 %d ，持續 %d 回合。
		躲閃機率和閃避加成受敏捷加成。]], "tformat")
t("Tumble", "翻筋斗", "talent name")
t("You must have an empty space to roll to.", "你需要有空位來滾動。", "logPlayer")
t([[In an extreme feat of agility, you move to a spot you can see within range, bounding around, over, or through any enemies in the way.
		This talent cannot be used while wearing heavy armor, and leaves you exhausted.  The exhaustion increases the cost of your activated Mobility talents by %d%% (stacking), but fades over %d turns.]], [[你迅速地移動至範圍內可見的位置，躍過路徑上所有敵人。
		該技能在身着重甲時不能使用，使用後你會進入疲勞狀態，增加移動系技能消耗 %d%% （可以疊加）， %d 回合後解除。]], "tformat")
t("Trained Reactions", "特種訓練", "talent name")
t("%s is not usable while wearing heavy armour.", "%s 在身着重甲時無法使用", "logPlayer")
t("#FIREBRICK##Target# reacts to %s from #Source#, mitigating the blow!#LAST#.", "#FIREBRICK##Target# 對#Source#的%s迅速反應，降低了傷害！#LAST#.", "logCombat")
t("an attack", "一次攻擊", "_t")
t("damage", "傷害", "_t")
t(" #ffcc80#, -%d stam#LAST#", " #ffcc80#, -%d 體力#LAST#", "tformat")
t("%s(%d reacted#LAST#%s%s)#LAST#", "%s(%d 反應#LAST#%s%s)#LAST#", "tformat")
t([[You have trained to be very light on your feet and have conditioned your reflexes to react faster than thought to damage you take.
		While this talent is active, you instantly react to any direct damage (not from status effects, etc.) that would hit you for at least %d%% of your maximum life.
		This requires %0.1f stamina and reduces the damage by %d%%.
		Your reactions are too slow for this if you are wearing heavy armour.
		The damage reduction improves with your Defense.]], [[經過訓練後，你腳步輕快，神經敏銳。
		技能開啓時，你會對超過你 %d%% 最大生命值的直接傷害做出反應（狀態效果帶來的傷害除外）。
		消耗 %0.1f 體力，你將減少 %d%% 傷害。
		身着重甲時無法使用。
		傷害減免受閃避加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/munitions.lua"

t("Exotic Munitions", "異種彈藥", "talent name")
t([[You have learned to create and equip specialist ammunition:
Incendiary - Shots deal an additional %d%% weapon damage as fire in a radius %d ball. This cannot occur more than once per turn.
Venomous - Shots deal %0.2f nature damage and inflict numbing poison, dealing a further %0.2f nature damage over 5 turns and reducing all damage dealt by %d%%.
Piercing - Shots reduce armor and saves by %d for 3 turns, and your physical penetration is increased by %d%%.
You can only have 1 type of ammunition loaded at a time.
The poison damage dealt, armor penetration and save reduction will increase with your Physical Power.]], [[你學會了製造和裝備專門的彈藥:
燃燒彈- 命中後，對目標附近的敵人造成 %d%% 火焰武器傷害，範圍最大爲 %d ，每回合最多一次。
劇毒彈- 命中後，對目標造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並感染麻痹毒素 , 在 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並削弱其 %d%% 的傷害。
穿甲彈- 命中後，使目標的護甲和豁免減少 %d ，持續 3 回合, 你的物理穿透增加 %d%% 。
同時只能裝備一種彈藥。
毒素傷害、護甲和豁免削減受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Incendiary Ammunition", "燃燒彈", "talent name")
t([[Load incendiary ammunition, causing attacks to deal an additional %d%% weapon damage as fire in a radius %d ball around your target. 
		This cannot trigger more than once per turn.
		The damage will scale with your Physical Power.]], [[裝填燃燒彈, 對目標附近的敵人造成 %d%% 火焰武器傷害，範圍最大爲 %d 。
		該技能每回合最多觸發一次.
		傷害受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")
t("Venomous Ammunition", "劇毒彈", "talent name")
t([[Load venomous ammunition, causing ranged attacks to deal %0.2f nature damage and inflict numbing poison, dealing %0.2f nature damage over 5 turns and reducing all damage dealt by %d%%. 
		The damage will scale with your Physical Power.]], [[裝填毒彈, 對目標造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並感染麻痹毒素 , 在 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並削弱其 %d%% 的傷害。
		傷害受物理強度加成.]], "tformat")
t("Piercing Ammunition", "穿甲彈", "talent name")
t([[Load piercing ammunition, causing attacks to reduce the target's armor and saves by %d for 3 turns, and increasing your physical penetration by %d%%.
		The armor and save reduction will scale with your Physical Power.]], [[裝填穿甲彈, 使目標的護甲和豁免減少 %d 持續 3 回合, 你的物理穿透增加 %d%% 。
		護甲和豁免削減受物理強度加成.]], "tformat")
t("Explosive Shot", "爆炸射擊", "talent name")
t("You require incendiary, venomous or piercing ammunition to use this talent!", "你需要至少一種特殊彈藥（燃燒彈、劇毒彈、穿甲彈）來使用該技能！", "logPlayer")
t([[Fires a special shot based on your currently loaded ammo:
Incendiary - Fire a shot that deals %d%% weapon damage as fire and covers targets in radius %d in sticky pitch for %d turns, reducing global speed by %d%% and increasing fire damage taken by %d%%.
Venomous - Fire a shot that deals %d%% weapon damage as nature and explodes into a radius %d cloud of crippling poison for %d turns, dealing %0.2f nature damage each turn and giving affected targets a %d%% chance to fail talent usage.
Piercing - Fire a shot that explodes into a radius %d burst of shredding shrapnel, dealing %d%% weapon damage as physical and removing %d beneficial physical effects or sustains.
The poison damage dealt increases with your Physical Power, and status chance increases with your Accuracy.]], [[根據當前裝填的彈藥進行一次特殊的射擊
燃燒彈- %d%% 火焰武器傷害。在半徑 %d 碼範圍內用粘稠的瀝青包裹敵人 %d 回合, 減少 %d%% 整體速度並增加其受到的火焰傷害 %d%% 。
劇毒彈- %d%% 自然武器傷害。爆炸會形成半徑 %d 的致殘毒氣雲，持續 %d 回合, 每回合造成 %0.2f 自然傷害並使目標使用技能有 %d%% 機率失敗。
穿甲彈- 在半徑 %d 碼半徑內爆炸，造成 %d%% 物理武器傷害 ，並 %d 個移除有益的物理效果或持續技能。
毒素傷害受物理強度加成, 狀態觸發機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Enhanced Munitions", "強化彈藥", "talent name")
t([[You create enhanced versions of your ammunition, granting them additional effects.
Incendiary - The explosion radius is increased by 1, and the ground beneath is ignited dealing an additional %0.2f fire damage each turn for 3 turns.
Venomous - Inflicts leeching poison, dealing %0.2f nature damage over 3 turns and causing you to heal for 100%% of all damage the poison deals to the target.
Piercing - Punctures the target’s armor, increasing all damage they take by %d%% for 3 turns.
You only have a limited amount of this ammo, causing this talent to have a cooldown.
The damage dealt will increase with your Physical Power, and status chance increases with your Accuracy.]], [[你製造出強化版彈藥, 獲得額外效果：
燃燒彈- 爆炸範圍增加 1, 點燃地面每回合額外造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害持續 3 回合.
劇毒彈- 感染吸血毒素, 3 回合內造成 %0.2f 毒素傷害 , 毒素造成的 100%% 傷害會治療你.
穿甲彈- 擊穿目標護甲, 目標受到的所有傷害增加 %d%% 持續 3 回合.
你的強化版彈藥有限, 所以技能有冷卻時間.
傷害受物理強度加成, 狀態觸發機率受命中加成。]], "tformat")
t("Alloyed Munitions", "合金彈頭", "talent name")
t([[You mix together your munitions, leading to powerful new effects:
Incendiary - Targets struck by the explosion have their armor and saves reduced by %d for 3 turns, and your physical and fire penetration is increased by %d%%.
Venomous - Shots deal an additional %d%% weapon damage as nature in a radius %d ball, which applies numbing poison as per Exotic Munitions. This cannot occur more than once per turn.
Piercing - Shots deal %0.2f physical damage and maim the target, bleeding them for a further %0.2f physical damage over 5 turns and reducing all damage dealt by %d%%.
The physical damage dealt, armor penetration and save reduction will increase with your Physical Power.]], [[混合你的彈藥, 造成更強力的效果:
燃燒彈- 受到爆炸襲擊的目標護甲和豁免減少 %d 持續 3 回合, 你的物理和火焰穿透增加 %d%%.
劇毒彈- 造成 %d%% 自然武器傷害，傷害半徑 %d , 並施加麻痹毒素效果. 每回合最多生效一次.
穿甲彈- 造成 %0.2f 物理傷害並使目標流血, 5 回合內造成 %0.2f 物理傷害並減少他們造成的傷害 %d%%.
物理傷害、護甲和豁免削減受物理強度加成。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/pugilism.lua"

t("Striking Stance", "攻擊姿態", "talent name")
t([[Increases your Accuracy by %d, the damage multiplier of your striking talents (Pugilism and Finishing Moves) by %d%%, and reduces all damage taken by %d.
		The offensive bonuses scale with your Dexterity and the damage reduction with your Strength.]], [[增加你 %d 命中。你攻擊系技能 ( 拳術、終結技 ) 傷害增加 %d%% , 同時減少 %d 受到的傷害。
		受敏捷影響，傷害按比例加成。傷害減免受力量值加成。]], "tformat")
t("Double Strike", "雙重打擊", "talent name")
t("@Source@ throws two quick punches.", "@Source@快速打出兩次拳擊。", "_t")
t([[Deliver two quick punches that deal %d%% damage each, and switch your stance to Striking Stance. If you already have Striking Stance active and Double Strike isn't on cooldown, this talent will automatically replace your normal attacks (and trigger the cooldown).
		If either jab connects, you earn one combo point. At talent level 4 or greater, if both jabs connect, you'll earn two combo points.]], [[對目標進行 2 次快速打擊，每次打擊造成 %d%% 傷害並使你的姿態切換爲攻擊姿態，如果你已經在攻擊姿態且此技能已就緒，那麼此技能會自動取代你的普通攻擊 ( 並觸發冷卻 )。 
		任何一次打擊都會使你獲得 1 點連擊點。在等級 4 或更高等級時若 2 次打擊都命中你可以獲得 2 點連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Spinning Backhand", "旋風打擊", "talent name")
t("@Source@ lashes out with a spinning backhand.", "@Source@衝出去打出旋風打擊。", "_t")
t([[Attack your foes in a frontal arc with a spinning backhand, doing %d%% damage. If you're not adjacent to the target, you'll step forward as you spin, gaining up to %d%% bonus damage, which increases the farther you move.
		This attack will remove any grapples you're maintaining, and earn one combo point (or one combo point per attack that connects, if the talent level is 4 or greater).]], [[對你面前的敵人使用一次旋風打擊，造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		如果你離目標較遠，旋轉時你會自動前行，根據移動距離增加至多 %d%% 傷害。 
		此次攻擊會移除任何你正在維持的抓取效果並增加 1 點連擊點。 
		在等級 4 或更高時，你每次連擊均會獲得 1 點連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Axe Kick", "斧踢", "talent name")
t("@Source@ raises their leg and snaps it downward in a devastating axe kick.", "@Source@擡起腿，迅速踢出毀滅性的斧踢。", "_t")
t([[Deliver a devastating axe kick dealing %d%% damage. If the blow connects your target is brain damaged, causing all talents to fail for %d turns and earning 2 combo points.
		This effect cannot be saved against, though it can be dodged and checks confusion immunity.]], [[ 施展一次毀滅性的踢技，造成 %d%% 傷害。
		如果攻擊命中，對方的大腦受到傷害，不能使用技能，持續 %d 回合，同時你獲得 2 連擊點。]], "tformat")
t("Flurry of Fists", "流星拳", "talent name")
t("@Source@ lashes out with a flurry of fists.", "@Source@衝出去打出流星拳。", "_t")
t([[Lashes out at the target with three quick punches that each deal %d%% damage.
		Earns one combo point. If your talent level is 4 or greater, this instead earns one combo point per blow that connects.]], [[對目標造成 3 次快速打擊，每擊造成 %d%% 傷害。 
		此攻擊使你得到 1 點連擊點。 
		在等級 4 或更高時，你每次連擊都可以獲得 1 點連擊點。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/reflexes.lua"

t("Shoot Down", "強制擊落", "talent name")
t("#Source# shoots down '#Target#'!", "#Source#擊落了'#Target#'！", "logCombat")
t([[Your reflexes are lightning-fast, if you spot a projectile (arrow, shot, spell, ...) you can instantly shoot at it without taking a turn to take it down.
		You can shoot down up to %d projectiles.
		In addition, your heightened senses also reduce the speed of incoming projectiles by %d%%, and prevents your own projectiles from striking you.]], [[你的反射像閃電一樣快, 如果你發現一個拋射物 (箭矢, 彈丸, 法術, ...) 你可以不消耗時間立刻射擊之。
		最多可同時擊落 %d 個拋射物。
		此外, 射向你的拋射物飛行速度下降 %d%% ，你的拋射物不再擊中你自己。]], "tformat")
t("Intuitive Shots", "直覺射擊", "talent name")
t([[Activating this talent enhances your reflexes to incredible levels.  Each time you are attacked in melee, you have a %d%% chance to fire off a defensive shot off in time to intercept the attack, evading it and dealing %d%% archery damage.
		This cannot damage the same target more than once per turn.]], [[激活這個技能將你的反應提升到令人難以置信的水平. 每當你被近身攻擊, 你有 %d%% 機率射出一箭攔截攻擊, 躲閃攻擊並造成 %d%% 傷害.
		該技能每回合觸發最多一次.]], "tformat")
t("Sentinel", "哨兵", "talent name")
t("%s's %s is disrupted by the shot!", "%s的%s被射擊干擾了！", "logSeen")
t([[You take close notice of the target for the next 5 turns. If they attempt to use a non-instant talent you react with incredible speed, firing a shot dealing 25%% damage that causes the talent to fail and go on cooldown.
This shot is instant, cannot miss, and puts %d other talents on cooldown for %d turns.]], [[你在接下來的 5 回合內密切關注目標. 當其使用非瞬間技能時, 你立刻做出反應, 射出一箭造成 25%% 傷害打斷技能並使其進入冷卻.
該攻擊爲瞬間擊中, 必中, 並使其它 %d 個技能進入冷卻 %d 回合.]], "tformat")
t("Escape", "逃脫", "talent name")
t([[You put all your focus into escaping combat for 4 turns. While under this effect you gain %d%% increased resistance to all damage, %0.1f increased stamina regeneration, immunity to stun, pin, daze and slowing effects and %d%% increased movement speed. 
Any action other than movement will cancel this effect.]], [[你專注逃跑 4 回合. 處於此狀態時增加 %d%% 所有傷害抗性, %0.1f 體力恢復, 免疫震懾, 定身, 眩暈和減速效果並增加 %d%% 移動速度. 
除移動外的任何行動將終止該效果。]], "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/skirmisher-slings.lua"

t("Sling Supremacy", "投石索精通", "talent name")
t([[Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using slings.
		Also, increases your reload rate by %d.]], [[使用投石索時提高 %d%% 武器傷害，獲得 30 物理強度。
		同時增加 %d 裝填效果。]], "tformat")
t("Swift Shot", "快速射擊", "talent name")
t("Double Archery (#LIGHT_GREEN#%d%%#LAST# of a turn)", "雙倍弓箭速度 (#LIGHT_GREEN#%d%%#LAST# 回合)", "tformat")
t([[Fire off a quick sling bullet for %d%% damage at double your normal attack speed, as well as increasing your attack speed by %d%% for 5 turns.
		Each time you move, the cooldown of this talent is reduced by 1.]], [[發射一枚快速的石彈，造成 %d%% 傷害，攻擊速度是你普通攻擊的兩倍。增加你攻擊速度 %d%% ，持續5回合。
		移動將會降低技能冷卻 1 回合。]], "tformat")
t("Hurricane Shot", "颶風連射", "talent name")
t("Take aim and unload up to %d shots for %d%% weapon damage each against random enemies inside a cone. Each enemy can only be hit once (twice for talent level 3 and higher). Using Swift Shot lowers the cooldown by 1.", "最多發射 %d 顆彈矢，每顆對錐形範圍內的敵人造成 %d%% 武器傷害。每個敵人只能被攻擊 1 次（當技能等級在 3 級或更高時爲 2 次）。使用快速射擊技能會降低冷卻時間 1 回合。", "tformat")
t("Bombardment", "連環炮擊", "talent name")
t("Your Shoot talent now costs %d stamina but fires %d times for %d%% damage per shot.", "你的基礎射擊技能消耗 %d 體力，發射 %d 石彈，每顆造成 %d%% 傷害。", "tformat")


------------------------------------------------
section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/techniques/sling.lua"

t("Sling Mastery", "投石索專精", "talent name")
t([[Increases weapon damage by %d%% and physical power by 30 when using slings.
		Also, increases your reload rate by %d.]], [[使用投石索時提高 %d%% 武器傷害，獲得 30 物理強度。
		同時增加 %d 裝填效果。]], "tformat")
t("Eye Shot", "致盲射擊", "talent name")
t("%s resists!", "%s抵抗了效果！", "logSeen")
