section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/uber/wil.lua"

t("Draconic Will", "龍族意志", "talent name")
t("Be close to the draconic world", "熟悉龍之世界", "_t")
t([[Your body is like that of a drake, easily resisting detrimental effects.
		For 5 turns, no detrimental effects may target you.]], [[你的身體如巨龍般強韌，可以輕易抵抗負面效果。 
		在 5 回合內對負面效果免疫。]], "tformat")
t("Meteoric Crash", "落星", "talent name")
t("Have witnessed a meteoric crash", "曾親眼目睹過隕石墜落", "_t")
t("%s resists the stun!", "%s抵抗了震懾！", "logSeen")
t([[When casting damaging spells or mind attacks, the release of your willpower can call forth a meteor to crash down near your foes.
		The meteor deals %0.2f fire and %0.2f physical damage in radius 2 and stuns enemies for 3 turns.
		Lava is created in radius 3 around the impact dealing %0.2f fire damage per turn for 8 turns.  This will overwrite tiles that already have modified terrain.
		You and your allies take no damage from either effect.

		Additionally, your fire damage bonus and resistance penetration is set to your current highest damage bonus and resistance penetration. This applies to all fire damage you deal.
		The damage scales with your Spellpower or Mindpower.]], [[在施展傷害類魔法或精神攻擊時，你會釋放意念，召喚一顆隕石砸向附近敵人。
		隕石在 2 碼半徑內造成 %0.2f 火焰和 %0.2f 物理傷害，震懾敵人 3 回合。
		周圍 3 碼半徑的地形將會被衝擊轉換成岩漿，每回合造成 %0.2f 火焰傷害，持續 8 回合。
		你和你的盟友不會受到隕石的傷害。

		另外，你的火焰傷害加成和穿透將被設置成你最高的傷害加成和穿透，這對你造成的所有火焰傷害都有效。
		受精神強度或法術強度影響，傷害按比例加成。]], "tformat")
t("Garkul's Revenge", "加庫爾的復仇", "talent name")
t("Possess and wear two of Garkul's artifacts and know all about Garkul's life", "裝備加庫爾的兩件寶物並且瞭解加庫爾的一生", "_t")
t("Garkul's spirit is with you. You now deal 1000%% more damage to constructs and 20%% more damage to humanoids and giants.", "加庫爾之魂與你同在，你現在能對建築類造成 1000%% 額外傷害，對人形生物和巨人造成 20%% 額外傷害。", "tformat")
t("Hidden Resources", "潛能爆發", "talent name")
t("Have been close to death(killed a foe while below 1 HP)", "曾經接近死亡（在低於 1HP 情況下殺死 1 個敵人）", "_t")
t([[You focus your mind on the task at hand, regardless of how dire the situation is.
		For 5 turns, none of your talents use any resources.]], [[在嚴峻的形勢面前，你集中意念進入心如止水的狀態。
		在 5 回合內，所有技能不消耗任何能量。]], "tformat")
t("Lucky Day", "幸運日", "talent name")
t("Be lucky already (at least +5 luck)", "擁有大運氣。（至少有+5幸運屬性）", "_t")
t("Every day is your lucky day! You gain a permanent +40 luck bonus and 10%% to move out of the way of every attack.", "每天都是幸運日！幸運永久 +40，有 10%% 機率閃避所有攻擊。", "tformat")
t("Unbreakable Will", "堅定意志", "talent name")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE#%s's unbreakable will shrugs off the effect!", "#LIGHT_BLUE#%s 的堅定意志豁免了此效果！", "logSeen")
t([[Your will is so strong that you simply ignore mental effects used against you.
		This effect can only occur once every 5 turns.]], [[你的意志如此堅定，可以忽視對你造成的精神效果。 
		這一技能每 5 回合最多觸發一次。]], "tformat")
t("Spell Feedback", "反魔干擾", "talent name")
t("Antimagic", "反魔法", "_t")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE##Source# punishes #Target# for casting a spell!", "#LIGHT_BLUE##Source#懲罰了#Target#的施法!", "logCombat")
t([[Your will is a shield against assaults from crazed arcane users.
		Each time that you take damage from a spell, you punish the spellcaster with %0.2f mind damage.
		Also, they will suffer a 35%% spell failure chance (with duration equal to the cooldown of the spell they used on you).
		Note: this talent has a cooldown.]], [[你的意志是對抗邪惡魔法師的盾牌。 
		每當你受到魔法傷害，你會懲罰施法者，使其受到 %0.2f 的精神傷害。 
		同時，它們在對你使用的技能進入冷卻的回合中，會受到 35%% 法術失敗率懲罰。
		注意：該技能有冷卻時間。]], "tformat")
t("Mental Tyranny", "靈魂之怒", "talent name")
t("Have dealt over 50000 mind damage", "曾造成50000點精神傷害", "_t")
t([[Transcend the physical and rule over all with an iron will!
		While this sustain is active, 33%% of your damage is converted into mind damage.
		Additionally, you gain +30%% mind resistance penetration, and +10%% mind damage.]], [[用鋼鐵般的意志驅使整個身體。 
		當此技能激活時，你 33%% 的傷害會轉化爲精神傷害。 
		此外，你獲得 30%% 精神抵抗穿透並增加 10%% 精神傷害。]], "tformat")
t("Unlocked the Fallen evolution", "解鎖墮落者進階", "_t")
t("Committed a heinous act", "幹出一件惡行", "_t")
t("Fallen", "墮落者", "_t")
t("#CRIMSON#You give in to the darkness. You have fallen!", "#CRIMSON#你投身於黑暗。你墮落了！", "say")
t([[The code of the Sun Paladins can be a heavy burden.	 Wouldn't you like to let go?
		#{italic}##GREY#To give in to the darkness?#LAST##{normal}#
		
		#CRIMSON#This evolution fundamentally alters your class and character in a huge way. Do not take it lightly.#LAST#

		Any offensive combat techniques or unlockable Celestial talent trees you know will be exchanged for cursed versions, allowing you to cut a bloody trail through enemies, turning your radiance to gloom, and more while also gaining new combat styles and defenses.

		The following talent trees are swapped:
		- #GOLD#Radiance#LAST# turns into #CRIMSON#Gloom#LAST#: Project onto others your own hate, hindering them
		- #GOLD#Guardian#LAST# turns into #CRIMSON#Crimson Templar#LAST#: Use the power of blood to control and defeat the fools that oppose you
		- #GOLD#Crusader#LAST# turns into #CRIMSON#Dark Sun#LAST#: Call upon the energies of dead suns to crush your foes

		You will learn the following talents trees:
		- #CRIMSON#Bloodstained#LAST#: Make your foes bleed!
		- #CRIMSON#Darkside#LAST#: Every light casts a shadow, yours is powerful indeed
		- #CRIMSON#Hatred#LAST#: Manifest your hatred through bleeding
		- #CRIMSON#Dirge#LAST#: Sing of death and sorrow to strengthen your resolve

		You will forget the following talent trees, refunding any talent points: Shield Offense, Two-handed Assault.
		Also the cost of any talents of the Combat Techniques tree will be converted to hate instead of stamina.
		]], [[太陽騎士的行動守則也是一個重擔。你有沒有想過將其拋棄？
		#{italic}##GREY#並投身黑暗？#LAST##{normal}#

		#CRIMSON#此進階會完全顛覆你的職業並大幅度改變你的人物。不要輕易選擇。#LAST#

		你所知的所有攻擊性格鬥系或可解鎖的天空系技能樹都會被替換爲詛咒的版本，使你能夠一邊散發着黑暗的光輝一邊在敵軍中殺出一條血路，並且獲得新的戰鬥風格和防禦能力。

		以下技能樹將被替換：
		- #GOLD#光輝#LAST#變爲#CRIMSON#黑暗光環#LAST#：將你的憎恨投射到他人身上以阻礙它們
		- #GOLD#守護#LAST#變爲#CRIMSON#血紅守衛#LAST#：使用鮮血的力量控制並打倒那些敢於反抗你的愚民
		- #GOLD#十字軍#LAST#變爲#CRIMSON#無光之陽#LAST#：呼喚死星的力量來粉碎你的敵人

		你將學會以下的技能樹：
		- #CRIMSON#血染#LAST#：讓你的敵人血流成河！
		- #CRIMSON#背光面#LAST#：所有光明都會產生陰影，而你的尤其強大
		- #CRIMSON#憎恨#LAST#：將你的憎恨化爲傷痕和鮮血
		- #CRIMSON#輓歌#LAST#：對悲傷和死亡的歌頌增強着你的信念

		你將遺忘以下技能樹，並返還所有技能點：雙手戰技和盾牌攻擊。
		同時你戰鬥技巧系的所有技能都將消耗仇恨而非體力。
		]], "tformat")


