t("Kryl-Feijan", "卡洛·斐濟", "entity name")
t("This huge demon is covered in darkness. The ripped flesh of its \"mother\" still hangs from its sharp claws.", "這隻巨大的惡魔被黑暗所包圍。它的“母親”的碎肉仍懸掛在它的利爪上。", "_t")
t("and devoured as a demonic breakfast", "並作爲惡魔的午餐", "_t")
t("human", "人類", "entity subtype")
t("A female Human with twisted sigils scored into her naked flesh. Her wrists and ankles are sore and hurt by ropes and chains. You can discern great beauty beyond the stains of blood covering her skin.", "一位赤裸並且全身刻有扭曲符文的女人。她的四肢被鐐銬綁在了祭臺上。儘管她的皮膚上滿是鮮血，你仍然能發現她的美麗。", "_t")
