t("elf", "精靈", "entity subtype")
t("humanoid", "人形生物", "entity type")
t("Black-robed Elves with a mad look in their eyes.", "穿着黑色長袍的精靈，他們的眼中滿是瘋狂。", "_t")
t("Melinda", "米琳達", "_t")
t([[The woman seems to be freed from her bonds.
She stumbles on her feet, her naked body still dripping in blood. 'Please get me out of here!']], [[這個女人從鐐銬束縛中解脫了。
她蹣跚着向你走來，鮮血從她赤裸的皮膚上滴落。“請帶我離開這裏！”]], "_t")


