t("A horrid mass of pustulent flesh, sinew, and bone; this creature seems to constantly be in pain. Two heads glare malevolently at you, an intruder in its domain.", "一隻由無數碎肉、肌腱和骨頭組成的恐怖混合體，它看起來痛苦萬分。它的雙頭惡毒的看着你，因爲你闖入了它的地盤。", "_t")
