section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/dreadfell/npcs.lua"

t("vampire", "吸血鬼", "entity subtype")
t("The Master", "領主", "entity name")
t("A terrifying vampiric figure of power, with flowing robes and an intense aura of fright.  His cold, sinewy flesh seems to cling to this world through greed and malice, and his eyes betray a strength of mind beyond any puny mortal.  All nearby are utterly subservient to his will, though he stands aloof from them, as if to say he needs not the pathetic meddling of minions to help him overcome his foes.  Your eyes are drawn to a dark staff in his hands which seems to suck the very life from the air around it.  It looks ancient and dangerous and terrible, and the sight of it fills you with fervent desire.", "一個擁有強大力量的可怕吸血鬼，他的長袍無風自動，周身環繞着恐懼光環。他冰冷而強壯的肉體似乎在向世界宣告着貪婪和怨恨，他的眼神透露着一股睥睨天下的自信。周圍的不死族都完全服從於他，儘管如此，他還是表現出厭惡的神情，就好像他不需要這些廢物來禦敵一樣。你的目光被他手裏的黑色法杖所吸引，這根法杖似乎在不斷的吸取周圍的活力。它看起來古老而可怕，看到它的瞬間，你心底的慾望被徹底點燃了。", "_t")
t("and raised as his tortured undead thrall", "並作爲他的不死僕從永受折磨", "_t")
t("It has been months since the hero cleansed the Dreadfell, yet rumours are growing: evil is back.", "自從英雄肅清了恐懼王座後已經過去數個月了，但是仍然流傳着謠言：有一股惡勢力重新掌握了那裏。", "_t")
t("Pale Drake", "亡靈德瑞克", "entity name")
t("A malevolent skeleton archmage that has taken control of the Dreadfell since the Master's demise.", "一位邪惡的骷髏法師，自從領主大人死後，他便繼承了恐懼王座。", "_t")
t("ghoul", "食屍鬼", "entity subtype")
t("Borfast the Broken", "扭曲的波法斯特", "entity name")
t([[Thick skin hangs loosely from this short, shambling form. Tufts of hair sticking out from its chin give evidence of a once magnificent dwarven beard. Half its face seems to have been seared in acid at some point, the flesh melted away from the skull and an eyeball drooping low from its socket. There is a unique sadness to its eyes, and a slump of resignation to its gait.
What proud hero of renown was this before he was condemned to such a terrible fate?]], "在你面前的是一隻步履蹣跚、肌肉鬆弛的——怪物。從他下巴中伸出的濃密鬍鬚以及他的毛髮來看，這是一位矮人。看起來他的半邊臉曾經被硫酸潑過，血肉從他的臉部脫落，其中一隻眼睛從它的眼窩中掉了出來。他的獨眼有一種莫名的悲傷，透露着深深的無奈。如此威風的英雄人物怎會落得如此下場？", "_t")
t("ghost", "幽靈", "entity subtype")
t("Aletta Soultorn", "阿蕾塔·蘇爾頓", "entity name")
t([[What once must have been an enchantingly beautiful Higher woman now looks to be a ghost of utter despair. Her thin, elegant form ripples gently in the air, whilst her tattered robes seem oddly still. The ghost's face looks jittery and pained whilst her wild, glowing eyes move rapidly back and forth in their sockets.
Now and then she seems to see something and her jaw pulls back, her whole face splitting apart as she shrieks an unholy cry of pain and torment.]], [[這隻幽靈以前肯定是一位高等人類美人。她瘦弱而優雅的身軀在空中輕輕的搖晃，但是她的長袍卻始終緊貼着身體。她的臉部除了瘋狂便是萬分的痛苦，她的眼睛在眼眶裏不安的來回轉動。
有時她會看到一些東西，她的下巴會突然收縮，分裂的臉部會發出一陣充滿痛苦和折磨的哀嚎。]], "_t")
t("and offered to her dark Master", "併爲她的不死主人永世效忠", "_t")
t("skeleton", "骷髏", "entity subtype")
t("undead", "亡靈", "entity type")
t("Filio Flightfond", "菲里奧·弗萊特馮德", "entity name")
t([[A short, furtive-looking skeleton with padded feet. He moves quickly and silently, and seems to meld into the shadows with ease. In one hand he holds a sling, and the other a short dagger.
There is a cunning air to his hollow skull, and his empty sockets reveal nothing of what tricks and tactics he has planned.]], [[一個矮小的猥瑣骷髏，它的腳底有着一層肉墊。他迅捷而隱蔽，並且擅長融入黑暗。他的左手拿着投石索，右手則拿着一柄匕首。
他中空的頭骨裏有着一團靈活的空氣，他空曠的眼孔中再也看不到任何的狡詐和詭計。]], "_t")
t("and offered to his dark Master", "併爲他的不死主人永世效忠", "_t")


