section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/golem-graveyard/grids.lua"

t("the remains of Atamathon", "阿塔瑪森的遺骸", "entity name")
t([[This giant golem was constructed by the Halflings during the Pyre Wars to fight the orcs, but was felled by Garkul the Devourer.
Its body is made of marble, its joints of solid voratun, and its sole eye of purest ruby; the other one seems to be missing. At over 40 feet tall, it towers above you.
Someone foolish has tried to reconstruct it, but was unable to complete the task; the golem needs another eye to be complete.]], [[ 這尊傀儡之王是由半身人在派爾大戰中爲對抗獸族製造的，但它卻被吞噬者加庫爾所摧毀。 
 它的軀幹是用大理石鑄造，關節部分則灌入沃瑞鉭銜接，一隻眼由純淨的紅寶石構成。它的另一隻眼睛似乎已經失落。四十多尺高的巨像似乎默默地俯視着你。 
 一些蠢貨似乎想要重塑他，但由於找不到那隻眼睛而沒有完成。]], "_t")
t("Atamathon", "阿塔瑪森", "_t")
t("It seems that your %s is made to fit inside the empty eye socket of Atamathon. This is probably very unwise.", "你手中%s的外形看上去似乎可以安裝到阿塔瑪森的空眼窩內，但也許這樣做並不明智。", "tformat")
t("The socket seems broken.", "插槽似乎已經損壞。", "log")
t("#LIGHT_RED#As you insert the gem the golem starts to shake. All its systems and magics are reactivating.", "#LIGHT_RED#當你插入寶石傀儡開始震動。它的系統和魔法被重新激活了。", "log")
t("#LIGHT_RED#Atamathon walks the world again, but without control.", "#LIGHT_RED#阿塔瑪森重新來到了世界，不過它失去了控制。", "log")
t("Activating defenses. Targetting hostile. **DESTRUCTION**!", "啓動防禦系統，瞄準目標，**啓動摧毀命令**！", "_t")
t("Cancel", "取消", "_t")
t("Insert", "插入", "_t")


