section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/golem-graveyard/npcs.lua"

t("Atamathon the Giant Golem", "傀儡之王阿塔瑪森", "entity name")
t("This giant golem was constructed by the Halflings during the Pyre Wars to fight the orcs, but was felled by Garkul the Devourer. Someone foolish has tried to reconstruct it, but has lost control of it, and now it rampages in search of its original creators, who are long dead. Its body is made of marble, its joints of solid voratun, and its eyes of purest ruby. At over 40 feet tall, it towers above you, and its crimson orbs seem to glow with rage.", "這隻巨大的傀儡是半身人在派爾紀對抗獸人時所造，但是被吞噬者加庫爾摧毀。有些笨蛋試圖重修它，但是控制核心已經丟失，現在它在瘋狂的尋找它的製造者——某個死了無數年的傢伙。它的軀體由花崗岩製成，它的關節由沃瑞鉭製成，它的眼睛則是純淨的紅寶石。它有着40英尺高，像鐵塔般站在你面前，它閃亮的紅寶石眼睛似乎散發着怒意。", "_t")
t("DESTROY!", "毀滅一切!", "_t")
t("LIFE-ENDING SYSTEMS ACTIVATED!", "屠殺系統已啓動!", "_t")
t("GLORY TO THE HALFLINGS!", "半身人萬歲!", "_t")
t("YOUR DEATH IS NECESSARY", "你的死亡必不可少", "_t")
t("ACTIVATING PAIN GIVING SUBMODULES!", "啓動痛苦強化模組!", "_t")
t("YOUR LIFE WILL END, PLEASE DO NOT RESIST!", "你的生命即將終結，不要試圖抵抗!", "_t")
t("RESISTANCE IS FUTILE, YOUR WILL BE EXTERMINATED!", "抵抗無用，你將被徹底毀滅!", "_t")
t("PLEASE STAY STEADY AS YOU ARE ERASED FROM THE WORLD!", "請你坐穩扶好，等待被移除出這個世界!", "_t")
t("EXECUTE PHASE COMMENCING!", "執行程序已啓動!", "_t")


