t("ominous, dark runed staff", "不祥的，黑暗符文的法杖", "_t")
t([[Carved with runes of power, this staff seems to have been made long ago, yet it bears no signs of tarnish.
Light around it seems to dim and you can feel its tremendous power simply by touching it.
The Sorcerers seem to have awakened its power.
#{italic}#"And lo they came to Amakthel himself, and thousands were killed in the assault on his throne, and three of the Godslayers were broken beneath his feet. But Falion with his dying breath pierced the great god on his knee with the icy sword Arkil, and seeing his opportunity Caldizar, leader of the Godslayers, advanced with the Staff of Absorption and struck a terrifying blow against Amakthel. So fell the greatest of the gods by the hands of his own children, and his face was forced into the dust."#{normal}#]], [[杖身銘刻着符文，這根法杖似乎是很久以前製造的，雖然它毫無侵蝕的痕跡。它周圍的光線會變的暗淡，當你觸摸它時可以感受到驚人的魔力。
惡魔法師們似乎喚醒了它的力量。
#{italic}#“終於他們直面了阿馬克泰爾，並且上千人犧牲在了他的王座前，其中有三名弒神者倒在了他的腳下。但是法利恩用他死前最後的力量將冰刃阿奇爾插入了真神的膝蓋，看到這一機會，凱爾帝勒，弒神者的首領，立刻上前並用吸能法杖對阿馬克泰爾造成了致命的一擊。這樣真神最終倒在了他自己的兒女手中，他的頭顱也化作了塵埃。”#{normal}#]], "_t")
