section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/last-hope-graveyard/zone.lua"

t("Last Hope Graveyard", "最後的希望墓地", "_t")
t("You were not the first here: the corpse was turned into an undead.", "你不是第一個來到這裏的：那個人的屍體已經變成了亡靈！", "log")
t("The corpse had a treasure!", "屍體上有寶物！", "log")
t("There is nothing there.", "那裏什麼也沒有。", "log")
t("In rich families the dead are sometimes put to rest with some treasures. However they also sometime protect the coffins with powerful curses. Open?", "一些富有人家在埋葬屍體時有時會用一些財寶陪葬。然而他們爲了保護棺材同樣也施予了強大的詛咒，你確定要打開麼？", "_t")
t("Open the coffin", "打開棺材", "_t")
t("#YELLOW#You hear all the doors being shattered into pieces.", "#YELLOW#你聽到所有的門都被打碎了。", "log")
t([[As you tread softly down the stairs a large stone slab slides into place behind you, blocking all retreat. The air is still and stuffy, and in this tight space you feel as if in a coffin, buried alive.

Adding to your unease is a rising feeling of dread, overwhelming fear in fact. A hall of doors lies ahead, and behind each you sense a power of great malevolence and unholy horror. At the end of the corridor you see a faint light beneath a large black door, and you have a vague sense that the other doors are enslaved to this one - obedient, subservient, and waiting...

You hear the sound of a woman sobbing, and every now and then it turns into a fit of pained moans and screams. They echo round the dark chamber and through the darkest parts of your mind, reminding you of every black deed and vile sin you have ever committed. Guilt, horror and terror flood through your thoughts, each competing for stronger control of your psyche. Your only clear thought is of escape, by whatever means you can find.]], [[當你躡手躡腳的進入時，你踩到了某個機關，身後落下了一塊巨石堵住了所有的退路。空氣又悶又熱，並且在這封閉的空間裏，你彷彿被活埋在棺材裏一樣。

使你感到不安的是一種恐懼感，一種超過畏懼的恐懼感。大廳的門就在前方，你能感受到門後潛藏的怨恨和邪惡能量。在轉角的盡頭你看到黑色的大門下面透出昏暗的燈光，並且你能模糊的感受到其他的門受牽制於這扇大門——順從，謙卑並且奴役……
    
你聽到一個女人的哭泣，時不時還夾雜着一聲痛苦的哀嚎和尖叫。聲音在密室裏迴盪並且通過黑暗傳入了你的大腦，提醒你所犯的每一項罪過。內疚、恐怖和害怕如潮水般襲來，它們每個都緊緊抓住了你的靈魂。你唯一的想法便是逃離此地，不擇一切手段。]], "_t")
t("Mausoleum", "陵墓", "_t")


