t("Murgol, the Yaech Lord", "奪魂魔領主穆格爾", "entity name")
t("You can feel the psionic waves of power come from this yaech.", "你可以在這隻奪魂魔身上感受到龐大的靈能。", "_t")
t("and flushed out to sea", "並被扔進海里", "_t")
t("humanoid", "人形生物", "entity type")
t("naga", "娜迦", "entity subtype")
t("naga tidewarden", "娜迦潮汐守衛", "entity name")
t("naga tidecaller", "娜迦潮汐呼喚者", "entity name")
t("A slithering noise accompanies the movement of this strange creature, whose snake-like tail gives rise to the body of a beautiful elf-like woman. As she moves her delicate hands water rises from the ground, and you feel that here is no mere monster, but a creature of awe and power.", "在這隻奇怪的生物爬行時伴隨着摩擦的噪聲，像蛇一樣的尾巴卻支撐着美麗動人的軀體。當她遊動時，她將面前的水擡向大地，你感到面前的不是怪物，而是令人敬畏的力量。", "_t")
t("naga nereid", "娜迦海衛", "entity name")
t("Green eyes stare out from behind strands of long, golden hair, which falls down in waves over smooth, pale skin. Your eyes are drawn to the bare flesh, but as they look further they see dark scales stretching out into a long serpent's tail. You look up as she moves, her hair parting to reveal a slim and beautiful face with high cheekbones and full lips. Yet for all the allure of this wondrous creature the terror of the serpentine tail sends shivers down your spine.", "綠色的眼睛後面是披落在白皙肩膀的金髮。你的眼睛被裸露的肌膚所吸引，但是當你往下看時，你會發現黑色的長蛇尾巴。當她移動時你看向她的臉部，在金髮之下是紅潤而美麗的臉龐，有着高顴骨和豐滿的嘴脣。雖然從各方面看來，她都很完美，但是仍掩飾不住你眼皮底下的蛇尾巴帶來的恐怖。", "_t")
t("Lady Nashva the Streambender", "激流盤旋者納紗瓦女士", "entity name")
t("Water circles slowly on the ground around this naga's tail. Her dark tail is coiled tight, making her look short, but her calm and confident stare assure you that she will not be easily overcome. As the water begins to rise around her the air starts to shimmer, and you feel her dark eyes are penetrating into you deeper than is comfortable.", "水流緩慢的圍繞着這位娜迦的尾巴旋轉。她黑色的尾巴蜷縮起來，使她看起來較爲矮小，但是她沉着而自信的臉龐使你感受到她無所畏懼。當水流在她周圍蒸騰時，星空都彷彿失去了光芒，你感到她的眼神看穿了你的內心。", "_t")
t("and brought back to Vargh for experimentations", "並被帶去瓦爾弗成爲實驗對象", "_t")


