t("humanoid", "人形生物", "entity type")
t("orc", "獸人", "entity subtype")
t("orc baby", "獸人寶寶", "entity name")
t("Crawling on all fours, this green-skinned creature is far from cute, with vicious little sharp teeth and nails, and slime still sticking to its skin.", "雖然只能用四肢在地上爬行，這隻綠皮生物和可愛卻絲毫沒有關聯。它有着鋒利的牙齒和指甲，並且它的皮膚上沾了一層粘糊糊的液體。", "_t")
t("orc child", "獸人兒童", "entity name")
t("This small orc has a malicious and greedy look in its eyes. Its veins pulse with new life and it moves with surprising speed. Though not fully developed you can still see the muscles forming on its long limbs, leading to clawed fingers and toes.", "這隻小獸人的眼裏透露着怨恨和貪婪。它有着旺盛的活力並能以驚人的速度移動。雖然還沒完全長大，但是你能看到他全身上下微微隆起的肌肉。", "_t")
t("young orc", "年輕獸人", "entity name")
t("This young orc is almost fully formed, with hard muscles prominently visible beneath its thick skin. Whilst it has lost some of the wild energy of its younger siblings you can see the gleams of intelligence and cold calculation behind its dark eyes.", "這隻獸人已經快成年了，它的皮膚下有着強壯的肌肉。雖然由於狂暴能量的影響它失去了許多兄弟姐妹，但你仍可以從他的眼中發現一閃而過的智慧和狡詐。", "_t")
t("orc mother", "獸人母體", "entity name")
t("Orc Greatmother", "巨型獸人母體", "entity name")
t([[This giant, bloated form towers above you. Mucus and slime ooze from every orifice, dripping onto the cavern floor. Orc children fight over the right to feed from her distended teats whilst small babies are regularly emerge from folds of flesh. The sight and the smell make you retch.
Here stands a tremendous form almost the size of a dragon. Bloated skin rises in thick folds, seeping viscous slime from its wide pores. Hundreds of hanging teats feed a small army of squabbling, fighting young orcs - only the toughest of them are able to gain the precious nutrients to grow stronger, the weaker ones left to wither on the mouldy floor. At the top of this towering hulk is a shrivelled head coated in long tangled hair. Dazed eyes peer out with a mixture of sadness and pain, but as they fix on you they turn to anger, the creature's face contorted with the fierce desire to protect its young.]], "站在我們面前的是一隻跟龍差不多體型的怪物。皮膚下鼓起了無數浮腫的肉塊，粗大的毛孔裏不斷流淌出粘稠的液體。上百個乳頭餵養了一批互相爭吵打鬥的獸人——只有最強壯的才能獲得補充營養的優先權，弱小的只能在地上等待死亡。數十個生殖器在不斷的抽動，不時的擠出新的獸人。在這隻怪物的頭頂是一頭蓬亂長髮的枯萎面容，茫然的眼神中混合着些許悲傷和痛苦。但是當她看到你時，她變的異常憤怒，她憤怒的面孔裏透露着她護子的決心。", "_t")
t("and given to the children as a plaything", "併成爲孩子們的玩具", "_t")
t("#PURPLE#As the orc greatmother falls you realize you have dealt a crippling blow to the orcs.", "#PURPLE#當獸人母體倒下時你意識到你對獸人部落造成了致命的打擊。", "log")


