t("The portal brought you to what seems to be a cell in the basement of the tower. You must escape!", "傳送門將你送到了這座高塔的一個小房間裏。你必須逃離！", "_t")
t("As you climb up the steps, you see Tannen standing with his drolem, reading a scrap of parchment.  As he reads, his eyes grow wider, and he starts sweating and pacing back and forth.  When he reaches to stuff it in his pocket, he sees you and jumps back like a startled cat.  \"No!  Not now!  You have no idea what's at stake!\"  He retrieves a fistful of brightly-colored flasks from his robes, and his drolem's eyes glow as it springs to life, metal screeching in an impressive imitation of a roar.", "當你爬上樓梯，你看到泰恩正和他的龍傀儡站在一起，手中拿着一張羊皮紙。在他閱讀的時候，他的眉頭緊皺，汗如雨下，不斷來回踱步着。當他攥起紙條試圖放進口袋裏的時候，他突然望見了你，如同一隻受驚嚇的貓一樣向後跳了幾步。“不！不是現在！你根本不懂，現在是生死攸關的時刻！”他從長袍中拿出一把彩色的小瓶子，身旁龍傀儡站了起來，眼睛放射出光芒，金屬的響聲如同真龍的吼叫一般，讓你印象深刻。", "_t")
t("Tannen's Tower", "泰恩之塔", "_t")


