section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/temple-of-creation/objects.lua"

t("bright pearl", "閃亮的珍珠", "_t")
t("Eldritch Pearl", "埃爾德里奇珍珠", "entity name")
t("Thousands of years spent inside the temple of creation have infused this pearl with the fury of rushing water. It pulses light.", "造物主神廟千年的時間裏，這顆珍珠它被注入了波濤的憤怒。它向外輻射着光芒。", "_t")
t("tract", "小短文", "entity name")
t("A tract revealing the history of the Nagas.", "一篇講述娜迦歷史的小短文。", "_t")
t("note", "筆記", "entity name")
t("A note.", "一份筆記。", "_t")
t("ornate orichalcum trident", "華麗的奧利哈剛三叉戟", "_t")
t("Legacy of the Naloren", "納魯精靈的饋贈", "entity name")
t([[This incredibly beautiful -- and powerful -- trident is made of the rare metal orichalcum. An amazing pearl is seated in head of the trident, as it spreads into three razor sharp prongs.
It is imbued with the greatest strengths of all of the most powerful Naga warriors.
Slasul gave it to you as a sign of his faith in you. It is a sign of hope for all of the Naloren race, that one outside of their tribe could be so trusted.]], [[這柄擁有着強大力量的三叉戟通體由奧利哈剛金屬打造而成。一顆閃亮的珍珠鑲嵌在其頂端，向前延伸而出的，是三道鋒利的三叉戟刃。
它被灌輸了娜迦即納魯精靈一族最強大戰士的力量。
現在，薩拉蘇爾將它賜予你，作爲他對你的信任。同時，它也寄託了納魯一族的希望，只有你能受到他們如此的信任。]], "_t")


