section "game/modules/tome/init.lua"

t("Tales of Maj'Eyal: Age of Ascendancy", "馬基·埃亞爾的傳說：卓越紀", "init.lua long_name")
t([[Welcome to Maj'Eyal.

This is the Age of Ascendancy. After over ten thousand years of strife, pain and chaos the known world is at last at relative peace.
The last effects of the #FF0000#Spellblaze#WHITE# have been tamed. The land slowly heals itself and the civilisations rebuild themselves after the Age of Pyre.

It has been one hundred and twenty-two years since the Allied Kingdoms were established under the rule of #14fffc#Toknor#ffffff# and his wife #14fffc#Mirvenia#ffffff#.
Together they ruled the kingdoms with fairness and brought prosperity to both Halflings and Humans.
The King died of old age fourteen years ago, and his son #14fffc#Tolak#ffffff# is now King.

The Elven kingdoms are quiet. The Shaloren Elves in their home of Elvala are trying to make the world forget about their role in the Spellblaze and are living happy lives under the leadership of #14fffc#Aranion Gayaeil#ffffff#.
The Thaloren Elves keep to their ancient tradition of living in the woods, ruled as always by #14fffc#Nessilla Tantaelen#ffffff# the wise.

The Dwarves of the Iron Throne have maintained a careful trade relationship with the Allied Kingdoms for nearly one hundred years, yet not much is known about them, not even their leader's name.

While the people of Maj'Eyal know that the mages helped put an end to the terrors of the Spellblaze, they also did not forget that it was magic that started those events. As such, mages are still shunned from society, if not outright hunted down.
Still, this is a golden age. Civilisations are healing the wounds of thousands of years of conflict, and the Humans and the Halflings have made a lasting peace.

You are an adventurer, set out to discover wonders, explore old places, and venture into the unknown for wealth and glory.
]], [[歡迎來到馬基埃亞爾的世界！

現在的埃亞爾大陸是卓越紀。在長達一萬年的衝突痛苦和混亂之後，我們所知的世界終於進入了一個相對和平的時期。
#FF0000#“魔法大爆炸”#WHITE#所造成的影響已經漸漸減輕，大地的傷痕也慢慢開始癒合。在派爾紀末，各個文明也紛紛開始重建家園。
#14fffc#圖庫納國王#ffffff#和他的半身人皇后#14fffc#米雯尼雅#ffffff#建立並統治聯合王國已有122年了。
在他們的統治下，王國天下太平，無論是人類還是半身人的居住地都欣欣向榮，一片繁華。
十四年前，國王因年紀過大而去世了，他的兒子，#14fffc#托拉克#ffffff#繼承了王位。

精靈們的王國安詳而平和。住在埃爾瓦拉的永恆精靈們試圖讓世界忘記他們在魔法大爆炸中扮演的角色，在精靈王#14fffc#艾倫尼恩·加威爾#ffffff#的統治下快樂地生活着。
而自然精靈則遵從古老的傳統，住在森林當中，由不朽的賢者#14fffc#奈希拉·坦泰蘭#ffffff#統領。

一百年來，鋼鐵王座的矮人們一直小心謹慎的和聯合王國的人類們開展貿易活動，儘管他們的種族爲人所知甚少，甚至也不知道他們的統治者姓甚名誰。

儘管馬基埃亞爾大陸上的居民都知道是魔法師們幫忙終止了恐怖的魔法大爆炸，但他們也沒有忘記正是魔法本身造成了這場災難。因此儘管大家並沒有公然抓捕魔法師，法師們也寧願避開公衆生活。
無論如何，這是個黃金時代，所有的文明在過去數千年中經歷的不幸正在好轉，甚至人類和半身人之間已經形成了長久的和平。

你是一個冒險者，追尋古老的力量、寶藏和榮耀。你勇敢的踏入被遺忘的大陸、未被開發的森林，和神祕封印的廢墟。在這個所謂的和平年代，誰也不知道最終會找到些什麼。
]], "init.lua description")
t("Though magic is still shunned in Maj'Eyal, rumours abound of secret havens of mages.", "儘管魔法在馬基埃亞爾大陸遭到排斥，不過傳說仍然有一個法師的祕密庇護所。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Rush talent lets you close in on an enemy quickly and daze them, disabling them whilst you hack down their friends.", "衝鋒技能可以讓你快速接近敵人並眩暈目標，你可以藉此時機擊倒它的同伴。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Stunning an opponent slows down their movement and reduces their damage output, giving you the opportunity to tactically reposition or finish them off at less risk.", "震懾可以減緩目標的移動速度，降低其傷害輸出，這樣可以爲你製造機會解決它們，或者降低他們對你的威脅。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Movement is key on the battlefield. A stationary fighter will become a dead fighter. One must always seek the position of greatest tactical advantage and continue to re-evaluate throughout the battle.", "移動是戰鬥制勝的關鍵。一個固定不動的戰士只會變成一個死的戰士。戰鬥過程中你必須隨時調整你的走位以保持你的優勢。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("In the Age of Pyre the orcs learned the secrets of magic, and with their newfound powers nearly overcame the whole of Maj'Eyal.", "在派爾紀，獸人祕密學習了魔法，他們恐怖的魔法力量差一點毀滅了整個埃亞爾大陸。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The orcs once terrorised the whole continent. In the Age of Ascendancy they were rendered extinct, but rumours abound of hidden groups biding their time to return.", "獸人曾經給整個大陸帶來了一場浩劫。在卓越紀，他們幾乎已經滅絕，不過傳言他們正準備祕密地捲土重來。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Intense willpower lets wyrmics take on the natural powers of dragons.", "高強度的意志使龍戰士可以獲得龍族的自然力量。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Alchemists can transmute gems to create fiery explosions, and are known to travel with a sturdy golem for extra protection.", "煉金術士可以轉化寶石製造強大的爆炸，同時他們還可以召喚傀儡來守護他們。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("In the Age of Pyre the giant golem Atamathon was built with the sole purpose of stopping the orcish leader Garkul the Devourer. The golem was single-handedly destroyed by the orc, who then slaughtered an army of thousands before the demonic fighter was finally slain.", "在派爾紀，人們建造了傀儡之王阿塔瑪森以對抗獸人首領吞噬者加庫爾所領導的獸人軍隊。加庫爾不僅孤身一人親自幹掉了傀儡王，在他倒下之前，還單槍匹馬斬殺了上千人的部隊。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("None know what the Sher'Tul looked like, or what caused them all to disappear thousands of years ago. Their rare ruins are a source of mystery and terror.", "無人知曉夏·圖爾人的長相，也沒有人知道爲什麼他們在幾千年前突然消失了。至今我們仍能從他們僅存的廢墟里感受到他們的神祕和恐怖。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("In deep places dark things dwell beyond description or understanding. None know the source of these hideous horrors.", "地城深處潛藏着無法用語言描述或理解的黑暗事物，無人知道它們是從哪裏而來。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Who knows what dark thoughts drive people to necromancy? Its art is as old as magic itself, and its creations have plagued all the races since the earliest memories.", "天知道是怎樣的墮落思想才能使一個人成爲死靈法師。這門藝術就像魔法一樣歷史悠久，它的出現在最初的歲月裏給所有種族帶來了非常的劫難。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Some say that in their early days the Shaloren kings experimented with necromancy to preserve their flesh after death, but with little success. The Shaloren vehemently deny this.", "傳說很早以前永恆精靈的王侯們利用死靈法術進行試驗，試圖讓他們死後的肉體仍能永葆青春。不過他們並沒有成功。但永恆精靈們都否認這個傳說的真實性。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("120 years ago Toknor and Mirvenia united the human and halfling kingdoms and wiped out the orcish race, thus establishing the Age of Ascendancy.", "120年前，圖庫納與米雯尼雅將人類與半身人的王國聯合起來，擊潰了獸人軍團，自此開啓了卓越紀元。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("\"The Spellblaze tore Eyal apart and nearly brought about the end of all civilisation. Two thousand years on its shadow still hangs over many lands, and the prideful mages have never been forgiven their place in bringing it about.", "魔法大爆炸撕裂了埃亞爾大陸，整個文明差點被徹底摧毀。兩千年歲月已過，爆炸的陰影依然籠罩着很多地區。那些高傲法師們鑄成的大錯令人們永生難忘。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Some are cursed with mental powers beyond their full control, turning them to a dark life powered by hatred.", "某些被詛咒者承受了超出他們控制的靈魂力量，終其一生都活在憎恨和黑暗中。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Dreadfell has always been shunned for its haunted crypts, but of late rumours tell of a darker and more terrible power in residence.", "恐懼王座一直以來都因鬧鬼而爲人所避諱。但最近有流言傳出，有位帶着更加強大的黑暗力量的主人統治了此地。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Some Sher'Tul artifacts can still be found in hidden places, but it is said they are not to be trifled with.", "雖然有人說還能在某些未知的地方找到夏·圖爾的上古神器，不過普通人最好不要接近那種地方。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Drakes and wyrms are the strongest natural creatures in the world, capable of powers far beyond most other beings.", "龍與巨龍是這個世界上最強大的自然生物，它們所擁有的力量遠在其他生物之上。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Giant worms tear open huge passageways through the deserts in the west. It is said great riches lie buried beneath the sand, still decorating the corpses of those who went there seeking great riches.", "西部沙漠中的巨型蠕蟲挖掘出了很多巨大的通道。傳說在那沙洞深處埋藏着很多誘人的寶物。不過除了寶物之外，更多的便是那些尋寶人的屍體。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Arcane Blades employ a fusion of melee and magical combat. Their training is harsh but the most dedicated rise to great powers.", "奧術之刃是一個混合了魔法與近戰的職業。他們的訓練非常嚴酷，同時他們的力量也極其強大。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Wild infusions call upon the powers of nature to protect the flesh and rid oneself of afflictions.", "自然紋身可以召喚自然的力量來保護你的肉體免於傷害。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Shield runes act instantly, letting one protect oneself quickly whilst also preparing to flee or launch a counter attack.", "護盾符文爲瞬發技能，可以在你準備逃跑或者反擊的同時提供防護。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Greater training in the use of armour lets it be used more effectively, blocking more damage and reducing the chance of an enemy hitting a critical spot.", "高級的護甲訓練可以有效提高你的防護能力，使你格擋更多傷害並降低你受到致命一擊的機率。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Thick Skin talent reduces all incoming damage, letting you survive for longer before needing to heal.", "硬化皮膚技能可以降低所有受到的傷害，讓你在能夠使用治療以前存活更長的時間。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Regeneration infusions act over several turns, letting you anticipate damage that will be taken and prepare for it.", "恢復紋身的效果持續數個回合，開啓後每回合會恢復一定的生命值，使你的戰鬥更加從容不迫。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("In the most dire circumstances teleportation can be the best escape, but is not without risk.", "大多數情況下，傳送技能是逃命的首選方法，不過也有一定的風險。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Ziguranth are an ancient order vehemently opposed to magic. Some have become so attuned to nature they can resist arcane forces with their will alone.", "伊格蘭斯是一個古老的反魔陣營，他們中的一些人可以依靠自身的意志力來抵抗奧術能量。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Records say that giants once lived civilised lives, with mastery of many crafts and sciences. Now, though, they have adopted nomadic cultures, turning hostile against those that encroach on their lands.", "據史書記載，巨人族曾經也有高度發達的文明，掌握着許多手工和科學技術。不過現在他們已經適應了遊牧生活，他們會攻擊任何試圖侵略的敵人。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Zigur was founded by escapees of Conclave experiments during the Allure wars between humans and halflings.", "伊格是由厄流紀人類與半身人戰爭中的孔克雷夫實驗逃亡者創立的。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Thaloren and Shaloren elves have never had good relations, and have been outright hostile since the Spellblaze devastated many Thaloren lands.", "自然精靈與永恆精靈之間關係一直不佳，自從魔法大爆炸摧毀了很多自然精靈大陸之後，他們之間更是相互敵視。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The third elven race, the Naloren, were rendered extinct after a huge cataclysm swept the eastern side of Maj'Eyal into the sea.", "精靈第三分支，納魯精靈，在魔法大爆炸將馬基埃亞爾的東部地區沉入海底後，徹底滅絕。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Trolls were once seen as little more than beasts or pests, but the orcs trained them up for use in war and they became much more intelligent and fearsome.", "巨魔的力量原先不過與野獸和毒蟲差不多，不過後來獸人因爲戰爭的需要對它們進行了訓練。現在他們變得更聰明更可怕。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Some say that the foot of a halfling is lucky to own. Halflings do not take well to those who enquire too forcefully.", "有人說半身人的腳是幸運護身符。對於這一點半身人可並不贊成。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Nargol empire was once the largest force in Maj'Eyal, but a combination of the Spellblaze and orcish attacks have dwindled it into insignificance.", "納格爾王國曾經是馬基埃亞爾最強大的國家。但是經歷了魔法大爆炸和獸人的入侵之後他們已經變得無足輕重了。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Some of the most powerful undead do not fall easily, and only through extreme persistence can they be put to rest.", "那些最強大的不死族並不是那麼容易被打敗的，只有通過不懈的戰鬥才能將它們徹底置於死地。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("History says little of the ancient race of yeeks that lived in halfling territory, but vanished before the time of the Spellblaze.", "據史書記載，有極少數的古代奪心魔族居住在半身人的國度，不過自從魔法大爆炸之後他們就銷聲匿跡了。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Dwarves are naturally a inquisitive people, but do not enjoy such inquisition turned on them. Most live secretive lives in their closed-off city, the Iron Throne.", "矮人們好管閒事，但他們自己卻不喜歡別人來打攪，他們大多數居住在祕密的地下城市——鋼鐵王座之中。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Alchemists can bind gems to armour to grant them magical effects, to protect the wearer or improve their powers. Some commercial alchemists can imbue gems into jewellery.", "煉金術士可以把寶石中的魔法效果附到盔甲上，保護他們或者提高他們的能力。一些高級鍊金師還能把寶石製成首飾。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The Spellblaze was followed by the Age of Dusk, when disease was rife and civilisation collapsed. Necromancers and fell sorcerers took advantage of the chaos to spread their vile deeds.", "魔法大爆炸之後到來的是黃昏紀，那是一個疫病肆虐文明潰敗的時代。死靈法師和一些墮落法師利用當時的混亂來散播他們的惡行。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("After the Spellblaze came the Spellhunt, when the normal people rose against the arrogance of the mages and hunted them down like wolves. Some survived and went into hiding, but many innocents were killed.", "在魔法大爆炸之後便是獵魔行動，人們對造成這場災難的法師們趕盡殺絕就像獵殺牲口一樣。一些倖存的法師得以躲藏起來，但更多無辜的人被殺害。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Demons are thought to come from another world, brought to Eyal by magical forces. Some are highly intelligent and follow their own ambitions. To what end, none know.", "人們認爲惡魔是被魔法力量從其他世界帶到埃亞爾大陸的。有些惡魔具有高度的智慧並有他們自己的野心，沒人知道他們的真正目的。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The art of potion making fell into decline after the Spellhunt, and only a rare few now master the gift.", "獵魔行動之後鍊金技術嚴重衰退，現在只有極少數人掌握這種技能了。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("It's said that some rare powers can save your soul from the edge of death.", "傳說有些罕見的力量可以在死亡邊緣拯救你的靈魂。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Rumours tell of a shadowy cult kidnapping women and performing strange rites. Their intentions are unknown, and they have so far evaded capture.", "傳說有一個邪教組織，他們綁架婦女舉行奇怪的儀式，沒人知道他們真正的目的，至今他們還沒有被抓捕。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Though slavery is illegal there is still a black market for it, and in some areas men are even used for blood sports.", "儘管販奴被嚴令禁止但地下交易卻仍然存在。有些地方奴隸甚至被作爲一種血腥運動項目的道具。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Maj'Eyal is the biggest continent in the world of Eyal. Though records suggest other continents and islands may exist it has not been possible to cross the wide and stormy oceans since the Spellblaze and the Cataclysm.", "馬基埃亞爾是埃亞爾世界中最大的一塊大陸。雖然有記載世界上有可能還存在着其他大陸或者島嶼，但自從魔法大爆炸和大災變發生之後，穿越浩瀚的風暴之海已經不大可能了。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The effects of the Spellblaze were not all instant, and many centuries later the Cataclysm tore the continent apart once more, devastating coastal areas the destroying all of the Naloren lands.", "魔法大爆炸造成的影響並非僅侷限於那一瞬間，這場大災難過去了幾個世紀，大陸一次又一次被撕裂，沿海的納魯精靈王國受到了毀滅性的打擊而從此滅絕。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Archers are fast and deadly, and with pinning shots can render their foes helpless as they swiftly dispatch them.", "弓箭手行動迅捷而致命，他們可以使用定身射擊將敵人分散並各個擊破。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Reavers are powerful fighters with corrupted blood, and the strength to wield a one-handed weapon in each arm.", "收割者是流着墮落之血的強大戰士，他們雙手各可以裝備一件單手武器。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Corruptors feed off the essence of others, and can use their own corrupted blood to launch deadly magical attacks.", "墮落者可以吸取他人的精華，並使用他們的墮落力量發動致命的魔法攻擊。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Clever rogues can lay traps to damage or debilitate their foes without having to go near them.", "聰明的盜賊可以在不近身的情況下安置陷阱對敵人造成傷害或者削弱他們。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Rogues can move silently and stealthily, letting them approach foes unaware or avoid them entirely.", "盜賊可以悄無聲息的移動，在敵人毫無察覺的情況下悄悄近身。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("A movement infusion can let you quickly approach a ranged opponent, or quickly escape a melee one.", "移動紋身可以使你快速地接近一個遠程敵人或者逃離近戰敵人。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Invisibility lets you escape notice, giving you the freedom to move or recover your resources, but reduces your damage.", "隱身可以使敵人忽略你，讓你自由移動、恢復能量，不過這會降低你的傷害和治療能力。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Poison is the domain of assassins and master rogues, and its cunning use can cripple or kill enemies over a long fight.", "毒藥學是盜賊大師和刺客的技能，它可以在一場長時間的戰鬥中削弱或殺死敵人。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Summoners can call upon a variety of natural creatures to protect and support them, reducing the risk to their own flesh considerably.", "召喚師可以召喚不同的自然生物來支援和保護他們，這樣可以減少他們直面敵人的危險。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("The highest sorcerers are known as archmages, and the masters amongst them are said to have the power to change the world. They are feared immensely.", "元素法師被認爲是最高級別的法師，而其中的魔導師更是擁有改變世界的強大法力，他們也是世人最懼怕之人。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Bulwarks are defensive fighters that can take hits more readily than other warriors whilst preparing for the most effective counter attacks.", "盾戰士是防禦型的戰士，他們可以比其他戰士職業承受更多傷害，在防禦的同時他們也能隨時做出反擊。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Brawlers are trained in the use of their fists and mastery of their bodies. They can be as dangerous in combat as any swordsman.", "格鬥家通過學習對自身力量的掌握，並將其發揮至極限，他們的拳頭是他們唯一的武器，但其殺傷力不亞於任何一個持劍的戰士。", "init.lua load_tips")
t("Lightning is a chaotic element that is hard to control. It is said that those most attuned to it are eventually driven insane.", "雷電是一種混沌的元素力量，難以操控。據說掌握雷電法術的人也都因此而陷於瘋狂。", "init.lua load_tips")


